description: The Way to Love is a 1933 American Pre-Code romantic comedy film, starring Maurice Chevalier and Ann Dvorak.
Following a terrorist attack, Kovic, a racist cop of the french anti-terrorist squad must work with a young Arab recruit, and an idealistic cop. Everyone will change during the investigation.
A director falls into insanity because of the films he is making, and we follow his attempt at making his last film, an anthology of surreal films.
Vasanth, son of an MP, falls in love with Heena. But Heena seems to be the main suspect for a bomb attack on his father. Vasanth secretly helps her return to Kolkata and soon follows to meet her.

In the Middle Ages, a young servant fleeing from his master takes refuge at a convent full of emotionally unstable nuns. Introduced as a deaf mute man, he must fight to hold his cover as the nuns try to resist temptation.
Feature film based on the animated series, "Captain Planet", in which a superhero teams up with young environmentalists around the world to protect the planet.

Two passionate people with dreams swap places accidentally by fate and their common key to get back their lost life is to defeat the antagonist through the girl whom he wants dead since she can foresee the future.
A stolen VCR enables whoever watches it to predict the future--but it also shows satanic rites and devil worship.

In this movie we explore the abandoned World of a man's fear. Discover the secret that is buried deep inside his mind. Are you ready for a ride into Madness? Follow him on his dark journey to the Heart of Nightmares.
A young New Zealand Samoan man called Adam (Neil Amituanai) ventures to his motherland to try and impress his crush Mary (Gloria Ofa Blake), who claims she only likes "real" Pacific Island men.
A film star helps a young singer and actress find fame, even as age and alcoholism send his own career on a downward spiral.
Romantic thriller centered around the life of Ashley Montgomery who is suffering from dissociative identity disorder. (DID)

A man and a woman challenge their cosmic love by descending to the Earth. Through time and space they are drawn to one another, the only thing they have to overcome is their earthly hatred for one another.

Reggie is the quintessential black British geezer: a man that loves to 'cherps'. He'll take it fat, thin, black or white. But when ONE man had TOO many women, he had SEVEN days to make a choice. To cherps...or not to cherps?
When a young boy accidentally triggers the universe's most lethal hunters' return to Earth, only a ragtag crew of ex-soldiers and a disgruntled scientist can prevent the end of the human race.
A man is conflicted when he falls for a free-spirited woman that he knows that his mother will not like.
Three Presidential Democratic Candidates running against each other, accidentally hire the same American lounge singer for their campaign, and compete for her love. A farce ensues.

movie_name: Xiang Gang qi an 5: Jian mo
description: The Teenager's Nightmare: The police have their hands full with a slippery rapist preying on helpless teenage girls. Gun: Three teenagers' lives change forever when they find a package containing a gun, hand grenades and ammunition.
Brian and his long-estranged paintball team are back on the bus after five years and they're up for one final mission.
Two best friends must fight corruption in the Philippines to find a man called Ninong, who is responsible for the loss of their loved ones.
During a visit to see their wife and mother's grave. Jerry and his daughters Melanie and Barbra are going to experience a night they will never forget.
After Atlantis, Josh continues his quest for survival. But things get complicated when he finds out that his brother, Arthur, still lives.
After the death of a young woman's parents, Elaine goes to live with her eccentric Aunt Tilda whom she's never met before in a quiet mountain town, Bloomfield.

Heidi, a radio DJ, is sent a box containing a record - a "gift from the Lords". The sounds within the grooves trigger flashbacks of her town's violent past. Is Heidi going mad, or are the Lords back to take revenge on Salem, Massachusetts?
A major Motion Picture like no other, which will have an A list cast - The story of how 6 men founded and 12 men went up against President Nixon for the founding challenge - TO SAVE THE WHALES.
During their nightly poker game, a group of lowlifes are terrorized in their own convenience store by a masked killer.
An alienated teen discovers a mysterious book with directions to create a Soul Doll that makes her popular but soon leads to terror.
The story of three survivors of an infamous WW 2 massacre at the hands of the Waffen SS and their relentless pursuit to bring its commander to justice.

movie_name: The National Union of Space People
description: As Britain looks set to succeed in the first step towards world nuclear disarmament, outer space has other plans that could spell a catastrophic end to Britain, Europe and the world.
When a mission is sabotaged and a beloved spy assassinated, a team of agents must determine who among them is the rogue while continuing the mission.
An intrepid newspaper reporter attempts to solve a series of murders committed by a gorilla carrying the transplanted brain of a human.

In an alternate Japan, territorial street gangs form opposing factions collectively known as the Tokyo Tribes. Merra, leader of the Wu-Ronz tribe of Bukuro crosses the line to conquer all of Tokyo. The war begins.
Singer Lili Brown is attracted to dance hall manager Duke till she realizes he does that to all the girls. Nice guy Duke sets her up with composer Joe Brooks.

movie_name: Harley Davidson and the Marlboro Man
description: Forced by the imminent foreclosure of their friend's bar, two lifelong buddies will decide to rob a bank's armored car, not knowing that its cargo is not money but a new street drug.
In a raging nuclear war between the East and the West, a group of three people head on a journey into the forbidden zone.
A young man seeks to learn martial arts from an old master to avenge his father who was killed by a skilled martial artists who travels the land killing his opponents.

movie_name: Sakariba nagashi uta: Shinjuku no onna
description: A woman receives a large compensation when her father is imprisoned after suffering a personal injury while driving under the influence.
A spoiled heiress (Olive Borden) sets her sights on a handsome pilot but he wants nothing to do with her.
Inspired by the animated movie Bambi, it will transform the innocent deer we know into a killing machine.

Inside the Circle is a quirky romantic dramedy that tells the story of a girl who believes in relationships and marriage, and who falls for a comic book and superhero-loving man who does not share her same beliefs.

In January 2016, three friends venture out into a small wooded area in a Utah canyon in search of a chupacabra. What they found was much more disturbing than a creature. They were never heard from again.
An arrogant police officer eager to stop crime in the city which also associated with the death of his father and sister.
The lives of ten strangers intersect through a terrifying chain of events as a mutating fungus begins to spread through a small town wiping out everyone that comes into contact with it.
An isolated remote island community is threatened by an attack by tentacled silicates which liquefy and digest bone and tissue.

Higanjima is an eerie island occupied by vampires, from where none has ever come back alive. When teenager Akira hears that his missing brother has been seen in the island, he decides to investigate with several friends.
Young trumpeter is responsible for his two sisters. The younger sister needs major health treatments. Jerico encounters many obstacles when he turned to becoming a gigolo to support his family.

Filmed as a traditional Japanese play, a yakuza boss is released from prison, but finds his gang usurped by a shady politician. With the help of his former cell mate he decides to assassinate the politician with an explosive pen.
Lodge, a gaming geek, takes his playing very seriously, unlike his babyish friends who'd rather be immature. He decides to shake things up by introducing two unconventional people to their group.

Emerenziano, a middle-aged tax inspector, is in search of a wealthy wife. He travels to Italy where he meets three sisters, who, though wealthy, are not by any stretch of the imagination young or beautiful. He decides to marry one of them.
A group of backyard friends in a small town near Warsaw grows into a gang, and soon rules the whole town.
The wife of the North Kenya District Commissioner joins him in Africa and encounters trouble with the natives.
Cool Cat is the Coolest Cat in the World. But Butch the Bully hates him and always tries to bully him, and Cool Cat shows kids how to win and be cool.
A gang member back-stabs an entire team which pulls off successfully an ambitious heist done with all precautions. What is his motive and is it justified?

A wise-cracking TV reporter is on the trail of an unstoppable killing machine who's survived death by lethal injection, escaped from prison, commandeered a semi-truck, and is bent on revenge as he thunders the roads leading to Hollywood.

Gharer Lakshmi deals with the story of a poor girl married to a rich man's son. And the extent to which a rich man can go to and harm one's own child by keeping him away from his wife and child. Destiny plays a part in reuniting everyone.
The Amityville legend lives on when a resident of a local boarding house dies under mysterious circumstances.
May Britt plays a seemingly innocent farm girl convinced that her slovenly uncle (Cameron Mitchell) is the man responsible for the bloody scissor-murders of several local girls.

Flap is a Korean-American gangster who arrives in Korea and befriends a struggling actor named Seung-hwan. They experience a string of one-night stands until Seung-hwan meets Yeong-ju and attempts to make her give up her wild ways.
Detective investigates the murders of his former Marines that might be linked to a paranormal experience they encountered in Afghanistan.
In the reign of King Louis XV, a handsome student, Des Grieux, meets his charming cousin Manon just when she goes to the convent of Amiens to take the veil.
A mentally challenged man trying to keep his mother's only wish alive at any cost while trying to reconcile with his first and only real crush.
As Japan is preparing to host the Olympics, a gang member wanting to go to America is sought after by the police after helping his friend conduct a robbery.

Jeong-suk and Sang-hyeok's happiness comes to an end when they steal money from the mob. At first, they believe their lives can go on as always, but they soon find themselves hunted by gangsters and pursued by the police.
The angels look down upon King Solomon with his many wives and concubines and realizes one thing is lacking in his life Love.
A trickster-for-hire, known as the Tricky Expert, is hired to ruin the lives of a father and son by making them think that he's a part of the family.
Toward the end of WW2, three people with conflicting values realize that in order for them to survive they will have to learn to trust and accept each other.

A supernaturally-gifted woman must summon her inherent powers to combat a five-hundred year old curse come to life as her friends unwittingly resurrect a vengeful zombie from the ancient, Aztec civilization.

Wealthy Edward Morgan becomes charmed with a curly-haired orphan and her pretty older sister Mary and arranges to adopt both under the alias of "Mr. Jones." As he spends more time with them, he soon finds himself falling in love with Mary.
They influence our decisions without us knowing it. They numb our senses without us feeling it. They control our lives without us realizing it. They live.
A group of college friends on a spring break camping trip are stalked and slashed by an unknown creature with the ability to make them hallucinate through sound waves.
A man wrongly convicted of conspiracy to commit espionage against the U.S. is offered his freedom if he can rescue the President's daughter from an outer-space prison taken over by violent inmates.
A group of friends reunited to play a game. Each one of them expects to get something about it. The rules of the game are to tell a story of horror for each candle.
A mutiny erupts on a freight vessel resulting in the ship owner being killed and the captain put out to sea. 15 years later, the captain re-enters the sailors' lives, new seeking revenge
Surrendered to an omnipotent desire, a defenceless married housewife will come face-to-face with unexplored and unprecedented feelings, when a seductively alluring young playboy swears eternal love.
A reserved schoolteacher battles against family conflict when he falls in love with the 'wrong' young woman.
During the joseon dynasty in Korea, the princess travels to the Qing to have a beneficial marriage. On her journey to the Qing, she meets and falls in love with a magician.

Athidi(Mahesh Babu) is falsely convicted for killing his adopted parents and goes to jail for 13 years and when he comes back he loves Amrita (Amrita Rao) unaware that she is the daughter of his adopted parents.
A quantum physics professor is forced to take action after being drugged by the shaman of jewish cult who wants him to come back home and become the man he once was.

A chorus girl falls for a young man pretending to be his boss, a millionaire. WHen his boss returns from a European trip and finds that the woman he loves is engaged to his secretary, complications ensue.
For the sake of justice, a young ranger uses his martial arts skills to against his father and brothers, and grows into the role of a true hero.
A maid is kidnapped and scratches a message onto D.C. the cat's collar and when his owner Patti discovers this, she plays amateur detective with the help of D.C. to try to find the culprits.
After an outbreak of a deadly infection which turns the population into flesh eating zombies a small group of survivors band together to escape from the diseased.

Angels fall from the heavens. They then turn into Vampires. Only one man can save the world as we know it. 'The Becoming: 2015' is an explosively campy contemporary vision of ancient 'End of Days' mythology... ... ... with Vampires.
A wagon train is robbed by a gang of bandits who kill everyone but a pair of young brothers. Years later, the brothers join force to bring the bandits' leader to justice.
A band of unconventional Jewish school girls becomes a troupe of unlikely heroes in this action adventure film.
Jmac, college kid gets tangled up in the entertainment world. He begins to have a lot of trials and tribulations while trying to get to the top of his career.
According to the demands of the villagers of Vellimala, the government is forced to build a dam there. But as it becomes unsafe, the government decides to destroy it, sparking a violent protest.
A married Frenchwoman living in Brazil returns to her native country to visit her ailing elderly mother. There, she ends up rekindling a love affair with a man whom she hadn't seen in twelve years.
During a crisis of faith Mary is involved in a terrible accident that leaves her fighting for her life.
An impromptu fashion shoot at a book store brings about a new fashion model discovery in the shop clerk.
When a nobleman is threatened by a family curse on his newly inherited estate, Sherlock Holmes is hired to investigate.
A man tries to cure his friend of his video-game obsession by using a virtual reality machine. When the device traps his friend in a virtual world, he goes in to help him fight for his life.
A man wakes up with no memory of himself or surroundings. He is guided by a mysterious creature as he uncovers what has happened to the world.

The father of Veera Simha Reddy is a revered man in a village and his son Bala Simha Reddy settles in the USA.When his father gets killed in the village politics, Bala Simha returns to India and takes revenge on who killed his father.

A gang of evil ninjas has stolen the sacred sword of the Lady Mayu and are demanding that her family exchange her for the family treasure. The world's greatest swordsman, Shuranosuke Sakaki, is called in to get the sword back.
Tomek is a college student studying physics. He falls in love with Julia, but misses his chance with her. He then gets mysteriously transported back in time to the day he first met her.
Two Indigenous characters have an encounter that sets off a cosmic and environmental connection link to the past and future.
Subhash Patel (Jagapathi Babu), a retired army officer, takes on a group of drug traffickers. ACP Catherine, a corrupt lady officer, vows to find out the reason behind his mission.

movie_name: At Night All Wolves Are Grey
description: Private detective Varg Veum investigates a case where his good friend Evans, a highly decorated ex-army officer, is falsely accused of bombing armakon, a weapons storage facility, and to prove him innocent.
Raja after knowing that his sister is killed by her husband and father in law, decides to take revenge on them.
In retaliation, a retired Assassin's children are taken by a child Trafficking organization. He puts together his former team of professional killers to get his kids back.

In their blue hotel room, a clandestine couple of two married lovers plan an impossible future, as death shutters their already frail tranquillity. Now, the noose tightens more and more around innocents and sinners; but, was there a crime?
A Willow Springs racing legend battles a 56 Chevy known as Rosemary's Baby for glory and immortality.
A farmer makes a living disposing of bodies. One day, 3 bodies are delivered - except the young woman is still alive. If set free, the gang'll come after him and his daughter.
A distinguished professor finds his well-ordered life topsy-turvy after he is forced to take in a pregnant widow.
In a struggle to get himself and his family out of debt and poverty, Baraka quits school and decides to enter a professional boxing competition to get the money he desperately need. Will he succeed?
Boy loses the girl of his dreams. Struggles with ED through relationships with four beautiful women in search true love only to fall in love and propose to one who is marrying the girl of his dreams.

movie_name: Scott Rivers Makes an Offensive Porn Film About Serial Killers
description: Scott Rivers And His Friend Chloe Newton Have Recently Came Into Bad Luck With Chloe Going On Holiday To Poland He Decided To Make A Film About The Last Few Months And Finds A Stripper To Play The Role Of His Friend.
Racial tensions arise from a love affair between a Finnish nurse and and a Somali doctor in the late sixties, when African immigrants were very rare in Finland.
In England during World War II, a repressed dressmaker and her sister struggle looking after their seventeen-year-old niece, who is having a delusional affair with an American soldier.
Environmental researcher Louis Roth and his family are lost at a mountain in China. His son is lost too, and he finds a bunch of kids which also are lost in the forest.
A television crew of a reality show for ghost hunters visits a haunted motel in search of paranormal activity. Will they be able to make it through the night?

Sofía, a dentist, and Tristán, owner of a shoe store, live in the same building but have never met or even seen each other. Disenchanted with love, both have sworn never to fall in love again, until they finally meet.
The rise and fall of a soccer club owner, discovering the harsh reality of the sport, often connected with crime and fraud.
Identical twin mathematicians investigate a mystery hidden within the works of the Surrealist painters, the music of Bach and the physics of Einstein.

An over-the-top action-packed Filipino jungle action flick about a super tough CIA agent. Bloody violence, a jungle full of bamboo death traps and some double crossing keeps things more than interesting.
A story full of ghosts and scares about the theme of cursed figures and the principles surrounding the law of cause and effect.
A landlord narrates the love story of his son and a young girl whose mother's prayer helped him to have a child.
When Jessica and Rob start dating, Jessica knew her ex-boyfriend would cause some problems. What she didn't know is how far he was willing to go.
Joon Soo, who decided to move to Seoul to fulfill his dream of being a musician, accidentally meets Hee Jeong, who just broke up, while he was singing a breakup song to a monkey in a zoo.
Empty Girl follows the story of Mallory, a woman from a remote hunting town, who returns home after many years to unravel the bloody sordid past of why she left in the first place.
A young gymnast, who tries desperately to please her demanding mother, discovers a strange egg. She hides it and keeps it warm, but when it hatches, what emerges shocks them all.

In 1915, Tom and Viv elope, but her gynecological and emotional problems disrupt their honeymoon. Her father is angry because Tom's poetry doesn't bring in enough to live, but her mother is happy Viv has found a tender and discreet husband.

movie_name: Tales from the Crypt: Demon Knight
description: High-level demons collect low-level demons as warriors in attempt to obtain a key containing the blood of Christ. The key is guarded by immortal warriors called Demon Knights.
Billy and Liz are international war correspondents covering the dark and dirty side of television news reporting, often at high-risk missions.
Queen Christina of Sweden is a popular monarch who is loyal to her country. However, when she falls in love with a Spanish envoy, she must choose between the throne and the man she loves.
A cab driver with a gambling debt accepts a job to transport a valuable briefcase, and gets in over his head when the case is stolen.
A former FBI agent turned small-town sheriff agrees to help the FBI chief infiltrate the Chicago mafia when the FBI chief's son is killed by them.
Work causes a single mother to move to China with her young son; in his new home, the boy embraces kung fu, taught to him by a master.
A ancient mythical creature terrorizes a small town and abducts a young girl who returns years later with no memory of her abduction only for the creature to reappear and terrorize the town again.

Four friends and their professor are headed to a Native reservation when a run-in with a satanic cult alters their trajectory. Witchcraft, black magic and some sick billionaires put them onto a path of unspeakable terrors.

Baashir travels home to bury his sister but upon his return he is tasked with grave responsibility. However to take on this task he must first eliminate those who are responsible for his sister's demise.

movie_name: Mang quan guai zhao shen jing dao
description: A ruthless gang of renegade martial artists are raiding small towns across Canton, raping and pillaging as they go. After his mother is killed by the gang, the Man in White teams up with three kung fu experts to get revenge.
A gang of robbers armed with a union army cannon rob the bank holding bounty Killer Acquasanta Joe's earnings to date. He pursues, crossing and double crossing along the way.
The journey of a female scientist who, at the end of times, discovers that true faith can bring miracles.

Thailand's answer to Bruce Lee, Panna Rittikrai portrays a mad hard case thug on the run. Thailand's finest action packed film with stunts galore. A terrorist leader orders his crew to take hostages and hurt people pretty badly.
In a world where everyone is unknowingly immortal, a pistol-packing priest fights to change what happens between lives.

A famed Hollywood director is nearing death and reevaluating his life. What troubles him most is the son he abandoned. As he is shown a film of his son's painful life, he is offered the opportunity of a lifetime: to set things right.
After returning home from the jungles of South America, anthropologist Nathan Haswell introduces a gruesome set of cannibalistic rituals to an unprepared world.
A girl trapped inside her house since birth holds a dark and hideous secret and if let out, could reek havoc to whom ever crosses her path.
Five best friends try to find out what true friendship is by climbing Mount Semeru, the highest peak in Java.
During the 1970s, car delivery driver Kowalski delivers hot rods in record time but always runs into trouble with the highway cops.
Three best friends endure heartbreak, humiliation and hangovers to get dates for the wedding of a lifetime.
A disgraced cop must work with a conspiracy nut to prove the existence of a killer, alcoholic merman before an upcoming bikini contest on the lake becomes a bloodbath.
A new clue to the whereabouts of a lost treasure rekindles a married couple's sense of adventure -- and their estranged romance.

When a lonely man finds out the love of his life has a conjoined twin, who happens to be a serial killer, he must take drastic measures to keep his love life intact while keeping himself out of big trouble.
When a master monster make-up artist is sacked by the new bosses of American International studios, he uses his creations to exact revenge.
Jenny was made for love and Lana for gambling. In this old-fashioned country, Lebanon, women have no say. Defying everyone and everything they will fight for their freedom whatever the cost.

Daisuke Senzaki has been selected to go through training to become a rescue diver within the Japan Coast Guard Special Rescue Team. At the side of the grueling training he finds love in the local girl Kanna.
The stunning landscape of Western Australia is the backdrop for an impassioned tale of love and grief in Gregor Jordan's adaptation of the acclaimed novel by Tim Winton.
Alexander Wolfe is a retired hit man who is lured back into the cruelty of his old ways . Unknowingly he is obligated to assassinate his only chance for survival.

When an underachieving loser blows the remainder of his inheritance, he lures his kindhearted, mentally challenged best friend into helping him film snuff movies, but it all goes to hell when the dead become undead.
An experimental feature film about people in different cities who are trying to escape their loneliness through love, lust or a combination of both.
After a rash of crimes in which people are kidnapped, murdered and their cars stolen, a police detective assigned to the case zeroes in on a creepy young guy named Mike.

Poor Lisa and rich Mitsi are like two peas in a pod; however, a rash act of defiance will lead to a tight collaboration between Lisa and Mitsi's father, who pays a hefty reward to bring peace into his home. Can Lisa become the other woman?
Two cops go undercover to infiltrate a violent drug ring, and are in for a shock when they find out who's running it.
The last surviving Secret Service Agent has two hours to get the President of the United States to a peace summit that will save the world from final annihilation.
While sorting the affairs of his late Uncle, a man accidentally stumbles across a series of dark secrets connected to an ancient horror waiting to be freed.

Members of an elite security team deployed to rescue a VIP on an exclusive island.The rescue mission becomes a desperate attempt to survive, escape the island and elude the sinister presence that seeks to harm them.
A group of employees are working their last week at a movie theater that is going out of business when a mysterious figure begins to murder people.
Three pro surfers - gifted Shane, once-great Mickey and rising young star Keoni travel to Madagascar, Bali and Hawaii in search for the ultimate wave.
A film memoir based on NZ filmmaker Gaylene Preston's interviews with her father about his World War II experiences.

Debar is a story of a family of three brothers where the eldest brother loses his life while Making arrangements for the youngest brother's education. And how the youngest brother pay back to the widow of his brother.
In 16th-century Zazzau, now Zaria, Nigeria, Amina must utilize her military skills and tactics to defend her family's kingdom.
A private investigator, mentally disturbed by his father's suicide, goes undercover in a mental institution to discover the murderer of a friend who was a doctor at the clinic.
When his close friend Dr Henry Jekyll is accused of a horrific murder, lawyer Gabriel Utterson launches his own investigation, only to discover a secret more shocking than he could have imagined.
Marion Kelly is on a mission to find the missing children of Darkwood House. Have they been taken by the entity they call the Nursery Man?
A company team building trip spirals out of control after a night of dabbling with a Ouija board. As the death toll rises they uncover that all is not what it seems.
Beans decides that the only way to grasp the American Dream is to take it. State Property follows Beans and his crew, as they take over the city creating mayhem as their empire builds.
The female ninjas need to protect their particular master's unborn infant from enemies. They use all types of intimate tricks to obtain the work done.
Set in Perth Australia in 1988 the Langford boys can't be beaten. Will Jim, known as Einstein to his mates, make it through his school days with the Riff Raff that's surrounds him.
An Ancient Evil Unleashed. A supernatural thriller based on the terrifying legend of The Mothman. Rachel and Katy work together in a large, empty museum.
After firing 121 employees, CEO Joy Mittal is tormented and terrorized by ghostly apparitions during a late night at the office.
Abducted without explanation, two men are forced into a daily steel cage brawl testing their will to live.

Once in a Summer (Hangul) is a 2006 South Korean melodrama/romance film directed by Jo Keun-shik. The film stars Lee Byung-hun and Soo Ae. It won Best Film and Best Director (for Jo) at the 15th Chunsa Film Art Awards in 2007.
A TV news cameraman, hailed as a hero for pulling a woman from a burning car, finds that his ratings-hungry boss is deliberately placing him in dangerous situations in a quest for even more ratings.
Guards of a casino beat Hou Hsian-Shan because he was caught cheating. Fortunately, kung fu expert Ma Ta rescues him.
Two brothers return to a small mountain town in search of their long lost parents only to discover that the place has a monstrous taste for tourists.
When two LA burlesque dancers accidentally get involved in a mob hit, they hit the road and end up in a small town in Texas only to turn the town upside down and the mob after them.
A film adaptation of Steve Martin's novel about a complex love triangle between a bored salesgirl, a wealthy businessman and an aimless young man.
With socialite Tracy Lord about to remarry, her ex-husband - with the help of a sympathetic reporter - has 48 hours to convince her that she really still loves him.

Claudia Piovani, and artist and photographer, has a strange and unexplainable spiritual encounter. From then on she has strange dreams and visions. Is she going crazy or is she being contacted by a spirit from another world?

In the wake of the Cairo Fire, Essam feels guilty for betraying his friend Samir by messing around with his wife Madiha. Essam decides to take revenge on Madiha's father who pressured him to marry her to avoid a scandal.

movie_name: The Poor Hoodman 2: The Robot's Origin
description: The story about a little robot named Michael, who is going through really tough and struggling times because of the apocalypse of humans destroying every robots. So, it is their duty to stop them but it can be really difficult..

Hailed as India's first stereoscopic animated film, 'Krishna Aur Kans' is an exciting narrative full of action and drama. The movie chronicles Krishna's early years -- from his birth as the nemesis of his tyrannical uncle Kans.
After his ex-wife and daughter are kidnapped by a Mexican drug kingpin, a rogue DEA agent heads south of the border to rescue them and to settle a score.
Just when Paolo, an Italian in Paris, is ready to propose to his girlfriend Greta, he sees beautiful young Cecile on her bicycle.

Five brilliant, black African students decide to systematically target and assassinate key members of their country's government in order to force the President to make immediate and effective changes for the benefit of the people.

movie_name: The Pagan King: The Battle of Death
description: On his deathbed, the reigning king bestows power to an unexpected heir who must find strength within himself to unite his people against the violent crusades which threaten their freedom.
Feature length film derived from editing together episodes of the television series "White Hunter"(1958).
Three stories happening in one city. Three different life dilemmas. One Friday evening and one unexpected end.
Two white collar thieves compete fiercely against the other trying to steal millions from an old baker, that he won in the lotto.

More than a million people died in USA in a week. Later it turned out that a similar situation is observed in many countries of the world. A secret CIA unit was brought in to investigate the incident.
Two lovers romance is impeded by voodoo in the Caribbean. They are drawn into destructive rites, rituals and practice of Obeah. The young woman is the evil spirits focus.
A mysterious stranger arrives in a village situated in the Thar desert and crosses paths with a veteran cop investigating a case of brutal killings.

movie_name: And They May Still Be Alive Today
description: Tired of waiting for love to happen to her Clara (33) decides to make it happen. Passive and kind, Vlad (31) is the perfect partner. Her project? To live the perfect love. Her inspiration? Books, films and folklore.
University students, planning a bravery initiation test for their fellow classmates, choose a campus bridge rumored to be haunted by a vengeful female ghost.
A factual historical epic about the loves and lives of General Custer and Crazy Horse leading up to the fateful battle at the Little Bighorn.
The Love is Forever is a 2015 Indian romantic movie directed by Honey Vee starring Manoj Verma, Rana Jung Bahadur, Manoj Pandit, Manpreet Singh and Sonia Bindra, Viraat Attri as lead characters.
20 years after the Revolution of 1911, Huo Zhenshan opens a school to promote Chinese martial arts. But a new challenge in the black market emerges.
Musical retromovie from the 60's in Czech republic. Story about star-crossed lovers - student Tereza and a boy who deserted from the army.
A transgender woman who survives prostituting herself in Paris, returns - with her two male lovers in tow - to her family home in the countryside to look after her dying mother.
A simplistic bloke with innocent eyes who sees movie stars getting money and girls and says, "Why not me?"

Hiroshi Ando aka "Zoo"Synopsis.....This collection of shocking, unpredictable stories feature the first screen adaptation of the number one young author of his generation, Otsuichi. Working...                See full synopsis »
A woman keeps her son away from the ancestral rivalry of two families in the village. However, after an unforeseen incident, he takes it upon himself to punish his enemies.
Bewakoofiyaan is a slice-of life comedy when recession strikes and the lack of money tests love. Is living on love and fresh air really possible?

A lonely divorced addict gets trapped inside a self-storage warehouse with his son where he is forced to face his demons. They battle thirst, hunger, and withdrawal. But is there is something darker than just dope-sick hallucinations.
An ordinary man turns himself in to ICE for punching an aggressive agent, but as the night progresses, the situation is not what it seems.

The wife of a nefarious TV Evangelist hires a savage bounty hunter known as the Headhunter to kidnap her husband and inflict terrible pain before killing him off. But things are not all what they seem in the world of 'saving lives'
After recovering from her injuries on the battlefield, Ahmad wants to return to the front, but due to the special circumstances of her family, she stays in Tehran and works in a cannery.
A story of youthful misadventure set against the backdrop of a lawless border terrain during the last gasps of the Irish boom.
A man wakes in a hospital bed with no recollection of who he is, and learns that he's wanted by the police for committing a series of murders.
16 year old Valetika Romanoff wakes to find a bullet wound in her leg. She is told that she is not who or where she believes she is.
Middle-aged lust :a man ,in his thirteenth and therefore omen-filled marriage year ,cheats on his wife.

Fingers is planning a half-million-dollar bank robbery in gang boss Cobra Collins' territory. Fingers' moll Connie tries to bluff Cobra into thinking the hit won't be for another week when the call comes through saying it's now.
The shorted re-edited American version of Submersion of Japan, in which Japan slowly sinks into the sea as the US and Japan work together to stop it.

movie_name: Thunder Ninja Kids in the Golden Adventure
description: Three young martial artists travel to the big city to retrieve a sacred statue that was stolen by ninjas for a criminal gang.
Rivalries are renewed and love is rekindled when a group of old friends return to the U.P. for their high school reunion.
Natalia and her friends go out partying one night and end up subduing a man to their sexual, carnal and most violent will.
A group of female friends on a hen weekend in the countryside find themselves hunted by a beastly - and very hungry - troll.
When a bartender is beaten up and nearly killed by a gang of bad guys , a mysterious woman arrives to town to give her justice.
A group of explorers surveying an abandoned goldmine are trapped in a cave in, and find themselves at the mercy of a slimy, mysterious creature.

Only known as "Assassin", the man with no name, is a hired killer for the U.S. Government who is paid to terminate ruthless individuals deemed too dangerous to society, until he becomes a marked man himself by his own comrades.
Frank and Melissa run a hand to mouth meat processing business until Laura arrives on the scene and everything changes
A lesbian with commitment issues befriends a widowed mother who is visiting her workaholic daughter.
A dark spirit's vengeance shatters the life of a couple in their new home. The couple must now decide to leave or stay behind to their possible death.
Batman, along with a number of his allies and adversaries, finds himself transplanted from modern Gotham City to feudal Japan.

movie_name: Gintama 2: Rules are Made to be Broken
description: The Yorozuya gang returns to protect the country's shogun when the Shinsengumi police force finds itself in a crisis.
Leonardo de los Reyes gets framed by some hoodlums for murder, he escapes from prison and gets revenge to the people who harmed him.
A man wants to get married to the woman of his dreams but her grand expectations of a proposal slow down his plans, he enlists her friend to help but things take a different turn.
Bhumika and Vedhika are trying hard to remind Balayya of his past. In the process, they take him to the villain's residence and asks to fight with him. Now, time for yet another fight

movie_name: Las luchadoras vs el robot asesino
description: A lady wrestler and her police-officer boyfriend battle a mad scientist who has developed a murderous killer robot and uses it to kidnap wealthy people.

Before heading off to college, a group of high school seniors throw themselves the best Spring Break party ever. But when party goers begin to die, the teenagers must figure out how to survive the evil demon they summoned.
Shante Smith is a relationship expert who uses her knowledge of the male psyche to help women get what they want.

Omar is a mid-level gangster in Oslo, living alone with his fast food restaurant owning father. A family secret is revealed when his "dead" sister isn't dead at all. Omar is set out to find his sister at all costs.
Actors who are out of work eventually get their break in a show that has been under preparation for a while.
Traveling from France to Tangiers, a man looks to reunite with his former love, though their romance ended some 30 years earlier.
A man creates a hit list with a stranger during a drunken night out and must then race to try to save those he marked for death as the bodies pile up and all fingers point to him.

movie_name: Tabu: A Story of the South Seas
description: On the South Pacific island of Bora Bora, a young couple's love is threatened when the tribal chief declares the girl a sacred virgin.

Lucas and Clementine live peacefully in their isolated country house, but one night they wake up to strange noise... they're not alone... and a group of hooded assailants begin to terrorize them throughout the night.
Joe is an Alien on Earth. At least that is what his father told him before he died when Joe was eleven. He finds it difficult to adjust, and to find a compatible girl friend.
Condemned to life without end, and to an undying passion for a lost love he can never find, a vampire stalks a beautiful young woman.
Xiao Fung, a notable swordsman, has killed the son of a local warlord, Lee San, and the 3,000,000 tael that Lee's son was transporting, now seems to have gone missing.

In a small western town, a man meets a girl whose father is a land agent. To please her, he buys a plot of land from her father. Next thing he knows, he's mixed up in a plot to drive him off his land.
Tautly directed biker film, told from the woman's point of view. The heroine sets out on the road to avenge her brother's murder, toting a shotgun and meaning business.

Vijay is recruited by a police officer to masquerade as his lookalike Don, the leader of an international gang of smugglers. Things go wrong when the officer is killed and Vijay is left to fend for himself.
An upstanding pastor uncovers a dark and twisted underworld as he searches for answers surrounding his daughter's brutal murder.
A private detective searching for a killer comes across a satanic cult from another dimension, monsters called up from hell and murderous ninja assassins.

The prequel to the popular character, Laughing Gor (Michael Tse) in the highly rated TVB drama series Emergency Unit. This movie tells the story of Laughing and before he join the police ...                See full synopsis »
Out to prove that Hester is not a murderer, detectives Phyllis and Duke Maratindel try to stay one step ahead of the police as they track down the real killer.
A failed pianist sells his soul to the devil in return for his becoming the greatest musician in the world. The catch: every time he plays he turns into a horrible monster.

Police Sergeant Dutch Van Den Broek (Harrison Ford) and U.S. Representative Kay Chandler (Dame Kristin Scott Thomas) lose their spouses in a plane crash, and they soon discover that their spouses were having an affair with each other.
When two people head down a river to retrieve their boss' hydrochloric acid barrel, they run into too many obstacles to return with it and have to face the consequences.
Just before World War II, the Chinese and American governments mount a joint operation to prevent the Germans and Japanese from taking over the strategic island of Mandon.
While struggling to cope with the death of her boyfriend, a young woman begins to form romantic feelings for her new supportive female friend.
Three young women gathered in a coffee bar in Bangkok tell and discuss three original ghost stories with each other.
Gigi is engaged to Mara but is in love with Anna, who, however, is about to marry a certain Gustavo.
In order to give her son a good future, Ganga sets out on a journey to Kolkata to find her husband who left her.
When a ruthless drug lord murders the family of a little girl in Spain, he makes a fatal mistake: letting her live, setting in motion a bloody chain of events in this tale of revenge and its cost.
An expedition exploring the Amazon jungle comes across a jungle goddess who lives among the animals and fears none of them--and apparently has found the secret of eternal youth.

Alok rejects a potential bride Ashwini as he feels she is too traditional for his liking. But when he is travelling to Goa by train, Ashwini happens to be his co-passenger. During the journey, Alok starts developing feelings for her.
Relationships and loyalties of a criminal family planning its next big heist are tested when some shocking revelations strike them.

Jorge works at Tevelunga magazine, and its director commissions him to do a story on transvestites. He hires a photographer so the two of them infiltrate the scene without arousing suspicion and be able to make the top note of the summer.
The tale of a hard-fisted, kris-wielding muslin fighting hell-bent in an uphill battle for survival JUN ARISTORENAS in a walloping role that surpassed his previous performances.
A young man falls for the commissioner's sister, Anjali, who betrays him. After finishing his time behind bars, he sets on a mission to save another girl named Anjali who is chased by a gangster.
Spring break for seven college students is derailed with one wrong turn. A flat tire on a deserted road leaves them stranded after dark with a meancing drifter who may or may not be trying to help.
Tamia has it all nice house, nice car and a loving relationship, until one day she catches her boyfriend cheating.. That's when she comes up with the 90 Day Rule..
A live stage production of the musical, filmed at the Playhouse Theatre in London, commemorating the 40th anniversary of the release of The Rocky Horror Picture Show (1975).
Bumbling simpleton Yeong-koo is back, this time he gains superhuman powers and takes on the role of the super-hero Golden Bat.

A famous conductor divides his obsession for music with the sickly love for his muse. A strange love triangle is formed among conductor, wife, and muse; the wife ends up accepting the situation rather than lose her husband.
A team of four paranormal investigators explore a house with a dark history only to find they share a hidden past connected to the location.

Gaby is a neurotic single mother who is living a content yet incomplete life. Sean is a hectic single dad known to lose himself to his work. It's difficult enough for them to get together, but the real test is how they stay together.
A group of filmmakers set off to a remote part of Western Australia to shoot their low budget period drama. But something doesn't want them to finish. and is out to kill them all. One by one.
Mario decides to tell his family the truth about himself. But when he is finally ready to come out in front of the entire family, his older brother Vicente ruins his plans.
Two strangers must discover a way to escape a sinister family who wishes to sacrifice their souls to an evil presence.

A group of young AN recruits located at a South Korean outpost go offroading in the Korean country side during their lunch break. Little do they know that they have crossed into the North Korean border...

movie_name: Dwellers: The Curse of Pastor Stokes
description: Where do exorcized spirits go after being banished from the bodies they inhabit? Some say they follow the priests back to their church and make their new home there.

A road movie on a bicycle. Jasper leaves an alley cat race and goes on a physical and spiritual journey on her bike, through Chicago's nighttime streets, to a destination that holds an emotional secret.
Perky dance student, Mi-hye--nicknamed "Jjang-gu"--falls in love with a journalism major named Jin-ho. However, she becomes the target of a trio of jealous, would-be kidnappers

A recently widowed young farmer is mistaken for the notorious leader of a ruthless gang of bandits. Now, a feared convict, the police, and a band of thieves are after him. Can he stay alive, and save his loved ones?
While returning from a vacation, siblings Paul & Marilyn fall prey to a pair of homicidal mechanics and their bloodthirsty pet monster.
An alien creature impregnates a woman who gives birth to a man who was abducted by aliens three years ago. The man reconnects with his wife and son for a sinister purpose.

The husband is a hard worker, and a tough man in more ways than one, but he is unable to pleasure his wife when making love to her. Therefore, she is unhappy, until she decides to take pleasure from men outside of her wedlock...
A man who spends his days in boredom meets a woman, who throws his life into chaos. Koji Fukada's first film adaptation of a comic book.

Mishrarag - A Symphony is a 2009 Indian Bengali film, directed by Amar Bose and produced by Mani C. Kappan. The film stars Keka Sarkar, Druba Kundu and Sharmila Sen in lead roles. Music of the film was composed by Aloke Nath Dey.

A young couple is tormented by an evil entity evoked in a childhood ritual. For years they are afflicting by a series of horrifying tragedies, leaving them broken, and seemingly unable to defend against its attachment.
An outlaw gang hanged by a posse in the late 1880s comes back from the grave to terrorize the descendants of the posse's leader.
Longing for love but inept at close relationships; a problem brothers Óskar and Maggi have in common but deal with in different ways.
A Mulher Do Meu Marido is a romantic comedy about two couples - Pedro and Joana, Brazilians; Martin and Pilar, Argentines - involved in an involuntary couple's exchange.
Space pirates, led by diabolical Colonel Fraser, take over a cargo ship carrying anti-matter explosive and an important official. Space marines, led by Captain Gray, must stop their evil plans.
The trials and tribulations of a small town in middle America trying to grapple with the disappearance of a teenage girl.
A wicked baron oppresses Gypsies but is fascinated by the beautiful Carla, who loves a stranger on a white horse.
In downtown Japan, a lonely computer nerd tries to maintain a peaceful existance while being stalked by a gang of deviant homosexuals who want to use him for their brutal S&M activities.
Honest police officer, Dev, tries to fight the corrupt system prevalent in Daulatpura because of a powerful criminal. He vows to end the tyrant's hooliganisms and bring peace to the town.
2011, preparations for EURO 2012 in Poland are entering their final phase. However, tempted by 5 million EUR, the President of of Poland decides to sell the rights to EURO to the Czechs

A young gentry from an impoverished Orthodox family is forced to flee from the Minsk Jesuit Collegium, having avenged the death of his friend to a Latin teacher. On the way, Prantish accidentally becomes the owner of an unusual "property".
The film is made up of three omnibus horror tales laced with Singaporean humour. In sequence, they are "Roadside Got Ghost", "Forest Got Ghost" and "House Got Ghost".

Seenu has enrolled at the same college attended by Nandini, the only daughter of a don. Seenu is angry when her father's men beat him just because they think the two are falling in love, but it also becomes a challenge to win Nandini.

Greta, a mysterious woman with amnesia, is taken in by the wealthy Mr. and Mrs. von Ravensbruck. The three soon enter into a love triangle that turns deadly, as Greta's gruesome past is slowly revealed.

In Colonel Putin's Moscow, 1984, an American businessman finds danger, corruption and romance. Was this mission purposefully designed to fail? Abandoned, who can he trust, the KGB, the CIA? Will he ever get home?
Nau Van returns home several years after staying in America on the anniversary of his father's death to meet his family. Unbeknownst to them, he returns with his long-term boyfriend, Ian.
When a young wife discovers her husband of two years is involved with his beautiful secretary, she applies for a job as secretary to a business rival.
A tram engine discovers the secrets of his hidden abilities as a "hybrid engine" and confronts an old foe from the past, while trying to fit in with the engines of his new railway.
Manuel da Cruz, a young apprentice in the saddle, is discovered by the cattleman João Gama, who marvels at his skill, deciding to make him a great bullfighter.
Boy meets girl, they fall in love, crisis arises and happy ending ensues complicated by deafness, insensitivity to individual challenges and saved by personal sacrifice.
After twelve-year-old Jessica-Ann's teacher breaks her neck, Jessica-Ann starts suspecting her cold and overprotective mother as the killer.

After Melissa and her family seek shelter from a storm, they become trapped. With no sign of rescue, Melissa comes to realize that she and her girlfriend Amy might have something to do with the horrors that threaten her family.
Alex is possessed by a powerful demon, now that he became a vessel he is going to infect people with a demonic virus that transforms people in self mutilating paranoid freaks.
Raman, a journalist, goes to Japan to expose a smuggling racket run by Narendran accompanied by the spirit of his brother Kalyanaraman.
The story of two young men, "It" and "Tan". Their destinies were set to be born on the same day and almost at the same time. Both were raised and grew up in a totally different ways.
A gang of tough women bikers are the only thing that stands between a crowd of zombies, which have been accidentally let out of their secure cave, and those still alive in the town.
Cabaret performer Ivy Stevens in an affair with a low-rent traveling salesman is dumped in a 'Dear Jane' letter and finds solace in joining the Salvation Army.
An insight into the experiences of soldiers on the front line and the lives of those they leave behind.
After surviving an invasion on her peaceful homeworld, a beautiful avenger must stop a powerful psychopath from gaining immortality and rescue her kidnapped sister.
A poor family man brought up in the fishermen community and tries to bring the change in their lifestyle. Later realizes that he is a rich man's child.
Delphine and Yvan's love story told by Thierry Roland and Jean-Michel Larqué like a soccer game broadcast.

Helinä is tired of her monotonous life revolving around her young children, while her husband is away on business. At the hair salon she meets other frustrated housewives. Together the find an attractive solution to the problem.
A cross-cultural romance blossoms in Hong Kong when an American ex-Marine (Sean Faris) and a ballerina from Beijing (Grace Huang) fall in love.
Two friends murder random strangers just for the month of October, but things turn bad when one of them decides to stop doing these horrific acts.
Two young men meet at a psychiatric hospital, where they become friends willing to fight against injustice.
Brian Yuzna's debut amateur movie is, in his own words, about an artist who blows his brains out against a canvas for art and becomes a protagonist as a hologram.
Hazuki clips her nails every time it rains. She caressed herself with these fingers back then. Hazuki, an editor of a publishing company now, is attracted by Shiori, the head of planning.
When a contract killer and a thief discover they share the same lover they vow to eliminate the other.
After winning 7 Million Dollars on the lotto, friends and lovers of Clark attempt to kill him for the money.
Famed Argentine folk singer Soledad abandons her planned artistic tour throughout Spain to accompany her schoolmates on a trip to the city of Bariloche.

Two lonely strangers seek refuge in a one night stand and are shocked to uncover a remarkable connection. They realize they must risk exposing their secrets and painful pasts with each other, for one last chance at love.

Dika and his family want to move out of his house for a reason, and Dika doesn't feel good about it. But as time goes, his feeling is getting better about his new house while he met his high school crush after a long time.

Yu is a two-armed swordsman who is betrayed by a jealous rival, but initially seeks a life of simple pleasures until an accidental meeting with another patriot sets him back on the road to bloody, brutal vengeance.

The story of two sisters who have nice and calm life and their daughter are about to get marry. But when they held a family party a young stranger guy comes to their party which challenges their life.
A developer relocates to a remote island with his family, where the cursed land takes over his soul and makes him a killer.
Work-life balance breaks down for Paris's most gifted armed robbers when a grave mistake forces them to work for a crime boss in a high-stakes heist.
An intelligence officer attempts to save the city from a psychotic serial killer who kills people just to hear their loved ones cry.

Amon tries to fill out the emptiness in his heart with violence against former band members and their relatives regarding the shock he had suffered from watching the girl, he is in love with kissing the lead singer of the band.
A gang of poverty-ridden juvenile delinquents progress from petty theft to hard crime, but a kindly judge manages to set most of them on the right path after they are finally apprehended.
A software engineer creates a program that triggers a warning text to everyone in the vicinity whenever a bomb explodes. As he continues to develop it, corrupt enemies try to snatch it from him.
A lawyer struggling with fear and lack of composure suddenly becomes fearless and flawless after purchasing an item from a beauty shop.
A compilation of 3 short horror stories. 'Wooden Clogs' directed by Kenji Nakanishi, 'Regeneration' and 'Last Day as a Teenager' directed by Takayuki Sato.
On a farm in the Canadian North-West, a young widow becomes the source of a jealous rivalry between her little son and her new husband.

Carlo and Melissa's idyllic vacation suddenly changes when Melissa discovers an ancient book of demons. Melissa becomes possessed and it's up to Carlo to stop the imminent ritual that will bring about the rebirth of a 400-year-old demon.

Samir is in love with Sonia but has unfortunately lied to her that he was already married.When she wants to meet her wife,Samir approaches his dutiful nurse Naina to play 'wife'a drama that turns out into a comedy of errors.
A professional assassin accidentally injures a girl on a hit job. Out of a deep sense of guilt and a need for redemption, he takes on one last job to make things right.
A teen girl is haunted by a dark spirit, only to discover that the demon has come to fulfil a curse on her.
After her abusive husband leaves, Monica asks her neighbor to look after her son while she's at work. Mildred's angry daughter's just moved out, so she's happy to have JJ.
A Taiwanese man returns to the island after years abroad when he inherits a house. When he and his fiancé move in, strange things start to happen.
Follows an unconventional story with universal themes, deeply steeped in the mythology of Bee Keeping.
The story is about a visually challenged guy, Vimal, struggling with life and his amazing journey of fulfilling an unusual dream of becoming IAS officer despite his low self confidence.
About the Soviet border guards who declassified the operation called "Cobra", organized by foreign intelligence. The purpose of this operation is to take daily photographs of a military facility.

This Oscar-nominated film is the story of two men who are opposites: one gay, the other straight; one a fierce communist, the other a fierce individualist; one suspicious, the other accepting; and how they come to love each other.
A thief operating along the highways of rural Australia gets caught in the crossfires of an ongoing police investigation after he mugs a serial killer.
A rich half-caste is abandoned after a mock marriage, has a stillborn baby, and weds the man who helps her.
Josefina depicts Middle Age Juan's love angle, Juan was a prison guard and the lady he loved's son Sergio was a prisoner in prison, and he loses his job because of his love.
5 boys go on a camping trip and tell scary stories around a campfire. Can the boys handle stories of werewolves, balloons, and a DVD store owner?

A deaf woman boarding with an elderly laborer suffers many hardships upon the latter's death. The old man's son offers to care for her, but she feels she must leave in order to protect the young man's reputation.
A troubled teen runaway is sent to live with a new foster family, but their carefully composed life may not be as it seems.

A secret wing in a prison is operated by a shadow government agency running experiments on death row inmates. When the experiment goes awry, the violent inhuman test subjects escape and overrun the complex.
When a couple books an Airbnb rental for their first Christmas, an evening of romance turns into a nightmarish twist of events.
Legs Sadovsky gets four other high school girls to think for themselves and react to a teacher's sexual harassment, which gets them suspended. They bond, and rebel, at an abandoned house.
Two corrupt LAPD Captains have come to a Beijing restaurant to kill a Beijing Police Captain who is failing to cooperate sufficiently with their plans but it is not as easy to get away as they think.

The classic Arthurian tale of tragic love. In medieval times, Lord of Cornwall decides to marry an Irish princess Isolde. However, his most loyal knight Tristan becomes bewitched by her beauty and they fall hopelessly in love.

After her father, a judge, is murdered by corrupt officials, a young woman must set out do recover the Blood Rain Sword, which her father had left to her, and encounters obstacles from the villainous Chao Pai.
Two 25-year-old men who meet by chance, fall madly in love, and are then separated due to an unexpected event. For the next thirty years they pursue the hope of finding each other again.
A gritty action drama based on the life of Yasuke, an African slave who gained his freedom and became a samurai in 16th century Japan.

Still hurting after their breakup, Tabby's stunned when she comes face to face with ex girlfriend Heidi at a friend's sleepover. Forced to spend the night together - can they put the past behind them? Or will they fall in love again?
A Russian mobster teaches three Latino teens the tricks of the criminal trade in this gritty urban crime drama.
When a taciturn children's author takes a vacation in a sleepy town, she is tormented by a malicious entity (Social Horror).
When a one night stand goes messy, three men have one hour to dispose of the corpse before they are discovered.
The quarrelling heirs of a deceased millionaire are not allowed to receive their share of wealth until they have found his son, who has long been lost in the forest.

movie_name: You and Me Against the World
description: With every member of his old gang out to get him, an ex-criminal finds it hard to trust anyone. But the doctor who tends to his wounds may get the chance to be his one and only ally.
When two teenage boys play a pirated video game, they become recruited to the service of the lord of war, the father of all conflict and war since the beginning of the earth.
A scholar, tasked to copy a sutra, meets with a mysterious old lady and her daughter in the mountains.
Torchy conducts a one woman campaign against a corrupt mayor and crime boss, and when the reform candidate is murdered, she takes up the banner.

When college professor, Peter Proud begins experiencing flashbacks of an earlier life, he's mysteriously drawn to a place he's never been to, but which seems familiar and where he soon finds his previous incarnation's wife.

In the future, new technology allows memories to be downloaded and traded in the black market. When a customer witnesses the murder of a politician, Allen Childs is accused of the crime and must attempt to clear his name.
Upon his release from jail, two-bit thug Don Keys gets caught up in the kidnapping plot of a mobster's daughter.
The wheels spin out of control when a secretary impersonates her no-nonsense boss to make her admirer feel appreciated.
The world's 10 deadliest assassin's are called upon to face the ultimate evil and he's been waiting lifetimes for them.
A woman boards an overnight train and gets placed in a compartment with her former lover and his wife.
When a farmer's daughter is brutally killed by vampires, he enlists the help of expert hunter Derrick McGregor and his team to track and kill the blood-sucking brood.

A 200 year old curse is unleashed on the small town of Las Mesas. George Eagleblood the fledgling Shaman and Carol Winters of the Las Mesas PD along with surviving officers fight to escape fight the city overrun by the curse of the GOUL.

Fifty-three years after being attacked by killer shrews on a remote island, Captain Thorne Sherman is hired by a reality television crew to return to the island in question. The shrews attack again in short order.

A married couple, desperate for money, turn to soliciting sex to strangers they meet online. Unable to handle the encounters, the husband snaps and takes the lives of all those who laid with his wife.
A young couple get locked in a storage facility only to discover that there's someone or something trying to make sure they never see the light of day.

Kang Dae-woong, a descendant of a fallen family of four generations, is in danger of overturning his sins through the conspiracy of the richest man, but escapes the crisis with the help of Kim Dae-gam, a former leader of Lee Jo.
As a coincidence, Murat founds his ex-love Selma after several years in his town. He would like to make up and regain her trust and love. However Selma already have a different life style.

Several players from different backgrounds try to cope with the pressures of playing football at a major university. Each deals with the pressure differently, some turn to drinking, others to drugs, and some to studying.
A crew of hardy road workers, led by a bickering father and son, must survive the night when they accidentally awaken an ancient Irish vampire.
When a TV reporter sets out to uncover a small town's hidden secret, she unwittingly becomes embroiled in a story that began with the curse of a Louisiana doll-maker over 40 years earlier.

Daniel and his best friend Devin go on a road trip to New Mexico, but when things quickly take a quick turn and the two end up in Mexico they must navigate their way back to the United States in a wild and crazy adventure.
Axel Foley returns to Beverly Hills to help Taggart and Rosewood investigate Chief Bogomil's near-fatal shooting and the series of "alphabet crimes" associated with it.
A family of cannibals consume evil doers in exchange for eternal life. But one member of the tribe grows out of control and goes rouge.
The daughter of a wealthy mayoral candidate and her friends are held for ransom by a group of daring criminals.

Hardcore gym goers and instructors at the local gym find themselves trapped in the showers when they are surrounded by a hoard of killer creeps. Their mission is to reclaim their clothes and escape before its too late.
Three beautiful, vengeful witches awakened by an ancient book, the Necronomicon, bring production of a film in their old family home to a deadly halt.
A cabaret singer in Germany is in love with a young American boy, and must convince his disapproving father that she is worthy of his son.
Fresh from prison, five friends try to stay crime free but inadvertently find themselves caught in a Triad war.
An ex lawyer now fisherman sees his fishing boat sunk by a lightning. His insurance company claims "Act of God". Sue the insurance company or God/churches?

Ex-Delta force Army soldier realize that not only is he adopted but his mother is the God of sun and his father is the Galaxy creator. His uncle who killed his Father is now sending an Army to kill the planet earth which he has to defend.
When a straight-laced warehouse manager investigates a missing bag of rice, he follows a trail of clues that leads him into the depths of Singapore's underworld.

Ravi is a son of a millionare and he does not value the true love of Annu; his office assistant. When he gets married to Rita, his life becomes miserble and soon realizes the evil plans pf Rita's family
15-year-old Oliver Tate has two objectives: to lose his virginity before his next birthday, and to extinguish the flame between his mother and an ex-lover who has resurfaced in her life.
A young man and woman meet at the beach. The man falls in love with her despite her perpetually moody personality. She soon reveals that she is dying and has only a few months to live.
The Adversary has acquired several enemies throughout his lifetime. Enemies that want nothing more than to see him dead and gone from this world. His time on this earth is about to come to an end.
Hitman Vincent Novena goes deep undercover portraying a priest in an attempt to get close to his target, a gangland traitor.
A musician takes time out to do some archeology and seeks out the hiding place along the Sussex coast of a lost fabled crown that supposedly helps protect Great Britain against invasion.
Jo and Gilly date. They find out they're brother and sister. Jo moves away. Gilly finds out that he's not Jo's brother and that Jo's getting married. Can he stop the wedding in time?
About 3 wild girl, Alesya, Sofea and Hani who lead a hedonistic teen life. Their life is about to change when one of them fall in love with an Islamic preacher, Firdaus.

After watching their small business go up in flames, three lifelong friends need money fast. Opportunity knocks when a local drug lord offers them a small fortune to smuggle 25 million dollars worth of Ecstasy from Amsterdam to Barcelona.
Indie doc crew travels to a small town to document a bizarre and seemingly unnatural case, ending in extreme tragedy.
As a means to distract herself from an affair, a love-addicted woman befriends a cleaning lady, badly scarred by burns. She soon learns, these scars run much deeper than the surface.

A group of people run a TV show where they set up locations to scare people. Things go horribly wrong when the producer wants them to get darker as they set up an asylum to spook the new target: a creepy guy who used to work there.
While vacationing, a girl and her parents are taken hostage by armed strangers who demand that the family make a choice to avert the apocalypse.

A family purchases a home robot designed to look like a grandmum. Their neighbours immediately buy a more expensivve model as the two families always try to up the other one. Both grandmums...                See full synopsis »
A female U.S. Army Special Agent is sent to a remote, all-male outpost in Afghanistan to investigate accusations of war crimes.
After 15 years in prison a talented racing driver and mechanic returns to life to fulfill his last promise to his dead beloved - to bring back Luce, the car bearing her name, and to dispense justice.

movie_name: Frankenpimp's Revenge: The Romeo and Juliet Massacre
description: Cartoonist: Romeo Montague, a skilled (dying, bloated and drunken) former vampire-killer and his star-crossed bad-girl-with-a gun-partner: Julie Crapuletti, returns in this campy, erotics sequel to the infamous cult-classic:'Frankenpimp'.
Peter has been cruel to children, animals and servants for a long time. One night he is ambushed and wakes up in a coffin, trapped after an earthquake, in the city's Gothic cemetery.

Buddhist monk and ex-cop Jin seeks answers when his sister is killed. He enlists the help of his ex-partner Achara and go-go dancer Pat Black to beat down bad guys, outsmart a U.S expat hotel owner, and end a corrupt regime

Herodias, spurned by Egyptian prince who is in love with Salome, has him secretly thrown in dungeon next to the Baptist. Herodias threatens to kill her lover if Salome does not ask for death of the Baptist.
It tells of a twin, separated at birth, one a mysterious young man named Sandino (played by Danilo Montes) who would transform into a monstrous hairy creature resembling a wolf man.

Three young programmers come across an abandoned technology meant to detect supernatural presence. They reverse engineer the tech and create an app for their phones which allows them to see ghosts, thus endangering their own lives.

Tó is a black boy from Zona J, a tough neighborhood in Lisbon, and falls in love with a white girl, Carla. Tó dreams to live in Angola, where his parents were born, however the reality the two teens are in makes everything complicated.
Its a revenge drama of a girl Naina, on social media. And victims who try to take them on, get killed without a trace or a clue for police to find out.
Two booksellers search for diamonds in Africa, along the way meeting a visually-impaired gunner, a hungry lion, and a tribe of cannibals.
A dying CIA agent trying to reconnect with his estranged daughter is offered an experimental drug that could save his life in exchange for one last assignment.
In WW2, an American aircraft carrier sails around the Pacific on a decoy mission until it joins the battle of Midway against the Japanese forces.

movie_name: I Am Going to Kill You
description: After a whirlwind romance, an expectant mother moves into a condo with her boyfriend. Everything is perfect - until she starts receiving anonymous death threats in the mail, triggering her past mental health struggles.
An ex mercenary, turned hired hitman is in a race for time to save his daughter's life who suffers from Cystic Fibrosis.
Soof is reaching 40 and has everything she ever wanted: three children, a small catering business, a sweet husband Kasper, and a lovely home. Until she starts asking herself: 'Is this all there is?'

LOL is back! This time our characters are showing that extreme stand-up comedy and real interaction with real people has a place in the world! Based on true events. Follow good and evil during their journey.
The story about a wild week at the Spanish coast. Romance at the beach, competition on the dance floor. Salty water, sweet kisses...
A war-torn soldier is pushed to the edge of morality as he struggles to keep his family safe after a northern escape turns into a nightmare as they become hunted by the enigmatic people of the snow.

The story about love, life, and friendship of four street punks friends. From their hometown in Malang, East Java, they plan a journey to Jakarta with the purpose to help their friend confess his love to his crush before her wedding day.

A black dockworker Pedro getting mixed up with a gang of arms smugglers and falsely imprisoned on a charge of murder. He is finally released and Mr. Mil convinces him to become a luchador/wrestler under the name of "Black Power".
Four millennials spend a weekend at an old mansion on a mysterious lake in southern Georgia. From the Executive Producer of Holloween and Scream 4. Please don't go into the attic.
An offbeat romantic comedy about a silver-painted street performer and the soft spoken zoo worker who falls for him.

A research team rescue the survivors of a plane crash on the Greenland ice shelf and things are not what they first appear to be. Action roller coaster as they make towards to the coast and safety in permanent darkness of the Arctic.
Graphic, abstract and disturbing hallucination exploring the planes between life, paradise and hell, loosely based on Dante's Trilogy La Davina Commedia.
The new neighbors must battle the block, and each other, for complete control of a hypnotic, blood-thirsty machete in order to save their stagnant marriage.
A 17th century scandal and a miscarriage of justice, impact on a young couple who adopt a little girl in 2019.
It follows a stripper who pisses off the FBI when she becomes the best candidate for their new agent program.

Rosa, a shy and romantic girl of sixteen, spends the summer holiday in a lavish mansion with her widowed mother. Along the way they are accompanied by two young bachelor men as fate takes its course on the naive young girl.
An independent film crew on a group location scout are attacked by a mysterious masked killer, who appears "hell-bent" on murdering them one by one.

During WW2 the atomic bomb secret was hidden by a failed Nazi Colaborator on Jones Beach. Now, a young German Spy has 6 weeks to find the deadly secret, but encounters one obstacle, He falls in love with an American Girl.

On 16 November, 1941 at the La Dessa U. S. army post in the Philippines, a Japanese carrier ship off the coast transmits a coded message to the contraband radio of Nazi spies. The spies ...                See full synopsis »
A colonel's daughter marries a farmer in name only, but returns to him when her lover threatens suicide.

A team of military contractors investigate the kidnapping of their friend and pilot. They use their skills to race against a doomsday clock, fight the enemies they've made over the years, and attempt to save their friend AND the world.

Hyungtae is a game programmer working on the ultimate online dating game. Working 24/7 on the 30th floor of the tallest building in Seoul, the company's future, whether or not it sinks to the bottom depends on the success of the game.
Story about a vampire who falls in love with a woman and tries to "re-humanize" himself in order to be with her.
On New Year's Eve, the driver of a ghostly carriage forces a drunken man to reflect on his selfish, wasted life.

In the wake of Kuruc Péter's demise, Zalán and Luca find themselves on the run, fearing retaliation from the fallen kingpin's forces. Meanwhile, underworld leaders seek to leverage the events, including the eager Áron Székely.
Mutants threaten to overwhelm the last bastion of civilization left after the great apocalypse. Only one man stands in their way, but he's running out of bullets.

A rivalry between the region's bosses shows the misuse of power and rank and its consequences even against a young couple who dared to rebel against planned but unwanted marriage to one of them,a story of injustice and abuse .
A Louisiana con man enters his steamboat into a winner-take-all race with a rival while trying to find a witness to free his nephew, about to be hanged for murder.

Against the backdrop of mass emigration in early 1900s Greece, an impoverished laundress finds herself enamoured with a handsome aristocrat. However, prejudice and shrewd machinations keep them apart. Will he be hers to keep?
Soviet plane crashed in Egypt. Pilot made it alive, but heavy traumatised. Years after he is back in USSR with a mission CIA give him.

Two scientists, embark on a experiment with unconventional ways of doing science, based on intuition and the intelligence of the heart. Throughout the process unheard of scenes of action and intriguing stories occur.

Two of Japan and China's greatest heroic swordsman find themselves caught in a plot to protect a young child. But will national distrust and simple misunderstanding keep the two kindred spirits apart?
Based on the Greek myth of Apollo and Daphne, this fable-like film depicts through its four characters the anguish of love that has difficulty coming together.
A horror-thriller centered on a woman (Wilson) suffering from a medical condition that causes her to sleep her life away, waking briefly on rare occasions.
Standing on the precipice of adulthood, a group of friends navigate new relationships, while reexamining others, during their final summer before college.
