Rebellious teenager Stevie finds his mother's gun, and along with his girlfriend impulsively decides to rob a bank. The pair find themselves in over their heads as they take hostages and the FBI negotiates Stevie's absurd demands.
A young couple seek to build a future for their troubled relationship, but their attempts are thwarted by guilt, suspicion, and hopeless indulgence in their own suffering.
A crew of treasure hunters accidentally unleash an evil force when they discover an ancient burial site off the coast of Nova Scotia.
Ram wants to avenge his friend cop Laxman who's mysteriously killed while pursuing a case. As he closes in on a gang named Cobra, he realises that their leader may be his own brother, Prashant.
The Expendables will square up against: an arms dealer who commands the might of a massive private army.
FBI agent Sara Cameron races against time to prevent her terror nemesis from striking a major target in Madrid.
A disbarred lawyer takes credit for a late friend's book, which becomes a smash hit but the tables turn on him sooner than he suspected.

movie_name: Strange Aeons: The Thing on the Doorstep
description: Soon after his marriage to the beautiful but mysterious heiress Asenath Waite, poet and scholar Edward Derby exhibits alarming personality changes and mood swings. His graduate advisor, Dan Upton investigates.
A vaudeville-like musical about courtship, temptation, secret love and vibrant cabaret life in turn-of-the-century Warsaw.

Kaaliyan and Jaishankar are like dictators in neighboring villages separately, but in contrast to Kaaliyan, Jaishankar is selfish and bad. Engagement of Jaishankar's sister with Kaaliyan triggers rivalry between the two villages.
A series of mutilated corpses is upsetting a town in central Italy. Police believe that this is a wolf, but it might not be a wolf as others.
The spoiled young heir to the decaying Amberson fortune comes between his widowed mother and the man she has always loved.
On his last night of freedom a killer plans the worst killing spree the city of London has ever seen. But as the evening progresses, his reality begins to crumble around him.
When Civil War veteran-turned-Egyptian-tomb-raider returns to America to solve the death of a loved one, he gets more than he bargained for.

When local teenagers start turning up dead in more brutal ways than you can throw a honeydew melon at, Adam and his friends vow to uncover the identity of and put a stop to the psychopath responsible.

After finding an old nautical phone washed up on the shore, Natalie begins having dreams of the device ringing, followed by the presence of a shrouded woman in black. Natalie's already fragile grip on reality begins to slip.
A single mother and waitress, a misanthropic author, and a gay artist form an unlikely friendship after the artist is assaulted in a robbery.

A story about two people who didn't find their way in big city. He came from the countryside and works in steel factory, she's working in factory restaurant. Their lives change when they meet and fall in love.

A group of five snowboarders get trapped in an abandoned cabin due to a massive whiteout. Soon they will find out that a demonic spirit haunts the cabin and won't stop until it kills every each one of it's new occupants.
A man returning to his old neighborhood after a prison term finds that the friends he used to hang out with are now a violent street gang that is terrorizing the community.
Seven friends, who are reunited at a dinner party after years apart, relate and are affected by a traumatic event that unites them unexpectedly.

Charlie Cooper is a special agent of the future able to transfer his consciousness to bio-mechanical bodies at will. But when a computer virus corrupts his system, he must face one of his greatest challenges yet: mortality.
Using several clips from previous Gamera entries, this film deals with alien forces sending all the monsters Gamera has faced in one final battle to rid the planet of its last hope.
A performance of love and qualms between a man and a woman, between the elders and their young; and a hostile poem of love and betrayal to the Motherland.
A loner madman necrophile, with also the passion of the ancient Egypt culture, start to mummifies the bodies of young victims to satisfy his desire for love and sex.

movie_name: The Villa with the Water Lilies
description: An affluent Athenian belle arrives at a quiet village with her ailing brother, only to find herself entangled in the unwelcome romantic advances of the village's handsome doctor. Can love bloom in the elegant villa with the water lilies?

In small town near the coast of Black Sea people accidentally found part of ancient Greek statue of goddess Aphrodite. The archaeologist Anatoliy tries to find whole statue but instead he found his love.
A fading midwestern town, in which Frendo the clown a symbol of bygone success reemerges as a terrifying scourge.
The latest short film before lock-down is Do It For Me. As I told you, the story-line is similar to Jannat but with more skin showing, and outpacing the serial kisser Emraan Hashmi.
Policemen versus bandits, with women of both sides of the law in a rampage of revenge for past killings of their fathers.
Genius British guy kidnaps a woman and is convinced that by following certain psychological steps and well planned charm, her brain will have no choice but to trigger feelings of love towards him.
A newspaper correspondent who has convinced his publisher he is married implores his friend's wife to pose as his bride.
A palace in Jayamahal is disowned by a rich family. Three generations later, the family returns back to their ancestral palace and soon experience some unexplainable activities.
A love story between Jae Hoon, who couldn't let go of his ex-girlfriend, and Sun Young, who is splitting up with her boyfriend. The couple got trouble and were hurt by love.
A Lolita incarnated, lost girl, seeks a psychiatrist to help her dissect her life and the secret behind her obsession with red.
The life story of Ed Gein, the notorious serial killer and grave robber who inspired several classic horror films including 'Psycho' and 'The Texas Chainsaw Massacre'.
Ho-jeong finds out her boyfriend has fallen in love with a man while studying abroad. She demands one month of dating to win him back.

The Village Hidden in the Leaves is home to the stealthiest ninja in the land. But twelve years earlier, a fearsome Nine-tailed Fox terrorized the Village before it was subdued and its spirit sealed with in the body of baby boy-Naruto.

A man meets a girl in an Alpine Lodge and decide to make the relation permanent, but they lose each other, each thinking the other to be disloyal. When the meet again, both are engaged, to others, and she is mother of his child.
When a rare Lakota Ghost Shirt falls onto the black market in a small town in South Dakota, the lives of local outsiders and outcasts violently intertwine.
A woman and her new husband returns to her hometown roots in coastal northern Florida, and must deal with family, business, and encroaching real estate development.
The bloodiest epic of a handfull of gallant men. A saga of heroism . The war cries. The clash of sabers. And the agonies and screaming death.
Trapped in an apartment and surrounded by ghosts that are always just out of sight, Lorraine must confront her greatest fears.
Private detective Victor Grishanin committed murder by negligence, while investigating the strange death of his father.
Chin Siu Ho plays a young man who believes himself to be an orphan. Until one rainy night when he and three different men find themselves taking shelter from the storm in the same place.
Love test for two students in USSR's Moscow: 23-year old ambitious straightforward builder Alexei, and 20-year old Zhenya, the daughter of prosperous parents that already have a fiance for her.
During the Depression, a con-man promises rain to a desperate drought-ridden Kansas town and marriage to a local desperate spinster.
A brain-dead sheriff, a stolid secret agent and a sexy scientist team with a grumpy retired monster fighter to battle a 60 foot, three-eyed cross between man and dinosaur.
Two lovebirds separated by fate, and has to deal with a heartbreaking feeling of longing for each other.
Swish, energetic kung fu action with everyone hunting a golden dragon statue and a killer called Moon Night Cutter.

During Passover, Masha Shelly, a pregnant true crime podcaster, travels to the secluded town of New Egypt, Indiana to investigate the murder of a firstborn son, unearthing a dark entity with insidious designs on her own unborn male child.
A guy recruits the assistance of professional seduction experts in order to become the world's greatest pick-up artist.

Following the murder of her family at the hands of her father in the wake of World War I, a young woman goes to live in a convent. However, the demons that plagued her father follow, reawakening the nightmares of her past.
The war amongst men had an influence on the beings of the forest. Now the beings demand revenge. Balance between men and the forest has been broken.
By day they are janitors, cleaning up after your messes. By night they scrape the scum off the city streets. They are....Ninjanitors.
Alka Singh, the leader of a political party, and her obsessive love for Rohan Mehra, a rising star of Bollywood.

Sentry follows two soldiers, Dipshit (DP) and Striker on Stag duty. Its 0300 when they came on shift, after being out on operations for weeks, exhaustion is setting in, tiredness is taking ...                See full synopsis »
Old Monk is a romantic comedy. It tells the story of a love crossed youngster. Will this young man find his one true love or will Lord Krishna's curse on him prevail?
The movie tells the story about love and forgiveness. This story of opposites of feelings - love and hate, faith and doubt, grace and guts, triumphs and regrets.
A young woman meets an undisciplined ex-classmate ... when romance flourishes, it leads them on an adventure that puts their lives in peril.
After pulling off a major bank heist, four college kids must choose between the money and their lives when trapped in a safehouse by a geeky suburban dad who moonlights as a righteous serial killer.
A scientist, Owen Reid, tries to discover the reasoning behind the phenomenon of a fog that sweeps over the U.S. causing the disappearance of life that goes with it.

It is an emotional journey of an aging Naxalite leader Kondarudra Seetharamayya, who wants to meet his son in his last days . Police are in pursuit of him as he eliminated a political personality who is the father of Home minister.
Seven swordsmen share a thirst for revenge against a common enemy. After perfecting their skills, they set out to find their target but discover their enemy is more skillful than they suspected.
In 1988, young sisters Katie and Kristi befriend an invisible entity who resides in their home Name Toby.

Detective Kenichi Itami from the The National Police Agency and Akira Iwatsuki from the cyber investigation team investigate a complex murder case. The victim was under investigation by the cyber investigation team.
Five years after their summer together in Barcelona, Xavier, William, Wendy, Martine and Isabelle reunite.
This anthology film consists of nine incidents in the late 19th and early 20th centuries when assassins changed the course of Japanese history.

A woman becomes possessed and dies after a monster is released from an antique vase she had purchased. Twelve years later the monster is re-awakened. First he possesses the family's dog, before moving on to the woman's nephew.
After receiving a letter from his deceased brother calling him back to their childhood home, a young man finds himself trapped against a sinister force and the reality of his own tragic past.
Kate has a huge crush on Jason, her classmate. And as she tries to reunite with him during her senior trip, things get a little messy.
A man finds a ring that gives the bearer great power but the goddess to whom the ring belongs wants it back.
Following the TV Series "El Maleficio", Enrique finally finds the pictorial work he was looking for. A being from beyond informs him about the author.

Leon, the 40-year-old former soldier who is an alcoholic now, gets a job as a bodyguard. His duty is to take care of one of the Mafia leader's daughters. His problems begin when he falls in love with the 16-year-old girl.
When Bharati's brother is killed, the love of her life, Raja, helps her to get to the bottom of the mystery and they stumble upon a big conspiracy involving powerful people.
The story revolves around the death of Poornima Rao, a senior executive in a reputed IT firm, who dies jumping of the high raised IT tech park while taking a selfie.
After the mysterious disappearance of their mother, estranged brothers reunite and discover an unknown supernatural force.
A former snowboarding champion embarks on an Everest expedition to reclaim his tarnished reign, but a vicious Yeti attack wipes out his his team.

Franck and Simon are both good cops and partners. Simon has been troubled since he killed three in a drunk driving accident, but when Simons son witnesses a murder, and is hunted by ruthless killers, he's efficiently back.

A female detective with PTSD investigates the murder of her partner and unearths a serial killer while a derailed cop with short-term memory loss fights for his innocence after being suspected of killing his father.

movie_name: Raw: The Curse of Grete Müller
description: A group of teenagers want to shoot a documentary about the legend of Grete Müller. They visit the forest which is supposed to be haunted.
Chasing their dream of landing their own hunting show, two hunters head into the dense, secluded mountains of West Virginia only to realize they are not alone.

Presenters of paranormal TV show "Ghost Hosts" are filming in an abandoned haunted building as part of a Halloween special. The stories surrounding the horrifying ghosts of the mansion are about to become reality.
A group of masterless samurai living in Edo's red light district must fend off a militia bent on wiping out local prostitutes.

Fundamentalist Christian Blaine Carson kidnaps agnostic Sophie Alexander from an abortion clinic parking lot and takes her to the mountains to force her to have his baby as they are pursued by the FBI and National Guard.
The deadly adventures of Bunnyman continue in the third and final flatulent film in the Bunnyman trilogy.

The true family of Frank Di Angelo is from underworld. His gang is made up a rough group of headstrong men. Mistakes, debts and treasons have unavoidably brought them face to face with Andrei Milhov, member of the Russian Mafia.
A young man struggles in life, Hustling drugs to underground cage fights, to support his mother and his self, he becomes known as a successful fighter where thats the turning point of his life.

A 12-episode serial in which a son avenges the death of his father at the hands of corrupt politicians. He develops a wide variety of complex devices in his crusade . . . Ray guns, robots and a 'vanishing belt.'
Graduate student Aiko has always had low self-esteem because of the birthmark on her face. When her story is cinematized, she falls for the director who accepts her as she is.
Ashraf marries the daughter of a rich businessman, hoping to inherit her fortune. When she marries him against her father's wishes, she is disinherited from her father's wealth.
Kashma Baba, the son of the famed Baghdad thief Ali Baba is a cadet in a medieval Persian military academy where he runs afoul of his rival Hussein, the evil Caliph's son.
A fun getaway for a group of friends turns into a bloody, twisted battle of survival of the fittest.

Gianni, a man suffering of Oedipus complex, finally falls in love with a woman named Lola. However, he finds out that Lola is attracted to his brother Paolo. This causes Gianni to go on a killing spree.
A college professor engages authorities at the Witness Protection Program as he who investigates the disappearance of his wife and daughter.
Simon McGee, a chubby, half-Korean stand-up comic wrestles with his Korean heritage through his crush on a beautiful Korean girl.
Compilation of 3 episodes of "The Adventures of Superman" tv series: episode #33 ("Superman in Exile"), 36 ("The Face and the Voice"), and #51 ("The Whistling Bird").
The heroic battles of Souliotes to defend their land from the Turks, until Ali Pasha with the help of a traitor, he manages to conquer Souli.
A tragic love triangle story between Hwa-Yeon, a daughter of a nobleman, her true love Kwon-Yoo, a servant and the man who will be King, Prince Sungwon.
A special agent works to free a group of hostages held captive inside New York's Empire State Building.
A rebel leader returns to his city for a final confrontation with the evil king he is fighting. However, he finds himself attracted to the king's beautiful niece.

Jean DeBois kills a man who pesters his beautiful daughter Renee. Subsequently, Renee is blackmailed by an unscrupulous suitor, Captain Blake, who threatens to expose her father if she refuses to marry him.
An Argentine bank robber offers a future full of money and recognition to a young boxer with an unpromising career.

Two troubled men stay in a empty house to avoid the harsh winter weather. The longer they're there, the more strange and bizarre their surroundings become while dark secrets and unspeakable evils are revealed between them
In a near future, a lonely writer develops an unlikely relationship with an operating system designed to meet his every need.
Continues the romantic story of Javier and Angela, who, after having sworn eternal love and having their first child, decide to divorce.
Two young couples take a swing at handling their relationship problems through psychologist-prescribed partner-swapping.
In a clandestine study, while she is filming a porn movie, a strong attraction comes on between Marisa, one of the actresses, and Dick, former acrobat and now her 'protector'.

A writer, looking for some peace and quiet in order to finish a novel, takes a room at the Baldpate Inn. However, peace and quiet are the last things he gets, as there are some very strange goings-on at the establishment.
A young student is devastated when he finds that his girlfriend is cheating on him. In order to find out why she did it, he decides to spy on her and her lover.
An endocrinologist in a dysfunctional marriage with an aging, alcoholic wife journeys to Africa seeking a drug that will restore youth.

Gyeongsung grew up and was brought up in a gang of thieves. He is in love with the boss's daughter Mu-young. One day, he learns the truth about his father, whose death his boss is guilty of. Kyungsung wants revenge.
An embittered music composer, estranged from his family, self-destructs after learning his sweetheart has married another male.
A peon's son who is an aspiring IAS officer is compelled to change his path leading him to turn into a gangster.

Two reporters from the Pacific Union investigate the 104th meridian as the World Trade Federation launches their corporate blitzkrieg. Now everyone must escape westward to post apocalyptic California.

Vehicle for Little Vera star Natalya Negoda, here a young student who meets a 50 year old con artist (he'd tried to dupe her mother into a fake apartment swap) and lands up in a Black Sea hotel room with him and the corpse of a policeman.

In the street racing underworld 2 gangs battle it out. Only the fast survive and the new breed of transportation is the all wheel drive, 2-liter rocket ship from the land of the rising sun. So buckle up and gear down for ultimate turf war.
Robert O' Rourke is a prisoner in his own world. He suffers in silence, plagued by visions he cannot control. Soon Robert awakens into a nightmare that is very real and will change him forever.
A filmmaker struggles to finish this movie despite the script. Meanwhile, the main characters Copper and Katie incite an incident in their search for a story.
A frustrated New York housewife goes on vacation in the Caribbean and has an affair with a local man.

Zhu Yanzhi (Charlene Choi), disguised as a man, seeks to learn martial arts with an elite clan. Once she begins her intense training, Zhu finds herself at odds with her trainer and superior, Liang (Chun Wu).
An immigrant coal miner finds himself in the middle of a bitter labor dispute between the workers and the mine owners.
An entertaining but silly and fairly forgettable action film with much tongue-in cheek James Bond influence,
Félix, operator of dodgem cars in a fairground, becomes obsessed by one of his customers, a mysterious young woman named Lola.
A real-life story of Canadian outlaws who nearly incited a native uprising in 1879 British Columbia.
A man and woman are kicked out of the Court of Heaven on trumped up charges of bringing shame onto the Kingdom.
What seemed like a breezy idea for an engineer to net him millions of dollars, leaves him on the run for his life and piecing together why he's being chased.

movie_name: Barun Rai and the House on the Cliff
description: Newly-weds Soumili and Harmesh Banerjee have just moved into their dream home and life should be perfect. But their love is being tested by unexplained incidents. Enter Barun Rai, As his expertise lies in solving paranormal activities.
Bored, sexually frustrated Sarah accepts a position as an apprentice to a "sexual sorceress" and magical sexual hijinks ensue.
Kang Jin-kyu is imprisoned for killing a man who had wronged him. However, his mental anguish increases when he learns that his son has betrayed him and joined the gang of his enemy.
Five people are offered one million dollars to spend six months together in an isolated mansion, with cameras watching their every move.
Storm, a young police officer, has resigned from his agency to return to his life of crime. The caveat is that he must become an anonymous person who no longer exists.
Depicts the adventures of Dr. Refaat Ismail, a single hematologist who finds himself faced with a series of supernatural events.

After his wife and son got brutalized by a street gang, and a corrupt criminal justice system puts the perpetrators back on the street, a NYC factory worker teams up with a vigilante group to find some measure of bloody justice.
A family move to a new, creepy house. While the parents fight a lot, their youngest daughter missing. It said that she was taken by a supernatural being called Wewe Gombel.
Revolves around Soo-hyun and the three sisters. While he is falling in love with the youngest sister Mi-young, he also tries to seduce her two sisters. Everything become complicated.

A desperate wife agrees to have a baby cloned from her comatose husband's DNA. However, the husband gets better and they get rid of the baby - until the past comes calling decades later in a mix of mystery, lust and violence.
A troubled young woman returns to her dying grandfather's house to rediscover the supernatural incident that altered the course of her life.
When a naively innocent, aspiring actress arrives on the Broadway scene, she is taken under the wing of several theater veterans who mentor her to ultimate success.
He and She are the personification of love, they live in an ethereal and surreal dimension. Their love becomes hatred and anguish until death.
After fulfilling a contract killing in Los Angeles, a French hit man becomes the target of a hit himself and tries to flee back to Paris.

A micro-budget independent film made by an (almost) all-Latino cast and crew. Inspired by sci fi classics and B Movies, the film pairs unlikely heroes with unlikely weapons in an attempt to save the Earth!
Radit and Jani are a young couple who are determined to get married despite opposition from Jani's parents. Without enough money and steady work, they have to live a hard life.
A teenage girl dying of leukemia compiles a list of things she would like to do before passing away. Topping the list is her desire to lose her virginity.
Inspired by true events, the film narrates the heroic tale of NSG commandos, who step in to save innocent people when terrorists attack a temple in Gujarat.
The adventures of an orphaned boy named Pete and his best friend Elliott, who happens to be a dragon.
A thief gets more than he bargained for when he steals a video tape containing various stories that each tell a story about a mysterious artifact.
A cab driver finds himself held hostage by a hitman who forces him to drive through the roads of Dubai and help him kill his targets.
CONQUERING WOES AFTER BEING USED, ABUSED AND ACCUSED. A tale of a vulnerable, unsuspecting woman on a trail of rebuilding her shattered life.
Bomba, the Jungle Boy and now animal protector, discovers human skeletons which turn out to be those of his parents.
A television reporter and her cameraman are trapped inside a building quarantined by the CDC, after the outbreak of a mysterious virus which turns humans into bloodthirsty killers.

Petra is driven away by a raging mob after engaging to merry 3 bachelors in her 1800's home town. On her flight toward the capitol, she lies her way into a vicarage. Based upon Bjørnstjerne Bjørnsons famous 1968-novel "The fisher girl".
A maniac killer in a red cape and hood is killing off American tourists on a tour bus by gouging out their eyeballs.
The viewer is presented with footage found at the scene of a crime on the land of an old farmhouse where seventy years prior, the infamous "Moorland murders" took place.

Young men are vanishing from a small, Oregon town and the only suspect is beautiful, young recluse Veronica Chandler. Eddie Hooper sets out to solve the mystery, but his fascination with Veronica could make him the next victim.

Down on his luck and financially strapped low budget horror filmmaker Mandalor is the laughing stock of the film community. His films are terrible and the contrived, poorly done ...                See full synopsis »
A group of teen social media stars living together in a mansion in the Hollywood Hills where they film their ruckus lives 24/7 becomes the victim of a crazed stalker.
A secret service agent's wife will have to take his place and bring back her primitive instincts to survive and save her family.

In Havana, Raul dreams of escaping to Miami. Accused of assault, he appeals to Elio to help him reach the forbidden world 90 miles across the ocean. One night, full of hope, they face the biggest challenge of their lives.

Daveeth arrested for killing two of his friends. Arguments going on in the court, daveeth says "I'm not the killers, they are the Killers, a true story behind me, if u know the story, you can find that what is truth.

A young man has only ten days to locate his soulmate as dictated by the stars, otherwise he could lose a fortune. He thus embarks on a journey through love, looking through twelve girls to find the one who fits his horoscope.
The affair between King Edward VIII and American divorcée Wallis Simpson, and a contemporary romance between a married woman and a Russian security guard.
Schizo the Clown is jovial one minute, angry the next. Either way he's a deadly mass murderer using clown tricks to kill his victims. But whatever you do, don't call him "Clowny".
A single mother is forced to kill ten people over ten days by the psycho that kidnapped her daughters.
Yilmaz is released from prison, while trying to talk to the girl he loves, on the other hand, he embarks on a tough struggle against the order established by a landowner.

A group of students investigates a series of mysterious bear killings, but learns that there are much more dangerous things going on. They start to follow a mysterious hunter, learning that he is actually a troll hunter.
Two werewolves spend a hot summer evening chasing down their cocaine dealer. A touching story of friendship, loyalty, and perseverance.
The opposite lives of a workaholic architect and a fiery artist are upended when their chance encounter in breathtaking Peru shifts their views on life.
A FedEx executive undergoes a physical and emotional transformation after crash landing on a deserted island.

This is a story of a man and a woman who try to defy the odds and prove to everyone that men and women can be just friends. Sounds simple enough; yet it becomes one of the most complicated journeys of all time for the two friends.

Arya is the quintessential Good Samaritan, who lives for the ones he loves most. When he falls in love with innocent small town girl Geetha, he thinks he can have that happily ever after. But fate has a lot of obstacles.
Dr. Laurience, a brilliant but unstable scientist experimenting with transferring minds, becomes vengeful when his magnate patron withdraws his support.

movie_name: Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind
description: When their relationship turns sour, a couple undergoes a medical procedure to have each other erased from their memories for ever.
A poor girl must choose between the affections of dating her childhood sweetheart or a rich but sensitive playboy.
When Earth is invaded by an alien army of horrors, a giant robot named Gaiking is constructed to defend the Earth.
While driving on a remote highway, a man is torn between choosing to reunite with his estranged wife or taking up with his lover.
A madcap private-eye caper about a team of detectives who are following, and are being followed by, a group of beautiful women.
A Young man fights for his lost bike with courage. Honest Gangster with his foolish brother who destroyed everything. This is a remake of Tamil movie Polladhavan aka.Ruthless Man (2007)
Nora Mason becomes entangled in a family mix-up of murder and scandal that threatens to ruin her career and entire future; Unless the mother she does not know can find a way to save her.
When a doctor's immortality medicine goes horribly wrong, he creates a blood-sucking daughter. Decades later, a doctor goes undercover to bring the vampire plague to an end.
Evil aliens attack Earth and set their terrible "Plan 9" into action. As the aliens resurrect the dead of the Earth, the lives of the living are in danger.
It's day one of the end of the world, as vampires take over the Earth in one night of blood and slaughter. Four strangers must work together if they are to stay alive.

A coven of Sexy, modern Day vampires ravage the American Midwest with the thirst for blood, while a romantic twist puts the vampires at odds among themselves and with the murderous Illuminati that seek to gain their immortality.
400 years after the murder of a Native American Girl, paranormal occurrences haunt a successful young writer.

A city is portrayed as a hub of illegal activities. To avenge his brother's death, Rajveer joins MLA Shamsher Singh Grewal's group. He soon leaves the gang when he discovers a shocking truth about the MLA.
After his fiancée is killed in a car accident, a gifted surgeon revives her severed head in hopes of finding her a new body.
When Ranae agrees to babysit for a family with a tragic past, a run-of-the-mill Saturday night quickly turns into a confrontation with unspeakable horror.
Two female police officers fight to survive a police force filled with corrupt superiors and the brutal criminal mafia.
The house five people decide to stay on their trip to an island has some dark secrets that will unleash each of their inner fears and secrets as well.
After getting rejected by the woman he loves, a bitter man goes to a shaman for revenge. Soon after, villagers become infected with rabies and leeches.

A well to do couple assume the property left to them in a family will. The idyllic Lake Evermore and it's population of eager to please townsfolk begin to change as the Turner's inquire about the towns isolation from the outside world.

Once out of a psychiatric clinic with a life to restart 42-66 will have to dwell with his past and an haunting and violent present. Followed by a supernatural presence he will face a perverse boss and his tedious henchman.
Rogue Lorry Drivers risking their lives on the edge while getting double crossed by an unscrupulous haulage Boss involved in human trafficking.
John McClane attempts to avert disaster as rogue military operatives seize control of Dulles International Airport in Washington, D.C.
An American troop stranded in the Italian wilderness, struggle to find their way back to safety during World War 2.
A Korean-American rappers manager who falls for one of his female fans uses the rappers identity to talk to her, and must decide if he should reveal his true identity before it's too late.
According to the will of an eccentric millionaire, one of four randomly chosen strangers will become his heir if he/she can double $5000 by honest means.
Female migrant workers eat dirt at the hands of a sadistic ranch foreman during grape-harvesting season in the San Joaquin Valley.
A pretty young girl and a sweet but plain-looking boy fall in love. Will their relationship prevail?

Sirisha (Priya Lal), grows up living in her beautiful dream aspires to major in music but has to promise her father that she would marry the man he chooses if she wants to moves to the city and learn violin.
The peerless swordsmith, Meng Yezi, suffered the calamity of family extermination from the traitor Zhao Han served in the court for casting the famous Hanguang Sword.
Ghouls, cannibals, Aliens and an evil robot in a giant maze like mansion, surrounded by eerie swamp land. Would you spend the night for $10,000?
When a photographer unwittingly takes a job from a sleazy pornographer, she and the models are soon targeted by a leather gloved assailant.
During the Meiji era, a gambler called Ocho takes revenge on three gangsters who killed her father, shelters a wanted anarchist and confronts a British spy.
An orphaned teenager finds himself being dominated by his aunt who's hell-bent on keeping him with her...at all costs.
In the aftermath of Jose's death, another young couple find themselves embroiled in a chaos that neither has the energy or inclination to try to understand.

Three tales about a morally-questionable doctor, a quarantined relationship, and a rich businessman sent spiraling into debt due to the SARS outbreak. Each person is "affected" by SARS in their own unique way.

While on vacation in Cape Coast, Ghana, a man's plan to propose to his girlfriend becomes derailed after his younger brother accepts a bet, forcing them to spend a night in one of West Africa's oldest haunted slave castle.
In 1920s Warsaw, a legendary conman tries to exploit the financial problems of a vaudeville theatre in order to rob a bank.
A newly appointed professor finds that his student has a crush on him and wants to marry him. He ignores her advances and marries an orphan. Not the one to give up, she continues to pursue him.
THE ACTION - ADVENTURE - FANTASY FILM TELL THE STORY OF A PEACE-LOVING MAN WHO IS PUSHED BY CIRCUMSTANCES TO FIGHT AN AVARICIOUS FAMILY VICTIMIZING HIS TOWNSPEOPLE.
What we think is just a normal day at 'Creek High' - a group of school teachers battle an unknown alien force. They must work together to stop the alien virus from escaping and taking over the world.
Stark opposites, Fateh Singh and Pooja reach Canada with dreams in their eyes. They cross paths and sparks fly. However, life has a different plan for them.
Harold "Speedy" Swift, a fan of Babe Ruth and the New York Yankees, saves from extinction the city's last horse-drawn trolley, operated by his girlfriend's grandfather.
A group of people who feel betrayed by their government and let down by their Police force form a modern-day outlaw posse in order to right what they see as the wrongs of society.
A group of diamond thieves on the run kidnap the wife of a recently discharged marine who goes on a chase through the South Carolinian wilderness to retrieve her.
A love triangle develops between a beautiful yet dangerous vampire (Catherine Deneuve), her cellist companion (David Bowie), and a gerontologist (Susan Sarandon).

When the zombie apocalypse begins, a group of survivors discovers a news broadcast. Hoping to rally with the news team and any other people their message has reached, the survivors embark on a trek toward what promises to be their salvation
Former special operative MacGruber is called back into action to take down his arch-enemy, Dieter Von Cunth, who's in possession of a nuclear warhead and bent on destroying Washington, D.C.

It's a story about some teen aged boy and girl of a University. A romantic story but in this story viewers will get a heavy sad and deep message. Which will make them realized a universal truth about transgender people and their feelings.
A group of college kids on Fall break find themselves in a bad situation when they become stranded at the infamous Camp Blood.

A romantic comedy-drama, Nothing in Los Angeles chronicles a young artist's bittersweet love affair with the city of Los Angeles, focusing on the fleeting nature of personal relationships and professional dreams.
The listless love lives and insecure domestic arrangements of a group of Wellington 20-somethings are scrutinized with insight and irony in this film.
To escape the horrors of urban life, a young family moves to the country only to face the largest recorded volcanic eruption and the totally real horrors that followed.
Rich kid Teto is determined to prove himself to Paula, his love interest. But when he tells her he grew up poor, the lie spins out of control.

Lisa Templeton begins a new job as a cleaner at High Hopes Hospital, a mental institution in Amityville, Long Island. Initially delighted to get the job, Lisa soon realises that all is not as it seems.
A collector comes into possession of the skull of the Marquis de Sade and learns it is possessed by an evil spirit.
With the help of his uncle, a man travels to the future to try and bring his girlfriend back to life.

Heloise is a woman with a dark and twisted past; with a sexually abusive father, a cruel mother that forces her to become a child bride; and DIONA, a vision of hatred and rage that manifests itself with her whenever Heloise is afraid.
A group of friends come together to celebrate their lifelong friendships and the death of their best friend.

Zoe finds the best flavor for a big coffee-and-doughnuts chain, but the story needs to be better than 'invented in a lab with a test group'. She's sent to Colombia to get a story, while there she meets Diego, a single coffee farmer.
When three sisters go on a big family vacation with their husbands, unexpected events shake the foundations of their marriages.
As kids, they escaped a UFO death cult. Now, two adult brothers seek answers after an old videotape surfaces and brings them back to where they began.

Marcos is a divorced man who finds himself broke and stuck in his Job. Armed with an Idea he decides to try to achieve his dreams. But his brother and sister in law may end up changing his plan for an adventure that he will never forget.

A TV talk-show hostess and her boyfriend investigate a shady magician who has the ability to hypnotize and control the thoughts of people in order to stage gory on-stage illusions using his powers of mind bending.
A crippled circus acrobat is torn emotionally between two ambitious young trapeze artists, one a talented young American and a less-gifted but beautiful Italian.
Sampaguita's humble dedication to the child left behind--your neighborhood child--or your own children.
Kyle Hackleman delivers a new generation of crime and barbarous mischief in this dreaded slasher film.
A sweeping small town romance exploring the grit of craft, the heart of family, and the pains of love, told over the span of several years.
Art school graduate Helene moves back to Virginia Beach where the brokenhearted music scene is left in despair over a mysterious death.

A pair of Tokyo policewomen who pack their own brand of "deadly weapons" do some serious undercover work as they take on the toughest cases the department has to offer in this steamy mix of cop action and softcore drama.

Marala Telupana Priya is a story about a girl Vaishu (Vyoma Nandi) a daredevil and an ardent bike racer. She falls in love with a young music director Jaya Krishna (Prince Cecil) and tries to come to terms with his sudden disappearance.
A college student returning home for Halloween is forced to face his childhood fears when an escaped killer takes refuge in his family's "Haunted Hayride".

Hawaii has fallen under the control of a ruthless cartel of seven gangsters. The FBI acquires the services of an ex-agent turned assassin, Drew Savano, who in turn assembles a team of seven hitmen to stop them.
Five small time criminals plan the kidnapping of a rich girl. Everything that could go wrong with the plan actually goes wrong, leading them to a weird massacre.
Seven guests are invited to an after party on the abandoned floor of an office building, handpicked to play a series sadistic and deadly puzzles.
A sicilian girl madly in love with a famous singer plays any trick to enflame him. Will she win his heart?
Orhan and Filiz are recently married couple. One day, because of misunderstanding they fall to loggerheads.
In this tongue-in-cheek sequel, the benevolent bog creature falls for the vegetarian, plant-loving daughter of the evil scientist who created him.

A hippie girl wandering on a California beach is taken in by a Korean War veteran who lives in a nearby mansion with his sister. The girl soon begins to suspect that the mansion is home to some very strange goings-on.

movie_name: The Ghosts of Hanley House: 50th Anniversary Edition
description: A re-cut version of The Ghosts of Hanley House (1968). It removes some footage that contains plot holes from the original and replaces it with newly-shot material.
A Romeo and Juliet love story between the son of a brutal Italian bootlegger and the daughter of his bitter ex-partner, who is engaged in a blood feud with his one-time friend.
A BRUSH WITH SATAN is the ultimate horror adventure ride through the mind of a Drug Fueled Alcoholic Painter under deep sleep psychosis.
A beautiful lady falls in love with a rehabilitating Casanova, only to find out he is the best friend of her drug-lord fiancé
A young couple must navigate a blossoming romance, amidst a war between their families' competing pizza restaurants.
Hervé, a wealthy and confident Parisian, finds himself lost in the middle of a small Romanian village. While he imagines himself returning quickly to Paris, the return paths will shake his illusions.
An American pilot impulsively joins His Majesty's Royal Air Force in Britain in an attempt to impress his ex-girlfriend.
Badal falls in love with a woman who agrees to marry him on a condition that leaves him in a life-shattering situation. What did she ask for?

When Hiccup and Toothless discover an ice cave that is home to hundreds of new wild dragons and the mysterious Dragon Rider, the two friends find themselves at the center of a battle to protect the peace.
After a chance meeting, a teenage couple's relationship blossoms into intimacy. However, an unexpected pregnancy throws their school life into fits.

As a youngster, Jake witnessed the sight of his best friend lying dead and his father wielding a shotgun. Trying to gain closure, Jake returns home to find the truth about what really happened that fateful night.
Fearing she will die, a physicist's wife hopes her husband will be consoled by the orphan she adopts.

In the vein of Pumpkinhead, The Midnight Friend is a modern horror tale about unchecked, all- consuming rage told from an African American perspective. An ancient African Totem, gives high-schooler, Steven, a deadly outlet for his anger.

movie_name: Dhar Wars Episode V: The Dhar Mann Fam Strikes Back
description: Luis rushes to complete his training while the rebels find a new place to hide. Dharth Vadhar also has an army that could destroy the rebels.
An ex-mercenary is forced out of isolation when three mysterious men kidnap and brainwash the city's children afflicted with the Geostigma disease.
A businessman strives to find the solution for the existing power cut problems present in his community.

A young couple meet while on a suicide mission that has much to do with love, suspense, and murder. Despite their mission being deadly and intriguing, the couple falls in love, as all young people do when in exciting situations.
Jake Singer is at loose ends in New York City, and neck deep in psychoanalysis with the outrageous Dr. Morales, when he meets the enigmatic and beautiful widow Allegra Marshall.
Two brothers suffer the death of their gambling father at the hands of a bad loser. While one studies, the other supports him by gambling and racing cars.

movie_name: The Good, the Bad and the Loser
description: The Bad discovers a golden Buddha statue floating through the countryside and wants it for himself. So does The Loser, a drunken libertine posing as a Buddhist monk, reluctantly tied to his occasional partner-in-crime The Good.

The hunters are still on Morgan Locke's trail. As the latest closes in on him he finds an unlikely ally: one of Locke's victims, out for vengeance on the powerful vampire. Three hunters, with three objectives, in the final showdown.
A freelance agent must transport a package for a mysterious employer, leading him into a web of betrayal and deceit.
Two friends, on the verge of bankruptcy, decide to rob a finance firm. To their surprise, another team of professional hit-men also attempt a heist there at the same time.
The Story about Kitano Akio competing in All Japan Road Race Championship , the International Class A 500cc class.
Agent J is a 2007 Taiwanese action romance film composed of three unrelated chapters about stories between agent J and her three boyfriends.
Twin 18-year-olds hitchhike to their mother's funeral in Spain. The journey changes their lives forever.
Two brothers named Jamar and Suwo came back to the land of Java to avenge their father, who was a Sultan, after years of exile in America.
A charming, attractive woman inadvertently causes a great disruption when she takes a job at a busy office by stealing the attention of all of her male co-workers--except the one she fancies.
An encounter specialist loses his wife because of terrorists. Later, he is sent on a mission to catch hold of a big terrorist.

movie_name: How to Use Guys with Secret Tips
description: A messed-up life's woman buys a video tape named 'How To Use Guy with Secret Tips' that will change her life forever.
In 1945, Hollywood actress Ella travels to a Nevada Divorce Ranch for 6 weeks with her young son in order to be able to marry a man she hopes she loves. Nothing is ever simple.
A young trapeze artist must decide between her lust for Sergio, the Happy Clown, or her affection for Javier, the Sad Clown, both of whom are deeply disturbed.

Ricardo, a divorced doctor, falls in love with Claudia, and tries to know her by getting close to her brother Julio César, who is also his workmate. But everyone misunderstands him, starting to suspect he's chasing Julio César.
A group of women with various criminal skills are thrown into prison during World War 2. They escape and proceed to head off to destroy a chemical lab in a well fortified valley.

Pearl has given up on her artistic pursuits. Her mundane existence is disturbed when a voice claiming to be Jesus starts speaking to her through the radio. The voice encourages her in a series sexual visions, fantasies and torments.
JESS LAPID in a daring and dangerous role that he alone can perform he jumped his way to fame and glory his acts of valor won the gratitude of his fellows.
An English Duke from 1876 is inadvertedly dragged to modern day New York where he falls for a plucky advertising executive.

The story is about 3 teenage sisters experiencing the best of teenage life but on the other side not having the attention of their father. Here comes along the girlfriend of their uncle to fix things up for them
Robin Hood decides to fight back as an outlaw when faced with the tyranny of the Sheriff of Nottingham.
Two brothers who are forced off their farm in the debt stricken mid-west become folk heroes when they begin robbing the banks that have been foreclosing on farmers.
Obituary-writer-turned-author Abby is used to making up quirky, charming characters for her books, but in Bliss those characters have sprung to life, and Abby is fantasizing about moving right in.

When terrorists plant a bomb on a commercial flight, the passengers aboard the plane must fight to keep the plane in the air and all the passengers alive: the bomb is rigged to detonate whenever the plane dips below 800 feet.

movie_name: Kishiryu Sentai Ryusoulger vs. Lupinranger vs. Patranger
description: A Gangler remnant, Ganima, captures Tyramigo and the other Kishiryu inside his safe. To save them, the Ryusoulgers chase after Ganima and come into contact with the Patrangers and Lupinrangers.
A cynical former CIA spy-turned-private investigator finds the love of his life...two weeks before her wedding.
Three brothers who are obsessed with animals are given permission from their parents to travel around America with a camera documenting wildlife.
A woman faces with herself while staying in her remote family house deep in the forest, for the first time after her child vanished in these very woods four years ago.
A pharmaceutical rep struggling to live among the elite attempts to sell a new spinal-treatment drug to poor people suffering from deformed, degenerative posture.
The Ottoman leadership entrusts Antar with the task of preventing the Pasha of Bagdad from using local leader Mustapha's united hill tribes against the Ottoman Sultan.

The daughter of Jessica Barrett discovers she is carrying a child that is growing abnormally and begins to experience the same symptoms as her mother. It is up to her family to save her from her demonic offspring.

When a terrible accident happens people die. Lily, the mother of the family, is lost in a world of anxiety and entities that haunt her life and her dreams. She has lost loved one's. Everything you believed is suddenly not true.
A detective participates with the fight club in prison after chasing a criminal who killed his fiancé.

After discovering an antique Ankh pendant, Annabeth Prescott relives moments of a past life in Ancient Egypt-including a love triangle she swears she's experiencing again. Based on the novel by Leyla Kader Dahm.
A romantic interaction between two young footballers profoundly affects one of them throughout the rest of his life and career.

When a war between the Mexican cartels breaks out, an American ex-pat is quickly thrown into the center of the violent power struggle when the daughter of a slain Narco boss enlists his help to escape to the US.

The life of a producer of popular gossip shows, suddenly changed drastically when she met a young cleric who appeared in his office to teach her religious lessons as the wish of her father as a debt favor to him.
A female gunfighter returns to a frontier town where a dueling tournament is being held, which she enters in an effort to avenge her father's death.

movie_name: Amazing Sucking Slit-Mouthed Woman is Real
description: Dressed in a coat and with her mouth ripped open, she attacks the terrified women and men. But the legendary monster is also a woman - Surrounded by numerous men, she is locked up, bound, and humiliated.

The most sensational 'media crime' investigation of history has started. In RE-EVOLUTION the flashbacks and the interrogatories weave, challenging the audience to rebuild the story of four suspects accused of having freed humanity.
Jim is a test pilot. His wife Ann and best friend Gunner try their best to keep him sober. But the life of a test pilot is anything but safe.
A young boy tries to impress a young girl hardly and he too succeeds in it. But there lies the twist, because of a single phone call.
A private investigator reads a book of sinister origins and unknowingly puts his daughter and himself in a fight for their lives...and their eternal souls.
A stately home robbery takes an evil turn one night when a gang of young thieves are caught by the owners of the house and then hunted across the estate for the proprietor's entertainment.
In Mexico City, a former CIA operative swears vengeance on those who committed an unspeakable act against the family he was hired to protect.
A man leaves a woman, a woman leaves a man. Both meet for a short while. Great changes await them at the end of this journey.
Never take your mistress on an annual guys' getaway, especially one devoted to hunting - a violent lesson for three wealthy married men.
To rekindle their love, a divorce judge orders a couple whose marriage is on the rocks to re-enact their four-day breakneck courtship.
A youth group sets out on a mission to help an elderly man save his home from being demolished. Could this house actually be haunted?
The film tells of the pursuit the federal authorities conducted upon the common people and their links with revolutionary fighters during the agrary reform.
In a lawless future, an enforcer called Ragnarok interferes in various problematic situations on different planets.
An eccentric man mistakenly locks himself out of his apartment and wanders the streets at night without his medication.
A botched wedding proposal between two small town youngsters spirals into an epic Montreal night of chaos, confusion and destiny.

After the vast majority of the world's water supply is lethally contaminated, a small group of survivors who have taken refuge near a rare clean water source are thrust into a deadly game of cat and mouse and must defend their lives from infiltrators who aren't what they seem.
In five days the world changed. As a retired Intelligence agent turned UFO investigator races to discover the fate of the human race, an alien observer searches for the human woman he loves.
A couple struggle to learn the truth about the origins of their unborn child-- a demonic entity that emerges from the body.
A war orphan invokes malicious animal spirits to take revenge on his murderous uncle. Inspired by The Kalevala, the Finnish national epic.
Meghana and Sujit both in relation and married with someone else take the same route to Vizag India from USA. As they travel together, they get to know more about each other.

A female photographer teams up with a policeman to try to bring down a corrupt police officer who framed her for drug possession and during her investigation, finds that not everything, or everyone, is what they appear to be.
After being implicated in the theft of the Jade Dragon Sword, Fan Ying is banished to the Dragon Swamp for 20 years.
This movie is the video recording of the researchs undertaken by three friends on what sounded like an urban legend.
It was inspirated by American black and white film-Cult of Cobra which was produced under the banndr Unviveral International Picture and produced by Howard Pine and directed by Francis D. Lyon.
A murderer who assumes the identity of a new deputy is unbeknownst to the sheriff planning to pin a separate murder on him.

movie_name: Oh Yaara Ainvayi Ainvayi Lut Gaya
description: The film is a love-hate-love story of a couple who file for divorce and after going out of their way to trouble their partner, they finally realise their love for each other
The London Tombs is a dark, zombie-infection horror based at the London Tombs Experience, near London Bridge.

Steve Gordon, an American agent posing as a black market operator, is in Tangier on a mission to stop the plans of three atomic scientists who are there to pool their secrets and sell them in a package to the Communists.
Raghav, who changes his identity to Abu for a reserved ticket and Priya, who impersonates her Muslim friend, meet in the train and fall in love. Things change when they realize their true identities.
A love story about the 70-year-old romance novice Sungchil, the flower seller who moves his heart Geum-nim, and the people who cheer them on.

Mayor Stiles' daughter Donna is killed the night after a lousy date with the shy Mitch. Of course this makes him the main suspect. When Mitch gets free on bail, Styles hires ex-cop Mace to follow him.

A beautiful gypsy named Yesenia has no set path in life. During a caravan trip she meets Osvaldo who is enrolled in the militia, they both fall in love despite their differences and social prejudices.
A possessive, narrow-minded ex-boyfriend and a mature, broad minded boyfriend to be. Who will Thara choose? And the mystery unravels
Set in Norway and has a crack team of Allies sent to blow up an underground Nazi factory where the Germans have taken a crashed Spitfire that contains a new radar system that the krauts want to copy.
In this mythical tale of justice and grace, rural Mississippi townsfolk shoulder the pain of generations as something wicked lurks in the enigmatic kudzu of the woods.

Jayantabhai is a street-thug and small time gangster, who unexpectedly falls in love with his enemy, who is Simrin. A romantic caper about how people unknowingly fall in love with people they least expect to.
"Punto y raya" is the story of a young Colombian recruit who, while patrolling his country's border, is befriended by a Venezuelan adversary, and the tragic consequences of their relationship.
Terrorists in the process of kidnapping a child get trapped in a house with an extremely deadly snake.
Martin is a total loser who makes a deal with the devil to become the greatest rock star in the world.
A group of rowdy co-eds throw a party at a haunted house. The resident ghost doesn't take kindly to uninvited guests and kills them off one by one throughout the night.
Javier is crushed after his new bride leaves him. When his psychiatrist has no answers, he turns to the arms of his ex-girlfriends.

A famous American tenor, relaxing on a farm near Naples and singing for pleasure in the fields, is mistaken by a lady journalist as an unknown talent she has discovered.He plays along with her and even falls in love.
Sabine" is the story of a sex slave who through perseverance overcomes adversity. But can she ever really love a man?
The daughter of his deceased girlfriend grows up to love the sculptor who has adopted her, causing a complication for his future with another woman.
A small town drama that follows two lost souls on a journey of murder, betrayal and a love that just might be powerful enough to save them both.
Two students are hired by a Hollywood film producer to shoot a horror documentary about the curse of The Wooden Devil.
A precode romantic melodrama about a burlesque dancer and a country boy who must pretend to be married.
Selina, a lethal vampire, embarks on an emotional blood-soaked journey of redemption after fatefully reuniting with her long lost human son.

movie_name: My Imaginary Friend (Aka: A Horror Film for a Pandemic)
description: A horror film composer in need of inspiration goes to his childhood summer home in France that's left him with lifelong nightmares and an imaginary friend named Alula.
Four supernatural tragedies. Drama and horror collide during the course of a day and night in the lives of ten people.

Alex, a burned out LA cyborg cop, is forced by commissioner Farnsworth to find his former cyborg partner and lover Jared who's about to deliver sensitive data to cyborg terrorists who wish to wage war against humans. Is he being played?
A woman recovering from the death of her husband suspects that her house has been invaded by demonic spirits. She summons a paranormal expert to help her get rid of them.

Jin-hong is a coldhearted prosecutor who's obsessed with catching the man who murdered his mother. He quickly becomes the prime suspect when the deceased woman returns from the grave to avenge her death.

Twelve-year-old Kareem Manning hires a criminal to scare his mom's new boyfriend -police officer James Coffee - but it backfires, forcing Coffee and Kareem to team up in order to save themselves from Detroit's most ruthless drug kingpin.
A taxi driver finds out the woman in the back of his cab is out for revenge against the man that abused her as a child: him.

movie_name: Syupeo Hong Gil-dong 8: Hong Gil-dong dosahaggyo
description: Korean folk hero Hong Kil-dong is back to save the day, this time he must team up with a fellow martial artist to take on the forces of evil that threaten the land.
The adventures of a restless martial arts student called Dragon, who, while constantly pursuing a girl, gets involved in the affairs of a gang of thieves.

Fernando, a talented chef, arrives to the village of Cadaqués during the 70s, residence of the internationally renowned Salvador Dalí. The paths of the chef and the artist will cross and cause the birth of a new culinary genius.
After the death of his wife Ethan goes down a very dark path and finds spiritual guidance and martial arts training from master chuck.
Anmol is made to work as a maid in her own house by her step-mother and step-sisters. Later, a singer falls for her and decides to free her from her evil family.
Three zombie-apocalypse survivors Cage, Grit, and Tank must go on a zombie slaying adventure across America to try to deliver an antidote to stop the zombie virus and save the human race.
The inhabitants of a small Pacific island present a formidable challenge to a sudden invasion of their territory.
American Fashion Publicist Gabby invites Paco, a talented Mexican Chef, to move with her to the USA, with the hopes of building their lives and careers together.

movie_name: I Can Get It for You Wholesale
description: A ruthless fashion designer steps on everyone in her way in order to reach the top of her profession. Eventually she is forced to choose between her ambition and the man she loves.
Post-horror comedy musical about a brilliant opera singer who hates music and gets an opportunity to revenge on all the people from her past who raised her to become a musician.
A conman disguises himself as a groom in order to con a wealthy yet a troubled businessman, later reforms his criminal ways to win his ladylove.

Tadaomy works as a loan shark. He hires Tukasa to work for him. One day, Tadaomy's debtor, Okabayashi, asks to borrow two million yen more. Tadaomy trusts Okabayashi who has payed back sincerely, but Okabayashi suddenly disappears.
An L.A. man is shocked to discover that his loving and caring elderly mother has become a vicious monster.

After international doctors are taken hostage by Nigerian rebels, a joint special ops force extract the doctors from their captors. But will they survive the vicious prehistoric jungle creature hunting them.
Three childhood friends discover their worth and inner strengths, as they experience love and being loved.
When blood and tears from three innocent victims are spilled Hell releases an unholy horde of evil carnival freaks to collect the souls of the evil doers and bring them to Hell.

movie_name: Mobile Suit Z Gundam: A New Translation - Heirs to the Stars
description: Ten years after the One Year War, Camille Bidan becomes involved in the conflict against the Titans as the pilot of Zeta Gundam.

Raised by uncaring parents, failed at school, abused as a teenager .. now it's time she took matters into her own hands. Have an unsolvable problem then give her a call .. she will fix anything for a price. The girl with no name.
A moving true story about volunteers protecting antelope against poachers in the severe mountains of Tibet.

Explores a documentary about a radio show that takes calls from people claiming supernatural experiences. Soon a caller claims that as a schoolboy, he encountered a huge-headed infant. Both the TV and radio crews investigate.
Bad blood, fraught relationships, and forbidden love enmesh three rival prominent sugar plantation families in the military era of 1990's Nigeria.
During a team-building retreat in the mountains a group of sales representatives are hunted down one by one.
A self-critical county boy must outwit the ruling class to save his ancestral home before the bank forecloses at the end of the summer.

movie_name: The Life and Times of Judge Roy Bean
description: In Vinegaroon, Texas, former outlaw Roy Bean appoints himself the judge for the region and dispenses his brand of justice as he sees fit.

The son of an island chieftain, young Kehane defiantly opposes the efforts by crooked pearl hunter Bucko Larson to invade his domain. Larson and his minions hope to dissuade our hero by introducing him to seductive Ruby.
A woman believes herself to be the reincarnated spirit of an ancient prince's lover. Meanwhile, a murderer turns out to be the reincarnated spirit of the prince himself.
Chintu Tyagi is an ordinary, middle class man who finds himself torn between his wife and another woman.
Two strangers, a man and a woman, are framed for a jewel robbery and thrown in jail. After they get out, they join forces to track down the real thieves.
Two Bachelorette parties are pitted against each other in a fight to the death to try and save their Brides-To-Be when they are trapped in sinister Mexican holiday resort.
A con man, Alex, has a girlfriend, Amanda, that is crazy for him. Unfortunately for Alex, Amanda is really crazy and will do anything to keep him.

movie_name: The Last Time I Committed Suicide
description: In 1946 Denver, an aspiring writer who enjoys irresponsible adventures with his friend writes a letter about his life before and after the suicide attempt by his sad, commitment-seeking girlfriend.
The story of brothers who grew up together at terminal named "37th tochka", dealing with a gangster crew and overcoming obstacles in life when they moved to Ulaanbator city.
24 year old Polly Marie Davis spent 186 days in the clutches of a madman. Her body was battered and broken but her will to survive never wavered.
Ronald Cheng plays a low-level Triad who is spotted by a trio of cops, who think he is really a undercover officer who has lost his memory.

Two unlikely companions embark on a perilous adventure through the badlands of an unexplored planet as they try to escape a dangerous and disorienting reality where all thoughts are seen and heard by everyone.
THIS ACTION-DRAMA INTO THE PSYCHOLOGY OF ASSASSIN, PEPE DE LUNA SACLAO, PRINCIPAL SUSPECT IN THE KILLING OF CATANDUANES GOVERNOR JUAN ALBERTO AND TARAC VICE-GOVERNOR NICOLAS FELICIANO AND HIS PILOT.
A girl is among the few survivors of a dystopian Earth. Riding a war tank, she fights against the tyranny of a mega-corporation that dominates the remaining potable water supply of the planet.
A veteran motorcycle racer does a deal with a rich industrialist to ride his specialized custom designed bike, Sidewinder 1.
A skilled mountaineer races against time to rescue his mute daughter from the clutches of human traffickers in Bulgaria.

Helen, informed of the danger which menaces an excursion train because another engine on the same track is running wild, mounts a motorcycle and speeds down the track to warn the passengers of their imminent peril.
A gang of two cronies stand by and support each other in every calamity they face, only until one of them falls for a girl and decides to marry her.

Traci, Felicia and Cinnamon have been framed and lawyer Larry Abrahams agrees to represent them if they investigate and avenge the murder of his friend Nitro. The girls go undercover at Nitro Records and use their martial arts skills.
Princess Caroline travels incognito to Stockholm and meets the Prince Birger, who also uses a fake name.
A stressed father, a bride-to-be with a secret, a smitten event planner, and relatives from around the world create much ado about the preparations for an arranged marriage in India.

A "normal" guy who is married to a hot actress gets worried that she is involved with her costar. This worry turns into jealousy and causes problems in their relationship. This is a story about trust and a comedy about the actions between men and women.

movie_name: The Flintstones in Viva Rock Vegas
description: In this live-action prequel to The Flintstones (1994), the Flintstones and the Rubbles go on a trip to Rock Vegas, where Wilma Slaghoople is pursued by playboy Chip Rockefeller.
A young girl struggles to survive after a group of home invaders break into her house to steal her family's priceless artwork.
An ex-con and thief must allude the authorities and the criminal underworld as he attempts to locate a stash of jewelry stolen by the Nazis.

From the roaring 1920s to the ruinous Spanish Civil War and Adolf Hitler's rise into power, the lives of an Irish schoolteacher, a provocative heiress and her Spanish muse are intricately interlaced, sharing the same destiny and passion.
This faux-documentary follows a butoh master, a fashion designer, and a filmmaker racing against time to create art and help a young girl in love.
At a secluded summer house, a group of teenagers are stalked by a killer who escaped from the local mental institution.
Survivors of an airplane crash find themselves within the borders of a government testing area and pursued by predators.

Prema Natakam is a 1981 Indian Telugu film, directed by SubbaRao Katta and produced by M. Sankaraiah. The film stars Murali Mohan, Sharada and Chiranjeevi in lead roles. Music of the film was composed by Chellapilla Satyam.
Judoka Marc Saint-Clair tries to save the world from nuclear disaster fighting Chinese and Russians.
He's spent decades dodging the law. He's escaped from jail twice by helicopter. He's given millions to the poor. This is the story of how Greece's most wanted man became a folk hero.
A group of college students struggle to uncover the reason they are being viciously picked off by dark beings.
In Goa, Pritam meets his love Geeta after many years. They decide to get married but the feud between their respective children creates tension in their marriage.
It is based on U.S. Marshal Mason Pollard who is specialized in engineering the fake deaths of witnesses that leaves no trace of their existence.

Two teenagers from different families, grow up to be friends and promise to always be there and protect each other. The presence of a new student makes their friendship tested with a teenage love choice.
A married couple must fight for their lives when a playful re-enactment gets taken too far after unexpected guests arrive.

The unlikely love between Luisinha, a humble girl who lives on a small pension in Lisbon, and Daniel, a wealthy aristocrat who decides to fight for the girl who loves against the prejudices of his family.

Kadir is a man victimized to his mother's black magic to separate him from every woman , including his wife , that would ever think of approaching him But things went upside down as oppose to his mother's expectations.

When a group of pleasure-seeking, All-American jocks follow an alluring, but deeply disturbed bartender to a remote island, they unwittingly fall prey to her mission to rid the world of the...                See full synopsis »
A newlywed bride becomes infatuated with another woman who questions her sexual orientation, promoting a stir among the bride's family and friends.
A young couple gets kidnapped and treated like farm animals after stopping at a roadside diner to eat meat.
A young man struggles with how to defend his people, his country, and his ideals in the wake of the Lebanese Civil War.

Six friends go on a road trip to Sin City. On the road trip they have an encounter with a UFO. Plum takes control of the situation, finding herself in the middle of it all with Jack the leader from the other planet. Dr. Hollins, Scientists Tara and Landon all try to save the world.
Professional hit-man Charlie Wolfe finds himself in three tales of murder, blackmail and revenge after a botched contract assignment.
Follows the struggle of middle-class Hong Kong immigrant John Chung making the best of his family's new American life while working as a modest fish broker in the city's infamous docklands.
Sonny Chiba is a young gambler on the run. He pretends to be an innocent student, and is taken in by an honorable Yakuza in Tokyo's Asakusa district.
A strangled prostitute is found outside the city of Mar del Plata. A detective, a journalist and a clairvoyant collaborate in a complex investigation that trigger other crimes.

Two extraordinary love stories unfold 500 years apart. As modern lovers struggle against those who seek to separate them, a Christian soldier pursues a perilous romance with a young Jewish girl in the shadows of the Spanish Inquisition.
A young naive American and a cynical older British diplomat disagree over politics in 1952 Vietnam and over a beautiful young native girl.
kamal and Afreen are married recently,they are living happily with Kamal's family.But soon Afreen's past come to haunt them.

A group of NYC adventure seekers travel to Hollow's Ridge, a supposed haunted land, only to find themselves trespassing on Native American holy land. It's there that they came face to face with a shapeshifter.

Seven friends--three women and four men--meet for dinner. Everyone must put their cell phones on the table. No matter what message comes in, anyone can read it and listen to the phone calls. However, this leads to a lot of chaos.

A US professor of archaeology and his young research team uncover a sealed ancient pagan tomb under the mausoleum of the real life Roman Emperor Domitian. This unleashes an evil deity that starts haunting people involved with the dig.

movie_name: Cats & Dogs: The Revenge of Kitty Galore
description: The on-going war between the canine and feline species is put on hold when they join forces to thwart a rogue cat spy with her own sinister plans for conquest.
Seven strangers are granted the gift of supernatural abilities by the grace of God, and must assemble to become The Seven Hands of God to watch, serve, and protect their fellow human beings.
Jesús was framed for a crime he didn't commit, he serves his sentence and then goes home to get revenge.

movie_name: Sefarad: To Be or Not to Be
description: The Edict of Expulsion of the Sephardic Jews in Spain went public with the Alhambra Decree in April 1492

A chance meeting of two morose lovers sends them spiraling down a surreal rabbit hole. Their relationship is challenged by their pasts, their futures, their perception of time, and a vampire death cult.
Danger-filled espionage adventure as Secret Agent 33 pits wits, guns and fists to foil a Commie Spy Plot of Destruction.
Tensions rise in a wealthy family when a son refuses to wed the woman of his parents' choice and instead marries a dancer/singer.

One million euro is the ransom to free Lucia, Senator Silvestri's young daughter. However, once the ransom is paid, the kidnapper asks for ten million Euro for the other ten people he is detaining: one million for every human life.
Four creatives come of age and discover who they are in a surreal, alternate version of the United States.
A private detective, a young woman, bank robbers and crooked cops all embark on a chase for a piece of paper that will lead them to three million dollars.
A group of friends flee to the mountains to escape the zombie apocalypse, but unwittingly head straight into a zombie bear attack.
A tough female ex-cop-turned-bounty hunter goes after the gang of a crazed killer who murdered her partner.

Summer, 1972. Two step-sibling youths inhabit their affluent uncle's isolated beach home while he's away. There they encounter and harbor an enigmatic drifter, with whom they form a strange, troubling bond.
A teenage rapper uses his Gran's magic powers to help him in his revenge against those who put her in the hospital.
Having a boss like Sarah makes Angga and his co-workers, Richard, Boni, and Rudi, feel like they are working under the supervision of a demon in hell.
A happily married couple embarks on a journey in an effort to overcome a tragic loss - and rekindles their love for each other.
A well-trained gangster sets out to bury the life of a crime boss, but instead digs up a painful past.

After unexpectedly, and mysteriously, inheriting his estranged grandmother's mansion, Stanley DeFeo finds himself in the small town of Amityville - surrounded by buried family secrets and a sinister plot against him.
In London in 1958, a young photographer seeks media stardom to keep the love of a beautiful, aspiring fashion designer.
A secret cabal, The Shadow, works to bring about the return of Goth Azul - the Undead God - in the rich world of SAGA, populated by elves, orcs, dwarves and dragons.

Orphan Hernan becomes a ward of a fencing master and learns to be a skilful sword fighter. He crosses swords with the ruthless, Ignacio de la Vega who will stop at nothing until he has acquired the title "maestro".

Gang boss Nick Gerro wants to distribute moonshine statewide but is frustrated when the distrustful hillbillies of Pine Flats refuse to cooperate. After one of his men, Bull Hymer, is ...                See full synopsis »
An auto driver Ranga, who fails to pass SSLC (10th Standard) even after repeated efforts. The enmity between Bomb Naga and Ranga continues and the story revolves around love, death and sentiments.
In Cold War Moscow, a female spy steals secrets from an idealistic politician - and falls in love with him.
An outcast, teenage live streamer must enlist the help of four popular kids after he discovers that a werewolf is tracking one of them in their small rural town.
A team of parapsychologists try to figure out a strange phenomenon occurring in an apartment building.

In the 1950s, a poor Georgia cotton farmer and his sons search for the gold presumably buried on the farm by their great-grandfather, but problems related to poverty, infidelity, unemployment, and booze threaten to destroy their family.

A professor of literature is retiring to her father in Parga because of a condition in her heart. Though she has to live a tranquil life without tensions and dangers, she falls in love with an Athenian architect.
Before heading off to college, an overthinking teenager asks out a former girlfriend in an effort to reconnect and hold on to his past.

Several individuals consult a marriage bureau, including a peer of the realm, his butler, a lonely school teacher, a French girl on the run, a country vicar and a newspaper reporter sent by his editor to do an undercover story.

During a hot summer somewhere in the early-1980s Athenian urban jungle, three friends experiment with a difficult love triangle. Will their ambivalent feelings and the unbearably lingering identity crisis consume them?
A week in the life of a Mexican short order cook who travels home to Tijuana on Sunday to see his family.
An American horror writer, haunted by childhood nightmares, moves to an old mansion in Italy with her husband and young son only to discover the nightmares were real.
A light hearted comedy, from the thirties. One of the most successful ones in Hungary. The ever enchanting story of a beautiful girl falling in love with a rich man.
Tells the story of the 108 Heroes who stood up against a corrupt government. Each hero has his own unique fighting skill, but they are all willing to die to uphold justice.
A sewage worker gets trapped inside a septic tank during a water contamination crisis and undergoes a hideous transformation.

movie_name: You Can't Take It with You
