description: The son of a snobbish Wall Street banker becomes engaged to a woman from a good-natured but decidedly eccentric family, not realizing that his father is trying to force her family from their home for a real estate development.
In 1589, six innocent women were accused from the inquisition of witchery in the small ligurian mountain.
Eve and Charlie are having a baby, but they're no longer together. After years of history and months of separation Charlie and Eve have 24 hours to find out whether they have a future together.
A romantic comedy set in the world of battle re-enactments, about an irresponsible guy who has to shape up in order to win back his wife.

movie_name: Frankfurt: The Face of a City
description: Girl goes to the bright lights of Frankfurt when her boyfriend goes into the army; the seamy side of life is not as attractive as she expected.
THIS SEX-FANTASY MOVIE TELLS THE STORY OF A TOAD WHO TRANSFORMS INTO A GORGEOUS WOMAN AND THE YOUNG MAN WHO PROTECTS AND FALLS IN LOVE WITH HER.
Marty is the host of a deadly game show called Run. Die. Kill!, but when he is chosen to play his own game, he comes face to face with the ruthless world he has helped create.

movie_name: The Girl at the End of the World
description: Katie and Dan are in a long distance relationship but when a catastrophic event knocks out all technology, they must find a way across oceans and land to be with each other at the end of the world.

movie_name: Kamen Rider Super Den-O Trilogy: Episode Yellow - Treasure de End Pirates
description: Ryotaro and the Imagins find themselves in November 2008, where the DenLiner is stolen by Kaitou Daiki, Kamen Rider Diend. As Daiki tracks his past self, he faces off with Time Police officer Reiji Kurosaki, aka Kamen Rider G Den-O.
Five teenagers frantically run for refuge down into a basement. They barricade themselves inside as they are being hunted down by an insane killer upstairs.
A group of warriors prepared their whole lives for an apocalypse that never happened, and now they must find their way to fit into society.

Rajveer, an aspiring police officer is given a task to save Abbas from a cold blooded criminal Nazeer. Though Abbas and Rajveer hate each other but realizing the tragedy behind his parents death brings them closer.
After their executions are faked by the authorities, three criminals are forced to become assassins under the Shogun's command

Lida sells modern real estate developments to the new middle class in Phnom Penh. Her relationship with her boyfriend is deteriorating so she escapes to the beach, but finds there that the specters from the past haunt in sublime ways.
Two couples in their twenties, who are struggling to find substance and meaning in their lives and relationships, meet by happenstance in a New York City Irish tavern called The Four-Faced Liar.

An FBI agent tries to foil a domestic terror plot, only to find out that the director of the agency is intimately involved with the terrorists. Through a high level informant he discovers that the terrorists get money from Silicon Valley.
A seaman on board a sailing ship battles mutinous crew members, a corrupt millionaire trying to take over the ship and falls in love with a girl who turns out to be his adopted sister.
Rush week turns unexpectedly hellish when a band of sadistic, masked, homicidal maniacs holed up in an abandoned warehouse wreak havoc on a bunch of not-so-innocent college kids.
After spending their teenage years incarcerated in a youth facility, Tonya Gault, Dianne Mitchell, Laureen Graddy, and Carla Ochoa, rediscover each other later in life on opposite sides of the law.

Marco, Mario and Filippo are friends have a great passion in common, flying. They attend the Air Force Academy of Caserta to become pilots, with the ongoing war and the risk of being called into action.
The two young people, who started to get to know each other, decide to meet face to face after long letters. The woman sends her sister instead of herself.
The East Side Kids uncover the body of a murder victim, but must protect the innocent girl accused of the crime.

From absolute poverty to absolute power! "El Don" is the saga of a common man with uncommonly fierce ambition who rises to rule an empire of unspeakable evil only to discover that the love he thought he had forgotten still rules what is left of his heart.
An exiled band of Hell's Angels strike a bargain with the Sheriff of a local town, let them stay and the town is safe. But a local girl strays into their lair and sparks off a full scale Angel war.

A clown of the street falls in love with a girl with tuberculosis, and, trying to find a way to cure her, he takes her to a monastery. The clown returns to the street performances with the dream of meeting with the girl again.

A man (Micheal) searches for his legacy, a way to be remembered forever. In a time of desperate financial trouble, a mysterious stranger shows up with an answer to Micheal's needs. Desperate and curious, he accepts.
The music band Revolution Z goes on their first tour by the sea coast, joined by their new vocalist, prominent Bulgarian singer Geri-Nikol, who has seriously annoyed everyone else in the group.
Lee Lien-ying is an eunuch who enters the Forbidden City with a big secret. One that will have his head on the floor if the wrong people find out.
A stalwart Spanish soldier turns to a life of crime to prove his love for a mysterious and promiscuous gypsy woman.
Charles Wilcox III finds himself on the street after the death of his Grand Dad. His anxiety disintegrates into complete madness, pulling others with him into a deadly encounter with an ancient evil.
Recently divorced Adriana tries to get revenge on the woman who took her husband away from her by going on a European cruze along with them.
While reporting on a missing girl, a young journalist becomes entangled in the world of the deep web, where nothing and no one is as they seem.
Two lovers meet one night at the door of a wake and begin to walk together. The route will oscillate through different spaces until the night becomes day.

When Sid's friend goes missing, he and new girl Sarah investigate disappearances in their tower block. Uncovering the secret of a vengeful ghost possessing a horde of zombies, they must fight for their lives - and their souls.

As WWII rages on, a group of Nazi paratroopers land on the hidden city of Palandria to exploit its wealth, and they start taking hostages. Can Tarzan, the powerful King of the Jungle, and his trusted companions, Cheeta and Buli, save them?

Shy girl Molly is having a party. She is inviting her school bullies and has planned one hell of a night. After a party trick goes horribly wrong, each guest is forced into a macabre game of life and death by an ancient demon who forces them to tell horrifying stories.
Nefeli moves to her boyfriend's flat. After a while she discovers that strange hallucinations invade her life.

movie_name: Woman Chasing the Butterfly of Death
description: A depressed young man crosses paths with a woman who commits suicide, a book salesman obsessed with the will to live, a resurrected female corpse, and a archaeologist and his unstable artist daughter, in a fantasy tale of life and death.
Bumi then becomes Instant Champ, who has strength and superiority after being injected with the serum. When the serum disappears, Bumi is back into a mediocre man.

After Caitlin is stalked by a killer who is known on the internet as Smiley, she gets help from her friends to uncover his origin story. After learning about Smiley's origins they realize their mistake as Smiley hunts down.
Superb swordplay film, depicting more daring swordplay and acts of chivalry from the debonair swordsman, Third master. This film is based on the novel by prolific writer of Wuxia Ku Lung.
Three young men flee Hong Kong after stealing diamonds from oppressive older gangsters and attempt to hide with friends in Paris, but professional hitmen peruse them relentlessly throughout France.
When Casey is infected by a murderous demon, Meadow, her best friend, is forced to figure out how to exorcise the creature while keeping them both out of jail and the insane asylum.

Jun Jie and Xiao Yue have been together for almost 10 years. They made a pact to get married on their 10th anniversary. Now Jun Jie wants to break up. Xiao Yue agrees but with one condition. He has to find her a groom for the wedding.

Shabnam is an ambitious girl who wants to be a dancer. Her mother was also a great dancer but her father Tony is against it. Then comes Rahul in her life like a storm with a proposition to allow Shabnam to take part in dance competitions.

Teenager Yun Yue lived in the world for three hundred years. And the master of fox clan Bai Chen can fly back to heaven and become immortal. The encounter of them, made the predestined relationship be covered by mysterious veil.
About an American's reaction to the Danes' way of chatting about one another behind their backs. A rumor begins to flourish. A serious one. About death. perhaps even murder.
Ramji, an acclaimed music director, is impressed with Reena's singing prowess and gives her an opportunity to sing in his movie. However, things take a turn when Reena's true identity is revealed.

An impoverished woman who has been forced to choose between a privileged life with her wealthy aunt and her journalist lover, befriends an American heiress. When she discovers the heiress is attracted to her own lover and is dying, she sees a chance to have both the privileged life she cannot give up and the lover she cannot live without.

movie_name: A Boy. A Girl. A Dream.
description: On the night of the 2016 Presidential election, Cass, an L.A. club promoter, takes a thrilling and emotional journey with Frida, a Midwestern visitor. She challenges him to revisit his broken dreams - while he pushes her to discover hers.
Four unlikely assassins genuinely care about their customers and victims, meanwhile a prosecutor is on their trail.

When an airplane lands in Los Angeles after sending a radio request for police and medical aid, one of the passengers, matronly Mrs. Judd, tells Police Inspector Bruce what happened: After ...                See full synopsis »
When DEA agents are taken captive by a ruthless South American kingpin, the Delta Force is reunited to rescue them in this sequel to the 1986 film.

This sequel to "Yossi and Jagger" finds Dr. Yossi Gutmann reminiscing about his love ten years after his death. When he encounters a group of young soldiers, one of them, Tom, reignites his romantic feelings.
A progressive town erupts when a traveling rodeo lands within its city limits and the councilman's daughter falls in love with the cowboy.
L.A. shop owner Dana and Englishman Sean meet and fall in love at first sight, but Sean is married and Dana is to marry her business partner Alex.

Toño y Cirio son agentes viajeros que trabajan en una funeraria repartiendo ataudes en su camioneta "El último traje" tratando de sobrevivir a las diferentes aventuras que les depara el camino. Música, acción, romance y mucha comedia.
Although they live married lives, two strangers keep running into each other, starting a friendship that could blossom into so much more.
As Bidin tries to convince his Thai girlfriend's family to let him marry her, he also has to settle an issue between him and an old enemy of his.
After finding out about the brutal murder of his fiancé, Shavar seeks revenge against a masked killer with a penchant for yard work weaponry. Fall will be the season of fear.
Based on a Malay folklore about a vampire who emerges after the death of a woman during childbirth, the 'pontianak'.
Selma, who wants to learn the truth, starts to investigate her husband Kemal's past. She will encounter things she never expected.
Anna, a young 8-year-old girl, begins to have unexplained nightmares; as they intensify, the family turns to their local priest for help.
Kao is given a mission by his elderly master to take a cursed sword and solve petty squabbles between skilled martial masters.
A woman tries to help her twin sister, with whom she has a strong connection, recover from a trauma. But weird things surround their lives.

Car racer Burn 'em Up Barnes, son of a wealthy manufacturer, leaves home to make his own way in the world. After being robbed by hoodlums, Barnes joins a group of hobos who take him in and show him the carefree life.
After moving into their new home, Eric and Jane Marshall discover a dark and deadly inhabitant still roams the hallways of their vintage home.

A lazy, incompetent middle school teacher who hates her job, her students, and her co-workers is forced to return to teaching to make enough money for breast implants after her wealthy fiancé dumps her.

movie_name: Untitled Callumny Films Female Lead Project
description: What happens when a tale of a myth becomes reality? A lesson in the perils of myth-making and myth-makers.
Mr. Wu, a Hong Kong movie star, is kidnapped by four unpredictable criminals disguised as police officers. Will he get rescued?
A gifted, but self-destructive street racer struggles to redeem himself in an effort to save his mother, and himself from tragedy.

Seventeen year old Elizabeth and her younger sister, Sam, are thrust into circumstances more terrifying than living with their abusive, alcoholic mother when they are forced to move into their deceased Grandfather's house.

An overworked movie star and his stunt double exchange identities and lives so he can get a much needed break, but when the movie star is taken hostage by a ruthless cartel, it's up to his stunt double to bring him back alive.

Part Three, the big battle. The blind fortune teller and his crew, Tiger and the Japanese brother and sister prepare to battle The Grandmaster, Devil Mask, and Infinite Ninjas. There's a battle every minute with epic weapons!
An ex-NYPD officer-turned-sheriff of a small rural Georgia town has to contend with a gang of thieves who have taken a wealthy doctor hostage.

Two buddies inadvertently get involved with the mob, and start working for them. Then one of them falls for the daughter of a land owner that they're supposed to be extorting money from, and they turn against their bosses.
Deep in the Ellsworth Mountains of Antarctica, an unauthorized military installation must shut down its' secret mission of keeping a behemoth creature alive for scientific study.
Rick and Fred, two husbands who are having difficulty in their marriages, are given a Hall Pass by their wives: for one week, they can do whatever they want.
In september 2012, four film students disappeared while making a documentary in an abandoned building in downtown Mexico city. This is the footage recovered from the shooting.

movie_name: Red and White III: Hearts of Freedom
description: The third and final movie of "Red and White" trilogy and set during the Indonesian revolution in 1947-1948, as a band of guerrillas fight for Indonesia's freedom on land, sea, and air against the Dutch empire.
Follows a group of five teens heading off to a cabin for a "romantic" weekend. They are hunted down by The Lashman for being unruly teens and disturbing his peace.

Dara Singh plays the mythological Samson character to the hilt as he must contend with a love starved princess and her all female warriors, a sorcerer and his magical dwarfs, a dinosaur sized lizard, and a rebel in love with a hand-maiden.

After escaping a freak accident, Mahesh witnesses strange events in his new house. He feels that these are paranormal events. Whether the accident is caused these or other way around? Can he solve this puzzle before everything falls apart?

Srimanthudu is a 1971 Indian Telugu film, directed by K. Pratyagatma and Produced by G. Radhakrishna Murthy. The film stars Akkineni Nageswara Rao and Jamuna in lead roles. The music of the film was composed by T. Chalapathi Rao.
Eric feels his life falling apart -- until Fyodor Dostoevsky's naked (and hairless) reincarnation enters his apartment and helps him find true love.
Three best friends spy on their families, sneak into each other's house, and organize elaborate pranks.

In a small New Mexico town, teenager Hilary gets into her first fender bender and innocently exchanges her personal information with the other driver, a terrifying and bizarre serial killer who stalks the country road for his next victims.
French Army Colonel Raspeguy leads his paratroopers in battle against the Communist Viet Minh in Indochina and against Algerian guerrilla during the Algerian War.
Searching for stability and justice, Timur "The Lame" becomes a world conqueror in order to unify all people, nations, and tribes under one banner.
A man tries to uncover an unconventional psychologist's therapy techniques on his institutionalized wife, amidst a series of brutal murders.
Upon arriving in a small town where she has inherited a rundown mansion, a famous horror hostess battles an evil uncle, and townspeople who want her burned at the stake.

In late 1800s England, Jude plans to go to the city and attend university but marries early and becomes a stonemason. When his wife leaves, he moves to the city, where he befriends his liberal cousin Sue.
A couple fights to hold their relationship together as a memory loss virus spreads and threatens to erase the history of their love and courtship.
Based on a legend from India, Sejon sets out to rescue Chungchu who was abandoned in hell by her husband.

The fight of the protagonist and his group S.E.E.S. with the strange monsters called 'Shadows' is getting closer to the end. Makoto and his allies engage in life-or-death battles with Shadows in order to end the Dark Hour.
A weekend camping trip takes a turn for the worst when a group of college students unknowingly desecrate a sacred Indian burial ground.
Unconditional love: Crown princess Mireille is obsessed with testing loyalty of potential suitors - using her little sister Angelique as a decoy, judge and executioner if they fail.

As change sweep Japan, an honest man joins the Shinsengumi out of respect for their leader and because he wants to live and die as a samurai. However, as his involvement goes, reality and idealism come into deadly conflict.

movie_name: Cris De Niro: The Watchman of Ephraim
description: Cris De Niro and his new counter-terrorism firm, The Watchman Agency unknowingly become targets when they stumble on a connection between a rich Iranian businessman and a drug cartel plotting a terrorist attack more catastrophic than 9/11.

On a trip to her hometown, workaholic Ally reminisces with her ex Sean and starts to question everything about the person she's become. Things only get more confusing when she meets Cassidy, who reminds her of the person she used to be.
Based on the 1995 novel "The Children of the Dead" by unorthodox author Elfriede Jelinek. About the mental repression of the Holocaust in post-war Austria, with zombie children.
Scotland Yard is after a homicidal maniac called The Blue Hand, which is what he uses to kill his victims.
A trio of desperate criminals break into the isolated country house of an elderly goldsmith and his wife. But their chosen targets turn out to be far less defenseless than they seem.
A cross-cultural romance and an intercultural friendship between Ram, Rosy and Anu goes through a roller coaster ride of love, laughter and misunderstandings.
Bobby Samuels risks his life when he escapes jail to find the only family he has left in the world... His little sister Scarlett.
The world's most notorious heiress and bachelorette is kidnapped from the Italian countryside. Will she survive the ordeal?
Michael Mourer is a family man and a successful Realtor. However his current listing could be his last as he is unexpectedly black mailed with a harsh time restraint.
A Phoenix secretary embezzles $40,000 from her employer's client, goes on the run and checks into a remote motel run by a young man under the domination of his mother.

Broken Gardenias is a Dark Comedy about Jenni, an orphaned semi-savant, who with the help of a street hustler named Sam, steal a car and head to Los Angeles to find Jenni's, father whom she hasn't seen or heard from since she was 6.

After escaping a cult suicide, a paraplegic hospital patient is tormented by malevolent spirits and cursed to kill whomever hears her voice, unless she offers up the soul of her innocent nephew in place of her own.

movie_name: May the Devil Take You Too
description: Two years after escaping from demonic terror, the young woman is still haunted by unnatural vision. The dangers that await her and her friends are increasingly threatening: the figure of darkness rises to take their lives.
On Audrey's 40th birthday, her brother is marrying a girl he met in France. Secrets are revealed prior to the wedding. Audrey and the young, French fiancee do NOT get along.
Anti-Romantic-Comedy starts where most rom-coms end - then gets real. Four funny flawed fierce females discover what they don't know: about themselves, their families and Western Civilization.
A physicist who invents a time machine must travel back to the past to uncover the truth about his creation and the woman who is trying to steal it.
A country doctor discovers the fountain of youth, but his curiosity is clouded by addiction and the results are deadly.

movie_name: Prince Nezha's Triumph Against Dragon King
description: Tells the fable from Chinese mythology about the young warrior Nezha who takes on a group of evil dragons.
A guy takes his friends to the somewhat secluded wilderness of Scotland in the search for the paranormal. And they find some pretty spooky stuff.

Jacob Webber is going to die. With an incurable disease, he refuses to accept that his life is almost over. Running from the truth, Jacob enters a taxi cab. Little does he know, the cab is a rolling deathtrap and now its kill or be killed.
When his father is killed in a train wreck, Larry Baker vows to unmask a mysterious criminal called "The Wrecker," who has targeted the L&M Railroad for deadly" accidents."

A playboy's encounter with a woman in the National Library's elevator gets complicated. His invitation to the next meeting was accepted with the riddle she gave him. The answer to the riddle is the time and place of their next meeting.

Teen runaway Libertaria escapes a genetics factory and teams up with her addict father to rescue her adoptive mother from the evil Collective in this post-apocalyptic animated musical by award-winning composer Sabrina Pena Young.
A team of historic preservationists documenting evidence to save an old plantation unwillingly uncovers the voodoo mysteries behind its walls.
A married man and a free spirit find love - and tragedy - in this powerful, bittersweet gay love story that was inspired by a real-life 1997 hate crime.
Hu Bolin is man struggling for survival with his baby in a zombie plagued apartment block. He thinks they are the last survivors there until he meets Li Yue and rescues her from zombie attacker.
A playboy adventure novelist joins his publisher on an expedition to Voodoo Island in the Caribbean, where a cancer researcher is being forced to turn the tribes-people into zombies.
Set in the 1930s, the film tells the tale of a series of strange murders revolving around a pair of embroidered shoes.

A group of underprivileged local school kids go against all odds to form a soccer team to compete in the JG Davidson Cup tournament to fight the reigning champion - the highly privileged British school, St James.

Anthology features three family-friendly fantasy-horror tales; "Sleeping Beauty", "Zombies" and "Querubin: Maria Leonora Theresa." It's an adaptation of the radio drama series written by Severino Reyes, which was popular in the 1950s.
A young man is guided by his mother in a methodical manner to avenge his father against the perpetrators who falsely accused and killed him.
An origin story set on Cybertron, home of both the Autobots and the Decepticons. The film is said to focus on the relationship between Optimus Prime and Megatron
When the small fishing town of Martino Bay is rocked by a series of brutal killings, film composer Lewis Kerwin finds himself at the centre of the investigation.

movie_name: Bastard Son of a Thousand Fathers
description: A doctor-turned sociopath develops the ultimate, addictive, illegal drug and will stop at nothing to get it in the hands of 'customers'.

A mysterious creature carrying a highly new contagious strain of the rabies virus infects a teen age girl and it's up to her uncle to hunt down and find the creature in hopes of saving is niece and before the it unleashes a new epidemic.
Marseille. Heaps of flowers and funeral wreaths... "A man who no longer defends his colors is no longer a man."
A family finds that the refrigerator in their kitchen is a gateway to Hell, and they must battle a witch.
Television lose viewers, making YouTube begin to be seen more, generating a war between internet and television figures for trying to get a briefcase with vital information about YouTube.

After drinking his pal's science experiment, an everyday guy realizes his body now has the ability to regenerate after any kind of injury. Deciding he will use his power for good, he quickly learns that fighting crime isn't so easy.

A young, married couple move into the wife's aunt's estate after inheriting the sprawling property. Soon, weird occurrences begin to happen around the house, and they start to suspect the tenants are responsible.

Evan Hanson is the best motocross coach in the country. After leading his daughter Callie to the national championships, he decides to set his sights on a more personal challenge - saving a local dirt track from a motorcycle gang.
Nick Black A Serial Killer From Plymouth Has Came Back On The Radar After Going Into Hiding For 4 Years Since That Time He has Now Found A Girlfriend Who Just As Dangerous As Him.
A schizophrenic housewife kills off each of her terrorizing apparitions, unsure if these demons are merely figments of her imagination or part of reality.
Jake has to go to brother's wedding in Hawaii. He hires a bride to pretend he's engaged as his brother is marrying his ex. Anna the rental bride falls for Jake.

Santhosh and Nayana are both creative directors at an advertising agency.Nayana is straight forward and believes in hard work,Santhosh is just the opposite.What happens if these two contradicting personalities fall in love with each other?

movie_name: Story of Kale: When Someone's in Love
description: Dinda is saved by Kale from her toxic relationship with Argo. Dinda and Kale then have a relationship together. The relationship that start out beautiful, turned into a new nightmare.
Seenu - Ravi Teja, is fondly called as Dubai Seenu. His sole aim in life is to fly to Dubai and earn tonnes of money. In the process, he gets hold of a broker and gets duped by him in Mumbai.
About Nazife, a fishing woman who loves Bahriyeli Ahmet. Nazife cooks and sells fish to support her family. Ahmet and Nazife love each other, but they are to poor to get married.
A nurse begins a new job at an old dark house and finds herself reluctantly working for a mysterious mad doctor preparing a dangerous experiment in order to cure himself of acromegaly.
Two elite fighters who survive an apocalypse, now have to survive as escaped slaves in a new world, with a shared goal to free themselves and their families.
When two drug-addicted lovers attempt to move to California and start a clean life, demons from the past force them to fight for what they know is right.

Chuad meets Tonliw and falls in love with the TV show host. That's when he decides to seek the help of Pen, Tonliw's best friend. Pen's also got her own set of problems in the form of a controlling doctor boyfriend.
A failed singer in Los Angeles gets caught up with a secret society and faces danger beyond her comprehension.
A group of young adults on a humanitarian trip to Mexico encounter a village with a demonic secret that causes them to face realities they never knew existed.
Two ambitious girls, despite their parents' wishes, have their hearts set on careers in professional football.
After inheriting her grandfather's house, a young woman must confront the mystery of his sudden death and the evil that hides inside.
Feature film based on the popular video game centering on a squad of U.S. Army Special Forces soldiers with state-of-the-art weapons.
On a vacation to Paris, a young photographer meets and falls for a French girl who invites him to experience more of what France has to offer.

Es una película con un método totalmente novedoso y experimental. El mismo no se refiere solamente a la parte técnica, sino especialmente a la argumental, donde la realizadora enfrentó el ...                See full synopsis »
The descendants of Baron Frankenstein return to the family castle to search for the family fortune that is supposed to be hidden there.
Ifenkili is a crude village goat herder who doesn't care about being picture perfect for her lover. However, this could make her lose him to the daughter of his wealthy employer.
A rich teenager hooks up with a group of street kids and experiences the time of his life in this fast-moving action.
Explores the journey to the underworld of suffering body dysmorphic disorder and how it becomes potentially quite addictive.
Follows a married couple as they go on a camping trip to try to overcome a rough spot in their relationship.

A Romeo-and-Juliet kind of love affair. The difference here is what sets the two lovers apart: their soccer teams. Being a fan of Corinthians, Romeu has to fake he really likes Palmeiras, in order to gain Julieta's heart.

An unscrupulous filmmakers documentary is the catalyst that unites five diverse yet intimately connected people, as they are each forced to re-examine the myth of the Monster from their ...                See full synopsis »
Multi talented Cho wants to learn from the God of Gamblers and contacts his disciple. They are attacked by a crime boss with a plan to misuse GoG's good name to make millions.
Combining action, comedy and sci-fi, Kampung Drift is a cross-genre coming-of-age tale of Johan, a teenager in search of the meaning of life and love through drift racing.
A man who travels in the past has met by chance a woman who travels in the present at Khaosan Road, in Bangkok, Thailand and becomes a porter of her and leaves the road together.
A golf-crazy songwriter tries to avoid the long, solitary hours of concentration needed to produce a hit musical. His producer and his secretary conspire to get him back on track.
Young James Adams joins CHERUB, a top-secret branch of the British Secret Service that recruits orphan children, training them to work as spies. Charles Henderson Espionage Research Unit B
The film revolves around Prakash and his four friends, they get addicted to watching porn videos. In that daze, they rape their own college mate Swathi.
András, the struggling screenwriter one day wakes up to find his girlfriend replaced by a different girl, who acts like nothing happened.

After her birthday party, ad executive Michelle finds herself caught between cheerful Tony, dreamy Bill, youthful Jeb, and rich Tiger. Overwhelmed with stress, another complication quietly forms in her life.
23 People are transported to surreal realities after accepting a call from a mysterious number - but can they return ?
Three females from a private detective agency are hired to find out what happened to a man who went missing while scuba diving.
Four very different college girls drive to Fort Lauderdale, Florida for spring break and seek out various adventures and romance for themselves.
An enslaved, black African man's quest for freedom thrusts him to the forefront of ancient Japanese society as a Samurai warrior who fights to reunify a country rife with despots and warring clans.
A small town is terrorized by a mysterious killer who only strikes during a full moon. The police won't believe just who, or WHAT, that killer is... A ferocious MAN-WOLF!
An Iraqi war veteran with PTSD and his naïve martial arts students get mixed up with mobsters and dirty cops.

movie_name: The Soul of the Murdered Kingdom by Wiktor Grodecki
description: A Polish war Captain rejoins his reconnaissance on a Caribbean island occupied by Napoleon's sister, Pauline Bonaparte and is stricken by controversial power struggles with the local population.
A cold and mysterious character working at a cash truck company responsible for moving a lot of money around Los Angeles each week.
After attending a funeral of a parents a group of close friends realize they may have only 20 summers left to travel and find romance.
A Rich kid were goes for exile for two months for his family conditions to take over their business. What is the circumstances he faced while in exile ? What shows impact on his life ?
During a family reunion in 2000, guests decide to read out laud their "where i see myself in 10 years" wish lists which they wrote down during their 1990 family reunion.

When her sister dies in 1846, Bette moves from the château to Paris to work as a theater seamstress. She helps a handsome, starving artist. When her niece lures him away from her, she plans a devious revenge.
During one of Oregon's most violent storms, a young cellist seeks solitude and comfort in the safety of her large apartment, but soon realizes she might not be home alone.
The life of Ahmet, who is approaching death step by step, becomes completely different when he meets doctor Zeynep while investigating a murder.

Shafeek's father wanted him to become a chef, but he chose to serve his country instead. On his annual leave from work, Shafeek, now a young soldier, must deal with his family, his bride to be and a gang involved in illegal activities.
A woman, unhappy with her fiancé, travels to Italy to find her true love; and all she knows about him is his name.
Sabata helps a band of Mexican revolutionaries steal a wagon-load of gold from the occupying Austrian forces of Emperor Maximilian I.
In 1986, a 10 year old boy with autism escapes a mental institution to go find his here, a declining rock radio host, to help him find and kill god.

Thomas Bezug, the richest man in the world, is a solitary, domineering and cruel cripple who hardly can move on his crutches. He dwells a fanatical love for his son, whom he holds like a monkey in a cage.

Retired boxer Trigger McSquarejaw must join the world of fighting to support his son's LDS mission but risk falling back into a life that distanced him from his son -- all the while claiming what made him feel alive in the past.
Rennie Cray (Caviezel) embarks on a bloodthirsty rampage to avenge the death of his wife who was struck down by a serial killer - a man who hunts and kills women using his '72 El Dorado.
After breaking off a long-term friendship and seeking refuge in an Instant Messenger server to get her first kiss, Alissa Bradley's life begins to spiral.
In a dark and cold Helsinki, an unlucky taxi driver Veli-Matti struggles to maintain relationships with his children and estranged wife. Sometimes, losing everything is just a beginning.
An American fashion photographer and his entourage start behaving in a completely different way than usual when they visit an island paradise, where they experience passion and ancient rituals.

Su Can, born into a family of officers and had a love for martial arts since he was a child. When he goes to the capital to get the martial arts exam, he gets framed with banned drugs, leading to the destruction of his family.

Siddharth strives to help flood victims and saves the relief material from falling into the wrong hands. This sets off a war between him and a corrupt politician, which leads to many twists and turns.
An ex-Professional kick-boxer, hooked on heroin, is offered a chance to resurrect his fighting career by entering an illegal Street Fight competition.
A Manson-style cult uses a long-lost "Fab Four" song to jump-start the zombie Helter Skelter. A popular radio DJ plays the song inadvertently creating a flesh eating zombie in a walrus costume.

A young card player tries his luck in a back-alley poker game attended by the higher-ups from various crime families in London, but complications arise, when the stakes are raised higher than he had intended, or is it all part of the plan?
A mysterious nomad known as the "Artist" practices a dark art form passed down through the generations.
Two belligerent college students accidently reactivate a toxic wishing well, setting off a series of events that brings havoc to a small community.
An editor is hired to make sense of endless hours of security camera footage, footage that may have captured the brutal killings at 641 Vail St.
Tired of being a push over, Curt Mummer creates an alter ego, that helps him stand up for himself, and others.
After trying to cover up a car accident that left a man dead, a crooked homicide detective is stalked by a mysterious man claiming to have witnessed the event.
While searching for his enemy in Istanbul, Murat meets a woman named Zeynep. However, the emergence of Bekir causes Murat and Zeynep's happiness to be left unfinished.

Nick and Charlie (Peter Falk and Charles Durning) are two crooks that rob Harry Winston's jewelry store. Nick portrays a rich elderly brother and sister by using prosthetics and make-up to con the manager.
A small Indian village is terrorized by terrorist Kalanag, who wants to destroy the country and become its ruler.

Markus goes home to his teenage daughter, Mathilde, when his wife dies in a train crash. All appears to be a tragic accident until a mathematics geek, who was also a fellow passenger on the train, and his two colleagues show up.

American Gothic horror story, but then different. Severe camera and shadowy lighting dominate in this story about a family of poverty-stricken nobility that takes it all out on a 19th-century plantation. Outside evil is afoot.

movie_name: A Ton of Grass Goes to Pot
description: A group of friends plans to smuggle a ton of marijuana from Mexico to the U.S. by using a hot-air balloon.

movie_name: You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger
description: Sally's parents' marriage breaks up when her father undergoes a mid-life crisis and impulsively weds a prostitute. Meanwhile, Sally's own marriage also begins to disintegrate.
Eddie Grant is a radio station sound-effects man whose honeymoon takes a turn for the worse when they discovers the corpse of a program producer in in their honeymoon suite.
A desperate woman hires the world's worst method actor to pose as her boyfriend, as she goes home for the Chinese New Year.
A white-collar worker goes through a bittersweet life after she broke up with her ex-boyfriend, and eventually gets her true love.

Augusto is a very successful businessman whose whole life revolves around his family. After a disturbing vision of a demonic prophecy, his perfect life enters a spiral of paranoia, violence and terror.
Depicts bizarre phenomena on the set of a drama that reenacts ghost stories, presented as behind-the-scenes footage.

Rose comes from a military family with lots of rules and structure. She winds up in an abusive marriage married to the son of the local mob godfather. Unable to escape, she calls her dad for help, who is ready for war.
A surgeon, feeling guilty over his daughter's facial disfigurement, for which he was responsible, kidnaps young women in an attempt to fix his daughter's face. Remake of the classic 1960 horror film.

In desperate need for cash for his son's custody battle, a blue collar father is enticed by a loose cannon friend to embark upon a no one gets hurt kidnap for ransom plot of a hedge fund owner and his asthmatic pregnant wife.

The routine of an inept apprentice gravedigger changes when a new employee arrives at the cemetery. Together they must locate abandoned graves, but strange events make them think about the implications of tampering with the dead.
A disillusioned junkie veteran gets unwillingly caught up in the chaos surrounding two Chinese immigrants, and the debt they owe a crime boss.

Mermer Family lives a double life working at their family owned restaurant while being undercover assassins for an international organization. After their secret is revealed, this dysfunctional family needs to work together to survive.
After teenage Fiona witnesses her mother's brutal murder, she runs away, befriending a rebellious loner who triggers her need to release the demon within.
A young woman running an animal sanctuary in the outback takes her revenge on a trio of kangaroo hunters who terrorized her.
Doc is an intern who has been invited by the United Nations' Children Fund, along with his fellow interns, to a deserted area in Sichuan to run physicals for poor children.
The life of one of the world's most renowned hackers is in danger after he develops an app that can hack any social media account and get any information using just a phone number.
Mary is an impetuous romantic who marries British aristocrat Lord Philip Rexford on a whim. Their marriage is successful, though, and they grow closer over the years.

Sweety meets Sanjay and both fall in love with each other. After dating for a while, they attend to a party where Sweety gets to see the true colors of an intoxicated and flirtatious Sanjay, making her wonder if he really is her true love.
A brash stranger and his sheep arrive in a small town, but not soon after, the townspeople decide they've seen enough of him.
Elsa returns home to visit her "dying" father, and Seth does his best to open his mind to new cultures as these two love birds learn a new side of each other.
A 36-year old detective falls in love with a nihilistic 19-year old shop-lifter and wonders if the relationship which develops can last.

movie_name: The World, the Flesh and the Devil
description: A miner trapped in a cave-in resurfaces, and upon discovering mankind has been wiped out in a nuclear holocaust, sets out to find other survivors.

Set in London, Kathryn Miles's marriage is threatened when she discovers her husband's longstanding affair with her best friend but surprises everyone when she uses it to create a new life for herself.
A man hides his true identity from a girl in order to marry her. But she soon learns the truth and demands a divorce. The situation gets tricky when she finds out that she is pregnant.
A group of Rogue Angels assigned to deliver damned souls to hell turn dark, becoming executioners of mankind before they have the opportunity to repent.
In 16th century Italy, mercenary Marco is hired by cruel duke Astolfo whose unjust reign is threatened by the notorious outlaw the Red Mask.
Story about a IT professional settled in US and married to an Indian girl. After marriage both living a happily ever after life but things changed when his ex-fiance ruined his marriage life.

Armand and Leila are in love. Together they plan to go to New York for an internship. But few days before their departure, Mahmoud, Leila's big brother, comes back from his long-term stay in Yemen, during which he has changed drastically.
Naciye sings on the streets to live and one day she is discovered by a famous casino owner. Then Naciye falls into love with her piano teacher Cuneyt. Casino owner Ekrem starts to make a trouble.

movie_name: The Beach Girls and the Monster
description: Surfers are being brutally murdered. Is the culprit a sea monster or just one of the teens' jealous parents?
Three students find an abandoned hobby film set in the forest. The old Nazi bunkers in the woods seem to be related.
A vengeful widow hires a professional killer to train her son so that he can hunt down and kill the men who murdered her husband. The quest for revenge soon becomes an obsession.
A successful executive in the cosmetic industry has three sexy girlfriends in three different states. When they decide to visit him in L.A., he's in big trouble.
A wealthy young girl in Las Vegas getting a divorce from her banker husband becomes involved with a lady gangster and the G-Man that is after the gangster lady and her gang.
The Prince is set to learn the Ethics and Royalty of His Kingdom. Will his personal instructor let him through?

Raafat works on one of the ships and meets with his ex-girlfriend Madiha, who refuses to marry him because she wants to marry a wealthy person. They plot to make millionaire Azzouz falls in love with Madiha so that she can have his money.
An Ex-French Soldier begins participating in underground street fights in order to make money for his brother's family.
Barbara befriends Bennett after her brother Jonny is attacked in a graveyard by a ghoul. Barbara and Bennett seek shelter in a nearby home only to find the current occupants are not hospitable.

For Ari, nothing feels like anything. He doesn't do relationships, doesn't do attachments. There's only sex. That is until he meets Tiina. Together with Tiina and her closest circle of friends, this could be their last summer of freedom.
A troubled character climbs a steep mountain attempting to reach the peak. Along the way, he must face his internal demons.
A college graduate discovers his first day on the job that he's the only living employee and the mark in a global spy game.
A Group Of 5 Fans of KATRINA KAIF decide to kidnap her and the film is about their journey to track her and in the process what happens to them.

The film covers the coming of age of all these friends, as they try to solve a Rubik's cube called life. It also covers a lot of issues like acid attacks on girls, suicides, misunderstandings, false prestige and more. And Sri loves Chanda.

Shinji, a popular geisha, falls in love with a small coal mine owner Shimada and fights with him against a cruel rich coal mine owner Osuga, who exploits his workers. A lot of action, romance and swordplay.
Kevin Sorbo stars in this sci-fi action film in which a squad of elite human soldiers faces down an alien army on their home planet.
American ambassador is kidnapped by terrorists after an accident with the plane that was taking him to the Philippines, for a special mission.
A low budget horror filmmaker gets in touch with an eccentric who is trying to film his consciousness during drug abuse.
When a career workaholic vows to abstain from kissing and sex until she finds her true love, she abandons her list of qualifications and searches the stars for the answer.
Three Exotic Dancers seek to exploit rich celebrities at a Secret Hollywood Sex Party; entirely unaware their desires are a gateway into a house of unimaginable horrors.

the young and gifted Rodi struggles with his economy and arrogant publishers. Petter offers his a lucrative job - picking up a parcel with cocaine after an airplane drop. From he says yes, his life is turned into a life and death struggle.
An unsophisticated peasant from a small Czech village must choose between his wife and a stylish English-woman who introduces him to the cultured life of Prague.

A mid-western couple is transferred to Washington DC for work and meet the neighbors, a super-intense couple. As their friendships develop, confusion unfolds in this country mice meet city mice adventure.
Electrical Girl centers around a horny young woman (Sophie Ngan) who has electrical genitals. When young Jan gets sexually aroused, she emits bolts of electricity from various orifices.

movie_name: Yakuza deka: Kyofu no doku gasu
description: Detective Hayata's mission is to infiltrate a nightclub at a ski resort and confiscate a lethal poisonous gas.

The second movie directed by Humayun Ahmed. A village drama interweave around a charming girl, a folk singer, his love interest and the local aristocratic family's involvement, the movie provide with some beautiful songs.
A former Navy SEAL and his retired combat dog attempt to return to civilization after suffering a catastrophic accident deep in the Alaskan wilderness.
Shankar and Chanchal earn their living by doing road shows. Once, Shankar sees Natasha on a circus poster and dreams of working with her. He gets an offer to work in the circus in Russia
This is when your boyfriend finds out who his real friends are who will really help him when it's time to pay that bond money
When baby Sebastian is born on 12/12/12 everyone around him starts to die. Pretty soon, his mother realizes that her son is the spawn of Hell.

Varada grows up with his mother as his father is getting married to another woman. Hence he develops hatred towards his father and starts punishing the people who go for a second marriage and extra-marital affair.

With the murder of his father, Hector is forced to defend the family's coveted lands. That's when an old novel changes the boy's trajectory and brings him closer to the truth about the death of the patriarch.

A brilliant military scientist inadvertently creates a zombie while trying to save his dying wife, setting off a deadly outbreak of flesh-eating beings who are living humans by day, yet revert back to the vicious dead by night.

Unexpectedly, a railroad worker falls in love with his co-worker's sister, unbeknownst to him that his boss' daughter has set her sights on him, envious of their true feelings. Can love prove more powerful than her wilful fabrications?
The story is about Kazem, a middle-aged man who lives in a village. He has left the university because of a former love but when two sisters enter his life he falls in love once again.
In a dystopian future where criminals and anarchists take over detective Jimmy Cloud fights for justice and freedom, and soon finds himself inmidst brutal chaos.

In this Romantic Comedy, a spoiled fashion reporter seeking to write more meaningful stories is sent undercover to the Philippines to do an expose' on the Romance Tourism Industry, where she gets her story and a much more.
Maruthu is a rustic action entertainer where Vishal plays the role of a labourer. The story revolves around his relationship with his grandmother.
Margaret is a nurse in England during WW2, and married to a secret agent. Things get complicated when she falls for David, an American pilot.
A young man and two of his friends find strange cryptic messages in various locations. Since then, strange things start happening to them.

A woman in her thirties gets into a relationship with her rich ex-boyfriend in order to get her handsome boss jealous. However, things get messy when the new business partner of her boss is the sister of her ex-boyfriend.
The martial arts expert Liu Chung is living in Hong Kong where he makes Kung Fu movies. When Lius father is kidnapped in Paris he has to come to his rescue and fight a big crime syndicate.
An anarchic, hip-hop inspired comedy that follows four city boys on a wilderness trek as they try to escape a mysterious huntsman.

A psychosexual odyssey through the wanting, taking and giving electric heart of a new york summer night, by the morning a hero and her remembered powers return home. A fairy tale, a myth, a midnite summer dream about power and love.
A young girl babysits in a house that's reputed to be haunted. As the night wears on, she begins to unravel as strange occurrences point to an evil presence.
Ishqeria is a story of a small town girl who falls madly in love with the most sought after guy in college. It is a journey of first love, growing up and second chances.

A psychological thriller promising suspense and a touch of dark comedy at the expense of a few select individuals seeking audience with Death hoping to barter for an extension while clutching in their hand a bloody eviction notice.
A famous ventriloquist whose career is going down hill takes his anger out on his strange puppets who seem to have a life of their own.

Frankie Cochran, a 22 year old US Marine hero and counter terrorist specialist returns home from a tour in Afghanistan to discover his best friends are being blackmailed by a shadowy Internet hacker group with ties to Terrorists.
Nami is an ex-convict who becomes a hostess to support a sick woman who bailed her out. In doing so, she gets involved in a local gangster's scheme to take over the bar she works for.

Helen and Bone live in a repressive futuristic dystopian society they badly want to escape from. Mysterious Jason hires them to steal a disc for him. It's practically a suicide mission, but he claims he can smuggle them out, in return.
The almost-human son of "Brundlefly" searches for a cure to his mutated genes while being monitored by a nefarious corporation that wishes to continue his father's experiments.
I don't give a damn how you'll do it but only have 7 GOLDEN DAYS to win this war. GO' and Blast your way through but for heaven's sake WIN THIS WAR.
What seems to be a chance encounter one day at a coffee shop leads to a full-fledged romance, but the couple must fight for their relationship to survive the craziness that is show business.

Watch the full movie, Pyar Ke Rahi, only on Eros Now. Pyar Ke Rahi is a 1982 Indian Hindi film, directed by Atma Ram. The film stars Kanwaljit Singh, Padmini Kapila and Neelam Mehra in lead roles. The film had musical score by Aziz Nazan.
The devil is in the woods, corrupting and murdering children. A blacksmith has made a man who wants to be a bird.
About a stop-motion animator struggling to control her demons after the loss of her overbearing mother.

Dracula is resurrected in modern day London. Inspector Harry Dixon's investigating the murders left in his wake when he crosses paths with Lara Van Helsing, a hunter, hot on Dracula's trail. They must team up to take him down.
A former hacker gets hired in a start-up to destroy their database. But CEOs are vampires who collect people's digital souls in the cloud.
Two best friends and roommates are terrified by the vengeful spirits dwelling in their apartment. Based on the novel published by Kobunsha and written by Nanami Kamon.
Inspector Balram is wrongly suspended and jailed when he sincerely fights against the atrocities of influential dons. After the mafia kills his wife, he takes the law into his hands.

Returning to the ancestral castle long after the death of the monster, the son of Dr. Frankenstein meets a mad shepherd who is hiding the comatose creature. To clear the family name, he revives the creature and tries to rehabilitate him.
While courting a young woman by mail, a rich farmer sends a photograph of his foreman instead of his own, which leads to complications when she accepts his marriage proposal.

movie_name: Stray Cat Rock: Delinquent Girl Boss
description: A wandering tough biker girl aids a female delinquent gang in their battles against an all-male Seiyu group over a fixed boxing match.

On the 8th anniversary of death, judgment of the wandering spirits begin. The day the fate of the perpetrator and victim cross paths and buried memories awake, wrongdoings are judged, and grudges are dispelled.
Part supernatural; part creature feature; part atmospheric horror. At its narrative core, it's an origin story - Are you who you think you are?

Ahlam who is studying medicine in the college is in love with Dr. Parviz and wants to marry him. But according to her tribe's laws and traditions she must marry her cousin Farhan. She decides to face her family and find a solution.
A young group of monster fanatics attempt to save their hometown from Count Dracula and his monsters.
A woman dying of a terminal illness discovers that the only way to save herself may be death itself.
A man wakes in a hospital with no memory, and quickly finds himself on the run in a locked down hospital with the Cartel on his tail. He scrambles to find his true identity in the most vicious way.
A frustrated teenage girl creates her perfect man in a virtual reality machine and in a freak accident, gives him life.
A war, religious conflicts, and misunderstandings create obstacles for a couple of different faiths.

Operatives from a secret organization known as 'Regimen' must recover the contents of a missing Briefcase while battling members of the Renegade faction and a mysterious gunman, who all share a common goal.
A young woman and her successful husband attempt to mend their relationship during a week long stint at a remote cabin.

Mechanic Stella owns a gas station with introvert Lenni. When Stella accidentally kills Lenni's abusive mother, they try to dump the body. They run into trouble, thugs and cops but stick together as they fall in love with each other.
The story of one man's hilarious - and doomed - attempts to wield life's ultimate double-edged sword: infidelity.
A former L.A. drug dealer tries to go straight but his past and his underworld connections bring him into the focus of the DEA, the Mexican feds and the Mexican drug cartels.
A terrifying new retelling of the most famous horror story of all time, as the Prince of Darkness travels to England to begin a global reign of terror.

Elon, who suffers from bipolar disorder, wants to please his father, the head of a mafia in the south of France, and participates "in spite of himself" in crimes. However, every action has consequences and a heavy price to pay.
A nurse taking care of her daughter's mysterious affliction struggles to hide her secrets when uninvited strangers take shelter in her house during a lethal blizzard.
A hostel warden becomes the target of a dreaded politician and his gangster son, but little do they realize that it is they who should fear him.
Narco Soldiers is a timely, action-packed crime thriller that explores the resurgence of the Caribbean drug routes and one couple's violent, Bonnie and Clyde-style rise to power.
A group of college friends rent an Airbnb for the biggest music festival of the year. A weekend of partying quickly takes a turn, as the group is murdered one by one.

In this hybrid of music and film, a teenage girl ventures into the woods to solve the disappearance of her beloved younger brother. Terrifying discoveries transcend the search beyond time, bringing happiness at the cost of her very soul.
Desmond Dube and Nomsa Buthelezi star in this hilarious family film. After meeting a mysterious Kung Fu master, Doris becomes a crime fighter - causing mayhem for those around her.
A courier is hired to deliver a package. Not knowing it contains the bodily remains of the the receivers nephew. He is then hunted down and forced to fight his way to answer from his boss.

A down-on-his-luck archaeologist returns from a cave expedition that contains a cursed relic that's also a portal to Hell. He discovers that the only way to stop the curse on his family is to go back to the cave and destroy the relic.

Yuna has a crush on Haru. She sees him on the train every morning when she goes to school. She doesn't know anything about him and he goes to a different school from her. One morning, she wakes up and finds Haru sleeping right next to her.
Based on a polemic novel by Amy Yamada, Bedtime Eyes is about the intense love relationship between a second rate Japanese jazz singer and a black American GI on the margins of the law.
Two souls lost in a world of modernisation find each other in a moment's need for clarity and appreciation.

A group of criminals stumble upon a lodge after a bank heist. As they hold the owners hostage and plan their next move they encounter an evil in the woods that is hungry and will stop at nothing to feed on their flesh.
The son of a world renowned Iraqi writer faces the aftermath of his father's assassination in Baghdad, and his undeclared love for his best friend.
Srividya is molested by her husband Radharavi. Radharavi has affairs with many other women. Srividya has a son, whom she raises on her own. However, things change when her son grows up.
Two smart con-women and a bunch of quirky gangsters are pitted against each other while in pursuit of a mythical vessel fabled for its powers.
A small town community comes together to eradicate the heroin epidemic from its midst by whatever means necessary.
In Hawaii, an undercover DEA agent and her civilian friend stumble upon a drug trafficking operation, and have to enlist the help of all their colleagues/friends to go after the vicious drug kingpin.

The youngest son of an alcoholic former boxer returns home, where he's trained by his father for competition in a mixed martial arts tournament - a path that puts the fighter on a collision course with his estranged, older brother.
A desperate woman discovers super powers while pursuing vengeance in the sex trade underworld for the murder of her husband and child.
Paul goes from one job to another but never seems to be able to keep one long enough to earn much money. His wife despairs at him, particularly when he gets involved with gambling.
A group of twenty-something friends set off on a rousing journey and face beguiling dilemmas of love. Will any of them find the love they're looking for?
An independent film director casting for his new movie encounters a young actress who is prepared to turn the audition back on him.
The true story of Irishman John Riley who led a small battalion of his countrymen against the great American army in their battle against the Mexico in the 1840's.
A team of UFO investigators find themselves fighting for survival as alien monsters hunt them on the slopes of Mount Adams.

A stagecoach of travelers, a gunslinger and two outlaws arrive in a deserted mining town lit by the glow of a reddish full moon. As their worlds collide, they are hunted by a beast that only appears on the night of a blood moon.
Four men kidnap an old girlfriend on Halloween night as a joke to ruin a real estate deal, only to have a very real clown-masked killer stalk them seeking revenge.

Fred rarely gets through the day without falling to the ground with crippling pain. After meeting Regan and visiting an acupuncturist, he finally begins to find relief for both his chronic pain and his persistent loneliness.
An aspiring fashion designer struggles to find success and love. The story cuts into her life once a year, always on the same date: her birthday.
The Mayflower Fleet is ambushed escorting civilians out of a war zone. The Commander has critical intelligence and is the only survivor.

Gwen is shaken and confused by a recent breakup from the guy she thought was the one. In searching for the truth, mixed identities, comic hi-jinks, and lover's games ensue in this screwball comedy set against the backdrop of a dart league.
A Samurai kills a Blind Man who tells him to "Repay his debts." Because of the Samurai's actions his entire family is to bear a terrible curse.

movie_name: Hua gui you xian gong si
description: Two salesmen once worked in the countryside and came across a female ghost and a sissy ghost, and their driver was killed by the ghosts. They were so scared that they had to find a new job.
A detective must fight for the redemption of his soul when he finds himself trapped in a mysterious hospital that serves as a gateway between heaven and hell.
In this future, nature is restricted and virtual games now provide both the landscapes and the hunting grounds. A group of hunters will make it outside for a traditional hunt.
TRAINED IN THE WAYS OF THE ESTEEMED AND BROUGHT INTO A COURSE OF LIFE ALTERING "TWISTS AND TURNS", RED STAR IS A HIGH IMPACT ACTION THRILLER ABOUT 3 WOMEN WHO OVERCOME ALL TO PRESERVE THEIR FACTION.
During the American Civil War, two friends join the Bushwhackers, a militant group loyal to the Confederacy.
Arnab tries to help Ruksahana, who is found under mysterious circumstances in a house. He lets her stay at his home until he discovers something strange about her.
A struggling actress finds herself in the middle of a real-life spy movie when her younger brother shows up after being chased by a mysterious stranger who murdered his lover.
Panda (Xtended Reality) discovers a new island within the era that is just as unsafe as the previous. He meets a trustworthy person to get him off the Island, but it requires a deal...

The freedom war between Dominion and the rebels has just begun. Trikalypse joins forces with the rebel leader and her team of freedom fighters. They must now fight back to bring Dominion down and expose him to the world.
After cleaning Shanghai of criminals and mafiosi, the hero Lee Sung-sun moves to Tianjin at the request of a friend to help in the fight against the mafia.

movie_name: Kamen Rider Fourze: Everyone, Space is Here!
description: The Earth is threatened by the mysterious beings and the Kamen Rider Club goes to the space to avoid them being awakened. Kamen Rider Fourze and Meteor have to fight for the destiny of the Earth and for the friendship of all beings.
A son aspires to follow in his famous MMA father's footsteps, but along his journey must figure out how to break the abusive cycle, if possible, that his father has continued.
A man with spiritualist powers is told by his mentor that a demonic entity is returning to destroy his daughter's soul, and that he should take drastic measures to prevent this from happening.

When a quest for the gold of the legendary island of Felder is brought to the King, young Princess Velora becomes intoxicated by the sense of adventure. She commandeers the quest, but quickly discovers that Felder isn't what it seems.
A Special Forces soldier is sent into Bulgaria when a chemical agent from WWII is uncovered that can reanimate the dead.

The Silver Ninja Empire has a big meeting. A Ninja Master tells his students about two members who have broken one of the Ninja Commandments and have been cast out, stripped of their ninja powers and exiled to their birthplace.
Decades post-high school, Ram and Jaanu meet at their school's reunion and explore their past thoughts consisting of affection, care, depth and grieve all over the period of one evening.

Hedi, a young man with great dreams, is struggling his way through social conventions in Tunisia. While his mother tries to decide his life for him, Hedi meets Rim and suddenly he discovers that his world goes beyond and above conventions.
The story of two brothers leaving behind their violent past only for the parents to be killed in the present forcing their old ways, they seek a revenge path of destruction.

All Hallows Eve - the perfect night for a ghost hunt. At least that's what documentary film-maker Julia Marsh was told when she joined 'Paranormal Investigations Inc' for their Live Halloween special.

Rachel (Nirina Zubir) is a tomboy girl whose childhood friend is Farel (Irwansyah). This friendship is tested when Farel admits that he has fallen in love with Luna (Acha Septriasa), a feminine girl that makes Rachel wrecked by jealousy.
Nitta Sayuri reveals how she transcended her fishing-village roots and became one of Japan's most celebrated geisha.
A radio presenter shares a strange connection with a blind listener. She jumps upon an opportunity to contact him, but her conflicted guardian stands in her way.

A psychiatrist and his orderly take four male patients to a beach resort in Alexandria to help them integrate into the society and overcome their mental illnesses. The four patients and also meet their new soul mates.

In the wake of Israel's 2006 bombardment of Lebanon, a determined woman finds her way into the country convincing a taxi cab driver to take a risky journey around the scarred region in search of her sister and her son.
Set in a fictional town in Pennsylvania, a private investigator hired to solve a decades-long string of murders uncovers a terrible secret.
Qassem has an accident that causes him to have amnesia. A rural family finds him and gives him the name Hammady. He lives happily until another accident makes him regain his memories.
Two strangers meet and sparks fly during the weekend that they are planning their respective weddings.
Nearly a century after his creation, Frankenstein's monster finds himself being hunted by Count Dracula, but why?

After his parents are murdered, Bin is taken into the care of relatives. He begins to act strangely, the new occupants of his house experience horrific nightmares, and a mystery unfolds as a terrible secret is revealed.

Philip Sanderson awakens to find himself in a hospital. He soon finds himself in the middle of a bloody war between monsters that look like everyday people and the small band of resistance fighters who know their true identity.
During the last two years of her life, Princess Diana embarks on a final rite of passage: a secret love affair with Pakistani heart surgeon Hasnat Khan.
While building an irrigation system for a Southwestern desert community, an engineer vies with a local cowboy for the affections of a rancher's daughter.
An outgoing president and an incoming prime mister have a second shot at love in this romantic comedy.
A murder, a case of driving under the influence of alcohol, a hit-and-run, and an investigation which links the incidents together. A film about how a family suffers due to drunken driving.
When three virgin friends decide to end their dry spell on the night of their graduation, they make a bet that will make their nights one of the most craziest nights of all time.
Bat Masterson's old friend Billy Burns convinces him to become marshal of Liberal, Kansas and help the residents fight drought and a destructive range war.
A mild-mannered guy, who is married to a monstrous woman, meets the woman of his dreams, and schemes to find a way to be with her.
Filmed in New York, story of naive young woman from Hong Kong who goes to New York to study. Street-wise cabbie cousin takes care of her in the big city.
A Man meet's a married women a married women meets a man. Nothing can keep them apart but everything must keep them apart. What would you do?
When two military-made, weaponized dinosaurs attack a small mountain town, it's up to the sheriff to figure out a way to stop the creatures before the dinos escape and wreak havoc nationwide.

A young engaged woman is infatuated with an attractive but confused young man who is later revealed to be her betrothed's half-brother. Can you tell your heart when to fall in love? A story of first love.
Kathy, a small town Ohio girl, is a big fan of TV series called Chickboxer. She decides to take up karate in order to channel her TV heroine and take on the local crime wave.
Every hero has a beginning. Before Antonio became El Niño, he would have to overcome his first battle. But would also be his biggest tragedy, forcing him to embrace his fate as El Niño.

Their paths cross in the elevator of an anonymous student block in Munich: Clara, Motek, and Sin are three strangers in Germany, longing for acceptance and warmth, searching for a spark of the feeling we call "home".

A millionaire's wife leaves with their son after she realizes that her husband is a womanizer. Will the son, who grows up to be a taxi driver, reunite with the father, or will the adopted son, a womanizer himself, succeed in his evil plan?
Jake has fallen into depression after lost of his love one. His sister, Tila has a plan to cheer him up and take him out on a camping trip to a ghost town, where he learns how to bring back the dead.

The psychology and life of Brazilian hitmen, common in the Northeast part of the country. In this particular case, the story revolves around a young and idealistic politician from Salvador, whom the enemies are eager to eliminate.
Aayush falls in love with Sheetal at first sight, unaware that fate already had them together somewhere in the past.
A director of a low budget movie decides to kill her fellow cast and crew members as they have used her art to become rich and famous.
While investigating a criminal conspiracy, a hard-charging journalist unwittingly falls for her source -- a sweet-talking thug with amnesia.
Two sisters who suffered abuse as children at the hands of their sadistic father decide, after his death, to use witchcraft to bring his spirit back to get revenge.
Three medical students are doing an internship at a hospital. As part of their new responsibilities, they have to take charge of the morgue.

Fah is an adamant non-believer in destiny. However, one day her path crosses with Zen and Tae, the former seems like a perfect example of a man and the latter a pilot. Both men fall helplessly in love with Fan. Whom will she choose?
Two backwoods amigos (Tom Lester and Ray Stevens) enter a contest to win a hillbilly bus and hilarity ensues.
Four families in a Heartland town are tested in a single day when a tornado hits, forcing paths to cross and redefining the meaning of survival.

A group of romantically scarred friends break up couples who really aren't right for each other. As the business takes off, the leader's childhood dream-girl reappears in his life, engaged to a guy who's totally wrong for her.
Srikanta, who indulges in petty illegal activities, gives a lift to a journalist en-route to Agumbe. The duo talk about their life and experiences throughout their journey.
A military-flavored, World War Two, song-and-dance B-feature in which a fund-raising effort save a boys club from being closed.

Romantic comedy about an actress who stars in a sexually explicit mini-series adaptation of a best-selling erotic chick-lit novel, and her loving but tortured stoner boyfriend is forced to deal with it.
A corrupt cop gets himself transferred to Hyderabad where he has a change of heart while trying to teach his estranged but dutiful father a lesson.
Gaetano and Delia, a separated couple, try to pick up the pieces of their broken love, recalling all the faults and the mistakes which led them to where they are now.
Police inspector Madan Singh is married to Sushma, whose brother Arun is a violent leader of mill workers. Arun is shot dead by Madan when the former tries to kill the mill owner. Sushma leaves him.

Bria invites four of her friends to her family's summer house in the mountainous town of Desper Hollows. The town is all but abandoned save for the five friends - and a deranged psychopath intent on picking them off, one by one.
A troubled man talks to his suicidal sister's psychiatrist about their family history and falls in love with her in the process.
A woman is unexpectedly forced to choose between the husband she has long thought dead and the fiance who has finally brought her back to life.
Kala Viplavam Pranayam is a story of four school friends trying to figure out their interests and options after school.
Set in a village in Tamil Nadu, Ganesh and Oothukaattan are two very different men who oppose each other.

During an archaeological expedition on Bouvetøya Island in Antarctica, a team of archaeologists and other scientists find themselves caught up in a battle between the two legends. Soon, the team realize that only one species can win.
A recently dumped divorcee in his late-twenties sets out to plan a wedding-sized divorced party in an attempt to get his life back on track.

Writer Jay and womanizing sportscaster Max have been friends since birth. Jay introduces his editor Samantha to Max and they hit it off. Max wants Jay to try to seduce Sam to test her before their wedding.
Against overwhelming odds, nine men fought like hell - to uphold a glorious tradition of courage and heroism.

A tough Hong Kong cop's 16 y.o. daughter disappears in Pattaya. He goes to Thailand to find her and must deal with corrupt cops but an honest one helps him track down culprits involved in illegal organ trafficking.

An unexpected trip to the sun-kissed island of Corfu, combined with a harmless fabrication, will change forever the life of a live-in housekeeper who has a chance encounter with a handsome young stranger. Is he her Prince Charming?
Rafael, an actor who just got a role for a ghost movie wanted to have more feel in his character. He plans to get the ability of seeing ghost by open his "hijab".

ALMOST RELATED Synopsis: Almost related is an action packed, erotic comedy thriller that profiles the obscure intricacies of ancestral Japanese assassins. Almost Related highlights a series...                See full synopsis »
A kid is hypnotized by a scientist to kill his parents and ends in a mental institution. As a grown up he returns to seek revenge over the scientist.
A military surgeon teams with a ranking Navy flyer to develop a high-altitude suit which will protect pilots from blacking out when they go into a steep dive.

Three men vacation on a deserted beach near The Black Sea, trying to get away from women and society. However, two women arrive and try to claim the vacation spot as their own. The groups scheme to run each other off the beach.
Kidnapping. An ex-cop against an ex-convict with a girl standing between them. Nobody wants the clash, but at the end, it is inevitable. Everyone must do it's own choice. And someone has to loose.
A mysterious group known as "The Twelve" makes war with the Grigori...fallen angels who walk the earth. House of Fallen is loosely based on the Book of Enoch.

It is about an old conflict about inheritance (old house). In order to sell the house, all members of the family should gather in the house as per the will. But they face a ghost tries scaring and stopping them from selling the house.

Post-bankruptcy Greece:A man hides from his dark past.A girl in search of true love. Two down-on-their-luck brothers try to save their father's business.They will cross paths with unpredicted consequences.
While Caroline Keller is away on business, hit men gun down her wealthy husband and his mistress. Caroline realises she is the next target.
A terrifying journey into one man's twisted world of torture and cruelty, in which a young woman must fight back against a sadistic, psychopath hell bent on breaking her mind and body.
Listless millenials muse over unrequited love on their way to self discovery in this character driven suburban neorealist story.
The passengers of a train are taken hostage by a vicious criminal, after the police fails to capture him.
After a suddent disappearance to Harry Osborn, Peter Parker Uses his responsibility and meets up with his old friend Eddie Brock and turns out he had something could change Peter's Life for good.
David envisions an unusual project, he tries to recreate the love between two women that can only meet through the Polaroid pictures he takes of them.
A young student fighter trains for a kung fu tournament. A remake of the Shaw Brothers' 'Five Fingers of Death'.

movie_name: Jin ke, shang ke, biao ke
description: Yang Liansheng is in Northeast China to raise funds for Sun Yatsen's challenge to Yuan Shikai to lead the Republic of China.
A Quiet Road is a 90 Minute single location horror film with big scares in tight spaces like "Paranormal Activity" and nightmarish ghouls like "The Conjuring".
Vijay who is a corrupt officer by day, turns a vigilante by night in order to make the city crime free.
Tarik is a criminal in Istanbul. Selma is a young woman with an unhappy marriage. Their roads will intersect.

A suicidal stockbroker convinces a Black gang and a Latin gang to join forces and use street moves to sway a hedge fund. A vicious fast moving Action Comedy from the writer / director of The Weathered Underground.

A wealthy American has a chance encounter with a joyful young French woman, and anonymously pays for her education. She writes letters to her mysterious benefactor, nicknaming him from the description given by some of her fellow orphans.
Despite being depressed over his dead fiancée, a law enforcer is tasked to watch over a businessman's daughter which is not to their liking. Witness how proximity almost always lead to a budding.
