A soldier reunites with his wife to take in the attractions at their favorite Halloween spot. But when real terror follows them home, they must fight for their lives - or become the next attraction.

Village lad Vishnu is happy-go-lucky, with his life revolving around watching movies at a tent screening hall. Then, he falls in love, but just when he decides to get married, she goes missing. Can he piece his life back together?
When tradition prevents her from marrying the man she loves, a young woman discovers she has a unique talent for cooking.
One woman's obsession with online dating and her determination to find 'the one' leads her to look for love in all the wrong places.
Two friends of a man help him avenge his father's death. Years later, he reunites with his friends who have now become criminals. What they don't know, is that he is now an undercover cop.

An upright ex-army man, Jai fights a solitary war against corruption and injustice. With a simple mantra to pay forward, he starts off by helping one person and forms an ever growing circle of people helping each other.

All grown up, three ex-school girls, Chucky, Lilly and Athena, are on a mission to find out who is killing their classmates. All the while they fight not to become victims themselves. The trail is full of blood, drugs and punk rock.

On October 31st, two preteens in a small town accidentally awaken an evil that has lain dormant for decades. They are forced to survive through a terrifying Halloween night of cat-and-mouse, from the monster known as "Bloody Bobby."
Max is very ill. He decides to steal in his own company. But when he tries to run away with the money, he has a car accident that takes him to Emma's pigs farm.

A woman who believes in Communism falls in love with the Son of a Wealthy businessman. On a Road Trip, They realize the difference between their Lifestyle and Mindset. They break up but soon Their Heartbreaking love story took a big turn.

When his little brother gets lured into working for a drug dealer boss, a mechanic is forced to join him and winds up torn between both worlds until a female undercover FBI agent proposes a plan to take the dealer down.
A group of college students travels to a mysterious island to attend a rave, which is soon taken over by bloodthirsty zombies.

Krishna and Mahalakshmi have been in love since childhood but obstacles stand in the way. When a mafia gang attacks the Rajanna family and abducts three children, Krishna makes it his mission to rescue them and prove himself to Mahalkshmi.
A wandering ballad singer in the Appalachians meets an ugly bird-type creature, is transported back in time, finds himself involved in the Devil's work.

Set in the late 1800's, Bloodletting is a Horror Western Thriller about 3 handcart company pioneers who find themselves descending into madness while stranded in an abandoned fort surrounded by what appears to be a haunted forest.
A family moves to a small town in California where they plan on starting a new life while running a long-abandoned funeral home. The locals fear the place, which is suspected to be on haunted ground.

A land surveyor is sent to work on Romney Marsh, where her predecessor went missing months before. The new surveyor's strange experiences may either hold the key to the mystery, or simply deepen the frontier marshland's enigmas.
In Japan, Lieutenant Colonel Yuki (Yusuke Iseya) recommends the creation of spy training school "D Kikan".

On the planet Latimer, reawakened Takeshi Kovacs must protect a teenage tattooist named Holly while investigating the death of a yakuza boss alongside Gina, a strangely familiar no-nonsense CTAC agent.
A young couple of underachievers eat cereal, play video games, and try to face the tribulations of an unwanted pregnancy.
This film got nominated and also official selection in two well known film festivals in the year 2020 and 2021.
Although Danny is hoping to live up to his past glory, his new career as a ghost hunter has mixed results due to his ragtag team of paranormal investigators.

Cole Thornton, a gunfighter for hire, joins forces with an old friend, Sheriff J.P. Hara. Together with an old Indian fighter and a gambler, they help a rancher and his family fight a rival rancher that is trying to steal their water.

After breaking up with her girlfriend, a Brooklyn musician moves back in with her mother. Playing for tip money in an old friend's bar, an unexpected relationship begins to take shape. Based on the life and times of Alyssa Robbins.
In 1943, an Allied hospital ship is sunk by the Japanese in the South Pacific where a nurse and a Marine become marooned on an island abandoned by natives.
Jai Mummy Di is a light-hearted family comedy that portrays the trials and tribulations a couple has to undergo due to the dynamics between their respective mothers.
A young hockey player becomes an overnight star of the Toronto Maple Leafs and falls in love with a beautiful young singer. Their relationship is plagued by his "jock" nature and decadent lifestyle.
A man's newly transplanted heart leads him on a dangerous journey to find out who murdered its donor.
A youthful Shaolin initiate inadvertenly separated from the rest of gang joins forces with dashing adventurer (Biao) on a request to protect a priceless artifact from his greedy brother.
A film crew is in the midst of making a zombie movie, when suddenly everything becomes very, very real.
Myrah is a Hindi movie released on 23 Nov, 2018. The movie is directed by Anil Dhoble and featured Sukanya Surve as lead character.
A ruthless youngster becomes a kind and humble husband for his wife but as fate turns brutal, his patience is tested.

Thien Tam, a young but weak boy comes home after his treatment at the hospital to find that his cousin-sister, Hai Lam, has gone away from home. Tam decides to go look for her but then finds something horrible behind her missing.

Vampire's have been walking among us without us even knowing for centuries. Five friends decide to go out for a night on the town, but soon things change once a mysterious stranger decides join them and the body's start to go missing.
Gu-chang meets a sweet, cute girl, also a college student. They date. Later, he discovers her dissociative identity disorder, when she becomes vicious at times.
A psychopathic Japanese executive accidentally triggers a journalist's 'dark side'. They begin to connect over the Internet and make a complicated bond.
The lives of two men--a cop and a criminal--are questioned in the wake of a deadly epidemic in a futuristic, post-apocalyptic Hong Kong.
A usual working day turns unusual for Guru and Harini when they get trapped in their haunted office. A patterned game unlocks a mystery and a lift is their only way out.
A martial artist is targeted by a fearsome foe who plans to eliminate the greatest fighters in the world.
HD. Baseball fans Andres and Julissa fall hard for one another and have to keep Andres' love of a rival team secret from Julissa's father.
A struggling artist must win back the trust of a blind sculptor whose acquaintance revived his failing career.
Newlyweds on a honeymoon road trip accidentally kill someone, but their attempt to cover it up triggers an escalating array of deadly supernatural events.
One hundred soldiers of the Ukrainian Insurgent Army, led by Michael Duda (Hromenko) fearlessly fighting with the Bolshevics and with the Nazis.

When JW becomes a drug runner in order to maintain his double life, his fate becomes tied to two other men: Jorge, a fugitive on the run from both the Serbian mafia and the police, and mafia enforcer Mrado, who is on the hunt for Jorge.
Legendary luchador, Mil Mascaras, faces unbelievable horrors when the vengeful head of an Aztec chief is resurrected on a college campus.

A theater producer and his protege star fall in love and decide to wed. In route to their nuptials, tragedy strikes and the would-be groom ends up bound to a wheelchair. Nine years later, the wife tries to adopt a little girl.
A woman comes back to Hong Kong and helps the police investigating the murder of her twin sister, with whom she had a telepathic link.
A young American studying in Paris in 1968 strikes up a friendship with a French brother and sister. Set against the background of the '68 Paris student riots.

Community college burn out in the making, Crispin, lands his first job at the local, rundown Northwood Pizza. And through his experiences with friends, coworkers, and a kindling relationship, Crispin learns to embrace his higher ambitions.
For avid gambler Felix, marriage is like roulette - a game with a 50 percent chance of winning. Unfortunately, his wife Pola sees things differently
A trio of Mexican scientists and a squad of American soldiers encounter a being with God-like powers inside of a high tech government facility.

About a lurid tale of magic and secret societies during the reign of Luis XVI, focused on the figure of the Italian occultist Giuseppe Balsamo, known under his alias of Count Alessandro di Cagliostro.

movie_name: RiffTrax: Star Wars: The Last Jedi
description: Well, Luke Skywalker is still drinking discolored milk - not much has changed in the 'Star Wars' universe. The guys at RiffTrax may not be consuming strange liquids, but they are poking fun in this comedic audio track.
Returning from Ankara to Istanbul by car to catch up with her engagement tonight, Onur is first overtaken by a bride driving a bridal car, and then meets her at the stopover.

The wife of the virtuoso Paolo Sarto, Sigge, asks the detective Stuart Webbs for his help. Her husband has been suffering from severe anxiety since a strange visit. A little later the body of the visitor is found in Sarto's garden.
Four women set up a private detective agency. This time, they are trying to take back a valuable vase from a powerful gangster.
A young newspaper writer returns to her hometown in the English countryside, where her childhood home is being prepped for sale.

movie_name: Fairy Tail: Priestess of the Phoenix
description: Follow Fairy Tail's dream team as they lend a helping hand to a girl with little memory and a grudge against wizards.

Employees of an all-American furniture superstore Orsk come to work every day to find ransacked and vandalized displays and items, six people volunteered to stay in for a night to find out what is causing the strange disturbance.
The Wolf Man and Count Dracula beg Dr. Edelman to cure them of their killing instincts but Dracula schemes to seduce the doctor's nurse.
Simultaneously released English language version of a German anti-occupation, liberation film in which an Austrian spearheaded an uprising against Napoleon in the Tyrol.
From young visionary, Larry Alexander, comes this breakneck semi-animated portrait of back-alley "super racing".
After a vampire leaves his native Balkans, he murders a Czech artist, assumes his identity, and moves in with the dead man's American cousins.
A deep examination of how a relationship -supposed to be as intimate as that of two people linked by blood- comes to resemble that of two total strangers.

A famous author is suspected to be part of a murder, which eerily resembled the plot in one of her novels. A cop tries to figure out whether something sinister exists behind her charisma. An unofficial Indian adaptation of Basic Instinct (1992)
A young man's life descends into a living hell, as the consequences of his actions finally catch up with him.
An unlikely heir to a fast-food empire discovers a New Mexican town where foodies salivate over the culinary treats of a feisty female chef.
A disgraced action movie star is forced to drive a mysterious package to the Mexican border while being chased by Bounty hunters and beautiful female assassins.
John Wrath was a one-man Ninja Army, until one day when his cover was blown. Causing him to enter into witness protection. But now, his government is calling him back for one more FIGHT.
When a mayor running for re-election is caught on video smoking crack, he'll do whatever it takes to keep it out of the wrong hands. Inspired by true events.
When her mother is killed, a bereft daughter must risk everything to uncover the terrifying truth at the Hospice.

Pete and Debbie are both about to turn 40, their kids hate each other, both of their businesses are failing, they're on the verge of losing their house, and their relationship is threatening to fall apart.
Six young Executives on a wilderness team building retreat must escape the wrath of a vicious Beast descended from Pontius Pilate.
During a civil war between humans and androids, In the year 2090, a robotics engineer tries to bring her fallen lover back to life.
Jackson Bolt is an emotionally distraught detective who must clear his name in the death of his partner.

Horrifying shocker as a biological experiment goes haywire when meat-eating mutant roaches invade an island community, terrorizing a peaceful New England fishing village and hideously butchering its citizens.
After being sent to a sinister religious retreat by their stepfather, two siblings fight to escape in order to save their mother from harm's way.
In the future world, everyone speaks Mandarin. three magical stones, threaten humankind. Destiny will choose a hero for an adventure. The story of an underdog.
After discovering that she is the reincarnation of an ancient goddess, a bartender goes on a mission to rescue her kidnapped devotees.

movie_name: I Awoke Early the Day I Died
description: A nurse who uses her looks to gain the confidence of her new patient happens to be a compulsive swindler.
A heroic, fact based, action-packed drama about the world's first and greatest female fighter pilot.

A group of scientists have developed the Resonator, a machine which allows whoever is within range to see beyond normal perceptible reality. But when the experiment succeeds, they are immediately attacked by terrible life forms.
Two Canadian detectives, one from Ontario and the other from Quebec, must work together when a murdered victim is found on the Ontario-Quebec border.

A FINALIST in The Monthly Film Festival 2021. On the verge of losing her family business, an audacious antiques dealer agrees to break-up an engagement for a wealthy socialite. Everything changes when she meets her match.
An ex-gang member must recruit a Jesuit priest to save her younger sister, not only from the prostitution ring that she fell into, but from the demon that's possessing her body.
Six high school students find themselves lost in the woods when they discover their teacher's mutilated body and realize they are being hunted by a strange creature in the forest.
Kallookaran Joy is a single father who has left his gangster life behind to lead a peaceful life with his daughter. Things take an unexpected turn when his past comes knocking back to him.
A dramatic story of three friends happily spending time on their own in a mountain cottage in the High Tatras. On the arrival of the wife of one of them their perfect friendship is put to a test.

Overhearing his boyfriends talk of "a new toy for Christmas," young, cute, but aimless Ricky copes with online hookups and drugs. Depressed, Ricky considers suicide, until he meets another boy who makes him wonder should he stick around?
Indian army special forces execute a covert operation, avenging the killing of fellow army men at their base by a terrorist group.

In Bolivia, Butch Cassidy (now calling himself James Blackthorn) pines for one last sight of home, an adventure that aligns him with a young robber and makes the duo a target for gangs and lawmen alike.

Husband and Wife move to an old house before the birth of their firstborn child. Suddenly they find a mysterious bottle underneath the broken wooden floor. The bottle might be home to a creature that could potentially put them in danger.

Dose number one - two men go to a bowling tournament but one of the two has just killed his wife. Dose number two - pair of cousins follow their Gram Paps' passion for Halloween who gives a new meaning to trick or treat.
After a virus kills all of the Earth's adults, rival children battle for control of an abandoned theme park.
Two sociopaths who go on a killing spree, are interrupted when a man accidentally runs over one of the psycho's legs, leaving him badly injured.
A Berlin-set drama centered on a 40-something couple who, separately, fall in love with the same man.
A rancher, his clairvoyant wife, and their family face turbulent years in South America in this adaptation of Isabel Allende's best-seller.
A royal prince is raised by adoptive parents and experiences romance and adventure on his way to his destiny.
Throw out the script. Roll the camera. Grab your guitar and pour the Whiskey. You might get a crowd. You might not.

movie_name: Stacy: Attack of the Schoolgirl Zombies
description: Girls surrounding 17 years old are affected by an illness that make her to be 'Stacies': they feel a strange and momentary happiness until they become zombies.

A middle-aged husband's life changes dramatically when his wife asks him for a divorce. He seeks to rediscover his manhood with the help of a newfound friend, Jacob, learning to pick up girls at bars.
An inventive crime thriller told backwards reversing day by day through a week following a local sheriff's quest to unlock the mystery of three small-town criminals and a bank heist gone wrong.

movie_name: Saint Seiya: Legend of Crimson Youth
description: The Sun God Abel returns to life, bent on punishing the humans and cleansing Earth from their presence. When Athena joins him, leaving humans to their fate, the Bronze Saints must defend the world in their greatest battle yet.
A woman who struggles in relationships doesn't find the love she wants until a much-younger man appears, but she's still not convinced.
John, an escaped convict, takes refuge on the farm of Widow Couderc. He becomes the older woman's lover and admits that he's on the run. The widow's in-laws, who despise her,
Frustrated with the lenient criminal justice system, an LAPD homicide cop goes vigilante on various criminals, including a serial killer of women.
Lao San, is a retired Marine veteran who lives in his world of innocence and optimism due to a brain injury. He assumes the role of a dedicated vigilante and fights people whom he considers bad.
When a top alien assassin defects and leaves the realm called The Magnate, the leaders fear destruction of their civilization and are forced to make desperate choices.

A teenager's life took a turn after a parody horror film she made. She met someone who promised to make her dreams come true - until that very person turned out to be a living nightmare taking Aubrey's talents and labeling them as her own.
A penniless musician is unwittingly forced to trade places with a look-alike diamond merchant/thief causing a comedy of errors by everyone involved.
A voiced over spoof of an old monster movie. Scientists and a group of children are attacked by monsters from another world.
The story about So-hee who lost her happy family due to her husband's sudden death, and experiences strange and creepy things after visiting Neulbom Garden, a rural mansion left by her husband.
A Martial Arts Champion is transported to another realm to team up with a group of past warriors hoping to defeat a powerful enemy.
A female wrestler who has decided that she no longer wants to wrestle, but whose mother (a former wrestler herself) wants her to keep wrestling to make money so her brother can have the operation.

Jo has just come back to Japan for the funeral of his parents, who were killed in Africa where the family had been living throughout most of Jo's life. Once the funeral was over, he missed the boat home, so he ends up staying in town.

Camden, who suffers from agoraphobia takes in Randy, who suffers from claustrophobia, as a roommate. Unfortunately, Randy turns out to be a serial killer, and Camden becomes a prisoner inb his own apartment.

Six young adults return to their abandoned high school 10 years after leaving to discover a malevolent presence stalks the hallways and classrooms... They thought they'd never leave. Now they never will.
Hijacked in open waters, a fully laden supertanker is commandeered by Pirates whose covert agenda is infinitely more devastating than their ransom threats.
Vetrivel, a young man who believes rising rivalries are essential to succeed in life, finds himself in deep trouble when his girlfriend is abducted by his enemies.
When a deal goes wrong, four small-time drug runners flee to a safe-house where a malevolent entity craves to be unleashed.

movie_name: Super Stooges vs the Wonder Women
description: Three men with supernatural powers interfere in a tribal warfare to prevent evil Amazons destroying the inhabitants of a village.
Don Pepe (John Regala) is a policeman whose wife left him for another man because he's poor. He will do everything to become rich and take back his wife.
A mild mannered man is forced to deal with his dark past when a friend from his former life comes to collect on an old debt.
A security robot operator in Detroit forms a connection with a young woman in North Africa who is trying to escape her engagement to a much older man.
Beautiful but ailing girl is married to a harsh man who doesn't care for her. Only after she dies does he realize that he actually loves her.
A man in search to stop his psychopath brother from killing members of a secret government organization who will stop at nothing to kill the brother who has stumbled upon its secrets.
A common man gets a unique opportunity to become the Chief Minister for one day and administer the state. He accepts the challenge and takes action against the corrupt, which earns him many enemies.
A computer programmer who receives strange phone calls from a fetish prostitute he may have murdered struggles to find out if he's being haunted by a prankster - or a ghost.
A man and woman meet in college and are on their way to a lifetime of happiness when their plans get hijacked.
When two detectives are fed up with the system that's not working, they seek the help of a martial arts master to bring Justice to the Streets.
This compelling tale of love and betrayal, set in the upper Egyptian countryside, follows the story of Amna as she plots her revenge on the engineer who destroyed her family's honor.

After an Ayahuasca vision transports him to a haunted castle, Alec meets Hanna who tales him the story of her mother's forced marriage and how the forbidden passion with her father was in danger when the princess pregnancy became obvious

To save her land, a young woman hires three vets to search the desert for a valuable meteorite. When they reach a secret lab that opened an inter-dimensional portal, alien attacks terrorize her team, the scientists, and military police.
A psychotic man stops taking his medication and goes on a killing spree after having bloody visions.
A witch is killed and wrapped in a shroud. Now a sect wants to take possession of the cursed shroud. A nun, raped for not having delivered the shroud, will enact her revenge.
A masked man is killing a group of underworld hoods, which has the police and the hoods equally baffled.
A young man embarks on a journey to find three magical stones in order to stop an evil threat from consuming the world.
A young man named Paul is in search of true love. Paul's dad, Paul Senior, has hired a matchmaker to find eight dates for Paul Junior to go on in his quest to find a girlfriend.

3 interlocking stories from the dark days of World War 2. A soldier on a suicide mission. A troubled family with a monster in their bomb shelter. A supernatural investigator on her most dangerous assignment yet.

The U.S. government initiates a program to create genetically-modified cybernetic super soldiers, but it goes awry when the test subjects escape from their holding cells. Set on an island in an undisclosed location.

Impersonating an Imperial Army officer by wearing a "red lion's mane", a poor servant returns to his village after 10 years of absence to end the village's suffering caused by corrupt officials and businessmen.

4 half siblings stand to inherit $3,000,000 each from their dad, if they work together as family for 2 years. 3 of them go to Mexico as bounty hunters to get a bail-jumper, who's connected to the kidnapping of a billionaire.

Dr. Hackenstein is a genial but somewhat misguided scientist. He murders the locals for their body parts, but it's not for power or scientific research; he just needs them to put his wife back together.
Stranded on a deserted island, a group of people struggles to survive against a swarm of supernatural flies.

A wealthy Havana club owner and his family are torn apart by the violent sociopolitical upheaval brought about by the transition from the dictatorial regime of Batista to the Marxist revolution led by Fidel Castro in 1950s Cuba.

Adi and Kirana have been married for a long time but are still childless. Adi decides that a move outside of town. Kirana starts to feel that there is something strange with their new home. a girl ghost who she calls "SISTER".

movie_name: Ang Baril Ko'y Pito, ang Sundang Ko'y Siyam
description: Funnyman Chiquito , as the village idiot who kills people with laughter by day, and literally kills his enemies by night.
A group of wayward teens are sent to a detention camp in rural North Carolina, where they discover a horrific past among the grounds and its keeper.
A family moves into a house with a haunted past. The new family starts to take on the attributes of a family that previously resided in their house leading to murder.

movie_name: On a Dark and Bloody Ground
description: In 1986, Miller's End, Kentucky has become the target of something wicked. Many fall victim to a malevolent presence as a lawman and a mourning father are hell bent on solving the mystery and saving their town.

There is a dark tale of a woman who lives in the shadows. A group of family and friends are about to discover that there worst fears are actually becoming reality. They later learn that a dark past will always come to haunt you.
When a woman discovers that her husband has been unfaithful to her, she decides to respond to his infidelities in kind.
When the leader of a successful band of narcissistic hellions sees his kid brother gunned down on stage, he vows hard rock revenge.
A detective investigates her father's dying words; the name of a girl who has been missing for 9 years.
An intelligent son of a former entrepreneur takes revenge on a powerful and rich businessman who is as smart as he is.
An undocumented immigrant violently attacked by Nazis survives and, with the help of his friends, goes on a brutal hunt for revenge and redemption.
A suicidal ex-navy seal struggles between his Faith and his lust for revenge when his estranged daughter is held captive by ruthless gun runners.
A man nicknamed 'Spots' goes to Seoul to scour the city with his uncle. They search every bar and all the lowlife areas trying to find the men who stole their gold statue of Buddha.
A weak personality father trying to prove to his son that he's courageous, so he decided to join a TV Show about courage, and he faced a lot of crisis in a comic way.
Three inept agents and Miss Colombia set out to rescue Miss Venezuela, who has been kidnapped by a mysterious villain.
The star of "The Texas Chainsaw Massacre" returns in a story about frat boys lost in the big city while hunted by a violent leader and his elite gang of gun-happy guards.

A hitman specialized in executing cheating spouses contemplates redemption after falling for a single mother. When the killer blows off a very important hit, his partner in crime sets out to finish the job.

Rage and revenge drives a highly respected police detective to stay on the trail of a power hungry auto magnate within the department who is systematically eliminating any competition that stands in his way.

A comic book collector meets two beautiful, mysterious sisters who run a secret collectors' society. To acquire the rarest of the rare, he must battle a demonic presence in the sisters' deadly storage facility.
Paige's best WWE matches, including her debut match on RAW vs AJ Lee and her intense NXT fight with Emma.
Ten years have passed, and Sidney Prescott, who has put herself back together thanks in part to her writing, is visited by the Ghostface Killer.
A horror anthology of seven intertwined tales that follows the paths of several serial killers on their nights of terror and destruction through Los Angeles.
A sweeping romance set in one of the most unlikely of places and times - a displaced persons camp in Germany just after WWII.
Michalis, a rich Athenian, is in Cyprus where he meets and falls in love with the popular singer Christina.

movie_name: The Black Devil and the White Prince
description: Yu believes that she's in-love with the White Prince "Shirakawa". But every encounter with the abusive Black Devil "Kurosaki" who she hates, she gets one step closer to loving him.

Duyen, a wedding dress staff, who decides to continue a pregnancy despite Hung, her lover advising her to have an abortion. He hit by car while chasing her. When he woke up, he saw all men around are pregnant instead of their wife.

Katya has read an ad in newspaper, where Russian immigrant in Miami has claimed that would marry any woman in 24 hours, if she was able to cook tasty borshch. So, Katya went to Miami towards her destiny.
After a train accident, a woman survives and is mistaken for an other woman she just met on a train before the accident.
An elderly woman battling Alzheimer's disease agrees to let a film crew document her condition, but what they discover is something far more sinister going on.
An ex-marine returns to her hometown after Iraq and helps a 20 year old woman, who is otherwise facing prison, prepare for military boot camp.
A young college student has recently moved out of her old, haunted boarding house, escaping from followers of Mangkoedjiwo Sect who seek revenge over the death of Sri Sukmarahimi Mangkoedjiwo.

movie_name: To Live and Die in Tsimshatsui
description: An undercover cop Ah Kit and his best friend Ah Bong are sent in to get evidence on a crime boss known as Coffin Tung. After a raid goes wrong and Tung is killed, his gang splits into two factions.
Two children, who essay the roles of Shah Jahan and Mumtaz as kids, are separated when the girl shifts her residence. The boy pines for her. Do they unite as adults?
Earth has fallen to alien invaders, Katherine continues to rampage around the colonies with her rebel fleet. Renegades brings the story to a close and not everyone is going to make it to the end.

She is a former soldier, daughter of the Land Marine who was assassinated while on a mission. She was approached by a warrior to join the Project Busaba, a project to train tough girls to be assassins to serve the nation.
As various members of the Frank family come together for a college graduation party in Chicago, they find their bonds being tested, and strengthened, in surprising ways.
A cowardly man unwittingly unleashes three spirits seeking revenge against the family he works for. The spirits take turns taking over his body, causing all sorts of mischief along the way.

Three couples at different stages of their lives meet in New York in a world-famous jewelry store. The events at the chance meeting in the store of these strangers with very different motivations all impact the couples' lives.

An Australian outback police detective is sent on a special assignment to the UK, to return an Australian citizen accused of murder. Only this is not an ordinary man, he is a UN high commissioner for peace talks taking place in London.
TV crew uncovers terrifying mystery in a reclusive family's home in rural Maharashtra, where strange events threaten their survival as they uncover a mind-bending truth.
A criminal meets his childhood sweetheart during a bank robbery. He takes her as a hostage and the two renew their relationship which culminates in a lovers' suicide.
IS SOCIETY TO BLANE - for the bruised and twisted minds of a city's slums - snarling, growling, and grumbling as they are? "Barkada" awaits your verdict.

CEO Seung-tae is in an affair with his sister-in-law So-young. One day, a rookie named Young-chul finds out about them and threatens to tell the CEO's wife. Hye-sun is scared that her affair will cause trouble with her half-sister.

movie_name: Cameron Decker: The Thin Blue Line
description: Government contractor hired to go after a domestic terrorist that brings the judicial system to a halt.
After Dexter is confronted with robots who wish to "destroy the one who saved the future," he uses his time machine to see how he saved it.

Policemen Brian and Mike use an elderly woman's apartment for surveillance, hoping to catch a fugitive gangster. They develop a warm relationship with their hostess. Meanwhile, each man develops a romantic relationship.
Two English women and their female servant are kidnapped by pirates and sold to an Arab sheik. However, they all fall for the captain of the pirate ship that captured them.

Living in self-imposed exile in the Mojave Desert, Nat Wedderburn runs a small business installing sprinklers. A troubled young man he hasn't got over a fatal accident that left him scarred five years earlier.
In a remote military outpost in the 19th century, Captain John Boyd and his regiment embark on a rescue mission which takes a dark turn when they are ambushed by a sadistic cannibal.
After a Mexican is arrested for a crime he didn't commit, he finds out that in this prejudiced town the only thing that can save him, will also be his demise.

Set in a future Bangkok, the story picks-up after a hit-gone-wrong on "Iron Cop", the area police chief. The would-be killer "Pae", together with his equally inept collection of thugs, now become wanted men themselves as the Thai underworld bristles with the shame & dishonor of such an ignoble bungling.
An ungrounded young mother and her thoughtful teenage son are banished to a remote provincial town by her domineering father.
Two escapees are on the run in the wilderness of an unspecified country. Wherever they go, they are followed by a menacing black helicopter.
What seems like an innocent wine tasting weekend turns into a bizarre, wicked, sensually overheated debauchery, culminating in a murderous grand finale evening and fateful morning after.
A sister and brother, the last heirs of a family of acrobats, are called upon by a Buddhist monk sect to retrieve an artifact that their ancestors have protected throughout the ages.

A guy and four of his friends visit his crippled uncle, a taxidermist who lives with his housekeeper next to a movie set. Pretty soon people start being killed in the manner they are in the script of the movie being filmed next door.

Amid death in Nazi-occupied Lamia, a Greek-Australian army officer has an affair with a compassionate Red Cross nurse, only to get separated during a mission in Cairo. Will the mother and her child ever reunite with the missing father?
Four architects on a recce trip to Goa find out that the voluptuous lady inviting them to her villa for a night is a witch who feeds on youth. Will they survive the night?
A love story about two people who fall in love but are violently torn apart only to be reunited through tragedy again.
A psychopathic gangster rapes and murders a woman and then her brother kills everyone responsible one by one.
A nurse, a policeman, a young married couple, a salesman and other survivors of a worldwide plague that is producing aggressive, flesh-eating zombies, take refuge in a mega Midwestern shopping mall.
A soldier who once saved the entire country is assigned to guard a genius child whose intellect is needed to foil the plans of an evil villain.

movie_name: Visceral: Entre las cuerdas de la locura
description: A washed-up boxer, who finally gets his big break to prove he is worthy of the champion's gloves, becomes a vessel of pure evil and a relentless instrument of destruction of the human flesh. Is he hell's next champion?
Follows a man as he joins a sleep trial that allows him to rebuild his life with his girlfriend who died in an accident through the use of lucid dreams.
When a lady named Faride takes revenge against her husband Kemal through black magic and AMMAR jinn, it bought out immense power of darkness against her also.

For 100 years, stories have been told about a cult near Hackett Ranch where people have been kidnapped and never found. The owners of the ranch say they know nothing about it. Guess where this year's rodeo is?
In the early twentieth century, an aging actress and her lover visit the estate of her elderly brother.

England, 1795: the young Catherine has just married Charles Fengriffen and moves into his castle. She becomes the victim of an old curse that lays on the family. On her wedding night she is raped by a ghost and gets pregnant.

Atilla the Hun gives a Silver Saddle to Altar as a gift. The intention of Kostok is the get rid of the Huns and seize the valuable saddle. Little Tarkan who is compulsory abandoned by his foster-mother in a cave, his cry attracts the attention of a wolf and the wolf magnifies Tarkan like his own cub.

Nazar's daughter Supriya and Saratbabu's son Kalyan study in same college, where they both engage in few fights.Slowly love blossoms under these petty things. But their parents are rivals in the town.
A priest secretly leads rebels in their struggle against the corrupt military dictatorship of the Central American country of Puerto Santo.
A true life story of a South African serial killer who murdered 36 women in a job for hire post in the 80s and 90s.

A terror leader is making a massive plan to disrupt national stability. ADC Nabid is hunting down the tail of terrorist outfit. But the situation becomes worst when series of attacks occur anonymously.
The worlds of a depressed psychologist and an emotionally disturbed homeless young woman collide. While trying to rescue her they fall in love, and each gets a second chance at a new life.

A rich heiress and her friends head for a weekend of fun at her isolated ranch house in the middle of no man's land. They soon find that the caretaker's dark past, has taken him down a bloody killing spree.
After a tragic accident a teenage girl is resurrected with the use of black magic. She uses her new-found powers to exact vengeance on her tormentors.

movie_name: A Nightmare on Elm Street 3: Dream Warriors
description: A psychiatrist familiar with knife-wielding dream demon Freddy Krueger helps teens at a mental hospital battle the killer who is invading their dreams.
A YA horror adventure set in Hell told as a modern, dark and re-imagined version of the classic Alice in Wonderland story.

A team of scientists conducting a biological study in the underground sewage system discovers a group of alien-looking eggs that they subsequently destroy. However, unknown to them, one of the eggs had hatched and escaped.

Ten years after a failed music career, Sylvie runs into her former bandmate David, now busking and living in a tent on the streets of Portland, and offers him a place to stay for three days while her husband is away.
A young woman gets her chance at stardom as her family faces down eviction, but once production begins, she realizes too late the cost of her involvement.

Alona (Miya Nolasco) feels suffocated by her mother's overprotective behavior. Deprived of male company, she answers the first guy who counts her. In trying to control her daughter, the more she is losing her now.

When Adam and Erik sneak away from their party to buy alcohol from a dealer, ambiguities arise about the price. A problem which eventually shoves the guys into a feud between the most superior dealer-gangs in Stockholm.

A sacred statue is stolen from the Shaolin Buddist Temple after a vicious Warlord assassinates the Abbott of Shaolin. A group of Shaolin nuns and village girls assemble to bring the Warlord to justice.
The true story of Terry Jean Moore, a young woman who is imprisoned for 7 years on account of a "five dollar" robbery. In prison she gets pregnant by a jailer and has to fight to keep her child.
Best friends Lucy, Eva, Ashley, Beth and Margot have a sleepover like any other - until murder joins the party. A tale of friendship, betrayal, madness, and the search for some decent dick.
A guilt-ridden hit man tries to quit his job after a traumatic killing, before his boss kidnaps his wife in order to make him do one last job.
Dave Campbell lives a life that can only be described as 'funny because it isn't happening to you'. One day, he decides to dedicate his efforts to a worthy cause...with minimal results.
The Story of sixteen under-aged kids who chose not to run from the advancing British Army in our last war with Great Britain war of 1812.
A troubled Iraq War veteran struggling to reintegrate into society sets out on a cross-country journey with the hope of reuniting with his young son.

Shadyside, 1978. School's out for summer and the activities at Camp Nightwing are about to begin. But when another Shadysider is possessed with the urge to kill, the fun in the sun becomes a gruesome fight for survival.

movie_name: The Glory and Misery of Human Life
description: Two young lovers, Anna and Martti, are split apart but are reunited many years later when their lives have changed considerably. Anna is a war widow; Martti a writer, is married, and has five children.

Original title "Kanku Purayu Ma Amba na chok ma" won Many Govt Awards. It's story of an NRI girl, who hates India but lives with Indian culture. A love Triangle and conspiracy of marraige settlement for green card.

A group of people venture into a remote village to ask a mysterious faith healer to cure their ailing loved ones, unaware that through unforeseen consequences, every miraculous "healing" would soon be repaid in kind.
A doctor and his assistant hunt down a vampire named Count Frankenhausen, who is terrorizing the populace.
A mathematician genius, Mathi, has another identity, Cobra, who commits intelligent crimes using maths.

A young woman returns home to her family vineyard after her father dies in an accident on the winery. But when his death is ruled a murder and her mother becomes the prime suspect she must uncover the truth.

movie_name: Salem and the Witches of Hollow City
description: When an evil witch threatens to banish Halloween, a black cat, a scarecrow, a pumpkin, and a ghost startle together to stop the evil witch before Halloween fades away forever.

Su-man and his friends visit upscale bars to collect money from the patrons to use in the war against Japan. The Japanese colonial police get wind of their activities and begin to hunt down the fundraisers one-by-one.

Mad with grief after the death of his Kiowa wife, Talbot awaits death under a tree with her body beside him. She begins to haunt him because he won't burn her. His father, who bought him the wife, thinks her sister might reason with him.
A man becomes an unwitting superhero after a drunken night leads him on a quest to save his love, his life, and his species from a murderous barbecue enthusiast.
This film tells about the vengeance of Yan Qingyi in order to revenge her sister and finds ways to approach Ren Haoming, the president of Renshi Group, who is a sadist.
A young couple in need of a break, venture off into a vastly remote area, and discover strange noises originating from deep within the woods.
A post-apocalyptic tale, in which a lone man fights his way across America in order to protect a sacred book that holds the secrets to saving humankind.
Hell's Kitty is a comedy horror series based on the true life events of Nick, a Hollywood writer, and Angel, his possessed and very possessive pussycat.

movie_name: Bikram Singha: The Lion Is Back
description: Gupi, a conman faces hurdles after he meets a girl who pretends to be his daughter, later learns that he has a deadly doppelganger ACP Bikram Singha Roy.
A reclusive, introverted singer-songwriter falls in love with an ambitious, pragmatic girl who changes how he sees the world and himself.

Aftermath asks the question, "What would happen if the man on the street really did try to stop a bank robber?" The answer involves an insane florist, an irate fruit cart vendor, and a slimy lawyer named Uncle Stan.
It tells the story of of an average middle-class boy who wants to become a successful singer in his life despite having obstacles in his way.
If you're guilty, beware The Laughing Mask. Jake Johnson lost his wife and child to a psychotic killer known as Laughing Mask and goes to extreme measures to achieve his revenge.
Two Marines follow Princess Lulu into Iraqi-occupied Kuwait to save her from the evil Colonel Fawwaz.

After returning from a woodland hike, Clara's daughter's behavior turns increasingly bizarre and dangerous. Convinced that her daughter is possessed by the Devil, Clara turns to Father Daniels, the family priest.

Set during a mysterious nationwide blackout, a violent gang of criminals launch an assault on a police station. But soon the criminals and cops inside are forced into an uneasy alliance when the compound is besieged by demonic creatures.
A soap opera about the love affair between a poor composer and a high society woman, who almost sacrifices herself for him.
A rescue attempt of a German traitor during World War I has unexpected consequences and sets off an adventure across the Arabian desert.

Mae Doyle comes back to her hometown a cynical woman. Her brother Joe fears that his love, fish cannery worker Peggy, may wind up like Mae. Mae marries Jerry and has a baby; she is happy but restless, drawn to Jerry's friend Earl.

In the 1930s, Marjorie Kinnan Rawlings moves to Florida's backwaters to write in peace. She feels bothered by affectionate men, editor and confused neighbors, but soon she connects and writes The Yearling, a classic of American literature.
A small shop owner catches a little mutant Octopus and accidentally becomes involved in a conspiracy involving genetic mutation experiments and a giant kaiju Octopus.

A business man must choose between keeping his promise to marry a poor village belle, or making it big by wedding his boss's daughter: a wealthy Westernized girl who bares a striking resemblance to his first love.
A unique encounter, meanders the past, present and the future of two people meeting for the first time.
A famous social media influencer, Hunter Mills, returns to his deceased father's small town ranch after he loses his marketing job in the big city, and discovers the importance of true connection.
A couple who sacrifice everything to achieve the highest possible accolade in the culinary world - a Michelin star.
Venu, an orphan, who works as a taxi driver, is accused of kidnapping Gopika Varma, an NRI. When the police come after him, he tries to prove his innocence.

On 25th April, 2011 a horrific and tragic incident occurred which remained unsolved. Till the date no explanation or evidence found to be satisfying to suggest what exactly happened on that day. This film is a record of those events.
A child cannot stand the idea of having a new brother and dreams about drinking milk from the breasts of his mother again. The child asks the moon to bring him a teet only for him.
After many years of rambling across Europe the aging Giacomo Casanova is impoverished. He wants to return to Venice but he doesn't dare going there directly, because he was a fugitive when he left.
An evil warlock now rules the magical planet Ressear. To conquer her fallen empire Sofia Hayden must find the legendary Royal 4 reincarnated bodies.

The action of the film develops in the last days of the Great Patriotic War. The Nazis are retreating from the occupied cities with battles, and in one of them a young sniper from the Hitler Youth is lost.
A young Shaolin follower reunites with his discouraged brothers to form a soccer team using their martial art skills to their advantage.
A hard-working young man meets and falls in love with his sister's bridesmaid. He soon finds out how disturbed she really is.
A Sicilian seamstress who idolizes her husband must deal with several family crises upon his sudden death.
A mad scientist kidnaps and mutilates a trio of tourists in order to reassemble them into a human centipede, created by stitching their mouths to each others' rectums.
A disturbed movie theater employee imagines that by changing his own life he can change the direction of the movie he watches every day at work.
After the mysterious death of a young man his autopsy reveals a jump drive in his stomach. It contained footage that goes back six months before his death and was title "The Truth."

Pooja and Rahul join their ten year old son Bunny in a boarding school Bunny is kicked out of the school for his weird behaviour A deeply upset Pooja takes him to a psychiatrist for treatment the doctor suggests a unique therapy
Undercover cop Nico Giraldi travels to New York and Las Vegas to find a crooked cop who gave his squadron back in Italy a bad name.
Disguised as clerks, two young Americans slip into a sleepy Mexican village where they are caught by a ruthless band of bikers and turned into slaves to help with their harvesting of drug crops.
Six college-aged friends have fun on a camp out until all but one of them begins acting strange and violent.

An Australian sheep rancher fulfills his promise to his dying mother by visiting his uncle on the French Riviera. He meets and falls in love with a Russian princess who was forced into a bad marriage to save her family from the Communists.

Quirt Evans, an all round bad guy, is nursed back to health and sought after by Penelope Worth, a Quaker girl. He eventually finds himself having to choose between his world and the world Penelope lives in.
Sato is 27 years old, lives in the northern prefecture of Sendai and is single. He is searching for the spark and explosion that will change his life and give him love and romance.
A citywide blackout turns a police officer's task of transporting a dangerous criminal into a fight for his life.
Dr. Jekyll faces horrible consequences when he lets his dark side run wild with a potion that transforms him into the animalistic Mr. Hyde.
A depressed wealthy businessman finds his life changing after he meets a spunky and care-free young woman.
Abandoned by her fiancé, an educated black woman with a shocking past dedicates herself to helping a near bankrupt school for impoverished black youths.
The cast of a horror film go out for dinner with their director one night and they all exchange horror stories.
A group of uninspired old friends become the only hope for survival against an unwelcome shape-shifting creature during their high school reunion.
When Chris Shaw takes his friends out to an isolated house to make a web video, they summon an evil spirit and must fight for survival once it begins to hunt them down.
When a man confesses to his fiancée that he had a "one night stand," he's shocked when the fiancée accepts his suggestion that she see other men.

Three couples who know one another are stuck at home during the beginning of lockdown. Jonathan, Clarissa and Paul will see their lives turned upside-down, forced to look at each other and ultimately at themselves.
The story follows this brother-sister incest from a women's perspective, rather than looking at the taboo romance from a conventional male point of view.
Wyoming cowhand and gambler Trampas is sent by his employer to Mexico to buy a bull but in Laredo he unwillingly joins three Texas Rangers on a dangerous mission into Mexico.

A perpetually stoned 17-year-old wannabe singer believes only one thing stands between herself and stardom - her psycho ex. She elicits the aid of her ex-con brother but he wants more than she's willing to give - her newborn baby girl.

Attacked by terrorists and hunted by demons, a journalist finds herself unwittingly teamed up with a mysterious ex-priest and cocky history professor to recover the ancient relic that controls time before it falls into the wrong hands.
A when a film crew arrives to shoot their overnight stay at a haunted house, things get a bit dicey.
Follows a young woman discovering a frightening video game character intent on crossing into the real world.

Peter meets an old girlfriend Ellen. They agree that if they are still single a year later they will get back together. Shortly after he meets Vera. During a trip Vera's interest turns towards Leslie. Is it to late to get back with Ellen?

A bunch of hippies move into an abandoned farmhouse out in the woods in rural New England. Deputy Richard is always hassling them and of course when the bloody Bigfoot murders start, the hippies are blamed.

In the streets of Paris, Juste collects the last memory of people only he can see, before helping them into the afterlife. Juste is a ghost. But one day Agathe recognizes him. She knew him when he was alive.
William Lee wrote, produced, directed and starred in this film, which concerns a secret agent guiding an adventurous female professor on a search for the Treasure of the Ninja.
A clothing designer tries to save her struggling boutique store by having a tumultuous weekend sale of her shop's inventory by playing on the addictions of shopping for the women of Beverly Hills.
From a famous Chinese opera, the story of The Butterfly Lovers: the attempt at romance by a young couple is thwarted by conflicts with family.
While trying to solve the murder of his mentor, a man learns of an underground brotherhood of blue collar workers, who eavesdrop on the powers that be, in order to acquire key information.
The story follows complicated relation between Adas Miauczynski "Cezary Pazura" and Gosia "Katarzyna Figura".

Everyone loves camping in the woods. It's usually a calm, relaxing getaway. For five friends, it's the perfect way to send off one of their own. Amongst the partying and debauchery comes something much more sick and depraved.
150 Years ago The British (Queen) took something that's doesn't belong to them. It's priceless, it's pride, it's dignity. Today, He wants it back at all cost.
Prabhu, a college student, falls in love with Shruthi, a governor's daughter. On knowing about their love affair, her father imprisons Prabhu and forbids him to meet Shruthi.
An immortal Scottish swordsman faces off with other immortal warriors in order to obtain a coveted ability.
Leopard is a rough man who works for Ching Yun and Cheng Ming. He bullies his very elderly colleague, supervisor Lao Ma. He is brutal with his girlfriend Ting Ting.
An overweight bachelor is fat, 40 and fed up--to the gills--but when his obese cousin Sal dies at 39, he must finally come to terms with his own weight problem.
A disastrous season on a remote Yukon mine becomes a fight for survival for a feuding family of suburban low-lifes when one of them shoots dead a Sasquatch.

movie_name: Darkness on the Edge of Town
description: After a deadly encounter with his Russian half-brother, Nick Salt must find St. Stephen's golden shotgun and avenge his friends.
A deserted old building is discovered by several young people. An unknown mystery surrounds the building.
Seductive vampire Carmilla Karnstein and her family target the beautiful and the rich in a remote area of late eighteenth-century Gemany.

A businessman from New York breaks his engagement to follow his new lover, an aspiring model, to her home city of Shanghai where he learns that her life is in danger by a group of gangsters, thereby endangering his own life.
A photographer plagued by horrific nightmares in which he kills the young female models he shoots is shocked to discover that there is a serial killer in his city who is targeting attractive women.

When five high school seniors head to a house party, they end up at the wrong address, where they are confronted by a murderous husband and wife who have sinister plans for the young females in the group.
An indecisive guy who has been rejected by several women, finds himself in a spot when he has to choose between two women.
A three-way friendship between two free-spirited professional football players and the owner's daughter becomes compromised when two of them become romantically involved.
Sargad is about a young woman, Elina, that drives to a cabin with her mom and younger sister to spread her dad's ashes. They encounter three brothers that will make their weekend a living hell.

A fashion photographer and seven models travel to a South American island fortress, ostensibly to do a fashion shoot. In reality, the photographer is a mercenary, and their job is to free an imprisoned rebel leader.

KIRI CRAW's body was never found. Only three living people know the truth of what happened to her: her jock boyfriend; a spiritual fanatic incarcerated for her disappearance; and her mentally disturbed brother.
A man who joins the HK police force to track down a murderer and then struggles with his desire for vengeance and his new-found respect for the law.
A retired police detective and a young amateur sleuth team up to find a serial killer who's resumed a killing spree in Turin, Italy after a 17-year period.
A young lady in dire financial straits meets a homeless old woman who gives her a love potion, but she must promise not to use it for her own gain.
A pretty young Azeri woman Giuli and Georgian guy Mitro are very in love. But because of traditions she can not marry him. Young people run away to get happy together, but without success.

A Pittsburgh detective is kicked off the force for beating a rape suspect and moves to L.A. There, he becomes the central force in a bullet ridden neighborhood battle to win back its streets from brutal gang members.
A young blacksmith returns from beyond the grave to exact revenge on the clergymen, who framed and sentenced him to death as a witch in 1666.

Brianna married a man she thought would protect her forever. But soon discovers Vincenzo has a dark secret and an evil family with connections controlling his narcissistic sociopathic traits and will go to any lengths to keep the secret controlled and hidden.
Max works in a marketing agency, the days are alike, he can't take the life he leads anymore, he meets Rose, a young student who will change his fate.

A woman walks into the life of a debt collector, who works for a loan shark, claiming to be his mother. He tries to turn over a new leaf moved by her affection, but can he do so after having ruined the lives of so many people?
Five sisters in 19th century England must cope with the pressures to marry while protecting themselves from a growing population of zombies.

movie_name: A Few People, a Little Time
description: The unusual bond between a blind female writer and an acclaimed poet changes their lives and forms an exceptional creative cooperation, free of politics and the complexities of mundane life.
College kids stray from a hiking path to become trapped in a parallel world where a deadly nightmare begins to claim them one by one.
When a group of friends decide to spend a night in a resort, they start disappearing one by one. Now who will survive till the end of the night?

movie_name: Teenage Dead Girl: The Worst Case of the Mondays
description: High schooler, Barbara, and Crazed scientist gets killed by a mysterious killer. When their consciences switch their bodies they're reanimated as zombies. Both decide to track him down and look for a way to reverse the switch.
A woman whose husband is fighting in Vietnam falls in love with another man who suffered a paralyzing combat injury there.

It's story of how the girls leaves the love of her life just to pursue green pasture in Australia only to find out that the same guy would have touched new heights in the same country he is in after she left her.
This is a comedy about couples from the same family, hit by the economic crisis in Mexico. The plot turns around the eternal question of whether it is worth it to live as a couple.

Teenager Malencia Vale leaves home in order to participate in a program designed to groom leaders in the effort to rebuild the United States, which has crumbled due to biological war and natural disasters.

movie_name: Around the World Under the Sea
description: The crew of a five-man submarine travels the world oceans, planting sensors on the ocean floor to warn scientists of any impending earthquakes.

Spy Quest is about when two Spy's take a journey to find out who took the diamond, and the Jewels. The two spy's are trying to find out who the person was who took the diamond before their time is up.
A young woman from a small mining town turns into a cold blooded killer after being kidnapped by a gang of ruthless human traffickers.
Tine wants to get rid of a gay admirer so he finds a fake boyfriend: Sarawat. The two become close and intense emotions soon erupt. As Tine and Sarawat enter the second year of their relationship.

During a Solar apocalypse, a physicist and his military wife escape underground at the Collider. Survivors expose a deadly truth kept by the government alliance with aliens. Now they must prevent time from destroying their hope of escape.
A bizarre love triangle forms between a young Catholic upskirt photographer, a misandric girl and a manipulative cultist.

Skimmer Barnes and Tommy Whelan are towing their motorboat with their car when they decide to pursue a limousine so they can talk to its occupant, Jane Townsend. However, they only succeed ...                See full synopsis »
After a plane crashes in the heart of the Amazon, the survivors are hunted by an unknown jungle predator and must desperately find a way to escape.

Nora and Hae Sung, two deeply connected childhood friends, are wrest apart after Nora's family emigrates from South Korea. 20 years later, they are reunited for one fateful week as they confront notions of love and destiny.
An emotionally disturbed yoga teacher tries to survive an apocalypse caused by an experiment at the Large Hadron Collider in Geneva.

Town Mall 2 is an adaptation of the famous horror novel 'Town Mall'. This film revolves around the mystical story of Ariani's life which eventually invites the revenge of the ethereal beings who continue to haunt her life.
An uncouth lady finds love with her cousin's ex, but her cousin tries everything possible to thwart the new relationship.
An estranged father and son - a career criminal and a strong-willed cop - must team up when the latter's child is kidnapped for ransom.
Shiva falls in love with Pooja, a girl raised in the US, who is in India visiting her grandparents. When she wants to return to the US, he creates a fictitious character to impress her.

movie_name: Dr. Satán y la magia negra
description: In the hell, the King demon orders Dr. Satan to return to earth to destroy Yei Lin, a powerful Wizard of black magic, and steal the formula that transforms all metals into gold in order to become the master of the world.
Four young girls head out into the Canadian woods for some outdoors fun. They wind up running into 2 brutal and sadistically inhuman rednecks. A blood-soaked fight for survival ensues.
Manicurists Sally, Irene, and Mary hope to be Broadway entertainers. When Mary inherits an old ferry boat, they turn it into a successful supper club.
An axe murderer terrorizes a small Northern California mountain community, while two young computer-obsessed adults attempt to solve the killings.
Inspired by true events, a horrific serial killer threatens the lives of a peach farm workforce in a rural town of Northern California.
A desperate prostitute seduces Trent, a recently released ex-con, to help her escape her pimp. Only things go horribly wrong when Trent tries to buy her from her pimp and things get violent.
A police officer from Vizag finds himself in a rut when false allegations are levied against him. He has 24 hours now to prove his innocence.

David's wife died 2 years ago. He, his teen daughter Rachel, her cute friend and 2 in-laws trying to fix him up with a friend, are all spending the weekend at his beach house. David still "talks to his wife" and neglects Rachel.
A bad taste extreme low budget splatter movie filled with zombies, witches and gallows of blood, just to save your day.

Anna leaves Athens to live with her boyfriend in Glasgow: a new life that triggers traumatic memories. But as it descends into violent paranoia, Anna realizes that one of her new co-workers holds the key to her past in Greece.
Dealing with the struggles of society when released from jail, Big Syke must maneuver through the dangerous streets of Inglewood as the "Last Thug Standing".

A girl who wishes for a traditional relationship free from technology finds love in a boy who happens to be a web developer. Will the boy bow down to the girl's tech free whim or will the girl embrace the very thing she vowed to avoid?

movie_name: Mrs. Stevens Hears the Mermaids Singing
description: In the 1920s she wrote a scandalous novel about two women in love. Now, it's 1964 and everyone wants to know, "Who was the muse?"
A group of road tripping friends find more than they bargain for when they stumble upon a brothel specializing in a peculiar type of service.

Shun and Nagisa first meet and fall in love during high school. However, despite strong feelings, they go their separate ways. Years later, Shun is now living alone in a rural area when Nagisa arrives with his six-year-old daughter, Sora.
A group of rich decadents pick up wanderers from the streets and take them back to their large villa, where they are initially treated with consummate care but things take a turn for the worse.
Motorist Martin Delambre attempts to keep evidence of his family's bizarre experiments in teleportation hidden from his wife, who is hiding secrets of her own.

Jake Alexander never knew his father who went to military prison for brutally killing a man. Fighting is in his blood, he is looked after by his uncle Jack former kumite fighter and Uncal Duck to train him to the fight of his life.
During the French Revolution, a French nobleman saves the 10-year-old son of Louis XVI and Marie Antoinette from the guillotine with the help of an English woman.
A lonely man's voyeuristic obsession with the private lives of his co-workers spirals into a desperate attempt for attention and a violent spectacle of horror.

Based on the autobiography of Lee Sang, a psychologist in the 1930's who blindy ignored the relations his wife was having with the men around her as well as ignoring the girl who was flirting with him
Griff wants to maintain just a superficial relationship with his all-gay boyfriend, who gets seriously wounded in a gay bashing.

Based off of the tale by Hans Christian Andersen, Little Mermaid tells the story of a young mermaid leaving the sea for a human she thinks that she knows. Everything isn't as it seemed and she must face the harsh realities of the world.
A grieving couple travels to a small town to recover from the death of their child, but the wife's grief causes her to slowly lose her mind.

The residents of a suburban high-rise apartment building are being infected by a strain of parasites that turn them into mindless, sex-crazed fiends out to infect others by the slightest sexual contact.
Jane left gymnastics when an injury killed Olympics hope. Now 43, she gets a chance to perform a demanding "dance" in the air with Serena. The intimate act makes her forget her dead marriage.
Kevin takes his wife Joy to the beach for a vacation. What he doesn't realize is that there are clowns coming out of the ocean.
In order to inherit a fortune a young woman agrees to marry a young man. She soon discovers that his family harbours a dark past involving a monstrous beast.
Newlyweds are terrorized by demonic forces after moving into a large house that was the site of a grisly mass murder a year before.

movie_name: Syupeo Hong Gil-dong 5: Buchae dosawa Hong Gil-dong
description: Korean folk hero Hong Kil-dong is back to save the day, this time he must take on the evil Golden Magic King, who has the power to transform villainous people into monsters under his control.
Feeling his life has been ruined by constant rejection from women, a 40-year-old virgin decides to kill all of the women who've scorned him.
When a nuclear device causes an electromagnetic pulse that kills power to more than 200 million people, a teenage girl must help lead her family to survival in a dark new world.

A malevolent dark web scheme ensnares a group of friends to take an adventure to help restore an old Finca in Spain, which on the surface appears benign, but is a cover for a deeply disturbing set of nightmares
When a rash of demonic possessions occurs in Los Angeles, the Vatican summons an Irish Priest with mysterious powers: Ciaran the Demon Hunter.

British retirees travel to India to take up residence in what they believe is a newly restored hotel. Less luxurious than advertised, the Marigold Hotel nevertheless slowly begins to charm in unexpected ways.
After the murder of an amateur paleontologist over a controversial fossil, a coded map to the dig site plunges the man's son into the same world of scientific cover-up that killed his father.
Weekend campers, an escaped convict, young lovers and a police officer experience a night of terror when a hostile visitor from another world descends on a small Arizona town.

When Alkis is released from prison, he accidentally meets a girl and falls in love with her. She will return to her rich friend and Alkis finds his old collaborators, with whom he organizes another robbery.

Duke lives a life off grid as a border smuggler. When a job goes south he becomes embroiled in a deadly mission against his will, sending him on an epic journey. Old scars rip open as he's pursued by gangsters, border cops and past demons.
A provincial youngster who travels up to Paris to sit an entrance exam for a "grande école". His path crosses that of a young woman and they strike up a short-lived relationship.

Melanie has just gained consciousness to discover that she is being held hostage by the Walker family so they can harvest her special skin in order to create a breakthrough skin care cream, and bloom the business; also she's not alone..
Mexican immigrants in a small Texas border town, under attack by a local militia group, hire a band of mercenaries to protect them.
Thirumalai, a mechanic, falls in love with Sweta. However, her father, the owner of a TV channel, is unhappy with their relationship. He takes Arasu help to create differences between the couple.

Rescued from Syrian extremists, suffering PTSD and haunted by the death of his wife, ex Devgru Lieutenant Chase Black is pulled back into an op where he is torn between the influence of an enigmatic ex-SAS Major and his former Chief.
The story of a man suffering from Schizophrenia and the psychotherapist who tries to find him with the help of his young Bi-Polar patient.

Abahani's father was killed during a function. With Police not doing enough to solve the murder and catch the killer Abahani takes the help of one young lad to solve the murder mystery by connecting the dots.
L.A.'s Chinatown is disrupted by the cross-town rivalry between two kickboxing clubs, as the competitive sport is catapulted from the ring of a gymnasium to a ring of fire.
At the discovery of his ability to work miracles, Juvenal becomes a media sensation, but now he's prone to those who want to exploit him.

A middle-aged man discovers an injured refugee woman trembling in the corner of his bar in Kabukicho. He quickly becomes aware that her life is in his hands when he learns she is hiding from the yakuza.
Django's father is framed by his business partner Clusker and shot by a bounty Killer. Django inherits his fathers part of the business and a score to settle with Clusker.
A portrayal of the triumphs and tragedies of two English families, the upper-crust Marryots and the working-class Bridgeses, from 1899 to 1933.

Franz, a retired allied WW11 spy is losing his memory to alzheimers. As his memory fades he recounts his stories to his grandson. He tells of his lost love Anne (Bridie Latona) and his assignation attempt on Hitler.

To pay back her blood debt to a valiant king, Red Sonja, the She-Devil with a Sword, agrees to lead his doomed army to their certain death against the invading plague-ridden forces of Dark Annisia, Sonja's blood sister who's gone mad.
A docile man gets enraged when a politician's son throws acid on her face and later kills the miscreant. He is then hunted by the police and politicians who wants him dead.
When two people who no longer believe in love find each other, nothing can get in the way of their blossoming romance - except for a playful farce of miscues, meddling, and mistaken identity.

ANA is: a) An investigation of a cyber-sect linked to the disappearances of several women online. b) A moodboard of the aesthetization of self-destruction. c) A found footage documentary about today's subcultures.
They're only stories - or are they? Delve into these terrifying French shorts for some quick scares, if you dare. A compilation of Horror shorts from daring French filmmakers.
A biographical fiction about a second-generation Korean in Japan named Kwon Hyi-ro (AKA Kin Kiro) who became a national hero in South Korea after holding 18 Japanese citizens hostage in 1968.
Soviet KGB General Marenkov defects to the Americans and together with his CIA handler Harry Wargrave they plan an operation meant to reveal the KGB agents in Europe.
A group of teenagers break into an isolated storage facility with the intent of robbing the lockers and unknowingly unleash a terrifying menace that turns them into zombies.
A bank manager and his wife, still grieving over their daughter who died in a fire, become pawns in a bank heist with ties to corruption and fraud.
A young girl is kidnapped by a serial killer. The serial killer uses manholes to kidnap and kill his victims. The young girl's older sister tries to save her before it's too late.

PREYTA follows estranged siblings as they return to their childhood home. When they recover memories of the terrifying Entity that tortured their family when they were children, their presence reawakens Preyta and it begins to feed again.
Following the loss of his family, a man attempts suicide only to discover upon waking that he can identify people who are about to die
Gautam and Anu grow up in traditional households, where they are barred from speaking with people of the opposite gender. How do the two handle their newfound freedom when they move to a city?

Strange incidents occur in the heart of shonajhuri forest in rural bengal (the backdrop for both stories) which develops an ominous character of its own that allures and finally engulfs our protagonists.
Two years after their loved ones were murdered in obsessive rage, the survivors are dragged into a horrific psychological breakdown - and blood soaked plan for revenge.
Kelby is back to his town for his father's funeral. The past that seemed as nightmare and he has forgotten all about is came back.
When Rachel discovers that her twin sister was actually killed in cold blood and did not die in a car accident, she must incite her sister's spirit to take revenge on the killer.
A psychologist is trapped inside a mental institution where all the patients have escaped and are on the rampage.
Two Chinese men go to Copenhagen. While one of them philanders around with various Danish and Asian women, the other falls in love with his Chinese tour guide.
A famous playwright's life is turned upside down when she is forced to look at the choices she has made.
A case full of valuable diamonds ends up in the hands of an evil crime boss and it's up to a vengeful cop to take him down.
A young California surfer has to grow up in a hurry when he is thrown into a Peruvian political prison in 1980.
When Retired Hit-Man, Declan Mandelbaum (AKA: The Stoagy), discovers that his accountant has made off with his entire life savings, he must get a nine-to-five in order to pay his bills.

Eylül, who does not remember the last month after her accident, learns that she was in Bozcaada during this time and goes to Bozcaada to follow the truth and gets close to an artist named Tekin, who knows her.
Most dreaded animal killer and wildlife photographers / animal protectors duo meet in an ironic mistaken identity kidnap drama in dense Indian forest, to learn about human nature.
An instagrammable love story: When Emma leaves LA for adventure in Bali, she realizes that only by loving herself can she truly enjoy the magic of real love with another.
A support group of killers is held regularly. The participants sit in a circle of trust and share their transgressions.

Fu Sheng plays the son of a man who is destined to die at the hands of a swordsman carrying a sword with a teardrop design forged into its blade. He believes that if he carries the sword then his father won't die.
When a bunch of giant monsters attack the city, the heroes of the DC, Marvel, and Harry Potter universes must team up to stop them.

Racky, Brad, Boy, Bimbo and Egay are stowaways from Olongapo City trying to survive in Manila. When they met up with Eric and Anton, they become one big happy family. "Topo Topo Barega," an expression meaning "all for one, one for all."

Chingachgook is about to marry the daughter of the Delaware chief, when the Hurons kidnap her. Chingachgook and his friend Deerslayer try to rescue her though white scalp hunters interfere until the tribes unite against the palefaces.
A twelve-year-old girl is transported by a magical black stallion to the mystical world of ALBION, where she discovers that she alone is the key to saving an entire race of people.
After a doctor commits suicide when his research into human embryos is terminated, his widow seduces and then executes revenge upon those she holds responsible.

The film is a sequel to evergreen Mammooty's gangster film Samrajyam that came out in 1990. The film plots the eventful life of Jordan who is forced to take charge of his father's empire after 23 years.
A single mother who is a renowned hired killer finds it difficult to achieve a balance between her personal and work life.
Three friends decide to become men before graduating college but the women they fall for are not eager to have sex with them. To what length will the friends go to keep their promise?
Set against the pulsating backdrop of rustic North India, Love Hostel traces the volatile journey of a spirited young couple, being hunted by a ruthless mercenary.

Two sisters struggle to cope after the tragic loss of their mother, when they stumble across a mysterious necklace. Emily must overcome this demonic spirit and her mother's sins or risk more tragedy in the family.
A communist journalist and an American liberal photographer try to cohabit with their different perspectives of love and life.
After John is forced into a life of crime to provide for his family, he's too to slow in realising he's in too deep and wants out. Can he get out and save his family?

Fans of an obscure Canadian TV series embark on a location bus tour. When the bus breaks down in a junkyard, this band of misfits find themselves at the centre of a real alien invasion - can their childhood hero help them save the planet?
