On December 5, 2011, the day after the parliamentary elections, the incredible happened. Residents of large cities in Russia, outraged by the large-scale rigging of the voting results, went to rallies.

movie_name: Saikyô heiki joshikôsei: Rika - zonbi hantâ vs saikyô zonbi Gurorian
description: Rika never expected to encounter the living dead as she skipped school to visit her grandfather. She is forced to survive and discovers incredible zombie fighting skills.
Former C.I.A. spy Bob Ho takes on his toughest assignment to date: looking after his girlfriend's three kids, who haven't exactly warmed to their mom's beau.

When a vlogger and her crew embark on their annual river float to commemorate the untimely loss of their friend, they are plunged into a life and death battle with a mysterious local, a sinister paranormal force, and their own fears.
Odessa and Kyle James were just your average American boys until the night they went upstairs and killed their parents in cold blood... and smiled.
For the love of the beautiful Elena the young fisherman's son Marcello turns a whole village upside down.

San Francisco Inspector "Dirty" Harry Callahan must foil a terrorist organization made up of disgruntled Vietnam veterans. But this time, he's teamed with female partner Inspector Kate Moore, with whom he's not too excited to be working.
When Kashan and Nazish cannot give the 'good news' of a baby to father Ranaji even after 3 years of their marriage, all hell breaks loose and the couple's relationship is put to the test.

Thirsty one night stands, confused straight boys, rooftop confessions and a ménage-à-trois that explodes with hilarious results - it's all just part of the package in this latest offering of spirited story-telling from our Gallic friends.
A scientist creates Proteus--an organic super computer with artificial intelligence which becomes obsessed with human beings, and in particular the creators wife.
Horror Anthology produced by filmmakers from around the world, which explores the subject of Demons, with inspiration from Ancient Mythology, Religion and the Cosmological Horror of H. P. Lovecraft.

An infamous inmate on death row is offered once in a life time freedom when a film crew comes to visit him for material, but he must be able to give them five horrific tales for their upcoming project.

movie_name: The Nightmare Returns: A CarrotKiller101 Movie
description: As summer break begins, Arhold, Henry, and Stan are dealing with trouble, that is until they went to bed last night.. and each of them - are about to face - the worst nightmare yet..
After hearing stories of her, a passenger on a cruise ship develops an irresistible infatuation with an eccentric paraplegic's wife.
Somewhere in the countryside near Wilhelmshaven, rural physician Dr. Fachmin is in his second marriage to the much-younger Rachel.
John returns to LA with PTSD from duty in Iraq. 4 guys are beating a hooker outside his home. He acts, leaving 2 dead and 2 hurt. Their gangster boss escalates things.
Follows a single mother who wakes up in a medical facility to find that everyone is dead and she's nine months pregnant.

movie_name: What a Wonderful Time to be a Woman
description: Heartfelt, comedic, and violent, What a Wonderful Time to be a Woman follows Cordelia Renee' through a winding unkempt path of teenage angst and mayhem as she and those who love her come to terms with the trials and tribulations of life.
Recently cuckolded and reeling from a messy divorce, a hapless former singer hits the road and the bar with his all-too-helpful best bud.
When Jenny Cross has to spend summer vacation with her deadbeat dad in his creepy commune, she thinks clean living and boredom will kill her. But some fates are worse than death.
A young man must complete his work at a Navy Officer Candidate School to become an aviator, with the help of a tough Gunnery Sergeant and his new girlfriend.

The alarm blips for the 6th time in an army base on a Swedish Island. Two female bird photographers try to stay hidden as Russian special forces "in ninja suits" make short work of the Swedish conscripts on their way to steal a secret code.

Mara and Clara were switched at birth and grew up in very different environments. Mara lived as the poor daughter of the couple Susan and Gary Davis and Clara, their real daughter, was brought up by the rich Amanthe and Almira del Valle.

Living the good life in Southern California Photographer Peter, his fiance Sara and her mute son Dennis travels to Sweden. Next to Peters's inherited Mansion is an old Haunted Orphanage that no one in the small village wants to talk about.
A young man in a personal tailspin flees from US to Italy, where he sparks up a romance with a woman harboring a dark, primordial secret.

movie_name: Dark Side by Aaron Alexandre Dumas
description: A Filipino American fortune 500 CEO uses his Dark Side to embrace adversity and overcome the struggles of life to succeed and bring those who did him wrong to justice.
A neurotic couple's obsession with a mysterious puzzle comically unravels their world, disconnecting them from reality and jeopardizing their fragile relationship.
A young girl in another solar system asks an innocent question that sets off a chain reaction of adventure, destruction and tragedy.
An ambitious lumberjack abandons his saloon girl lover so that he can marry into wealth, but years later becomes infatuated with the woman's daughter.
An alien prince is raised by a professor on Earth. When an alien witch arrives to destroy him, the professor and the prince's young friends must combine their skills and abilities to rescue him.

A group of teenagers decide to go on a trip to Via Transilvanica, where they find a ghost named Katharina. They decide to bring her back in town, and try to integrate her into society. Katharina was Vlad the Impaler mistress.

movie_name: Master Z: The Ip Man Legacy
description: While keeping a low profile after his defeat by Ip Man, Cheung Tin Chi gets into trouble after getting in a fight with a powerful foreigner.
Well done bio pic of a notorious Filipino gangster in the late 40's until his death at the age of 26 in 1951.
Four ex-samurai are hired to find and kill ninja infiltrators who are intent on destroying the Matsuyama clan.
A female WWII pilot traveling with top secret documents on a B-17 Flying Fortress encounters an evil presence on board the flight.
A group of college students are led by their professor into the mountains in search of the Yeti. The students start to be killed off one by one.

ONE is a story of a journey that takes a group of friends to a strange place where one entity lurks waiting to unleash evil upon its hapless victims. The whole movie set from an evening of a Friday till morning of the successive Sunday.
The story of the film revolves around the inheritance struggle of a very old house, where the grandmother asks all her family members to live in this house for a few days before agreeing to sell it.
A group of five surviving soldiers in the late 1300's are returning home, however along the journey they encounter an unforeseen turn of events.

Sedat, a young man, meets three women while traveling by train. Things get complicated when Sedat, who has a relationship with the singer Cahide, falls in love with a woman named Nalan, whom he met on the train.

A Media Press Team Looking for the Craftsman Beyond a Haunted Bungalow, But Gets Trapped by a Team of Rubbers in the same Bungalow. Who will survive? The Runners or The Press Reporters? is the key point of the Movie.

CIA Colonel Harper's men are robbing military armories in order to supply South American rebels. They hide near Granite Lake, a small town policed by sheriff Jack Steiger. When colonel's men let loose on the town, Jack must stop them.
On a Mysterious Island Grand Masters of Martial Arts train the Greatest Warriors of all time to find who will become the ultimate Island Warrior

Two rather different families are joined when Meja and Sunny choose to get married on the Swedish countryside. 10 minutes of madness during the wedding leads in to a year long trip that turns the lives of everyone involved up side down.

A grief-stricken man who just lost his mother has a one night stand with a maid. What he doesn't know is that she's a virgin. He returns to his sad world of perfume business while she, unable to forget her first lover, follows him.

movie_name: Love and Death in the Garden of the Gods
description: An old professor rents a mysterious old villa, and finds a tape recorded by a previous occupant, detailing her debauched lifestyle and the events leading to her murder.
With the younger sister being targeted by monsters, the elder sister must protect her by training hard as a Demon Hunter.

Two men opposite sides of social conflict look for answers to the first bloody violent event with conflicts. The real search is not about the answers, but the right questions. Do they have the strength to stop the drums of civil war
In Paris, six people all look for love, despite typically having their romantic aspirations dashed at every turn.

Ajay takes on one last mission for Interpol, finding out who a rogue agent, who killed his brother, is working for. What Interpol thinks to be a simply criminal organization turns out to be a bio terrorist cell whom have a plan for a big bio terrorist attack that would mean the end of days. Ajay and Interpol must do anything in their power to stop it from happening.
Anna is a poor girl who loves Erik, the son of a rich farmer. His parents are however determined to make Erik marry the rich Britta.

It tells the tale of a young girl named Jade and a terracotta warrior named Magnus who must team up to fight the creatures that keep attacking their Qin dynasty underground city, and who eventually fall in love.
Set near the turn of the 18th-century in China, thirteen women train to become nuns after they are ravaged by bandits.

Ngau, a cook in the Hong Kong countryside, is trying to save his son from a vengeful evil spirit who was wronged years ago by Ngau's past life. In the process, Ngau seeks the help of Mrs. Bud Lung, who can communicate with the other side.

A newly married couple discovers disturbing, ghostly images in photographs they develop after a tragic accident. Fearing the manifestations may be connected, they investigate and learn that some mysteries are better left unsolved.
The story is about 5 characters who have a dream of becoming great musicians. To accomplish this, they look for a peaceful place to work on their music.
A married couple decide to spend a weekend in a remote cabin, but the romantic journey takes a turn for the worst, when a sneaking suspicion becomes pure madness.

Paranormal Investigator Trevor Night discovers his son has the gift to see spirits. Using his son Trevor begins to study spirits in the hope of finding his deceased wife but in doing so risks the relationship of father and son.
Calling Bell is a hindi dubbed Horror movie. It follows the incident that a group of friends encounter, while on a vacation.

Sikandar is union leader of workers in a factory which is owned by Chawla a corrupt criminal lawyer . when he refuses to take bribe. Sikander and his family are killed .Sikander returns back. how will he face Chawla ?
A young brawler falls in love with a beautiful artist and must choose between his support system and his dreams.
The siblings Riitta and Anja love the same man, the treasurer Jyri Mara. Riitta ends up marrying Jyri, but when the couple loses their children Riitta gets jealous and mad.

Coming from a police family, Tom Hardy ends up fighting his uncle after the murder of his father. Tom believes the killer is another cop and goes on the record with his allegations. Demoted then to river duty, the killer taunts Tom.
Special unit of police and border guards are fighting against foreign smugglers in Far East of Russia in early 90s.
Notorious gangster, Pat Tate, rises through the ranks of Essex's criminal underworld. A prequel to the 'Rise of the Footsoldier' franchise.
In this film, an illiterate guy named Sankar gets married. When his learns that he is not educated, she leaves him. The movie is about how Sankar proves himself by becoming successful.
A duchess persuades a wife to leave a Polish violinist but she returns when he is wounded in a duel.

Judyta and Adam love each other very much, but everyday life starts getting hard. Judyta's daughter turns eighteen soon and she has just "unblocked the fuse in a hormone bomb". Despite the problems, Judyta and Adam plan to get married.

Zara (Gillian White) and Brian (Michael Jai White) are living the perfect small town life when a mysterious stranger from Zara's secret past kidnaps their daughter and now they must race to save her life.
A tough, New York City ex-cop relentlessly searches for his kidnapped teenage daughter whom is held by a twisted psycho after mistaking her for the daughter of a wealthy businessman.

When a meteorite crashes in the forest of New Mexico, a team of scientists realize that it brought with it some spores that alter the molecular structure of living creatures and turns them into blood-thirsty beings.

Way Institute, a mental hospital, was believed to have been abandoned, given it's location. A man is brutally injured during a mugging and is accidentally taken to Way. What treatment lies ahead for him, makes him wish he was dead.
A passionate writer of film versions for the visually impaired meets an older photographer who is slowly losing his eyesight.
A mysterious disease starts infiltrating a group of gypsies while encamped in the dark woods of Northern Jutland.
The party to end all parties. Spending Halloween night in an abandoned asylum. Nothing could possibly go wrong. Or could it? For one night only. Have you got your invite?
A young Scottish man travels across America in pursuit of the woman he loves, attracting the attention of an outlaw who is willing to serve as a guide.
The movie, "Ronquillo: Tiagong Akyat" was based on the true-to-life story of Santiago Ronquillo, a notorious and dreaded bandit of the 20s and one of the infamous outlaws in Philippine history.

Nathalie and her children move from L.A. to her childhood cottage in the charming town of Mistel Isles, Michigan. With help from the friendly locals and a little bit of magic, she just might re-discover love and her lost Christmas spirit.
A down on his luck philosophy student rents a room in a mysterious town and soon discovers one of the tenants may be conjuring up pure evil with the haunting music he plays at night.
A man and a woman in their mid 20s hangout for a day with each other. They have dreams, doubts, feelings, opinions, like anyone else. But the change is about to come.
Spider-Man must come face-to-face with with his future, as it is thrown at him from multiple directions. He will face his own friends, and decide to save everyone, or the ones he loves.
Taking place 1 year after the events of 3rd Generation, Aaron finds himself fighting to keep his family and the United States together.

A young woman chooses celibacy, turns to religion, and demonizes men in order to control her intense sexual desire. Her sister suddenly visits her seaside village, which opens many old wounds and leads to tragedies.
A black comedy centered on a recently engaged celebrity couple and the fans who have been following every stage of their romance.
A free-spirited, aspiring painter moves to Venice, California where she falls for a charismatic gallery director and learns that commitment is a choice - love is not.

In this parody of the sword and sorcery films, a princess is deposed by an evil sorcerer. She enlists the aid of Deathstalker to battle the forces of evil, including a clone of the princess, and win back her kingdom.
THE FEARLESS CHAMPION OF THE GOOD AND THE RIGHT BATTLES WITH AN ASSORTMENT OF TROUBLE-MAKERS WHO SOW FEAR AMONG HIS TOWNMATES.

Striving for a higher standard of living, a former ice-cream man and a wrestler convince a well-known mobster to hire them. However, they both soon realize that criminal life is not what they were looking for.
A woman meets her male partner for a coffee at his place. The woman discovers a male intruder upstairs and struggles with the decision of waiting for the cops or killing him.

In France, prior to Louis XIV ascending the throne, a young baroness is forced to marry against her will and is caught up in a web of treachery and murder, threatening her and her husband, whom she has come to love deeply.
As Risa's ability to see ghosts continues to disrupt her life, her uncle's peculiar behavior leads her to discover a haunting mystery at his new house.
Er Niu receives a note which was written by her father just before he was murdered. The note includes a list of enemy names. So she works with her brother to start a journey of chase and revenge.
Nalan reminds Murat of his dead wife. After a while, Murat convinces himself that Nalan is his dead wife, Sabiha. Murat loses his sense of reality when a new man gets involved.
Eve is a jungle girl brought up by apes. She is captured with a number of apes by a mad scientist, conducting mind control experiments on them. Eventually she is liberated by a young explorer.

Mark, a local cop is investigating a string of jewel robberies. He soon discovers that the men behind the crimes is the notorious"Red Devil" and his band of Ninjas. Mark teams up with Billy, a man out for revenge.
Famous real life giant sapphire called the Star of India has been stolen. Special agent Nick Goldman is assign to find it.

Sherry Troy, returns, from the war, to find her brother and his family have been savagely murdered. When her retired father is attacked on his ranch by the same gang, they join forces to wipe out a mobbed up arms dealer and his gang.

The story of Alex, a humble police watchman who decides to take control of his luck. After his girlfriends breaks up with him, he decides to steal $ 80,000 and lead a life full of adventures , fulfilling all of his desires.
A young American nurse finds herself haunted by childhood trauma, when she is employed at a remote house to care for a sinister old psychic.

In London UK, a town full of deep seeded corruption, a recently disgruntled Metropolitan Police CID from Special Branch and a relentless freelance Photojournalist, team up to uncover crimes against humanity.
Shruti and Bittoo become partners in their very own "Wedding planning ka bijness" in Delhi and in the process discover friendship, love and one another.

Two best friends accidentally fulfill a pact they made in college when they get drunk in Vegas and get married. With a six month waiting period to get a divorce does the marriage blossom or does the friendship fail?

Max is around thirty and lives with Emma, his best friend. When she tells him that she is moving out, a lot of doubts grow inside Max pushing him to go out at night to a strange and transforming walk through the night of Barcelona.
A couple's road trip is cut short when they pass by an area where millions have mysteriously vanished.

A group of friends with different backgrounds is trying to enjoy a spooky experience at one of the most famous escape rooms in the world. Little they know the game will turn into a true fight for survival.

Based on the 16th-century Chinese novel Feng Shen Yan Yi (The Investiture of the Gods), the story tells of how King Zhou of Shang becomes a tyrant due to the wiles of Daji, a vixen spirit who is disguised as one of his concubines.
A spirit reaches out from beyond the grave in an attempt to contact a young woman to help it avenge its murder.
Rusty, a broke trucker facing eviction agrees to help his sexy neighbor track down her husband's murderer, but he must overcome the ghosts of his past if he's going to do the job.

On Christmas' Eve, uncle Greg and uncle Lillo are suddenly forced to take care of 8 year old nephew. His parents were mistakenly arrested for cultivation of drugs. The two uncles are very different, and inadequate to the task.

From young age Neer (Anubhav Regmi) and Anjana(Sedrina Sharma) were in love however Anjana dies at young age. Than after many years later Anjana's twin sister falls in love with older Neer, however Neer isn't interested in her.
A man gets a job opportunity with a definite requirement of unmarried male, so he decides to conceal his marriage.
BigBraden finds a cow who he befriends, while one of his friends plots against him and his new cow friend.
An evil entity begins to torment a mother and daughter, who are forced to face the inexplicable presence that inhabits the walls of their new home.

Felix Baker, who is a former United States Marine and Law Enforcement Officer returns to Los Santos to meet his friends, unaware of the troubles he will face sooner than expected. Baker is caught by his past and new rivals show up.
A group of high school students are forced into a game where they are hypnotized to commit suicide on an unknown command. Where no one is safe from a sudden death, how can they avoid their fates?
A perpetually miserable man finds happiness when he starts dating a manic pixie dream girl, to the befuddlement of his cynical best friend.

When an angelic teenage virgin is inexplicably impregnated, she discovers she is the linchpin of her stepfather's satanic plan, and must revisit traumatic events from her childhood in order to defeat the Devil.
While investigating a coastal area known for mysterious and unexplained occurrences, an artist and her ex-boyfriend discover an unusual relic and find themselves haunted, and hunted, as a result.

An ancient idol causes mysterious events to unfold upon various characters who come in its vicinity. Can the damages it cause be prevented? Will it be smuggled out for a huge price? What is the history of the idol?

Dutch Art collective KIRAC is known for their provocative films about the established art world. In their twenty-third film in the KIRAC series, they lure a conservative philosopher into a trap by having a sex date with a leftist student.

Three lonely herdsmen starved of female companionship creates the girl of their dreams, from a broom, some straw and a few rags. The creation - Sennentuntschi, lives and breathe to cook, clean and look after the three.
A group of survivalist friends start to disappear one by one at a private camp in this thrilling Korean horror.
A man fails to break up the relationshiop between the girl he loves and her fiance. He decides to prove his love by writing lyrics for the songs she composed and entering them in a contest

In a small border town, a sheriff and his 'associate' who are involved in an operation in which they divert marijuana through the border, must kill another smuggler who has gone into business for himself.

A team of collegians probe the mysterious deaths occurring in their campus wherein the victims die immediately after accepting a friend request on social media from a girl, Mona, who has gone missing.
A headstrong textile student tries to overcome her problems by accepting a summer job offer in Kyrsyä, an offbeat, remote village.
A police officer gains supernatural powers after she's exposed to chemical weapons during a botched undercover operation.
Snow White and her sister Rose Red try to help two princes stop an evil dwarf from robbing the royalty of their wealth.
Jaejoon, isn't your ordinary postman, he delivers letters to Heaven from those missing their loved ones.

On a train heading into the small mountain town of Tranquility, Danny Acuff kisses a beautiful woman before hopping off a still-moving car. At the Tranquility station, the woman, whose name...                See full synopsis »
About a young and ambitious teacher in East Berlin. She is confronted by sloppy attitudes and social problems.
A beautiful Russian ballerina (Goldie Hawn) falls in love with an American news correspondent (Hal Holbrook). The K.G.B. is most displeased, and does everything it can to break them up.
Ji-na and Sang-min are a divorced couple. Rather than going their separate ways, they keep taking revenges to each other.
A couple. A kidnapping. A secret. A weekend to meet the parents becomes a weekend of trying to stay alive for perfect couple Steven and Erika.
A man awakes aboard a dying space prison with no memory of who he is, 2 hours of oxygen left, and 11 of the universes most deadly criminals between him and the last escape pod.
Harlan Draka is a Dampyr, half-human and half-vampire, but he doesn't know it. Soon he will have to face his powers to destroy a terrible Master of The Night.
When a crew of scientists returns from Mars with a sample of the space spores that contaminated their ship, the sample escapes and grows into an enormous, rampaging beaked beast.

movie_name: Hello Again - A Wedding a Day
description: Zazie is invited to her best friend's wedding. She decides to do everything to prevent what is in her eyes the mistake of his life. But when she finds herself trapped in the time-line of the wedding, things get complicated.
The lovely Ramkuvar takes on the identity of Hurricane Special and comes to the rescue of the kingdom of Laxminagar from tyranny.
A wife is bored by her overweight slob of a husband, so she gives in to the temptation of a slickly seductive poet.

While shooting a Halloween news story on horror writer H.P. Lovecraft, reporter Rebecca Marsh discovers that the "fiction" Lovecraft wrote is actually true and the creatures and cults described in his writings really exist.

movie_name: In search of love and the perfect croissant
description: A young couple's one night stand leads to a challenge to run around Paris to find the perfect croissant. When they do they they get married.
An AK Original Series - After losing his father, young Vito is left to take over the family business.
A French fugitive arrives in Genoa, where he becomes entangled with an Italian woman and her daughter.
Jack is in a rut and unsure what to do with his life. He tries to stay focused and get his life in order, but all manner of distractions get in the way.
Indira hates men and only employs women in her company and personal staff. Kaasi enters her life as a driver and soon, one by one, his entire family is employed in her house, with a desired motive.
A recently jailed martial arts master teams up with a wronged woman to take down the man's brother, a coal baron who rules a small town with an iron fist.
Shiva decides to give his criminal life and marry a dancer Seema.But his past still haunts him forcing him to take back the criminal life.
A couple gets involved in a series of difficulties to achieve love and even give up their dignity in exchange.

movie_name: The Untitled Work of Paul Shepard
description: A documentary filmmaker turns the camera on himself to examine the modern day relationship using his own past relationships to guide him. As filming progresses his producer starts to question how much is fact and how much is fiction.
Pipin Kartika is obsessed to get a foreigner / "bule", to be her husband. Frustrated of meeting many jerk bules in Jakarta, Pipin decided to move to Bali to find love.
An ex-mobster is being attacked by people from his past, but they aren't after him because of what he did, but what his sister did.
A group of civilians run for their freedom when they find themselves caught in the middle of a Black Ops program designed to cure PTSD.
A businessman pretends to an aspiring model, only to win love of an model who falsified about being in relationship with the same businessman.
A terrorist places an atom bomb somewhere in an American metropolis. The president of the U.S. has no other choice, he has to call Delta Force.

movie_name: The Hand That Feeds the Dead
description: Under strong influence from his burn victim wife, a wealthy aristocrat does skin transplants from young women, who were captured, operated on against their will and then killed, to fix his wife's burnt body.
An assassin is given a contract to kill seven people around the world only to discover the targets are also assassins who have been hired to kill him.

Deputy Johnson is a Forest County Deputy Sheriff, dispatched to the Manning Home for a 911 hangup. Deputy Johnson arrives to screams coming from inside the house. He rushes into an unknown terror that waits for him 69 years in the past.
Based on actual events, a fisherman tries to survive in the freezing ocean after his boat capsizes off the south coast of Iceland.

"Godrat" of a man from the south is forced to flee against a conspiracy designed for him, because his family no longer accepts him and the people of the city no longer believe him, but after a while he returns to seek revenge.
Las Vegas drug dealer is in deep with the Italian mob over a large amount of missing cocaine. He must get creative to get out from under the mob before they take the ultimate course of action.
Raghu begins walking a fine line between good and evil as he exacts violent revenge on two criminals who killed his family 15 years ago.
When a sole survivor of a fateful hiking trip to the mysterious Dark Peak was taken into police custody, nothing could have prepared them for the horrors they were about to uncover.
Devaraja Prathapa Varma, an underworld don and wealthy businessman wants payback for his brother Karthik Varma's murderers.

movie_name: The Diary of a Big Man
description: A two-timing bigamist finds himself concocting scheme after scheme with his best friend to prevent either of his wives from discovering his bigamy.

A private detective operating in Miami is hired to protect the wife of an African head of state in town for diplomatic business, and to recover the daughter of the leader of a criminal organization, who has been kidnapped by a rival gang.
Eight young adults are sent to do community service at Grizzly Park. There, they are hunted by an escaped serial killer along with the animals of the forest.
In the City of Dallas Texas, during a 24-hour period the paths of 5 people interlace in a violent scenario that will change their destiny.
The real version of the famous US hit movie "Love Story" remade in 1971, but with a swap of roles and happier ending.

Nicholas Moore hires taxi driver Trevor to help catch his fiance cheating. With misunderstandings, and mistaken identity, these defective detectives find themselves on an adventure more dangerous than they bargained for.

Richest man in village, Saban is arranged to marry a beautiful Peril but the girl thinks he is rude and uncivilised bear. After learning this Saban becomes the best gentleman in the world to try to teach her a lesson.

Dr. RJ Stevens is a talk show host who visits his family in the deep south. While there he reunites with his brother Otis, his sister Betty, his cousin/rival Clyde and his childhood love interest Lucinda Allen.
Two women being blackmailed into becoming indentured sexual slaves. One of the women submits readily and the other resists.
A taxi driver finds himself trapped in a time loop. He picks up a pretty woman in a rural area at night. Later she disappears. The loop starts over, when he switches the meter back to vacant.
Sophie, a young volunteer, meets her kindred spirit in Roxie, a girl with a life threatening medical condition and a unique wish to meet Bigfoot.
A man's job requires him to clean a house, which turns out to be haunted. In the course of trying to exorcise the ghost, he falls in love with her.
This film by writer/director Alexis Jacknow will follow a woman's desperate attempt to fix her broken biological clock.
The tale of two brothers with serious financial woes. When a third party proposes they turn to crime, things go badly and the two become enemies.

The abduction of a young American, the son of a wealthy businessman. But when the three kidnappers and their hapless victim get lost in the mountains, they end up spending the night in an abandoned cottage that is under a gypsy spell.
The horror/suspense thriller feature film GEHENNA opens with an intense scene where a large man is running through the dark woods while screaming.

Circumstances force a tough single mother and her two daughters into a life of crime and they quickly become outlaws on the run, picking up partners along the way, and traveling to different states, pursued by the law.
Two car thief brothers, who journey to the south of France for new opportunities, wind up in the cross hairs of the local crime boss.
Planning to steal a massive fortune, a trio of thieves break into the farmhouse of a wealthy family, who prove to be more ruthless adversaries, than expected.
A newly married woman brings an antique Jewish box into her home, unaware that the box contains the ghost of Abraham Ezra.
After a collision with a shipping container at sea, a resourceful sailor finds himself, despite all efforts to the contrary, staring his mortality in the face.

The sultan's succession causes unrest in the west. Bartholomeus joins Réka and her daring squad. Together the make their way to Constantinople to fulfill a dangerous mission. How far will Bartholomeus go?
An ex-con reunites with his estranged wayward 17-year old daughter to protect her from drug dealers who are trying to kill her.

In New York City, potent strands of bath salts have surfaced and have attracted the most devoted bath salt junkies. A young aspiring chemist has developed an even stronger batch... but something has gone horribly wrong.

In a city filled with desolation and faithlessness overturned by gang bangers and police corruption. A stranger ZEKE (protagonist) bursting on the scene to deliver hope, restoration, and a warning of imminent destruction
Continuing the adventure from Road of Bones, the heroes of the film, led by Margelatu, after a series of events and overcoming some obstacles, bring to the country the weapons bought from Vienna.
Incurable romantic Lotte's life is upended when her plans for a picture-perfect wedding unravel--just as her self-absorbed sister gets engaged.
A young couple, in love and facing a life-changing decision, find one seemingly ordinary July 4th cleaved in two by the flip of a coin on the Brooklyn Bridge.
Framed for a robbery he didn't commit, a man flees to a Caribbean island and gets involved with a woman, gun-runners and murder.
A jaded detective struggles to capture his mother's murderer, but with the help of a FBI profiler they quickly realize, the most dangerous serial killer is the one who wants to be possessed.

A mainland security officer must race against the clock to retrieve the son of a man who's holding an entire school hostage.
A woman who lost her daughter to suicide investigates a theory that may have to do with the young girl's death.

Friends travel to a remote Forest in search of treasures that are rumored to be buried there, what they don't know is they are venturing onto ancient Indian burial grounds and are about to make a terrifying discovery.

Dating in any city can be difficult. But dating in Los Angeles is even harder. Between all of the bling, celebrities and velvet ropes, Haley hopes that someone real steps out from behind all of the smoke and mirrors.

Penniless and without a future, an English teacher agrees to tutor a pampered woman, only to become enmeshed in a strange reality and a downward spiral of desire and illusion, guilt and self-contempt. Will the ugly truth set him free?
A secret vampire cult, which has its headquarters beneath the town cemetery, searches for victims for its human sacrifice rituals.

Love is Blind: follow up to the acclaimed web series of the same name. More than just cultural clashes and forbidden love, the movie expands on themes of murder and retribution. Starring Wanly Florexile, Everyone is a SUSPECT!
Two federal agents battle a gang that hijacks trucks carrying materials vital for the security of the country and sells them to foreign powers.

A backwoods team of Missouri kids race to solve a 100 year old mystery and save their friends in this family friendly action adventure. Chased deep into ancient caves they must escape treasure hunters hot on their trail or be lost forever.
4 Hong Kong cops launch a "Sex War Operation" and trying to fooling around in Macau in one night, but things doesn't appear like they expected.
In a desert purgatory, the incarnation of Death loses his powers and falls in love with a corpse as they try to regain their destiny.
Follow Alex and the Checkered Ninja who embark on a frantic hunt for the villain Phillip Eppermint, who has evaded a prison sentence in Thailand.

A group of New England ghost hunters, who have been exaggerating their paranormal discoveries, summon an actual demonic force. The vengeful spirit follows them home, and won't leave until it has taken a few souls.
Two childhood friends, on opposite sides of the law, unite to protect the patrons of a nightclub under attack from opposing forces on the evening of its grand opening.
Wartime secret agents are on a mission to destroy a deadly new type of torpedo hidden in a German stronghold in France.
They collect toys. She collects souls. A group of friends must stand together to take down the demon, Princess Acula, before it is too late.

Before his visit to the "The Kamasutra Garden", William, had never been to a brothel. The girls were young, beautiful and every man's fantasy. However, William soon discovered the complex lives and secrets of the women who worked there.
Six women on a beach tell each other their fantasies. These stories are shown to us as little sex vignettes.
A young man has to risk his life and even humanity by crossing the border to USA to save his young Mexican sister.
A microbiologist is trying the figure out the source of a bad odor that is spreading across New Belgrade blocks, having thought that it may be in a direct relation with a rampant suicide rate.
Movie star Nick Walter uses his fame, connections, and ability to travel throughout the world as a cover for his real occupation, that of an international spy.

In July 1944, with the Allies landed at Normandy but unable to push past German forces, a young German soldier is enlisted for a spy mission by a mysterious American OSS officer named Harry which could turn the tide of the war.

When the king is drugged and abducted by his ambitious brother, a lookalike relative must take his place to keep the evil sibling off the throne.

An all-guts, no-glory San Francisco cop becomes determined to find the underworld kingpin that killed the witness in his protection.
In Hong Kong, three drug dealers attack and rape a loving lesbian couple, murdering one of the girls. Three years later, the other girl runs into one of the attackers and decides to take revenge.
A group of Swedish tourists rents a cabin in Germany and are attacked by the demonic beings inhabiting the woods around them.
Super genius Edison Crane faces his first true test in the form of a world-ending threat that only his could confront.
A psychiatrist groups together a crew for a funded study that reveals more then just a haunted asylum.
The rich landowner La Tigresa suffers several attacks and seeks help from Santo. The attacks continue but Santo protects and she falls for him.
Shiva and Athulya try to make their long-distance relationship work. However, Athulya's colleague Karthik develops feelings for her, which complicates the bond between them.
A man and his family travel 3200km (1984 miles) by bicycle, from the State of Paraíba to Rio de Janeiro, Brazil, in search of a job.
After being cheated on by an insecure man, Brazilian chef Isabella Oliveira moves to San Francisco and finds success as the host of a cooking show.

A skilled tailor accidentally uses the wrong measurements to make an outfit for an arrogant man. This leads to a chain of confrontations and an unexpected attraction.

movie_name: The Sun Is Also a Star
description: A hopeless romantic ambivalent about his future in medical school falls for a hard-luck young woman who doesn't believe in love.
Nicky Larson, the best private investigator in the business, is called for a high-risk mission: to recover the perfume of Cupid, a perfume that would make irresistible the one who uses it.

The protagonist Arthur is a successful attorney. He doesn't care who is defendant is - an innocent person or a jerk. His sole goal is winning. He considers life to consist of predators and prey. He is committed to never be the prey.
Following the events of Superman: American Alien, Max Landis details the darkest night in Superman and Robin's life as they attempt to defend Gotham City under orders of a preoccupied Batman.
A bankrupt entrepreneur attempts to recoup some of her losses by getting a washed-out boxer she picked up as a tax loss back into the ring - an idea her protégé isn't fond of.

When a group of private investigators known as the Lost and Found group visits Spiritual Woods they come across something truly unholy while tracing the footsteps of the missing students from the "film" Spirit in the Woods.
Four friends marooned on a mysterious farm en route to a wedding are terrorized by various creatures and zombies.
The ronin, Sako Kanbei has to rescue the beautiful Princess Tsubaki from danger while young samurai of the Numata Clan stand up against their corrupt Chief Retainer and evil clan mistress.
In the tradition of classic horror movies, "Don't Look" is the story of five friends who leave NYC for a weekend they'll never forget.

movie_name: Whisper - Between the Shades of Time
description: WHISPER tells the story about a group of gifted women living in Munich, Bavaria during WWII, chosen by a higher power to protect mankind's future from a devastating cataclysm to happen in 2026.
A live-action version of Mad magazine's classic comic strip featuring a pair of rival spies trying to outdo each other in an escalating game of espionage.
Two stepbrothers are separated after their father is killed. At adult age, they become petty thieves and try to find their father's murderer, who allegedly goes by the name of Agarwal.
A crazed scientist tries to keep his terminally ill wife alive by transfusing into her the blood of young women he murders.

When a group of college kids go to a spring break getaway at a cabin in the woods, they venture into a cave and take a ritualistic artifact--sacrilege to a coven of deadly witches--who in turn hunt them down.

A reporter Kyle Deeders is following a story regarding the homeless who are missing. The answer is more evil than he could have thought of. His investigation pits him against Father Sebastian Michaels and his followers of vampires.

Emily is distraught over a bitter custody battle that lands her in the custody of her undeserving father. Her dad plays on her emotions to spite his ex-wife. At wit's end, Emily crafts a daring escape plan with an unlikely accomplish.
A mystic-infused love story that follows a young couple's journey to India to collect their adopted baby.

Three friends (two guys and one girl) retreat deep into the wilderness for some camping, but after finding a dead body buried near their campsite, they are preyed upon by a shape-shifting cursed entity. Nothing is as it seems.
The Hero Factory's mission: to build the bravest, most advanced Heroes in the galaxy! When rookie Rocka responds to a civilian distress call from the planet Quatros.
A woman becomes immersed in a brutal love triangle when an unwelcomed admirer kills her abusive husband even though she's already having an affair.
A former beauty queen plots the death of her overbearing mother with the help of her pen-pal, a serial killer on death row.
When young girls start to go missing within a religious cult, older followers fear a long-told prophecy while the younger members suspect abusive elders are killing them off.
Kammaran Nambiar is a crooked man whose life story as an unscrupulous Indian peasant is turned into a film where he is glorified as a freedom fighter with much manipulation of history.

movie_name: The Loving Dead: A Romantic Zomedy
description: James is having second thoughts about his marriage during the zombie apocalypse. Fighting to survive the undead and struggling to sort out his relationship issues, he discovers how delicate life is and where his heart really belongs.
After stuffing themselves on Thanksgiving, three sisters make an ill-advised bet as to which of them can lose the most weight before Christmas while finding true love in the process.

movie_name: Fall in Love Like a Star
description: A superstar musician falls in love with his manager and struggles to choose between his career and true love.

In a distant future, a masked cult has taken control over evil. One female Assassin from a Taiwanese clan seek revenge. A Russian Interpol agent is investigating the cult which could bring him to his death if unlucky.

movie_name: Lucille Love: The Girl of Mystery

An ambitious young executive is sent to retrieve his company's CEO from an idyllic but mysterious "wellness center" at a remote location in the Swiss Alps, but soon suspects that the spa's treatments are not what they seem.
After a number of shocking drownings at Colven Lake, a local amateur filmmaker accidentally uncovers a dark secret that will not only put her life in danger but the local townsfolk.
A fading comedian and a suicidally despondent ballet dancer must look to each other to find purpose and hope in their lives.
Two years after aliens land on Earth, survivors from Sydney, Australia, fight in a desperate war as the number of casualties continue to grow.
The schoolgirls of St. Trinian's are more interested in racing forms than books; as they try to get rich quick, they are abetted by the headmistress' brother.
Millions infected, countless dead, and the lucky few survivors struggling to find the last safe corner for humanity.

The continuation of the romance between Caramel (Michelle Ziudith) and Dave (Dimas Anggara) who plan to visit Switzerland for a holiday. However, Dave cancels the trip at the last minute, leaving Caramel alone with another guy.
A troubled FBI agent works to foil a terrorist plot whose secrets are hidden in the details of different historic events.

Anni happily starts working as underground ticket seller. A passenger in a rush leaves owing part of the ticket. He happens to be a postal service night pilot. He pays his debt and they start dating, in spite of their opposite schedules.
A group of survivors are hiding out in a home in complete cold and darkness, as the creatures use light to find victims.

A deformed hunchback kidnaps a bride on the day of her marriage and holds her hostage while his connection to her and his targets is revealed in a series of flashbacks that unfold as he starts seeking revenge.
A demented serial killer stalks and murders women in order to use them for his cooking. Meanwhile, two investigators attempt to find and arrest the murderer.
The Trouble with Doubt is a twisted tale of good vs. evil as seen through the eyes of a precocious five year old boy Jack, and his alter ego Blue Bunny.
A ruthless mafia hit man is transformed when he rescues a woman who takes the fall for one of his hits.

Ayra (Sharon Cuneta) is an heiress who came home to bury her dead father and who later discovered that her family's estate had been taken over by Edwin (Richard Gomez), her childhood sweetheart and the son of their former overseer.
An American woman is terrorized by the ravages of war and a lecherous Prussian lieutenant when she becomes a Red Cross nurse overseas during the Great War.
After a new party drug puts his sister into a coma, ex-MMA fighter Gael Havens becomes a vigilante to avenge her.
Shekhar (Feroz Khan) helps C.B.I agent Rekha (Shahida) uncover a plot to smuggle military secrets out of the country.
A relationship guru and best-selling author finds himself falling for the licensed therapist who questions his methods.

The town of Red Hollow has come under the thumb of a malevolent rising evil, claiming more and more victims alarmingly fast, putting Carley and her friends to the task of finding a way of putting a stop to it; before they too become victims.

Three unique and strange women each battle their own literal and metaphorical demons. Their lives soon collide due to the mysterious appearance of a massive prism and the nonsensical becomes the sensical.
Intrigue involving corrupt warlords and rebel spies in the Chinese provinces. Rebels take on the warlord power with brains and fearlessness.
The plot is no more than a will-they/won't-they, I hate you/I love you, odd-couple Rom-Com; It goes through all the emotions of a human's heart from sad to mad and glad.
SWITCHH as an action movie about friendship, love and betrayal, the plot revolves around three con artists who use their charm to dupe wealthy victims out of cash.
Both an homage to and a re-imagining of the original 1968 film, this update follows a group of survivors trapped in a farmhouse battling a siege of undead zombies....in 3D!
An imprisoned I.R.A. fighter is freed to help stop a brutal, seemingly "faceless" assassin from completing his next job.

Set entirely within the claustrophobic confines of a computer screen, a teenager uploads a video of a fake murder that goes viral. When it turns out to be a real crime, he and his friends must survive the killer who now targets them.

In 1999, a voice actor moves from Il Mare, a seaside house, and leaves a Christmas card in its (magical) mailbox. An architecture student receives it in 1997, and a friendship separated by 2 years begins.

In need of some extra cash, a beautiful rock singer poses for sexy photos for a men's magazine without telling her boyfriend. It gets complicated when she falls in love with the photographer who's taking the pictures.
A heartthrob singer, Tony Paige, also known as "America's Boyfriend" decides to wed a Swedish actress.
Some of Europe's leading horror filmmakers unite to bring you a collection of terrifying horror stories.
On his request, the sensitive sister of a real estate agent visits a house he intends to sell, only to cross paths with its resident curse.

When their quiet beach town is invaded by a mysterious threat, five kids - a gamer, comic book geek, inventor, skater and martial artist - must band together and use an arsenal of homemade gadgets to fight back.

After a string of bad luck, a debt collector has no other choice than to spend the night in a haunted temple, where he encounters a ravishing female ghost and later battles to save her soul from the control of a wicked tree demon.
As a young man (Justin) returns from the War in Iraq and experiences the Physical and Mental difficulties of trying to re-adjust to the life he once knew.

movie_name: A Dragon Ball Z Fourth of July
description: Bulma is sad that Goku bought all the fireworks for the Fourth of July and that she and Vegeta don't get any to fire off.
Biography of the famed motorcycle daredevil, much of which was filmed in his home town of Butte, Montana. The film depicts Knievel reflecting on major events in his life just before a big jump.
The film holds mirror to the social evil of human trafficking, organ trade and violence happening around us.

An amnesiac soldier, seeking his lost love, arrives in Archangel in northern Russia to help the townsfolk in their fight against the Bolsheviks, all quite unaware that the Great War ended three months ago.
Charlie Graves, the recently resurrected Serial Killer, embarks on a bloody rampage through the city streets as he makes his way back to the wooded confines of Deer Park.

Ji-hyeon is enjoying her life after a female sex-change operation. One day a boy knocks on her door claiming that she is his father. Her attempts to act like an ordinary father conflicts with her life as a woman.

Alfi (Raditya Dika) is an employee who works in Mr. Jeremy's (Tarzan) company. He falls in love with his boss' daughter named Amira (Pevita Pearce). Helped by his friends in the office, can Alfi date his boss' daughter or lose his job?
A one-handed madman uses various detachable devices as murder weapons to gain revenge on those he believes have wronged him.
After her brother's tragic death, a young girl is approached by three men who claim they can bring her brother back to life.

A father moves with his three sons and their beautiful, hard working servant in a big, old house in the countryside, where a weird drowsiness seems to occupy the four men. Will it be possible for one of them to break free?
Rosi is a disturbed teen, the night after her grandmother's burial, Rosi begins to kill her whole family.

Halil is an honest greengrocer with an ordinary life. One day his friends take him to a local night club where he meets a beautiful hostess, Sabiha. The two fall in love. Little does Sabiha know about Halil's life before they met.

Nobu, an old, bigoted, Japanese-American traditionalist, is unable to reconcile the needs of his wife and two daughters with his own conservative view on life, which forces them to leave him in pursuit of their own happiness.
A Louisiana football legend struggles to deal with life's complexities after his college career is over.

Duke Thornton is a man with a violent past who tries to change his life but a desperate gang of criminals force him out of retirement once more. The robbery may succeed, but they're going to pay a heavy price.
Two young lovers get lost in the forest, where they meet various characters, while their parents are looking for them.
Set in 1928, Meredith is a 35 year-old unmarried woman who arrives at a remote lighthouse island with her uncle, the new head keeper.
Deals with the vivid everyday life horrors that can be easily encountered in familiar places around subjects like noise between floors, secondhand furniture, mannequins, and social media.
Roger becomes stranded on a remote military post while his husband serves overseas, and seeks comfort with the sexually frustrated army wives in the community.
Woman's husband buys her a mystery trunk in which she finds an old doll... and soon, nightmares and mysterious, frightening things start to happen.

The youngest professional basketball player in Europe and the Middle East loses his dream of playing and the love of his life at the same time. Surviving war, tragedy and heartbreak he brings the culture of the world to America
Jaan, an orphan, falls for Moni, who belongs to a wealthy family. The two face challenges on social grounds when their relationship is opposed openly.
The main character (Thora Birch) follows the "PIG Theory" and ends relationships after six months in order to avoid heartache until she meets a man (Chris Klein) who wants to disprove her theory.
A serial killer returns to a small town on the anniversary of his initial spree, forcing a young cop - himself a survivor of the original massacre - to catch him before it's too late.
Agent Rude Buay is confronted with an impasse as three high ranking members of the Dragon Drug Cartel once assumed dead, return and team up with ex-convict Johnny Too Bad.
Boaz the barbarian, who's girlfriend is killed by the Devil's son, seeks Jesus to bring his girlfriend back to life. Boaz time is limited as he finds out that Jesus has just been sentenced death.

Low budget horror film actress Lisa Cook stars as herself in this series of horror shorts comprised of her own nightmares. Lisa dreams of various serial killers, slashers, creatures and other horrors that terrorize her in her sleep.

Stephan Bonnar is Troy Jennings, a mixed-martial-arts superstar whose girlfriend is kidnapped by ex-fighter Lucien Gallows. In a desperate attempt to rescue her, Troy must challenge eight fighters and face Gallows in a fight to the death.
A deadly shape-shifting alien infiltrates a country house occupied by two lesbians, and proceeds to study their behaviour, for a sinister purpose.

movie_name: Shango: The Lightning of the Orisha
description: O'Shang a man born into ancient African royalty in the 1700's finds himself forced into slavery and must use his new abilities to hunt down the European colonizers who enslaved his people.
A deadly affair leads to a brutal murder which takes Dillon and Stacy into an evil world of the undead.
Seven rogue soldiers launch a preemptive strike against a newly discovered alien civilization in the hopes of ending an interstellar war before it starts.

Dennis is a handsome & bookish college student. His brother, Bill, is a roughhewn ladies' man & thief. Together they search for their dad, confront their expectations of each other, themselves, & their attitudes towards women.
The daughter of a long dead cult leader escapes her troubled life by returning to the house she grew up in on the weekend of her father"s prophesied return.
When a rich woman's ex-husband and a tabloid-type reporter turn up just before her planned remarriage, she begins to learn the truth about herself.
Two long time best friends who are highly trained Army Rangers and Special Ops Soldiers during the Vietnam War go elk hunting in the Colorado Rocky Mountains and end up hunting each other.

He was born on 12 June 2006 in the Kannauj district of Uttar Pradesh state. He lives with his family in Kannauj, Uttar Pradesh.And watch the movie to know all about Ishu Yadav. The movie will be launched in 2025.
When two sisters go to an isolated cabin in the woods to film a passion project, family secrets start to get in the way, as do masked strangers filming a passion project of their own.
Children of two family rivals fall in love with each other and married off but later the marriage brings more animosity between the families.
Badrinath is looking for a typical bride; Vaidehi is looking for an independent life. Together they must break with tradition and redefine their role.
A waitress from Texas and a college student from Pennsylvania meet during spring break in Fort Lauderdale, Florida and come together through their shared love of singing.
Pak Kong Tung, a leader of a Triad group, accompanied by his men Chan Wai and Siu Lung, makes a drug transaction with drug dealer Hu Tai Sing.
Two best friends, Eun-ha and Eun-jeong, decide to help their widowed parents marry each other. However, problems arise when Eun-jeong steals Eun-ha's boyfriend in the process

Years after a series of murders in 2017, book author Michael Lane suddenly begins to receive calls from the unknown. Instead of concentrating on his bestselling book, he becomes obsessed with this mystery and loses control.
A cop is assigned to a case of escorting a criminal to Japan while dealing with relationship problems, and his enormous change in appearance as a result of being dumped.

The sudden death of his wife plunges a terminally ill man into profound grief. Realizing how little he knew her and how little he showed her his affection, he devotes his last weeks to fulfilling her long-cherished dreams.

As a nobleman named Kain was viciously murdered, he was reluctantly raised as a vampire. He sets out on his journey through the lands of Nosgoth to seek revenge against the people who murdered him and to find a cure for his vampiric curse.
The village head is a man who sticks to honesty while making judgements and is admired and felicitated for this quality. When he falls prey to a conspiracy, he fights to ensure that justice prevails.
An injustice is committed against Maya, a transgender woman who had to pay with her life. But that is not the end of Maya. She will return to see justice done.
A white liberal teacher and his 17-year-old African-American female student fall deeply in love with tragic consequences.
An American skydiver wakes up in the middle of nowhere in Spain and must recount the last five agonizing days to figure out how she got there.
A group of Katoeys (ladyboys) are caught in a border dispute after their plane crashes, when a group of six straight soldiers reluctantly takes on a mission to save them.

Vengeance is on John Slaughter's mind 20 years after his family was killed in a massacre in the late 1800s. As a grown man, he returns to the scene of the crime, the sleepy town of Ghost Rock, to remind himself of the tragedy.
Anthology compilation of of the most Insane, scary, extreme and downright stupid. Independent Low-Budget Movie Trailers from across the globe.

movie_name: Viernes de Ánimas: El camino de las flores
description: Andy has a sixth sense that allows him to see the afterlife. While staying with one of his friends, he's able to feel some vengeful spirits, that are desperate to make contact with the living.
A story of the illegal immigrant experience of people from the mainland of China who have made it to Hong Kong for a better life.
An Englishman's (Melvyn Douglas) fiancee (Phyllis Calvert) comforts his son (Philip Friend) who has lost a leg and a family in World War II.

Laura and Christine have been friends forever. One day they meet the mysterious and fascinating Maria, and their friendship is put to the test. For Laura it is a meeting that changes the world she thought she knew so well.
When six best high school buddies are cross the forbidden forest and broken all the rules in there, something evil follow their back and causing death among themselves.

A multiple homicide at a luxury villa in Malibu sets two detectives down a harrowing path of truth about a young girl who was brutally bullied her entire life, while discovering another woman has taken up revenge.
While recovering from a suicide attempt, Ben Layton accidentally falls in love with a girl who was very nearly, almost his sister - and then things start to get weird.

movie_name: Trip Ubusan: The Lolas vs Zombies
description: Lola Nidora, Lola Tinidora, and Lola Tidora of Kalyeserye, with their little niece Charmaine, attempt to survive a zombie outbreak.

movie_name: Absolutely American: A Comedy Heated Rally with Action
description: A coming of age, zany whimsical Asian-American Peter with loving hearts, struggles with an embarrassing secret, discovers his American roots and finds love with Nancy, wins with nonviolence.

movie_name: Farewell to Space Battleship Yamato: Warriors of Love
description: The Comet Empire approaches, and the Yamato is ready to face them. But this will be the last battle for both sides.

A retired soldier becomes a notorious dacoit due to a conspiracy and circumstances in his personal life. He is pursued by police officers, who enlist the help of two local tricksters in an attempt to catch him.

At a United States private school for international students, sensitive and lonely student Tristan Hou develops a forbidden love for one of his teachers, the tenderhearted Elise Ahn, during the Corona pandemic.

Two CIA agents - a kung fu master and a suave womanizer - track the stolen formula for a super-sterility drug from Spain to Hong Kong, battling Neo-Nazi terrorists and a Vietnamese spy ring for its possession.
A powerful spirit that once threatened to destroy the world is back! Naruto's mission is to protect a priestess named Shion, who is the only one with the power to seal away the monster.
Unlock a world of paranormal terror in this tale of a researcher who discovers evidence of ghostly horrors, Apparition of Evil explores the sinister realm between life and death.

December 1940. A desperate woman seeks solace for a crime by confessing to a military chaplain. The despicable deed sets in motion a chain of events, and an innocent with bloody hands has to pay. Can there be redemption for the guilty?
A U.S. Army major is assigned to lead a squad of twelve condemned soldier-prisoners on a dangerous mission behind enemy lines in WWII.
A group of friends must confront their most terrifying fears when they awaken the dark powers of an ancient spirit board.
Aristocrats, writers and police professionals invent Jack the Ripper to cover up a series of supernatural murders in an effort to keep London from knowing that humans are on the verge of extinction.

movie_name: The House Next Door: Meet the Blacks 2
description: When best selling author Carl Black moves his family back to his childhood home, he must team up with oddball neighbors to do battle with a pimp, who may or may not be an actual vampire.
A Texas family moves into a house which is terrorized by the spirit of the infamous Mexican weeping woman.

movie_name: The Morning of the Fourth Day
description: Amir is a foul guy who has killed a man in Abadan, he returns to Tehran and continuing his misdeeds trying to convince his girlfriend Zarry to escape with him to the south of Iran.

George Schneider is an author whose wife had just died. His brother Leo gives him the number of Jennie Malone, and somehow they hit it off, and just when things are moving along, the memory of his first wife comes between them.
Two gay brothers inherit their Uncle's business - a private men's gym in Manhattan - only to discover the members are all straight and their silent partner is the Mob.
A thriller about a sparring couple who's evening turns into a fight for survival when their car is hijacked. The film is edited into jagged shards, creating a feeling of reality versus memory.
A strike team of mercenaries hunt for a missing naval vessel. Upon finding the ship, they find out that the crew has been infected and are members of the walking dead.

Abused male seeking relationship with a woman who can love him, or otherwise provide some form of companionship before he loses his mind, or hurts others. Needs help immediately. Please respond to ad, or contact (213) 372-6354.
An arthritic Nova Scotia woman works as a housekeeper while she hones her skills as an artist and eventually becomes a beloved figure in the community.

When the staff inside a renovated film studio finds a co-worker dead one morning, the pieces of a 40-year puzzle add up to an angry ghost who has let the last person step inside her house. Will they get out alive?
Benoit Ray is an out of work actor. Out of total desperation he uses different character disguises in order to rob armor trucks.

movie_name: Bleach the Movie 2: The Diamond Dust Rebellion
description: After the treasured Ouin is stolen, Toshiro Hitsugaya disappears and becomes suspected of treason. When the Soul Society calls for his capture and execution, Substitute Soul Reaper Ichigo Kurosaki vows to prove Hitsugaya's innocence.

Three childhood friends graduate from university and try, against steadily increasing odds, to enjoy one last summer of immaturity.
Lizzie Borden, who killed her parents with an axe, is jokingly summoned by a group of girls having a slumber party.

When a cold-hearted lawyer represents a woman she believes to be a cold-blooded killer, she learns how wrong her initial assessment was, but will have to risk her safety to find the supporting evidence.

Karan Abhyankar is tasked by the Chief Minister to kill an underworld don Bhau in an encounter. The catch - Bhau's aide Kaka has kidnapped the Minister's son so that he can get Bhau released in exchange for the Minister's son.

The activities of Nubi (Myrna Loy), a minx-like, Hungarian gypsy girl who, while on the run from her abusive husband, takes shelter in a farmhouse, where she seduces and holds in thrall all the male members of the family.
A young window cleaner turns into an apartment burglar tipster. Will he be able to start a new, more honest life?

During his summer vacation on Nantucket Island in 1942, a youth eagerly awaiting his first sexual encounter finds himself developing an innocent love for a young woman awaiting news on her soldier husband's fate in WWII.

A failed London musician meets once a week with a woman for a series of intense sexual encounters to get away from the realities of life. But when he begins inquiring about her, it puts their relationship at risk.
Sampaguita's bright young stars, the sensational discoveries of 1956, together again to thrill you - in their newest romantic-comedy.

Nothing less than a phenomenal, astonishing and pioneering film. This spectacle of an angry, ego-driven youth tormented by his own emotional impotence, low self-esteem and resentment towards his parents.
A mysterious beast that lives in the storm drains beneath the city begins to hunt and feed on a drug cartel.
Purushothaman Nair is jobless while his wife Devi is a teacher and they have a daughter. The film speaks about love, romance, and the bonds between family members.

Ace (Motorhead's Lemmy Kilmister) is the head of the Sunset Society - a secret vampire organization that hosts the best parties in Hollywood. Even as the blood flows freely, the club will do anything to keep their existence a secret.
Housesitter Toby Smith takes on a job at an annexe in a secluded area, which on the first appearance seems like a normal holiday home annexe.
The son of a wealthy landowner is expelled from his family after standing up for the factory workers at his father's business. He meets the daughter of a poor peasant and they fall in love.

movie_name: I'll See What I Can Do
description: Carlton leach is let loose after being found out that he is sex offender. He then spends time reflecting on his sad life in a caravan skint and fat
Smugglers dump 50 million dollars worth of cocaine in the sea. Trying to recover the contraband drives a corrupt coast guard colonel to piracy and murder.
After being framed for murder, Madhurey, an IPS officer goes underground and takes on the loan fraud going in the local market. He falls in love with Anita but his prime motive is to destroy KTR.
A former marine arrives at a mental asylum housed in a remote castle to run it. There he attempts to rehabilitate the patients by letting them act out their craziest fantasies and desires.
A dejected small-town music teacher grapples with guilt and regret when his ex-pupil who once loved him returns home as the star he always wanted to be.

movie_name: You Don't Mess with the Zohan
description: An Israeli Special Forces Soldier fakes his death so he can re-emerge in New York City as a hair stylist.

Elbab Elmaftouh, Known in English as "The Open Door", another great movie about women's right in their different role and life and thier struggle between her father with his old style and her husband that doesn't understand her.
A mother and daughter, still wounded from a bitter custody dispute, hole up in a run-down apartment building, where they are targeted by the ghost of a former resident.
Elisabeth meets the love of her life on her bachelorette night, and the weekend they spend together is the beginning of the end.
Sathya, the protagonist goes back to india on request of her Ex and helps her in finding her missed daughter, which leads to twists and turns!
Hank Williams, an amateur hunter, teams up with Bigfoot Hunter, Trevor Farleys, and an aging bear slayer, Willis Hampton, to sabotage a crazed hunter and win a local hunting competition.

Set in the dizzy world of TC 2000 racing La Leyenda tours the action genre overflowing with adrenaline and speed, and where everyone races for the finish line. Lucas Vallejos and Juan ...                See full synopsis »
At the house of their target, two hit men bide their time waiting for the kill, only to find death already arrived in the shape of black magic, devilish spirits and the occult.

Two tales - one of an 1890's traveling Freak Show and the other a current day "death Rock" band - intertwine, twist and dovetail in blood and Horror as we learn the answer to the question: "Who really are the freaks?"
Balu comes to the city and stays with his friend. He falls in love with Sumithra, his landlord. But her evil cousin Mahesh, who has an eye on her, creates a rift between them.
The story of some Chinese reformers who escape from the Qing army and later battle the foreign expeditionary force during the Boxer Rebellion.
THE GREATEST ADVENTURE STORY OF OUR TIME. Filmed for the first time in the Philippines--in thrilling sepia tone and exciting natural color.
In a country, where people constantly live in fear, an everyday citizen turns the tables on the hijackers and becomes a vigilante, bent on righting the wrongs of a cruel world.
A shy country boy gets caught between the peer pressure of his buddies and his love for an overweight, strong willed but likable girl.
After the tragic death of her fiance, Karlina encounters strange dreams that call upon her return to her mother's village. Out of curiosity, Karlina start her mysterious journey.
As an Orc horde invades the planet Azeroth using a magic portal, a few human heroes and dissenting Orcs must attempt to stop the true evil behind this war.
A few possess the ability to hone in on the sounds of the universe. We follow Trance on a journey where passion fights duty.
When work moves Jason across the world, he can only bring his love, Carla, if they are married by Christmas.

A man and woman who have been together for 8 years choose their "allowed" celebrity hook-ups, not realizing how soon they would actually be meeting them in real life, and their couplehood is shaken up.
An out-of work merchant seaman single-handedly tames a powerful street gang "The Souls" that has been terrorizing his neighborhood on New York City's Lower East Side.

movie_name: Satria Heroes: Revenge of the Darkness
description: One year has passed since Satria Garuda Bima-X defeated VUDO and the earth is in peace again. Ray and Rena are rebuilding the Parallel World again. However, new evil forces attack and old enemies rise again to devastate the earth.

A young woman suffering a psychotic relapse is receiving messages from a ghost-hunting TV show when she starts to believe that her apartment is being haunted by a dark figure with a plastic-bag-covered head.
A YOUNG ACTIVIST HIDES IN A SOUTHERN LUZON PROVINCE WHEN MARTIAL LAW IS DECLARED AND WITNESSES HOW THE COMMON FOLKS ARE CAUGHT IN THE CROSSFIRE BETWEEN GOVERNMENT AND REBELS.

Five different stories of sureal misteries. The labyrinth of Pasar Setan a.k.a "Satan Market" of the mountain, the mistery beyond Wayang Kulit shows, the curse of Music Box, the cult of Palasik and redemption at the Parking Locket.

A loan officer who evicts an old woman from her home finds herself the recipient of a supernatural curse. Desperate, she turns to a seer to try and save her soul, while evil forces work to push her to a breaking point.
A struggling actor who seems doomed to lead the life of a loser. When finally gets a lead role as a superhero named "Badman," he feels like everything is possible but fate strikes again.
1933. A city boy arrives in his late mother's birthplace to discover the locals have been pestered by drought, old fights and a cougar. He turns out to be pivotal in all of these.
After avenging the death of his father and brother, a man must now content with another vengeful male.
A photographer is haunted by nightmares of his mother's murder at the hands of a werewolf-type creature, but soon realizes it's more than just his memories that are rising to the surface.

Tells of two brave jawans, who unite the cowering villagers and with the help of a group of students, fight against the atrocities of a notorious dacoit and in a final showdown kill him to free the village from his menace.
Our hero Colin is bitten by a Zombie; he dies and returns from the dead. We follow him as he wanders through suburbia during the throes of a cadaverous apocalypse.
Brody is back. Nancy has a new man. His children do not want to see it. He is alone. He is alone, but wants revenge.
A man must survive a prison where hardened criminals battle to the death for the wardens' entertainment.
Alma falls in love with Julio, a famous singer, but her parents oppose that idea thinking that is just one more of her rich girl whims.
A monomaniacal zoologist is pathologically jealous of his beautiful but unfaithful wife Evelyn and will not stop short of murder to keep her.
Mon Mane Na is a 1992 Bengali romance film featuring Prosenjit Chatterjee and Silpa Das. It was Silpa Das first film.

A vigilante, Franck Denard is released from prison after serving 10-years for a crime he didn't commit. Discovering he's on borrowed time with a brain tumor, he sets out for one last blood-thirsty fight seeking redemption and vengeance.
A frontiersman on a fur trading expedition in the 1820s fights for survival after being mauled by a bear and left for dead by members of his own hunting team.
A young man who wants to help his friend in love coincidentally falls in love of the girl his friend loves.
A Chinese mandarin hopes to regain favor with the Emporer by betrothing her to him, but he doesn't know she's secretly married to the American consul and pregnant.
Polat Alemdar Erhan and Cahit are yet again on the front lines only to discover a military coup attempt in Turkey.

France employs local secret agents in Vietnam 1922 to eliminate resistance. The rebel leader's pretty daughter gets captured. Later an agent seems to have fallen in love with her and helps her escape. He flees, too. Lots of martial arts.

Ted Daniels, a ranch hand working for a rodeo, captures a magnificent wild horse that he tames and trains. As Ted is recovering from an accident that happened during a rodeo, the rodeo owner cheats him out of his horse.
In this low-budget potboiler, a teenage love affair faces various hardships following a tragic drag-racing incident.
Lim Chang-ryeong is a professional assassin. Although he plans to retire from his profession, he decides to take on one last job and kill the infamous North Korean spy Agent Heo Du-shik.
Michael and Bruce are the joint owners of a computer software company which is the subject of a fierce takeover bid by a rival corporation.

A love story about three stages of love; when love strikes in a moment of bliss; the moment after the initial spark when the lovers discover each other's real personalities; the birth of deeper and stronger feelings.

In the aftermath of events of The Last Aztec Warrior, Antonio Ferrera's past has finally caught up to him. His old cohort turned enemy kidnaps him and his family, forcing him to break a notorious arms dealer out of prison.

The enchanted lives of a couple in a secluded forest are brutally shattered by a nightmarish hippie cult and their demon-biker henchmen, propelling a man into a spiraling, surreal rampage of vengeance.
An action drama based on a true story about a young Colombian girl who changes the direction of her life when she gets kidnapped in Colombia.
A documentary crew follows cult classic horror director, Alfred Costella, as he makes his final film - An all practical masterpiece...with a dark twist.

A greedy Manchu (Qing) general wants it all. His troops scavenges through the countryside on a deadly mission of theft and lust until two young fighters and an over-the-hill master decide to fight back.
Four young adults find themselves in peril when visiting an abandoned warehouse which is believed to have once housed several troubled mental patients.

Santhanam plays the role of a jobless youth whose only ambition in life is to marry a beautiful girl. The rest of the story shows how he achieves this with the help of a love guru played by VTV Ganesh.

In Detroit, a lonely pop culture geek marries a call girl, steals cocaine from her pimp, and tries to sell it in Hollywood. Meanwhile, the owners of the cocaine, the Mob, track them down in an attempt to reclaim it.

An NSA Agent's PTSD nightmares tease what he can't remember. He joins the daughter of a murdered investigative reporter to reveal The Undetected, the Omen Seven and unravel their terrorist conspiracy against our country.
A wealthy business man's wife proves herself to be resourceful after being abducted by thugs looking for a R20, 000 ransom fee.
