Steve Rogers, a rejected military soldier, transforms into Captain America after taking a dose of a "Super-Soldier serum". But being Captain America comes at a price as he attempts to take down a warmonger and a terrorist organization.
The world's deadliest hitman chooses redemption rather than his designated Triad target and finds himself on the run in Hong Kong with a mysterious and beautiful computer hacker.
Three stories intertwine, crossing through a missing novelist, a troubled detective and a soul searcher who meets a perfect stranger.
Over the course of five social occasions, a committed bachelor must consider the notion that he may have discovered love.
A sadistic group of clowns kidnap an unsuspecting man and his daughters, forcing him to play a deadly game in order to save his family.

A lost but ambitious exotic dancer meets a depressed, unmotivated Hollywood tour guide in this dark romantic comedy about finding our way through the signposts life offers us, and courageously living a life beyond our wildest dreams.

Four young women driving across the desert to Las Vegas have their road trip turned upside-down when they pick up a handsome, seemingly-friendly hitchhiker. When their car breaks down near a roadside motel in the middle of nowhere, they find themselves trapped with a woman-hating, masochistic killer.

When an elite special forces commander accidentally uncovers an insidious military conspiracy, his family is brutally murdered. Now the target of an intergalactic manhunt, they will stop at nothing to silence him.
A man who lived his life as he was was told he should, not as he would have chosen to, is brought out of his shell by a beautiful young woman.
A man takes revenge from two corrupt encounter specialist officers and a criminal lawyer for framing him as a maoist and for killing his wife and unborn child.
A newly married couple is framed for the murder of a police officer. She is sent to prison, while he is sentenced to die in the electric chair. She sets out to prove their innocence.
Ubable to speak or hear, Sam-ryong is nevertheless key in opposing a gangster who is demanding extortion money from his place of employment.
It's a gritty one-of-a-kind Zombie Film unlike anything ever put to film. It revolves around Anabel and her dead uncle trying to thwart off the militias not other zombies.

In the distant future, a man goes on the run from a scientist who wants to harvest his very rare, ultra-healing blood. But when her science project gets shut down, the scientist goes crazy and decides to kill everyone left on this planet.
A bank executive receives a bomb threat while driving his children to school that his car will explode if they stop and get out. A remake of the 2015 Spanish film "El Desconocido."

Summer 1989, East Germany. Adam works as a tailor, Evelyn as a waitress. They are planning a vacation together when Evelyn finds out that Adam is cheating on her and decides to leave for the holiday on her own.
Michael Dorsey, an unsuccessful actor, disguises himself as a woman in order to get a role on a trashy hospital soap.
Following the death of his father, an estranged man returns to his hometown and reminisces about his youth, leading him to search for the land their family once owned.
A young filmmaker begins shooting his 'perfect horror film' during a movie marathon, oblivious that a real life killer will exploit, inspire and alter the outcome of his movie.
Mysterious experiments are going on at the BioGen4 Research Labs...and now, those experiments...are loose. Monsters...creatures...hungry for flesh and blood.

An idyllic town is thrown into chaos when two powerful Pokémon, Dialga and Palkia, cross paths and battle, distorting the dimensions of time and space. The only hope comes from Darkrai, a shadowy Pokémon shunned by the townsfolk.
The story centres around the Saviour family and their enemies who are trying to steal the families Legacy.

Three men, disillusioned in love and intent on getting away from all women, rent a cabin and retreat there. But the young woman who owns the cabin, unaware that it has been rented, is on her way there to escape from an unhappy engagement.
A memorable battle declared by a fearless young warrior to win back his love from the clutches of her heartless captors.

Ma is kidnapped and tortured. Since then, his girlfriend Amy senses he's no longer the same person, and becomes convinced that something supernatural is corrupting his soul. Policeman Pit is determined to get to the bottom of the case.
A former CIA operative turned political talk show host is hired by a disaffected corporate shareholder to expose her company's cover-up of an incident and deaths in an Ecuadorian village.
While hiding in a small town, a former mobster finds out the man he snitched on is sending men to kill him.
Prince Karl Heinz enjoys his carefree life as a student in Heidelberg. He falls in love with the beautiful Käthe and everything is fine and dandy till his father is reported very ill.
A comic book artist struggling with his "Brenda Starr" strip decides to draw himself into it when his comic book character is disappointed and leaves the strip.
Mario Almada returns as "el fiscal de hierro"; in this entry his family is kidnapped by gang leader Ramona Pineda.

In this feel-good romcom from Nollywood, a successful events planner, Mo, is a trusted matchmaker for her friends. But privately, Mo dreams of finding herself a special man - one who may come along sooner than she thinks.

Heads roll as two cops, Chuck and Andy, go against Mr. D'Angelo, the biggest drug dealer in Florida, and his ruthless enforcer Fred, who has no legs but does have two mean double barrel shotguns built into his wheelchair.

After a night of partying, four friends are kidnapped by a mysterious man. The friends wake up in a basement, and realize they are part of something horrifying. A human breeding farm. They are to be milked, bred, and much, much worse.
Alvin Lacy after serving years on the LAPD, hasn't given up on his dreams to become a successful comedian in Hollywood.
Set in the spring of 1972, Lacy, a teenage hitchhiker, gets lost in the forest of Bruce Peninsula, where she spends many hallucinatory, surrealistic days and nights attempting to escape.

A switched-locale remake of "Dangerous (1935)" about a jinxed, hard-luck dame , Vicki Moore (Brenda Marshall), and the men who show her that life is worth living no matter how ponderous and complicated.
She, leader of a religious sect, leads a group of people. All live together in a claustrophobic place. The arrival of a mysterious character changes everything.

Ji-hun takes a break from his art studies in Paris to return to Korea and visit with his family. While there, he falls in love with a young widow. However, their future happiness seems doomed as she is already engaged to be remarried

An Egyptian remake of The Rocky Horror Picture Show from 1981, completely reinvents O'Brien's classic, refocusing his efforts on a horde of flamboyant vampires who enjoy nothing more than a sing-a-long.
A successful businessman meets the woman of his dreams, Amanda, only to discover she harbors a shocking little secret about her past.

movie_name: The Lure of the South Seas
description: A picturesque and authentic tale of South Sea life as lived by the last of the Polynesians and the whites who listlessly go native.
Surviving members of an aristocratic English family are threatened by a legendary monster when they venture out on chilly, foggy nights.
Nympho is a lust story of a girl called Rachael. She is a nymphomaniac. She is a sex addict. She is not a single man woman.

Krish and Chitra are lovers. Due to a minor difference between the two, they go separate ways. The break-up in love deeply affects Krish, who goes into a state of mental depression. He spends his life narrating his tale of woes to people.
With his parents about to move back to Brazil, Gus, an immigrant teenager raised in the US, meets Chrissy, an American college student that will transform his life during dark times.
An Anglican vicar's son secretly weds a dissenter's daughter and recovers from amnesia in time to save her from shame.

Two funny toy factory workers from Lwów get fired. They find a baby in the park and take care of it until it is by coincidence taken to Warsaw by a wealthy man's daughter. The two mates are not going to abandon their child.
Story of a couple in a contractual relationship where they meet only for 2 hours a day and behave like strangers during other times.
A young Turkish pilot Timur fall into love with Yildiz. While he going to duty to Cyprus he gives a letter his mom to transmit Yildiz. But his mom lies to Timur.
A father and his two teenage daughters find themselves hunted by a massive rogue lion intent on proving that the Savanna has but one apex predator.
A single mother of three struggles to stay afloat all the while taking care of her sick mother amid a custody battle. Would letting love in threaten all she has worked so hard to protect?
After a difficult romance in a class-divided society, the love birds find out marriage is not what they thought it would be.
Bob is coming to terms with his unsuccessful attempts at becoming an actor when he is bitten by a vampire named Susan - the daughter of a crazed vigilante slayer.
In the village Karrild, Countess Sonia Hard Borg and the young unmarried woman Marta give birth to one daughter each. Marta dies after birth, so her little girl Betina comes under the Countess care.
A cattle rustler tracks his missing brother to a farm run by two settler witches who entrap young men as spirit-slaves. He must find a way to destroy their ancient power to liberate his brother.

Ria Khan believes that she must save her older sister Lena from her impending marriage. After enlisting her friends' help, she attempts to pull off the most ambitious of all wedding heists, in the name of independence and sisterhood.

The only failure of the successful businessman Celal is his son, Bulent, the incompetent man. Celal gives his son one month to stand on his own two feet and set things right, or else he will be barred from inheriting.
Jay gets a horse from his grandmother. Riding becomes his obsession but gets injured. His grandmother gives away his horse, thus changing their lives forever.
After the Republic's victory on Christophsis, Anakin and his new apprentice, Ahsoka Tano, must rescue the kidnapped son of Jabba the Hutt. Political intrigue complicates their mission.

In a town with a dark history, two children encounter malicious spirits within their house that threaten to possess their bodies and summon an evil that has been lying in wait for centuries to reign it's terror upon all of mankind.

Irfan, an innocent man with an ordinary life, is portrayed as the evil incarnated by media trials. Is there a journey back to normal life for a man accused of terrorism? Is there more to Irfan than what meets the eye?

Rashid, the spitting image of legendary Zimbo, plans to steal beautiful Princess Zulina's treasure. Meanwhile, the real king of the jungle and Leela find young Mala in the wreckage of a small plane and decide to adopt him as their son.
A film that delves into one of Australia's Worst Civil and Human rights claims. Sue became a ward of the State as a baby and went on to be admitted into the worst mental asylums in the country.

Newsweek Chu is a publication of private behavior exposure and the press keeps a group of bridle-wise paparazzi. The members are instructed to track a girl band and they follows the girls into a cruise.

In the year A.D. 29; the banishment of a young guardian angel will shape the course of human history. Nearly 2000 years later, drawn back into her role as guardian, the question is who or what is she protecting?
A female reporter with marital problems is sent by her boss to cover the campaign of a young political neophyte who's running against the local crooked political boss.
After classmates destroy life-size wooden folk art statues during a wild high school graduation party at a remote cottage, a mysterious killer starts picking them off one by one.
In a post apocalyptic world, a gang of ruthless murderers fight the living and the undead trying to survive.
Babak who suffers from Leukemia falls in love with a famous singer named Parvaneh. Although at first she takes him for granted, but gradually a relationship begins that changes their lives.
In the 5th century BC, rival kingdoms Rome and Alba entrust their fate to a duel to death between their respective chosen champions, the 3 Orazi brothers for Rome and the 3 Curiazi brothers for Alba.
A self-indulgent and vain publishing magnate finds his privileged life upended after a vehicular accident with a resentful lover.

A class of graduating high school seniors celebrate their last night together at the annual school lock-in. They never could have guessed that they're about to encounter the legendary "Coast to Coast Killer".

Zack and Sham, two youngsters who love drift racing. Even though drift racing is much for men Zack's girlfriend enters in drift racing and becomes competitive in drifting. How their lives roll with racing, love and competition.
A tale of possessiveness and distrust towards one's partner and the eventual redemption by sacrifice.
In Victorian-era London, a troubled clairvoyant police detective investigates the murders of Jack the Ripper.
Former racing champion John Lee Scott coaches young driver Dustin Rich. The learn of a new Italian model that can reach 300 kilometers an hour developed by an 80 year old racing expert.
Honoring the one-year anniversary of a close friend's death, 7 friends embark on a road trip in search of a mysterious urban legend known only as Wormwood.
On his way to work, Teddy spots Charlotte, an incredibly beautiful Woman in Red. He really wants to meet her, but what would his wife say?
Retired CIA agent Frank Moses reunites his unlikely team of elite operatives for a global quest to track down a missing portable nuclear device.
Four ordinary people came from somewhere to harbour to find a work which living for pursuit, things change when they arrive and met someone.
The trial and tribulations of a strong-willed woman who elopes and gives birth out of wedlock without telling her ex-husband.
When Terry rejects the son of the wealthiest and most powerful man in town, they start to make life difficult for her and her father.
Desperation causes a man to arrange a fake marriage in order to access the inheritance left to him by his late father.
The government is testing a new weapon to make their soldiers invisible. However before active use they need to test it on captured animals.
In the aftermath of a tragedy at a summer camp, a group of camp counselors find themselves fighting for their lives against a masked killer.
A female office worker takes a diet supplement made from wasps which transforms her into a sex hungry wasp woman.
Kenan is brought up by his foster father, Azmi Bey. As he grows up, he falls in love with Azmi Bey's beautiful daughter Nalan. Nalan is diagnosed by Pleurisy, which leads to a series of tragic event.
Un pobre obrero esta profundamente enamorado de una mujer rica, pero ella no le pertenece. Mientras lucha por conquistarla, aprende una valiosa lección.
A singing shoe shiner in a 'not-so-musical' world decides to help a rich tycoon with countless foes before he passed away, only to learn that being rich is not any easier than being poor.

movie_name: Johnny King and the Warriors of the South Seas
description: A Polynesian paradise is shattered when outcast Johnny King must join the perilous Captain Smith to save King's tribe from the dreaded Kwai-Kwak warriors, who will stop at nothing to destroy Johnny's tribe and curse their dead forever.
An exploration of foot fetishism as Travis, a traffic programmer falls heels over head for a beautiful blonde named Cynthia.

Set in the nostalgic Seventies, this film tells the story of a house filled with a sinister presence. From grotesque wax dummies to a doll that once belonged to a drowned child, everything within the house is evil and haunted.
A home invasion on Halloween night turns deadlier for the intruders as hidden secrets and dark truths are revealed about the house's occupant.
An Israeli-Lithuanian scientist is asked by a Russian oligarch to develop software that will match people around the world.
A VENGEFUL SPIRIT terrorizes a man and his family, forcing him to confront a long buried secret from his past...or risk losing all he holds dear in life.

That oozing pink terror, "The Blob," lives again in this irreverent and hilarious send up of the 1958 classic. But this time, Steve McQueen has to face off against a wise-cracking pile of goo when, for the first time, The Blob speaks!
A man is alone in Paris during the month of August while his woman and children go on vacation. He meets a young English girl posing as a model who came to Paris for a shoot.

Love has many faces, but Joel and Jenny love with earnestness, but when their love is tested in the fire of adversity, it has to overcome that. When reality is not what it appears to be, can love survive?
the movie discuss the people of random areas in Egypt and the unjust from the government toward these people
Two films that are spin-offs from the popular sixties Japanese TV show "The Guardsmen," about undercover security forces against organized crime.
Two best friends travel to their father's summer home for a getaway, while being pursued by a group of sadistic animal masked killers.

movie_name: Justine: In the Heat of Passion
description: Justine daydreaming about her teacher, Professor Robson. He then invites her to join him on his travels throughout the world.

Xiao Yang is in his teens. He cares about the people around him in his naive way. But apart from Xiao Ma, no one really appreciates him; even though he never gives up showing his love to his family and friends.
Somewhere in south west Texas, where a christian cult is said to have resided in the past, a deputy sheriff investigates a number of suspicious deaths.
It's a right of passage for a young man called Jake who has never been out in his life and his friends decide to take him on a trip of a lifetime.

Futaba lost her first love, Kou, in middle school when he suddenly moved. In high school, she met a guy who resembled Kou, but has a different last name. She needs to know if he is the same guy, and why he moved without letting her know.
Shin, a good family friend and business partner of the DeLeon family, assumes his role as head of the Coast Mafia.

A spiritualist medium holds a seance for a writer suffering from writer's block but accidentally summons the spirit of his deceased first wife, which leads to an increasingly complex love triangle with his current wife of five years.
Daniel Read's a high school basketball superstar who comes into contact with forces of antagonism, mainly premarital sex and HIV which could derail his bright future.

A confused and tormented young man (known only as "The Patient") relates his dreams and memories to a mysterious and sadistic doctor. As The Patient dives deeper into his mental landscape he discovers a shocking truth.

A young socialite and a rich playboy elope to Atlantic City. However, she soon realizes he's not the man she wants him to be and tries to call off the wedding. A jewelry store robbery, murder and other mayhem are soon involved.
A ruthless Viking seeks vengeance against his old enemy by kidnapping his daughters, but the plan is hindered by an unknown macabre presence from the legends.

Guna (Karthikeya) is a happy-go-lucky guy who believes the solution to solving issues is not through violence but through compromise. But what happens when he's forced to the extremes by someone close to him?
An older sister takes her fearless runaway sibling on a road trip, to share the most chilling tales surrounding their hometown.

Three college girls stop at a roadside diner on their way to Las Vegas. But, after skipping out on their bill, they must try to escape the diner's owner who has more on his mind than the cost of the food.

The Shaw Brothers' take on James Bond. Pursued by the murderous Skeleton Gang, three people travel from Bangkok, Thailand to the ruins of the ancient Siamese capital Ayutthaya in search of lost treasure, using three small Buddha statues.
Four men who were involved in the investigation of a German millionaire at the end of World War II are found murdered with tiny dolls left next to their corpses.
Love stories set in a town beyond the mountains. A rebellious daughter, a single mother, a farm boy dreaming of a boy on the school bus. A lyrical story of love and loss.

movie_name: Hell House LLC III: Lake of Fire
description: The Abaddon Hotel will once again be open to the public. Russell Wynn has taken his audience-interactive show, Insomnia, into the abandoned hotel that is rumored to be haunted.

The film tells the female agent Ameera after a failed mission, private life crisis, conspiracy, and attempt to create organizational struggle Resident Evil dark story found during the processing of personal crisis.

movie_name: Pure Bloodlines: Blood's Thicker Than Water
description: Continuing on from the successful action/drama/romance/martial arts indy film 'Pure Bloodlines:The Ties That Bind us'. Comes the sequel 'Bloods Thicker Than Water' hot from winning a media award at the 'London Hall of Fame'. Twin brothers Eric and Alec continue the hunt against head vampire Mr Visconti and his supernatural assassins.
Professor Paris Catalano visits Venice, to investigate the last known appearance of the famous vampire Nosferatu during the carnival of 1786.

A beautiful woman sees her husband murdered, and is abducted on orders of a powerful land lord who covets her body. She may look like a tamed puma, but eventually she will find ways to find freedom and love again.

A man and his daughter are mistakenly killed by three poachers hunting deer in the woods. 5 years pass and the poachers return to the area of the crime along with a rich hunter looking for his money shot. Question is are they alone?
A grieving teenager is horrified to discover that her father's new girlfriend looks identical to her dead mother.
Three bone-chilling Stories pulled from classic films deliver three horrifying fates: A deadly seance, a mad experiment, and an unholy sacrifice.

A mysterious virus has overtaken the secluded mountain town of Webb Creek. With no help from the outside world, the town has to do battle with the greatest threat their community has ever faced: themselves.

Residents of a retirement home build a machine for self-euthanasia in order to help their terminally ill friend, though they are faced with a series of dilemmas when rumors of the machine begin to spread.
The affair between a politician and a contemporary dancer is affected by mysterious forces keeping the lovers apart.

Seven years after a rogue nuclear blast, Army veteran Colin Hyde returns to his former home and battles forces real and imagined in a final attempt to free himself from the traumatic memories of war and his haunted civilian life.
At the opening party of a colossal, but poorly constructed, office building, a massive fire breaks out that threatens to destroy the tower and everyone in it.
Upon the sudden death of his mother, a struggling young writer reluctantly returns home to care for his estranged, Alzheimer's-stricken father, an experience that transforms his life.

A married man in his fifties who has lost all interest in his wife suddenly meets Juliette, a young woman. She reignites love in his life but triggers violent arguments with his wife. Their indifference soon turns into chaos.
A ferry driver discovers a boy who won't get off the boat, and in trying to help him stumbles upon a supernatural mystery threatening the homeless.
The movie revolves around the life of an honest police constable's daughter and sacrifices for her love.
Two British best friends and in-laws, Dawn and Jackie, work together at a factory. When Dawn is diagnosed with a brain tumor Jackie shares $100,000 she's got from her secret lover with Dawn.
Sadao and his orphaned buddies attempt to prevent his aged grandmother from being shaken down by a gangster, his goons, and his lawyers.
A Story of 2 Couple go for a gate away in an haunted village and experience something super natural.
A recently widowed woman is on the road with her precocious young son, determined to make a new life for herself as a singer.

A Bosnian girl Mother dies of Cancer. She must move on and help her Dad take care of her Sister with the help of her Aunt. She must also accepting her Dad moving on. The hardest lesson is letting go of her mother.
Sameer, fast at losing his temper is re-located to Goa where he falls in love with Rani. But Sameer's new roommate Sunny, has some plans of his own.

When a desperate and lonely bank robber chooses the wrong hostage, he ends up stuck with the most unexpected partner in crime: a sheltered, uber-Christian middle aged woman hellbent on saving his soul.
A young man moves to Los Angeles to make something of himself -- but finds that such a task might take a little more work than he thought -- in this hilarious romantic comedy.
Stuart Bliss is a marketing genius for surplus military materials. When his wife Janet packs her bags and leaves for unknown destination, he starts to see signs of apocalypse everywhere.

movie_name: La schiava io ce l'ho e tu no
description: Demetrio Cultrera, is a young, rich car dealership Sicilian bachelor who becomes engaged to the beautiful Rosalba Giordano, daughter of a local business owner Giordano Tuna Company.

movie_name: Tomorrow I'll Wake Up and Scald Myself with Tea
description: Jan is a decent, boring man, living a decent, boring life as a rocket designer. When his adventurous twin brother dies in a breakfast accident, Jan decides to impersonate him, unwittingly becoming a part of a Nazi time travel conspiracy.
A weekend reunion becomes a confrontation with an incredible, inhuman creature as a group of young adults are forced to face the terrible sins of their past.
Derrick and Tori, best friends and avid players of Dungeons and Dragons, navigate the social labyrinth of turning a friendship into a relationship.

movie_name: Snuff: Diary of a Serial Killer
description: Ned has problems. His house may be haunted and he may just be possessed. This paranormal activity leads to a bloodbath and a trail of dead bodies. Pray for the young women because Ned is coming.

Teenage twins obsessed with filming their lives with camera phones move to Dead Island, which is a little too true to its name. They find they are not so welcome and come home one night to be terrorized by a pair of serial killers.

A desperate American couple discovers all is not what it seems when they uncover a high-stakes underground scam while traveling abroad. To expose the truth and get back to the U.S., they must risk their lives to save their daughter.
Follows a gang of Somali pirates who find themselves in the midst of a massacre. A 14-year-old boy is their key to survival, but he must decide how far he would go in the name of self-preservation.

Chile 1973 is ruled by the dictator Pinochet. The wealthy don't see the violence, terror, executions etc. including Irene. She's engaged to an officer in the fascist military. She meets Francisco who opens her eyes to truth and love.
Two aliens who crash on Earth must find a buried weapon that will destroy the planet and their own society if not stopped.
Marya is the wife of medical student Victor Sablin, who finds it impossible to deal with military life when he is inducted into the Russian army during World War I.

A dogged, witty young man that journeys back to his desert hometown to avenge his father. Between him and his goal, there are a few greedy old townies, a legendary stack of money and the blonde, blue-eyes love of his life.
Ten men took away his life. Now ten men will pay with their's. Ryan is left for dead, but returns to his old ways for one last revenge trip. And it's going to be bloody!
A young girl stows away aboard a luxury liner which is full of musical stars--and which her father just happens to be the captain.
After spending 3 unforgettable hours with an outlaw, a beautiful young widow turns her story into a worldwide famous book.
A contract killer who has little enthusiasm for his work faces a dilemma when he is instructed to kill the woman he loves.

Set on a country estate where six priests are sent to rid a teenage girl of demons. While waiting for the ritualistic tenth hour, the priests start to uncover demons of their own as well as the dark secrets that haunt the estate.
While Hirono is in prison, his rival Takeda turns his own crime organization into a political party, whose two executives stir up new tensions in their thirst for power.
A young woman is introduced to the new world of the rich and famous only to discover its dark and dangerous side.
It's a simple story of fondness. "Dead End of Trust" tells the story of a love - from inside - a love made of same "blood" still some time remains which is worth more than what has lasted so far.
A deaf and mute writer who retreated into the woods to live a solitary life must fight for her life in silence when a masked killer appears at her window.
A mother and daughter in a remote cabin are faced against two maniac thieves who won't stop terrorizing them until they're dead.

Borneo, 1942: An American soldier escapes WWII and becomes the king of the headhunters in the jungle. Two British soldiers are parachuted into the area to find local support for the battle against the Japanese.

movie_name: Things We Do When We Fall in Love
description: Two unfortunate secret lovers who are constantly looking for a solution to their situation went to a trip out of the city, into the outskirt hoping to find a conclusion to their affair.

One day a mysterious box arrived and a curse began to spread all over. The source of the box is 'Jukai Village'. The village is hidden in Jukai Forest, a suicide spot that once you enter it, you can never come out.
In an ordinary abandoned house - On what could be your ordinary street - A gang of desperate criminals have found something - or has it found them.
A family struggling with loss find themselves at the mercy of an ancient demon trying to destroy them from the inside.
Following his uncle's mysterious death, a young man returns to his childhood home in a secluded village from the Carpathians.
A tale of a hairstylist that has been blindly forced into the streets by her family Then, she gets railroaded into a group of thugs where she becomes unaware of the danger that surrounds her.
A retired DEA agent is out to hunt down and take out a Jamaican drug posse that has targeted he and his family for murder.
Two gangsters engage in a violent feud to get ahold of $500,000 belonging to a recently-deceased rival.
After enduring a bad breakup with his long time girlfriend on the side of an old Oklahoma highway, a young man moves into a 1968 VW Beetle with 8 foot spider legs.

Athena Dizon plays a trick on campus heartthrob and bad boy, gangster, Kenji de los Reyes. Setting up an arrangement to pretend as lovers-to make his ex jealous-they found themselves falling to each other yet falling apart.
A gun runner, dishonorably discharged from the military, is swept deeper into a revolution in Cuba when he crosses paths with an enemy from the past and a beautiful revolutionary and her son.
Jeeva loves Meena, a widow with a son, and respects her even more when he learns about her past. However, Jeeva is forced to marry Divya as her father kidnaps Meena's son in order to threaten Jeeva.
A young man, with a traumatic upbringing, is forced home by a family tragedy only to find himself embattled with local religious extremists.
A young girl fights to save her mother and unlock the meaning of a symbol used as a gateway to create hell on earth.
A boxing champ gets involved with a Broadway show and a shapely chorine...who's engaged to his new sparring partner.
A murdered body is discovered at a Gaming App launch party, guests grow suspicious of each other as they become players of the deadly game.

movie_name: Gabi on the Roof in July
description: An ambitious painter on the verge of a big break confronts his moral decay when his idealist, hell-raising, younger sister comes to stay with him in New York City for the summer.
A parody of recent Korean movies including My Sassy Girl, Swiri, Peppermint Candy, Attack the Gas Station and others.
The classic story gets a new spin when a young girl is intrigued by the secret experiments of her uncle, until she's confronted by his creation.

A young apprentice healer tries to suppress his supernatural abilities so he can fit in with the other kids, but when a malicious spirit breaks out in his apartment he decides to use his abilities while dark family secrets are revealed.
Nathan Hale is mistaken for a infamous hacker, forced to travel across New England with a short tempered Detective to prove his innocence. Will he be able to prove that he is NOT THAT GUY.
The residents of a small town team up to kill a group of evolved sharks that can swim in sand, and are terrorizing local beaches.

The master of the secret Monkey Fist Kung Fu style must fight a gang of warrior thugs who are terrorizing a small village that he is visiting. He teams up with a young Silat expert who has been trying to defeat the bandit gang on his own.

movie_name: Oigye Eseo on Ulemae 9: Mujeok Ui Paiteo Ulemae
description: Superhero's Epserman and Daily must team up yet again to take down Khan, a villainous alien who has invaded earth to avenge his brother, who was defeated by the Thunderhawk.
A modern day update of the classic Poe story, The Fall of the House of Usher, has gay themes incorporated into the main story.

Revolving around the modern Greek woman and her perspective on love in general, not one, but twenty-one brief and vivid vignettes attempt to shed light on an ever-present matter: can there be consequences in Cupid's eternal game?
An unsuspecting, down-and-out man in a washed-up hick town has his life turned upside down when a drop-dead gorgeous stranger walks through the door of the local bar.

Supervising the razing of a mysterious building, a young demolition engineer discovers past inhabitants entombed within its walls by a vicious murderer. Now she must turn the tables before she becomes the killer's latest victim.

In the 7th century BC, a Roman soldier presumed dead returns home and joins his two brothers in a winner takes all battle against three brothers from a rival city-state for power of the Italian peninsula.
A group of college students break into an abandoned convent and become possessed by demonic spirits.

Masha is a young provincial girl, trying her best to succeed in a big city. She studies all day, works all night, and dreams of winning the heart of a popular singer. Will the fairy-tale romance happen?

Veronica has a secret. One she will do anything to keep from being discovered. A month from now, her partner Detective Sean Michael will be brutally murdered and she's the only one that knows how it happens, because she saw it in a dream.
Four US Government agents interrogate the sole survivor out of twelve college students on a relief mission in Haiti. While looking for answers, they encounter the dangers of Black Magic.

Navy SEAL Ryan must deliver his ex-SEAL brother Justin to justice for murdering Jennifer, a scientist in charge of a secret project. But Jennifer is not dead and Ryan quickly finds himself on the wrong end of a gun aimed at them both.
New teachers must partake in a sadistic ritual on the first day of school. It provides one possible answer to the lifelong question: What really goes on behind those closed lounge doors?

movie_name: The Werewolf Versus the Vampire Woman
description: Elvira and her friend Genevieve travel through the French countryside in search of the lost grave of a medieval vampire, Countess Wandesa.
Dr. Benjamin Crumb and his family run a Bed and Breakfast in the woods where the family conducts procedures on some of their unwitting guests (inspired by historical events)
One refusal changes the life of a young couple in love in this romance-drama starring Saif Ali Khan and Twinkle Khanna.
A young romantic navigates college dating while striving to reconcile homosexuality with his classic, cinematic ideals.

The Truth of IT follows the story of Penny Wise, a once loved and revered clown who fell victim to Stephen King's demonization of her whole self. A documentary team follows her life story in hopes of clearing her innocent name.
It tells the irreversible story of two brothers when the money they took from their uncle to pay their debts to the loan shark turned out to be fake.

Today is the day, she's on the square but he's on the road. Inspired by The Divine Comedy, here is their descent into Hell, on their wedding day: a great day that will separate them for life and death.

When the past confronts Father Gaudio, he needs to soul search a life-threatening decision. Adviced by long time friend, Father Coyne, still loved by Angela, and introduced to his son, Joey, Father Gaudio make an honorable life choice.

When one billion yen goes AWOL, "Joe the Ace" (Shishido) spies an opportunity to get rich quick, but things soon go wrong as it turns out he isn't the only one who'll stop at nothing to get his hands on the missing cash.

A cop goes undercover in to infiltrate a drug ring as Cinderella Pu, a Chinese dancer with a unique martial arts style. An agent, who is actually at the center of the ring, is attracted by Pu and claims he can make her a star.
Sick young man drives around in his daddy's camper, looking for lone stray females to kidnap, torture, rape, and murder.

A gangster owes money to the Mafia. He kidnaps his cousin to use her as collateral; killing her by mistake. After her brother joins the Mafia, he learns who is responsible; taking revenge against his own brotherhood.
A passionate holiday romance leads to an obsessive relationship, when an Australian photojournalist wakes one morning in a Berlin apartment and is unable to leave.
A young Pakistani woman rediscovers her traumatic childhood through the grips of jinn (demonic) possession. Based on true stories.
In future Tokyo, a young woman in the privatized police force tracks down her father's killer while battling against mutant rebels known as engineers.
Based on the hit Comic book series - an unlikely alliance of six crime fighting vigilantes join forces to stop an indestructible warlord from gaining the ultimate power to destroy their city.

An Orthodox priest, Father Nikolay, the brother of a Yakuza boss, is drawn into in a mob war in Japan. He escapes to the small Russian village of Glubokoe, where he finds that war has found him again.
Supernatural chaos escalates when a troubled woman with a dark past dabbles with the infamous Ouija board.
A man returns to his small home town from the Vietnam War and discovers corruption, graft, a crooked Sheriff and other dirty deeds.

A former Marine awakens in a labyrinth with no recollection of how she got there and soon discovers she's one of fourteen pawns in a winner-take-all survival contest called "Theseus" set up by a cabal of elites for their entertainment.

A young woman goes missing. A mystery of epic proportions follows. Was she murdered? Was there a cover-up? Did she commit suicide, or have a horrible accident? Her mother won't stop searching until she's found the answers.
After being sent to an unconventional camp for wayward youths, a group of famous influencers learns what it is like to lose the privileges they have in a deadly way.

Daniel, a biologist studying the disappearance of fish, is haunted by paternity. It is by looking for a woman who could be the mother of his children that he will come across a strange fish and discover what he really lacks: love.
Orphaned girl goes to a new country to work and gets picked to be groomed as an MMA fighter. She fights her way to the top now has a chance to save the livelihood of her village.

Booha (Saad), a butcher coming from the countryside to Cairo to find the man whom his late father left his money with, gets tangled in the big city, finds love with kouta (Maie), and gets exploited by Farag (Hosni).
An elderly man tries to find a perfect groom for his granddaughter, Maya, who returns from Mumbai. However, he is unaware of the fact that she is already married to a photographer.

A player needed a random girl friend to bring home to his mom, but the young girl fell for him for real. Although touched by the girl's actions, the man hesitated to accept her love because of a relationship years ago.

movie_name: Bee Bop highschool; Koko yotaro march
description: A sly prep school thug uses his girlfriend to lure Hiroshi and Toru to a fight, but the scheme escalates to an all-out war between everyone involved.
A New York inventor needs cash to develop his big idea, so his adoring wife decides to raise it by divorcing him and marrying an eccentric Florida millionaire with a capricious high-society sister.

Raj (R S Manohar) is a honest and sincere police officer. He is assigned a task to nab notorious gang who smuggle diamonds. Ironically, Raj is ought to settle his debt and for money, join force with the same gang.
A generational curse, comes true in a senseless act of injustice to Ponni and her family. Driven to seek vengeance by Sangaiya, with whom she shares a bitter past.

movie_name: Xiao mian sha shou sha xiao zi
description: Action packed epic! Very rare film! Two top killers, the smiling assassin (Barry Chan) and the gritty kid (Chu Xiao Hua) team up to take on the darker forces in the martial world. Nonstop high level shapes foo fighting-a must see!
A group of stage actors lock themselves in the theater for a rehearsal of their upcoming musical production, unaware that an escaped psychopath has sneaked into the theater with them.
A group of officers of the Russian Imperial Guard prepare a revolt in December 1825, when about 3,000 officers and soldiers refused to swear allegiance to the new tsar.
An injured and amnesiac male who robs to survive in a desert, is rescued with people with an agenda of their own.
Bisma, a teenager with natural martial arts talent, has a crush on Bella, a girl at his college. But her boyfriend, Attar, always annoys Bhishma, until a mysterious man trains him to fight back.
With the murder and investigation of a runaway Mexican-American teen in the down and out town of Bushwick, Brooklyn, Det. John Mejia must see that justice is done.
Dheena works for his brother Adhikesavan, a gangster, and is very close to him. However, things turn sour between them after a misunderstanding leads to the death of their sister.
A boy who grouse watching movies from projector room as his father is a projector man, tries to get a girls love using his theatre experience.

Un pueblo entero oculta el secreto de un asesino que anda suelto a quien se dice el tigre. Antonio Aguilar entra al pueblo cantando sobre su caballo bailoteando para entremeterse en el asunto. Hay venganzas y canciones de sobra.

movie_name: Red Peony Gambler 3: The Flower Cards Game
description: After saving a blind child from being hit by an oncoming train the gambler known as Oryu-The Red Peony is accepted as a guest by a Yakuza boss only to become involved in a romantic dispute between two members of rival clans.
Akin and his friends thought they were sitting down for a friendly game of Rummikub, but instead things got super heated between them. A few of them started exhibiting some strange behavior.

Jenny's parents and siblings are always trying to set her up with a man when she visits them. What they don't know is that she's already met the right person, her "roommate" Kitty, 5 years ago and she wants to marry her and start a family.
A rich man's daughter rents a cheap apartment and pretends to be broke. She falls in love with her poor neighbor who drops her like a hot potato when he realises she misled him.
A toll booth operator travels to her ancestral village in hopes of claiming an inheritance - until she discovers the unsettling truth about her past.
A frustrated detective deals with the case of several gruesome murders committed by people who have no recollection of what they've done.
The story of the Mortamuth Stanley murders is made into a creepy-nightmarish movie by a director who has an obsession with killing his actors.
A group of horror fans find themselves unwilling participants in a nightmarish role playing game that pays homage to a classic horror film.
A short, nondescript man, Mithilesh Shukla marries a tall and beautiful woman. Now jealousy and Mithilesh's own insecurities threaten to wreck his happy home.
A cop finds a mysterious map from the Age of Exploration inside a stolen painting, and enlists the aid of his antiquarian brother to solve its riddles .
The origin story of Bhavesh Joshi, an Indian superhero, who sets out to fulfill his slain friend's wish to clean and reform the country, by training himself to fight and wearing a mask.
A small "Dance-ercize" studio fights for its existence against the unscrupulous owner of a rival club. The conflict boils down to a "Dance Marathon" to settle the score.
A team of developers working on a video game called Gangland find themselves mixed up in the real-life criminal underworld.

Salem prepares for the marriage of Faqiha who lives with her uncle the submerged composer. A film company calls him and asks him to compose, he take Fakiha with him to sing the melody to the director and the producer.
Relentlessly pursued by gold digger Viola Hatfield (Gwen Lee), millionaire Michel Towne (Rod La Rocque) decides to put her off through a marriage of convenience. Based on a story by Elinor Glyn.
A woman blessed with magical powers by the gods and living in a place where you are forbidden to use them, teams up with a princess to summon the gods and bring down the oppressive regime.
A young man falls into the path of gambling and fraud after experiencing betrayal in love from one woman after another. But, finally he finds out that honesty is the best path.
Two women from opposite sides of society find themselves the infatuation of a mysterious killer while struggling with their own convictions and misconceptions.

movie_name: Girl Slaves of Morgana Le Fay
description: Two French girls get lost in the woods and accidentally enter the realm of sorceress Morgana Le Fay - who gives them the choice of either staying young forever as her lovers, or rot in a dungeon for eternity.
Based on international intrigue to seize world power by gaining possession of hidden oil deposits in the United States.

A boxer, fresh out of prison for killing his opponent during a match, and his ruthlessly ambitious friend - both of whom get wrapped up in conspiracy and betrayal as they choose different paths to live new lives.
An L.A. artist suddenly finds his life upside down when his art show is canceled and his model girlfriend leaves him.

The intersecting stories of three people who face difficult choices in life-changing situations are used to illustrate the theories espoused by Henri Laborit about human behavior and the relationship between the self and society.
Several escaped prisoners and two hostage women along with a sheriff's deputy find themselves trapped in a mine shaft, where a cannibalistic mutant is hunting them for food.
At the close of World War II, a young nurse tends to a badly-burned plane crash victim. His past is shown in flashbacks, revealing an involvement in a fateful love affair.
The film is based on a true story. It talks about the end of War and defeat of forces and the relation between Kurds and Arabs by the end of 1991,
Sheriff Pat is hunting a killer who is gearing up the volume of his victims. The mayor is threatening to bring in the Natl Guard. A drug dealer muddies the pool of suspects and involves the CIA.
The son of a Jewish Cantor must defy the traditions of his religious father in order to pursue his dream of being a popular singer.
Sarath is deeply in love with Shari looks for the perfect opportunity to tell her. The movie revolves around a wedding, where who marries who is answered.

Deep in the mountains of Southern California a team of four explorers embark on a journey to find a priceless artifact. Their inner most deadly desires begin to take control of them as they get closer to finding what they seek.

A group of college students set out into the Northwestern wilderness to document and prove the existence of the mythological creature, Big Foot. But this weekend adventure quickly turns into a fight for survival.
This film is about an upside down world, where being homosexual is considered "normal" and heterosexual is considered "not normal".
Marines turned mercenaries-for-hire are on the run from Joseph, one of the soldiers from their squadron turned detective.
In the isolated desert town of Caineville nothing and no one and nothing can be trusted, not even memories. Going home can be murder.

Five friends are invited to the father's house of one of them. They decide to film their weekend to make a little souvenir. Nothing goes as planned and their film will become proof that strange, violent, mysterious, and scary things exist.
Prem, the younger prince of the Kingdom of Khazaag, born in an auspicious astrological time to be the future King goes through his biggest obstacle in life, Geet, his only love.
A surreal period film following an university professor and his eerie nomad friend as they go through loose romantic triangles and face death in peculiar ways.

A ruthless and treacherous prime minister writes a self-incriminating letter conspiring to overthrow the emperor. The letter is stolen by a group determined to expose his treachery, and he will stop at nothing to get it back.

Mario and Olivia fall madly in love. One afternoon, considering that every relationship ends, they end up breaking up. During the big fight, Miamor, the street cat adopted by both, escapes and disappears, like the love that united them.
Daisy is a beautiful no-nonsense employee in an advertising firm. Her female co-workers want to help her find someone, meanwhile the male co-workers are betting on who can bed her first.
Two con men selling phony stock flee to Mexico ahead of the law, where they run into a woman friend from their earlier days, who is now a bullfighter.
A celebrity power couple who is in a live-in relationship fake their breakup to see how far their pursuers will go to win them over.
A troubled young man gets the unique opportunity to spend one more day with his deceased mother before she returns to heaven.
After a trapeze performer is injured during an accident, she is moved to a minister's house where they both fall in love.

The erotic novelist Taeko is writing a morbid story of a family destroyed by incest, murder and abuse. Her assistant, Yuji, sets on a mission to uncover the reality of this story, but the reality might be too much to bear.

A young scientist fights to find a cure to save his true love from a ravaging illness, that has turned her into a blood crazed creature, as they hideaway from their warring families in a post-apocalyptic world.
Father goes to an American Legion convention in Hollywood and the family goes along, visiting a studio a causing havoc on the set.
A guy, bored by his own life, have dreams coming true after an accidental agreement with the Dreamaster.

Detective Kelly discovers her partner's disappearance is the latest in a string of previously unconnected cases, and who's the prize-winning gardener whose success might be less due to green fingers than to his unique fertilizer recipe?

Manorama, the daughter of a rich, orthodox family is married off, leaving her childhood friend Deodhar and his secret love for her, in despair. When tragedy befalls her, and traditions seem unfair, Deodhar must fight for what's right.
The firefighters of Hong Kong's Pillar Point division battle an out-of-control blaze that threatens to plunge the city into darkness.
A girl goes into seclusion seeking answers only to discover that her life is being controlled through an alternate reality.

It is the story of Juan, an islander from Tigre who works in a hostel, and Julieta, a young and beautiful producer of a famous television program that looks for talent. Despite their differences, they feel an irresistible attraction.

movie_name: Pokémon the Movie: The Power of Us
description: Ash meets five residents who come together to save the day when a series of threats endanger the annual Wind Festival and the entire population of their home, Fula City

A series of short stories set in a nightmarish post-apocalyptic future. A handful of desperate survivors scattered around the globe endeavour to survive life-or-death struggles through harsh yet beautiful dystopian landscapes.
A guy gets ditched in love, turns his life around by surrounding himself with close positive people. He's associated with three women.
Two police detectives are assigned to investigate the murders of several young women at a health club.
A love triangle between a guy and two girls, who are best friends but the complete opposite of one another.
A wisecracking NYC private detective earns a living by exposing cheating husbands to their wives, but when he falls for a client, he starts to reconsider everything he believes.
Story of boy and girl, how relationships change over a period of life and how hard is to say Bye sometimes when you want to end the relationship.
A group of people who repressed the grisly memories of what happened after a childhood swim to a pipeline, now find that they simply can't forget the past.

A government paralyzed by political correctness, incapable of making decisions. One man has no choice but to make decisions from the shadows, taking on the leadership of global terrorism, NARCO's and the Underworld.
Elena has married Andrea,knowing it's a social match .Little by little,she falls in love,really and truly.But her husband has been very stand-offish,since their wedding night.

Mahmoud is an overly jealous husband who keeps watch on his wife Sou'ad after driving her to work. He suspects that Sou'ad has a relationship with her boss and he asks her to resign. She agrees in order to teach her husband a lesson.
An under-appreciated intern entrusted with a million-dollar necklace races to find out which of his money-hungry roommates betrayed him as he battles a desperate criminal duo bent on stealing.

In the tribe of Ndongo, a great tragedy occurs. King Ngola dies and after his death, the eldest son creates a climate of terror by hunting down suspects and future heirs to the line of succession, etc,etc.

movie_name: Dreams of Glory: A Boxer's Story
description: Two up-and-coming young fighters struggle to reach the top of their sport and survive the difficulties of life outside the ring. An inspirational drama with exciting boxing footage.
An orphan grows up in Veerakudi village under a taxi driver who names him Rayyar. He grows up to avenge the death of his parents who were mistaken to be naxalites and were murdered brutally.

movie_name: Killer School Girls from Outer Space
description: When a shooting star lands in Small Town USA, a teenage couple decide to check it out. They discover their shooting star is a flying saucer piloted by Killer School Girls from outer space on a mission to destroy the earth!
In an attempt to end alimony payments, a working class man tries to set up his ex wife with potential husbands.
An old flame discovers her ex-boyfriend from the past is a relocated FBI informant out to stop the bad guys.
A wealthy woman who lost her hearing to meningitis meets a doctor who is concocting a serum that will cure deafness.
A military-led government sends out a Special Forces team to track down an unknown creature in an abandoned warehouse.

Failing at another job, Fiadh must return home to take care of her mother, "Mental" Maggie. When the strange goings on appear to be more than her mother's eccentricity, she decides to dabble in the field of paranormal investigation.
A friendship with a top-secret robot turns a lonely girl's life into a thrilling adventure as they take on bullies, evil bots and a scheming madman.
A working-class girl is thwarted and embarrassed in her attempts to move up socially by her gauche family and unstable father.

The Phantom, descendent of a line of African superheroes, travels to New York City to thwart a wealthy criminal genius from obtaining three magic skulls which would give him the secret to ultimate power.
Raja, a thief, and Amar, a goonda, plot to settle in London with the money earned from a robbery. But when Raja gets arrested for killing gangster Sudarshan, Amar's ex-boss, he feels Amar framed him.

Fontaine Leglou is an anesthesiologist in a psychiatric clinic. She loves her job and she loves Michel, her companion with whom she has lived for several years. So why, when he asks for her marriage, Fontaine does not know what to answer?

This is a story about love, friendship and music. Two copywriter brothers have lost in pop music contest called Jhankaar Beats for the last two years. They take the help of an apprentice to compete in a music contest.
Three youths who studied abroad in Canada all return to Hong Kong. They cramp into a cheap Tsimshatsui motel and begin a first come first serve competition of love.
Popular and beautiful Fanny Trellis is forced into a loveless marriage with an older man, Jewish banker Job Skeffington, in order to save her beloved brother Trippy from an embezzlement charge.

A crack Team of Army Rangers plans and executes a covert mission across the southern Arizona border into Mexico to rescue a young Hispanic female who has been kidnapped from Arizona into the sex slave trade by the Mexican drug cartel.

movie_name: Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade
description: In 1938, after his father goes missing while pursuing the Holy Grail, Indiana Jones finds himself up against the Nazis again to stop them from obtaining its powers.

A pro-wrestler who is traumatized from years of childhood abuse, finds himself raising his children on his own and struggling with debt. His plot to defraud the cartels underground fighting operations turn sour as places his son in danger.
A young swordsman is forced into a tough situation. He must resolve a potential power struggle that involves his adolescent crush Fuku.
Romance--comedy--punctuated with songs--dances--Charito gives Leroy the runaround in a big comedy romance.
A horror film in which residents of a small town must survive a zombie attack stemming from the Three Mile Island accident.

movie_name: Doli Chadh Ke Dulhin Sasurar Chalali
description: Sanjay who is from a simple background falls in love Madhu who is from a wealthy family. Her family fix her wedding to Dinesh and she reluctantly accepts. She decides to meet Sanjay one last time but events don't go as planned.

Jenny, a Navy Seal-Intel Officer, leaving duty after 15-years in the Middle East takes a job as bodyguard for a brother and sister in Beirut who, under Jenny's watch, are kidnapped in a political plot to control the voice of their father.
I AM NO ONE is a documentary film written, directed, and edited by Jason Hoover about a man named Charles Lake who moonlights as a serial killer in Chicago, IL.
When a celebrated LAPD homicide detective inadvertently discovers that he is a serial killer, he chases himself through time, across decades, to stop himself from killing.
An American sailor falls in love with a fisherman's daughter and convinces her that Jesus is more powerful than the gods who have cursed her.

After her childhood friend suffers a terrible motorbike accident, marketing prodigy Skye is pulled from her corporate lifestyle and drawn back to her country roots; where past demons, old relationships and the motocross track await her.
A young mother must protect her daughter from a rogue scientist on a murderous rampage to steal the girl's psychic powers for herself.
A priest gathers together a team of desperate people to rob a church and kidnap a young woman with a dark secret.
During WW1, a train is stopped by a bombing ;a young soldier takes advantage of the opportunity to go to his native village to see his parents .

Passion Island - a place where individuals with different goals met, weaving colorful stories as their paths intertwined...Simon and Johanna divorced years ago, citing different values and goals in life.
Chew Chor Meng and Hong Kong actress Kitty Lai (Li Meixian) lead the cast in this Mediacorp telemovie.
A physician discovers that two children are being kept virtually imprisoned in their house by their father. He investigates, and discovers a web of sex, incest, and Satanic possession.
A horror film that depicts St. Nicholas as a murderous bishop who kidnaps and murders children when there is a full moon on December 5.
Ordinary people meet in a laundry service in Budapest, Hungary and they share the same thing, their dirty secrets.

At her family's remote ancestral home, Kelly (Rica Peralejo), her boyfriend, Choppy (Dingdong Dantes), and a group of their pals fight boredom by dabbling in a supernatural game called Spirit of the glass.
A gangster and his flunkies abduct and kill a man's daughter. Soon, the man's adopted son sets out to avenge her death.
Wealthy thrill-seekers pay huge premiums to have themselves inserted into military adventures, only this time things don't go exactly to plan.
A tragic car accident in the middle of nowhere finds six stranded college students fighting for their lives after making a horrifying discovery in a remote farmhouse in this rural frightener.

movie_name: Halloween: The Night HE Came Back
description: A shy and introverted aspiring actress moves to Haddonfield Illinois to reconnect with her brother Bob. Unaware of the town's secrets and her connection to them, a familiar presence engulfs the innocence rebuilt on Halloween night.

movie_name: In the Name of the King: A Dungeon Siege Tale
description: A man named Farmer sets out to rescue his kidnapped wife and avenge the death of his son, two acts committed by the Krugs, a race of animal-warriors who are controlled by the evil Gallian.
An illusion, or reality? The future, or the past? One girl, or two? Human, or something else? Nothing is what it seems in this post apocalyptic world.
Lola is pregnant. But she does not know who the father is: Jamal, the black muslim, son of diplomats, or Felix, the pennyless jewish messenger. Jamal and Felix meet at Lola's, and the race begins.

Fame-hungry Gemma asks her boyfriend Danny and his media student mate Nathan to film her Big Brother audition. They hear about a sex party and change course, but soon wish they hadn't as the party goers turn out to be devil worshippers.
Action king Fernando Poe Jr. exacts retributive justice one more - An eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth.

When the world is gripped by a plague unleashed by the evil lord Chaos, and humans are turned into rabid creatures, mankind can only be saved by three young women, descendants of a Goddess, with the power to stop Chaos' evil.
A trafficker is arrested and when he escapes he reaches the Lacandona Jungle, where a doctor treats him for his wounds.
A theatrical hit and a classic vampire thriller set in today's Latin America, Tremendous Dawn re-tells the story of Dante, a human vampire who must take blood form strangers in order to survive.
A hillbilly deacon, who is actually a cardsharp in disguise, becomes involved in a small-town fight game.
A wealthy couple battles a poor laborer over the rights to a small ranch house, but events take a shocking turn after an enormous terrorist attack cuts the three off from civilization.
Vikings reach the new world, but their efforts to stay are ill-fated. Back home, secrets are exposed, and two women have a reckoning.
Slip confronts a monopolizing taxicab company whose criminal tactics aim to drive its rivals out of business.
In 1910 Wisconsin, the people of Black River Falls face murder, disease and arson- all while something is killing their livestock.
In the eve of the Day of the Dead, among mysterious old rituals of the Vilnius region, ghosts of the past and present start to appear.
The clash of two mighty forces. This time, the cobra strikes with deadlier venom against the diabolical aristocrat of evils.

1992 Belgrade. Aleksa works the night shift at an occult magazine to avoid military police, draft and war. Old colleague, Mrs. Kosara, offers him shelter at her place. Soon, a dead friend warns him in his dream about the old lady.

Fuerza, (pronouced Foo-where-sah), is a woman endowed with superhuman powers that must stop a galactic entity who is threatening to drain the life forces from the inhabitants of Earth as a source of nourishment for its survival.
A love triangle that highlights the frustration and anguish of three young Pakistani Punjabis whose lives are affected by decisions enforced on them by their elders.
The reverse writing of "Medusa" indicates a surreal story of a woman (Yangzom Brauen) in the woods, where she meets Satan experiencing a heavenly vision after consuming hallucinating mushrooms.

Everyone in town knows the story of Old Aunt Ethel. It's said she makes Halloween candy and pumpkin pie out of the kids that trick-or-treat at her house. This Halloween, the neighborhood teens are going to find out the truth.
After stealing and hiding a van with $20 million inside, Jimmy wakes up in a safe house living room getting beaten to death by a very curious band of thugs.
Bound together by the same secret, the same love, the same face, they challenged each other's place in the sun.
A struggling widow falls in love with an illiterate short-order cook whom she teaches to read and write in her kitchen each night.
A woman suffers a traumatic incident as a young girl, whereas she doesn't know which reality is the real one.

Vietnam vet with a degree in poison gas application goes to Turkey to relax after his recent job . Richard is a hit man and "friends" with the Godfather. Richard is also after the goons who killed his parents. Many twists and turns

In 1947 a Gandhi follower and a freedom fighter were brutally attacked. Due to unavoidable circumstances, the freedom fighter son gets trapped in the mafia world and the story revolves between 1942 to 1986.

A group of elite, military operators are thrust on an adventure of intrigue and espionage. This journey leads from ancient religious relics to extraterrestrial technology and lastly to the Order of the Knights Templar.
A murderer finds himself on trial in Hell, caught between a bitter prosecutor and an inexperienced defense attorney.
A vigilante with special powers uses them to exact his own justice and to dethrone a corrupt corporate America.
A diverted time travel excursion marks an innocent history professor as the killer of a prominent political figure.

The son of a virtual world designer goes looking for his father and ends up inside the digital world that his father designed. He meets his father's corrupted creation and a unique ally who was born inside the digital world.
Three buddies after 'Fast Money' try flying drugs into the U.S. from Mexico. When they meet with unexpected dangers, the trip turns turbulent.
A new father struggling with fatigue, emotional insecurities, and a failing marriage joins a dating app, only to swipe right on what may be an inhuman presence.
Centuries ago in the Orient, the fiscal exactions on the people lead to a revolt against the usurper of the throne, and the empowerment of a new leader.
Dr.Veera, a mad scientist, creates an A.I. based Robot 'Puli' which travels back in time to make things in Veera's life right.....
A woman living in a secluded house in the hills is forced to deal with her dark and twisted past after killing an intruder in the middle of the night during a home invasion.

A bizarre and tragic love story involving swineherd, village fool, teacher and an agricultural pilot. The story unfolds in a remote village in the communist ruled Yugoslavia at the down of Soviet occupation of Czechoslovakia in 1968.
It is the night of Pine Valley High School's ten-year reunion. Suspense and horror intensifies as former classmates mysteriously disappear one by one.

A girl is about to inherit a fortune, but she is missing in Africa. Only then, family charges Congo Bill, an adventurer, to find her, and bring her back to civilization. He follows a legend about some White Queen, but his path is full of difficulties, by an inhospitable jungle, and the man who will lose the fortune if the girl is found alive.
A kidnapped diver is taken to an island inhabited by a mad scientist and his half-animal, half-human creations.

Shi Guiqing, who raised her daughter alone, suddenly passed away. When her daughter Shi Xiaowei picked up her belongings, she found a group photo which showed some clues to set her on the way to find her father.

The story of the film follows Karan Khanna, a politician of Indian origin in the United Kingdom, who is accused of killing his wife. He tells his lawyer that a spirit committed the murder and should be tried.
A cynical American expatriate gets involved in smuggling and gun-running for the rebels during the 1925 Syrian insurgency against French occupation.
A lady reporter and two college students search for the "Gold Special," a train that disappeared without a trace.
A small desert town is terrorized by a powerful, seemingly possessed car, and the local sheriff may be the only one who can stop it.

Sally sits by her window earning money for an operation so she can be a dance teacher again. Jimmie is an ice cream salesman hoping to advance. Their romance is sidetracked when she uses her savings to help him out of a fix.

Amid a series of murder victims drained of blood, a high school teacher's vampire-like behavior marks him as the prime target of an NYPD special unit investigation. With the manhunt closing in, he struggles for a last chance at redemption, or, forever embraces his demon.
Two street-wise Chicago cops have to shake off some rust after returning from a Key West vacation to pursue a drug dealer who nearly killed them in the past.
Luo Kun and Bao are two night duty security guards at an underground garage, where a certain parking spot, known as the "mortuary parking", is violently haunted.

A young man discovers his powers after surviving a violent crime, finding himself in the middle of a war over the future of humanity, which a secret society seeks to control the empowered and their abilities.
Shiva, a bus conductor, robs the corrupt in order to fund an organisation that aids those with disabilities. To avoid detection and trial, he pretends to be his twin, who has disabilities.
When an estranged Black woman inherits a haunted plantation, she must decide whether she will sell the property or face her family's ghosts.

Photographer Francesca builds Maia's confidence while having to control her own obsessive and sexual desires towards Maia. As they spend more time together, Maia becomes the object of her obsession and things slowly spiral out of control.
Tom Sharky is demoted to vice after a bust goes terribly wrong. He and his team stumble across a mob murder tied to prostitution and government.
Two American Legionnaires on convention in New York share adventures and rivalries in an around show biz.
Henry Durand is a young federal agent who is given a difficult assignment: spy on his mother and her boyfriend who is suspected of leading a gang of art thieves.

Randy and Mitch invites two other couples to spend a relaxing vacation in Randy's rest house. At first, the rest house seems like a paradise but soon, the vacation turns into a nightmare as the guests turn up dead one after the other.
Two teenagers fall in love, but their feuding families and fate itself cause the relationship to end in tragedy.
A stripper/fortune teller uses a magical Haitian amulet to keep young, and in so doing forces others to kill for her.

movie_name: The Woman in Black 2: Angel of Death
description: 40 years after the first haunting at Eel Marsh House, a group of children evacuated from WWII London arrives, awakening the house's darkest inhabitant.
The film, commissioned for the centenary of the Turkish Air Force, was filmed in collaboration with the Turkish Air Force in the air base in Konya. Some aerial scenes were notably performed.
A secret organization has perfected the cloning process for multiple breeds of dinosaur along with the ability to control them using a specialized technology.

The film follows an Egyptian young woman who travels to Lebanon, and faces lots of trouble throughout her journey, until a Lebanese man offers help, and their relationship develops into a deeper connection.

In the year 2019, a plague has transformed almost every human into vampires. Faced with a dwindling blood supply, the fractured dominant race plots their survival; meanwhile, a researcher works with a covert band of vamps on a way to save humankind.
The story of two teens, Cassandra and Lucas, as they get involved in a timeless love story against many odds.
When a group of kids are being targeted by an evil ancient demon called, "The Devourer." They must stick together and find out why he's targeting them.

movie_name: Dateline Chicago: Arrest the Nurse Killer
description: Based on the horrific 1970's murder of 8 nurses in Chicago by Richard Speck that paralyzed the city of Chicago!
Two guys and a female hitchhiker are terrorized by a monstrous looking man driving a giant monster truck.
A French gang of thieves flies over to Chicago for a one time job. However, things seem to get out of hand soon.
The idyllic life of Tarzan and Jane is challenged by men on safari who come seeking ivory, and come seeking Jane as well.

movie_name: Everything Is Terrible! Presents: The Great Satan
description: The found footage collective, Everything is Terrible! Has taken over 2,000 forgotten VHS tapes and re-contextualized them in order to tell the tale of The Dark Lord himself, Lucifer.
Running--dashing--not so much fear dear life--as for freedom. Destinatin: Tundo: Isla Puting Bato the warpath of justice.
A middle-aged man's relationship with a young model is questioned by his daughter, who's dating an older man herself.

movie_name: The Last House on the Left
description: After kidnapping and brutally assaulting two young women, a gang unknowingly finds refuge at a vacation home belonging to the parents of one of the victims: a mother and father who devise an increasingly gruesome series of revenge tactics.

movie_name: The Warrior and the Blind Swordsman
description: Dutch colonial army in West Java holds a tournament to select the best warrior to confront local freedom fighter Parmin (Jaka Sembung). The winner is a blind swordsman. Things get complicated when magician seductress Dewi Magi intervenes.
As an ex-con attempts to rekindle his relationship with his young daughter, he learns that she is being brainwashed by a sadistic cult.
The terrifying story of a family that experienced the biggest demonic possession after moving into a house plagued by malicious spirits.

Joon Ho and Ah Yeong have been best friends since college and now a couple living together. Ah Yeong is making the best of her situation, but she feels his boyfriend Joon Ho is wasting his life in excuse of preparing for an exam.
A struggling actress must fight for her life when she's pitted against a group of actors inside a death-trap theatre.
An underworld kingpin recruits people endowed with 'Luck' from across the globe to take part in a series of challenges designed to test their 'Luck' factor, as gamblers around the world bet on them.
A vagrant enters the lives of an arrogant upper-class family, turning their lives into a psychological nightmare in the process.
A mad javelin thrower kills teenagers in the school. All promising athletes are executed in the most brutal way. Especially naked girls in dressing-rooms or saunas.

A Turkish Bey's daughter is in love with an adventurous young man, but her father is forced to arrange a marriage of convenience with Lima, Prince of Tibet - to prevent an invasion by the Mongols. She has to fight hard for her love.

In a post-apocalypse world inhabited by the Amish, a roving gang led by the corpulent Hog is making life miserable for the peaceful townspeople. Only one lone gunfighter dares to stand in their way. He never draws first - he's the reactor!
Pagona loves Yiannos, her father's sheeper, who wants to marry her with Dimos, the son of other sheeper of the nearby village. However, Crystalo loves Yiannos too.
When a Caribbean family vacation takes a disastrous turn, a father finds himself at the mercy of a cold-blooded fisherman, and a desperate race against the clock to save his wife and son.

Ex-mercenaries, who have seen and done horrible things, decide to retire and open up a used car lot in Scottsdale, AZ. They sell a lemon to the wrong person, and find themselves reverting back to their old ways as mercenaries.
A video game programmer is recruited by the government to fight terrorists using virtual technology.
When a genetically engineered weapon escapes containment from a top secret lab in Northern California a dark chess match begins amongst the members of the "Recovery team."

In the rural town of Wickenhaven, a psychotic tanning salon owner is responsible for the disappearances of many young, innocent girls, while his wife, an exotic purse designer, is willing to overlook his evil nature.
Passion, criminal instincts an traditions melt together in this film, that shakes our conception of crime.

Ashok is on the search for love when he meets Anjali. He falls in love with Anjali but is heart broken when Anjali turns him away. Anjali is supposed to be arranged in marriage to someone her father chooses for her.
Quien dijo que eran el sexo débil?. Cuatro valientes y aguerridas mujeres pelean contra una pandilla de criminales que quiere apoderarse de una valiosa fórmula de un cientÍfico.
On their way to Vegas, a group of friends celebrating a birthday get into an accident and end up going the VERY wrong way while looking for help.
When her mother is sick and dying, 14-year-old Maria is sent to live with Catholic nuns. But when one of her caretakers falls for her for the wrong reasons, her arrival slowly turns sinister.
Stranded on a cruise ship, a newlywed couple must fight COVID, and other passengers until they find a safe port.

When a pilot becomes the sole survivor of an airliner crash that kills over 300 people, he works with a psychic and a priest to determine who is responsible for the incident and pacify the vengeful souls of the victims.
After years of hiding, the notorious American leftist radical, Abbie Hoffman, discusses his life, his cause and the opposition he endured.

American car designer Carroll Shelby and driver Ken Miles battle corporate interference and the laws of physics to build a revolutionary race car for Ford in order to defeat Ferrari at the 24 Hours of Le Mans in 1966.
Mentalist who can read the minds of others, irrespective of how hard they try to hide details from him. Imagine what would happen if cops choose to use such a man to solve crimes?
