A Chicago playwright uses self-hypnosis to travel back in time and meet the actress whose vintage portrait hangs in a grand hotel.

An American high school girl travels with her family on Spring Break to what she believes will be a relaxing week of sun and cute boys in Cabo only to discover her parents have decided instead to spend their vacation in Reykjavik, Iceland.
Alvy Singer, a divorced Jewish comedian, reflects on his relationship with ex-lover Annie Hall, an aspiring nightclub singer, which ended abruptly just like his previous marriages.
The youngest one of the Seven Fairies falls in love with a poor decent young man named Dong Yong, but the love between a mortal and a fairy is not allowed by the laws of God in heaven.
A spy/terrorist film set in a modern day world where a man who sees his family killed plots to set off two bombs in revenge.
While on their way to visit family, Tori and Ricks country detour takes them on the ride of their lives.
Inspector Raj Singh sets out to avenge his father, who was killed by Shankar. However, he is shocked when he discovers that he has a stepbrother who now works for the culprit.
A complex story of murder, passion and haunting memories for three estranged brothers and their ailing father.
An American journalist returns to Cambodia to bring out the girlfriend he was forced to leave behind when the murderous Khmer Rouge took over the country.

movie_name: È solo questione di punti di vista
description: Two guys find an old map that signs the exactly position of the fountain of youth. So they came to the rescue, but some guys have the same objective.

movie_name: Left Behind III: World at War
description: The world falls into chaos as Nicolae Carpathia detonates nuclear devices across the globe and stages multiple devastating attacks against both the Tribulation Force and an international militia, led by U.S. President Gerald Fitzhugh.

The story of a friendship between a tough, young Rock N Roll performer trying to make it on the Sunset Strip, and an old, wise, retired Jewish lawyer. A sometimes funny, sometimes touching story that leaves you wanting more.
On his way to prison, a man gets intercepted by a secretive government agency who task him to monitor a secret experiment in exchange for commuting his sentence.

Dedicated boxers square off against trigger-happy drug pushers in Brian Clyde's remarkably assured first feature, developed under the aegis of exec producer Roger Corman. Classy little actioner, reportedly made for a mere $100,000.

Several Crime Syndicates on London have just discovered they've all hired the same hit man to kill one another. A scarred up punk called, RAMBLER. Now they've put a massive bounty on his head. The streets of London are about to burn.
A band of thieves steal from a Mexican bank and travel to Argentina to launder the money. Upon their arrival the plan goes south and it's up to them to figure out what went wrong.
Two couples spend a weekend in the country, only to cross paths with a brutal serial killer. As the body count rises, suspicion spirals into paranoia, climaxing in a terrifying battle for survival.
A romantic getaway for two troubled college sweethearts turns into a struggle for survival when unexpected guests - and the surrounding environment - exhibit signs of a mysterious infection.

After a tragic accident that killed her parents, Liza is unable to walk and spends her days trolling vloggers. When she witnesses a murder online, the police dismisses it as a hoax, and it's up to Liza to find the killer.
Azhagar and his friend Paraman kill the person who humiliated Kanugu's brother and surrenders themselves to the police. However, they soon learn that Kanugu has betrayed them.

To save her shop, a quirky baker struggles to win a national baking contest against a scheming reality-show diva while caught in a romantic jam between a bake-a-holic competitor and her old flame, the show's most critical judge.
Sam, receives a call from Emily a nearly blind woman who is running from her murderous ex in the woods. She must survive the ordeal with Sam being her eyes using video call.

During Covid19, Carlos flees from his home- pulled towards a mysterious mountain in the wilderness where he thinks he can stay safe and reconnect with his childhood. But when Joey steps out of the woods, things take a dark turn.
Narayanankutty, a differently-abled man who owns a stationery shop, gets caught in a murder case. He must seek help in the investigation and prove his innocence.
While on a trip to Los Angeles, a couples relationship is tested when an unexpected individual enters their lives.

A group of five people working to stay alive in a post-apocalyptic future discover what they think is a safe, abandoned farmhouse, but they soon find themselves fighting to stay alive as a gang of bloodthirsty predators attack.
Gabrielle has the ability to see, speak and allow the dead to possess her body. Not all of the spirits hanging out in purgatory have good intentions. Based on the graphic novel by Everette Hartsoe
Sam discovers his great grandfather's diary containing a map, he and his friends venture out in the treacherous underground city to find the notorious mobster's famed lost heist.
Three parapsychologists forced out of their university funding set up shop as a unique ghost removal service in New York City, attracting frightened yet skeptical customers.
A hacker tries to sell sensitive data related to a scam and an NIA officer accidentally gets involved, saving him from getting killed.

Two brothers kill their parents during a hunting trip at their cabin. They ended up at a psych ward only to break out 15 years later. Evil comes home but they see it has been occupied and goes to the extreme to reclaim their cabin.

Adapted from Ron Arias' novel, The Road to Tamazunchale, Fausto Tejada, is in the final chapter of his life. Still full of imagination, this remarkable everyman blurs the realities of memory, time and space, changing lives for the better.
A psychological thriller, which explores the destruction of a young couple's seemingly perfect marriage.

Myra made the mistake of stealing money from the mob. Now on the run, she is betrayed by her boyfriend and loses the money to an innocent bystander, Gina. They are pursued by a pack of bloodthirsty mobsters and a relentless hitman.

A young mother and scientist, whose world is disturbingly turned upside down when she loses her son in a tragic accident, is offered the chance to be a mother again. Only it comes at a cost, and with an unnerving twist.
Alone in the woods, nature photographer Harper witnesses a violent crime. After being captured by the culprits, she uses her survivalist skills to try and make it out alive.

The relevant epic story of the strong-willed, courageous and independent woman before her time, Kurmanjan, who is revered to this day for her diplomacy for saving her nation from complete destruction when the Russians invaded.
A nightmare has arrived, the Invasion is here. Darkseid of Apokolips has set to Earth after a Mother Box is opened. Earth's heroes are soon to bring justice against Darkseid's inevitable strength.

Stones of power are given to chosen fighters trained by a master in order to overthrow the master's plan to destroy humanity. The fighters do not necessarily get along even as the world heads toward peril.

movie_name: Di Renjie zhi fen tian yi huo
description: Di Renjie heads to Wei Zhou where there were four plague to hold the position of the prefectural governor and in the process he is injured and encounter all sorts of weird incidents.
Fred, a commercial director, decides to learn the flute to relieve his stress. His music teacher is none other than Isabelle, a flutist he once saw playing in the subway. He falls under her charm.
Building designer Bill and his family move into a seemingly wonderful house, but not aware of the house is haunted.
An immortal Scottish swordsman must confront the last of his immortal opponent, a murderously brutal barbarian who lusts for the fabled "Prize".

An abandoned school has become a film set. There is a rumor that various strange phenomena occur there due to the curse of a student who was harassed, locked in the basement and disappeared without a trace.
Soldiers in a rural English town are being brutally murdered by an unknown creature. Two sisters living nearby realize they might understand what's happening.

Break a mirror. Walk under a ladder. Step on a crack. Some of the many innocent superstitions that everyone knows. But someone at a posh performing arts high school is taking them a deadly step further.
A lonely son of a rich industrialist falls in love with a poor girl but life won't be easy for him without his mother's consent. A local goon is also deeply in love with the same girl.
A woman wakes up on a distant planet and finds the crew of her space station viciously killed. Her investigation into what happened sets in motion a terrifying chain of events.

movie_name: Cool Cat Stops a School Shooting: A School Safety Film
description: Cool Cat is in class when an active shooter attacks his school, and Cool Cat shows children different techniques and safety tips on what to do to stay safe, and then Cool Cat comes face-to-face with the shooter - But what happens then.

A clumsy, easy-going but tough restaurant chef witnesses a murder of a cop. This leads him to a world of trouble, as the killer seeks to silence him. Luckily, the vengeful partner of the dead cop is there to help him.
Jason witnesses a brutal murder, which he ignores, because with his condition he sees hallucinations like that every day; but this time it was real and the killer wants him dead.
A creepy German-made Wallace thriller about the ghost of a hanged man who returns to fulfill his promise. All of his accusers must die.

Ginger grows up in a slow town. Because of her wild attitude, her father decides to send her to a strict boarding school. Despite the strictness, the girls have fun getting into flapper lifestyle trouble including flirting.

Choi, Mun-oh decides to become a police officer over the objections of his girlfriend. He hopes to serve his country and is determined to fight the prejudices and stereotypes the public holds of the police through nobility and honesty
Two out of work musicians put on drag to get work in an all girl band. Inevitable comical romantic complications ensue.
Skateboarder named Orpheus and friends go to Hell to stop television signals that are brainwashing America.

movie_name: Katmandú, un espejo en el cielo
description: In early-90s Kathmandu, an inspired Catalan teacher arrives in town to work at the local school; however, she will soon encounter the region's extreme poverty and its weak educational system.
Determined to prove herself, a police officer must go undercover at a seedy lounge to catch a serial killer.

The story of Poles moving to the west of the country after the war - to the lands originally inhabited by Germans - and starting a new life there. Lonely boy Bozek meets a girl called Lucyna and wants to run away from his wartime past.
After his release from prison, Danny has to fight to get his respect back from the new breed of street racers now ruling the roads.

In post-1821 Peloponnese, a humble farmhand dares to fall in love with the beautiful sister of the area's haughty landlord, only to trigger a dangerous cycle of unbridled violence. Can there be redemption for the proud ones?

A group of friends leaves in the forest, Julie pregnant for several months disappears strangely. These friends look for her but, unhappily for her, she will fall on the two brothers "Digouline" and Douly", still alive !.
Stimulator champion Du Jieke challenges formula one championships for his crush on formula one driver Lu Lili to a stimulator championship.
Two friends go to an abandoned building to cut out its copper wiring. When they get there, they come across a band of mercenaries raiding the former Area 53 facility for alien weaponry.
A young African man challenges the leaders of Malaysia's biggest drugs and human trafficking syndicates, in a mission to clear his name and to free the love of his life.

It's Boonchu's second year in college and he tries to impress his girlfriend by running for University President to help those poor students and reestablish new rules and conditions of the scholarship.
In the brutal world of dating and mating, every single woman needs a fan. Kate Maxwell just happens to have two.

Baba turns to crime to support his brother, Avinash. However, Baba keeps him distant from the underworld nexus, but problems escalate when Avinash becomes a cop and is assigned to arrest his own brother.
A dedicated L.A. police detective and a female psychic must stop a demonic serial killer who was given the powers of resurrection, teleportation and possession.

Delivering humanitarian aide to a remote region of Asia, a group of British and Americans encounter the horrors of flesh eating Piranha when the monsoon begins and the water swells trapping them inland.
An update to the 1996 film 'Twister', which centered on a pair of storm chasers who risk their lives in an attempt to test an experimental weather alert system.

The film is centered around a little girl Lucy who grows up with a monster named Sammy in her closet. The two's relationship is typically happy until Sammy hears people claiming he isn't real, or if they try to take Lucy away from him.

movie_name: The Investigation: A Haunting in Sherwood
description: Private investigator Gareth Morris went missing in 2018 while investigating noises coming from a house in Sherwood.He hacked in to the homes security system and recorded everything.A chilling found footage horror to chill your blood.
Irina, a dying 100-year-old vampire, a motel manager, and a broken prostitute live a in a world of literal and figurative decay.
Ninjas and dragons - a match made in heaven? See for yourself. Starring Dong Li and Zia Qing and co-starring Sun Kenfa, Xu Li, Song Wenhua. Directed by Ding Zhuolun.
An investigative officer investigates a sensational and challenging murder case, which has many layers.
Akari Inoue and other students are kidnapped and incarcerated. They are forced to participate in a game of kill and survive. The last survivor will receive one hundred million yen.
Octogenarian who enters into a state of dementia after the sudden suicide of his wife, sparking a series of paranormal events that will put his family's lives at risk.
There were stories of a 15 foot long fish-like creature prowling in the shallows near Smevik Island in Lake Bullaren, Sweden. Now in 2020 it's time for a new attempt to capture the legendary beast.

A man suffering nightmares as a result of childhood PTSD meets the woman of his dreams. Neither can help themselves from the pitfalls that opening their hearts creates, or the pasts they never properly healed from.
In 1937, a Chinese martial artist returns to Shanghai to find his teacher dead and his school harassed by the Japanese.
Mac, an ex-prisoner and Monika, a doctor who no longer practices, hide from their past unsure of how to face their future as their relationship develops.

Julia is trying to make a career as a pastry chef when she wins the grand prize of the Four Seasons' Cooking Competition: an apprenticeship under Roberto Banando, a world famous European chef. It turns out, Roberto is a Mammoni.
In the English village of Midwich, the blonde-haired, glowing-eyed children of uncertain paternity prove to have frightening powers.

Tommy is an innocent cavalry officer who falls in love with a beautiful Apache woman (Yara Kewa) after rescuing her from a nasty gun smuggler named Honest Jeremy. When Jeremy and his gang find Tommy, gruesome violence ensues.
A florist, who abides by a strict five-date limit with any man, finds herself wanting more with the new restaurateur in town.
Carnage, death, and despair await the ignoble remnants of a persecuted family who assemble for the wedding of their daughter on the eve of an evil 100-year-old curse.
A cockney girl and her soccer team of thugs confront an Indian player who she had previouly had a fling with.
Shelly Wong creates a high concept video game that has big market potential, A Triad boss get s wind of it and hires a posse of ninjas to steal it.
A group of young people head to Ibiza for the holiday of a lifetime - all the sun, sea, and sex, they can handle. If only there wasn't a zombie outbreak getting in the way.
Jean Bellard and Carl Mank, two Western engineers supported by Hamid are in search of a terrorist group that murdered their colleague in the Tunisian desert.

A speculative story about what happened at convicted murderer and alternative healer Linda Burfield Hazzard's "School of Health" in Olalla, Washington in 1935 when it mysteriously burned to the ground.

Two siblings begin to develop special talents after they find a mysterious box of toys. Soon the kids, their parents, and even their teacher are drawn into a strange new world and find a task ahead of them that is far more important than any of them could imagine!
Chelsea helps Leny overcome his life from a down-spin as his reality comes crashing down after he discovers his wife in bed with another woman.
Russian author Fyodor Dostoyevsky (Sir Michael Gambon) must write a novel in twenty-seven days in a deal to pay off his gambling debts, and feverishly dictates the novel "The Gambler".
A struggling writer fleeing from his failed marriage stumbles across a beautiful seaside town and finds himself drawn in by its bizarre inhabitants.
The untold story of how a CIA officer trained a network of agents who found the Soviet missiles in Cuba.

Sequel to the 2012 film "At Stake: Vampire Solutions", the AS:VS team is back and facing a host of new problems as they work to avoid government shut down, and fight to stay alive while combating the growing vampire threat.

In the midst of World War 2, intelligence services from England, Germany and Russia collided in a fierce fight for the mind of Nicky Raus, a genius German Jewish scientist who has been developing a powerful state-of-the-art secret weapon.

A young man takes a job at a failing pizzeria in hopes of solving the disappearance of a missing employee. There he's forced to confront his troubled past to not only find the missing worker, but save himself.

Emily Burns is being held captive in a room with no idea how she got there. Determined to escape and return to her family, Emily discovers clues within the room that help explain why she's there...but will they help her escape?
A family from Afghanistan moves to a foreign country to live a better and happier life, but they desire to have it all.
In a Swiss church, Antonio Carrera is getting married to the pretty daughter of an Italian Mafioso, as army police marches in and takes him to the compulsory Swiss military school.
A former government employee is forced to team with a teenage girl to take revenge against an underground government that murdered their families.
A young man hates his father for abandoning his mother, which led to her death. But after knowing the truth, he avenges his mother's death along with his look alike step brother.
Ivy Morgan, a college student in New Orleans, falls for Ren Owens, the last person she expected to enter her rigidly controlled life. Based on the novel 'Wicked' by Jennifer L. Armentrout.
A depressed middle-aged tour guide who lives in his own bubble gets another chance to experience and face reality through a chirpy girl.
Five bizarre stories with no apparent connection to one and other eventually become intertwined, resulting in surreal circumstances.
A rebel crosses swords with an influential rich man after falling in love with his daughter. However the girl's father is hell bent to break their relation at any cost.
Mike is planning a kidnapping of a multi millionaires Daughter in order to bribe him for $5M., but things take an unexpected turn.

Hanuma is engaged to struggling musician Mahrous. She meets film producer Khaled, who decides to take her to fame. She forgets her people and she's torn between following her desires or returning to the right path.

When everything you know tells you one thing, but your heart knows differently. A chance encounter, love at first sight, a trip to a foreign country, a perfect weekend, a life changing connection. - And then.
While one tough woman with an invisible robe has stolen 18 babies for her powerful master, two other tough women and the cops try to stop her.
A maniac cut and burn the body of the victims without a real reason. Annie (Frances Williams) the sister of one of the girls killed, wanna know more about this mistery and for her starts a nightmare.

Bill and Jo Harding, advanced storm chasers on the brink of divorce, must join together to create an advanced weather alert system by putting themselves in the cross-hairs of extremely violent tornadoes.
See the longest, the most exciting, the most gripping, the most violent bare-knuckles VIOLENT scene ever to hit you between the eyes. Screentime: 10 minutes.
Ajay Mehra, an amateur boxer, takes revenge against Balwant Rai, a crooked businessman, after his elder brother is killed.
Sex, drums, tequila, social networking, a pirate, morning after pills, Jesus and a gun. It's one hot mess!

movie_name: Confessions of a Teenage Jesus Jerk
description: A teenage boy coming of age during the Reagan years discovers that he really enjoys many pleasurable things that are frowned upon by his family and their religion.
A New York press agent applies his show-business acumen to revitalize his ailing father's Indiana fruit farm.
A pharmaceutical company recruits a well-known scientist to help develop a vaccine against a deadly virus.

Themed around a BDSM relationship, exploring light and dark, stillness and motion, freedom and constraint, this is a beautiful short essay in yin and yang, with a brilliant sound track and compelling visual composition.
What is meant to be a weekend party across the border soon becomes a heartbreaking journey that tests the boundaries of companionship, romantic love and personal ethics.
Tells a story about a group of special police unit force lead by Roslan, who has been trying to bring down a robbery gang lead by a guy named Asyraff.

A terrible battle ensues when gRinde's forces launch an unexpected attack on Aksdal's outpost of G2. Amid the chaos, the knight Sleivscudd discovers that his long lost arch enemy Svein Harry Berge is behind the attack.
The story of the youths of a small village who are struggling to break the bonds of medieval exploitation and feudal serfdom.
Raghu (Suyog Gorhe), a film student, must prove himself as a successful filmmaker before Bhargavi's (Mitali Mayekar) family allows the couple to tie the knot. Does he succeed?

movie_name: If You Want to Live... Shoot!
description: A young cowboy, Johnny, playing in a rigged poker game is forced to shoot one of the other players. The cowboy takes quick leave as he is accused of murder and a reward for his capture is posted.
István Pongrácz, the Lord of Nemec dislikes living in his age, so he lives his life like a medieval nobleman.
Separated by the ravages of the civil war, a young woman sets out in search of her missing husband, crossing battle lines and breaking stereotypes in the process.
A dark, gritty drama that wraps around Louie Lazaro. a drug addict and a male dancer. As he tries to escape the evils of his past.
Lakshya a police constable gets some extra ordinary powers in his body after he is saved from a blast. But all his powers fail when he sees the red colour.

Andreas has everything a man can wish for. A wonderfull wife, a big house on the country and a great job. But a sudden car accident puts him in a wheelchair. He is paralysed in his legs and he is also now impotent. Will his marriage work?
Jay, a bodyguard, races against time to save his boss, businessman Dato' Hashim and his daughter Nadi, against a hostile hostage situation.

A sadist lures fledgeling actress to his den of horrors, promising them fame if they act in his "snuff film." They realize only after they are tied up that he really means to torture, rape, and kill them for all to see.
An author who spends a weekend locked in a haunted lighthouse as a publicity stunt for his next book becomes a target for powerful supernatural forces.
An off the wall horror anthology of a detective on a hunt for a sadistic and crazed killer who targets web based formats. In a cat and mouse chase of horror that'll get under your skin

The story unfolds in an underclass neighborhood of Mexico City, a place where a unique troupe features a circus act, led by Don Ramón (López Moctezuma himself.) He and his wife Petra (...                See full synopsis »
Max, a prize boxer who has developed a drinking habit after his girlfriend Susan left him, gets involved in dirty business once she asks him to help her find her missing husband.
A hardboiled PI tries to find the truth about a Jade in a dark and shadowy world balancing various dark forces in this unusual Chinese film noir.
Marion Fish makes a documentary following her attempt to find her best friends killer. Little does she know that she is actually the subject of the killers own filmmaking ambitions.

A group of friends gather for April's birthday party/game night. However, the game takes an unexpected turn when somebody mysteriously dies. Now the group must play to the end and hope their game strategy keeps them alive.
A single mom takes her family to Georgia for the funeral of her father--a man she never met--and she and her clan meet the crass, fun-loving Brown family.

The trilogy picks right up where True 2 left us. Gena's awakes to find that her mysterious savior is Quadir. Before happily ever after, Gena has 72 hours to go back to Philly to check on Bria and Gah Git and let them know of her plans.
A group of outcasts, including a vagabond and a prostitute, gather at the outskirts of the industrial area of a large Czech city, one of the things that helps some of them survive is alcohol.
After tragedy strikes, a grieving father discovers an ancient burial ground behind his home with the power to raise the dead.

Jim Mills is offered a job working as a courier for a US senator escorting an ancient Chinese artifact from Los Angeles to Shanghai as a gift to the Senator's generous benefactor. Things are not as they appear.

Unemployed engineer Jaggi opens a small business on the advice of his friend, but winds up in trouble when he falls for the daughter of a millionaire and tells her that he owns a chain of restaurants.
A man is tormented by nightmarish visions after enduring head trauma while camping in the Catskill woods.

Jaunii a teenage who's a film tech at his college with three of his friends that must have a film documentary project done on an abandon house, they thought was abandon but finds out a psychic killer who has a dark side.

Whisked away from the paparazzi and her high-profile life to for some relaxing time in beautiful Puerto Rico, Natalie falls madly in love in a local all the while her scheming half-brother is trying to take control of the family fortune.

A man who lost an arm and his family to a tribe of cannibals returns ten years later to bring back his teenager daughter, only to find that she grew up into a beautiful blonde woman who became the cannibals' queen.
A take on Clive Barker's 1987 horror classic where a young woman struggling with addiction comes into possession of an ancient puzzle box, unaware that its purpose is to summon the Cenobites.

movie_name: I Was, I Am, I Will Be
description: A touching love story that challenges stereotypes about the courage it takes to face the stranger, to take risks and to accept challenges.
When Scott Carey begins to shrink because of exposure to a combination of radiation and insecticide, medical science is powerless to help him.
After the apocalypse, a grieving recluse is visited by a desperate woman who draws him out of his home, and forces him to confront his inner turmoil.
This is the story of Two Mormon Missionaries on a mission to spread the word of Jesus Christ of Latter Day Saints in a zombie infested apocalypse.

Gloria is being driven around Southern Italy when the car breaks down. Her driver Claudio pleads with her to wait at the beach, while he gets the car repaired. Now truly alone, Gloria's grief is transformed by the blue Ionian Sea.
Lucy has severe sleep disorders, involving sleep paralysis demons, and is institutionalized after the death of a loved one. Only to discover the demons may be realer than Lucy thinks.
When Edward, a buffoonish Spirit Hunter, repeatedly fails to banish a bathroom spirit, he inadvertently uncovers a disheartening truth.

A haunting tale of family life. A vulnerable young boy finds his mother pushed out of the family home by a strange new woman, and he must confront the terrifying supernatural forces that seem to move in with her.
The film continues the story of teenage Billy Batson who, upon reciting the magic word "SHAZAM!" is transformed into his adult Super Hero alter ego, Shazam.

In 1941, a 16-year-old aspiring artist and her family are deported to Siberia amidst Stalin's brutal dismantling of the Baltic region. One girl's passion for art and her never-ending hope will break the silence of history.
A musical comedy about Kalle Svensson, a sergeant in the navy, and his loved one Nanette Raquette who works as a gymnastics teacher.
Thomas, the son of a prison warden, falls for and seduces inmate Martin. When Martin is released from jail, they try to build a relationship and a life together but no one will let them alone.

The streets are lined with cash and the only way to get it from the gangsters is to steal without hesitation and gun for your life like there's no tomorrow -- and when the bullets finish blazing, only the illest will be left standing.
A disillusioned head of a mob falls in love with his yoga instructor. When she is kidnapped, he has to embark on journey from Istanbul to Mumbai to save her.
A timeless story of a boy's adventures growing up in a small Southern town, Yazoo City in the 1940s during World War II, roaming with his friends, playing practical jokes, and getting into trouble.
Prior to his marriage, a young man asks for the property of his fiancee's father, a millionaire, to be written in his name.
The big-screen adaptation of Perry's stage play about the trials of marriage and what happens to one family when a sexy young temptress arrives on the scene.
A crimefighting organization called the Angels goes up against a drug-smuggling ring headed by a female kung-fu killer.

A man implicated in the triple homicide of three Hollywood starlets begins his own investigation. Needing assistance, he enlists the two detectives on his tail in order to expose a conspiracy more explosive than any of them imagined.
Is an 1981 Indonesia superhero movie directed by Lilik Sudijo. This film played by Teddy Purba, Ami Prijono and W.D. Mochtar. This is the first superhero film in Indonesia that adapted by comic book
Bill takes Trina into his depression camp cabin. Later, just as he finds showgirl LaRue who will support him, Trina becomes pregnant.
A film director meets with an accident and his life takes a major turn. What happened before and after the accident and what he is seeing which no one can see.
Based on an incredible true story of the Battle of Saragarhi in which an army of 21 Sikhs fought against 10,000 Afghans in 1897.
The romp revolves around a dinner party hosted by the young and vicacious Nayla to introduce Fares, the love of her life, to Silvio, her new fiancé.

A young man finds himself in the middle of a universal battle between good and evil when he sets up residence in a trans-dimensional valley. Only his father's mysterious crystal pendant and its lost matching scepter can guarantee victory.
After moving into opposing condo communities, two couples consisting of retired special op veterans band together to take down a psychological experiment orchestrated by a power-hungry HOA President.
Follows Jane Austen as she strikes a Faustian bargain to find love, and ends up time traveling from 1803 to the present day.

movie_name: Chicken Strips: The Trials and Tribulations of Becoming a Garage Band
description: When childhood best friends, Kyle, Steven, and Ruben are forced to perform in a music festival, conflicting priorities and visitors from the boys' past push their friendship to the breaking point.

A middle-aged woman, a single mother to a teenage son, suffers from an unknown disease. On an ordinary train ride she meets a man, who offers to change her life. Her teenage son does not approve of the changes.
A ruthless German spy, trying to get out of Britain with vital information about D-Day, must spend time with a young woman and her crippled husband.

The descendant of the servant of a cruel and vicious samurai returns to the town where she was born, only to find that a cat who is possessed by the spirits of those murdered by the samurai is trying to kill her.

The world's last superhero, Thomas Harm, lays dying on his deathbed. Thomas Harm is not your regular superhero, everyone knows his true identity, he lives a very opulent life and has taken ...                See full synopsis »
A preacher whose ancestors were cursed by Druids battles Satan, who has taken the form of a huge snake.
The Struggles of Rhoma Irama with his family before be a famous singer . And start with the kidnappings his wife and childrens

Daigo doesn't go to school anymore. His sister, Kiriko, is worried and their father is no help. Now Daigo is missing. He's in danger, and Kiriko will have to follow him into a world of nightmares to discover the truth.
Staked to the ground naked in the scorching desert of Mexico, lies a nameless young man left for dead.
A struggling couple visit a marriage counselor for the holiday as a last resort. Soon after they realize he has sinister intentions that may make this thanksgiving their last.
A woman gives birth to a twin girls but they steal one of them. When grow up the twin sisters must meet each other once again and fate bring them together.
Jeong-woo tries to be a good wife and mother but, after witnessing her husband's adultery, her anger drives her into the arms of another man.

Sisters Olanna and Kainene return home to 1960s Nigeria, where they soon diverge on different paths. As civil war breaks out, political events loom larger than their differences as they join the fight to establish an independent republic.

After serving for the war, Mak invites three soldiers whom he befriended, to his home. Upon arrival they witness the village terrified of a ghost. The three friends hear rumors that the ghost is Mak's wife. Based on Thai folklore.
The daughter of a wealthy man takes French lessons so she can go to France with her fiancée, but ends up falling for a poor man who studies civil engineering.
Two American soldiers in Viet Nam , with differing opinions , are tasked with escorting a singer and her manager back to friendly territory after their unit is engaged by enemy forces.
Korean investigator, Park Ho, and plucky Japanese reporter, Hineko, expose themselves to danger when they uncover a gang of North Koreans responsible for many recent murders in Tokyo.
Osman is the head of the family after his father's death. Coming back from work he is killed. Zehra his sister is determined to find his murderer and revenge Osman.
A Polish woman living with her wheelchair bound paralysed husband falls in love with a Russian man. The trios actions affect each other deeply, leaving them to deal with profound consequences.
A well-known gangster is released from prison, and decides look for his daughter with the help of a troubled young woman.

Boy loses girl, boy meets girl, ex interferes, boy drowns his sorrows in comic books, booze and pot - but, with the help of his friends and a couple of German dominatrix, everything works out in the end.
Napoleon's tumultuous relations with Russia, including his disastrous 1812 invasion, serve as the backdrop for the tangled personal lives of two aristocratic families.
A man and woman who are complete opposites of each other fall in love with each other and face obstacles to be with each other.
An enigmatic faith healer - who appears to possess genuine magical powers - and a political fixer vie for influence over a senator and his family.

After an abrupt break up from her girlfriend, Angela finds herself bullied to the point of wanting to take her own life. However, before she can follow through with it she is abducted by a serial killer.
Alcatraz. 1937. A young prison guard working the night shift experiences a string of chilling disturbances culminating in the bizarre death of an inmate at the most famous prison in the world

What is a ghost? Does it have a shape or size? or a gender? or is it an evil force? there are no perfect answers for such queries. There are stories saying that few people have seen a ghost. But there are no apparent evidences..
A group of thieves are stranded in a semi-trailer after the only member capable of driving the getaway truck dies during the heist.

An influential entrepreneur develops an irrational OCD, making him the ideal puppet for a lobbying organization. He must break free before the nation's children, including his own, are irreversibly modified by the mob he's helping create.

A descendant of Blackbeard living on the Outer Banks becomes possessed by a family heirloom. He turns into a murderer and stalks a local bartender. Authorities are searching for the mysterious killer.
A married man fell in love and had an affair with a woman. He then needs to choose between his family and his kept woman.

After quitting his job of thirty years a conservative Christian radio personality discovers his new fiancee is a porn star. He soon learns that the girl of his dreams could be much more than he had bargained for.

A fortune teller tells a store clerk with a romantic disposition that she was a Spanish noblewoman in an earlier life. The girl begins to live the part of the Spanish noblewoman and romance and comedy ensue.
The story follows the lives of four unemployed engineers who turn criminals to avenge an anonymous, yet dangerous cybercriminal.

Fernando llega al pueblo donde vive Amalia y ambos se enamoran. Fernando tiene que regresar a la ciudad para terminar su compromiso y así poder estar con Amalia, pero estas cosas jamas suceden como uno espera
An eccentric Texas lawman's desperate pursuit of a pair of psychotic killers takes him across the Mexican border and into a bizarre and horrific world that will challenge his every skill to survive.
This is a shortened version of the 1949 Republic serial "Ghost of Zorro," and was released to television as part of a syndicated package in 1959.
A rich businessman and a young woman are attracted to each other, but he only wants an affair while she wants to save herself for marriage.
Professional assassin Chev Chelios learns his rival has injected him with a poison that will kill him if his heart rate drops.
A story of Vienna following World War I, in which the butchers became millionaires and the aristocrats became beggars, told against a background of mother-love and sacrifice.
A professional thief turns state's evidence on his Mafia boss and enters into the witness protection program.
A Murdered Hillbilly returns from the dead to seek revenge on the town that put him to death in 1958. The small Town of Dackson is about to learn that the legend of 'Hellbilly', is true.
"Music" never gets old and so does "Love". The story is telling that music and love are the most fundamental companions regardless of the time.

Perpetually single Sawyer makes a fake wedding registry to burn off some Christmas loneliness. Her friends find it and think she's become secretly engaged. Too embarrassed to tell the truth, she instead finds a "fiancé" for the holidays.
A manga artist becomes suspicious of his employers when a garbled message is discovered on tape. As he forms a team to investigate, Godzilla and Anguirus set out to help defeat the invaders.
Julien Saint Dominique, an agent of the French counter-espionage service in Berlin, investigates the kidnapping of a functionary taken by German communists into East Germany.
When a small town near the Arizona-Mexico border is wiped out overnight, suspicion falls on the lone survivor. But a roll of photos the survivor took that night tells a different story.
An ex-MI6 agent is thrown back into the world of espionage and high stakes to uncover the shocking truth about operations conducted by unknown secret services.

movie_name: Re-Live: A Tale of an American Island Cheerleader
description: Rowena, a transgender movie star returns home for her high school reunion. Rowena's plan to live her childhood dream of being a cheerleader falters when her mother's cancer begins to worsen. She learns to value the family she left behind.
A luminous coming-of-age novel about a young female scientist who must recalibrate her life when her academic career goes off track.
The story of love of Leily with Majnoon which has lots of suffering and pains and ends with their death on a sand storm.
The story of Manfred von Richthofen, the German air ace during World War I and his struggle with the enemy aces and some jealous German officers.
Espionage thriller set during World War II that tells of one man's war on a squad of thirteen soldiers.
During the Mexican Revolution, a macho rebel general falls in love with the independent-minded daughter of an aristocrat in the town he is occupying.
1985-set socially-relevant horror pitting a junkie against an evil creature manifested from the fear and loathing which resulted during the AIDS crisis.

After a serious accident where "Pacey" loses his family, he begins to see visions with the message "it's coming". Struggling to understand this distressing message, he experiences the darkest state of his reality.
An American naval officer is recruited for an operation to eliminate his lookalike, the infamous terrorist Carlos The Jackal.
An outlaw who was raised by Native Americans discovers that he has five half-brothers. Together the men go on a mission to find their wayward, deadbeat dad.

Manuel Venegas regresa a su pueblo para conquistar al amor de su vida, Soledad. Pero para su sorpresa la encuentra casada con otro hombre. Sin importarles nada, ni las diferencias socials, ambos están dispuestos a luchar por su amor.
A vampire who works as a taxi driver meets and romances a young woman whom he turns into a fellow vamp, which prompts her jealous and estranged husband to try to kill both of them.
Interweaving love stories centering on real individuals who are utilizing medicine to explore new frontiers of love, sex, and the human form.

Lookalike brother's Govardhan&Harshvardhan exchange their names in childhood and decide to live each others life forever without the knowledge of their parents but what will happen when their strict father will come to know about this.
If a year spent driving a town car in Las Vegas has taught Cameron anything, it's that everybody is looking for an outlet, even himself.
In this melodrama, a poverty-stricken woman raises her sons through many trials and tribulations. But no matter the struggles, she always sticks to her own moral code.

After decades of being in a marriage of convenience, Harriet meets a man she never believed existed. Romantic, attentive, caring, and charismatic. Will she follow her heart to love, or live in misery the rest of her life?
Three characters that will be linked in a strange triangle of mutual deception, different points of view and attitudes. A look at the relations marked by social and cultural differences.
The children from two rival families fall in love and try to convince their elders to give up the feud
A detective teams up with an amnesiac lady who can talk with the dead to solve a mass murder mystery.

An online channel reporter, finds a fake Facebook account of her niece. She encounters a boy Aalim from Libya. The FBI on the other hand wants to bring Aalim under their custody using Thaiyal Nayagi and her niece as bait.
When Realtor Sandra visits a foreclosed property with her client, the former owner Danny attacks them.
The Hindu god Hanuman teams up with Ultraman and his brethren against familiar Ultra-foes in this rare Ultraman movie co-produced in Thailand.
When guests are stranded in a remote hotel during a windstorm, they find themselves at the mercy of an unknown killer determined to murder every last soul.

Concerned with his pregnant wife Saling (Divina Valencia), rebel leader Ka Leon (Dante Varona) decides to take advantage of the government's amnesty program to rejoin society. But Ka Leon's past catches up with him.
Trigger happy cop Inspector Shiva finds his life in danger when he tries to rid the village of Bhavanipur from the tyranny of two evil brothers.

Besa, a young Kosovar girl, discovers she has a gift to communicate with dead solders from her war torn homeland. She falls in love with a dead war Soldier and the relationship starts to take a turn for the worst.
This dystopia takes place in the near future. The death penalty has been abolished throughout the world. The prisons are overcrowded. International organizations decide to conduct an experiment.

An American scientist prevents an assassination attempt on an oil sheik, who opens the gates of his harem to his saviour. There, nude girls invite him to explore their bodies. But has anyone escaped from the street of a thousand pleasures?
Nora, after a succession of terrible boyfriends, finds true love with the most unexpected of suitors: a 500-pound American Black Bear.
A group of high school seniors become targets of a masked psychopath in this chilling tribute to the beloved slasher flicks of the 90's.
A mayor's daughter poses as collaborator to help British agent escape to England with vital information to help the allied war effort.
A musician returns to his childhood home only to find that it is haunted by the ghost of a child. A remake of the 1980 horror film.
An unstable woman is forced back to her haunted house where she will relive her most troubling nightmares.
At the end of the Cold War, a former guerrilla fighter and an ex-Stasi agent face off in a race to recover stolen Nazi treasure and a sense of their former glory.
A demonic army commander captures the king and takes the kingdom under his control. So, a young man decides to fight against him to save the king and the kingdom.

A paranormal investigator gets a call about a place being haunted by some demonic forces in the deep of the woods. But as things started getting unfurled, he realizes that he wasn't the one who was there to investigate, HE was the TARGET.
The telegram that Jim Comway receives states that the woman he was to marry, Laura, could not move to a country she didn't know, and marry a man she felt she no longer knew
The plot is being kept under wraps. It is rumored to follow a treasure hunt through the heart of Hollywood.
Plagued by reoccurring nightmares after having turned ten years old, the young men and women from four separate families seek to uncover the truth of their connectedness.
The border guards face spies parachuted into Romania to recover and take abroad the secret documents of a forestry plant.
A man is on vacation and meets a married woman. She falls in love with him intensely while her husband begins to have suspicions.
When Darius Atkinson learns about his new found ability, he will stop at nothing to solve his fathers murder.
Three boys who work at a pizza store are thrown into three different stories when one boy had to cover for another boy and make a delivery.

The two-hour scripted feature THE CANNIBAL IN THE JUNGLE follows the story of an American scientist who was convicted of killing and cannibalizing two colleagues in the jungles of Flores, Indonesia in 1977.

movie_name: Adventure at the Center of the Earth
description: Mexican horror film with a variety of classic monsters, bat-like creatures, a rat-faced monster, dinosaurs and a cyclops.

Song Ha, a young Vietnamese woman arrives in Budapest with a distinctive goal: she wants to discover her roots. While she investigates the past, a romantic relationship blossoms between her and Viktor, a Hungarian man.
For their ghost hunting reality show, a production crew locks themselves inside an abandoned mental hospital that's supposedly haunted - and it might prove to be all too true.

Four years ago, Jess and her friends lived a nightmare that has left her almost killed by the unstoppable killer 'Thorn'. Four years later, Jessica and the survivors make an attempt to stop him once and for all.
Special Ops soldiers in Afghanistan unearth one of the U.S. government's secrets: the deployment and loss of the first female special Ops sniper eight years ago.

Beginning growing parting longing reuniting breaking and ending of the nostalgic forbidden love between a humble backwoodsman and a naive family girl is told through their secret letters and most private memories in narrative format.
With misfortune and disgrace in their separate pasts, Abel and Mary meet and start a new life together, proving that life really is what we make of it.
A small-town sheriff, haunted by a childhood encounter with the "Black Eyed Kids", comes face to face with the evil once again.

An egoistic and overprotective father, tests his soon-to-be son in law whether he is suitable for his daughter or not. Mayhem ensues after he learns that his future son in law is not that what he imagined.

movie_name: Li xian ji li xian ji
description: Lee acquires a video game disc, legend says that the game is a door of time travel and a player has to beat the game to open that door. Determined to save his girl, Lee begins his amazing adventure.
A retired policeman returns to his job to fight a crime wave that was once responsible for leaving his son without a mother.
College-bound Andy blurts marriage proposals to his sweetheart Polly and her pert swimmer friend Sheila.
A group of young unknown actors arrive in Hollywood with dreams of fame and fortune. When they are cast in a horror film they become the unsuspecting participants in a snuff film - theirs.
An anthology of three Edgar Allan Poe stories: "The Case of Mr. Valdemar," "The Cask of Amontillado" and "The Tell-Tale Heart."
Two boys grow up being influenced by each other's respective fathers. While one becomes a singer, the other becomes a local goon. Incidentally, both love the same girl in college.

A slave-turned-gladiator finds himself in a race against time to save his true love, who has been betrothed to a corrupt Roman Senator. As Mount Vesuvius erupts, he must fight to save his beloved as Pompeii crumbles around him.

A filmmaker attempts to create a cutting edge 'freedom of speech' documentary with every star name and dollar he can enlist. However, he inadvertently unleashes holy hell from a 500-pound comedian on the verge of a nervous breakdown.
In order to help a friend, Ganesh pretends to love a girl. She hates him when she finds out the truth. Eventually, he truly falls in love with her and must convince her of his true feelings.
Rajesh Sharma, working with the Indian Government on a top secret research project, has to deal with enemy agents, explosions, murder and last but not least a dangerous look-alike.

movie_name: New Initial D the Movie: Legend 3 - Dream
description: Mt. Akina's new downhill racing hero Fujiwara Takumi prepares for the final showdown against Red Sun's unbeaten leader and Akagi's fastest driver, Takahashi Ryosuke.

Josh's girlfriend wants to get married. Molly's boyfriend is married. Josh and Molly fly to the wedding in Chicago together and pretend to be engaged to make their parents happy. Comedy follows...does romance?
A hitman on the run from the police hides out in an apartment building in New Orleans, only to find out that the other tenants are evil personified.

After taking charge as the DSP of Singham Khurd, Dilsher Sikhon sets out to end the drug addiction among the youth of Punjab. This sets him against Bhuller, a vicious business tycoon with connections in high places.
A young potter's life devolves into chaos as he loses function of his body while being haunted by the physical manifestation of his childhood trauma.
RUSH is a comedy about six college freshman rushing fraternities and sororities, only to have their relationships change forever.
An expectant couple's intimate weekend turns to terror as they discover their secluded country inn is a haunted maternity home where infants and mothers were murdered.
Knowing he's about to move across the country a young stand up comic starts a new relationship with the understanding that it ends when he moves.
An unemployed school-teacher experiences life-changing problems when he speaks out against his dishonest brother-in-law.

Local interviews recall bizarre sightings in South Jersey during the 1970s and more reported decades later, including a gruesome tale from a group of friends deer hunting near the Menantico Ponds in December of 1995.
Four friends get together for a weekend getaway, exploring the woods. Only to find out they're not alone.
Heartbroken is the story of love between two youngsters who have two different perspectives and are from two different families.
A spoiled heiress who has jilted multiple fiancés embroils a commercial pilot in a series of wacky misadventures.
A New York district attorney works and flirts with his adversary and her kooky artist client, who is on trial for a murder she didn't commit.
Miami detectives Mike Lowrey and Marcus Burnett must face off against a mother-and-son pair of drug lords who wreak vengeful havoc on their city.
Love creates a new drug called Speed which was used by Hitler during WW2 to transform humans into superhumans. Agillan lost his wife and quits his job as RAW Agent.
A young hustler takes advantage of the love of a gay man, and pays consequences for it in the form of a demonic possession.
Thaddeus Hyatt is a chef who has mad cow. He kidnaps foreigners, kills them, injects his own blood into them, then feeds their meat to unexpecting folks in his restaurants.
The sequel to the cult classic Horrortales.666 . This promise to have the feel of the original. A lot of people from the original are involved.
Jo Doo-soo, a member of a gang, comes across and helps Joanna, a college student who is about to have her handbag robbed by the bullies on her way home.
After the kidnap of her little brother, Lacey, a rebellious yet cunning teenager, must use the skills her dead secret service agent father taught her to get him back.

Street dancer Pablo Garcia works hard in making his strict father Carlos Garcia proud by studying to become a doctor, however Pablo's life turns upside down when he meets Victoria,a professional ballroom dancer.
Seven friends travel to the countryside to play war in the woods. They stumble upon three paranoid and sadistic ex-soldiers.
Gérard, CEO of the factory "La voix du peuple", decides to close his factory by dismissing all his staff, starting with Jean Barbier, the chief of staff, and Phil Dechambre.
After his parents' deaths in a car accident, orphan Simon goes to live with relative Maria Bayona in the Spanish countryside. He soon begins to suspect that Maria is practicing black magic.
A tough ex-marine joins a smuggler shipping arms to Chinese bandits. When his old outfit takes on the outlaws,he has a change of heart.
Amidst the hot Italian summer of Rome, two unlikely people, a young American college graduate and a forty-something Italian writer, discover forbidden love, lust, and connection in the Eternal City.
An actress and her entourage spend a weekend on an island in the Atlantic. First her child is abducted, then a killer starts to eliminate the rest of the group one by one.

In the great tradition of Hsu Tseng Hung's The Silver Fox and Chang Cheh's Lengend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between all the clan leaders and certain death is one young woman.
Ten characters. Ten stories. Ten monologues. A chain of situations that reflect the constant flow of life. The poetry of the common actions with one issue in common: fair of freedom.
A bride's divorced parents find their old feelings for each other during the wedding reception and over the course of the next few days upsetting the newlywed's honeymoon.
Jeri is recently engaged, Bob recently dumped. When Jeri starts working with Bob, they hit it off. As they struggle to understand their friendship, Jeri's MMA fighter fiancé suspects something.
Four gay French expatriots share a business in Barcelona. When they and their parents are thrown together for a "coming out" party, another French Farce ensues.
Nick and his girlfriend must spend a night in their newly inherited abandoned building downtown, to disprove the stories of it being haunted to an interested buyer.
A small group of correctional officers and inmates must band together to fend off a mysterious attack when their prison bus is sabotaged on a remote stretch of highway.
The paths of a desperate man and an imprisoned young woman cross unexpectedly in the den of a mysterious killer.
Story of a boy named Behram who followed his dreams despite his father's disapproval but he wasn't prepared for what was about to come next.
A couple meet in South Korea. They have fun together, but when they fall in love, everything changes.

Akash, a medical student from a rich family, is also a well-respected poet and singer commonly known as Nishant. When he meets Shikha, an orphan and dancer, their relationship soon turns romantic, much to the disapproval of his parents.
A woman is boxed out by the male sports agents in her profession, but gains an unexpected edge over them when she develops the ability to hear men's thoughts.
Scientists use a brain-altering drug to conduct experiments, after one such project goes astray, they need to find another test subject in this Japanese splatter-punk film.

Dani is torn: he loves music but is afraid to fail. One summer, between his job as a waiter and night out with friends, he meets Sandra. With her, he discovers love and what it means to be one among many.
Carol Corliss, a beautiful movie star so insecure about her celebrity that she goes around in disguise, meets a rugged outdoorsman who is unaffected by her star status.
Tomie terrorizes an artistically inclined young girl and her widowed father, slowly integrating herself into the family.

The Moorish general Othello is manipulated into thinking that his new wife Desdemona has been carrying on an affair with his lieutenant Michael Cassio when in reality it is all part of the scheme of a bitter ensign named Iago.
The events of a couple trying to find a world within their relationship to deal with the death of their child.
A federal agent investigates when inconsistencies turn up in the photographic evidence of several murders recorded by mobile robotic cameras.
A young Housewife struggling to find joy in her life , joins a new job. Boss of the company makes her a offer she never thought of?
A film version of Genet's play. Two house cleaners, Solange and Claire, hate their employers and, while they are out, take turns at dressing up as Madame and insulting her.
Mike Gardner a small time fight promoter plans the biggest event of his life. An MMA underground tournament with eight fighters and only one all out winner competing for £250,000.
Suspecting that people around him are turning into evil creatures, a troubled man questions whether to protect his only friend from an impending war, or from himself.
When private detective Marco Santis is called to look for a missing reporter, he finds out that his estranged step son is missing too.
A retired cop is summoned by his ex-boss to save his kidnapped son from the hands of a deadly Japanese triad.
A detective has 48 hours to figure out which identical twin robbed a Manhattan bank and planned the perfect crime or both brothers go free.
A soon-to-be-married man encounters an exciting stranger after his plane suffers an accident on takeoff.
The Gang is back well, at least the Mob is. Follow Alex "Candyman" Sims as he tries to navigate the Chicago Mob and escape with his life.

When a madman calling himself "the Scorpio Killer" menaces the city, tough-as-nails San Francisco Police Inspector "Dirty" Harry Callahan is assigned to track down and ferret out the crazed psychopath.
Two worlds collide when a Triad leader and a taxi driver form an unlikely partnership. Now, they need to work together in order to survive.
A young film student wants his prized jeep fixed, so he turns to a television paranormal hunting team to get a paycheck and the scare of his life.

movie_name: À l'heure où les grands fauves vont boire
description: Torn from a dream while trying to seduce the woman he wants, Adrien decides to make it come true. To do this, he will call on Yoska, a Slavic intellectual recycled into moonlighting.

In the 80s, Turkey is in the middle of a politically turbulent period. Yusuf, who lives with a disability, doesn't get involved in politics, and prefers to work to support his mum. After the revolution, nothing will be the same for him.

What if your friends were lying traitors who want to make your life a living hell? When Marissa discovers this brutal reality on her 18th birthday she decides to take action, longing for justice and revenge. And she is not the only one .
Jackson Durai is a horror comedy about an undercover cop who goes for investigation to a village that has been haunted for more than a century.
Based on the novel by Len Kloosman, "Colour" is a sequel to "Task Force Retriever: Out of Angola" and features recurring hero Tony Harrington.

An American woman reeling from the untimely death of her adopted child inherits a castle in Romania. As she and her husband search for a new beginning, they must confront the truth of her family curse.

A college student struggling to find his purpose in life accompanies his physics professor to find a long forgotten ancient mysterious relic only to find themselves entangled in a worldwide conspiracy web that involves the Russian mob.
Billy (Robin Padilla) is already contented to be a drummer in a band but the course of his life will change when he went to a place and is known by a different identity as Carlos.
Two widowed sisters thwart a love match when they try to arrange marriages for their respective children.

Rudy Ray Moore's fourth in a series of cult favorites finds him playing an ex-cop called back into action to stop an angel dust producer. The angel dust hallucinations alone are well worth the price of admission!
In a post-apocalyptic plague-ridden world, a man and woman face unimaginable horrors when he suddenly becomes infected, and the only possible cure slowly drives him mad.

movie_name: What's the Time in Your World?
description: A woman comes back from Paris to her country after a long time. She meets a man that she hardly knows, but he knows a lot about her life.

Keiko, the daughter of a legendary sushi chef, runs away from home when his Karate-style regimen becomes too severe. Finding work at a rural hot springs inn, she is ridiculed by the eccentric staff and guests.

After a sorority girl breaks up with him, the headmaster of a college takes his own life. But what should be the end, becomes only the beginning when a magical evil 12" clown doll gets possessed by the soul of Mr. Whitman.
A man, along with his best friend and wife, must fight off a hoard of zombies who are attacking their farm, eventually realizing that there is something very peculiar about them.
While returning to Carpenter Falls, The Lawson family come to their final confrontation with The Wicked One, a serial killer with whom their last encounter has haunted them for a decade.

Living her life through the lens of grunge music, Scarlett, now officially a high school graduate finds herself lost in the crowd. When Scarlett meets Katie, she realizes she has no idea who she really is.
Kingship knows no Kinship and there can be only one Emperor in Aurangzeb's world. In Gurgaon, to bring down a criminal the law has to think like one.
A night of violence and carnage erupts after Russian assassin Mania Morozov executes the son of one of the city's most powerful crime families.

A woman supports a young student who was a pupil of her late husband. She soon falls in love with him and sacrifices everything for his success and happiness, knowing that it is impossible for him to love her in return.
The desperate lives of two estranged twin brothers converge over missing drugs, politics, racial prejudice, corrupt cops and an unplanned pregnancy.
A Manny Velazquez underground slasher tribute about a number of serial killers on the loose in Chicago and begins a murder spree.
Inspired by the real story of the conflict between the student from four different technician colleges in the 90s, where violence can be used to build friendships and enemies at the same time.

In a highly secured prison, 10 prisoners are found dead mysteriously. Erol and Selin are tasked with investigating the murders. The cause of death is the same for all: heart attack. But the truth is utterly different from that.

Promises of happier times dawn for the financially distressed Patterson family when father Sweeney and brother-in-law Archibald "Doc" Finney win a $150,000 grand prize in the sweepstakes ...                See full synopsis »

Action superstar Brandon Lee portrays rebellious government agent Michael Gold who is sent on a desperate mission to a Soviet-controlled African nation in order to uncover a top-secret laser weapons operation and destroy it.
An archeologist discovers his daughter is possessed by the spirit of an Egyptian queen. To save mankind he must destroy her.
A young man slowly loses himself more and more into a dream world and his own nightmares. But what if the dreams are real?
The story involves two elite combat warriors from China and India who lead covert forces to shut down a global, wildlife poaching, criminal organization.
A wall creates perturbation between two factions of a political party. Kaali and his buddy Anbu, who is a political aspirant, get embroiled in this brutal political rivalry.
A married couple, renewing their vows in a desert town, get entangled in a psychopath's deadly game of love and vengeance

Cal (John Lynch), a young man on the fringes of the I. R. A., falls in love with Marcella (Dame Helen Mirren), a Catholic woman whose husband, a Protestant policeman, was killed one year earlier by the I. R. A.
The story of a young girl, a crusader who takes up a challenging job selling condoms in a small town in MP, India.

movie_name: The Hunt of the Son of Beast
description: Andrew, David and his friends are taking a vacation to Kings Island when something strange and mysterious is happening and it's returning.

After being blinded by a group of tormentors, a teenage ballerina works with a local dancer to perform a duet for a hip-hop competition, but as the relationship between them unfolds, she discovers the true cause of how she lost her sight.
Sandra sees a ghost and begins to investigate her appearances, it is about a missing woman and a femicide.
A dead fetus lives on after death inside a woman's body, existing as a Womb Ghost. Unnatural termination of such life will turn the baby into the evilest and most vicious kind of spirit.
The love story of a DACA who was forced to return to Cuba and his journey of loss and discovery that proves that there is always hope through music and the attraction of love
Follows three men who are in love with a most beautiful waitress: An intellectual restaurant owner, a mysterious musician and an erratic businessman; taking place during the WWII.

movie_name: Jilbab Traveler: Love Sparks in Korea
description: Rania Samudra (Bunga Citra Lestari) is a travel writer and nicknamed Jilbab Traveler by the readers. When her father was sick, Rania decided to go home. But her father does not want her to worry and keep asking to continue her journey.
A mad scientist fills his basement dungeon with victims in an insane attempt to restore his daughter's eyesight.

Theo and Vincent are architects involved in change of environmental identities replacing 320 wooden houses by 32 concrete towers. 10 years later, in 1993, they meet. Discussing the conflict over the projects and ethics of architecture.
Amy is a single mom who suddenly finds herself lost while try to escape a nightmare that ends up being a frightening reality.
Four British villains raid a settlement to obtain explosives for use in a diamond mine. In doing so they nearly destroy the settlement, so and Tarzan pursues them to their mine.

When Carlitos is released after 2 years of "hard time", he attempts to redeem himself for the sake of his 5 year-old son. But when he's talked into "one last job," he gets embroiled in a situation far beyond anything he'd bargained for.
George Anton as Fyodor Dostoevsky validates his existence and protests the rambling memoirs of a bitter and isolated, Hollywood Filmmaker to stop the pain in his heart by fantasizing.
A woman working as a high-end bottle girl hears about a mysterious - and very lucrative - afterparty. But after she manages to get in, things go from bad to WTF..
A children's show host, Jeffery, becomes enraged when he finds out his show is being canceled and sets out to take revenge on those responsible.
How will 3 sisters save the Shakespeare Chateau, historic mansion and beloved family home, from a corrupt bank that threatens to foreclose on Christmas Day?
The action takes place in 1938. The film tells about a young artist Juris Upenajs who comes to Riga where he begins to build his career.
Ace pilot Blackhawk leads an international squadron of fighters to defeat the Nazis in World War II.
A red key to a public locker is also the key to solving a string of mysterious murders investigated by private eye Larry Morgan.
A comet is discovered to be on a collision course with Earth. As doomsday nears, the human race prepares for the worst.
After the death of a group of teenagers using the Ouija, the psychologist Fernanda and her son return to Peru, but they will find themselves surrounded by an evil entity as big as its wicked sect.

A boy who leaves his entire family for his girlfriend and they both get married then he goes with his wife to her house. It is realized that apart from the two of them, there is a third person in the house who is watching over them.

Three friends must discover what's behind the killings of local children, the victims drew the same picture before they died. They uncover the evil spirit of a circus clown and must send it back to hell before more children are murdered.
When a mysterious terrorist declares war on white nationalist cops, he starts a war that will tear the country apart.

Love Hotel. The best place to spend your holiday on February 14th. So this time, the doors of the hotel are open for everyone who wants to make Valentine's Day special, wants to believe in love again, or at least not be alone on this day.
After the usual family fight, Tora leaves Shibamata and falls in love with a geisha from Osaka, who is struggling with her own problems. Tora tries to help her.

On a Sunday, Eileen Tyler, still a virgin, leaves Albany to visit her airline pilot brother in New York but a chance encounter with a man on a city bus threatens to derail her upcoming marriage to boyfriend Russ.
15 years after the murder of her mother and brother, Rasty invites four friends to his parents' villa. The visit that is originally just for vacation, ends up far from their expectations.
A young designer and a married executive may be about to start an affair. A series of lunch hours play out the relationship.
Grace is an 18-year-old Catholic girl whose purity is overtaken by a demonic force. Will it consume her?

Shen Wei and Tong Xin wake up one morning in a bed, with no idea what happened or even who the person in bed with them is. The two split with few words, but each is missing something. What is actually happening last night?

movie_name: A Good Woman Is Hard to Find
description: A recently widowed young mother will go to any lengths to protect her children as she seeks the truth behind her husband's murder.
A prominent person from Delhi reach a palace,which is well known for its tradition and royalty to solve an issue. Consequently, instead of a solution, the issue becomes more and more complicated.
After the ZnMBe compound escapes containment, Jack and Beth race against time to find a cure before a pandemic breaks out.
When a heavyset girl discovers that whatever she does to her body physically affects her bully, she has to decide how far she's willing to go to exact revenge.

Salam is a consultant on a popular Palestinian TV series filmed in Ramallah who rather stupidly runs afoul of an Israeli checkpoint commander who uses his military influence to begin to manipulate Salam and the writing of the show.
Haunted by her troubled past, EMMA works as a hospital nurse while wrestling with murderous compulsions, but a romance with a young, terminally ill patient offers her a final chance at redemption.
Betrayed and on the run, a North Korean agent tries to uncover the volatile secrets hidden inside the eyeglasses of a dead man.
Tough Duke Mullane tries to open a new mine in the jungle, but the natives turn hostile...except for one lissome dancer.
When two 'poles apart' actresses, an energetic kid's TV host and a glamorous franchise superstar, are thrown together in an indie thriller, their chemistry lights up more than the screen.

The movie depicts the life and times of a group of schoolmates who are best buddies. As they journey through the most memorable times of their lives, lasting friendships are forged and extraordinary tales of romance blossom.

An emotional story of a man who rediscovers love after his wife suddenly and mysteriously leaves him. The plot further develops an intriguing insight into their separate lives leaving viewers at the edge of their seat until the very end.
Follows a tough, working-class, petty criminal who morphs into an anti-heroine to be reckoned with in a murky underworld, in the treacherous world of diamond smuggling.
A radio broadcaster's intense attraction to a mysterious woman opens the door to a tidal wave of powerful emotions and desires.

The UK has split leaving a post-apocalyptic England and the Enforcer Celeste alone, looking for something more than just survival. Maitland returns to find a death he wants but fate has different ideas for someone to follow, fear and love.

A reunion with friends changes the way Godse perceives the system. He begins to unravel the system's hidden agenda that robs off the careers and lives of students. What follows is a fight between Godse and the government for justice.
The year is 2222, three AI robots wake up in shipwreck on the planet they must do recon and figure out a way to get back to earth before they run out of power.

Mika is a fresh high school student who starts texting a mysterious boy. She is shocked when he reveals who he is - Hiro, a delinquent attending her school. What she doesn't know is that Hiro isn't as bad as he seems.

movie_name: Kiss Me Before It Blows Up
description: When two generations of Israeli women fall for a German woman and a Palestinian man, chaos follows. What happens with lovers who don't fit--but do belong together?
Imprisoned by an adult world that now fears everyone under 18, a group of teens form a resistance group to fight back and reclaim control of their future.
After escaping a Russian labor camp, three men must overcome the treacherous wilderness and each other, as their journey home turns into a brutal fight for survival.
An American agent, under false suspicion of disloyalty, must discover and expose the real spy without the help of his organization.

An animal loving vigilante Arjun Bakshi, unearths the fact that an underground illegal animal trade cell functions from Kolkata port. On investigating he chances upon a rare species of the Indian Striped Hyena (Lakadbaggha).
A baby boy discovered on an ocean liner in 1900 grows into a musical prodigy, never setting foot on land.

Emmi Rothner only wanted to cancel a newspaper subscription, but because she makes a typo in the address bar, the e-mail ends up in the mailbox of Leo Leike. It is the beginning of a long online exchange.
A woman tries to attract her reincarnated lover from her previous life but eventually turns to the aid of an evil sorcerer who rules over a tribe of cannibal midgets.

This interactive thriller follows a young couple who decides to spend the weekend in the girl's family farm, where a sinister homemade resides. The harmony ends when they find a piglet in the farm's grotto.

Surviving a vicious attack in her homeland, a traumatized but stunning young female singer-musician flees to freedom and a 'happy marriage' in Los Angeles where destiny leads her into a passionate and dangerous love affair.
Anne-Marie Stretter, wife of a French diplomat, lives in 1930s India. She takes many lovers as systems of oppression decay around her.
A weekend of darkness entraps a small group of lowlifes held up at a secluded bordello, as their leader transgresses slowly into total insanity...
Insane doctor Scivane returns to his home town only to spread horror around. Mix of vampire movie/science fiction/macumba horror/psychiatric thriller in very low budget production.
Gerrie, Richard, Rikkert, Robbie and Barry from Maaskantje are in a big fight with the village of Schijndel. When a zombie kills someone from Brabant, things get out of hand.
A folklore researcher ends up ordering a vintage demon from a mysterious website. A nightmarish experience follows.
A group of college graduates are thrown into a living nightmare when they venture into a cursed valley.
A couple go to Mexico for a vacation and mistaken for a thief and must get away before going to a Mexican jail to rot.
A sociopath gathers and drugs groups of college students to bring out their existing suicidal tendencies to the surface then walks among them to enjoy and record their deaths.
Paglu and Amu are childhood friends of Abhi and decide to save him from marrying the wrong girl. But then things go out of hand and it leads to chaotic and hilarious situations.

This is a love story. Everyone falls in love at least once in life. It takes a lot of effort and trust to make it work. What happens when there are misunderstandings between couples and how it affects their lives?
A crazed escaped mental patient holds 2 couples hostage and terrorizes them in a Malibu beach home during a stormy night.
At a Birthday party birthday boy Avinash was murdered by someone in the house. Who is the killer and what is the motive behind the crime?

Budhiparamaaya Neekkam is a romantic film written and directed by Vinod Narayanan after his acclaimed film "Govindan Kutty thirakilanu". The story of the film was said to be "very much associated with the culture" of Trivandram town.
Joan's (Patricia Medina) mother wants her to marry her pompous boss although she loves a soldier (Jimmy Handley).
A young woman struggling with anxiety escapes to a remote cottage, and becomes the victim of a deadly prank.
