Ravi, who works as a collection agent for a bank, realizes that a couple cheats gullible people of their money. He decides to give them a taste of their own medicine and falls in love along the way.
It is WWII and Japan has occupied Thailand. A group of unlikely heroes, comprising of mostly thieves and misfits, band together to oppose the Japanese.
At 3:01 AM, every morning, John Newman, recently widowed, awakens from nightmares. Are these nightmares somehow related to the rash of ritual murders occurring in his city?

Two girls with homosexual tendencies decide to open the luxury brothel "Rose Blue Light". Then, one of them has a brush with the law, and she gets hopelessly smitten by the investigating policewoman's beauty.
A group of friends seek shelter from a heavy rain in an old abandoned house. One of them gets possessed and acts as a conduit for the vengeful spirit of the house's previous murderous owner.
Due to the black magic protecting Maya, anyone who falls in love with her ends up mysteriously killed, so Vijay tries to get rid of the magic.

An artist who's failed to define her true self, returns home to S.Texas amidst a global health crisis. Trying to locate her mother's body, who died from a respiratory disease, she experiences a deeper emotional connection with herself.
ACP Bala investigates the murder case of a prominent figure known as Contractor Vishwas Narayan and stumbles on many suspects, who is the real culprit?

When a deadly outbreak spreads across an isolated island, the survivors, who have lost everything, must find a way to escape the virus filled island while survival on the island becomes threatened and while a dark secret unravels.
A hostage negotiator is lured into a trap set by a suspect claiming to have served in the First World War.
A drama that interweaves the life of a teenager, with his old baby sitter, her estranged husband, and their daughter.

movie_name: Revenge in the House of Usher
description: A young doctor visits the secluded home of his ailing mentor - Eric Usher - who believes the house itself is alive and plotting to drive him insane, manifesting itself through ghostly apparitions.
A group of pro wrestlers decide they've had enough of their lying, cheating promoter and plan to rob him during the upcoming big show.
A young timid Asian-American sharpshooter must team with a racist FBI detective to take down the local mob who murdered their loved one in 1970s South Boston
A writer, possessed by a terrifying story hunts for its secret heart in a mysterious landscape. He journeys into unknown, dreamlike places, haunted by the infamous Hum emitted from a strange factory.
When an underwater ocean lab is lost in a earthquake, an advanced submarine is sent down to find it and encounters terrible danger.
This Movie is about the streets of Birmingham Ala. and a local neighborhood Ex-Drug dealer that's trying to get out the Hood and got 1 chance from someone to invest in his dream !!

A sweet and rich girl loves a poor shepherd and so rejects marriage proposals from a wealthy chief shepherd. He blames her beloved for a theft that has never been done by the shepherd but his intrigues do not lead to the desired result for him.
After ghosts invade the human world through the Internet, a father must protect his daughter from the psychotic spirit of his ex-wife.
High School basketball coach, Dinah Groshardt, falls for the school secretary, Carly Lumpkin, and upsets the entire school in the process.
The Kiramager and the Ryusoulger team-up as they end up in a variety of movie worlds produced by Yodonna and the film's enemy Jamenshi and Minosaur.

Jack gets fed up with his publishing job in New York and his girlfriend and moves to Colorado, where he plans to write a novel. There he takes over his uncle's lodge and cafe, but runs into unusual problems with the oddball locals.
A German crime syndicate which imports weapons into the United States have had a special assassin's gun stolen in transit. Mucho mayhem follows.
In this vision of a shocking alternate reality, a group of US soldiers do the unthinkable and kidnap the President of the United States. Will they uncover the truth behind the Iraq War?
Constantly quarreling couple decide to try the jealousy angle when a naive young couple comes along.
A film teacher takes his practice to extreme levels of hand-on training, which traumatizes most of those who are subject to his abuse of power.
Three young ad-men enter the woods for a photo shoot, but a girlfriend's mysterious disappearance sparks a harrowing descent into unreality.
A former Imperial Russian general and cousin of the Czar ends up in Hollywood as an extra in a movie directed by a former revolutionary.
A rich man's past comes knocking when he is informed that one of his employees is his long lost son. He does not know that he's being cheated and that his real son is the one who loves his niece.
In order to woo a lady, a social misfit hires his brother who provides hookups services for men in need.
OTHELLO is a cinematographic essay about power, desire, jealousy and deceit; a thought on the boundaries between fiction and real life.

For Victor, days go by and are all the same. But this dull life could be disrupted because, little by little, it is clear that something is going wrong - Vi is sure: somewhere in his flat, or perhaps hidden in himself, Hell is ready.

Dick Purcell is an American taxi driver who wants to become a singer promoting cheese products. Oddly he thinks the way to do it is to become a gondolier from Venice. Along the way he sings and woos a sassy secretary Alice.
In a year with many international happenings, the most important thing for this gang is rock'n'roll and Elvis' last movie. This gang decides it all, and loyalty is everything.

Fifteen hundred years after the war of gods, the heaven declined. Yang Jian, the God of Erlang, made a living by working as a catcher. One day, Yang Jian was ordered to hunt down a young man, his own nephew.
"Demon Stone" is an 80's horror/comedy throwback film that tells the story of a young man named Mark who battles demonic possession with the help of an eccentric television show host.
A young genius accidentally invents a device that amplifies the paranormal activity within his family's house, possibly bringing back the spirits of loved ones, and unleashing things far worse.
Driven by revenge, Simon Carson is an elite killer for the local crime syndicate. One day he is sent to dispose of a young girl. He decides to instead save her.

Lily (Deann Baker) wakes up in a bloody motel bathroom with fuzzy memories of the previous night. As she copes with her trauma and struggles to figure out what happened, she begins changing into something inhuman.
The murder of a wealthy countess triggers a chain reaction of brutal killings in the surrounding bay area, as several unscrupulous characters try to seize her large estate.

movie_name: Wounded Warrior: The Wheels Keep Turning
description: When an old man's environmentally friendly delivery business is being threatened by unscrupulous drug dealers his fleet of cyclists take action.

The Journey to Aresmore follows the story of two 17 year old boys (Peter Townsend and Jack Cunningham) mysteriously taken into another world Known as Elithior. A world full of magic and ...                See full synopsis »

Gábor Bozsó is a professional burglar, but his daughter Éva, who knows nothing about it, is raised in an upscale institution. When she falls in love with one of her father's victims, things take a big change.
Desperate to save his fiancee from a demon that has possessed her soul, a man turns to his longtime priest for help.
A romantic comedy about a young, divorced woman who sets out to reconnect with her college sweetheart only to discover that he has been a part of her life all along.

A couple are looking for their child who was lost in the tsunami - their search takes them to the dangerous Thai-Burmese waters, and then into the jungle, where they face unknown but horrifying dangers.

movie_name: The Agency: Hunt for the Cure
description: In the second installment of the Agency Trilogy, the virus has been released. The C.I.A. is scrambling to stop the spreading of the infection.
An unsettled summer becomes the background of an erotic twist that track four characters into a fictional game. But playing fiction is not an innocent game.

After accepting a lucrative offer, a crew of space scavengers must transport a prisoner to an unknown planets facility, but they soon find themselves in a dilemma when the prisoner escapes and his true identity revealed.
A top secret organization is after Lewis Jordan when he comes into control of a dangerous formula that could lead to nuclear disaster.
Philippe Clarence, a famous Parisian dressmaker, seduces his friend's fiancee. But, for the 1st time in his life, this is for real. The film is also a sharp picture of the fashion world.
Two deceived women plot revenge against their husbands. A composer is cheated on by an adventurer whose girlfriend he falls in love with.
The story revolves around three friends who are desperately looking out for suitable job opportunities. Their lives get devastated when they try to unite two lovers.

A dark romantic comedy. Tom and Janet have been happily married for years. But a visit from a mysterious stranger leads to a dead body, a lot of questions, and a tense couples' trip with friends who may not actually be friends at all.

movie_name: That's What You Do When You Fall in Love
description: A girl that lives on an island meets an Athenian painter and accepts to become his model. She falls in love with him and follows him to Athens.
A young married couple comes home from a date night to discover that they are imprisoned in their own house with a methodical killer inside.
Deep in the wilderness, two best friends must learn to forgive and depend on each other more than ever when they stir up a group of dangerous locals.

Iskander, a young man living on the Kazakh steppes, finds French astronaut Julie after her capsule crashes. Julie now has amnesia, but Iskander convinces her they are engaged. (Russian with English subtitles)

The grand tale of a zombie holding a arm. He also travels the world learning about life, and the meaning of it all. He also meets a girl zombie holding a body. Will they fall in love? Will they complete that human body? Watch and find out.

When Commander Frank Evans escapes captivity in the Middle East he is treated as a pariah by the military establishment and works security. In doing so he crosses white supremacists and must apply his training to protect his family.
Feeling her time slipping away, a New York socialite party girl changes her identity and moves to Texas to find true love.
As if getting pregnant weren't complicated enough, Lucy sets out to uncover the unsettling truth about her fertility doctor.
An emigrant in Paris recalls the idyllic past in his homeland - full of hope, love, happiness, colourful characters and magnificent landscapes.
Tu Xiaoyi, Yao Zhetian and Qi Jingxuan are high school students in a small town, Lanxi, in southern China. This is a story about dreams, friendship, family and first love in their youthful days.

Munster re-brands his gas station as a museum after he mysteriously acquires a Peruvian mummy. Karen, who works the register, discovers that she has a psychic connection to the mummy that will change her perspective and her life forever.

movie_name: Ma si tuo na de lv xing
description: Shishi, a senior student from Beijing, comes to Shanghai to finish her thesis video. She meets Feng Chen, a local film director. Feng leads Shishi to visit places in the city and they begin to have feelings mutually in 24 hours.
The life story of slain legislator Vangaveeti Mohan Ranga Rao who was assassinated during the NT Rama Rao regime in 1989.
Based on true events, a dying Jewish man retells the story of how he and other concentration camp prisoners rose up against their Nazi captors during the Holocaust.

Set in 2020, A Guardian of Dimensions, NEWDaisy3 had a trouble with Dark Dimenisional Robot, DarkDaisy3 who cause for conquer all universes So Deerling decide help her to stop DarkDaisy3 and collecting Chaos beryl.

Alberto, a Colombian migrant working illegally in London to pay for his mother's operation back home, becomes convinced that God has a destiny marked out for him. This is a taught, poignant thriller with a captivating supernatural twist.
An advertising executive goes to Mexico looking for talent and finds a hot-tempered singer, who goes to New York to stay with him, his aunt and uncle, and decides to steal him from his fiancée.
A girl journeys far from her world to meet the Coven's, the family she married into. What she discovers is a dark secret that has been haunting her new family for years.

In this intense action adventure filmed on location in Sardinia, a beautiful secret agent (Barbara Niven) recruits a local sculptor (Franco Columbu) to aid her in rescuing a presidential candidate's kidnapped mistress.
A series of mysterious murders happened in a haunted barber house.Was it really supernatural forces or was it actually people behind the murders?

A happy-go-lucky Antony disappoints his Dad who was a teacher, so his Dad brings home 2 puppies to insult Antony and show him how thankful Dogs are. Antony despises the Dogs and never leaves any chances to trouble them.
At a popular NYC Italian restaurant on a dramatic, busy evening, there are 2 gangsters, cop detective, food-critic, ex bookmaker owner, his chef son, indebted gambler sous-chef etc.
On the run, three criminals find themselves holed up at a notorious old hospital that happens to be the hunting ground of a masked killer.

After NASA picks up a trio of mysterious signals from within our own solar system, astronaut Roger Nelson is dispatched on a multi-year solo mission aboard the Magellan spacecraft to investigate the sources.

Following Kick-Ass' heroics, other citizens are inspired to become masked crusaders. But Red Mist leads his own group of evil supervillains to get revenge, kill Kick-Ass and destroy everything he stands for.
When Vazelia's Makai Knight goes missing, German is summoned back from the dead to help Leon and Alfonso deal with the new horror that stalks his land.

movie_name: Win a Date with Tad Hamilton!
description: A small-town girl wins a date with a male celebrity through a contest. When the date goes better than expected, a love triangle forms between the girl, the male celebrity, and the girl's best friend.
A federal marshal stationed at a mining colony on the Jupiter moon of Io uncovers a drug-smuggling conspiracy. He gets no help from the workers or authorities when he finds himself marked for murder.

Four people travel into the forest in Chicago, Il. looking for a rumored ghost town buried deep in Triangle Woods. They soon realize some legends are true as they are hunted by hell on earth. Sometimes Horror exists for real.

At a late-night séance, attended by twelve people, the medium announces that three secrets will be revealed before midnight. However, as the bodies pile up, so do the secrets, leading to the darkest of them all.
A young woman is seduced by a charismatic highwayman who offers her promises of fame as a singer in exchange for romance.
After moving to a new neighborhood, a mysterious man starts introducing his landlord to the hobby of collecting crime statistics.
Rich, beautiful Rosita would do anything to win the love of the man with whom she is obsessed, but neither her beauty nor all the money in the world gives her what she wants.
An atheist man finds himself in the middle of a war between angels and demons, as the Revelation apocalypse unfolds, only to discover that he is God, and that war is being fought over him.

Fran Walker (Dame Elizabeth Taylor) walks into a piano bar for pizza. She comes back home with Joe Grady (Warren Beatty), the piano player. Joe plans on winning five thousand dollars and leaving Las Vegas, Nevada. Fran waits for something else. Meanwhile, he moves in with her.
After his brother is killed and father severely injured by terrorists, a young med student quits his studies to join the Indian Police Service to wipe out the terrorists.

A young cognitive science student enlists the aid of a paranormal psychologist and a young man with a century old secret to ease her sleep paralysis of the Omnicron, a demon conspiracy as old as time.
Unni, a bus owner, and his friend Sundareshan ply a bus service. The pathetic condition of his bus creates concerns for Unni. Things take a turn when a girl happens to come into their lives.
2 strangers, a man and a woman are trapped together underground when the building collapses around them, and are forced to create a new world.
A three kings seance goes horribly wrong and causes a group of friends to fight desperately to survive the night.
A young woman inherits an old hotel in Louisiana where, following a series of supernatural "accidents", she learns that the building was built over one of the entrances to Hell.
The heroes pose as gun dealers and acrobats in order to get close to the bad guys so they can avenge the death of one of their brothers.
A hardened gangster encounters by chance a woman he hasn't seen since childhood. They are both engulfed in the underground world of intergang warfare.
The human city of Zion defends itself against the massive invasion of the machines as Neo fights to end the war at another front while also opposing the rogue Agent Smith.
Clara just understand that her husband have a fling with another girl. While she is in Paris airport she decides to do the same.
SACKED is a sports romantic comedy about a young woman who creates a crowd-funding campaign to buy out a struggling quarterback's contract while they fall for each other's secret identities online.

After escaping from a sex trafficking ring, one teenage girl struggles to reconnect with herself and her family. To rescue her helpless friends, she must confront her own fears and help lead the police to her traffickers - at all costs.
A disgraced soldier finds redemption by going undercover and risking his life for Military Intelligence.
While investigating the case of a runaway child, two New Orleans detectives become embroiled in a centuries-long feud between two secretive vampire factions.
King Saul of the Israelites is visited in Jerusalem by the Prophet Samuel who foretells him that a war with The Philistines is inevitable and the shepherd David will become king.
For reasons of his own a sea captain pays one of his sailors to marry a singer, but not long after the marriage the two find they are actually in love.
A man in desperate need of money decides to disguise himself as an old man to teach two young women. He falls in love with one of the them and simultaneously romances their guardian.
It is a remake of an English movie, Trading Places(1983) directed by John Landis with the lead roles of Eddie Murphy, Dan Aykroyd and Ralph Bellamy.

A serial killer brings an unsuspecting new victim on a weekend getaway to add another body to his ever-growing count. She's buying into his faux charms, and he's eagerly lusting for blood. What could possibly go wrong?
Special Agent Owl infiltrates an underground criminal organization where his contact Komodo introduces him to prize-fighting, human trafficking, and illegal drug smuggling.
What seems to be a match made in heaven turns into a nightmare in this Indian wedding when the bride and her guests are transformed into a horde of zombies.
The writer of a bad TV series begins to rethink his life when he meets and falls in love with a beautiful actress.

Five years ago Alice's son was murdered. Every day is consumed with the need to find his killer. The arrival of a mysterious stranger leads Alice to suspect him to be the killer and coincides with a renewed spate of horrific child murders.

Paul is a photographer who runs into his first love, Anna in a busy Filipino market. The traveler's passions reignite, their principles on relationships, religion and morality clash. The night they spend together will change everything.

movie_name: Fist of the North Star: The Kaioh Saga
description: Super fighter Kenshiro faces the toughest opponent he's ever had, the sinister brother of Raul, Kaioh.

When a young woman inherits a decrepit mansion she finds herself entangled in a long forgotten family tragedy. With her very soul at stake, she must battle an evil reawakened by her presence or remain trapped inside Willows Manor forever.

movie_name: An Occurrence at Owl Creek Bridge
description: "An Occurrence at Owl Creek Bridge" is a psychological thriller that takes many emotional turns and finally catches the audience off guard as it ends with an unsettling, macabre twist.

Tatkshan is a brutal story of grit and indomitable spirit of Sub Inspector Harshvardhan Dubey,UP Police,who comes across mutilated unidentified human body in Lucknow.Investigating the case layer by layer leads to many shocking revelations.

Cracker County is under attack and lovesick dog catcher Bubba Blanche has been transformed into a ferocious, cigar smoking Werewolf in order to save the day. But first he's got to conquer a beer or two. And maybe a plate of chicken wings.

Angel (Jestoni) is hired by Cong. Savedra (Bob) as the bodyguard of his lover Gigi (Mikee). Soon, Savedra earns the suspicion that Gigi is in love with Angel. When he accidentally kills Gigi, he decides to frame up Angel as the killer.
Around midnight, a young couple and their transvestite maid prepare for an orgy. Their guests will be The Slut, The Star, The Stud and The Teen.
An erotic love triangle revolving around a writer adrift in the icy slopes of Kashmir where he discovers a woman with a strange, silent past.
An Indian mystic uses magical chants to raise women from the dead, then sends them out to perform revenge killings for him.

A family in turmoil returns to the small town where David, the father, had grown up. Their return to the countryside takes them into the middle of generational abuse and Satanic practices only to find help in an unexpected way.
An unseen master thief employs three girls for a job. The plot and story points are mostly influenced by Charlie's Angels.
A Platoon of U.S. Soldiers in Afghanistan searching for Taliban become trapped in a cave and are hunted down by a deadly creature.
ACP Ravindra Varma, a fearless and sincere police officer, is called to nab terrorist Milind Shinde, who has political backing.
Orphaned high school student Rick Riker is bitten by a radioactive dragonfly, develops super powers (except for the ability to fly), and becomes a hero.

Susan travels with her father to England for a vacation. Invited to a ball, Susan meets Sir John Ashwood and marries him after a whirlwind romance. However, American Susan never quite adjusts to life as a new member of the British gentry.
Perpetual wandering of a man who searches for his own identity, never reaching the final destination.

When the elevators in New York's 102-story Millennium Building start to malfunction, mechanic Mark Newman is sent to find the cause. After a series of gruesome and deadly "accidents" occur, Mark joins forces with spunky reporter Jennifer.
An ex-operative-turned assassin steals classified military tech that could revolutionize modern warfare. But as the agency struggles to eliminate him, a darker truth unfolds.

LADY TARANTULA AND HEXANNE The story of two orphaned teenage girls with supernatural abilities chosen to steal an "other-worldly" artifact for a mysterious pawnshop owner in exchange for their deepest wish.
Will and Jake Grimm are traveling con-artists who encounter a genuine fairy-tale curse which requires true courage instead of their usual bogus exorcisms.
Three groups of people intertwine and are left stranded in the streets on Purge Night, trying to survive the chaos and violence that occurs.
A reluctant teen must team up with his murderous inner demon in order to defeat an army of bloodthirsty creatures rising up from the bowels of Hell.

Gouda, a Japanese businessman in the Philippines, has a new development project: the establishment of a resort-hotel complex in a fishing village somewhere in Lapu-Lapu City in Cebu. While ...                See full synopsis »

movie_name: Guess What Happened to Count Dracula?
description: Count Dracula changes his name to Count Adrian and opens a strange nightclub called Dracula's Dungeon. Count Adrian sets his sights on making the lovely Angelica his latest vampire bride by giving her three bites to the neck.

movie_name: Paws of Fury: The Legend of Hank
description: Hank, a loveable dog with a head full of dreams about becoming a samurai, sets off in search of his destiny.
Pierre, a young musician in Paris, briefly catches sight of a beautiful woman dressed in blue and soon spends all of his time trying to track her down.

As the protagonist is searching for his girlfriend who has disappeared for 2 weeks ago, he happens to meet voyeurs and flashers in the midnight park. They established individual culture in here and get along with each other in unique way.

This adaptation of Emile Zola's novel "NANA," is about the sexual liaisons of a woman who through her relationships with different men, enjoys a life of pleasure and luxury. However, her lavish life-style does not always bring happiness.
Three guys go on an off road trip of a lifetime in their newly acquired Army Truck, but it all goes horribly wrong when they start meeting monsters.

In 1909, poor theology student Henrik falls in love with Anna, the intelligent daughter of a rich family in Uppsala. After marrying Henrik becomes a priest in northern Sweden. Urbane Anna hates living in the county, growing restless.
Dami, a local makeup artist, tries to reconnect with her ex-husband, even after finding out about his engagement to her client.
Colonel Whitlock run "The Devil's Room", a military base on a hidden island were research on biological warfare are being done under the cover of medical research.

An Irish immigrant lands in 1950s Brooklyn, where she quickly falls into a romance with a local. When her past catches up with her, however, she must choose between two countries and the lives that exist within.
6 friends want to celebrate a night party, but when they drive through a remote area something crosses their path, causing an accident. They find shelter in a hotel and the nightmare begins.
A sheriff must rescue an estranged family from a mountain during a volcano eruption and fight off a horde of lava-filled zombies brought to life by a curse.

movie_name: Yi Yi: A One and a Two...
description: Each member of a middle-class Taipei family seeks to reconcile past and present relationships within their daily lives.
While shooting on location in the South Pacific, a movie star is pursued by a handsome Naval officer who is convinced she is the girl for him.

You've run out of options, no school, no job. Steal a car, smash a shop with a heavy car and reap the proceeds! This movie is about underground England. The causes, the benefits, and the result of a life of 'crash and carry.'

Saeed is an employee of the airport flight monitoring department, a member of a spy group. In the crash of an Iranian Airbus plane by an American ship in the Persian Gulf, he loses his family and engages in insane behavior.
Showing the life(dramatization) of the hot boys or cash money millionaires and how it goes down in the magnolia,dirty cops,drug life and shoot outs with a twist of reality

A bounty hunter learns that his next target is his ex-wife, a reporter working on a murder cover-up. Soon after their reunion, the always-at-odds duo find themselves on a run-for-their-lives adventure.
A couple decide to adopt a child after they had a stillborn baby. But the adopted boy is caught doing bad things and is not as innocent as he claims to be.
A group of friends were haunted respectively with a supernatural forces due to their faulty deed against a little snake.

Chris, a prison officer is seeking justice to find Candidate 5238 "Jericho" an escaped prisoner who has gained powers beyond the typical super soldier, but with the R.O.N in the way, Chris is forced to fight back along side the resistance.

movie_name: Kureyon Shin-chan: Densetsu o yobu odore! Amîgo!
description: This is shinchan 1st horror comedy movie which was released in japan as the shinchan forteenth movie

movie_name: Nu sha xing da nao wu long yuan
description: When Polly was sold to the brothel in BAP, she acted shy and innocent; but when Chia Ling is sold to the brothel here, she behaves like a sexy saucy tease, who is going to have a wonderful time.
Teen thugs Hiroshi and Toru get caught in a street war when their prized school trousers are forcefully taken from them by punks from a rival school.
A tough CIA agent is called in to put a stop to a shipment of weapons to the Viet Cong from an arms smuggling ring.
When he is framed for being a spy because of his friend's illegal activities, David must escape from police, CIA, and assassins with the help of his cousin.
A former gang boss is forced to fight his way through the dangerous streets of Detroit in order to save his wife and estranged son from the same gang he once ruled.
Upon learning that his father has been kidnapped, Austin Powers must travel to 1975 and defeat the aptly named villain Goldmember, who is working with Dr. Evil.

movie_name: Daisy Derkins and the Dinosaur Apocalypse
description: An evil sorcerer teams up with a mad scientist to unleash Dinosaur Hell on Earth, and only Daisy Derkins and a hero from the future can stop them.

A child survivor of severe trauma, Eric can not overcome his past. As his mind begins to develop a mystical "ripple" ability, Eric crosses paths with several individuals who alter his direction in life as he yearns to change his reality.
A woman and her friends break into her abandoned childhood home, where her mother went mad and nearly murdered as a child.
A woman, whose husband is cheating on her, and an undertaker, who has been in love with her since their childhood, decide to fake her death so they can be together.
A young couple trying to reunite amid a city ravaged by a plague that turns its victims into deranged, bloodthirsty sadists.
Fresh out of prison, yakuza lieutenant Jiro Sagae is recruited by a new gang to help defeat a powerful rival family in this bloody, stylish crime film that inspired Japanese yakuza films of the '70s.
When the titular antagonist of an action game takes on physical form, it's only the game's less powerful protagonist who can save his creator's family.
Two aspiring filmmakers document the mishaps of their first feature film, with the guidance of their eccentric lead actor.
Siddhant witnesses the murder of his entire family while on a video chat with his sister Aishwarya. He teams up with his adopted brother Ajmal and fiancée Gayathri to seek revenge.
A commentary on Spanish society dressed as a thriller about the misadventures of a gang of young petty criminals after the real estate crash.
A bounty hunter from New Mexico and a gang of horsemen called "Four of the Apocalypse" set their sights on the town of Dogma.

After treating a Monmouth rebel against King James II in 1680s England, a young Irish doctor is exiled as a slave to Jamaica where he captures a Spanish galleon and becomes the most feared pirate of the Caribbean.

movie_name: Kamen Rider Super Movie War Genesis: Kamen Rider vs. Kamen Rider Ghost & Drive
description: Three months after the Roidmude threat has ended, Takeru and Shinnosuke are sent back 10 years into the past, where Shinnosuke encounters Mr. Belt before they had originally met while Takeru finds his father before he passed away.
An army major is assigned to train an all-woman squad of seven convicted killers, whose mission is to pose as hookers and go to Brazil to assassinate some Cuban officers.
Romantic action drama about the life of an easygoing youngster named Surya, whose life take some unexpected turns thanks to the three women he meets along the way.

Massimo is a member of the Sicilian Mafia family and Laura is a sales director. She does not expect that on a trip to Sicily trying to save her relationship, Massimo will kidnap her and give her 365 days to fall in love with him.

Long, long ago, there was a wolf-man tribe who had no women. All through history these desperate wolf men have attacked and raped female humans as a way to continue their species. But the ...                See full synopsis »
In this gothic rendition of the classic fairy tale, a merchant's youngest daughter is held prisoner by a mysterious winged beast.
In Germany, 1941, the Nazis pursue a Toymaker who has acquired a mystical book which gives life to inanimate objects.

A world-renowned African American is unsuccessful in his attempt to overcome his demons, even while hiding away at his Spanish wife's lavish estate in Spain. When he invites his old friend to visit, a risky love triangle unfolds.

The story of a hooded, berserk killer who terrorized the border town of Texarkana, Arkansas in 1946--leaving no fewer than five murder victims in his wake. He was never caught. Based on one of America's most baffling murder cases.

A small California desert town is being stalked by a motiveless psychopath who roams its streets killing at random. Captain Peters and his small police force are on the case searching for his whereabouts before he kills again.

In the near future, convicts are offered the chance to volunteer as medical subjects to shorten their sentence. One such subject for a new drug capable of generating feelings of love begins questioning the reality of his emotions.

In the newest outing of the Werewolf Game series Ten high school students are thrown together and tasked with killing and murder. They are given roles such as villager, werewolf and so on. The sole survivor will receive 100 million yen.
A teacher still haunted by the death of two teens that she accidentally caused as a young girl goes beserk when four teens start harassing her and then attack her in her home.
It tells a story about a couple who met fifty years ago and have to deal with mischievous boys and a pushy village chief; as the lovers accidentally end up in the house of an old man.

Love Exchange is a romantic journey of a culturally opposite couple -Siddharth Sathe and Shanoo Kapoor. They meet at their work place, become good friends and ultimately fall in love. Things are fine till they decide to get married.
Adwoa owns a very exclusive hair salon that charges thousands of dollars to schedule an appointment. When clients start disappearing the police start to question recent murders in the area.

Jake and Mitzi is a film that follows two teenagers from Philadelphia, Jake Evans and Mitzi Evans, on their journey to becoming the world's first Superheroes while defeating the world's first Supervillain, their scientist Uncle Shaun.
Erik and Brianna are life long Friends, will they choose to cross the line into something more Intimate?
A grad student and her friends become trapped at a women's academy run by a cult of homicidal feminists.
Due to the pandemic, Parker and her best friend decide to quarantine at the family lake house alone - or so they think.

An incredible movie beyond artificial intelligence. Riccardo builds and educates his artificial intelligence with all his strength till his artificial intelligence turns itself autonomously into a strong artificial intelligence.

movie_name: Pusti me da nadjem srcu lek
description: An older but still attractive widow falls in love with a younger man, which becomes the main gossip of her family and village.
An officer aiming to infiltrate a drug dealing family uses a lady with a past and her son as cover to gain entry and uncover their secrets
A team of special agents must stop a sinister mastermind from bringing the world's nations to their knees.
FROM A HUMBLE BEGINNING HOW DO THIS MAN BECOME KNOWN IN HISTORY OF BOXING - AS A TERROR INSIDE THE RING.
A house cat sees her mistress murdered by two servants under orders from her husband , and becomes ferociously bent on revenge.

A deranged woman tries to create the perfect man - by harvesting her one favorite body part from each of the imperfect men she dates. Beneath the murder and mayhem is a simple story of someone needing to be loved.
Set in the near future where a computer virus infects people and an artificial intelligence is gaining strength and dominance.
In the near future, 10 men are voted as the 10 who could lead the world; on the list is leading Hong Kong scientist Dr. Ken.
"Mad Max" clone set in the not-too-distant future about a group of people trying to escape to a safe haven called Neon City after a solar disaster that has decimated the Earth.
During the night of the biggest sports final of the year, two girls working in a gas station experience strange incidents. Is it just staged pranks or is it something of a more aggressive intent?
Crippled and foot bone damaged young boy Burhan loves Nuzhet. There is someone else, Dr. Ragip who is on the verge of marriage with Nuzhet.
A grizzled tank commander makes tough decisions as he and his crew fight their way across Germany in April, 1945.

An ace fighter pilot crashes in New Guinea, evades headhunters in the jungle, and is rescued. He attempts to return fifty years later to visit his downed plane, but meets opposition when he learns his story is still told among the locals.
In 13th century England, the dishonoured knight Roger Godberd leads a band of warriors on a quest to rescue the peasants he once swore to protect, his deeds inspiring a legend.
In the future where dormant powers awaken in certain people, a secret organization is formed to hunt these people down. A mysterious powerful boy Quon will stop at nothing to end this persecution.
Steve has gone missing but, luckily, his loyal sidekick (and nephew) Stu knows exactly what to do to find someone who can help locate his uncle: get human help.

Toshie is a nurse at a hospital in a rural area. She meets Yukiko, who has gone to the hospital to see a doctor. Yukiko has just gotten married and has been breaking out in hives every time she has physical contact with her husband.

World War II: Shortly after D-Day, three American soldiers and two Army Corps nurses are stranded behind enemy lines. They take a high-ranking German officer as their prisoner and try to orchestrate an escape.
Ten girls are suspected of committing a horrible crime, and until they confess, they won't be able to leave their school.
A failed host of underground television goes on a bloody rampage to rid the business of horror films.
The film narrates the events that occur when a unit of policemen from Kerala reach the Naxalite prone areas in North India for election duty.

Salvo is a body guard and hit man for a mafioso. After foiling an attack on his employer, Salvo hunts down the man who organised it and encounters the man's blind sister. She causes Salvo to question himself and his existence.
Two men write anonymous love letters to test if their wives are faithful. When their wives actually respond, the two men are left in a fix of what to do.
The legendary Clades are a family of explorers whose differences threaten to topple their latest and most crucial mission.
A seemingly innocent UN interpreter is caught between the FBI and a criminal dynasty in a grapple for vengeance.
A family of Russian emigrants run a small restaurant called Russian Nights in Santa Monica, California which makes most of its money one night a week when all the local Russians come down to party.

In Omiya, where the Kanto region's largest motorcycle gangs run rampant Masaki is sent to a juvenile training school due to a certain scheme. The motorcycle gang "Sakurajinkai" vs the gangster "Aobakai". The Solitary revenge begins now.

movie_name: Haven Lost: The Dragon's Brood Cycle
description: When a teenage girl is transported into a mysterious world, she goes to war with the despotic sorceress that has turned The Haven into a nightmare using dark magic.

movie_name: A Movie Will Be Shown Without the Picture
description: In 1979, American artist and photographer Louise Lawler screened the classic John Houston film The Misfits (1961) at the Aero Theatre in Santa Monica. She played only the audio portion of the film, leaving the screen blank for the duration.
They have dreams too. Try to understand. They are not like you but that is not really any threat to you. If you lived in space the situation would change you. Perhaps then, it would make sense.
A cleaver-wielding bridal designer murders various young brides-to-be in an attempt to unlock a repressed childhood trauma.
A specially trained squad of guinea pigs is dispatched to stop a diabolical billionaire from taking over the world.
A group of friends race their high-powered cars up and down a dangerous and deadly mountain road known as Mulholland Drive to see who can claim the title of "King of the Hill."
In 1949, a lead-footed housewife, Louise Smith, refuses to let the good 'ol boys run her off the road and crashes her way into NASCAR history.

Cherry Carson is a rich girl who falls in love with a gentleman she meets by chance on a train trip. Little does she know that he is the son of her father's greatest enemy, and their love is doomed to suffer.
After her supposed death, a young woman returns as the son of her noble family to precede the family's prestigious company, with a demon at her side to avenge her parent's murder.

Down on their luck, Best friends Ace and Deuce need money fast. They stumble upon a package from a transport gone wrong. What seemed like a lucky come up turns deadly as the packages owner will stop at nothing to get it back.

British hunter Thorndike vacationing in Bavaria has Hitler in his gun sight. He is captured, beaten, left for dead, and escapes back to London where he is hounded by German agents and aided by a young woman.

The Untitled Kung Fu Space Western centers on one of the galaxy's most charming outlaws, the leader of a funny, ragtag crew of rebel bandits that are put on a collision course with a legendary villain to determine the fate of the galaxy.

5 years after being dishonourably discharged from the Service for disobeying a direct order from Downing Street, John Venonesser has gone from a hero to a broken man. Living the life of recluse is about to change.

Rodel is a young salesman and Aleli is a young and innocent student. Aleli befriended a mature woman who is expert in love. The lady lured her to fantasize and to seek the love offered by men. Aleli dated Rodel who raping her.
A beautiful young woman is driven into a dark underworld of demonic possession, desire, and extreme indulgences when she learns she may be the devil's kin.
A psychotic craftsman pits two rival Kung-Fu masters against each other while designing special lanterns from a disturbing source.
Two unusually close friends share every aspect of their lives together. As their lives evolve, their bond remains the only constant.

A young woman, distraught from witnessing the murder of her parents as a child, develops her own unique martial art by playing video games. It's because of this she suddenly finds herself embroiled in the world of underground fighting.
A boy and a girl find themselves stuck in a whirlpool of such intense love that they would do anything, go to any extent and face all odds for the one they love.
Siddhu, a simple guy, falls for Nisha and gets attached to her. A series of events leads to their separation and Siddhu becomes a Rockstar. Why did they separate? What went wrong between them?

GRINGO, a dark comedy mixed with white-knuckle action and dramatic intrigue, explores the battle of survival for businessman Harold Soyinka (David Oyelowo) when he finds himself crossing the line from law-abiding citizen to wanted criminal.
A woman becomes involved with a man she barely knows. Complications develop during their sexual escapades.
Based on H.G. Bissinger's book, which profiled the economically depressed town of Odessa, Texas and their heroic high school football team, The Permian High Panthers.

Second lieutenant Miguel Aguirre's dream is to become a military pilot. After a bitter discussion with a superior Aguirre abandon his studies to be an officer. He leaves the officers military academy, but stays in Air Force as an NCO.
Munna is a college student who targets Khakha, a local gangster with whom he has a personal vendetta since childhood.

Raisa got a birthday present. A box with Bi Asuh in it, a maid who makes her grandma suffers and her sister missing. Raisa then asks her childhood friends help to find her sister and kicks Bi Asuh out of the house.
Freddy, a smalltime criminal on the run, takes shelter with a pastor and his daughter. Romance with the daughter ensues and causes problems.
A horror movie obsessed 11 year-old boy mourning the recent loss of his parents finds a real life slasher dying in his back yard.
A man accidentally runs down a young girl and has a curse placed on him by the girl's father, an occultist. He goes to a spiritualist for help in fighting the curse.
Jean-Claude Van Damme gets involved in a bank robbery with hostages situation and reflects about his life during it.

Yasu is a teenage wheelchair user. His grandmother and her granddaughter are truly cruel sadists, intent on subjecting trapped Yasu to the most violent treatment imaginable while the rest of his family is not around.
An action story set in the lawless zone trisected by Brazil, Argentina and Paraguay and centered on a DEA agent who is sent to the area against his will.
Greedy sailors capture a giant lizard off the coast of Ireland and sell it to a London circus. Then its mother shows up.

Austrian sex comedy about the head of the Meier Automobile company who's trying to sell his new talking sex cars to horny customers to have sex in them. He also has a sex robot modeled after his niece that helps customers test the cars.

Teen girl in 1963 finds freemasonry items in her late fathers briefcase including condoms and a book of rites. The book is taken to school and the girls form their own club. The mother finds the condoms and makes wrong assumption.

As a lifelong debt to a childhood friend, one man after experiencing a horrifying tragedy decides to participate in his genius friend's research. The man then awakens alone to discover it is now up to him to save mankind.
A small-time thief reforms after learning about the role played by his grandfather in building a dam.

Dying after being crowned Miss Texas Rose, Anabelle comes alive just before Elvis embalms her. He does his ailing dad's work. Anabelle later returns to the embalmer's farm to get away from her mom and be happy.

Kofi discovers there is a demonic entity named Hattie killing the children of Caroltyn. She fears her daughter Laila is next. In order to defeat Hattie, she has to battle her inner demons and grow strong in her faith.

Greedy Sonia has just lost her husband due to an overdose of sleeping pills. He left her a 300k life insurance policy but it doesn't cover death by suicide. She must prove at all costs that it was an accident.

In 17th-century Hungary, elderly widow Countess Elisabeth Nádasdy maintains her misleading youthful appearance by bathing in the blood of virgins regularly supplied to her by faithful servant Captain Dobi.

When the unplanned pregnancy of a small town high school teen and granddaughter of a renowned evangelist, triggers ghostly phenomena around a legendary haunted site, she must unearth the connection between the ghost's fate and her own.

In 2008, a reality television crew was dispatched to a small town in the United States to cover the story of an underdog high school hockey team on their way to the state finals. One by one, members of the cast and crew went missing.

The film follows life of Danny and Lace in a one day span as they struggle through life from crazy ex girlfriends to current girlfriends. Stoners to even more well Stoners. To truly discover more about themselves and the world around them.

Ajai, a talented musician, travels to Bengaluru with his band for a competition, and meets a vivacious young woman, who falls in love with him. Can he get over his past heartbreak and give love a second chance?
Raju, a honest and courageous young man faces a lot of challenges from a criminal minded person Seshu.

A group of party goers have trouble getting their boat ashore on a small island. The inhabitants of the island try to help, often with the help of an old sailor, and the results are absurd and hilarious.

movie_name: I Didn't Come Here to Die
description: The story of six young volunteers working on a humanitarian project in the woods. Horrific accidents, rash decisions and the unpredictability of human nature leads them all to the same disturbing conclusion. Volunteer work can be a killer.
A girl gets trapped inside a boys' hostel, which is under surveillance of a strict warden. Why has she entered the place and what happens next?

Johnny Rider is a kickboxing champion with a past. When he finds out a gang of drug dealers is responsible for the murder of his brother, Johnny becomes a man with only one thing on his mind...revenge.
Melvin, a high school student who doesn't fit in, becomes victim of a horrible prank, now he will seek revenge on all who wronged him... and even some who didn't.

Technology brings us closer. Or perhaps it brings strangers, a little too close. But how much can you really trust someone? With a new ride share service, you never know who you'll be getting in a car with. Or if you'll ever get out.
During the 1970s, U.S. Special Agent Cleopatra Jones proves to be an invaluable asset to the local police forces in the war on drugs.

A little girl dresses as a boy to steal so she can support herself and her guardian, who is like a father to her. One day while stealing, she meets a young man who gives her a job and they become great friends.
Ram Lakhan is the story of two brothers who part ways due to their ideological differences, but how they come to each other's rescue as the story unfolds.

An action film about the aftermath of the last military regime of Argentina, which was responsible for State terrorism and the cruel violence and oppression against the population, particularly in the case of the "Desaparecidos" ("missing" people).

While doing government funded research in the Pacific Ocean, an American Marine Biologist is attacked and swallowed by a 120 Ton Blue Whale and fights against all odds to survive the critical hours following, as the entire world watches.
Members of the Red Helmet biker girl gang wind up in Kyoto, where they get into conflict with other girl gangs and local yakuza thugs.

A small group of high school kids are tasked to make a documentary about a local business. The business quickly goes off the rails when the owners (Pam and Chester) discover that people dying increases their sales.

A wife gives birth to sextuplets, forcing the husband to sell three of their children due to poverty. When the wife finds out, she decides to leave her husband and travel abroad and many conflicts arise between siblings in the future.
Carter awakens to an empty, cold world deprived of all life. He quickly comes to realize that there is no escape from this nightmarish existence; not even in death.
A criminal organization that tortures people on an online webcam show, forcefully enters the life of two detectives.

movie_name: There Is No Pain in Paradise
description: Manuel's best friend dies of AIDS, then he begins a trip for the night in the city, finding a parade of wild characters.
Stephanie hears a strange sound coming from a stone she finds in the woods. Or maybe something under it.

Romina begins to fall in love with Valentin, a tourist on holiday in Costinesti with plans to become a musician. She helps Valentin to become an artist and, without realizing, he is starting to look a lot like someone from Romina's past.

When Clara starts her new job as a censor for a social media platform she is horrified by a murder played out on the platform that has gone viral. When she discovers her colleagues are hiding a dark secret she decides to take revenge.
A dedicated middle-aged cop must find the serial killer that preys on erotic models before his estranged daughter who's also in the photo shoot business becomes the killer's next victim.

1921: as Irish nationalists battle with British Forces, a young girl is torn between loyalty to her brother, unbeknownst to her an IRA leader, her fiance, a police inspector, and his comrade and rival in love, a British Army captain.
A crazed physician invents a death ray and threatens to destroy San Francisco unless he is paid $10 million.
The tale centers on an eccentric bag lady who rescues the stray cats of Venice and puts them on a boat to set sail for the New World.
The life of Fuat, a young writer, takes a completely different turn when a thief enters his boat one day. The thief is a beautiful woman named Gül.
A young couple travels to a deserted town to try and find their mysterious uncle, only to discover that ghosts are real and very dangerous.
When a paranormal research team investigates a haunting dramatized on a classic television series, they encounter a sinister supernatural force thought to be fictional.
Campus is a 2002 Indian Telugu film, directed by Dharma and produced by M-San. The film stars Venki, Rajdeep, Raja Shekhar and Enitha in lead roles. Music of the film was composed by Nawas.

The journey of Indian film industry's first stunt woman Reshma Pathan, it will trace the life of Reshma and her stint in movies as a body double for various actresses. Bidita Bag plays the lead role of feisty stunt-woman.
Two years after a tragic accident, six college girls are invited to a party inside an elaborate Halloween fun house. Once inside, the girls realize their hosts' intentions are not all fun and games.

Two sons, two daughters, grandsons, granddaughters, plans, records, a gramophone and a trunk get carried from one house to another every two months. There's also a plane tree underneath which they meet once every two months.
Karsh, an innovative businessman and grieving widower, builds a device to connect with the dead inside a burial shroud.

This time, it's a science fiction film titled, "2323 - the beginning", a Sathish Ramakrishnan initiative. Maayon, the protagonist, commences as a child prodigy, a pluviophile; an ingenious who can control weather.
A barkeeper saves a Yakuza boss' life and thus makes his way up in the organization. However his fear of nothing soon causes problems.

Jamie Klein is an out-of-work butch lesbian actor willing to try almost anything for a role. Femme, Butch, and Male Jamie all make appearances throughout this quirky, gender-bending comedy about struggling for success in Hollywood.
When a poor street girl inherits a crumbling corporate empire, she wonders if she has finally found her destiny.
A man abandons his wife and son and disappears. Years later his son grows up to become a cop. He is assigned to track down a gangster. He discovers that the gangster is his father.
Michael and Saravanan love Mamta though she loves Vijay. However, Vijay, who is brought up by a single father, hates the idea of love and rejects Mamta.
The tenants of the Sunset Towers must compete to learn who killed an eccentric millionaire and win a $20 million inheritance.

When challenged by a local gangster, a top martial arts student (Barry Chan) proves his skill and determination and defeats the thug. Now it's open warfare and fierce battles between the forces of good and evil.
Group of Mercenaries travel to the Philippines to recover a Red Cross Relief Crew when they are met with a disaster they didn't expect to encounter.
Violence in Korean High School, especially inside the WaSanGo (Volcano High). You won't be able to escape.
It's a story of Love Vs. Execrable. A path for smuggling but then to redemption, in the Golden Triangle of Thailand.
Follows Catwoman in an attempt to steal a priceless jewel. This puts her squarely in the crosshairs of both a powerful consortium of villains, Interpol and Batwoman.
When Alma returns home to help her family get their Native American heritage recognized, all she finds is the World-Famous Clown Motel that has been erected on their land.

From the legendary director, Emilio El Indio Fernandez, a powerful film of a woman fighting her rich established family to marry the man she loves. Starring Silvia Pinal, Amalia Mendoza and...                See full synopsis »

Police hero Joe Cameron and his family begin to get threatened from an unknown source. As evidence begins to stack up against Joe for murder and corruption, he descends into the Caribbean drug underworld to clear his name.
A methodical serial killer known as The Inferno Killer terrorizes the beautiful city of San Diego by murdering his victims according to the punishments within the 9 Circles of Hell.

Assassination at a charity event in Shanghai has 2 cops follow and fighting the assassin or follow a cute, Japanese woman pick-pocketing the victim. Drugs are involved. Chases with motorcycles, race-cars and helicopter follow.

A woman, an Arab immigrant in Canada lives a three-sided love story involving Sam, a fellow immigrant who writes her story and her love, left behind in the old country, but for whom her flame still flickers.
Shady town businessman Bolton seems to be the leader of the gang but even he takes his order from a higher authority who may have tried to take Marshal Corrigan's life.

The appearance of a Lady in Red results in a road accident. A head of a construction company finds himself in the afterlife, however, he is sent back to his body and becomes obsessed with the mystery brought on by a Messenger of God.

Newsreel cameraman Bob Adams heads to North Africa to cover an Arab uprising against the British. When he refuses to help his younger brother become a cameraman, Don becomes the dupe of less savory types posing in the trade.
The story of one of the most distinguished Navy SEALs in the history of the Naval Special Warfare Command.
IN THIS TRUE-TO-LIFE STORY, A YOUNG SOLDER IS TRAUMATIZED WHEN HE INADVERTENTLY KILLS INNOCENT CIVILIANS WHILE RAIDING A REBEL'S CAMP.
An account of the gangster Mahindra Dolas and his gang, which terrorized Mumbai City, and a massive war between Mumbai Police and gangs during 16 November 1991.

A peaceful accountant, after find again a love of youth, discovers a big embezzlement in the company where he works. Thanks to the fact, he ends up involving in a corruption network that supplies the Brazilian politician system .
Kidnap and Ransomed of his sister and forces him to return back to breaking the law and doing what he does best riding motorcycles and steeling money.
Poor Chow Ti lives in a demolished house with his son, Dicky. One day he heads to the junkyard and comes back with a green blob that turns out to be a cute, magical alien.
David Juneau turns into a one-man death squad when he discovers his brother has been brutally murdered by a group of criminals hell bent on finding his secrets.
In the Fall of 2006, Giorgio Frilli abandons Italy, in his mind run by the leftists and Berlusconi haters, to relocate to New York, where, he thinks, people love their president Bush.
After the violent loss of her young child, Jaq wages war against the vampires that plague Roach City. Her single-minded quest for vengeance morphs into a fight for the souls of all humanity.

Prithvi Kumar is an young IAS Officer who works as District Commissioner for Bellary District and whose honesty clashes with the illegal gaNi-dhaNigaLu (mining lords) and the corrupt politicians in the highest seats of power in Karanataka.
A violent crime unfolds when a backwoods babysitter agrees to help an abused mother escape her lunatic boyfriend.
A high school vigilante protects his community from the extortions of mobsters from a neighboring city.
A policewoman has always had the worst luck in love. On a trip to Malaysia, she finally meets the man of her dreams. However, her Perfect Man might not be all he appears to be.

The professional gambler Ross Hadley is the owner of a posh gaming establishment in the heart of New York. Hadley's main antagonist is his childhood friend Mike McGlennon who is determined to stop the gambling activities of Ross.

The evil local land baron forecloses on Angie's place, and she and her two daughters must leave and continue their life of crime. A reporter witnesses their heist of a bank, and helps them become folk legends by writing a story about them.

An elite operative in mourning strives to fulfill a promise to his fallen partner and recover a bioweapon controlled by a terrorist who is fighting to keep his legacy alive by executing his vengeful oath on New Year's Eve.
An ex-bounty hunter must head to Mexico to capture and bring back someone working with the cartel, but this bounty is not who he believes her to be.
A series of identical accidents kills racing drivers, but a dim-witted mechanic suspects they were not accidents.
A wealthy young man writes a play under a different name to prove to his overbearing mother that he can succeed on his own.

It follows Lucy as she's hired to write the script for a remake of a holiday movie. She joins a tour of the grounds and when she knocks an hourglass over, she finds herself transported back in time to 1946.

Medieval is an eleventh century tale of a band of international outlaws who are shipwrecked on the Iberian coast. Caught in a war between Spain, Portugal and the Moors, they defend a Monastic village against a savage Warlord.
In Copacabana, lesbian photographer Elvis is hired to deliver pizzas in the night shift on her motorcycle. Her first assignment is a delivery to the transvestite hairdresser Lady Madonna.
A former police detective, still recovering from his alcohol addiction, is seemingly drawn into L.A's criminal underworld after stumbling upon a local drug ring.
A Tyrannosaurus rex raised as a herbivore meets and takes care of an orphaned baby Ankylosaurus, all the while trying to fight his natural instincts of a predator and survive in the wild.
Ye-ji comes across mysterious water that enables her to lose weight and reshape her appearance. She finds her life is more in danger the more she desires to be beautiful.

After a winter storm strands five friends in a remote cabin with no power and little food, disorientation slowly claims their sanity as each of them succumbs to a fear that the snow itself may be contaminated or somehow evil.

In high hopes of finding an affluent husband for his charming young daughter, a bankrupt businessman takes a trip to a sun-kissed sea resort, and before long, a wealthy holidaymaker falls for her. However, is he truly who he claims to be?
Son grows up with father, leaves to go to big city in 1979. Father follows and tries to survive as a vampire in a modern world. Son finds girl, decides not to be a vampire anymore. Great ending!

After the rapture. God uprooted his faithful followers. Leaving everyone else in fear of an second coming. Meanwhile, those left behind have to survive amongst evil. The dead has risen to roam the earth.
Tulké is a day-laborer in a Nepalese mountain village. He struggles to reclaim his lost aristocratic identity, while a violent revolution disrupts every aspect of village life.
Spending the night in her car, a newly-homeless woman wrestles with exhaustion, her crumbling marriage, and the threat of mysterious, masked strangers.
Koottu is a Compus love story. Hari (Richard) and Balu (Aravindan) who are students and buddies in a college.

When Jiang Ziya violates the code of the gods, he is banished to the mortal realm. He is saved by a kind young woman Qing Luan but disaster follows when the river god breaks the curse and starts slaughtering the locals.
Beto the leader of the car club "the golden knights" falls in love with Kim, but Hector also have an interest in Kim.

The story revolves around the lives of 3 young friends, who struggle to establish themselves in the real world. They are working to make it big until they get caught up in a certain situation, only to get rescued by a common friend.
A rancher and a refined lady from the city fall in love each other. But the 200-years-fight between their families, will threaten their romantic relationship.
To help his discouraged son get through college, a funloving and obnoxious rich businessman decides to enter the school as a student himself.
When one of the QueenPin's team members is gunned down in her hometown, she must return to show her rivals she still has the throne.
A mother and her young son move to a new town only to find out that it was the sight of a horrific close encounter many years earlier, and the entity is still there.

A spoof of buddy cop movies where two very different cops are forced to team up on a new reality based television cop show, while tracking down the manufacturer and distributor of an illegally made semi-automatic firearm.
Scott's idea of the perfect woman is one that comes with no baggage. But when he meets Jessica, he realizes he is traveling with a few suitcases of his own.
Seven strangers on a Hollywood movie studio tour are trapped inside an infamous House of Horror and forced to tell their most terrifying stories to get out alive.
Dope Boys is a new animation action crime film about a young hustler from Miami in a gritty world of drugs and money, a rags to riches story about his life in the projects and his rise to wealth.

When an accidental death takes the life of a young boy, the family moves to a country home for a fresh start, only to discover there is something much worse than than their memories and guilt living in the attic.

movie_name: Jason Still Lives Part II - The Ski Resort Murders
description: Jason Myers is back and now in Colorado on a murdering spree during a blizzard that leaves Sheriff Cobb and Deputy Cheeks on the hunt for the madman.
Made up of nine shorts, Vore Gore (2021) is an anthology that explores the links between sex and violence, consumption and capitalism all under the umbrella theme of voraphilia.
Unsuspecting teens fight for their lives when a hungry bull shark hunts them in a murky, very remote reservoir.
It is the end of days as the zombies are fully adapted, our heroes must find a scientist surviving in an 80's fun park and then journey to the place where it all began, The Laboratory.

Five juvenile lost causes are sent to the Everglades where a war veteran tries to reform them using survival tactics. Their new skills and resolve are tested when a Miami drug lord targets them for trying to clean up their neighborhood.

movie_name: The Strippers and the Vampire's Daughter
description: When reserved model Judy Green inherits a seedy LA strip club from her estranged mother, she discovers too late that the strippers are a vampire coven who want her as their next queen.

Prequel to the first Missing In Action, set in the early 1980s it shows the capture of Colonel Braddock during the Vietnam war in the 1970s, and his captivity with other American POWs in a brutal prison camp, and his plans to escape.

This movie follows the story of the 3rd President of Indonesia, B.J. Habibie, young life when he was studying in the university in Germany, his struggle life as a student, and his love life before he eventually dates Ainun.

When a group of friends meet at a club in Miami for a final farewell after graduation, a wealthy couple invite them to an after party at a secluded private island. The friends soon realize that the island has more then just Islanders.
Caterina is a young amnesiac girl, who're in a little town without remember why she went there. She will join forces with Tommaso Carta, a novelist, to find out the mystery about her identity.

movie_name: The Thief Who Came to Dinner
description: A computer programmer decides to become a thief. And when he starts making waves an insurance investigator hounds him. He also meets a woman who becomes his accomplice.
A Married Man fells in love with another married women; where they cannot be together but can love each other till the end of their life.

A short fan film that bridges the DCAU (Young Justice mainly) and DCCU, a "what if" story where the Flash visits Bart Allen first, rather than Bruce Wayne, to help prevent Superman from taking over Earth.
Two dark forces entangle an 18 year old American gamer. She resides with an evil entity influencing her animus towards all. Then enters Jin.
A journalist takes his son with him to investigate pirate activity off the coast of Florida. But he gets stranded on a mysterious island--where he might not be alone.
Devaraj takes a job at the same factory where his father, retired Captain Ramakrishnan, is killed mysteriously while he is on duty. After he starts working, he must face many challenges.
An impromptu Bachelorette party week in Bermuda leads to an unsuspected find at a abandoned ship wreck. The women enter into a haunted reality that could change their lives forever.
Bee is falling in love with her senior surgeon co-worker. But his girlfriend who recently died in an accident isn't quite ready to give him up yet.

FBI Agents Luke Murphy and Jessica Rosen must resort to creative and unethical methods to combat Noah Moretti and his criminal crew who have partnered with a major cartel to traffic young women and children.
Eight depictions of horror twisted into one feature film with unpredictable turns at the end of each segment.

After losing contact with a clandestine energy research facility, a powerful venture capitalist contracts a private team of elite military operatives to retrieve a physicist who holds the key to an unprecedented alternate energy source.

A girl runs away from home seeking shelter. Soon, she meets a musician who is also looking for cheap accommodation; they agree to stay together pretending to be husband and wife, but things get murky with the arrival of two people.
Trapped in a first person, slasher virtual reality video game, a girl must learn to do battle with and defeat the slasher or she will die in the real world.
A group of 5 people trying to hide from a terrible threat hanging over them. But they can not hide themselves.
HUMOROUS ELEMENTS PEPPER THIS VEHICLE FOR TAMIYA, MOST REVOLVING AROUND THE VARIOUS DISGUISES HE ASSUMES.

After a failed marriage, Masha retreats to the sanctuary of her humble profession as a translator of serious literature. Financial difficulties force her to accept an offer to interpret during a seminar held by an English puppeteer.
A tongue-in-cheek film involving two rural yakuza clans in post-WW2 times who form baseball teams to resolve their differences. The film seems to go on a bit long.
A young woman becomes emotionally and romantically dependent on the man who foils her suicide attempt.
A rich girl steals her dad's Rolls Royce and heads off to Las Vegas to get married. However, her angry parents, a jealous suitor, and a bunch of reward seekers are determined to stop her.
Two siblings attempt to avenge the death of their parents. But the sister believes in the law while the brother believes in administering justice himself.

Petros is a 35-year-old successful chef and vinyl collector. Zoi is a romantic girl who designs and sews children's costumes. Their two worlds will be called into question when they come across a bookstore in downtown Athens.
Three brothers smuggle arms, and drugs from Mexico, into the US, thru Brownsville, Texas border crossing. All three are very successful smugglers with a heart.
Balan, a pilot, is cheated on by his girlfriend Rekha, who is an air hostess. He is in for a shock when he meets her after many years.
When a code that could save the world is secretly injected into a member of the 5 Elements clan, the fate of humanity and the world become intertwined with his fight for survival.
The Leprechaun returns once again, when a group of girls unwillingly awaken him after they tear down a cabin so that they can build a new sorority house.

Intersecting fortunes of two young men, Billy and Minor Daemon, who share an extraordinary gift for virtual reality gaming and go through a series of nightmarish events, including slavery, crime, and incarceration.
Two exorcists capture their work on video and upload it to YouTube. They come to the attention of a TV show that wants to boost its ratings. However, the studio crew remain skeptical.

Khoon Bahaa Ganga Mein is a story of a girl who has faced several problems and has seen bloodshed since her childhood. The film shows her struggle from an innocent carefree little girl to become the leader of the dacoits.
After her father forbids her from seeing her boyfriend, Pring commits suicide and comes back as a vengeful ghost that begins to enact her murderous revenge.

Young man inherits small fortune from his old uncle, on condition he lives in the old man's house for a time. Soon the uncle's spirit begins to manifest itself through the nephew's personality, requiring the presence of an exorcist.
A leading film actress is controlled by her producer who even refuses to let her get married. Therefore, she seeks the help of a lawyer who may be able to help her.
Two years after a women is killed in a fatal car crash, the trio of teenagers responsible for her death are suddenly being murdered - one by one.

Dr Eddy, Dr Suzana, Luthya and Vanessa arrive in Kampung Parit Polong to solve the mystery of a curse that has befallen the village. Is it related to a shaman who had been wrongfully maligned by the villagers in the past?

Unable to pay off a debt to a ruthless gang, a club hostess falls victim to their leader. Brimming with vengeance, the ghost of the innocent girl, with the help of her friends from the club, attempts to seek revenge against her murderers.

A group of best friends are bought together by a mere single commitment made many years ago to one another which results in taking down the biggest impossible yet suicidal heist ever seen in modern day 21st century.
Five best friends who came from a foreign country studied in Netherlands. There they struggled with money and a lot of things but their friendship was a journey worth more than money.
Two fledgling criminals kidnap a pizza delivery guy, strap a bomb to his chest, and inform him that he has mere hours to rob a bank or else...

In the 1960s, superpowered humans Charles Xavier and Erik Lensherr work together to find others like them, but Erik's vengeful pursuit of an ambitious mutant who ruined his life causes a schism to divide them.

movie_name: Variations on a High School Romance
description: Four years in the lives of five high school students and the trials and tribulations they face while falling in love and growing up.
Laurie Strode, now the dean of a Northern California private school with an assumed name, must battle the Shape one last time, as the life of her own son hangs in the balance.
Covers the Ill fated Operation "Market Garden", as seen through the eyes of Major Geoffrey Powell, who was assigned to the Parachute Regiment in 1942.
A group of moms celebrating ladies' night are forced to fight for their lives when their quiet town is overrun by a hungry horde of flesh-eating corpses.
A man receives a Ninjitsu death threat and needs to enlist in the aid of someone trained in the art of the Ninja to catch the would be assassin.

Lawyer Radmilo, the most eligible bachelor in his small town of Palanka, has spent years in love with Ljiljana, refusing all offers of marriage. He wants to marry Ljiljana, but she plans to marry Momchila.
Noah is chosen by God to undertake a momentous mission before an apocalyptic flood cleanses the world.
A crime lord ascends to power and becomes megalomaniacal while a maverick police detective vows to stop him.

movie_name: The School for Good and Evil
description: Best friends Sophie and Agatha find themselves on opposing sides of an epic battle when they're swept away into an enchanted school where aspiring heroes and villains are trained to protect the balance between Good and Evil.
In Paris, a young woman runs away from a reform school, joins a pickpocket academy, and finds herself falling for the handsome diplomat she's been blackmailed into stealing from.
Marlon has a crush on Jessica (running for high school senior class president). Jessica wants to attend Ramsey College. Marlon wants to go wherever Jessica is going. Problem: low SAT score.
Mahtab and Ava are classmates in their second year of college studying engineering. The story begin when they and other classmates go on a trip to Esfahan.

Two LantinX ex-NYPD officers turned P.I.'s inadvertently witness a crime and get sent to a small town to lay low. But things aren't as they seem and they have to work together to solve the mystery/ save the day.

When Dr. Horatio Kane is kidnapped and is forced to create an army of martial artists his daughter Kandy Kane is the only one who can help. She enlists the help of Steve Chase to save her father and the day.
A woman making a documentary about psychics searches for answers surrounding the disappearance of her sister.
A guest tries to stay inside the house of a man who can't kill him unless he's outside, because of believing guest to be equal to God.
The young warrior Son Goku sets out on a quest, racing against time and the vengeful King Piccolo, to collect a set of seven magical orbs that will grant their wielder unlimited power.

When her car breaks down in Hawaii, Beatrice Cooper a middle aged women, has a chance meeting with a handsome man half her age. They bicker, they fight, they have sex and he falls madly in love. Will true love win against the odds ?
The young Chef Ah Sheng struggles to grow as a professional chef in an industry where jealousy, love and money is always a temptation
Romantic Comedy about two girls who find love in the most unexpected places in modern-day Mexico City.
A vacation to Ibiza with many parties. Part of a family lives on the island and the rest is visiting, which causes much drama.
A stunt man is involved accidentally in a culture relics hustling crime and fight for himself in a series of dangerous adventures.

The drug war on the U.S.-Mexico border has escalated as the cartels have begun trafficking terrorists across the US border. To fight the war, federal agent Matt Graver re-teams with the mercurial Alejandro.
Detective Reba Rosemary teams up with FBI Agent Samantha Sage to solve a series of murders from 1984.
A young opera singer finds her career stalled because of her cold and passionless performances, until she finds romance with a handsome admirer.
Young women start a babysitting business until one of their friends dies. Years later, they go their separate ways, but someone starts killing them one at a time on Halloween.
In a school full of perverse teachers, where you earn grades by having sex, Nancy is the only honest person. But when she, despite studying a lot, fails her final exam... it's time for revenge!
At the request of their daughter, a separated couple has to live together for thirty days after the ex-wife comes from a long psychiatric hospitalization.
Jean Servais and Omar Sharif are explorers searching for uranium in the Arabian desert. They run into spies, thieves and two attractive mysterious women played by Juliette Greco and Luciana Paluzzi.
