Four heartbroken women come together and form an atrocious organization to rid as many womanizers as possible.
A dying prisoner tells the prison therapist about $8,500,000 stolen mob money hidden under a basement floor. A prisoner overhears it and breaks out. Who gets the money.
The film is about a man called Sannasi, who heads Thara Thappattai, a Karagattam troupe. Tharai Thappattai exposes how this art is slowly dying, and why we are all the worse for it.

After her boyfriend's death, a successful executive finds some unfinished scripts in the dead man's computer, and decides to make a film of them. Her relationship with the world of movie-making is going to change her life.
Only a very few in the White House know he exists. To all others he's an urban legend, a modern day assassin.

movie_name: Danger Zone III: Steel Horse War
description: An outlaw-biker named Reaper battles an ex-lawman named Wade Olsen while searching the desert for a cache of gold buried by renegade Confederate soldiers.

In a chalet that stands alone on a high hill that overlooks a camp in Sinai, lives Shady and Laila who seem deeply in love with one another living in their dream home. One day Laila wakes up and there seems to be no trace of shady.
Several friends trace their adolescence lived in 1997 in Albania, a period in which the country went through a dramatic social and economic crisis.
A man and woman in love are separated due to the machinations of the woman's mother. But years later, their paths cross once again.
A group of online chatroom friends find themselves haunted by a mysterious, supernatural force using the account of their dead friend.
What's life movie tries to answer questions in very beautiful way. Never give up attitude of main leads makes movie worth watching.
Revolves around a fabled Trinethri Idol, and how it affects several lives in the course of its journey from the 15th century to modern times.
A bandit leader kidnaps the wife of the policeman who killed his sister, but later falls in love with her.
Obsessed with living up to her dead father's legacy a young sheriff finds her mettle tested when locals are found ripped to shreds.
After a crazed farmer/zoo owner kidnaps a traveling couple, their family, a maid, a paleontologist and an amazing deer must work together to rescue them before they are fed to a dinosaur.
A story of teenage romance with a hard-hitting message that nothing in life should be taken for granted, especially love and the ones you love.
A man in search of his past, and a woman who lives in the moment, are brought together when they pursue the origins of a stray parrot in this comedic and romantic drama.
Based on the real-life love story of Moideen and Kanchanamala, which happened in the 1960s in the backdrop of Calicut.
When a gay man brings his fiancee home to meet his family, their lives are turned upside down when his aunt asks a hypnotist to make him believe he's straight.
Lan Tin-lung, master of the Liangyi Castle, calls upon all upright swordsmen to help wipe out the notorious Lunar Sect.

Mae (Nirina Zubir) and her friends have big obsessions to become big people but instead, they all end up becoming something that they didn't dream of. Be they frustrated young people who spent days together in a hut on the edge of river.

Letters to Ganesha is a romantic comedy indie-crossover film about Richie, an American writer struggling to overcome his writer's block. His long-time girlfriend Katie surprises Richie with a trip for them to India during the Ganesha festival hoping to remove obstacles.
True story of a transatlantic business correspondence about used books that developed into a close friendship.

A very young chemist invests a formula that can be revolutionize the whole market. At the beginnings nobody care the young chemist. Then competition is started to capture a formula. One woman changes everything.

movie_name: To Love or Not to Love
description: Elton had a mysteriously affair with Sia, Casey turned herself into a love expert after the heartbreak of Elton's cheat. The unfortunate couple accidentally encounters each other after 10 years.
Before taking off on a kamikaze suicide bombing mission, Second Lieutenant Nagayo arranges a marriage between his girlfriend Etsuko and Second Lieutenant Akashi, his navy officer friend.

A couple in a troubled marriage locate a meteorite, initiating an encounter with a mysterious creature. Their lives are turned upside down by the discovery of the creature, which is a source of both pleasure and destruction.
Peter is a fun loving person and his younger brother is college going youth. Things go head over heels for Peter as he falls in love with Devi (Radhika), a person who he is related to.
Mac McPherson is framed for murder and sentenced to prison at the Black Creek Prison Farm. He must escape to prove his innocence and find the real killer.
The fiancée of a brilliant surgeon is decapitated in a car accident, so he must keep her head alive while he searches for a suitable body in time for their wedding.
"Enough" - Reet loves her longtime friend Reine, but she is disrupted by their long separations. With Reine his job comes first.
In seventeenth-century England, Amber St. Clair aims to raise herself from country girl to nobility, and succeeds, but loses her true love in the process.

A work-obsessed senator is taken hostage on a ship hijacked by high-tech pirates, and her only ally to stop them from igniting a global economic meltdown is a man she hasn't seen in 35 years--her father. Inspired by actual events.
Shankar is the son of a corrupt businessman. When his sister is married against her wishes, she escapes living with Simon, a poor man whom she loves. The society strongly objects to this union.

A Dutch teenager is unaware of who or where he is. Police chase him. He gets a notebook describing himself as a student who helped a cute girl hack, got caught, and was punished with special training camp. What happened to him then?
Brothers Will and Larry along with their childhood best friend Charlie, always dreamed of going to Mars; ironically a tragedy or two just might make this dream a reality.
Story follows Jung So-Yool who dreams of becoming the best singer during the time of Japanese occupation of Korea.
Mild sibling rivalry between identical twin sisters Sylvina and Martina, intensifies when one of the girls tricks the other's sweetheart into proposing to the wrong twin.
Two security guards travel to a village to retrieve some stolen jewellery, and there they encounter feisty villagers and a ghost.
"Skeletons in the Closet" is the titular late-night, horror anthology television series featuring The Widow and her dead husband, Charlie.
Based on a traditional Japanese ghost story, the movie follows a man who falls deeply in love with a mysterious woman, only to find she belongs to the world of the dead.
A centuries old vampiress comes to the South and tells of her epic life story as a slave while she inflicts havoc on plantation owners in her quest to find her true love.
Janardhan Jakhar chases his dreams of becoming a big Rock star, during which he falls in love with Heer.
Two students marry in secret despite objections from the woman's mother. In a mosque in Hamburg, they promise to stay together, but the man commits to an act that will shake the whole world.
Saranam Gacchami is a 2017 Telugu language action-romance film, which deals with the sensitive topic of caste reservation in India.

Veteran-turned-mercenary Toorop takes the high-risk job of escorting a woman from Russia to America. Little does he know that she is host to an organism that a cult wants to harvest in order to produce a genetically modified Messiah.
A married professor and his married student find themselves in a dilemma when they are attracted to each other despite sharing a good equation with their respective partners.
When a producer misbehaves with actress Surekha, her friend Adi kills him. Surekha approaches Prasad, a lawyer who loves her, to save him, but unknown to them, Adi is playing evil mind games.
Movie star Grayson Kane is about to bring the hottest new comic book superhero to the big screen, but first, he must get the creator's approval...and she is no pushover.

movie_name: Along With the Gods: The Last 49 Days
description: In the afterlife, one guardian helps a man through his trials, while his two colleagues help a former guardian on earth.
An angry and alcoholic matriarch tyrannizes her spoiled, grown-up, children during an unwanted family get-together, where someone begins killing them one by one.
Beginning with the strange and gruesome murders of two teens en route to a Halloween party, all their lives are disrupted when an evil man named Desmond Samuelson arrives.

Dos hermanos ambiciosos tienen el deseo de hacer lo que sea con tal de salir adelante. Deciden tomar puestos de trabajo con el hombre mas poderoso de la region, y arriesgaran todo para lograr su mision.. incluyendo sus propias vidas.
40 years ago, a man made a pact with a witch in exchange for the life of his granddaughter when she turned 15. Now the time has come, and the family must fight.

It's a soaking wet day with rain pouring down and one of the best things to do is to go seek refuge in a great old cinema. There's just one problem: a murderer is on the loose and he also has taken refuge there.
Bwiza is young woman who has to choose between two men, a successful businessman from the city, who has bright future, or her childhoods friend who has nothing to offer but sweet nothings.
Dinda who escapes the Kuntilanak (female vampire ghost) terror, without the agreement of Aunt Donna, intends to meet someone who is believed to be her biological mother, Karmila.

movie_name: Wizards of the Lost Kingdom II
description: Three kingdoms have been overtaken by three evil lords and only a teenage boy with magical powers can restore peace to the land.
Two inseparable sister's visit to a remote mine town turns into a mind-bending fight for survival against menaces both human and supernatural.
A rouge news reporter looks into the murder of the District Attorney, who was killed after he started an investigation.
In a small town in North Carolina, a group of friends are stalked by a mysterious, machete wielding maniac.
Jealous piano teacher Orville Spooner sends his beautiful wife, Zelda, away for the night while he tries to sell a song to famous nightclub singer Dino, who is stranded in town.
During a long space war, the lives of two wounded enemies become dependent on their ability to forgive and to trust.
At the 1956 Olympic Games in Melbourne, the Hungarian water polo team faces off against the Russians in what will become known as one of the bloodiest matches in the sport's history.
The fastest and most eccentric driver on the legendary 1920s Bentley motor racing team convinces a misfit heiress to back his desperate scheme to beat the Germans in the Grand Prix of the century.

movie_name: I Love You, Don't Touch Me!
description: The story of a 25 year old virgin girl, looking for the right boyfriend, not realizing that "the one" has been next to her for many years.
In efforts to construct perfect android killing machines in a war against China, UK scientists exceed their goal and create a sentient robot.
A compilation of 3 short horror stories. 'Desire to Kill' directed by Kenji Nakanishi, 'Meinichi' and 'Cruel Kidnapping' directed by Tomoyuki Akashi.
A young writer moves into a house that is believed to be haunted, despite numerous warnings, but strange encounters force him to investigate the truth behind the myths.
The passengers and crew of a ship on a scuba diving trip in the Caribbean stray into the famed Bermuda Triangle, and mysterious and deadly things start happening.
A devastating heatwave is rising in Los Angeles, causing tensions to increase as the city teeters on the brink of hysteria.
After the events of "The Films of Jason Day-Boisvert" Jay tries to move on with life as normal as he can, but in the end he is haunted again and must film the movie "The Ghost Footage 3".
A coffee grower, single at almost 40, goes to the city in search of the only thing lacking in his life: love.

movie_name: Fate Grand Order: The Grand Temple of Time
description: The Chaldea Organization must deal with the Grand Temple of Solomon, the King of Magic, which has come to destroy the world.
An adventurous young girl in Florida gets herself lost in the Everglades and finds terror and excitement, as well as the rivalry of two men in love with her.
A New York Times travel writer comes to Tel Aviv after suffering a tragedy. The energy of the city and his relationship with a younger man brings him back to life.
When a city is burnt to the ground its survivors set forth to rebuild it concealing any scars it left behind.
A story of a father and son, two veterans from two very different Wars, helping each other to get through each day, and heal the wounds of War.

A broken down van strands a group of college students in the middle of the desert. Forced to hike their way out, they unwittingly enter a sacred Indian burial ground...A place they should have left alone.
The relationships between a veteran marshal, his bride-to-be, a rookie and his fiancée are severely tested when the young carabiniere is temporarily sent to a distant town.

Three best friends go out for a night on the town. But what starts out as an innocent night of drinking and recreational drugs quickly turns into a game of cat and mouse as the girls learn who they should and shouldn't trust.

17 year old Oliver meets his dream girl. Emotions are quickly reciprocated, making Oliver's dream a reality. But a lot of challenges arise separating them. Despite all the challenges it dawns on Oliver who is right for him.

When a widower hires a New Age caregiver to look after his beloved Spanish speaking grandmother-in-law and infant daughter, they all discover the deeper connection between grief, life, family and love.
"First Strike" pilots have the mission of destroying nuclear arms that have fallen into the hands of bandits.

Mo, a practicing Muslim living in West Hollywood, is learning to navigate life post heartbreak. Enter Kal, an All-American guy who surprises Mo by offering to break fast with him during the holy month of Ramadan.
A British East India Trading Company assassin seeks to redeem his past by thwarting a plot against a young nation's hope for freedom.

On the night of November 13, 1974, Ronald DeFeo, Jr. took a high-powered rifle and murdered his entire family as they slept. At his trial, DeFeo claimed that "voices" in the house commanded him to kill. This is their story.

movie_name: No More Love No More Death
description: The prequel to Taylor Wong's With or Without You finds Prince being raised as a trained assassin by his "father." Meanwhile, he falls in love with Tweedy, a singer who teaches him how to love.
An unofficial sequel to Kefir-Profit's unofficial Terminator sequel - This time featuring Superman, Rambo, Neo from the Matrix, Harry Potter and the evil Agent 007.

"Romeo's Distress" is a Weird, Shakespearean, Gothic, Horror-Thriller that tells a story of a boy name James, his unrequited love for a girl named Jane, and her father's sadistic (yet dutiful) response to it all.
Five girls stray from society on the hunt for something more special...you can find them if you follow the sound.
A young professional with a beautiful girlfriend finds himself in a crossroad when he falls in love with a new neighbor who just moved into his building.
A new trail of adventure sweeps across the screen as the "Tres Muskiteras" give you - THRILLING ACTION, STUNNING DRAMA, STRANGE ROMANCE.

DIRTY, a 90 minute action film based on true events. The story begins where two best friends (Christopher and Johnny) who grow up together from childhood hoping to live out their dreams. ...                See full synopsis »
In the midst of the bland suburbia of Australia a dark force is growing. An ancient evil that has terrorized the world for millennia has awoken.

CIA trained detective Solomon King has to use all of his dirty tricks and experiences to get revenge on the person responsible for the murder of his girlfriend. A trail leads him to a desert in the Middle East.
A biologist and his girlfriend must contend with the intrigues of his employer and the employer's daughter. The daughter of the employer wants to marry the botanist and hopes to separate the couple.
Sammo plays a Tai Chi master who must teach his son (Timmy Hung Tin Ming) how to kick some serious butt, after the son is bullied by a karate master (Carl Ng).
Desperate to find the perfect man, friends throw a party and invite all the eligible guys they know.
A young Nigerian man on the verge of being in an arranged marriage, suddenly questions his situation after an encounter with a stunning Latin woman, who is also about to be married.

Rishi Ram and his sister Rithu Ram, both of whom are martial arts instructors settled in Rishikesh. Their peaceful life is turned chaotic when they cross paths with a notorious martial arts gang, leading to a spree of furious violence.
A fun-loving couple, finding that they died and are now ghosts, decide to shake up the stuffy lifestyle of a friend of theirs.
When a poor guest arrives early to a creepy manor deep in the woods, he is greeted by the Lover's Grimm and told stories to pass the time before the party begins.

An aspiring fashion designer is mysteriously able to enter the 1960s, where she encounters a dazzling wannabe singer. But the glamour is not all it appears to be and the dreams of the past start to crack and splinter into something darker.

Charlotte accepts a job at a large country home to watch a couple's cat whilst they are away. However the Gothic old house may contain more than just a cat, as seemingly supernatural forces take hold of Charlotte's mind and body.

On a fishing boat at sea, a 60-year old man has been raising a girl since she was a baby. It is agreed that they will get married on her 17th birthday, and she is 16 now. They live a quiet and secluded life, renting the boat to day fishermen and practicing strange divination rites. Their life changes when a teenage student comes aboard...
When their computer hacker friend accidentally channels a mysterious wireless signal, a group of co-eds rally to stop a terrifying evil from taking over the world.
A family's serene beach vacation turns to chaos when their doppelgängers appear and begin to terrorize them.
Three girls. Two rooms. One diabolical psychopath with an axe. Zero chance of survival. Welcome to Motel Hell.
A young social worker and her partner are sent to investigate a case of child abuse in rural Alabama but soon learn that a sinister entity may behind the family's dark history..
A young woman who suffers a strange disease must travel to a mysterious island in South America, where the myths and the reality do not have differences.
Survivors of a global pandemic document their attempts to fight a roving band of zombies in this loose follow up to 2018's Virus Of The Dead
"ISI and DISI, alto voltaje" (High Voltage) deals with the extreme difficulties human beings encounter when attempting to be genuine and daring to fulfill their dreams and convictions.
The Office of Scientific Investigation sends A-Men agents to investigate reports of unusual magnetic activity in various communities.

movie_name: The Thin Man: A Face in the Darkness
description: A group of friends set out to create a YouTube video which will prove or disprove the Thin Man urban legend. Things quickly turn dangerous as they discover there is more to the myth than they bargained for.
An admirer of women falls from the balcony and dies while trying to see a woman sunbathing in the nude. In the moments before his death, all his erotic memories pass before his eyes.
A crew decides on making a documentary about the famous baron palace, but after trying to get the authorization of filming inside the palace, they fail to do so. And try to come with new ways
A gambling hall owner relocates from New Orleans to Chicago and entertains his patrons with hot jazz by Louis Armstrong, Billie Holiday, Woody Herman, and others.

Sammo is a single father / scam artist that uses his son in his scams. He's an alcoholic with gambling problems that likes to fight. He gets arrested and the woman who arrests him looks after his son while he's in jail.
Searching for a cure to Alzheimer's disease, a group of scientists on an isolated research facility become the prey, as a trio of intelligent sharks fight back.
In order to move on with her life, a young girl struggles to overcome the physical, emotional and mental torment she's faced growing up.

A mother of two who inherits a house is confronted with murderous intruders on the first night in their new home and fights for her daughters' lives. Sixteen years later when the daughters reunite at the house, things get really strange.
Parapsychologist Dr. Elise Rainier faces her most fearsome and personal haunting yet, as she is drawn back to her ghostly childhood home where the terror began.
Constantly dreaming of being killed by a faceless killer every night, Phuong Anh's life is disturbed. However, even more horrifying happens, when the Faceless Killer comes into life and pursues her.

movie_name: The Most Wanted Gun in the West
description: In the summer of 1891, a mysterious gun winds up on the homestead of Gehrig Russell, who must fight off an unrelenting attack by a posse of cowboys from hell bent on retrieving the cursed pistol.
When her twin sister dies in an area called Windsor Lake, a young woman teams up with a local cop to try to find out what happened.
After a kidnapping attempt, three female assassins and their hostage becomes trapped in an establishment run by a ruthless mobster and his army of killers and thugs with chaotic results.
A romantic comedy centered on three different couples with one thing in common: infidelity. Their stories connect over a long weekend in New York and Paris.

An assassin flashes between a nightmarish dream and her reality at a secret underground organization. When her latest mission involves killing a grieving mother, she discovers her target is closer to home than she realizes-much closer.

Suresh Sinha, a famous director, discovers star potential in Shanti, a woman he stumbled into one rainy evening, and casts her as the lead in a film. In a twist of fate, Shanti becomes a superstar and Suresh faces a decline in his career.

A Rome policewoman teams up with a British Interpol agent to find a crafty serial killer who plays a taunting game of cat-and-mouse with the police by abducting and killing young women and showing it over an Internet web cam.
Three young women who crash their car during a rainstorm are taken in by a bizarre family at their large, rural estate.

A dark twisted apocalyptic shocker about a group of humans and demons who must band together to fight for the fate of humanity. When an ancient prophecy unleashes an evil spirit, hell is brought upon the world.

Wayne and Biggs grow up together on the tough and dangerous streets of Kingston, Jamaica. Eventually moving to Miami, they begin a ruthless climb to the top of a criminal enterprise as they aggressively take control of the Jamaican mob.

-Before the flood, a stranger arrives in a city where the inhabitants indulge in drinking, lust, looting and torture. Bewitched by a magician, he searched in vain for an ideal young girl before raising the wrath of the gods.
A teenage boy obsessed with UFOs discovers a mysterious light in the sky. Soon, his whole family finds themselves targets of the supernatural.
Sumitra travels to Pandharpur to find a ray of hope, after Sangram killed her husband and son and took over their business.

Azia, lead homicide detective returns home after a year in the midst of an escalating murder case. She finds herself entangled in a web of intrigue and deception amongst those in her inner circle as she struggles to uncover the truth.

Single-girl anxiety causes Kat Ellis to hire a male escort to pose as her boyfriend at her sister's wedding. Her plan, an attempt to dupe her ex-fiancé, who dumped her a couple years prior, proves to be her undoing.

After the loss of her father, Christine decides she just wants to be alone for Christmas. She decides to find a place each Christmas to be away from everyone including family and friends that only she knows.
After being attacked and left for dead by her boss, the only way a woman can live is by becoming an unstoppable weapon.

When a landowner rapes a poor farmer's sister, the farmer demands that the landowner marry his sister. When the landowner refuses, the siblings disguise themselves as wealthy foreigners in order to marry the landowner and his sister.
The Thunderhawk team is back, this time they must protect an cosmic child from aliens who have come to earth to hunt it down.
Conducting a series of experiments in his makeshift home-lab, a skeptic IT worker tries to cure his harrowing hearing impairment.
After a tragedy befalls Gelimp's family, he now must journey out into the unknown with a group of brave warriors, heading into an adventure where some may not return.

On the night before his wedding, Ricco Alvarez is faced with a tough situation. His wife has stolen from Crime Lord, Brutus McDelta. Ricco has a choice to make; suffer the wrath of McDelta, or activate Operation Lima.
Based on the brief life of the Mexican composer of the famous waltz, "Over the Waves" ("Sobre las Olas"), Juventino Rosas.
A FORMER RAGS-TO-RICHES KANTO BOY FAILS TO REALIZE THAT SUCCESS IS NOT MEASURED BY ONE'S BANK ACCOUNT.
Dashratha, a righteous lawyer, leads a happy life with his wife, son and daughter who gets a job after college. However, trouble begins when his daughter falls in love with her employer.
An ER doctor teams up with an assassination target to rescue his wife, held hostage by corrupt criminals and, in the process, uncovers a conspiracy.
A toy shop owner/hero and his assistant/heroine battle a leather-clad vixen and her minions to prevent them from acquiring the pieces of a mystical skull.
A young graduate student is tormented by a stalker who hacks into her electronic devices and monitors her every move.
Three bumbling criminals have been trying to get their hands on the computerized control system of Mr. Twister, a talking monster truck with a mind of its own.
Two teenage runaways embark on a dangerous journey together in an attempt to escape their turbulent pasts.

A psychological thriller about Carla and Greg Forrest - a loving young couple preparing for the birth of their beautiful daughter. However, baby Amy's birth comes with a spirit and danger that no one could have imagined.

A suburban woman fights to be believed as she finds herself stalked by a threatening figure who returns to her house night after night. When she can't get help from those around her, she is forced to take matters into her own hands.
An unsuspecting courier has been the messenger between terrorist cells. Unfolding a plot to bomb a building he teams up with a cop and uses his knowledge of the Big Apple to stop the bombing.

When motorcycle junky, Anna, discovers her father dead along with a fistful of new enemies and only a palm-full left of amphetamines. She gets revenge blazing past cycle gangs and blistering her bike from Juarez to L.A. in under 12 hours.

Gary Revel investigates the attempted assassination of President Ronald Reagan. He proceeds into a world of intrigue, danger, and deadly battles, that rage over John Hinckley's obsession with Jodie Foster and President Ronald Reagan.
Covert security company Vanguard is the last hope of survival for an accountant after he is targeted by the world's deadliest mercenary organization.

movie_name: The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones
description: When her mother disappears, Clary Fray learns that she descends from a line of warriors who protect our world from demons. She joins forces with others like her and heads into a dangerous alternate New York called the Shadow World.

movie_name: Once Upon a Time in Corea
description: Set during the final days of the Japanese occupation of Korea, an adventurer and a jazz singer team up to steal a priceless diamond.
While camping seven friends stumble upon the murdered bodies of a vacationing couple and soon find they are fighting for their lives against a sadistic killer.

Crushing family dynamics have crushed Hana, an old-fashioned, respectable Czech mother, and a recent widow. The arrival of Brona and his sometimes depressed chicken changes the life of everyone, including Brona.
In a desolate future, where flesh ear implants are mandatory, a disillusioned government shoemaker falls in with a fringe group of outsiders fighting for their humanity.

After experiencing the bad disasters on Pengantin Island, a woman decided to calm down on the beach of Phuket, Thailand. Until one day his best friend in college came to visit and intended to persuade her to return to Indonesia.

Down-on-his-luck gambler Kan Au (Sam Lee) owes a big sum of money, and needs to go on a winning streak soon or the loan sharks will take the interest from his hide. Luckily, Kan finds a ...                See full synopsis »
In central Pennsylvania a professional paranormal team travels to a haunted house to investigate it and end up uncovering more than they ever imagined.
A brainwashed girl is convinced by her authoritarian mother that her dead father will resurrect if they prove their love for him. Until he begins to rot.

Transported to Barsoom, a Civil War vet discovers a barren planet seemingly inhabited by 12-foot tall barbarians. Finding himself prisoner of these creatures, he escapes, only to encounter Woola and a princess in desperate need of a savior.
Prem is one kind of a guy ,who loves any girl just out of attraction rather than love. But only until finds his true love and facing challenges it brings to keep it successful.

movie_name: Hikidashi no naka no rabu retâ
description: A radio DJ, Mao starts a new program called, "Love Letters from the Drawer" to assist people who need an extra push to send out their simple yet very important message for their loved ones.
Adaptation of a novel by Júlio Dinis, depicting the romantic and rustic life in Portugal, circa 1863.
A wealthy man invites four people to his private island to blame three of them for his daughter's sudden death. The next morning, the wealthy man is found murdered.
Naked bodies found on the outskirts of town in a shallow grave. A family living in the outback hiding a secret. A trio of masked men visiting in the middle of the night.
In feudal Rajasthan, a bunch of peasants rise up against the exploitative landowners and the age-old system of caste-based oppression.
The Candyman arrives in New Orleans and sets his sights on a young woman whose family was ruined by the immortal killer years before.

Satanas, disguised as bishop goes to visit Irma Vep in prison to announce its issuance. The ship that takes Irma is cast in prison by Satanas. Irma Vep returns to Paris. Captured in turn Satanas commits suicide in prison.
Sisters Jorie and Kaidon attempt to reconnect over a vacation in the woods after a terrible secret drove them apart.
Military drills in the snow capped mountains of the Northwest awaken a hibernating snow beast, and a group of skiers on vacation are about to feel his wrath.

A grizzled industrialist and lively widower wants to pass the torch on to his only son to start a new life with the right companion. However, both father and son share the same taste in women. Is there still hope for a poor lonely soul?
In a pursuit to belong, three college freshmen take off down a twisted, debauched, pride-busting road to brotherhood.
A kickboxing champion is forced to fight cyborgs in a tournament when the company kidnaps his fiancee.
A young pickpocket in the New York subways, living a fast, free, lifestyle is confronted by a woman with whom he had a one night affair.
The Hash House Harriers ("a drinking club with a running problem") encounter a killer Bee Keeper in a crazy Kiwi horror-comedy that is part Animal House and part 80's slasher movie.
Two teenage yoga enthusiasts must do battle with an evil presence that is threatening to rise from its underground lair and endanger their major party plans.
An observational glance inside the intoxicating evening of a young couple as they trip through the dangers of the night.
Follows Jake Young, a young boy who experiences a life-changing effect when he transports back to Bethlehem on the night of Jesus' birth after an skateboarding accident right before Christmas.
Two college students, Rajesh and Kaushik, fall in love with Anu. While Rajesh struggles to confess his feelings to Anu, Kaushik visits her house with his parents in the hope of winning her heart.

After her grandfather dies leaving a priceless heritage, a world-traveling party girl finds herself excluded from his will unless she marries someone. Desperate to get the money, she goes on a search for a rental husband.

The Don Juan of a small provincial town saves from suicide a young American girl who falls in love with him. The citizens, after having discovered that the girl is very rich, will do everything to organize the marriage between them.
Story of the central hero of Mahabharata who rises from nothing to becoming the world's greatest warrior ever born in history and emerges as the hero of the Kurukshetra war.
A young woman returns home after 13 years to her sick mother's crumbling hillside mansion and finds murder and swift death lurking in the dark.
Four heroes are tested and chosen from among the people to embark on a life-changing quest that'll forever alter the destiny of an entire race. Based on Igbo spirituality and cosmology.

Vince is a young boy when he witnesses his father murdered on stage at a political rally. 15 years later, he plots to infiltrate a dangerous arms dealer, and exact revenge on the men responsible for his father's death.

As the mousy Margarita arrives in Kos to promote a clothing brand's summer collection, a glorious mix-up will lead to a whimsical masquerade, and the romantic affair with a rich islander. Isn't it wonderful that love, too, can be blind?
Seattle undercover narc Jackie Parker (Stevens) is out to bust the drug smuggling ring commanded by Philip Bianco (Danova).
During the Great Patriotic War, battalion commander Pavel Akimov fell in love with the military translator Anechka Belozerova, but the circumstances of military life separated them.
Korean folk hero Hong Kil-dong is back to save the day, this time he must take on the black magical powers of an evil wizard, who has the power to raise the dead.

movie_name: The Fall of the House of Usher
description: 1950. Horror. A traveller arrives at Usher mansion to visit his friend Roderick (Kaye Tendeter) and discovers that Roderick and his sister (Gwen Watford) have been inflicted with a strange disease.

movie_name: A Year to Live, A Day to Die
description: Be careful what you wish for. "SCARFACE" meets "THE FALCON AND THE SNOWMAN" in this emotional action/drama by Kris Bentley.
Alan Armstrong, aka Spy Smasher, battles a Nazi villain known as The Mask, who heads a gang of saboteurs determined to spread destruction across America.

A low-born thief loves a Moroccan Princess. She must marry to escape death at the hands of her enemies. The groom is able to wed or cast away his bride simply by saying "I Marry You" or "I Divorce You" three times.
Kuo Tsing wins the hand of fair maiden Huang Yung. Almost immediately, however, clan rivalries leads to Kuo being wounded by Ouyang Feng and Huang being named new leader of the Beggar Clan.

A newly wealthy English woman returns to Malaya to build a well for the villagers who helped her during war. Thinking back, she recalls the Australian man who made a great sacrifice to aid her and her fellow prisoners of war.
Amigo is a fiction feature film that brings together psychological thriller and black comedy, bordering on the macabre, all in the form of an intimate drama.
A fatal explosion and sudden earthquake rock Los Angeles, and reporter John Benson seizes his chance to cover the breaking news of increasing seismic activity.

A young woman stops at a motel for the night while traveling alone. After a strange knock on her door, she takes her medication, which causes her to have hallucinations of her own worst fears while she is in the shower.
The inseparable love of two teenagers; one American, one Arab, knows no boundaries, as they sacrifice everything against their family's objections.
When an oil company unwittingly unleashes a prehistoric shark from its icy prison, the Jurassic killer maroons a group of thieves and beautiful young female college students on an abandoned island.
Unacquainted Emily and Oliver join the mile-high club together on the way from LAX to NYC--end of story. Except that they keep meeting constantly over the next seven years..
A young couple moves into a new apartment. Shortly, they discover that their search for a perfect life brings issues When Forces of evil stop at nothing to take their souls.
One by one the residents of a small, isolated town become infected by an insidious bug that turns them into violent, indiscriminate killing machines.
A middle-aged magician is in love with his beautiful young assistant, who is in love with his young protege', who turns out to be a bum and a thief.

Helmut, living in West Germany in the early 1980s, has a big crush on a fellow student, Britta. He does everything to get to know her, but, when she suddenly moves away to San Francisco, he's devastated.
They say it's fake. They say no one ever really get's hurt. But this time he's fighting for his life.
Seven friends go on a remote jungle vacation where they are terrorized by a primeval spirit, but as they struggle to survive they come to realize that they brought the evil with them.
As the apocalypse evolves, US Marshals are sent to a remote farmhouse in Colorado to retrieve a scientist in the Witness Protection Program who may hold the key to solving the unfolding pandemic.

Two pirates steal the clothes of royal investigators and claim to work for the famous Captain Lim Geok-jeong. The punish corrupt officials while trying to make themselves rich, never expecting to meet the real Captain Lim.
Chun-hyang, is secretly engaged to marry Mong-ryong Lee. Lee leaves for Seoul with his father and the new governor, Hak-do Byeon, begins coveting Chun-hyang.
A man is given the unique opportunity to relive the worst day of his life, in exchange for seven years off his own life expectancy.

Nella and Orfeo, communists, flee Tuscany with their children to escape fascism. Wanting to start their life over in the New World, they embark on a boat for America. They will in fact dock in Marseille, far from the land of their dreams

Terrified and bloody, Oscar Svendsen awakes clinched to a shotgun in a strippers joint. Around him 8 dead men, and police aiming at him. To Oscar it's clear that he is innocent. It all started when four chaps won 1,7 million on the pools...

Anirudh aka Anu along with his friends, he makes local movies and also runs a gang that lets students cheat in exams. His life changes completely when he meets Maithili, whose father hires Anu to help her clear her exams.
As the world is overrun by zombies, a group of scientists and military personnel sheltering in an underground bunker in Florida must determine how they should deal with the undead horde.

movie_name: Pata Nahi Rabb Kehdeyan Rangan Ch Raazi
description: Harman, who hails from a poor family, falls for rich girl Simran. He goes to Bangkok and returns to his land after earning wealth and success. He meets up with Simran and hopes to confess his love.
Five disparate youths, lost on a road trip to the location of the infamous 'mangrove slasher,' end up being pursued by a cadre of cannibal clowns.

It's ten years after the kidnapping of Martin Bristol. Taken from a backyard swing at his home at the age of six, he is forced to witness unspeakable crimes of a deranged madman. For years, Martin's whereabouts have remained a mystery...until now.

movie_name: Mom Thinks I'm Crazy to Marry a Japanese Guy
description: Lin, has a thing for Japanese culture while living in Taiwan. Lin got a Facebook message from a Japanese guy, Mogi. The two start to interact through Facebook. During the golden week holiday, they finally met in person in Taiwan.
The story of a family man who is frustrated with his frumpy wife, then embarks on affair with a random woman he meets, putting the stability of his home in a serious jeopardy.
Story concerns a paper mill, a mortgage and the struggle to obtain the lost formula for making paper from seaweed. Star is given opportunity to introduce many daredevil features.

movie_name: Pro zhenu, mechtu i eshche odnu...
description: A date. Maria and Vasin do not realize that in a parallel world they have a different life. Wonderful life, where well formed what they seem to be lacking today...
An angel tires of his purely ethereal life of merely overseeing the human activity of Berlin's residents, and longs for the tangible joys of physical existence when he falls in love with a mortal.
Explores the long standing question of whether a solid relationship can result from sex on the first date.

A cyborg is programmed to kill a scientist who holds the fate of mankind in his hands. He fails and hides in a diner in a desert run by a woman who likes him. The people who sent him are after him and so is the local arm wrestling champ.
The O'Leary brothers--honest Jack and roguish Dion--become powerful figures, and eventually rivals, in Chicago on the eve of its Great Fire.
Ling Fei is a young woman, who gives dance lessons during the day to earn money to pay for her sick mother's medical expenses.

Water, the gold of the land has disappeared. Greedy corporations, con artists, water pirates, militias and a crazy pyromaniac take over, ensuring lessons in science, critical thinking and quixotic wisdom make an exciting dark drama.
A defrocked priest, Adolphe Eloi, and his mistress, Berthe Granjeux, who will call themselves Holy Father and Holy Mother set themselves up as the leaders of a religious sect.
Five aimless youths are offered money to assassinate a local gangster. This is the beginning of their downward spiral into a life of crime.
In this re-imagining of Donald Farmer's 1993 cult classic, Tara (Roni Jonah) and her friend Meghan (Jasper Evans) encounter a group of cannibalistic criminals on the run.
Goaded by his buddies, a nerdy guy who's never "done the deed" only finds the pressure mounting when he meets a single mother.

Third Reich's Nazi propaganda epic about a heroic fictional German officer on board of the RMS Titanic. On its maiden voyage in April 1912, the supposedly unsinkable ship hits an iceberg in the Atlantic Ocean and starts to go down.
Dr. Julius M. Jordan is a bachelor from Philly. After breaking up with his ex, he decides to take his chances on the dating scene. He soon realizes that it may not be his cup of tea.
An American artist with a penchant for drinking blood begins seducing and dispatching residents of a small fishing town in Mexico.

After her daughter's death, wealthy American homemaker Julia Lofting moves to London to restart her life. All seems well until she is haunted by the ghosts of other children while mourning for her own.

movie_name: When My Baby Smiles at Me
description: Vaudeville performers, Dailey and Grable, have marital difficulties when he hits the "Big Time", which are compounded by his drinking problem.
When the wrong man is convicted of a string of murders the real culprit returns to continue their work.
Hunted is part of the Paranormal Chronicles, volume 1. Molly has been hunted for 150 years and now she does the hunting.
A tough fellow from out West falls for young woman who is being pursued by a smarmy high-society type.
A worn-out businessman and a beautician on the run collide in a Paris airport. Love arrives, all its hurdles be damned.

movie_name: Oblivion Island: Haruka and the Magic Mirror
description: A teenage girl discovers a magical world, which forces her to come to terms with her grief for her deceased mother, and her tenuous relationship with her father.
Unbeknownst to him, a soldier is sent on a doomed mission because of the high likelihood of him divulging secrets if captured and tortured.
An adulterous wife, a mercenary personal trainer and a paralyzed mafia boss with a chainsaw: three mentally deranged characters, one chaotic mess.
Four intellectuals, down on their luck, become unlikely criminals as a form of rebellion against a system that has crushed them.

After losing her job, making out with her soon-to-be former boss, and finding out that her daughter plans to spend Thanksgiving with her boyfriend, Claudia Larson faces spending the holiday with her family.
A law-abiding aerial inventor of the Jetwing gets mixed up with a gang of criminal air-heisters and reluctantly teams up with a Chinese policeman to stop their nefarious schemes.
The story about a young man who washes up on a deserted island and discovers that John F. Kennedy and Marilyn Monroe are alive and well and living in exile.
In 1988, Earth makes the first contact with an alien civilization. In 1991, these aliens, known as Newcomers, slowly begin to be integrated into human society after three years of quarantine.
Twenty years after 3 murders occur in a castle's "blue room", three men who each want to marry a beautiful girl decide to spend a night in the room to prove their bravery to her.
Based on the true life of Captain William Kidd, a Scottish sea captain who is commissioned to hunt pirates and the French, only to be accused of piracy himself.
1950s Madrid: The agoraphobic Montse raised her now 18 y.o. kid sister. The upstairs neighbor falls down the stairs and breaks a leg. The crazy Montse takes him in.
A lonely assistant finally finds love and must escape her monster of a boss before she and her new love become his next meal.

Ken Elkin is a randy young man who is told that the world is about to end. In a race against time, there's only one goal he wants to accomplish: bedding the love of his life, who just happens to be the local pastor's daughter.

movie_name: The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants
description: Four best girlfriends hatch a plan to stay connected with one another as their lives start off in different directions: they pass around a pair of secondhand jeans that fits each of their bodies perfectly.
A society on the verge of total collapse is agitated by military forces who try to make sure needed crops are harvested before the farm workers begin to revolt. Then a worker is killed by a soldier.
A hot tempered young boy gets into fight wherever he sees injustice around him. His life comes down crashing after he lock horns with a dangerous thug.
Fighter pilot Varun recalls his romance with Leela while being held prisoner in Pakistan during the Kargil War.
At a crossroads in his artistic career, Edgar Degas visits New Orleans in 1872, falls in love with his blind sister-in-law, and discovers inspiration, devastation, and everything in between.
A nerdy florist finds his chance for success and romance with the help of a giant man-eating plant who demands to be fed.

THIS IS AS REEL AS IT GETS. A loner kid gets fed up with the monotony of his existence under the shadow of his narcissistic friend and decides to make a change in his life, starting with a mysterious cerulean VHS tape.
A student receives a serial killer's brain in a transplant after being thrown into a pool with no water in it.

The story-line of the film revolves around a Crime Branch's Officer and a courageous girl from another agency, they are appointed to catch a criminal gang who leaves a trade mark at their every crime scene.

A precarious loner sneaks into a blind woman's home and begins living there without her noticing. Meanwhile, the woman mourns her recently deceased father and struggles to remain connected to the world.
A set of young adult siblings learn their suburban parents are actually trained assassins. After their parents explosive demise, the kids inherit an unfinished job with life or death stakes.
A young man must chose between fast money or the grind of a basic 9 to 5 in order to provide for an ailing mother and children.
The story of two friends Sasan and Bahram. Sasan is living in Brazil and Bahram is joining him too but they face many different challenges and adventures in between.
A school has a competition every three years in which they pick a Prince of Legend. 14 males students, including Kanade Suzaku, take part in the competition this year
Cult classic highlighting the contrast between Indian and Western values in the newly independent state.
A visitor from another galaxy, an experiment gone wrong and a mysterious freeway killer are all at the center of this horror anthology hosted by genre legend George Stover.
A long-distance couple spends a weekend together that makes them question the longevity of their relationship.
A look at a few chapters in the life of Poppy, a cheery, colorful, North London schoolteacher whose optimism tends to exasperate those around her.
An ancient wind carries with it omens of the apocalypse, stirring the pride, guilt and envy of a group of college kids to murderous rage.
A slow-burn suspense Christmas horror where six friends explore an abandoned hotel near a Christmas tree lot only to find themselves being murdered one-by-one by someone in a Santa mask.

Charlotte finds herself in a rut searching for a spark has a whirlwind night of romance and imagining a future with a man named Adam, he ghosts her and when she finds him ill, she spends her last days with him.

Endemic is about one woman's last efforts to escape her dead-end home town and forge a better life for herself and her son as a deadly virus hits town - having the effect of unleashing a person's worst fears before consuming them.

Jimmy goes to work with his uncle, the owner of a food factory. Before he gets there, he befriends an Irish family who happens to be his uncle's worst enemy because of their love for music and in-house band who constantly practices.

A young writer becomes intrigued with a mysterious dark-haired woman who claims to be his long-lost sister, starting an unusual relationship with her and prompting a downward spiral involving his domineering mother and lovely fiancée.
Kung Fu knight Shen Lang stumbles across grave robbers while on the trail of a martial arts mass murderer.
Under the leadership of a small-time bank robber, British inmates hatch a plan to escape by staging a musical.
Sivappu Sooriyan is one man's hunt for his missing family and to bring to book the perpetrators of their ruin.

movie_name: Detective Conan: The Private Eyes' Requiem
description: Conan and Kogoro Mori was tasked to solve a crime on a given time. The lives of their loved ones(as well as their own) are on the line. Solving the mystery means saving everyone.
The sisters Ellen and Sabine are dancers. Ellen marries a banker, Sabine is left by her lover. Sabine earns her living as an entertainment lady at the Blue Lantern.
A poet sells his collection of comic books and action figures in order to afford to hire a male stripper on New Years Eve.
Jacek, young violinist, loses consciousness after an accident and in his dreams he experiences extraordinary adventures while searching for beautiful Ania, his love.
A military experiment to create a race of super-warriors go awry, and legions of murderous zombies are unleased upon a surburan neighborhood.
It is the year 1938. Tension is in the air as China is in the throes of an impending war with Japan.

Gwen the Cat and Roger the Dog are secret agents who covertly protect and save the world without humans ever finding out. Their partnership is due to the Great Truce, which has stopped dog and cat hostility for a decade.
Although their relationship has been strained by lies and deceit, a former couple tries to remain friends but the temptation to fight their romantic impulses toward each other is difficult to resist.
The black sheep sister and best friend of a missing man uncover a secretive town hiding years of disappearances and murders.
After scientific advances trigger an apocalyptic event a lone survivor must embark on a quest to reconnect with life.

A hard-working, blue-collar dad just wants to provide a good life for his quick-witted 10-year-old daughter. His mundane San Fernando Valley pool cleaning job is a front for his real source of income: hunting and killing vampires.
A hard-boiled police detective sets out to capture a gruesome serial killer terrorizing the canals of Amsterdam.
When a confident college professor is courted by four eligible and well-established men, she struggles to decide who she likes the best.

Artist Pavel Alekseevich and his wife Nina spend their holidays in a small boarding house. For him, it is an opportunity to collect thoughts and paint a new picture. Nina has an affair with another man .

Ambitious American Selina heads to Italy to set up a devious tomato farm in order to receive the "Made in Italy" stamp. In Italy she runs into the Italian farmer Pasquale and the ghosts of Ancel and Margaret Keys. Things get complicated.
A young blonde Jane Freeman is found dead in the pool. She turns out to be a daughter of Professor Freeman who has been told his daughter will die unless he gives up his research.
When a devastating illness threatens to end Evan Lake's career in the C.I.A., he goes rogue to hunt down a terrorist who tortured him during a mission gone awry years ago.
First Love Letter is a 1991 an Indian hindi film directed by Shiva. The film stars Manisha Koirala, Vivek Mushran and Dalip Tahil in the lead roles. Music of the film was composed by Bappi Lahiri.
The American army sets up a special force to free three American officers who were captured by the Vietcong in Vietnam in 1968.
After Harvey Dent's face is badly burned and scarred, he becomes Two-Face and joins the Joker, Riddler and Scarecrow. There's only one man who can stop them all: Batman.

One year has passed since Clank defeated the terrorist leader Goldscar. He returns to the agency again in order to find his brother. Clank has to face the most difficult task yet; is it worth to continue killing or can we change who we are?

Five girls, five best friends, all haunted by their past mistakes of an April Fools prank gone fatally wrong, meet again after two years for a summer week long getaway in the woods to reconnect and reconcile.

The first chapter of the the General's Son trilogy follows Kim Du-Han's childhood, from the loss of his mother at age 8, to his rise as a gang leader who protects local vendors from expanding Yakuza forces in Japanese occupied Korea.

Super standard girl in school (May Who) is on a quest to win the love of a school senior heart-throbber (Fame) with her new-found friend (Pong). The only secret is that she can discharge electricity when she gets excited.
Petty criminal Dean struggles to raise his autistic son alone, and his life appears to be going off-track until psychologist Stevie arrives to help them both.

A master thief is blackmailed into stealing a most-prized urn. He must stay alive, outwit his ruthless mentor, recover his kidnapped girlfriend, and remain ahead of Korea's most brilliant detective bent on returning him to prison.
The manager of a service agency for the wealthy clashes with--and falls for--an inventor who is seeking funding for a new kind of tractor.

Two best friends leave everything behind in Texas to start a fishing business in Cancun But they have little to no money to pursue their dream, much less to pay the mob - but all this is minimal as the worst is still ahead.
Tensions rise when a stripper and religious protester are trapped together in a peep show booth and must come together to survive the apocalypse in 1980's Chicago.
Mae Nak dies during child birth but comes back to live with her husband as a ghost. The twist is that he doesn't know that she died as he was away fighting a war at the time.
Seeking revenge for the murder of his family, a man returns to Hong Kong to track down the killers. He becomes enthralled in further intrigue when his new boss is targeted by the same group.
When Huston Germanotta takes his family on a cross country trip to scatter his father's ashes in the Pacific Ocean, they are set upon by galactic pirates, who mistaken his wife for Lady Gaga.
She walked and talked differently, so they tried to hide her, but her determination to Live and Love, transformed her, and all those who knew her.
A village ruffian, who settles disputes in his native, takes on a big shot when he tries to sort out the rough patch in his marriage after several years.
Anna thought she landed the man of her dreams; how will she lure him back after her psychotic mother sets him up with a call girl?
The dreamer and inventor at heart, Roman Kalinka, received the prestigious specialty of an accountant. But Roman does not have a soul for accounting and the office. He is a "techie", an engineer.
Two self-aware characters in a "Call of Duty" style video game struggle with their screwy, frustrating existence.
South Korean exchange student Yoon Ji-ho tries to make love bloom between her uptight classmate Kaede and Yusuke, a very shy boy she's infatuated with since middle school.
A husband and wife's weekend in a mid-century modern vacation rental turns deadly when the husband discovers the owner is a psychopath with a backyard of buried secrets and designs on his wife.
A gladiators game inside an abandoned prisons in a Gothic city. Only an outsider retreating from the horrors of war can stop El Toro and his gang from their ruthless reign.

movie_name: Roundabout, the Shortest Distance Is Round
description: Three years after getting his teacher fired for kissing him, Haruto works as a host, selling his body to pay off his debts. Then the two meet again.
Tom, a journalist from the city, meets Rawi while writing a piece rural life. However, she is Maori and her family disapproves of the relationship.
A woman looks for those responsible for her husbands murder. Only to stumble upon a dark secret of why he was killed, that will send her down a path of vengeance.

movie_name: Red Shoes and the Seven Dwarfs
description: Princes who have been turned into Dwarfs seek the red shoes of a lady in order to break the spell, although it will not be easy. A parody with a twist.
Jake's life of illegal raves collides with his own life after he experiences disturbing flashbacks and premonitions, as side effects of using his crews new powerful street drug.
Raja saves Malini, a Sri Lankan refugee, from the camp guard who tries to molest her. Though both fall in love with each other, she is forced to return to her country.

A micro-budget movie crew treks into the wilderness to shoot horror scenes for their unsellable indie-drama. They soon find themselves in the midst of their own real horror movie, as they are hunted by a large group of creatures.
A freshly-out-of-the-grave band of Hard Rock Zombies is thirsting to take their sweet revenge, as they give the performance of a lifetime.
A writer for a greeting card company discovers the struggles and tribulations of living alone after breaking up with his unfaithful girlfriend.

When college students sign up for what seems a simple paid research study, they soon realize their lives are in danger. Unfortunately they've unknowingly volunteered their bodies as human collateral in an ongoing U.S. Military experiment.

An undercover cop struggling to provide for his son and ailing wife, must infiltrate a ruthless gang. But things turn sour when another cop blows his cover and he quickly finds himself battling for his life and the lives of his family.
During a game of Seven Minutes in Heaven, Bree and Connor must navigate how to get what they want while ensuring their reputations stay intact.

movie_name: The X Files: I Want to Believe
description: Mulder and Scully are called back to duty by the FBI when a former priest claims to be receiving psychic visions pertaining to a kidnapped agent.
Charlie, 27, is an artist who sees ghosts. She hopes to evade them by moving to a mysterious country town called Violet River, but death seems to follow her everywhere.
A brave robot volunteers to combat the mechanoid minions of a mad scientist bent on world domination.
A ransom scheme turns into a nightmare for a group of kidnappers who become victims of a horrifying secret that must be paid every spring.
As night approaches, a young hunter's survival skills are put to the test when a stray bullet from an unknown hunter tears through his father's leg and the battle to save him begins.

After a drug deal gone wrong, Bédé goes into hiding in the countryside at a reformative school for criminal youth. His location is found out, and he and the pupils have to protect themselves with whatever means they have.
A struggling single parent inherits her family's sugar cane plantation and soon comes face to face with the estate's dark and horrific past.
The people in the palace strive for eternal youth and a perfect look. The ruler falls in love with a lady who has eternal youth and a secret.

A young woman's supernatural ability to see ghosts is reawakened following the death of her mother. As she adjusts to her new, deathly surroundings, she and her loved ones become the target of some ill-meaning individuals.
While on tour, a garage band unearths a female, supernatural force named Azira. She angrily seeks out to murder all of the band members, for a start.
An American insurance investigator goes to Hong Kong to retrieve a famous diamond stolen by a local criminal organization.
A woman with crippling social anxiety is cursed. She must never be alone for more than a short period of time or "they" will come for her.
A young family is snowed into their home with a growing brood of aggressive spiders that attack by burrowing into your eyes.
A Hindi feature film set in the lower depths of Bombay's "C" grade film industry. Miss Lovely follows the devastating story of two brothers who produce sleazy horror films in the mid-1980s.

Mike and his friends make plans for a mountain vacation. Near where they're camping is a girls' school where men are strictly forbidden. But when Mike falls in love with a student, he manages to get into school as a music teacher.
When the Davison family comes under attack during their wedding anniversary getaway, the gang of mysterious killers soon learns that one of the victims harbors a secret talent for fighting back.

movie_name: The Bridge of San Luis Rey Remastered
description: An epic adaptation of Thornton Wilder's Pulitzer Prize winning novel. Now fully remastered, this star-studded film is restored with 40 minutes of unseen footage.
Students at a quantum academy attempt to create a collective consciousness, only to discover that they themselves are part of a greater experiment.
A woman reports her alien abduction story, but hypnosis reveals that her nocturnal visitor was a man dressed like Santa. Was she dreaming, or is there more to the story?

Two cops clash when they discover they are looking for the same prime suspects in an investigation. Working together against their will they pursue the suspects, but does one of them have a dark past that could put them in grave danger?
A fairy tale-like love story between young circus artist Lola and the bear Misha, who one day transforms into a human.

Gokul Das, an ex-gangster tries to make a living by becoming the driver of a millionaire, whose daughter, Priya is the target of some killers. Das tries to save Priya, but things are not what they seem to appear.
A terrifying monster grizzly bear comes out of a blinding blizzard to feed on the trapped residents of an isolated town.
Deniz goes to Izmir when she sees the danger of losing her great love Emre,who has not succeeded in forgetting. Melisa, who is competing to steal Emre's heart.
When a dysfunctional family goes to their recently widowed grandmother's cabin for Thanksgiving, they find out that their grandmother is actually a werewolf.

Based on the short story 'The Testimony of Randolph Carter' By H.P. Lovecraft. This faithful adaptation of "The Statement of Randolph Carter" tells the strange story of the demise of occultist Harley Warren.
A young woman, born at the turn of the 20th century, is rendered ageless after an accident. After many solitary years, she meets a man who complicates the eternal life she has settled into.
After evading an Iroquois war party, an intrepid band of seventeenth-century fur traders must traverse undiscovered wilderness where they are hunted by a legendary tribe of giants.
Calling a "career replay", a fiery analyst returns home and must referee her 18 year old brother and his rugged, west-side neighborhood friend - all while trying to dodge a new relationship.
As the daring thief Arsène Lupin (Romain Duris) ransacks the homes of wealthy Parisians, the Police, with a secret weapon in their arsenal, attempt to ferret him out.
A defense attorney begins to suspect that there might be more to her client, who is charged with the murders of a vacationing family, than meets the eye.

Jagannathan, a mafia don in Bombay moves to Kanimangalam village. He wins the love of the locals, but finds trouble with a feudal lord, Appan Thamburan, after he decided to resume a traditional festival banned by Appan.

Set in medieval Rajasthan, Queen Padmavati is married to a noble king and they live in a prosperous fortress with their subjects until an ambitious Sultan hears of Padmavati's beauty and forms an obsessive love for the Queen of Mewar.
A secret invitation only ultra marathon in the Appalachians' goes horribly wrong when the athletes stumble across an unknown creature turning the marathon into a race for their lives.
On the eve of the Russo-Japanese war at the beginning of the 20th century, small-town girl Okane has married an old wealthy man to escape a life of poverty.
Desmond Caine suffers from insomnia and spends his nights walking the streets. One night, he witnesses a murder, generating a strange chain of events in his life.

When a successful introvert is talked into going out for a night of fun with his friends before his upcoming wedding, they quickly become the target of a sect of merciless vampires, and must fight to survive until dawn.

Joshua and Penelope are survivors of a deadly infection that laid waste to humanity 25 years ago. When they encounter fellow survivor Abira, their lives are forever changed as they fight off the remnants of the infected.
A girl lives in a Village like everybody until a Demon possesses her Turning her into a demon and the family Must help her return back.

Scientists create amphibious supersoldiers and detonate a nuclear bomb. In the midst of the fallout, a monster arrives, leaving Japan defenseless. Mankind's only hope is an irradiated water goblin with death on its mind.

movie_name: Mama, There's a Man in Your Bed
description: A company president gets framed with a food-poisoning scandal and the only person who can help him is the evening cleaning-woman, who always seems to be at the right place at the right time.
A student of music education comes to the music festival where organizers mix him up with the conductor. He accepts the role which creates lots of comic situations.

The self proclaimed 'king of sabres', and 'king of spears', decide to settle whose weapon is better by each taking a student and training them in the use of their favorite weapon, and whoever students' comes out on top is the winner.
While Haley goes back to exploring the world and living in interesting places, Sal and Ty are left behind to think about what she meant to each one of them.
Members of an exclusive college sorority (where sadomasochism seems to rule the day) seek twisted new ways to humiliate a new pledge.
A woman with a dark past dedicates herself to taking care of multi-handicapped children. When a young musician comes into her life, she is forced to face her history, or it will destroy her future.

After a bizarre one-night stand leaves him infertile, a careless bachelor sets out to connect with the television presenter who, as the result of the anonymous sperm donation he once made, happens to be pregnant with his child.
A handsome young Athenian attempts to escape his abusive alcoholic father and the grinding poverty of his daily life by falling in love with a macho sailor who promises him a better life.
A love triangle on a college campus between two young students who try to deny their feelings for each other. The entry of a lecturer who has a soft corner for the boy, changes things around.
A meek Belgian soldier, fighting in World War I, receives a letter and a photo from "Mary Brown", an American girl he has never met. After the war, he travels to America searching for her.
After his divorce, music teacher Da Jiang goes to Russia with his friend for clothing business and he falls in love with a Russian girl.
An aspiring musician arrives in New York in search of fame and fortune. He soon meets a taxi dancer, moves in with her, and before too long a romance develops.
His life change after a terrible accident to his wife. An important discovery eggs fossils put him into a missing link to discover who was responsible for his wife's death.
A career jewel thief finds himself at tense odds with his longtime partner, a crime boss who sends his nephew to keep watch.

A mass suicide involving members of a cult takes place in the Canary Islands. Gabriel's younger sister, Cordelia, who he hasn't seen for years, was one of the cult followers. Gabriel decides to travel there and find out what happened.
John Cassini, in the lead role, as the lonely-guy production assistant who gets caught up in the world's most complicated drug deal.
Terrorists take over a plutonium bomb and threaten to detonate it in a Saudi Arabian oil field. A special anti-terrorist unit is sent in to stop them.

When Cal moves to Los Angeles to start a small hypnotherapy business he expects a quiet life of meditation and helping others. He doesn't expect to find a moonshiner squatting in his living room. Especially not a cute one.
The fate of Thorn and his bloodline are finally revealed as the final battle for the soul of Avondale threatens to destroy not just the small town, but the world beyond.

Five friends decide to spend their midsummer night at an old summer place in the Swedish countryside. In one of the cabins, an old evil force awaits them. They will have to try to survive the reign of evil.

movie_name: Yo-kai Watch Movie: It's the Secret of Birth, Meow!
description: Nate, Whisper, and Jibanyan travel to the past to help Nathaniel and Hovernyan create the Yo-kai Watch when dark forces conspire to undo the history of the watch.

A writer who kills himself but is brought back to life and feels his destiny is get revenge on those who took his idea and that will include a b-listed indie horror actress, Delia Fox and she must do bloody things to win her way.
A girl plays a prank on her playboy brother by dressing up as a schoolgirl and expressing romantic intentions, only to him to fall in love with her.
Returning from his father's funeral, Robert Foster is faced with the unimaginable; he hits a young girl with his car. In a desperate attempt to save her life, he seeks help at a nearby farmhouse.
When the commander of a Bulgarian castle is killed in combat, his steward brings up his two children.

Faalsund, a village in the Norwegian fjord landscape. After saving the life of the father in the Svytelma family, Tore becomes employed on their farm. But Tore's background soon catches up with him and he is confronted by the village.

Duane recovers from his delusional breakdown to find his freakish basket-bound brother Belial will soon become a father. But not everything is joyous as the once tight knit brothers no longer seem to trust each other.
Five kiwi flatmates find something growing in their basement much to their delight, but when the rightful owner comes knocking and finds that they have appropriated the goods things start to go awry.
The decline of Eva, torn by her love for Jean, a naval officer, and her lust for Dario, a sly smuggler.

Sara is an orphan child in a world destroyed by an alien invasion. Leaving behind her innocence, Sara unleashes the power of her psychokinetic abilities to survive the attacks of the invaders and free the human survivors.
Ed learns, after a series of blackouts, that he has split personality disorder - and that his alternate personality thinks she's a woman.
In the summer of 1955 a young romance is sparked in the setting of Lake Como where a local village girl Angelina is accidentally introduced to Stephan an American French traveler.
Andy Lau leads a pack of arrogant new recruits at a training center for an elite police fighting force.

An immigrant in San Francisco brings Indian magic with her through spices. To keep the magic, she must never leave the spice store or touch another's skin. One day, a handsome architect bachelor enters her store.

Cheon-dal and Kang-ryeong lose their six friends while battling communist guerillas. As these communists begin to take over the town, the two men desperately resist them to preserve their way of life.
In the aftermath of a global thermonuclear war three battle tested women wage war in a virtual video game against giant mutant sand whales.
In 1950s Hawaii, a bigoted and ruthless land baron, with political ambitions, bans his sister from marrying a native even though he himself has secretly impregnated a native woman.

The House On Cuckoo Lane...Some believe it is a genuine snuff film. Some believe its existence is purely rumour. This is the video nasty every horror collectors wants. But you don't find this movie...this movie finds you.
Taxi driver Appu is haunted by his past when his sister was killed by a eunuch who was also a powerful pimp. While trying to find him, he comes across another girl who is about to meet the same fate.
After Richard Heuberger's operetta of the same name, Géza von Bolváry staged a high-spirited confusion about infidelity and amusing entanglements in Vienna at the turn of the century.
A teacher in a remote village is hindered by zealot members of the community who ostensibly believe in old superstitions.

In this darkly comedic and uniquely angsty journey, twelve vignettes chronicle a young woman's inner monologue as she visits various NYC beaches in hopes of fulfilling her dream of being eaten by a shark.
Three women who are Taoist devotees are tricked by the Wu-Tung demon god into following their sexual desires.
A New York City detective investigates mysterious deaths occurring 48 hours after users log onto a site named feardotcom.
Ashwin, a famous photographer, works with Renuka, an investigative journalist. When one of their colleagues, Saro, gets killed during a political meet, Ashwin and Renuka decide to investigate.

Two young men Mammad (Babu Antony) and Circle Inspector Jayachandran (Riyaz Khan) team up in their war against an underground mafia and smuggling ring while also avenging the deaths of their loved ones.
On Halloween night, the rules are simple. House lights bring the kids to get candy. But, when it gets late and really dark, the rules change.
Two great friends are reunited after five years. Among so many things that have changed, the resumption of connection awakens an old feeling for which they remain unprepared.
An agoraphobic journalist begins investigating a series of disappearances in his hometown, all while never leaving his home.

Jean and Marina go to Athens for their summer vacation. There they are reunited with Marina's family, while preparing to spend a romantic getaway, Marina's family decides to accompany them. But nothing will go according to the plan
A fantasy-thriller set in present-day Moscow where the respective forces that control daytime and nighttime do battle.
A woman threatens to leave her husband unless he installs a toilet in their home. To win back her love and respect, he heads out on a journey to fight against the backward society.
Battlefield of the Mind II continues the story of MMA fighter Blaze Johnson who's life takes a major turn when he gets into a car accident and is told he cannot fight anymore.
A young boy is forced to leave his family in the South and move in with relatives he doesn't know in New York.
A young couple dreams of growing old together as they as they deal with the struggles of being in a long-term relationship.
A dramatization of Jesus Christ's life from the day he was crucified to the moment he ascended into heaven.
Hunting Souls is the story of an American couple who are dealing with the hardships of caring for their sick child. They discover that they are being hunted by a demon.

Three runaway teenagers run for the hills. What begins as a Huck Fin and Tom Sawyer story quickly turns into a relentless hunt through the forests driving three teenagers to the limits of their physical and mental endurance.
The citizens of Comet Valley are being taken over by seeds from an alien plant that has taken root there. A sheriff investigates the strange goings-on.
A group of Mexican immigrants find themselves in the middle of a human trafficking ring and seek shelter in a safe house, that is anything but.
Sentient cabins in the woods. Ghosts taking over the airwaves. Haunting visions ripping you from reality. Who knew one town could be shrouded in so much darkness? Welcome to Cellar, Ohio.
A poor but materialistic woman chooses a rich man with dirty money over the man who loves her, not suspecting the consequences on her life.

The most deadly fighter on earth, a man so dangerous in combat he only uses one hand, is after the greatest book ever written. This book, a tutorial in the "mantis fist", must be protected by an unlikely band of hero's.
A very dark, very serious tale of the sometimes seedy and very dangerous LA acting, modeling world, and what can happen when you push a person too far.

As viral videos seem to evidence the fall of Dublin at the hands of the undead, four Millennials in rural Ireland can't discern fake news from real. Has a dependent lifestyle left them too naive to weather their fate?

6 Students of criminology are going to spend their holydays in the town. After a first week doing hicking they Will discover a deposit of an abandoned morgue. Zombies will start to come to Madrid and all will come to an end.
A beautiful young amnesiac, recently graduated from college and soon to be married, is determined to recover a missing piece of her teenage years.
Raja (Shashi Kapoor), a Kashmiri boatman and Rita (Nanda), a beautiful heiress from the city, fall in love.
Two ex-convicts kidnap two women and take refuge in a museum overnight during a zombie outbreak in Los Angeles.
Zombies are back in this highly anticipated sequel to 2015's popular Zombieworld. In the wake of a terrible virus that claimed most of the human population, zombies have risen.
Legendary rock band Foo Fighters move into an Encino mansion steeped in grisly rock and roll history to record their much anticipated 10th album.
