A psychoanalyst in NYC exchanges apartments with a woman in Paris. When his patients show up, they talk to her and then pay. He returns early to NYC and becomes a patient.
In November 2015, a box of old VHS tapes and DVDs was found. The footage was edited together as a surreal horror trip that opens the gate to the new level of nightmare.

movie_name: Untitled Dragon Ball & Animes Mix Movie
description: Sokuriel, a young new fighter unconscious of his alien origins, joins Goku Jr and Boruto to save the universes of all anime against his claimed brother.

Leonor works in a brothel called El Paraiso, in a Caribbean environment. Juan, a man in love with Leonor, has escaped from prison. Both Leonor and John want a new life, but they are hampered by the shadow of their past.
Nanninella, a young girl, is exploited and abused by her father, whom she maintains with her waitress salary.

Once Jack Walker was Germany's greatest action star, the hero of countless Germanic martial arts and action adventures, women wanted him and men wanted to be him, the world was his for the ...                See full synopsis »
After his fathers death, Wesley Cash returns home to rebuild the family cattle business but his plans are wrecked by a group of ranch hands who have designs of their own for the property.

A police officer looking for a fresh start after the death of his pregnant wife is assigned to a remote island as their police in-charge but soon ended up in the middle of a political clash between two prominent figures of the community.

A young classically trained Russian ballet dancer lands an audition for a film with a famous director. Pressures of Russian values and tradition force a decision between career, love, and family loyalty.
An ex-cop turned hypnotist (Norris) battles a mysterious stranger (Bottoms) who believes himself to be the reincarnation of Jack the Ripper.

"Sebastian's Unholy Flesh'-the seventh film by Denver auteur filmmaker Dakota Ray is a cinematic decent into evil, chronicling the the emergence of a new evil, as an Unholy trinity of entities try to obtain Lucifer's ancient Unholy Book.
On the heels of a corporate scandal, a disgraced CEO retreats to an inherited family farm and discovers a dangerous shadow organization that seeks to control it.
After the birth of her first baby turn's her husband's well-ordered existence upside down and forces him to act in response to the unexpected twists and turns of life.

The Borg travel back in time intent on preventing Earth's first contact with an alien species. Captain Picard and his crew pursue them to ensure that Zefram Cochrane makes his maiden flight reaching warp speed.
A charming CEO meets a brilliant employee on her first day at work. Although attracted to each other, they struggle not to yield to their emotions.
A delinquent teenager is killed in a car accident, and is resurrected as an investigator of the supernatural.

After she had been raped by her father, a young woman leaves the town with her new born son. Years later, the son can't accept that his mother fell in love with someone else than the mythical father she had told him about.
During the Ming Dynasty one man will request a competition when his weapon is rejected. After a series of fights he is determined to prove his sword is invincible.
A group of youngsters plan to film a documentary about the tragic events that wiped an Argentine town off the map back in the 80s. Little do they know that their worst nightmare is about to begin.

movie_name: Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger vs. Go-Busters: Dinosaur Great Battle! Farewell, Eternal Friends
description: When the Earth is threatened by Space War God Borudosu, having already brainwashed Tyranno Ranger and Aba Red, the Kyoryugers and Go-Busters must team up to save the world.

Career soldier, Jimmy MacDaniel, returns home to settle a divorce with his wife. He finds his house in shambles, his wife murdered, and his young son has disappeared. Mac wants to find out what happened to his family and why.

The seemingly endless possibilities of dating apps send a group of friends into a whirlwind of sex, jealousy, and self-doubt in this ensemble comedy that examines dating culture in the age of swiping.
Heartbroken and cynical after he's dumped by his girlfriend, Ben makes the unusual decision never to leave his house again.
Violent emotions are stripped BARE - and a woman scorned STRIKES back with all the FURY of the oppressed.
In the seventeenth century, in Massachusetts, a young woman is forced to wear a scarlet "A" on her dress for bearing a child out of wedlock.
In a post-apocalyptic world, six soldiers on a covert mission must transport a mysterious package across a frozen archipelago. Noomi Rapace stars.
When the unjust government goes rogue, the residents of the Sucre apartment take a stand leading to the first night of terror.

Awie (Awie) and Wati's (Erra Fazira) relationship is going well and they plan to get engaged. Ziana (Ziana Zain) pretended that she had forgotten her feelings for Awie and pretended to be a friend who was ready to listen to her problems.

Chris Nielsen dies in an accident, and enters Heaven. But when he discovers that his beloved wife Annie has killed herself out of grief over the loss, he embarks on an afterlife adventure to reunite with her.

They are bonded, nonetheless, by friendship and affection for a hen, whose eggs just might make a difference to Prakash's impoverished family. When the boy's father sells the bird, the chums desperately attempt to raise funds in order to buy it back.
Female reporter goes on a trip around the world following genius fashion designer in a search for perfect article for her magazine
Two sisters live in the shadow of their mother's suicide, struggling to live their lives and protect their loved ones in the face of the Vietnam war.
Korean folk hero Hong Kil-dong is back to save the day, this time he must seek out a golden blade to defeat the Evil Demon king plans to raise an army of demons to take over the world.
A young man who suffers from guilt related to his adored sister's death encounters her ghost in a haunted tunnel. He makes repeated visits to the tunnel and re-experiences the past.

movie_name: It's My Party and I'll Die If I Want To
description: Join Sara and her friends as they celebrate her birthday in the reputedly haunted Burkitt Manor. The evil within the house has awoken and has brought along some uninvited guests.
A woman seeks revenge on her mother by creating for herself a scandalous marriage, but her plan backfires when she winds up falling in love.
Where a CBI officer Alexander marries Priya to unfold the mystery of a murder. He needs a file that could bring the murderer to trial but Ashok " PakashRaj" and his brothers try to get the evidence.
Five friends go for a college party in a abandoned clinic, where they unknowingly awaken evil spirits.
A circus on the verge of bankruptcy decides to save itself by staging a animal act with lions and tigers for the first time.

A young idealist scholar at an all-girls boarding school comes face to face with the institution's privileged students. Will they learn a thing or two about respect? Can a little discipline pave the way for a fresh whirlwind romance?
Seven years after the fact, a man comes to the realization that he was the sperm donor for his best friend's boy.
Rival gangs seek out millions of dollars hidden inside a luxury condominium that's scheduled to be demolished, but first they have to deal with the janitor who found the loot first.

An American gangster in Kuala Lumpur suffering from amnesia struggles with the images in his head. He is hounded by former gang associates and interpol while he searches for who he is, and a woman in a photograph.
Sheriff Rockwell teams up with the new sheriff of York County, a young woman, to solve a murder that happened on the county line.
From Director Armando Garces who provided the award-winning "Markang Rehas" and hit film "Patapon", comes another exciting film.
Young nobleman Richard Shelton returns from the War of the Roses to find his father murdered, a fugitive family friend blamed, and his uncle occupying his estates.
Four friends find themselves suddenly recruited for a top secret undercover mission that goes from business to personal before they have time to reload.
After a foiled assassination attempt on the president this ex-special forces soldier is sent to war Zones where he fights warriors in order to survive.
After receiving a serious injury, a young gymnast is forced to stop performing. This serious sport traumatizes her not only physically but also morally.

In an alternate futuristic society, a tough female police detective is paired with a talking dinosaur to find the killer of dinosaurs and other prehistoric animals leading them to a mad scientist bent on creating a new Armageddon.
Vanessa has beauty and brains but due to her geeky exterior, she can't seem to get noticed by her crush.

Yusuf Miroglu and his fiancee Zeynep goes to Diyarbakir to attend at the wedding of Cemal, who is his close friend from military service. Cemal gets killed by mysterious assassination during the wedding.
A noble, high-class scholar starts to write erotic novels in 18th century of Chosun dynasty. He falls in love with a king's woman.
Chaos ensues when a lethal, airborne virus infects the population of a South Korean city less than 20 kilometers from Seoul.

The story is told from two points of view: that of a young pregnant woman, and that of her husband, a soldier accused of being involved in the failed 1976 military coup and assassination of General Murtala Mohammed, the Head-of-State of Nigeria.
In medieval Spain, a young traveling philosopher tragically falls in love with his pupil when he is hired by an uneducated lord to tutor his beautiful wife.

When her soon-to-be-married little sister and fiancé become marooned at a mountain retreat days before their wedding, Amelia and the best man, Grayson Tanner, are tasked with stepping in to save the wedding.

movie_name: Guerra e Liberdade - Castro Alves em São Paulo
description: Biography of 19th Century Brazilian great poet Castro Alves, who died in his 20s and had a tormentous love affair with Eugenia Câmara
A boy driving from New York to Philadelphia with buddies, and a mysterious girl alone in her hotel room - complete strangers - engage in an all-night phone conversation on New Year's night.
A group of friends set out on a road trip to "the party of the century" in the middle of nowhere, but on the way, they break down and find themselves being hunted for a satanic ritual.
Pablo, a shy teenager, meets Marco, who is a few years older than him. Together they go on a impromptu road trip to the Mexican desert, a trip that will make them face what they mean to each other.
In 1945, General Patton sends Germany's confiscated gold reserves to Frankfurt, but the Army train is robbed by plotters who also hire a Swiss hitman to kill the General.

Baxter is transporting counterfeit bills across the border in the bottom of fox cages. When veterinarian Allen places the fox ranch under quarantine tying up the bills, Baxter's plan to get at the money means trouble.
Everyday people come together to help a lost tribe of ancient Persians on the other side of our galaxy.

Sravan and Appu are childhood friends and Appu loves Sravan. Arjun is a senior student and boxer in the same college. By the time Sravan realizes he loves Appu, she has committed suicide. Why drove her to take her own life?
A woman is forced to sit under a hanged rotting corpse in the middle of a burnt forest, until the authorities decide that she has been punished enough.
When an old friend's return home is disrupted by his sudden disappearance, what starts as a welcome home film becomes an unsettling search.
Texas ranch teenager (Withers) is sent to school in San Antonio where she learns to get along with others.
Brothers Sreedharan and Raman are feuding over their ancestral properties. Raman tries to amass all the wealth by making Sreedharan's daughter fall in love with a hired lover.
A self-sufficient librarian helps a distraught man search for a message left in a book for him by his former girlfriend.
Dante journeys through the nine circles of Hell -- limbo, lust, gluttony, greed, anger, heresy, violence, fraud and treachery -- in search of his true love, Beatrice.
In the depths of the city of Buenos Aires there is a strange house where ceremonies and rituals full of occult elements are performed.
After being bitten by a radioactive spider, Peter Park begins his journey to becoming the protector of New York City: The Amazing Spider- Man.
LABOR PROBLEMS AND ISSUES IN A DEPARTMENT STORE ARE USED AS BACKDROPS FOR THIS ACTION-COMEDY TEAM-UP OF LITO LAPID AND REDFORD.
Struggling with a horrific past, Claire Rhodes must confront a stalker turned murderer of her youth in order to win her life - but will her own demons help the killer exact his vengeance?

A memory transplant adviser has to solve the puzzle of his client's traumatic past to improve/reshape her present and future but in doing so, he uncovers a forgotten crime of heartbreak and treachery, unknown to the unsuspecting victim.
ACTION - at its greatest. A bandit - A Police Officer - Gunning down each other in a TENSION-PACKED STORY.
Two brothers must come together after several years apart, in order to solve a mystery going on inside their childhood home.
Amid a global pandemic, Tom Riley offers his services to people trying to determine whether they are experiencing paranormal activity.
When a group of millennials host a 1980's themed party, they accidentally run afoul of a confused serial killer, who thinks it's still the 1980's - and the killings begin again.
Karate master and anti-drug vigilante Kiba returns to his home in Japan, where he aims to wipe out the nation's drug industry.
A film crew shooting in the desert is terrorized by a vicious outlaw motorcycle gang (on dirt bikes, no less) who are after the women in the company.

Now the descent into the dark labyrinth of the secret culture in this pillar of pedagogy begins. This is a world where no one is who they seem to be and no one can be trusted; it is an astonishing journey of perplexity and uncertainty.
When a world famous superhero ends up in the hospital with gunshot wounds, it is up to his sidekick to save him from the super villains who have come to finish the job.

Dev, Bahman, Binda, and Jandu are daredevils, with a fascination for guns and power. The group of friends is heavily involved with illegal activities but one day they are forced to question their actions and choose between right and wrong.

A filmmaker who is trying to finish his short film records a murder by accident that everyone believes was a suicide. He and the witness of the crime will seek the truth but the murderer is on to their plan and is one step ahead of them.

movie_name: Wu shi, hua dan, da liu mang
description: Bruce is an action director at a famous Hong Kong TV station, the lead actress falls in love with him much to the disgust of a Triad big boss, who then hatches a plot to bring the lovers back down to earth.
A soldier convicted for murdering his commanding officer is dumped and left to die on a prison island inhabited by two camps of convicts.
Horror legends Lloyd Kaufman and Jim O'Rear take you on a spine-tingling journey through five blood-drenched tales that will make your skin crawl.
Thanasis inherits a castle supposedly inhabited by Count Dracula, and decides to settle the question.
A young boxer and a call girl get caught up in a drug-smuggling scheme over the course of one night in Tokyo.
A crazy woman who lives in an old mansion thinks she's with her brother/lover, who lures victims to her.
Two youngsters, who are orphan. Grown up themselves,by their hardwork. Gets to know that their teacher is one of their mom.
A young martial artist's unparalleled Tai Chi skills land him in a highly lucrative underworld fight club.

Paolo Mancuso is a gang boss whose rivals want dead. During a failed assassination attempt, he is bitten by an infected lab rat. In the short time he has left to live, he tracks down his enemies and kills them one by one.
The lives, loves, and battles of fictional characters in the Army's First Ranger Battalion during WWII.
A young man falls in love with a woman he meets online, but must decide between her and the career he's always wanted.

When Rajesh, a talented singer, and Geeta, a skilled dancer, meet and fall in love, it seems like a match made in heaven. However, their lives are turned upside down a Prince to whom Geeta had been betrothed enters their lives.
Johnny Crusier and his best friend Linus Anderson embark on a journey to the local arcade and discover a new game that will change their lives forever.

Abbie, recently divorced , travels to Dublin at the holidays to visit daughter Sofia who just finished her semester abroad. Abbie finds herself, and a new love, in Irish widower Bobby O'Connor (father of Liam). (Part 2 of a Trilogy).
Chinese martial arts expert Qiao Lin faces the band of Balkan gangsters who have fluttered with their cruelty to a whole city. The fate of the people is in his hands.

Cheng Li-sheung is a young, upwardly mobile professional finally ready to invest in her first home. But when the deal falls through, she is forced to keep her dream alive - even if it means keeping her would-be neighbors dead.
Late one night a shopping centre receives an unexpected visitor, what begins as an act of kindness turns into a night of horror.
An action packed and heartwarming story of the friendship formed between a tank-destroyer dog of the Red Army during WWII and a group of soldiers.
A member of a geological expedition, a former criminal named Jamin receives a strange letter, after which he quits his job and rushes to a nearby station through the tough land of the Taiga.

In London, the pregnant wife of an industrialist falls down the stairs, loses her sight and has no recollection of the events but suspects that a mentally traumatic experience prior to the fall caused her accident.
Adiong Untouchable is a sharp-shooter, Adiong Untouchable is a lady killer, Adiong Untouchable is deadlier.
Chulbul Pandey invites a fresh trouble when he kills the brother of a notorious politician and the former swears to wreak havoc in his life.

After a night of rides and fast food at Magical Midway Thrill Park, three friends descend into horror and a fight for survival as they discover the secret ingredient that makes Midway's meat so magical. You are what you eat.

After the death of his wife and daughter in a car crash, a music professor staying at a long-vacant Seattle mansion is dragged into a decades-old mystery by an inexplicable presence in the mansion's attic.
In the Australian Outback, two estranged brothers discover old secrets and family lies. As their friends start to go missing they fear they are being stalked by someone or something.
The film describes the original story. Heart + Ltd. is an organization that helps desperate and hopeless people win over the hearts of people they love.
A overnight summer camp begins with a summer of fun but when bizarre incidents happen it will be a summer the camp will never forget.

A group of random strangers are invited to a cinema to watch a horror film called Admission by Guts (which resulted in the disappearance of a couple of audience members who watched it at the same theater a couple of years earlier.
Desperate for a better life, a failed dancer turned stripper teams up with a hunky aimless bartender to find her late father's buried treasure.
A young woman organizes a meet-up party at her mother's house where things go awfully wrong and some of the guests disappear mysteriously. They keep on haunting her in unexpected circumstances.
Two safari tour-guides and business partners find in the African jungle a wandering stunning blonde who suffers from amnesia.

Lina is sick in the hospital, she always thinks that she has a daughter; one day she attacked by a nurse and escapes from the hospital. She returns to her home after several years and plans to live with her imaginary daughter again.
''A rich young, smart but innocent boy from a small village Raja who after facing ample difficulties goes abroad, comes back and is called Raja Abroadiya by the whole village''

movie_name: Kureyon Shinchan: Action Kamen vs Haigure Maô
description: Action Kamen comes to Shinchan's world seeking help from Shinchan to defeat the Haigure Demon. Then the adventure of Shinchan and his family begins.

A mother's preference for partying, boozing and running around with an assortment of sleazy characters results in her neglecting her nubile teenage daughter, who subsequently finds herself mixed up with horny teenage boys, scuzzy nightclub owners and murder.
Two off-the-wall detectives go in search for a killer, while vying for the affections of a young woman.
While none of these cowboys believe in vampires, bloody proof mounts until the gun-slinging "Miss Billie" and the sheriff are the last two standing.

An ex-marine is hired by a defense contractor to travel to Panama to complete an arms deal. In the process he becomes involved with the U.S. invasion of Panama, and learns an important lesson about the true nature of political power.
In a post-apocalyptic wasteland, a woman rebels against a tyrannical ruler in search for her homeland with the aid of a group of female prisoners, a psychotic worshiper, and a drifter named Max.
Psychiatrist experiments LSD on 4 volunteers, to investigate Coffin Joe's influence over them. Each patient presents a different reaction, involving sex, perversion and sadism.
A woman in exile in the wilderness, brings up her son with the help of a tiger. Once the boy becomes a young man he ventures back into civilization and trouble ensues.
A psychologist, a psychiatrist and a prison warden open up a long-closed prison, unaware that the ghost of an electrocuted convict haunts it.
After finding out about an illegal arms deal, a military intelligence officer goes rogue with highly sensitive data related to his organization, causing his mentor: a colonel, to hunt him down.
Venus Velvet is a story of love that lasts no longer than the brief period before the fall of a comet; a love story set against the background of the possibility of the world's ending.

movie_name: Did You Hear About the Morgans?
description: In New York City, an estranged couple who witness a murder are relocated to small town Wyoming as part of the Witness Protection Program.

Adèle's life is changed when she meets Emma, a young woman with blue hair, who will allow her to discover desire and to assert herself as a woman and as an adult. In front of others, Adèle grows, seeks herself, loses herself, and ultimately finds herself through love and loss.
They are searching for the city of Monomotapa and a it's precious jewel, but they haven't accounted for the Gods.
In Washington, D.C. during World War II, Jamie Rowan enters into a loveless marriage with scientist Pat Jamieson and becomes his assistant. Struggles bring them closer together.
A money-minded criminal has to deal with two rival gangs as well as an evil cop threatening his girlfriend.
A pretty but virtuous small-town bank clerk is the victim of a vicious rumor from an unsuccessful suitor that she spent the night with a notorious womanizer.

Rom-com Movie, directed by Raaj Shaandilyaa, stars Ayushmann Khurrana who plays a 'dream girl'. In every love story, there is always one trying to win the heart of the other, who could be the 'dream girl'.
A jockey transforms an injured colt into a champion Thoroughbred after saving it from the glue factory.
A scientist builds an unwieldy piece of time- travel equipment, pursuing his girlfriend's murderer through layers of space and time in an effort to save her.

An international terrorist organization is behind the inheritance left by the father of a well known businesswoman in Taiwan. With the help of some of her workers, she will have to find out who is behind this evil organization.
Two undercover detectives are underestimated as they use their wit, charm, and skills to outsmart the biggest arms dealer in the region and all of his puppets.

Ahmed and Khaled are two friends of the casual type who turn to conning to gain a living. They decide to move to Hurghada where they could trick tourists, but they meet two girls who will change their lives totally.
When a group of college students are kidnapped during a humanitarian mission trip, five men from a close-knit congregation set out to rescue them.
The Invincible Six Million Dollar Man is a South Korean remake of the American TV series, "The Six Million Dollar Man." It was later released in Lebanon as, "Billion Dollar Kid."
American mining engineer gets involved in civil war and international conspiracy in an African country.

Julia, a medical student, infiltrates a prison to find the witness to what she believes was her sister's killing. In the midst of violent inmates and corrupt officials, her inquiry risks to end suddenly - by her own death.

Five women go camping in the woods to celebrate a friend's birthday over 4/20 weekend, but when they cross the turf of an illegal marijuana grow-operation, they must fight to survive the living nightmare.
Conrad (Jason Bateman) is helped by his old friend Dylan (Billy Crudup) and returns the favor by falling for Dylan's girlfriend Beatrice (Olivia Wilde).

Ulla is a sensitive and principled 10th-grader in a small East German town. When Winfried falls in love with her, he adopts her passion for protecting the environment. Ulla tries to stop illegal trout farm and gets her classmates involved.
A female psychologist wants to understand the minds of a confessed serial killer who spent the last five years in a mental hospital because of his state.
About the pastor's daughter, who reconciled the irreconcilable fighters - the inhabitants of two neighboring villages.
A frustrated office worker discovers that he is the son of a professional assassin, and that he shares his father's superhuman killing abilities.
A Mexican drug cartel hijacks a sports fishing boat to trade the hostages for their imprisoned leader, but they target a boat with vacationing Navy Seals on board.
In 11th century Normandy, a Norman duke sends one of his knights to build a defensive fortress in order to guard the borders against Frisian raiders.
A man, with the aim of killing the person responsible for his family's murder, finds a girl with the similar history, and they both unite for the common aim.

movie_name: Fate/stay night [Heaven's Feel] III. spring song
description: The final chapter in the Heaven's Feel trilogy. Angra Mainyu has successfully possessed his vessel Sakura Matou. It's up to Rin, Shirou, and Rider to cleanse the grail or it will be the end of the world and magecraft as we all know it.
An unlucky in love nurse finds her life taking a detour when her mother places a personals ad in the paper, while on the other side of Boston, a plumber is trying to change careers.

Feryal and her husband Sinan have one rule in their relationship. They can have any relationship they want, but they must be honest about them. In a way, this is much more difficult than having a simple marital fidelity.

Richard Booker the owner of a successful commercial construction company, is going through a divorce from his wife Sue. Sue wants the divorce not Richard, infidelity is the grounds but ...                See full synopsis »
A photography student's life takes a turn for the worse when her dead sister is welcomed back into the family home.
On a hot 4th of July night, sparks fly between four people as they test the limits and possibilities of their own freedom.
Follow up to Los paquetes de Paquita. Paquita still works as a maid who aspires one day to become "the lady of the house". But this time, contrary to expectations, love will keep eluding her.

A silent film adaptation of Edgar Allan Poe's immortal tale 'The Gold Bug.' The finding of a gold scarab beetle and Captain William Kidd's treasure map leads William Legrand into an obsessed delirium.

When his brother is framed for murder, a detective quits the force and breaks all the rules in pursuit of the real killers. Teaming with a beautiful lawyer, they uncover city-wide corruption and betrayal in the process.

movie_name: The Horror of Making My Film
description: When a group of filmmakers shoot a Science-Fiction movie in an old haunted prison, they have to solve a mystery of science and faith to get out alive.
A passionate love story set against the backdrop of a Soviet Air Force base in Estonia during late 1970's Communist rule.

A shy teenage girl is asked to prom by her dream boy. Her past is uneventful, she has been bullied by the popular girls. Her brother on the other hand, is popular and hangs with the cool kids. At the dance, a prank goes too far.
In the distant future, a federation marshal arrives at a research lab on a remote planet where a genetic experiment has gotten loose and begins feeding on the dwindling scientific group.

Fritz, a young Tongan man grappling with his wrestling superstar father Baron To'a's legacy, both metaphorically and literally following in his deceased father's footsteps by fighting for the return of his dad's stolen championship belt.
When Gopal, a young man, gets adopted by Lingam, an ageing gangster living in Madurai, the latter goes to all extents to protect Lingam from his enemies and the police.
After faking his own death, a former CIA contractor develops a relationship with a foreign prostitute while awaiting the delivery of his new identity.
A man with a dark past hitches a ride that turns into a road trip to hell and leads him to the revelation of a family secret of biblical proportions.
After 2 years in prison Ricco is released and on a path of vengeance. His father, the head of a mafia family, is gunned down by the ambitious Don Vito and now Ricco is looking to settle the score.

Joe loves to rock and be wild, but the time has come for him to settle down. He is to marry a conservative daughter of a well-to-do man. On his wedding day, a fiery female artist kidnaps him in order to blackmail his future father-in-law.
A divorced woman who decides to pursue the man she's interested in learns he's her new friend's ex-husband.
A swimsuit fashion designer is determined to protect her scatterbrained sister from a South American heartbreaker, but a case of mistaken identity complicates matters.
A devout community suffering from a plague is torn apart by a beautiful young woman and the forces of witchcraft, black magic, and possession.

Akash, a software professional who comes from a broken home, is a cynical younger who does not really believe in the idea of love. But when he learns about his father's past and encounters love in close proximity in his life, does he find a happy ending?

After a terrifying childhood running away with his family from terrorism, Karim's life once again gets destroyed by terrorists during the 9/11 attack. His only hope of peace and revenge is to join the FBI.
Look at dark dirty seedy world of prostitutes in brothel and high society rich feeding off them. A struggle of a prostitute trying to raise her illegal child with dignity.
Rogue Cop Axel Falcon returns as The Last Zombi Hunter, during the Zombie Apocalypse in this film of bloodshed and gore.
Mankind's forgotten past is affecting its future as one young man finds himself caught in the middle of a war between descendants of the original humans.

movie_name: My True Love Gave to Me
description: Grief-stricken, Brian returns to Quick Lake, where he invokes an ancient ritual to return his wife from the dead in exchange for human sacrifice. Investigating the first murder, DI Sarah Cooper must uncover the truth, and save herself.

movie_name: The House of a Thousand Candles
description: An English diplomat's (Phillips Holmes) girlfriend (Mae Clarke) tags along as he takes a coded message to Geneva.
A hitman who's in Bangkok to pull off a series of jobs violates his personal code when he falls for a local woman and bonds with his errand boy.

Leon Guerrero, the Pinoy "Lone Ranger" symbolizes the fight of good over evil and the triumph of right over wrong. Lito Lapid plays the legendary crime-fighting gunslinger who champions the oppressed and punish the oppressor and tyrants.
A hit man working for "the Organization" meets and falls in love with a young woman who eventually turns on him for money. Larry Anderson
An aspiring artist/ex-con and affirmed bachelor is about to risk everything by painting himself into a corner with the forgery of a 15th-century masterpiece, and by falling for the wrong woman.

It was supposed to be the perfect getaway but Adam Payson and four friends are spun into a nightmare when a series of terrifying events forces them to Exit 13, trapping them in an abandoned cabin and in a race to escape the evil within.

A brilliant recent graduate struggles to find work. After falling into a babysitting job, she is introduced by the child's mother to the world of the international call center, its employees, and the fast pace that drives them.
A crack team of Navy Seal Six, get more then they asked for, when they come across a swarm of out of control Androids while out on a Top Secret Mission.

A British woman trying to escape Hungary with her freedom fighter lover and a group of Westerners, as the Soviet Union moves to crush the Hungarian Revolution of 1956, finds herself the obsession of an enigmatic Communist officer.

Vildan is an author of famous romance novels. But now she is blocked, so the publisher offers her to change genre and write a thriller. In the house in the mountains where she goes to write inexplicable phenomena start to happen.
Two independent adult actresses attempt to find meaning in their work and relationships; one with her best friend, the other with her worst enemy.
Lucas Caine awakens mysteriously in Tibet with no memory of how he got there. After returning home to Chicago, he discovers he is part of a centuries-old conflict between warring immortals.

movie_name: I Hate Toronto: A Love Story
description: A young man's life is struck by tragedy. The only way out seems to be suicide but he decides to have a bit of fun first. It takes 200 meaningless women to meet the one woman that could give meaning to his life again.

Jack Knight deals with the death of his father by looking through his old possessions. While saying one last goodbye to his father Jack starts gaining mysterious powers. Meanwhile, an evil scientist wants to destroy the city.
A veteran US Marine sniper is partnered with a rookie sniper as his spotter to take out a politician and a rebel leader in the jungles of Panama.

A kingdom called Rathanpur was taken ruthlessly by a feudal lord named Bhairav Singh. The princess of that empire was in a hopeless situation until a maverick cop named Sardaar Gabbar Singh came along.
New Year's Eve 1975: Two cop detectives are staking out Renzo. He's suspected of killing a cop among others. Will the 2 cops do the necessary to get their man?

During World War I, a British aristocrat, an American entrepreneur, and the latter's attractive young daughter, set out to destroy a German battlecruiser, which is awaiting repairs in an inlet just off Zanzibar.

A princess visiting the US is saved from being arrested in an illegal speakeasy by a prizefighter. They fall in love, but she must go back to her nation to become queen, and can't marry a commoner. Complications ensue.
A web of intrigue and conspiracy lies beneath the euphoria as the U.S. is about to put a man on the moon for the first time in over thirty years.
An enigmatic Japanese woman, abandoned by her wealthy Chinese husband in a remote Pacific Northwest village, becomes entwined in the lives of two rugged locals.

Waiting for her boyfriend to join her on a country vacation, three months pregnant Daphne bonds with his cousin Maxime, and their shared intimacy brings them closer together into a full fledged love affair.

Radio astronomers discover a mysterious signal in the deep sea that could be contact with extraterrestrials. After several terrifying manifestations threaten their beliefs, the team must fight to survive the ultimate evil.

And suddenly, overnight, the world came to a halt. Two men, two survivors, one kid, and hatred that separates them. A place forgotten by everyone, including the creatures that inhabit the Earth... until now.
When her fiancé bows out on the eve of her wedding, Michal refuses to cancel the wedding arrangements. An Orthodox Jew, she insists that God will supply her a husband. As the clock ticks down.
A young, successful married couple, find themselves faced with tests in their relationship, when a frenemy crosses boundaries.

H-Block is set against the real story of the breakout from the maximum security Maze Prison in 1983, which saw 38 IRA prisoners escape and only 19 ever recaptured, and 20 guards shot or stabbed, with one dying.

movie_name: Wounded Warrior: My Love is True
description: A father's love for his daughter has dire consequences when he tries to get her to break up with the man she loves.
A sea creature is terrorizing a small Gulf coast town. The creature is a mutation from the Deep Water Horizon's oil spill in the Gulf. But it's not the only thing that's mutating.
An honest lawyer seeks revenge against a powerful don and decides to break the law after learning that his revenge cannot be fulfilled through due process of law. Whether he succeeds in his attempt ?
Willy, Kurt and Hans are broke, so they sell their car and open a filling station. Then they all fall in love with the same girl.

A pair of city boys get in trouble with a backwoods North Carolina family, when the boys try to stop the abuse of the family's step daughter. A pair of locals decide to step up to help the boys and the girl.

Intent on delving deep into the abysmal realm of self-mutilation, Daniel locks himself in the bathroom and begins an esoteric conversation of blood and suffering with the goddess, Ishtar. Will his sacrifice open the path to enlightenment?
On December 16th, 2011, eight people on their way to Las Vegas stopped in the ghost town of Garlock, California. This footage documents what happened.

Meet Chuck and Lloyd, best of friends and hopeless stoners. They share an apartment and work together at an exterminating company. While conducting their daily duties, these best buds ...                See full synopsis »
A re-imagining of the Arthurian legend centered around Arthur's illegitimate son Owain who must learn to take up his father's mantle as king.

A low security psychiatric ward is plagued by more than careless staff when a woman named Mira arrives. The patients must discover if the demons she is battling are a disorder, or something deadly about to commit them all permanently.

The son of a joint family falls in love with the daughter of a powerful state minister. Everyone is happy when the two get engaged. But, in a surprise turn of events, the boy calls off the engagement.
The former World Heavyweight Champion Rocky Balboa serves as a trainer and mentor to Adonis Johnson, the son of his late friend and former rival Apollo Creed.
On Halloween, shy young waitress finds herself caught up in the midst of a night full of debauchery, mayhem and murder.

movie_name: Pathfinders: In the Company of Strangers
description: Three companies of paratroopers travel in a deadly mission to France to prepare the drop zone for the airborne attack on the D-Day. They have to install an Eureka transmitter and searchlight to guide the planes in the Normandy invasion.
Teenagers sneak into a closed department store to explore its haunted house attraction, and are attacked by someone wearing a Chinese doll mask. Is it the mall's legendary ghost, or something else?
After the death of is grandfather a royal Hebrew African Israelite elder, Garbial Sabie is passed on the mantle of The Lion Of Judah protector of his village.

A scream in the night - City girl Aisling O'Neill receives a frantic telephone call from her troubled brother Doran. He is lost on the mountain of Slieve De Danaan - lost, terror stricken - and running for his life.

Valerie finds herself alone in an old theater. She soon realizes she's trapped. Her fear intensifies as she begins to see figures lurking in the shadows, and it's not long before these figures begin to attack and menace her.
Crime lord Jim Belmont escapes FBI custody and begins a reign of thievery that is thwarted at every turn by Jerry Blake, the FBI's Operator 99.
Details the life of Declan, a former Irish insurgent who finds his violent past come back to haunt him when incarcerated on a narcotics charge in San Diego.

In the distant future, humans are declared "illegal residents" and hunted to near extinction by murderous robots. One day, a group of human scavengers come across a strange man named Killy, who may be the key to humanity's survival.
The recovery of a microchip off the body of a fellow agent leads James Bond to a mad industrialist who plans to create a worldwide microchip monopoly by destroying California's Silicon Valley.
When a troubled teenage girl undergoes an experimental hypnotherapy for her night terrors, something is unleashed which stalks her waking hours.
A violent youngster and a shy Brahmin girl fall in love but tragedy intervenes when the youngster is brain-damaged following a fight.
When professional ambitions clash with personal feelings for a modern-day couple, a love story from a bygone era may offer some wisdom.

After two years in prison for participating in an illegal street race, Roy says no to a new illegal winter race from Bergen to Murmansk in the North of Russia. But then he hears that his daughter will participate with a boyfriend.

Ad executive Bella is a nice and hardworking girl turning to her thirty,she devoted herself to love and work but end up got dumped and about to lose her job.Until the airborne secretary Kai showed up.

Rika, a bright, attractive, and driven young woman, is intent on marrying her dreamy boyfriend Seiichi Ono who is not only tall and handsome but also an up-and-coming executive. One day, Ono abruptly dumps her.
One man's descent into madness as he tries to discover what comes for him in the middle of the night.

Four dangerous men escape while en route to a high-security prison and go in search of the hidden treasure of Artwork, worth a fortune. But things start to go wrong for the gang when the town misfit sets out to stop them.
Two people in love decide to take their lives in two different directions. Their relationship is tested, their beliefs are shaken, their love is threatened.
After a deadly viral outbreak, an elite squad of special forces soldiers must infiltrate a quarantine zone to rescue a scientist who holds the only cure to save mankind.
In Britain, bodies of NATO paratroopers are being snatched during routine jumps by a mysterious red-beam of alien origin.

After settling into a turn-of-the-century home to recover from the tragic loss of her daughter, a young woman discovers a series of paranormal events that torment her even more than the death of her child.

When a young woman discovers a gift for seeing a person's death, she figures out how to use this to her financial benefit...that is, until a child dies in someone else's place - Money can be a cruel, powerful and deadly lure.

In the middle of Patagonia, Margarita waits for the train that will bring her a coffin and also a letter with memories and triggers a story in which she works as a servant and suffers Teresa's cries, and lavishes the pawn's kisses.

Longing for reunion with the dead and seduced by the chaotic allure of possession, a young woman struggles to find meaning in a barren, apocalyptic landscape, while those around her succumb to despair and madness.
When Nando's father got killed he decides to find out the reason of this father's death but he found a tribe village named as Mahasu
Princess Shizu's family is wiped out by an family of undead seeking revenge. The eight samurai can save her, but who and where are they?
LOGLINE: Angel Of Death A grieving mother must confront the angel of death to get her daughter back from the dead.
A con man and a Chinese government agent each have their own reasons for trying to recover a historical artifact from agents of Japan.

movie_name: You'll Be the Death of Me
description: Nothing can spoil falling in love in New York City, but a masked knife-wielding psychopath hell bent on keeping you single can certainly make falling in love more difficult.
A young woman is thrown into a world of mad science and blood-thirsty beasts while searching for her missing sister in a mysterious swamp.
When a single mother suffers a nervous breakdown, she is suspected of child abuse and her child is taken away. Her mental suffering escalates as she succumbs to her darkest fantasies.
A soldier-of-fortune steals some Russian nerve gas from Afghanistan, and brings it to the U.S. to be analyzed. A greedy millionaire rancher finds out about it and sets out to steal it.
Three college students on a wilderness getaway run into criminals and vanish, leaving behind home videos that the police scrutinize for clues.

When Karen Palmer's 11-year-old child Stevie convinces her to go to a local horror convention, in spite of her fear of all things horror, she finds herself fighting for survival against THE HARVESTER, a supernatural sickle wielding killer.
After being framed for the murder of a US Senator, a secret government security team comes out of hiding to thwart a high profile assassination.
After witnessing a man's death in a bizarre accident, Father Pergado goes on a spiritual retreat, where he encounters his alien double bent on world conquest.
A small-time gangster clumsily attempts to court a girl he has a crush on. Can he win her over and leave the underworld behind?
Two twenty somethings fall into what some would call love and others would call dysfunction while trying to figure out what they want in life.

movie_name: The Sixth Dumbest Thing in the World
description: A May-December romance blossoms when a lonely elderly woman saves her delusional upstairs neighbor from several suicide attempts, but after falling in love, and getting married the real romance begins.

A disease that turns people into zombies has been cured. Society discriminates against the once-infected zombies, as do their own families, which causes social issues to arise. This leads to militant government interference.

A trail of fear leads a lone Traveller into the ruins of a neo-apocalyptic valley. Discovering a decimated population, the few survivors warn of a monster beyond flesh, a scourge known only as The Phantom Machine.
A downcast young woman who suffers from mono-phobia wakes up isolated on a beach. Her friends are missing and she has no idea about how she got there.
When Carlos Andrés decides that the best way to contribute to his family is to become a porn actor, the only problem is that his girlfriend does not know about his successful career.

movie_name: Nishan e Haider: Captain Mohammad Sarwar Shaheed
description: On the 27th July 1948, As Captain Mohammad Sarwar moved forward with six of his men to cut their way through a barbed wire enemy's barrier, he Martyred when his chest was riddled by a burst of heavy machine gun fire.

A young woman is transformed into a vampire by a virus. The vampire doctor who's treating her hires a young scientist to find a cure. He and the girl fall for each other hard, but she, mad from hunger, escapes to wreak havoc on the city.
With the aid of a wealthy erratic tippler, a dewy-eyed tramp who has fallen in love with a sightless flower girl accumulates money to be able to help her medically.
An orphan girl escapes her caregivers to be with a young man raised at the zoo whose only previous friends are the animals.
A nightmare comedy about a school counselor whose compassion, generosity and dedication destroy the lives of everyone around him.
A bachelor lets his superiors use his apartment for their trysts but then discovers that the woman he loves is in a relationship with his boss.

A scheming brother and sister team headline Cabaret Diabolique. The show is fierce - the finale is an onstage murder. Is it real? Two detectives investigate the popular cabaret and untangle a web of madness.

For 50 years no girls were born in a small village deep in the mountains. A professor, his assistant and his female students from university arrive in this isolated village for field work. Will they make it back?

Swamy and Anand who look exactly the same, come from different backgrounds. Under dicey circumstances Pranavi, a young and pretty girl falls in love with both of them. How will Swamy and Anand solve their problems?
A lady doctor and three nurses fight off a number of men attackers, in a confuse plot about pills who have strange effects on women's self-determination and sexual behaviour.
When a vaudeville comic and a pretty young dancer have little luck in their separate careers, they decide to combine their acts; to save money on the road, they get married.
A sexy bride ditches her mobster fiancé at the altar and goes on the run, but things go awry for her when she seeks refuge by pretending to be a young man's mother.
Melissa and a group of friend go in a road trip to help her overcome her antisocial and shy behavior, instead they ended in the land of a serial killer.
A discount store clerk strikes up an affair with a stock boy who considers himself the incarnation of Holden Caulfield.

Independent filmmaker Arthur and breakthrough actress Clara are both avoiding mainstream responsibilities but stuck together in a Cornish Farmhouse they must confront the true reasons for their isolation.

The story of a man caught in a whirlpool of grief and rage over the murder of his wife, Prayer to a Vengeful God is contemporary revenge drama, presented in an austere visual style, completely without dialogue.

When John takes his friends to his deceased uncle's remote ranch to hunt wild pigs, it seems like a typical guys weekend. But as John and his crew trek deeper into the forest, they begin tracking the awful truth about his uncle's demise.
A brutal abduction goes from bad to worse when a middle-aged kidnapper falls in love with his teen victim.
During an escalating zombie epidemic, two Philadelphia SWAT team members, a traffic reporter and his TV executive girlfriend seek refuge in a secluded shopping mall.
An innocent child stumbles onto a collection of evil dolls in her new home that want to claim her as one of their own.

Two Captains is a thrilling murder-mystery, set in the present day, that flashes back to the sinking of the Lusitania in 1915 to unravel one of history's greatest mysteries, and reveal the shocking truth for the first time ever.
A college graduate steps up as a Mexican cartel don after his father dies in a coup by the Plaza Bosses and a dangerous sicario, who was his childhood friend.
A young woman must deliver a top-secret motorcycle to the US military after the man assigned to deliver it, her lover, is murdered by enemy agents.

On a journey of discovery what you find might not be what you were looking for. Almira's quest for happiness reveals that learning to love for real also means to let go of the her life as she had known it before.
A grieving widower documents his return to Vieques Island to hunt the thing he claims is responsible for his fiance's mysterious death.
An advanced civilization rescues a team of secret government agents from a plane crash and grants them superhuman abilities.
After learning about the dangers of time travel, a young scientist gets caught up in a dangerous mission to prevent it from ever being invented.
An ancient legend becomes a predicament to the faith of two lovers coming from very different cultural, religious and social backgrounds.
Corruption lit the heat. Retired CIA Frank Klein is brought into an international terrorist plot, which is exploited by deep branches of a south American government.
A documentary-style drama about the "Fouke Monster", a Bigfoot-type creature that has been sighted in and around Fouke, Arkansas since the 1950s.
Base on real events Yanga is story of a village of slaves that raise against of the Spanish empire before of the independence of México.
Based on a popular radio drama of the 1950s. A war widow is courted by a young chauffer, but his employer's daughter hopes to make him her husband
A group of students on their vacation trapped in the abandoned house of an archaeologist who set free mysterious demonic powers.
An old gunslinger and his daughter must face the consequences of his past, when the son of a man he murdered years ago arrives to take his revenge.
A female war Vet suffering from PTSD unable to cope with normal society, puts her lethal expertise to work.

A group of young political activists breaks the law to get attention to animal rights, by freeing caged animals from labs and farms during night time, leading to highly illegal sabotage actions, putting them under increasing pressure.

A weathered Lieutenant, his police force, and a local vigilante are all caught up in a dangerous scheme involving a troubled, recently-arrested man who's linked to years of female abductions and murders.

A story of love and obsession. A young radio personality who, after her mother dies, discovers she had been having a love affair for 15 years. Now she finds herself recreating her mother's romance by getting involved with a married man.
A woman hires an actor from an agency to pose as her fiance to make her dying grandmother happy, and they fall for each other during the ruse.
A police officer tracks down a cyber criminal that hacks the passwords of innocent people in order to destroy their lives.
Tensions mount in an Andalusia mining town between local Spanish workers and their British employers.
At loose ends drifter (Ivan Martin) stumbles upon a struggling painter (Drea de Matteo) as he searches for answers under the stars and rooftops of New York.
An aging widow from New York City follows her daughter to Los Angeles in hopes of starting a new life after her husband passes away.
A hardened bounty hunter, a gang of outlaws in his trust and a preacher are forced to work together and battle their way across the old west of the 1870s when the zombie apocalypse begins.

movie_name: The Ghosts of Somerville: Mrs. Micks
description: First in this film series of hauntings in this historic town. Found dead in her attic, eaten by her cats, Mrs. Micks makes her presence known to people living in her house, with witnesses' accounts and opinions by a psychic expert.
When a young soldier deserts the army, the officers decide to look for him on their own before the military prosecutor takes over the case.

movie_name: Ta dyo podia s' ena papoutsi
description: With her irritatingly outdated style, a meek and innocent country girl gets a drastic makeover to win the attention of her confident dandy boss. However, can a radical transformation help the charming mademoiselle win his heart?

Tells about the journey of Raga to find his true identity as a guardian of the universe. With the help of his uncle Jaya, Raga must face the forces of evil in order to protect two universes, the human world and the spirit world.
A couple search for each other years after the night they first met, fell in love, and separated, convinced that one day they'd end up together.

Alonzo is the host of a popular paranormal show Psychics, Magic or Frauds, that focuses on revealing the true side of the paranormal. In his mission of debunking frauds, his life is turned upside down when he offends a local Santero.
Life which is full of distresses of Hakan that can't get rid of the shadows of the past starts to change with miracles with his meeting Nur the angel.
Returning home from prison, a Vietnam War veteran sets out to clean up his hometown which has come under the control of a violent motorcycle gang.

The lives of Mouna, a weather scientist who falls in love with Yaazhan, a quirky and loving guy. What happens to their relationship after a couple of years and how things take an unexpected turn after the arrival of Malarvizhi?

In a future mega city, where most people spend most time hooked up to a virtual world, an agent, employed by a corporation supplying virtual reality, is busy tracking down killers/terrorists, both in the virtual and real world.

A sequel to mystic thriller Karthikeya (2014), which deals with the personal problems of Karthik and how he comes out of them. His pursuit of the truth leads him to find out the power of Indian ancient system and Tatva of Lord Sri Krishna.
A group of old college friends reunite for a trip to a forest in Sweden, Northern Europe, but encounter a menacing presence there stalking them.
A happy marriage lands in trouble after the wife's sister develops an infatuation with her brother-in-law.
A young woman engaged to be married finds herself in an affair with her soon-to-be stepmother's lesbian daughter.
When a dark power enshrouds the Earth after a total solar eclipse, the scattered Sailor Guardians must reunite to bring light back into the world.
Super Car 8B is the best car in China Big Race. fast Driver come to America to Race in famous race across USA.
A young mother in an abusive marriage confronts the darkness and discrimination in her small Southern town using the terrifying power of a Tarot deck.
Rebecca is a monster, but she wants to become a real human girl. Her family follows her to our world and embarks on a series of murders designed to bring her back into the fold.

The Greeting is a Thriller/Horror film that revolves a person, Sanjay approaching his therapist Dr. Raj to discuss about the issues that he's facing in his personal life. Their discussion leads to unravel a mystery that is unknown to both.
The dogs can talk at a family of 4, where mom loses her job the same day dad gets a job as pilot for a cute, single boss.
While investigating the local legend of a haunted cornfield, a group of young people are stranded and stalked over the course of one Autumn night.

It tells the story of women raped and left nearly dead, by a dark gang of five guys hided below a mask : Mister Pig, Mister Rabbit, Mister Frog, Mister Sheep and Mister Wolf. Now she had decided to get revenge.
After the death of her adoptive mother, a young woman follows the trail of letters written by her birth mother, finding romance along the way.

Emerald is an agent the Germans "have" inside allied intelligence 1944/WWII. With "help" from Emerald, the Germans catch Wheeler, believed to know the when and where of D-Day. Emerald is sent to be Wheeler's cell mate. Let the game begin.
When a MLA's son kills his wife, a man attempts to bring him to justice and hopes that his estranged sister a Judge, will support him in the cause.

Balthazar Blake, an apprentice of the legendary magician Merlin, must train his old teacher's successor - an introverted but resourceful physics prodigy - in the art of sorcery to prevent the return of Morgana le Fay.
A secret agent must race against time to stop terrorists about to unleash an unknown strain of the Ebola Virus.
The story of a bunch of misfits whose misconception about each others backgrounds end up in a series of chaotic, yet comic outcomes.

In a world of martial arts and magic, a dark assassin seeks the power of the four "Dragons," martial arts masters of supernatural strength. When his actions cause the death of a young man's family, his downfall becomes inevitable.
A handsome young drifter is found unconscious near a remote monastery, where he joins forces with a vengeful spirit as he seduces and converts each of the monks to join his league of the undead.
While visiting a cabin with her husband, Julianne becomes disturbed with horrific visions which question her sanity.
A young woman moves to another city after receiving a job promotion, but she begins to be stalked by someone willing to end her life.
A middle-aged businessman finds himself in thirst for romance adventure, and it seems that a proper partner is not far away.
Crossed phone lines in 1989 lead to a life changing conversation between two strangers, who eventually meet in an unusual way.
When her father is taken hostage, a woman is forced into a life of crime; and soon, everyone is after the priceless necklace in her possession.

Helle has been waiting for her husband Peter to retire. Her dreams are crushed when Peter comes home with a big surprise; he is pursuing a new career as a wine importer and has invested all their savings in a vineyard in Austria.
Six college friends unite for a weekend getaway where they find themselves fighting for their lives after a terrorist attack turns the local residents into rage infused zombies.
While dealing with the loss of their mother, a trans-person struggles to come out to their emotionally arrested father while he himself transforms into a giant mole.

On board a riverboat bound for Creek City, singer Jimmie Davis, who is going to become half-owner of a land development company willed to him by his uncle, shares a cabin with traveling ...                See full synopsis »
Some elite troops from South Korea trying to solve an amount of missing and death cases at the border between North- and South Korea.
One month before getting married, Lola finds herself traveling with her ex-boyfriend, his sister, and her recently deceased father's partner.
Chief Brody's widow believes that her family is deliberately being targeted by another shark in search of revenge.

Four sets of friends spend Halloween weekend at the Beautiful Creekside "Kamp of Antietam". Each attending is promised a "Once In A Lifetime" experience, but there's more than just fresh air and fishing going on at the K.O.A.
A few years after a one night stand, a married man discovers that the woman from that night is now getting married to his best friend.

When an expendable henchman suddenly enters the narrative after stopping the action hero, he must take over the role as protagonist and bring down the megacorporation that supplies disposable "bad guys" to villains in order to survive.
A stubborn, narcissistic film critic must co-exist with everything he despises at the same time in order to reach his version of utopia.
Arumugam lands in the city to protest to a minister about water pollution in his village. Here, he gets involved in a battle against corrupt politicians and rowdies, who leave him practically dead.

Maki travels from Japan to Hong Kong and Thailand in order to show the superiority of Japanese karate to those countries' native to martial arts. Romance, intrigue, martial arts are the ingredients of this films atmosphere.
A woman with no name teams up with a resourceful militiaman and a video-store clerk turned wandering gunslinger to rescue a scientist who may hold the key to ridding the world of the undead.
Ten strangers are taken to the snowy summits of the Andes; The challenge is to survive in an underground shelter.
An unruly class of gifted and charming teenage boys are taught by two eccentric and innovative teachers, as their headmaster pushes for them all to get accepted into Oxford or Cambridge.

Charlie Darwin is a Time Traveling vigilante, join him as he reflects his journey when cornered by his past wife Lara Darwin in 1984 who takes a fancy to this unknown older version of her husband and delves in to his life story.
A pensive man visits an empty house. A neighbor tells him the house is haunted but he ignores it. Park Jinseong's second feature that takes place in Jeju Island gazes into the pain of life.
Lost on a train of thought tunneling through the dark night of his unconscious, a former rabbinical student struggles to resolve a paralyzing conflict between his mind and his body.
A CEO hires a stand up comedian to seduce his sister after they two fight to the control of their family company.
When a private investigator falsely imprisoned in Asia discovers she's the patsy in a global conspiracy, she must team up with a Chinese cop to save the world.
The story revolves around a mysterious man, who is always there to help the poor and punish the ones, who are unjust and corrupt.
Two strangers stuck in Fairbanks during a layover end up falling in love after a line of questioning.
An American who has lived much of his life outside the country returns to Arizona for the first time in years and encounters villainy.
A martial artist with a tragic past seeks revenge on those who wronged him, but in doing so creates even more suffering.

An ex-CIA agent and his estranged daughter are forced on the run when his employers erase all records of his existence, and mark them both for termination as part of a wide-reaching international conspiracy.
An undercover Federal officer serving time in prison fakes his escape in order to infiltrate a heroin smuggling ring.
Not even a bullet can stop a real hero. Full-length sequel to the high-profile series with Pavel Prilunny

After her parents divorce, Cintia moves to her aunt Helena and begins to dream of becoming a DJ. When matters of the heart will stand between her and her objectives, Cintia's career will take an unexpected turn.
A horror film in production is put on pause due to an accident on set. The director decides to utilize the break to revamp the script. A trip to find inspiration proves to be a bad idea.

An honest and tough police officer working in Islamabad, is been dispatched to Karachi, where a psychopathic serial killer is on a lose who has been targeting police officers one by one by giving them a gruesome death.
The daughter of a peasant family that works on a landowner's property is in love with the owner's son but the parents force them to separate.She lands up having a child out of wedlock.
A group of stranded travelers takes refuge in an old abandoned house, only to find out that they are not the only residents of the building.
A doofus kung-fu cop and his wise-cracking pooch must outwit an evil genius before he unleashes Armageddon with his demonic mind-control ray.
A Christmas Eve party at a luxury residential building takes a horrific turn when a fire breaks out.
A detective teams up with a talk-show host to take down a homophobic serial killer on the streets of Toronto.

The Occupy movement spurs a family to move into an abandon house formally the residence of a serial killer. As the serial killer awaits execution on death row, they soon learn the house is already occupied.
When two occultists attempt to ressurect Ancient Forces, they find that their differences could lead to their destruction.

Lord and Bull are two adventurers recruited by Judge Warren for a mysterious mission. On reaching the village to know the details of the mission they don't find the judge and discover that many people want them dead.

movie_name: Seré cualquier cosa, pero te quiero
description: Based on the play "Llegó El Plomero", by Sergio De Cecco. A 40-year-old woman finds her daily routine complicated by falling in love with a plumber.
An American ninja's wife is held hostage by a sadistic Nazi chemist on an Asian island. He teams up with an African-American ninja to rescue her.
A journalist cum social activist tie between an elder photographer and a young student. Her dilemma and her dark life in the city of Mumbai in the late 90s
A remake of the 1989 film Abused By Beauty where a mother and granddaughter team drink poison water polluted by the government and turn into vicious, unhinged maniacs.
A drunkard priest who has been cast out by his community struggles to atone and regain his honour and dignity.

movie_name: Gekijouban Sekaiichi hatsukoi: Yokozawa Takafumi no baai
description: Yokozawa meets a man (Kirishima) and his life is turned around. Kirishima starts to blackmail and tease Yokozawa, but Kirishima might actually be trying to help him recover from an emotional period of his life in the process.

Clara, a lonely nurse from the outskirts of São Paulo, is hired by mysterious and wealthy Ana as the nanny for her unborn child. The two women develop a strong bond, but a fateful night changes their plans.

In early Republican China, rumors were going around about the treasure in Wudang Mountain. An American conspirator took his well-trained kung fu daughter to Wudang by sponsoring a Taoist martial arts competition, to steal the treasure.
The forces of good and evil clash in this martial-arts picture, as personified by warriors and overlords from the Orient's past.
A girls loses a leg and falls in love with a young doctor at the hospital, after her fiance rejects her because of her amputation.

A young woman, the only survivor of a mass killing, wakes up in a room she assumes is a police interrogation room. As the woman recounts the night to a detective, other memories make her interrogation a true nightmare.

Jenny leaves home at the earliest opportunity. However, live-in boyfriend Rick's associations with witchcraft and black magic soon take her down a path which leads to the most horrific experience of her young life.
A young couple meets with a tragic incident and one of them resort to scientific methods to retrieve lost memory .
The social lives of four coming-of-age sisters are shaken when they discover they are moving - to another neighborhood.
A UN reporter broadcasts a report on the appearance of a prehistoric monster that emerges from hibernation while a pharmaceutical company seeks publicity with a monster of their own. (US Version)
A young car thief on parole in Chicago steals the wrong car on the wrong night and finds himself as the driver and pawn for the mob and dirty cops in a vicious game of cat and mouse.

Through a series of dreamlike images, a girl and her three friends find themselves stranded in a dark and surrealistic forest by someone - or something - who has obsessively loved, watched, and waited for the girl ever since childhood.
Searching for his long-separated sister, a man arrives in Kolkata and gets into a brawl with the local goons.
Stanley Barker is looking for the woman of his dreams. She must love to cook. She must have an appreciation of old movies. And she must love romantic walks on the beach. Be careful what you wish for.

Frank Bass takes a stand and defends what he thinks is right. Gamblers and money-grubbing conspire to corrupt the industry. Frank's efforts climax as he promotes an over-the-hill champion in the final matches of his career.
Tony is in a race against time to save his kidnapped wife before she is murdered but as he unravels the mystery behind her abduction he discovers they are after more than money.
When a brooding young man from a sleepy southern town reluctantly accepts the lead in a rich girl's student film shot in an abandoned funeral home, a sinister entity is awakened.

Ray Scales wants complete control of organized crime in the city, but the old Mob leader (Daniel Baldwin) has other plans for Ray. Now only his retired hitman father can save him....but can anyone trust the mystery woman?
Spanish soldier Juan Ricardo is assigned to obtain evidence against Pedro the Fox, an old smuggler. His acquaintance with Pedro's wife Guerita ripens into mutual love.
A young Japanophile Belgian woman in Tokyo falls into a whirlwind romance with a Francophile Japanese student.

A conniving wife has her husband murdered, and also plans to kill his nephew, the only heir, with the assistance of her ex-lover. When she tries to double-cross the ex-lover, he and the heir team up and kill her bodyguards.
The life at the Military Academy of Agulhas Negras, with a cadet living remarkable moments during school times.
Sathya and Vasanth are two best pals since their childhood. An employee of Sathya's mother wants his daughter to get married to Sathya. He has selfish motives behind this desire.
A look into the inequities of the ghosts of society through three interwoven french new wave styled vignettes by three different visual and literary artists.

movie_name: Be My Cat: A Film for Anne
description: An aspiring filmmaker goes to shocking extremes to convince Hollywood actress Anne Hathaway to star in his film. First entry in Adrian Tofei's trilogy which includes We Put the World to Sleep and Pure.
The soul of a dead navy seal appears in his son's computer game in order to transmit a secret about a major terrorist attack
Peter as an artist is dangerously obsessed with his art and ambition, yet he manages to realize his dream with a way that he never dare to think of.
Put behind bars, a bank-robbing n'er-do-well schemes against the cop who locked him up. Once released, he's out for revenge.
A fireman takes an unexpected course of action when a man whom he's been ordered to testify against, after being held up at a local convenience store, threatens him.
The agent for the Devil takes the soul of a high school sophomore in exchange for a date with the most popular girl on campus.
Cynthia is a horror film about the 'perfect' couple and their desperate obsession to have a child which descends into a terrifying dark comedy.
Rafa's hooked on the pure, fiery feelings he gets from speed racing, but when his kid's mom gets mixed up with drug dealers, he burns rubber to save her.

movie_name: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea
description: When the Earth is threatened by a burning Van Allen Radiation Belt, U.S. Navy Admiral Harriman Nelson plans to shoot a nuclear missile at the Belt, using his experimental atomic submarine, the Seaview.
After becoming a widow with three children, Maria accepts the help of Genaro, the rich owner of a car dealership. She is willing to do anything for her family.
When tragedy strikes a family on the verge of a new beginning, they are forced to face the demons of their past in order to still have a chance at a future.

Against the will of his peers, Sheriff Nick Whittaker must compromise his principles as law enforcer in order to protect the citizens of Eden Mills from a colony of wolf-like creatures dwelling in an abandoned mine shaft.
Pooja and Chander connect over the telephone and fall in love when they finally meet. However, since Pooja's alcoholic father would never approve, she decides to run away from her house.

Hallam's talent for spying on people reveals his darkest fears-and his most peculiar desires. Driven to expose the true cause of his mother's death, he instead finds himself searching the rooftops of the city for love.

Some time after their botched operation to capture a known Palestinian terrorist, a team of Israeli agents starts to get killed off one by one. Their leader must get to the bottom of things before the killer(s) plan is complete.
Shiva and Nandini fall in love with each other but their parents are political heads of the village then complications arise when they elope.

As a thirty something acting teacher attempts to push a group of eager young performers out of their comfort zones, he struggles with his own ability to live an authentic and fulfilling life with his teenage son.
In order to win the love of an Aussie bombshell, a Middle Eastern boy fakes being in a relationship with the Middle Eastern girl his parents want him to marry.
A group of recovering addicts are taken on a retreat in the desert to work on their sobriety, only to find much more sinister forces awaiting them.
After having their first child, an interracial couple struggles to hold onto their marriage while dealing with temptations in pursuit of normalcy.
An architect's desire to speak with his wife from beyond the grave becomes an obsession with supernatural repercussions.
What should have been a lovely vacation in the sunshine state turns into a nightmare of catastrophic proportion when strangers find themselves trapped it what seems and endless moment in time.
"The Valley" is a medieval psychological horror about a young travelling family with dark secrets. The Valley has a brooding and eerie reputation, but everywhere has its ghost stories, right?
A young girl who is about to receive a large inheritance is abducted to an isolated sanitarium where a crazed doctor is performing strange experiments.

movie_name: Captain Sabertooth and the Treasure of Lama Rama
description: The orphan boy Pinky follows the Captain on an exciting and dangerous journey across the big oceans to the kingdom of Lama Rama, hunting for a treasure and the answer to who is Pinky's father.

A poor, uneducated mountain girl leaves her cabin in search of respect, a wealthy husband, and a better life in this fictionalized biopic of Margaret "Molly" Brown, who survived the 1912 sinking of the RMS Titanic.

After playing with friends, evoking spirits, Song DuoDuo, a psychology student at the medical college, begins to have a nightmare of three people playing Ouija board game and has a strong impression that something is haunting her.

A love story inspired by the life of a Latin American businessman, Gonzalo Mejía and his romance with Polish countess Isolda Pruzinsky; who met in Rome in 1906, fate brings them together and apart in unexpected moments of their lives.
It tells the story of Hernán. He unearths a human-shaped root for which he begins to feel an inexplicable attraction.
An egoistic wealthy man becomes a cop to settle a score, but gets into a feud with a local politician.
A girl fed up with the torture of her stepmother fled to her maternal uncle's village where she fell in love with a rich boy.
Julian's wife was raped when she protested his arrest, and later gives birth to a son. When the son dares to love the daughter of a wealthy Spaniard, he is hunted down.
Many students attending Westfield State University go missing over the course of a number of months, this is the police discovered footage of what transpired.
The 7 Swords, a primeval relic capable catastrophic destruction, falls into the hands of a young college girl who must now become its protector and fend off her newly sworn enemies.
Kannas and Kadalas are rag pickers who enjoy life to the fullest. Their lives take a turn when they meet Munna, who comes in search of his bugle that was stolen by them.
An uncompromising, visionary architect struggles to maintain his integrity and individualism despite personal, professional and economic pressures to conform to popular standards.

The story of the world's top aircraft repo man--who's lost his pilot's license. An extreme aviation film, based on the real-life adventures of Mike Kennedy, aircraft recovery specialist and the best jet thief in the business.

On the H.M.S. Defiant, during the French Revolutionary War, fair Captain Crawford is locked in a battle of wills against his cruel second-in-command Lieutenant Scott-Padget, whose heavy-handed command style pushes the crew to mutiny.

Haj Haidar is suspected of murder. First, this suicide crime is declared. His son, who is studying law, uncovers the story and, with the help of an investigator, searches for the killer. Something happens in this search.
After being discharged from the army, Antoine Doinel centers a screwball comedy where he applies for different jobs and tries to make sense of his relationships with women.
A man and woman from feuding families each pretend to fall in love, as part of a revenge plot. Chaos ensues when their fake romance becomes a reality.
A teenager's quest to launch Norwegian Black Metal in Oslo in the early 1990s results in a very violent outcome.
