A group of people work together to destroy a ghostly being who is haunting a house he used to live in.

movie_name: Winnie the Pooh: Blood and Honey
description: After Christopher Robin abandons them for college, Pooh and Piglet embark on a bloody rampage as they search for a new source of food.

For Craig, the trip was meant to be a quiet break where he could concentrate on writing his latest book. For his wife, Susan, and their two kids, it was meant to be a weekend away. For all of them it became a nightmare.
On a dangerous future Earth filled with monsters, an orphan tries to escape back to SkyArk, a man-made city in the sky, but he soon learns that he has a much greater purpose.
In the fall of 1986, six knuckleheads from Detroit travel north to partake in the annual tradition of deer hunting. But something horrific has been awakened and the hunters become the hunted.
When the neighborhood's beloved dogs are stolen by a comic book-inspired villain with an evil plan, it is up to eight brave and adventurous kids to set out on a mission to rescue their furry friends.
A group of friends out on a trip are trapped by a cannibal family that are trying to make sausages out of them

Sam Harrington (Edward Everrett Horton) is a simple horse lover who is mistaken for a champion steeplechase jockey and prevailed upon by Peggy Fairfax (Patsy Ruth Miller) to take part in an upcoming race.

In 1941 before the German attack in Greece, an officer and a soldier engaged in a spy operation within the Bulgarian borders. After returning to Greece, involved in the heroic defense of the fort Rupel in "Metaxa line", where their unit.

Gungaram, a poor, indebted farmer, works hard to educate his younger brother Jumna and make him a police officer. Years later, circumstances force Gungaram to become an outlaw and now the brothers confront each other as enemies.
The setting is Belgrade, Oct 1918, the closing days of World War 1, and the disintegration of the Austro-Hungarian empire.
Two newly paired cops who are complete opposites must put aside their differences in order to catch a gang of drug smugglers.

For seven long years mass murderer "Rabid Mike Darcy" has been planing his revenge on the police officers who left him to burn in a car crash. Tonight the battle begins if they are to save their loved ones.
A young couple is in love, but Nina's father has seen another young man as her future man. It doesn't help when Nina's lover is convicted.
The funny duo of Richard Gomez and Joey Marquez plays the parody characters of Clint Eastwood and Charles Bronson as they investigate crimes and track down criminals of screwball proportions.

Increasingly bizarre and disturbing events befall a businessman who arrives at an airport to find that his home country -- the same one he just departed -- seems to no longer exist, and neither does he.

A group of young amateurs participants in chats begin a risky game, attracted by the mysterious personality of a surfer. In one of these adventures, one of them dies. Then begins a nightmare of suspicion between them.
Clueless on a gruesome case, a skeptical and lonely policewoman in a small village, is guided by a newly arrived clairvoyance gifted boy, who claims that the murderer is the Virgin Mary.
Jacob Mclean, a young determined filmmaker and photographer, faces a sudden dip in life as he is haunted by a mysterious something from his past.

A forensic psychiatrist's husband is killed during a home invasion, but instead of identifying the killer, she recants. She stalks the newly released psychopath, deciding whether she wants to kill him, sleep with him, or try to know him.
Shankar, a graduate, awaits recruitment and lives as a tenant with Bhanu who seeks his company to stay away from her stepbrother. Meanwhile, Shankar begins to fall in love with Sarika.
An incompetent time traveler must team up with his unpredictable alternate self, to fix a paradox which is now slowly destroying the universe.

movie_name: Five Nights at Freddy's 3: This Happened Because of You
description: Amanda is lost in the middle of the huge amusement park. Death is right inside the amusement park. Amanda and her friends will have to face with an old enemy from the past who has unfinished business with them.
A small time crook that runs a loan sparking operation around a casino that runs dog fights meets a special someone that changes the course of his life.
A man tries to pick Sonia Jovovich "alias Anna" up in the bar but neither of them has the slightest idea who is the other one.

The story of 160 elite U.S. soldiers who dropped into Mogadishu in October 1993 to capture two top lieutenants of a renegade warlord, but found themselves in a desperate battle with a large force of heavily armed Somalis.

'Senses' is an unnerving exploration into the sights and sounds of the blind and the deaf. Experience the fears of the unknown through the eyes and ears of the disabled as they unite to survive a nationwide pandemic.
Michael Andrews gets a message from his brother Roy, it's about the Thomas Miller Tapes. He watches the tapes and then strange things begin happening to him.
A love story between a French filmmaker and a young Moroccan man. What is the connection between Gérard and the destiny of a country? The film is trying to give the answer.
Abandoned when young, Bhaiyaji gives shelter to Dev and Tutu. A game of defiance, deception and love follows when free-spirited Disha enters their life.

When Roger Canter, ex-Navy Seal returns from the horrors of combat, he only wants to marry his girlfriend and settle down. But when he is attacked and left for dead and his new wife brutalized, he is forced to vengeance.
A newly wedded husband plays a practical joke on his wife's family with full support from his wife and friends.
An infected T-Rex escapes from a Science Lab in downtown Los Angeles, destroying everything in it's path.
On a quest to cure himself of a rare blood disease, Dr. Michael Morbius accidentally infects himself with a form of vampirism instead.
A young English peer leaves England and Thumbs his way across Europe. He sings in hotels and restaurants to make ends meet. When he becomes successful he also finds true love.
the life of Francis Scott Key writer of the Star Spangled Banner and how he came to write the song that is known as the American national anthem.
An American woman goes to another country to find her husband with the help of a peculiar detective.

movie_name: The Witch: Part 2 - The Other One
description: A girl wakes up in a secret laboratory and meets Kyung-hee, who is trying to protect her from a gang. When the gang finally finds the girl, they are overwhelmed by an unexpected power.

movie_name: Poultrygeist: Night of the Chicken Dead
description: Zombified chickens attempt to kill the fast-food workers that cook them in a restaurant built on an ancient burial ground.
A Jewish Revolutionary Officer (ZOB) fleeing the Warsaw Ghetto encounters Nazi SS on the Vistula River. It becomes a race for survival and soon the hunted becomes the hunter.

New York City is in a panic caused by an insane murderer; Maria, a police officer is entrusted with the case; to do this, she pretends to be a prostitute. One night, she meets a possible suspect who holds her and her partner hostage.
What happens when a quiet martial arts master gets mixed up with a hustler with a product to sell, a hottie who knows no limits and a dumb rich guy who's caught in the wrong place?

Set in the distant future, mankind has harnessed the power of faster than light travel by harvesting the eggs of the largest species mankind has ever known. The only problem...they have to get them first.

Emma is convicted of a crime he never committed in a bid to save his sister Ella who gets caught up in a murder mystery that claims the life of her obsessive friend Caren and his girlfriend Vicky. William tries his best to bail him out.

The employees of a local Tattoo shop take a day off at the lake for food, fun and drinks. As the evening progresses, ghost stories and drinking combine. One by one, each person gets taken out, until it becomes a nightmare at Blood Cove.
Chakara is a 1980 Indian Malayalam film, directed by P. G. Vishwambharan. The film stars Jayan, Seema, Srividya and Sukumaran in lead roles. Music of the film was composed by G. Devarajan.

A group of military scientists attempt to pull off the greatest hoax ever by faking a miracle of god, with the hope that its message will lead terrorists in a new direction of peace and put an end to extremists and suicide attacks.
When the son of a landlord decides to modernize his business by replacing the horse carts with buses, a horse cart rider decides to challenge him.
Sidelined at a very young age due to stammering, the eldest of identical triplets develops hatred for his younger brothers and creates havoc in their lives as they all reunite as adults.

A boy stands on a station platform as a train is about to leave. Should he go with his mother or stay with his father? Infinite possibilities arise from this decision. As long as he doesn't choose, anything is possible.
The growing pains of three young women contrast with the immutability of the holy Bengal River, around which their daily lives unfold.

Adithattu denotes the 'lower strata in the society and the fishing community falls under this stratum. Adithattu will also explore the problems and livelihood of the fishermen community and will be a thriller subject.

movie_name: The Fallen: A Halo Fan Film
description: Set during the events of Halo: Combat Evolved, a group of soldiers and survivors from the Pillar of Autumn make their way across the mysterious Halo landscape fighting for their lives against Covenant forces.

movie_name: The Total Number of 3000 Juvenile Delinquents
description: Based on an autobiographical book titled "Tokyo Furyou Shounen Densetsu". The story takes place at a technical high school in the 1970s, where it is said that half of the school's 3,000 students are juvenile delinquents.
After Argentinean immigrant Laura discovers her boyfriend in bed with another woman, she and her Venezuelan friend Lili try everything they can to find the ideal man in Santiago de Chile.

Andrew Suire and Nicholas Sturghill star in this independent production that's based on a true story about a billionare who hires an assassin to wipe out the crooked cops who wrongfully murdered his son.

At the the Killington ski resort something has gone awry. Evil terrorists led by the sinister Greig have taken the resort hostage with a stolen nuclear device. It's up to Ski Patrol bum Matt Foster to save the day... and his fiancé.
When a college psychology student investigates a series of paranormal activities, she discovers there are some things science cannot explain.
When an amnesiac wakes up in a post apocalyptic world ravaged by a rabies type virus, he must band together with a small group of survivors.
A pregnant woman returns to her recently-deceased grandparents' old family home to spend time with her estranged mother. What begins as a tenuous reunion slowly turns terrifying.
A group of college kids accidentally create, and then unleash, a curse that makes anyone they come into contact with kill themselves and then turn into zombie demons.
Nack Solo goes through his own spiritual warfare and ultimately becomes incorruptible while trying to restore balance back into the system that was corrupted by his superior J Burden.
Betrayed by their king and condemned to torture, the last of the legendary Knights Templar discover the corruption of the city around them as they fight their way out of Medieval Paris.
Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren work to help a family terrorized by a dark presence in their farmhouse.

Chris and RJ reunite five years after coming out to their families and their church as gay men, where the factors that led to their separation are revealed as they mourn the death of their mutual friend Rodney.
Harvard symbologist Robert Langdon works with a nuclear physicist to solve a murder and prevent a terrorist act against the Vatican during one of the significant events within the church.

On the hunt for his next story - a series of events will force NY Times photojournalist Ryan Foster to make a difficult decision, resulting in consequences. Some expected. Others unexpected. All life-changing.
An FBI agent on vacation in the mountains begins to suspect that a Communist spy ring may be operating in the area.
Fran, who likes to think about dying, makes the new guy at work laugh, which leads to dating and more, now the only thing standing in their way is Fran herself.
A dejected bartender and an aging drag queen try to survive the eccentric and hostile nightlife of a corrupt city, as a masked maniac slaughters young gay men and drains them of blood.
A money launderer uses women's wrestling as a front for his illegal activities, but earns the enmity of a powerful mobster.
Following the aftermath of a horrific accident, a woman is voluntarily subjected to artificial intelligence for rehabilitation.
An ex-mercenary known for finding missing children is hired by a mixed martial arts fighter whose daughter has been kidnapped.

An inseparable couple Saira and Shiva find themselves in a complicated situation when a stranger claims to be her reincarnated lover from their previous lifetime, hellbent on destroying their relationship and winning her back.

Toko, who after a miscarriage, was left to the lust of a young man she met, but she escaped due to the robbery of Sarakin Company. Before Toko, who stood in a dead end, she no longer had "home, " "love, " and even "freedom."
Amrit's generosity and kindness initially lands him in the bad books of a dancer; then in prison; and then as false son-in-law of a very wealthy man.

After losing contact with his fiancée during a violent protest, a struggling musician arms himself to go after her but, quickly realizes his journey would be treacherous as a mysterious outbreak unravels.
In the course of a demonstration in Rome against the opening of a refugee camp, an apocalypse of zombies breaks out.

Two young sisters try to unearth the mystery of their mother's disappearance, journeying to an isolated mountain town where ghosts whisper into the ears of their living loved ones, luring them to a cold death in the town's lake.
A mild-mannered software consultant begins to change after suffering an animal bite. As unbelievable as it may be, he thinks he's figured out what's going on. He has no idea.
In a quiet small town in Minnesota, a group of high school seniors decides to go out on Halloween night when a series of vicious murders begin to occur.
A gifted young Black woman struggles to maintain her voice and identity after she’s offered a lucrative recording contract.

There are two cousins who are in search of the Yamashita Treasures in Japan. The map was given to them by their professor but also being chased by a group of Japanese treasure hunters as they made their way.

When their Mean Boss has a sudden change of heart after being visited by the Ghosts of Christmas, Pace is sent off to find a real Christmas Tree in the forest. A grand adventure begins where they set off on a search for the Magical tree.

A massacre leaves Kyle's sister dead, putting him on a path of revenge. Join us, as this tale of gore spreads from town to town, person to person, and kill to kill, leaving nobody safe, because, after all. Everyone Must Die!

A futuristic drama set in a time where love doesn't exist -- but it can be bought, in the form of a costly computer chip implant -- and centered on a couple struggling to maintain their link to one another.
Picking up right were the first film left off, this sequel to Indestructible (2009), looks to be even more gruesome then the original.
Pooran doesn't get pregnant so Mahmood marries a widow in the hope of becoming a father. Unpredicted things happen when the three of them have to live in the same house.
A war pacifist is blackmailed to pose as an SS officer and to disable the scuttling explosives on freighter carrying rubber cargo to be captured by the Allies.
A martial artist who makes his living as a professional hit man finds himself in the middle of a battle between both the police and the mob.

The year is 1984. A group of five friends vacation in a desolate Wisconsin town, unaware they are staying at the very house once occupied by Lazarus Slice, a notorious serial killer gun-downed there just one year earlier.
Five young heroes mistakenly armed with super abilities struggle with personal issues as they join together to fight a super-powered force which the military cannot control.

An aspiring director targets a ruthless gangster because he wants to make a violent gangster film. His discreet attempts to research the gangster fail miserably. Finally when he gets caught snooping, things hit the fan.

Dylan Johnson joins Foxworth Enterprises, a business secretly aiding in superhuman preservation. However, he is soon forced to team up with his arch enemy Switchblade to bring down the corrupt company upon learning of their true objective.
After forming an emotionally intense bond, a pair of lonely young girls encourage one another to delve deeper into the realm of eating disorders, with horrific results.

During the 1700s, pirate Captain Vallo seizes a British warship and gets involved in various money-making schemes involving Caribbean rebels led by El Libre, British envoy Baron Jose Gruda, and a beautiful courtesan named Consuelo.

A medical doctor comeback to his village. The place is ruled by Japanese invaders. They broke the doctor's hand but he manages to learn a special Kung-Fu, then takes his violent revenge and frees the village.
A futuristic world with no secrets or governments, one global nation that is threatened by a man with a bomb that he says is going to change history. Humanity's only hope is more time.
A young woman, whose boyfriend is in a coma, falls in love with an achievement-oriented young man, leaving her torn between the man of her dreams, and the man who makes her dreams come true.
Panamérica, 1980. A stupid president decides that all citizens must participate in a deadly car competition and sends an evil army to pursue those who resist.
A young naive reporter romances a female reporter who is quietly organizing a journalist union and joins her cause.

After the battle of Worcester at the end of the Civil War, the main aim of Oliver Cromwell's Commonwealth is to capture Charles Stuart. The future king's escape depends on the intrepid Earl of Dawlish.
After seeing herself drive down the street, Radiologist Gina McVey unravels a mystery centered around a broken mirror.

Gangster William Waldo (George Barcroft) forsakes organized crime for the commercial and easier spoils of evangelism. But now he has trouble from the Purity League, and the police still have an eye on him.
After serving in Iraq, two young Marines return home to Idyllwild California to settle a domestic dispute only to find themselves tangled in a web of deceit and murder.

The noble Liu family are separated when bandits besiege their city, and some treasure goes missing. Many years later, a group of youngsters are tasked with finding the treasure and a Liu family heir. A swordsman gets caught up in the tale.

'Habibi Rasak Kharban' (Darling, Something's Wrong with Your Head) is a dramatic feature that tells the story of a forbidden love in Gaza. The film is a modern re-telling of the famous ancient Sufi parable 'Majnun Layla'.
A formal tailcoat that gets passed from one owner to another affects each life in a significant way.

Unable to locate a ruthless killer, US Marshals must call upon infamous bounty hunter Chris "the Duke" Blaylock . Yet, Deputy Director JP Long is in for a big surprise when he learns the Duke is actually a beautiful woman.
Brian O'Conner, back working for the FBI in Los Angeles, teams up with Dominic Toretto to bring down a heroin importer by infiltrating his operation.
A duke kidnaps the gypsy Montero's young bride, intending to exercise a nobleman's then-presumed right to make love to her. But she dies, and Montero vows revenge.

In the early 1900s, an intense rivalry between two motorcycle racers competing for the Isle of Man TT is interrupted by WW1, and they find themselves brothers-in-arms as despatch riders delivering messages along the front line.

When terrorists try to seize control of a Berlin-Paris flight, a soft-spoken American co-pilot struggles to save the lives of the passengers and crew while forging a surprising connection with one of the hijackers.

movie_name: Son of Adam Daughter of Eve
description: Mina Bozorgmehr and Farhood Zandi are two young lawyers who start working at them same time. They share an apartment, but Mina thinks that Farhood is a author and Farhood thinks that Mina is a photographer.
Troubled kid turns trying to find his place in life after the death of his father as his mother falls apart, he turns to street racing to make a name and give him and his mom a better life.
A naive girl just out of a cloistered orphanage finds that being a 'good fairy' to strangers makes life awfully complicated.
An accountant ,in love with a girl who married a shady guy , becomes her bodyguard,without her knowing it.

Rohit desperately seeks his father's killer. Clues lead him to his home town where he finds a new police inspector, Ajay, in charge. He soon realises Ajay is none other than Deva, his father's killer.
A rebellious girl is sent to a Southern beach town for the summer to stay with her father. Through their mutual love of music, the estranged duo learn to reconnect.
When troubled teen Milo, who has a fascination with vampire lore, meets the equally alienated Sophie, the two form a bond that begins to blur Milo's fantasy into reality.

A woman refuses to evacuate from her dream home during the most dangerous storm in a decade. As it worsens, she must defend her home against mother nature, a band of looters, and something more sinister that arrives with the Hurricane.

Shreya introduces Gautham to her father, Ret. Gen. Hareendranath Varma, and family. He appears to be an adorable and lovable person until a cat-and-mouse game begins between the general and Gautham, who hides a big secret.

Still grieving from a recent tragedy, two brothers must fight for survival after learning a grim secret about their would-be step father. Alone in the wilderness, it will take survival skills and each other to save their family.
When the owner and operator of a luxurious island invites a collection of guests to live out their most elaborate fantasies in relative seclusion, chaos quickly descends.
This sword-filled thriller centers on the title location-an inn where the down and dirty meet to plot nefarious doings.

movie_name: Royal Shakespeare Company: The Two Gentlemen of Verona
description: Valentine and Proteus are best friends until they fall in love with the same girl; with friendship forgotten, the rivals' affections quickly get out of hand.
Kasaki the hitman needs to set scores with his target Ri after the syndicate hunts him and blackmails his childhood friend to kill him.

A Tale of Two Cities scenario contrasting Self-Sacrificial Love to Selfish Love set amidst the religions of the human-sacrificing Mayan and Aztec civilizations. A tale that tests the protective love between sisters AND their lovers.
In 1948, an assortment of shady characters are searching for Nazi loot, sunken off the coast of Peru.

The story of Orochi revolves around the life of the Monzen family. Aoi Monzen, a famous, but aging, movie star and Kazusa and Lisa Monzen her two daughters. Aoi hopes for them both to take ...                See full synopsis »
Carrie White, a shy, friendless teenage girl who is sheltered by her domineering, religious mother, unleashes her telekinetic powers after being humiliated by her classmates at her senior prom.
Recently retired narcotics detective Jack "Hellfire" Bradshaw witnesses his family murdered in cold blood. Left for dead, he awakens with one thought on his mind: bloody, bloody revenge.

Relatives of a recently deceased man meet at his eerie castle for a reading of the will. They encounter a sinister piano player who turns out to be a toy maker, and his toys are imbued with murderous intentions.

movie_name: Devoured: The Legend of Alferd Packer
description: Years after Packer terrorized a Colorado mining camp, similar murders have begun to occur. As the body-count rises, it soon becomes clear that the flesh-hungry madman may have survived for more than a hundred years.
A group of friends are tasked with finding the daughter of a village head who believes them to have helped her elope.
A year after the murder of her mother, a teenage girl is terrorized by a new killer, who targets the girl and her friends by using horror films as part of a deadly game.
A group of friends in the South confront the pressure of settling down and an unwillingness to grow up.

When the king is murdered, his baby son and heir is hidden in the forest where he is abducted and raised by a pride of lions. As an adult he uses his beastly strength and claw-like hands to take revenge against the new king and his armies.
In this chilling story based on real life events a family experience terrifying supernatural occurrences when their son acquires a vintage doll called Robert.
Govind (Sapthagiri) is a petty thief who seems to be down on luck and beaten down by life. What happens when he finds the opportunity to help someone find treasure?

When Seth gets dumped on his 18 birthday, his best friend Nick tries to throw him the best party ever. But everything goes wrong when Nick suspects Seth is turning into a zombie after spending the night with a prostitute.
Serum obtained from a brain after a mass murder transforms the good Dr. Jekyll of London into the evil Mr. Blood.

A young man gets hooked on a website called "Death Tube," which broadcasts actual murders in real time. At first he doesn't believe it is real, until he is brought into the site itself. The killing game is about to begin.

Episode 1: "The Serpent Sign" Miss Elaine Dodge, daughter and heiress of the late Taylor Dodge, whose murder has attracted such world-wide attention, has again had her life seriously ...                See full synopsis »
When a gang of satanic strippers kidnap an innocent young couple, a horrifying scenario ensues. Brides Of Satan is an Action Exploitation Horror film.
One man has a plan for a zombie outbreak, when one occurs it will take all his will to stick to it and all of his courage to change it.
An ethical hit man rescues an orphan girl who's been raised to entertain her criminal guardian, Big Daddy, and his Gangster Cronies.
STUFF STEPHANIE IN THE INCINERATOR is the twisted tale of a husband and wife, Jared and Stephanie, who delve into the demented fantasy games of the super wealthy.
An uptight, down-on-his-luck bounty hunter must recover a fugitive who is possessed by a mischievous demon hell-bent on continuing his party-animal life on earth.
A Spiritualist Medium agrees to help a grieving widower figure out why his daughter has developed a daylight phobia.
A Parapsychologist investigates an urban legend, revolving around a mysterious figure you are dared to meet while under hypnosis.
After accidentally killing a trespasser and burying the body in his Brooklyn Community Garden-Erroll finds himself haunted by his past and his simple life begins to unravel.
Story of the lives of three Soviet pilots who are united by disaster in a small town in the mountains.
When Tommy Cullen's son Jason is killed in prison for a crime he didn't commit, Tommy seeks out those he holds responsible for his son's death.
A homeless amnesiac man is battling dark supernatural elements and the US Government after finding he's over 600 years old.
Bondini is a story of the protagonist Minu and her journey of life and her pursuit in attempting to balance love and life.

After a crippling injury leaves her husband impotent, Lady Chatterly is torn between her love for her husband and her physical desires. With her husband's consent, she seeks out other means of fulfilling her needs.
In order to avoid alimony payments and a large tax bill, a boss marries his secretary, then finds out he really is in love with her.
The plot revolves around two young hearts falling in love. But their love faces trouble due to their differences in family status and by a conspirator.
Homicide detective Josephine Garcia must infiltrate a male dominated precinct in order to take down a corrupt cop.
Ito, a gangland enforcer, caught amidst a treacherous and violent insurrection within his Triad crime family upon his return home from a stint abroad.

Four friends are kidnapped by a madman and locked in a house with six other people. Each of the captives has to endure life-threatening torture to fill a device attached to their heads or they will be trapped inside forever.
A sales man and a pretty girl are running away from the father of her because of an arranged wedding.

movie_name: The Killing of a Sacred Deer
description: Steven, a charismatic surgeon, is forced to make an unthinkable sacrifice after his life starts to fall apart, when the behavior of a teenage boy he has taken under his wing turns sinister.
The evolution of the man, always follows the way that chooses his personality, for much that the reason pledges in looking for other ways.
In the near future, a financial crisis will hit Korea and slums arise. From those areas, a group of young people commit crime to survive.

Sequel to City of Savages Series. The Council of Vengeance wants to make a positive difference in the World and are focused on a better Society and eliminating those who create wrong but the evil Corps of Anarchy has other plans
Will was a vegetarian pacifist trying to forget his flesh eating past. But when the citizens of this small town pushed him too far, he went CanniBallistic!

When human remains are discovered on the land she is developing, an heiress, who spent her entire life running from a legacy of mental illness and addiction, must contend with real ghosts and reverse a deadly curse before it's too late.

Since the founding of the Church, there has always been a secret group as covert nuns that protected mankind from evil both seen and unseen. Our fighting nuns are in way over their heads as they encounter a new breed of super demons.
Three men have unforgettable encounters as they wind their way through the maze of modern relationships.
The charmed pig from Creanga's "Pig Story" is actually a handsome extraterrestrial armored in an anti-pollution suit

An auto mechanic falls for an attorney way out of his league. Things go off the rails as anxiety, fear of losing her and financial pressure drive him into a world of crime, chaos and ice. Will he lose his job, partner and unborn child?
In this sequel to 2010's "Terror at Black Tree Forest" Mare Strode returns, this time to pick up where the original killer left off.

movie_name: M e d u s a
description: Dozens of species of plants and animals are being driven to extinction each year because humans continue to use fossil fuels to warm.
Behind-the-scenes like of the Roller Derby circuit... A beautiful young woman joins a Roller Derby team, but her fierce independence and competitive spirit get her into trouble.
Book superstore magnate Joe Fox and independent book shop owner Kathleen Kelly fall in love in the anonymity of the Internet, both blissfully unaware that he's trying to put her out of business.

Long gone are the days of emerald cities and yellow brick roads. In this dark re-imagining of the Wizard of Oz, Dorothy Gale is now an elderly woman, broken by years of paranormal entanglement with a mystical realm.

When the reckless actions of an out-of-control LAPD officer get his partner killed in a deadly hostage situation, he gets suspended from the police force and heads to Mexico to face off against corrupt cops.
A random invitation to a Halloween party leads a man into the hands of a rogue collective intent on murdering him for the sake of their art, sparking a bloodbath of mishap, mayhem and hilarity.
A lonely scholar, on a trip to Istanbul, discovers a Djinn who offers her three wishes in exchange for his freedom.
After robbing and massacring a village, the head of a gang of bandits, Captain Jagunço, kidnaps Flô, Mayor Cisso's wife and tortures her.
A simple writing assignment uncovers long hidden secrets and reveals the horror in the history of a sleepy-town Inn.

Steve Tuttle, the titular lazybones, takes on the responsibility of raising a fatherless girl, causing a scandal in his small town. Many years later, having returned from World War I, he discovers that he loves the grown-up girl.

Strait-laced Rose breaks off relations with her party girl sister, Maggie, over an indiscretion involving Rose's boyfriend. The chilly atmosphere is broken with the arrival of Ella, the grandmother neither sister knew existed.

Esma, Berk and Hasan are three people who try to escape the troubles of life with the help of a video game called Discovery. These three young people is sucked into the game in a mystical way. They find themselves in a war in World War 1.
THE TRUE STORY OF A CRIMINAL WHO NO COMMITTED NO CRIME - HIS ENEMIES SAY THAT THIS YOUNG MAN IS SLY AND MUST NOT BE TRUSTED.

Tari (Indah Permatasari) is immediately confronted with a marriage agreement with Bian (Refal Hady) which says that they would divorce within one year because their marriage is only for the sake of his parents.

Following her divorce Jo Hayes purchases a slightly run-down, remote cottage in the countryside. With the help of her brother she intends to fix the place up and start again. However, her new life is put on hold when strange events occur.
This anthology will tear your brain in two, one short film at a time. Shown in the style of portmanteau films, it brings terror to a new generation.
Forced to retire because of shifting politics, Park Mun-su nevertheless finds himself called upon to root out a plot against the king
A former marine is trapped in an elite underground fight club. When cops swoop in they discover only one man left alive, him. But all is not as it seems. Is he the sole survivor or a mass murderer?
A Korean immigrant in L.A. encounters difficulties when he refuses to join the all-Korean gang in his highschool.
The story surrounding the marriage of three high school girlfriends who are about to wed their rich boyfriends.

A struggling, young, playwright battles traditional filmmaking practices, studio heads, critics, and even the mob to become the greatest movie-maker while building Paramount Pictures during the golden era of film.

In the picturesque Bavarian town of Oberammergau, two friends, Markus and Thomas, are using the instructions found in an old Jewish diary to gain access to a WW II underground military base formerly codenamed: CERUSIT.
On his deathbed, Victor, a successful writer, receives a visit from his daughter, who will tell the story of a night that changed his life forever and, by extension, his family and children.
Five men plot to steal a large sum of money from the local yakuza, but everything does not go as planned and the men find themselves hunted down by contract killers.
A racially abused black man vows vengeance upon all "white devils" while battling his mental demons and staying just steps ahead of the law.

Remnants is a post-apocalyptic action film about a young man who wakes up, unaware of his identity or whereabouts. Join him as he is taken into safety, and then watch as his world crumbles around him.

Scarlet is a single, workaholic Los Angeles matchmaker with no love life. Scarlet's mother is constantly trying to fix her up, to Scarlet's chagrin. Everything changes when homeless actress Sabrina crashes into her car, and into her life.
Five friends hold an Election Night party in a politically-divided Britain, with a populist right-wing party and a radical left-wing party battling for the keys to 10 Downing Street.

A woman journeys to Spanish California to marry a Spanish officer, but on the way she meets and falls in love with an American adventurer who is part of a movement to overthrow the Spanish in California.
The story of a real 18th-century French actress, leading lady of the Comédie-Française in Paris, who was believed to have been poisoned by a love rival.
A tragic car accident leads a family into a nightmare of supernatural terror as an ancient evil haunts their dreams.
Vijay falls in love with Meena. But Meena's brother opposes their marriage due to rivalry between both the families. Sendoorapandi returns from jail and tries to help his brother to win his love.
The revolt of two communist childhood friends turned leaders against capitalism, slavery and caste systems.

Five people receive an anonymous letter revealing a secret of theirs and inviting them to come stay at a mansion that houses a clinic run by a corrupt doctor who experiments on the brain of his comatose son.
Deep in the English countryside, Lisa and Charlie prepare for their wedding at a Tudor mansion. But an angry crocodile lies in wait, determined to ruin their big day.
Serena, a young girl trained as a killer for hire, teams up with an underground renegade group when she is contracted to stop a hired gun from assassinating a high profile target.

The Gingerdead Man seeks revenge against Sarah Leigh for causing him to live his life in the body of a gingerbread man. Her only hope is to team up with Larnell who has problems of his own in the form of a magical talking bong named Eebee.

Four blue-collar friends, recently laid off from the steel mill, take one last camping trip into the wilderness when they discover a backwoods cult with a cataclysmic agenda and must fight to survive.
A father risks his own life, to save his daughter from the infamous and deadly reality show "The Game".

movie_name: Billy the Kid, the Sunsine Gid Plus the Never Mind Company
description: THE MOVIE WITH ANACHRONISTIC REFERENCES TO HOLLYWOOD, WESTERN CHARACTERS IN ITS TITLE, ISA FARCICAL TAKE OFF ON "SPAGHETTI WESTERNS"
An orthodox youngster and a free-spirited lady fall in love, only to understand that they are different in all aspects of life. How do they realise their complex requirements and mistakes?
An aspiring writer returns to his home-town, re-unites with his estranged father and child-hood sweetheart.
A crime-drama-suspense genre film not often seen in Philippine cinema. A controlling patriarch loses it over his daughter's marriage and her attempts to escape from their incestuous household.

Cartographer Will Shepard hits the road for his latest job: to create a new, more accurate satellite survey of Armenia. During his assignment, he forms a bond with an Armenian expatriate and art photographer.
Four friends on their way to Las Vegas for the weekend get more then they bargained for when they're tire blows out in front of a house full of psychos.
Young Franciszek witnesses a church painting theft and films it. He is not going to reveal the perpetrator to the police, however, but to blackmail him.
Assigned to recover sensitive stolen data, a gruff FBI agent goes undercover as a kindergarten teacher, but is overwhelmed by the school's liberal, politically correct environment.
Two friends, one wanted to go camping, the other wanted to make a horror film for his YouTube page. They both got what they wanted.
An African travels back in time to life in 18th century Africa when he was a warrior fighting to free himself, his people and his beloved from captivity and slavery.

A sailor searching for a lost American explorer discovers him being held hostage on a remote island in the South Sea. The man is held captive by the island's natives, who have placed him under a voodoo spell known as "obeah.
A youngster driven by career ambitions often lets her personal life take a backseat comes across Dev and Akash who leave a lasting impact on her and her perception towards the world.
College students visit a secluded Halloween haunt. There they discover, the scariest thing about a haunt in the middle of nowhere, is the people who work there.
A nightclub bouncer in his fifties who's taken punches, literally and figuratively, struggles to raise his 8-year-old daughter.
Halfway into the Vietnam War (1959-1975), a special US combat unit is sent to hunt and kill the Viet Cong soldiers in man-to-man combat in the endless tunnels underneath the jungle of Vietnam.
A young doctor that has a desire for unusual experiments does the unthinkable and conqueres the Death.

'The Town' meets 'City of Gods' . A group of backpacking friends decide to make a fortune robbing third world countries in Africa. When their escapades bring them to Ghana, a veteran cop vows to take them in by any means necessary.

Disappointed that all his friends are married and happy, Ricky goes on the dating site and soon starts dating Danita, who seems to be way out of his league. However, everything comes at a price, he soon realizes.
A young struggling actor gets a lucky break after delivering flowers on set and falls for the leading actress and becomes a target for jealousy, all thanks to fame.
The world is in chaos; vampires rule the streets, searching for "The Day Walker". Two vampire hunters desperately try to keep her alive.

Janis witnessed her twin brother kill their parents. Twenty years later, she waits for him to come to kill her for her testimony that put him away. Trained in martial arts, she's ready. All Janis wants is closure.
Legendary Swedish sex bomb Anita Ekberg stars as Sister Gertrude, a cruel nun who discovers depraved pleasure in a frenzy of drug addiction, sexual degradation and sadistic murder.
Two circus performers are tasked with escorting relief in the form of gold bullion to a region hit by drought. On the way they are beset by countless bandits.
A prince and a fellowship of companions set out to rescue his bride from a fortress of alien invaders who have arrived on their home planet.
A touching coming-of-age story that follows an engineering boy who falls in love with a girl. To have had you once in my life is already enough.

In 1974, an unhinged CIA agent injects himself with the werewolf blood he found. After a killing spree, his body is put in suspended animation, then thawed out 20 years later by his crazy boss and a team of unsuspecting doctors.
Emin and Nazli live in Ottoman land under Bulgarian occupation. Things get out of control when a Bulgarian soldier falls in love with Nazli.
Charles and his group of men hijack a bus filled with politicians and demand the release of their colleagues from prison. An ex-police officer, Ali Imran, is summoned to solve the problem.
Nonso plans an overly dramatic proposal to his girlfriend. Everything goes wrong and then he goes missing.
Virus holocaust is not the only plague that threatens our future. New York City, 2012 A.D. In a plague devastated world, one tired man finds a reason to fight.
The comedic story of 5 children unexpectedly trapped in a haunted house where they encounter Dracula, the Wolfman, Igor and the Frankenstein monster.
A man is studying abroad in Italy, and while he does well, he yearns for his true love. After promising to meet her in Florence, they reconnect after not seeing one another for 10 years.
When Sanjay falls for his childhood friend Nithi, he refrains from confessing his feelings for her in order to respect their friendship.
A business rivalry puts a thriving romance in jeopardy when two incognito online daters decide to finally meet.
A young couple, bound by a seemingly ideal love, begin to unravel as unexpected opportunities spin them down a volatile and violent path and threaten the future they had always imagined.
During a family vacation that's splitting two parents apart, their young daughter falls under the spell of a terrifying local ghost story.
About a couple who have a great life and successful careers. But one day everything changes for the worst when their only child Zara, goes missing.
When an unhappy, overweight, older man is almost at his wit's end, a strange Voodoo witch comes into his life with a spell that unexpectedly changes his life forever.
Chandee, a strong-willed girl, along with Azad, vows to hunt down some corrupt politicians and police officers who are responsible for her family's death.
A family looks to prevent evil spirits from trapping their comatose child in a realm called The Further.
What was meant to be a fun weekend retreat turns deadly for a group of friends when agitated spirits haunt the house they're staying in to warn them of a maniacal serial killer nearby.

movie_name: Always Watching: A Marble Hornets Story
description: A small town news team discovers a box of video tapes where a faceless figure dressed in a dark suit, haunts and torments a family... slowly driving them insane. Soon after, they realize that the "Operator" has begun to stalk them as well.
A young hot headed yakuza gets in trouble with some drunk officials and have to go away for some time. At the new place he finds more trouble.

movie_name: Detective Conan: Strategy Above the Depths
description: A murder was committed on a ship. To solve the case, Conan will need to open a case from 15 years ago.
Taha is a failure man, he is fired from all jobs he did suddenly he find himself working with dangerous gang and becomes the leader of it.
A young woman's heart and jewels were swindled by three con-artists. As if this wasn't enough, they murdered her. With the help of a kind passerby, her ghost is now able to seek revenge.
Based on true events, six investigators head to one of the world's most haunted places to uncover the source of supernatural sightings and phenomena.
Saturday Night Fever tells the story of two people held captive by desires - theirs and of the others around them.
A single father and two women venture from the safety of their homes to face monstrous creatures to save the life of a young boy.
The whole life in one night. A young couple plays nearly any role of possible lifetime relationships.
Story centers on a crime fighter who's genetically engineered to be a superhero but fears using his powers and needs to be teamed with a former CIA agent.
A mad scientist implants an electronic device into the brain of an injured soldier, which turns him into a psychotic killer.
A getaway driver for a bank robbery realizes he has been double crossed and races to find out who betrayed him.
Blood is the tie that binds. Underneath the surface of a sleepy country town, a brutal drug war rages as rival crime syndicates battle to control the heroin supply that's fueling a rural epidemic.
A behavioral experiment treating humans like animals goes awry when a university student manipulates the research with deadly results.

movie_name: Silent Night, Bloody Night: The Homecoming
description: The abandoned home of Wilfred Butler, a wealthy but troubled man who committed suicide, has been willed to his grandson, Jeffrey. But an Axe wielding maniac has set up residence in the house - and he doesn't take kindly to strangers.
A tollbooth attendant's fascination with a young woman who works at a gas station leads him into a love triangle and murder.
A young couple are stranded in a remote location for several days without food or water, while a massive, giant, madman stalks their every move, proving it impossible for them to escape unscathed.

A young patient who is suffering from cancer is shown maternal love and affection by the nurse who tends to him. However trouble begins when her husband mistakes her affection for the patient to be something else.
Savia; a fame obsessed tabloid journalist, tries to find the cause and the cure of a life threatening epidemic that is ravaging New York City during the economic recession of 2001.
Two cops try to stop a mysterious serial killer dubbed "Car Woman" after the toy car she always leaves next to her victims in this surreal slasher.

In 1989, an unpopular high school girl named Lisa accidentally re-animates a handsome Victorian corpse during a lightning storm and starts to rebuild him into the man of her dreams by using the broken tanning bed in her garage.
Texas oil production head Ernie Garcia is shanghaied to Mexico to cover up criminal activities at the company's Mexican well, managed by Ernie's ex-wife Claudia.

movie_name: Mein Ek Din Laut Kay Aaoon Ga
description: A newly married couple Zohiab and Sheeza are coming home after their marriage but Sheeza pushes Zohaib and he falls in a ditch and than everything changes in Zohaib's family until a stranger from Morocco enters the scenario.
The husband sets up the breakfast table that his wife won't even at that day, cleans it, and does the laundry.

In the near future, as humanity faces an unprecedented environmental, social and economic crisis, a depressed council official and 7 other 'candidates' are caught up in a mad billionaire's plan to bring about the end of the world.
A magician attempts to use the power of the Millennium Comet to awaken the legendary Pokémon Groudon.
A Soldier has 16 hours to cross enemy territory with information that could end the war and prevent the apocalypse.
Mad scientist brings Dracula, the Wolfman, the Mummy, and Frankenstein's Monster to life... but there's a problem and they end up three feet tall.
Benny falls in love with his best friend's little sister. They hide it from her brother, who is trying to protect her.
In a major coastal city run by corrupt officials, a police detective is assigned to investigate a number of high profile criminals being murdered with no end in sight.
Successful author Veronica Henley finds herself trapped in a horrifying reality and must uncover the mind-bending mystery before it's too late.
A mad scientist develops an aftershave lotion that causes his gigantic bats to kill anyone who wears it.
Five runaways trapped in a sinister doll house must find a way out before the Toy Master's deadly creations find them.

Once they said God himself couldn't sink her. Then they said no man on Earth could reach her. But an underwater research agency, headed by Admiral James Sandecker, is assigned the job of finding the doomed ship in her North Atlantic grave.

An unlikely group of courageous soldiers and nurses are forced to embark on a dangerous odyssey as they attempt to journey on foot and by sea through the jungles and rivers of Asia with the entire Japanese Army on their tails.

When Giulia meets Libero, she discovers there may be another destiny awaiting her, as they embark on an intense period together. A choice that leads to Giulia being completely cut off from the Jehovah's Witness world she belongs to.
Billy and Jack (Janno Gibbs ad Dennis Padilla) are modern-day Robin Hoods who engage in petty scums to earn money for the upkeep of a daycare center for indigent and underprivileged children.
Bahadir is a lone high school student who cannot communicate with anyone. One day, he takes a gun and goes to school, hopes that he can change the world in this way.

The pretty Anna multiplies the romantic adventures, without managing to find the man of her dreams. Following a misunderstanding Anna is ready to do anything to find the one who could well be the man of her life
Suri leads a happy-go-lucky righteous life in Bengaluru, where he has a Tom Boy Mouna, his distant relative, wooing him. But, in his heart, Suri still harbours feelings for his first love Poorvi.
In this sequel to`End Of Days`, Jericho Cane returns to Earth as a death-dealing arch-angel, sent from Heaven to wipe out evil.
A recent widow meets an army major while skiing and despite pressures from friends and family becomes romantically involved with him.

The town of Anghenfil is full of stories - tales that hint at its stormy, magical past. And when a long dormant monster is freed after centuries trapped in a hidden cavern, the town again finds itself at the mercy of a ferocious enemy.

Supernaturals in LA and their savage instincts, clan turf wars, and scientific experiments, while a group of photojournalists are documenting sudden appearances of both Earth's mystery beings and unidentified entities from the skies.
A boy takes in a stray dog, later discovering that it is an ultra-intelligent runaway being stalked by a dangerous creature from the same genetic research lab.
When a father and son become stranded in the wild, they must confront the horrors of their past to escape with their lives.
A group of thieves meet up in the desert to retrieve stolen money and Karma takes its toll as bad things begin to occur.
After experiencing a peculiar and sudden breakup with her boyfriend, Elizia discovers a world of conspiracies, strange voices and horrifying visions.

A jaded US mercenary thought to have slaughtered her unit is brutally interrogated by a CIA Agent with whom she shares a sordid past. Their dark history is revealed as a hacktivist navigates the conspiracy surrounding the mission.

movie_name: Los siete colores de la venganza
description: In the beginning, she was a beautiful and innocent baby girl. With time, she has become a rebel and anguished teenager, whose main objective is taking the lives of the seven people who filled her baptism with violence and blood.

Witch from the first Witchcraft movie stalks the now teenage child. She attempts to kill his friends in order to slowly corrupt him to Satan. However the boy is able to defeat the evil Satanic witch, and not enter into Evil with her.
Phil Lemon and crew head to a small Island to exorcise a ghost, but there might be something darker at play.
Blackmailed into murdering, a casanova is presented with the opportunity of living two lives. One in which he commits the crime and the other in which he refuses and goes on the run.

In the year 2154, the very wealthy live on a man-made space station while the rest of the population resides on a ruined Earth. A man takes on a mission that could bring equality to the polarized worlds.

A group of middle-aged men want out of their marriages, so they hire an ex-mercenary to do the dirty work. Before long, everyone wants in on the action, and the wives of a sleepy coastal town find themselves on the endangered gender list.
A relief pitcher for the worst team in the league seizes the unlikely opportunity to work nine innings against the star starting pitcher of the league's best team when no one else wants to face him.

While filming the latest episode, the host of a survival TV show becomes stranded in one of the most remote places on earth and must use his skills to make it out alive while being stalked by something beyond his comprehension.
A woman who is torn between an unhappy married life and an obsessive ex-boyfriend who refuses to consider her unavailable.
This second part shows things from Miho's point of view, and reflects back on the death of a close friend which triggered the later incidents.
Bounty hunters Iria and Bob travel to Earth to capture an escaped bio-engineered fighting machine called Zeiramu.
Four people are given the chance to change their fates if they make one choice, to kill an innocent young woman.
Taught to hate all men - she learned to love one man - and on him heaped all the passion in her starved soul.

Ian lives a life full of hate, alone and lost he takes it out on the vulnerable people he sees around him, stalking the seedy streets of Portsmouth, looking for his next kill, never learning from his past, only fueled by it.
Believing her husband is having an affair with his secretary on their 10th wedding anniversary, an actress takes a multi-day taxi ride from Shanghai to Guilin with a friendly driver.

Employees attending an extreme team-building function for the weekend find new meaning in teamwork, thinking outside the box, and risk management as they fight for survival from a deranged killer bent on revenge.

Tung Yen goes into jail for her boyfriend, Walkie Pi, after they kill a gang boss together. On the other hand, Walkie Pi escapes to Holland. When Tung Yen gets out, she hooks up with club owner, Playboy Man, and runs the girls at his club.

In this action packed Hong Kong Yes Madam installment two friends in the police force are in love with the same man. After a certain incident one of them goes crazy and does everything she can to kill her former friend.

movie_name: The Flight: A Father's War, A Son's Search
description: The story of Dick Bridges, a WWII pilot whose plane was shot down in Austria, becoming the first American prisoner of war in Hungary.
An investigative journalist tries to save an innocent young woman from a Wiccan cult, but in doing so, is drawn into the bizarre and deadly world of modern-day witchcraft.
In 1944, three Navy pilots stationed in Hawaii and a P.R. officer go on a 4-day leave to San Francisco where they party with a good crowd in the executive suite of a busy hotel.
When Rex's best friend goes away to the school of her dreams, Rex is forced to fight her own battles with the occasional help of her ferret, Lucifer.
As a result of a drilling accident, a giant man-eating boa constrictor is released into a maximum security prison in Antarctica.
A new drug has taken Miami by storm but it has one side effect: It turns its users into deranged face eating maniacs.
Daniel, a teenager from Stockholm, spends the summer in Malmö with his mother and her new husband. Daniel take a job at McDonald's, falls in love with a girl.

movie_name: The Practical Man's Guide to Raising Dragons
description: When a father buys a petrified dinosaur egg for his son's birthday, it magically hatches into a being of fantasy and myth.

The most beautiful singer in the whole fish market finds herself not only singing at the local nightclub but also working side by side with a handsome, yet sour classical music student. Are they both willing to put aside their differences?

Tinto Brass - The maestro of Italian erotica is back! Lies, subterfuge, betrayal and mischief - FALLO! is a collection of six stories based on the joys of sexuality and the eroticism of a new generation of women.
Eeswar is a motherless child who hates his father for remarrying after his mother's death. He falls for a local politician's daughter which lands him in trouble.

In Sancharram ("The Journey"), Kiran is mortified by her growing lesbian desire for the effervescent Delilah, in an idyllic Indian village where arranged marriage is the only acceptable form of coupling.
A Psychiatrist's world can be a very tricky one. Add to that a disturbed individual targeting said psychiatrist. A story of deceit and misdirection.
A pregnant New York City social worker begins to develop romantic feelings for her gay best friend, and decides she'd rather raise her child with him, much to the dismay of her overbearing boyfriend.

A day in the life of Jane Grey, a struggling Black actress living in London's hard, beautiful city, grappling with unemployment. Her affair with a married man in flames, she slips unnoticed down between the cracks in the pavement.
Two honest detectives get caught up in a series of unrelated crimes and eventually discover they themselves are the targets.

The movie speaks about the events that goes around from 5 June 1967 till the victory of 6th October 1973 and the war of attrition leaded by the qualified war commander "Nour" which is played by Ahmed Ezz.
A rural politician marries a widow with kids and gains a respectable position. He trusts his stepson more than his own in political matters; thus upsetting his son beyond limits.
Claire Parker is going to die at the hands of a sadistic and depraved killer, she will endure a terrifying, unimaginable brutal death, and it will all happen again, and again.
A jazz musician finds himself possessed by an ancient spirit of vengeance that leads him into a new and unexplored world of voodoo and dead spirits. Based on the Valiant Comics character.
An unfulfilled gay man in a stagnant relationship finds his life changed forever when he meets a struggling writer visiting the Redwoods Country.
Roberts having dinner with his cardiologist and friend, Dr. Rico and evolves into their deep passionate friendship and how their lives are intertwined.
The story of a mother's passionate, undying love for her criminal son even in the most trying, compromising, difficult situations.

A modern-day African American journalist experiences a dual reality when wearing a mysterious locket - a forbidden dreamt romance with a white soldier in 1944 and a modern-day love with a white Civil Rights Attorney.

Teenagers in a mid-west town discover that they are destined to fight off an alien invasion as the crew of a spacecraft of unknown origin. They are aided by a mysterious patient in a psychiatric hospital and a frenetic comic book artist.

Vanessa has always had trouble in the dating world, never mind now being confined to her home. She soon discovers just how much you can get away with dating via webcam, but is the love she feels true or only a distorted version of reality?

Alex tells the story of a boy and a girl who live very different lives but are brought together by fate. This accidental meeting leads the two strangers to become the entire world for each other, taking them on the journey of a lifetime.
Since his childhood, Daniel has been trained to be a true gunslinger. And when he discovers a secret, he will travel to find his real parents. Will he ever succeed in his mission?
A Christian boy and a Muslim girl fall in a forbidden love in the town of Komotini. They decide to escape together, but the Turkish consul has another opinion.

Mika Hino is a sharp-shooting investigator that belongs to the infamous "Gator Branch." When an executive board member of a trading company is accused of being involved in a bribery, Mika is assigned to keep watch over him.
A group of friends decides to document their lives as they search for an underground fight club that exists in the dark web. They put everything on the line for money, respect, and friendship.
An ordinary family navigates the unpredictable circumstances caused by a mysterious phone call that puts them in a horrific situation.

Bullet Raja is killed by Babu, a goon, because both love the same girl. Raja fights with the god of death and is sent back to Earth into the body of Ravindra, a minister who was killed by his own associates.
A 15-episode serial in which Beatty goes to darkest Africa to rescue the Goddess of Joba, who is being held by the high priest.
A Mexican-American girl from San Diego lands the job of her dreams in New York, only to fall in love with the son of a prejudiced High Society family.

Talking to a stranger can be very therapeutic for the fact that you can say exactly how you feel without fear, judgment and insecurity. But what happens when that stranger becomes a reflection of the decision you should make?
Teenagers go missing in a supposed "haunted house" and a paranormal investigative team are called in to help find them.

A young woman becomes embroiled in a financial and political conspiracy while studying in Spain, as she meets a young musician with a somewhat dark past unfolded through the pages of his lover's diary.
With no one to talk to, a woman turns to a strange doll for help dealing with her bullies, when they end up dead, she fears the doll is responsible.
Rivalries, dark secrets, and sexual tension emerge when three best friends find themselves stranded on a yacht in the middle of the ocean desperate for survival.
A sexual thriller set in an insane asylum with 3 main story lines. How can seemingly normal and sane people can commit such horrific crimes in a moment of madness?
Adelaide Valentine, a post-modern young woman, is in the process of expanding herself amidst the sickness of her sister, who is a free spirited soul and has no bounds for love.
All the rules are broken as a sect of lawless marauders decides that the annual Purge does not stop at daybreak and instead should never end.

During one of the missions, of the Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao who are engaged in overseas security work for a long time discovers that foreign terrorist forces have extended their reach into China's energy lifeline.

Plot centers on a pair of college-age students fleeing from an unidentified enemy force. The duo takes refuge in what appears to be an abandoned building, but they quickly discover the building they thought was empty is anything but.

Respectable lawyer Peter picks up Anna, an Italian woman of dubious virtue, from the club and takes her back to his Uncle's place. They soon discover they are not alone. A gunman Quill (Julian Mateos), is waiting for them.
Adil who is tasked to annihilate Bulgarian hijackers that against Ottoman Empire. Meanwhile Adil meets Kristina and complex relationships are experienced between them.
The evil T.H.E.Y. organization is out to stop ex T.H.E.M. agent, Sandra West. Can Superseven thwart Their, (T.H.E.Y.'s) master plan?
A mysterious derelict wanders the streets of Los Angeles stealing human souls as investigators try to unravel the true nature of his killings.
A young man from the countryside rescues his lady friend from a difficult situation and exacts vengeance upon those who have caused it.
As the Civil War begins Ned Burton leaves his Southern love Agatha Warren and joins the Union army. He is later protected and saved from death by Agatha in spite of her loyalty to the South.
A young policewoman slowly goes insane while tracking down an elusive serial rapist/killer through Italy when she herself becomes a victim of the brutal man's obsession.

In a world covered in a germ ridden atmosphere which chronologically takes human senses one by one in relation to exposure, a man and a woman find each other via radio despatches from their bunkers forging a journey to find each other.
In small town USA, Ruby Rosenkreuz, a young college dropout, inherits the home of her vanished uncle. Her arrival coincides with the appearance of a supernatural event.
The story is centered on commercial pilots eager to fly higher and up-in-the-air attendants eager to land a man.
Four stories, four worlds that collide into one. "Death do us apart" tells a tale of friendship and survival in a world infested with zombies.

A government assassin discovers that he has developed split personality disorder. The first persona is attempting to compete his mission; the second is trying to stop his other persona from being a killer.
A salesclerk at Macy's department store finds herself pregnant after a one-night stand with a musician, who does not even remember her.
A couple's relationship is tested when uninvited guests arrive at their home, disrupting their tranquil existence.
A young man works night shifts at a bodega so during the day he can date his middle school crush in a lucid dream.

Six college students board an old school bus for a road trip to a rock concert. Halfway to their destination, their transportation breaks down, leaving them stranded with a sinister presence inside of an old, dark house.
A group of guys on a camping trip try to one-up each other with tales of violence, macabre, gore, and terror.
Lola se ve involucrada en una persecución hacia la muerte a medida de que ella se convierte en el blanco de un traficante de armas y debe luchar contra él.
Since Nick's arrival, Weston has been plagued by fear and murder. The unprepared police force has proven to be an asset to Nick, and the small town has become a safe haven for his dark deeds.
An attractive woman in her late thirties, is the successful owner of a thriving coffee-house but secretly longs for a child while fiercely defending her independence.
An evil vampire has found the girl with a blood type that will allow him to breed a new race of vampires. It's up to the slacker John and his friends to stop him before it is too late.
A romance blossoms between a very unlikely duo, can they survive the hatred and ignorance from society?
An honest encounter specialist's life begins to change with the arrival of a new police commissioner who has ties with a local don.
A girl in high school is stuck in a relationship with a boy whose family runs a cartel. She is tricked into joining a gang. Now she can't get out of her relationship nor the gang she joined.
A group of twenty-somethings are enjoying their stay at a lakeside cabin when a series of frightening and bizarre events derail their weekend.
Three gay gangsters mourn the death of their gay guardian, but end up celebrating his bright and colorful life.
A famous tenor manages to charm away a lovely young lady who was just about to be married to the opera director.

teenager was taken away from his mother by an organization and become the ultimate weapon. can he reconnect with his mother, and get some semblance of his old life? The childhood he never had, or will his new life be too much to run from?
Uncle Frank Kelly calls on Harry Crown to help him in a gang war. The war becomes personal when Harry's new girlfriend is kidnapped by Uncle Frank's enemy, Big Eddie.
A glue-sniffing boy and his girlfriend escape the government-controlled no-hope Aboriginal community they live in and go to the city, Alice Springs, looking for a better life.
A group of rebellious San Diego skateboarders who take it upon themselves to investigate their town's paranormal activity and wind up embarking on the adventure of a lifetime.

UNDER STJERNERNE is a multi plot feel-good romantic drama, that follows six story lines of love, all of them different but connected, and all of them asking the same question: Is there anything greater than love?
Despite being under heavy sedation, a young woman tries to make her way out of the Arboria Institute, a secluded, quasifuturistic commune.
The adventures of daredevil cargo pilots, also known as "freight dogs", who are hired to haul all sorts of dangerous cargo.
A murderer, with the help of Chinese vampires, does battle with the ghost of a dead gambling lord's wife and the gambling lord's living brother.

A family moves into an old house. They start getting harassed by a gang, who eventually invade the house while the parents are away and start terrorizing the kids, but they didn't account for the deadly supernatural presence in the house.
A private investigator discovers that all the other actors of a movie trailer he was in 20 years ago have met with mysterious deaths in the last three months and he might be next.
Attending an estate sale, Frank and Janice enter and stumble into a distorted maze filled with horror, evil, lies, trouble and no way out.
Can a determined single mom go the distance and win the tournament that could ultimately lead to a better life for her and her daughter?
A married couple on their honeymoon stop off at a back-woods garage to get their car repaired, unaware of what sheer terror is in store for them. What will it take to survive?
July 4th 2015 the world was invaded by zombies. Humanity was put to the test in a small town in Colorado, where it all began.
The adventures of three young boys, who want to capture India's most-wanted fugitive Dawood Ibrahim.
Dinesh, a software engineer, is brought to a psychiatrist by his boss after he seems mentally disturbed. His life turns worse when the voice in his head tells him to kill himself.

Sergeant Nick Nobleza (Jestoni Alarcon) is the straightest cop in the police force. He is assigned to infiltrate the drug syndicate of Mr. Villafuerte (Lito Legaspi). But Mr. Villafuerte is one step ahead as he sets up a trap of his own.
A family's harmonious existence is interrupted when the young son begins showing symptoms of anxiety that seem linked to disturbing events at home.

This is the story of Angelica, a 16 year-old girl who's battling a rare kind of cancer called Myelodysplastic Syndrome, her struggles to try to live a normal life, and her hopes of finding her first true love before it's too late.
A group of friends go to meet their favorite camgirl at a convention after party only to find themselves in deep.

movie_name: Gokaiger Goseiger Super Sentai 199 Hero Great Battle
description: In Gokaiger Goseiger Super Sentai: 199 Hero Great Battle, the 34th and 35th Super Sentai team must join forces to defeat the joint efforts of the Space Empire Zangyack and Black Cross King, who wants to invade Earth.
Smitten with unrequited love, a young man inadvertently gets involved in the kidnapping of his beloved, ruining her arranged marriage. Can things be set straight?
In a sleepy mountain town, Cindy's parents are murdered and her Christmas is stolen by a bloodthirsty green figure in a red Santa suit.

Claire and her husband lose their baby to a deadly virus while vacationing on a tropical island. Unable to cope, Claire believes her son is still alive and in the arms of a mythical sea creature in the mysterious village of Santa Clara.
Mohan, Pradeep and Ranjeet are struggling artistes who share the same house. When they decide to help each other find love by using their talents, their lives get entangled and chaos ensues.
In 2006, a group of thieves performed what is considered one of the most famous and smart bank heists in the history of Argentina when they rob the Banco Río branch in Acassuso.
A girl loses her mother from an early age and grows up with her father. Soon after her father succumbs to a heart attack. How will she survive?
Before midnight, a man must deliver a car full of drugs in exchange for his father's life but an uninvited passenger threatens his life at every turn.
Alice returns to where the nightmare began: The Hive in Raccoon City, where the Umbrella Corporation is gathering its forces for a final strike against the only remaining survivors of the apocalypse.
A man desperate for work is involved in a war between two gangs, putting his life in danger and all his friends, including his girlfriend.

A series of mysterious murders and unexplained deaths have occurred near a crossroad on an abandoned train line. Frustrated with a lack of answers, the authorities turn to a team of paranormal investigators to seek the truth.

Tomas Milian as the unconventional undercover cop with a pet mouse named 'Serpico'. Still difficult for an investigation commissioner Nico Giraldi, this time struggling with a gang who commits theft in luxury apartments in Rome.
In a last-ditch effort to stop a diabolical plot, a dead CIA operative's memories, secrets, and skills are implanted into a death-row inmate in hopes that he will complete the operative's mission.
Five young campers discover that a fifty year old legend of sacrificial killings is becoming their present day reality.
1979. Gábor H. works in a law enforcement institution. He robs a bank branch, gets into jail. 1989. Gábor H. and the similarly unemployed Sanyi want to get money by robbing.

movie_name: Everybody Is Going to Die, at Ten Acres High
description: Ten Acres used to be a normal town, but after the events that have taken place in recent years it was only a matter of time before Ten Acres High had something strange happen to it.
As his country prepares for war, top Egyptian official Ashraf Marwan makes contact with Israel and wades into a shadowy game of high-stakes espionage.

A young American journalist stranded in present-day Nicaragua falls for an enigmatic Englishman who seems like her best chance of escape. She soon realizes, however, that he may be in even greater danger than she is.
In this epic dramatic horror film, a young homeless man is turned into a vampire and must come to terms with his thirst for blood while falling in love with a wealthy, unobtainable girl.
A group of armed robbers are making a name for themselves but things go awry when they rob the wrong bank.
Lamont Cranston fights crime as The Shadow, using his powers of invisibility and the ability to cloud men's minds.

What is supposed to be an educational and collaborative weekend professional development session for the English Department of Prescott High School instead turns into a blood soaked nightmare when a masked killer targets them.
At the 2004 Republican Nation Convention, love blooms between a Republican delegate and a Democrat protesting the event.
A down and out bounty hunter takes down a underworld society. Cobra meets midnight run. The clock is ticking .
A blackmailer demands a huge ransom in exchange for information on how to disarm the seven bombs he placed aboard the transatlantic liner Britannic.

The characteristic loves of Margarida and Clara, the distinct moral of Peter and Daniel, the goodness of Joao Semana, and the dissidents, sensibility, tenderness, rituals and landscape involvement of the Minho.
A band plays the last gig of their tour in New Orleans. Next day worse for wear they head off for a boat adventure in the swamps. Bad move.
Fireman Bob Darrow (Tim McCoy)invents an original chemical fire extinguisher, and his rival, Dan Mitchell (Gayne Whitman), for June Madison(Marion Shockley), also has his eyes on Bob's invention.

The Battle of Karbala was fought on 10 October 680, between the army of the second Umayyad Caliph Yazid I and a small army led by Husayn ibn Ali, the grandson of the Islamic prophet Muhammad, at Karbala.
When Herrman is bitten a zombie apocalypse breaks out. This makes Melissa change their plans so they heading for the lab, but Herrman is still drinking.
Biological war has decimated life on Earth. Los Angeles is a windswept ghost town where Robert Neville tools his convertible through sunlit streets foraging for supplies.
Death returns to claim the lucky survivors of a deadly bridge collapse in this fifth frightening installment in the series.

Krishna Mehra who is an operative at Indian spy agency known as R&AW. She is assigned to track down the mole selling India's defense secrets, while all along grappling with her dual identity as a spy and a lover.
Unable to tell the difference between his nightmares and reality, SIndile battles a forgotten memory in his dark past.
A story of a woman and a man, half of her age being in love with each other despite the fact that they are both tied with someone else.
A chance encounter between two girls of the same name, "Nana," triggers a series of events and relationships.

Love blossoms between the son of wealthy man and his middle class neighbor. But their romance is put to the test both by a feud between the families and by the entrance of a rival for the girl's affection.
When Frank Castle's family is murdered by criminals, he wages war on crime as a vigilante assassin known only as The Punisher.

A TV crew, desperate to boost ratings, arrive on a remote Welsh farming island to investigate an intriguing incident. A local girl and her boyfriend had been abducted by aliens, who also impregnated her.
A paranoid mathematician searches for a key number that will unlock the universal patterns found in nature.

There is bustle in the townhouse of the Middelboe family in Helsingør. The house's only daughter, the adorable Bitten, must be married and her mother, Emma Middelboe, is busy trying to find her perfect match.
One of New York's biggest crime heads has offered to let the Ice Grill Bandits in on the biggest heist of the century, but the bandits double cross the mob and make their own deal.
A middle-aged jeweler is falling in love with a glorious woman. She, raising a son alone, is in no hurry to reciprocate a fan.
When three scientist launch a bio attack on a bus full of hot girls they create sex crazed zombies wreaking havoc on a small town.
