A toy factory worker, mentally scarred as a child upon learning Santa Claus is not real, suffers a nervous breakdown after being belittled at work, and embarks on a Yuletide killing spree.

A time-traveling recruiter for God's army on the run from a horde of demons must convince a fallen preacher, now the leader of an outlaw biker gang, he is the chosen one to save mankind from the end of days.
Follows the exploits of four youngsters sent back in time 1,500 years to the height of the Mayan Empire.

After a desperate plot to rob his company office, a mining engineer leaves town humiliated. He takes up work elsewhere, agreeing to help a threatened father and his daughter extract silver ore from their mine before the lease expires.

A child welfare officer becomes director of The League of Angels (Good Samaritans), an underground vigilante group that dishes out justice to abusers and tracks down a Mexican human trafficking cartel.

movie_name: The French, They Are a Funny Race
description: Major Thompson, an Englishman living in France, comments in his memoirs on the peculiarities of his French wife and friends.

Distraught after being fired from his job, Willi Willeboer leaves town for Oubaas du Toit's Paradise Game Reserve, where he falls for the owner's daughter, but she sees him as nothing more than a brother.
Follows six people, low-lifes, junkies, and strippers as they battle for survival in the midst of a zombie outbreak in a rundown area on the outskirts of a city.
In 1941, the IRA plans a campaign to coincide with the planned German invasion of England. Dermot O'Neill finds it easy to get into the IRA, but can he get out?
A student writer struggles to find a happy ending for her romantic story when her own real life romance falls apart.
Five oddball American commandos infiltrate a well-guarded villa to steal the documents for "Plan K" - which the Nazis intend to use to drive the Allies out of Italy.
Australia, 1879. An escaped band of outlaws and their police pursuers become the prey of an ancient beast though only to exist in Indigenous mythology.
A mysterious, morbid professor who has suffered a number of horrid events in his life tries to help a young troubled man, whose girl friend was killed during an illegal abortion.
Due to unforeseen circumstances, childhood sweethearts Gauri and Sankaran get separated. However, their bond withstands the test of time and reunites them years later.
A Mexican-American master chef and father to three daughters has lost his taste for food, but not for life.
Two sisters vacationing in Mexico are trapped in a shark cage at the bottom of the ocean. With less than an hour of oxygen left and great white sharks circling nearby, they must fight to survive.
A high school film club movie project is interrupted by nefarious thugs. Enter the high kicking school girls who will have to put their acting to use in a real-life situation.
Michael Myers is loose in Haddonfield again for one last night. Can Maxwell Loomis stop him once and for all? Will Judy strode and her friends survive? Find out in CNT FILMS HALLOWEEN 3
A woman's life is in dangerous because of the secret of hidden gold in the house left by her parents.
The animal is in motion, it is impossible to hold it. The bodies vibrate, dance and desire. Six episodes, six directors, and stories about body, movement, desire, and eroticism.

Amidst a growing pandemic, a scientist who is threatened by a powerful pharmaceutical company to sign off on a potentially dangerous vaccine, realizes he may be involved in a far reaching conspiracy of untold evil.

Rich Dr.Akarsh and young middle class girl Acchari meet by accident, and seem to have the perfect romance going for them. Just when you think there's a happily ever after, there enters the other woman, Aditi.

movie_name: Teree Sang: A Kidult Love Story
description: An under-aged couple fall in love, face opposition from the girl's wealthy parents, elope, and go on the run from the police.
A man awakens and finds himself trapped in a strange old hotel where the only escape is through a labyrinth of rooms filled with mystery, horror and adventure.

In a small town in Arizona, a mysterious man/spirit descends from the sky and manifests in a sports car and targets a local violent road-racing gang of motor heads, headed by a ruthless bully who'll do anything to get what he wants.

Six friends want to become popular by recording their adventures to be uploaded to social media accounts. They choose to go to the abandoned apartment and suddenly open a portal to the magical world and infuriate the portal guardian.
Barkha saves the life of underworld king Vicky, and as a result he offers her a job and also falls in love with her, but Barkha is in love with Sagar. Will Vicky tolerate this?
Two young people, Venkatesh and Nandini, get embroiled in a murder case when the strict principal is killed after he humiliates Nandini.
The future of Earth is in question when a strange reaction deep beneath its surface causes a massive rupture in the planet's inner structure.
Famed detective Byomkesh Bakshi investigates the murder of a man who had just thrown a party to celebrate his recovery from a long illness.
When a group of pensioners learns that their homes are to be torn down, they take action. An attempt to discourage soon escalates into murder of construction workers.
A Vietnam War veteran, Ki Gwang is an old bus driver. One day, he faced that his son had committed suicide. This was the beginning of his vengeance for the world.
A romantic comedy about a young man who pretends to be gay in order to rent an apartment with his dream girl. His plan backfires when she keeps trying to set him up with her male friends.

Tensions rise as two very different brothers, one a gay teen and the other newly appointed detective, enter into very unhealthy relationships that threaten to not only uproot their lives but their very existences.

In November of 2017, a broken video camera and smart phone were recovered from a recycling centre. The camera houses a memory card that contained disturbing and unexplainable material. This is that material.
Graduate student Calliope Girard's orderly life is thrown into chaos by unexplained seizures that unlock buried memories of a violent past.
Elegant martial arts action contrasts with brutal violence in this deadly dance of morality and greed.
A young jazz-composer turns vengeful commando against local drug Mafia Capos when his wife is killed at the hands of Caribbean drug dealers.

movie_name: Bruce Lee's Ways of Kung Fu
description: A martial artist seeks vengeance for his father's death against a warlord and his 18 female bodyguards who killed him.
Three women, four children, and many more people besides have deep love for a hotel owner, yet choosing the right partner for this man takes some doing.
Within a small country town, people are disappearing without a trace. It's up to one big city detective to discover if they're simply runaways or if there's something much more sinister at work.

During the battle between insurgents and the royalist Spanish army during the Mexican civil war, some outlaws seek treasure within a families compound only to find horrors they could never have imagined.
An unfulfilled married woman becomes intrigued by an alluring suitor whose attention soon becomes obsessive.
Lovers Renjith and Maria face several trials and tribulations under their strict parents as they struggle to be together.
A movie musical centered on merrily befogged Merriweather's attempt to restore his career - all while reuniting with his three children (from his three alimony-seeking ex-wives!).
Investigating reports of demonic possessions in a remote village, a skeptical military officer finds his beliefs tested by an enigmatic exorcist.
When an archaeologist's girlfriend unleashes vengeance spirit 'Dead Rose', he has three days to find her before the ill fate of her death.

A comedy romance inspired by the slew of publicly documented election love stories that sprung up during Obama's Presidential push. The plot follows the fortunes of a campaign team caught up in a whirlwind of euphoric romances.
Tom's pursuit of a normal life is discombobulated by three beautiful, strong-willed females. Romance and other forms of chaos ensue.
In the first major naval battle of World War II, the British Navy must find and destroy a powerful German warship.

After meeting online, Jack and Kristy go on a weekend getaway to the woodlands of rural Missouri. While discovering each other, they soon learn of the terrorizing horrors that the forest has in store.
Two brothers, both of whom are warlocks, use their powers and covens of witches to battle over the family fortune.
What begins as supernatural, not only is natural...but lethally human...What will be revealed by the Whispers in The Walls? The truth lies beneath.
Laura is a sex educator hired to teach sex in exchange for money. A rich family hires her to give sex education to their asocial son.
A young girl and her family are forced into hiding in a post-apocalyptic world overrun by a malicious government and the undead.
Renowned heist master Dean DeMarco and his crew are second to none at pulling off scores. Now they face their most challenging score, rescuing Dean's ex-girlfriend.
Anthological film consisting of ten spooky stories spanning the horror, sci-fi and fantasy genres, intended for young audiences, and hosted by legendary creature and film actor, Doug Jones.
Gokulan sees an attractive girl in his dream and is determined to find her. However, his father gets him engaged to another girl. Complications arise when he meets the woman of his dream soon after.
A troubled and abused youth, Tommy Fester, grows up to become something far more sinister...and deadly.
When Otis Tweedy and his wife Sarah move across the Atlantic to Cappawhite, Ireland, a strange set of circumstances threaten their sanity and their very existence.

At last, Michael is getting his life back on track when his elder brother Johnny shows up unexpectedly. Johnny owes money to some people who resort to extreme measures whenever a debt is to...                See full synopsis »

Following a major event at work, a play-it-safe workaholic finds herself traveling to her roommate's small hometown in Texas for Christmas, where she quickly gets wrapped up in all the cheer and drama the small town brings in a BIG way.

A struggling film critic decides to take on a "bad attitude" to achieve fame and success as the ANGRY MOVIE GUY. When his review destroys the career of a woman he's fallen in love with he must rethink his life.
Lara and Jorge fall in love. They decide to leave their families and live together without their permission.

Beth is a young woman who must struggle with being shunned by society for her past legacy, as well as developing a romance with a local fisherman, and then seeks protection by hiding out with a simple-minded hunchback.
Søren is looking forward to a relaxing camping holiday with his wife, Marianne. But nothing goes as planned, when his two daughters and mother-in-law join them.

Anne, married to a small-town Minister, feels her life has been shrinking over the past 30 years. Encountering "The Master" brings her a new sense of power and an appetite to live bolder. However, the change comes with a heavy body count.
Jailbird Danny was just released from jail when he meets innocent, sweet girl Engie, who works in the perfume shop next door. She tries to evangelize him but he runs away, as fast as he can.
After his father pass away, Bruce Chan leave his village to release his sister from prostitution. The pimp in one condition, that he fight for him in an underground fight club.
A failed gambler, intent on meeting a rich widow, tricks his widowed brother-in-law into boarding a cruise ship as dance hosts.
A race against time for two brothers where the stakes are life, death, fame and fortune and a thousand of the deadliest bikers in the country are in hot pursuit.
Vijay, who loves Rekha, is framed by her father for a crime he did not commit. However, he escapes from prison to prove his innocence and reunite with his lover.

Daisy is the all-American girl next door with a hunger for true love and an appetite for murder. Then one day Daisy meets the man of her dreams, only to discover that his own lust for killing might make her his next victim.

Angela, the beautiful Mexican mistress of a NY mobster, asks virginal Father Michael for protection after Zena, the mobster's wife, kills her cheating husband. Michael becomes torn between his vows, Angela and his sister - Zena.

"Pradeep in town" -an announcement in local newspaper finds Geeta, the daughter of the proprietor of Nan Ching Chung hotel, Mr. Verma, pedalling fast towards the theatre where the show is ...                See full synopsis »
The son of an egoistic businessman falls in love with an egoistic girl and has to convince her egoistic mother in order to marry her.
Anthony, a mute, starts experiencing the supernatural. Trapped in his own silent world, he is helplessly toyed with and haunted by unexplainable entities.
A trio of clueless minors embark on a quest to get into the local bar, in the hopes of scoring with the opposite sex.
'The Impact' is the result of a collaborative filmmaking initiative run by Create50. The feature film is comprised of thirty-seven short films made by various filmmakers from around the world.
Lathika, a pretty young woman is happily engaged to her cousin who works abroad. Her life turns upside down when she gets raped by her friend's brother and becomes unmarred mother.
In a remake of the 1940s film, Helen has been incapable of speech since seeing her husband die - will she become the target of a deranged serial killer targeting disabled people?

Three short films. Three women's harrowing journeys to find inner peace in their respective worlds, whether it is Earth (A Song For Swan), a parallel dimension (The Reve), or an alternate realm (Since).

A mother raises two sons in a seaside community. Son Jack stays in the village, marries a local girl, and presents his mother with a grandchild. But son Bob leaves his mother to pursue a business career in the wicked city of London.
Extraterrestrials traveling in high-tech flying saucers contact a scientist as part of a plan to enslave the inhabitants of Earth.
A conflict of interest between two high-kicking assassin sisters is complicated as they're pursued by the criminals who hired them and an equally high-kicking female cop.

A struggling novelist must bring to life a legendary story, daring into the dark alleys of Panama's mob world. Trouble begins when a mysterious competitor takes control of the labyrinth he walks into, where death is just the beginning.
Sunny Palomattam, a successful businessman in Singapore, enjoy his life with his girlfriend Sandra Valookaran. However, he is unaware that Sandra is a spy hired by his business rival Mohammed Ali.

movie_name: Tales of Love Madness and Death
description: Tales of love madness and death, based on the life and the short stories of acclaimed writer Horacio Quiroga
The neighbors of a frontier family turn on them when it is suspected that their adopted daughter was stolen from the local Kiowa tribe.
Although the home of cabinet minister Arthur Bennett is a hotbed of spies, moles, and double agents, no one knows the true identity of notorious German spymaster Strendler.
A teenage girl flees accusations of witchcraft only to discover she must enter a hidden world of magic and enchantment to embrace her destiny.

Cantonese Pop Star Aaron Kwok stars as a police detective who must pose as the son of a millionaire to catch a kidnaping ring. Trouble starts when the policeman's girlfriend starts working for the businessman.
A college student befriends two cute girls his age. He loses contact with them. He tries to find them years later.
A young valet driver gets involved in a government mission to take down an international arms dealer after he valets an agent's car.
A charismatic rapper falls in love with a young Jewish girl despite the confines of her religious background.
A giant monster eel attacks a group of high school students on a rafting trip down the American river. The government sends super agent Max Uzi to investigate the killings.

movie_name: Be Careful of What You Know
description: A childhood premonition of a future tragedy is realized by a young woman when she looks into the murder of her dead ex-boyfriend, and suddenly finds herself caught up in the same deadly conspiracy and cover-up that had gotten him killed.
Reymat is killed during an aerobatic exhibition in a plane. Hélène, his fiancée, to forget her grief, decides to become an aviator.
A group of friends are stalked and murdered whilst looking for psilocybin mushrooms in the Irish woods.

movie_name: Oh, My Girl!: A Laugh Story...
description: Little Opao (Dorothy Ann Perez) and Biboy (Jairus Aquino) grew up together in an orphanage in Taal, Batangas and promised themselves to be best friends forever. As they grow older they head...                See full synopsis »
The continuing adventures of former Chinese Imperial guard Chon Wang and American bandit, Roy O'Bannon.

Terrifying story of a girl (Rose) who struggles with the recent loss of her sister. Rose is haunted by her sister as she isolates herself from her family and friends. Blaming herself for her sisters death she may suffer her sisters fate.

movie_name: La ragazza dalla pelle di corallo
description: Arriving in Santo Domingo to study new methods of cultivation of tobacco, Fabrizio is hosted by American Barrymore who feels compelled to provide Mayra, beautiful mulatta, as momentary escort.
A deaf man in India can't connect with his family so he creates his own world through Bollywood- styled musical fantasies in sign language, leading him to America to win the girl of his dreams.
When the kids of a young widow inadvertently send an SOS while playing with their uncle Cy's Navy Signal Lamp, the Navy sends their top man to investigate and he falls for their mother.

Alan Kurdi (Kurdish: Alan Kurdî ), initially reported as Aylan Kurdi, was a three-year-old Syrian - The bodies of Kurdi and another child were discovered by two locals at around 6:30 am. The two men moved the bodies from the water,
A group of teenagers visit an abandoned mental hospital to summon old spirits but what they end up summoning is an ancient demon that have been kept away from humanity for a reason.

"El Bukanas" miente, roba y engaña a quien sea con tal de salir adelante. Pero tras no completar la entrega de un paquete a Los Ángeles, es perseguido por la mafia. Desesperado por pagar su deuda, se enfrenta a la mayor prueba de su vida.
An honest and upright lawyer becomes a judge; marries his disabled daughter to a crook, and is blackmailed to compromise his judicial judgements.

movie_name: Halloween 4: The Return of Michael Myers
description: Ten years after his original massacre, the invalid Michael Myers awakens on Halloween Eve and returns to Haddonfield to kill his seven-year-old niece. Can Dr. Loomis stop him?
A young Egyptian goes to the rescue of his employers, a wealthy European family, when they are menaced by a local strongman and his gang.
A man tries to become a better son after his intended bride rejects him and he learns he was adopted from a poor family.
A young girl institutionalized by her abusive stepfather retreats to an alternative reality as a coping strategy and envisions a plan to help her escape.
As a young East Los Angeles Latino pursues his dream of becoming a great Salsa dancer, he is enraged to learn that his little sister is romantically involved with his best friend.

Siblings Vibeke and Hans-Henrik are to celebrate her 21st birthday with a big party, at which their common friend Ulla reveals that she is engaged to him, and that Vibeke is adopted. Maybe that's why Vibeke realizes she wants him too?

movie_name: In the Name of the Gun
description: By tracking down outlaws connected to the man who wrongfully sent him away, a mysterious bounty hunter seeks his vengeance a decade later when he is released from prison.
When a retired bouncer is called in to secure crowd control at a famous club in downtown Los Angeles he finds himself in the middle of something far more dangerous than he could have expected.
A woman goes on the hunt for her dream man, armed with her wild imagination, her passion for Masala-films, and her ultra-sensitive sense of smell.
Two talented landscape artists become romantically entangled while building a garden in King Louis XIV's palace at Versailles.
The fighter Kwan searches in south for a magician of the earth to assert against the murderer of Chiu Yen.
Colonel Braddock launches a mission deep into the jungles of Vietnam to find the POW camp that he escaped from and free the Americans still held captive there.
In this inspirational movie, Karen Abercrombie portrays Meredith, the mother of a 40 year old Kayla struggling to start a business. Purple Roses is a Romantic movie of tenacity and success.
The residents of a small town discover that something more sinister than killer wolves is lurking in the backwoods: first the wolves start turning up dead...then people.
A lonely man becomes increasingly obsessed with the beautiful teenager he used to help care for his grandmother.
Three very different people from three very different worlds collide one winter afternoon in an anarchic Kolkata.

A former cop who has become a professional bounty hunter tracks a serial killer who kills with his bare hands. When the killer learns that he is being tracked he starts tracking his hunter leading to the invariable martial arts showdown.
While babysitting the daughter of Ed and Lorraine Warren, a teenager and her friend unknowingly awaken an evil spirit trapped in a doll.

Thomas, a teenager, is searching for the meaning of his life. In the process, he meets a strange guy named Leroy. Leroy shows Thomas that there is more to him than just an ordinary teenager. He is a werewolf of the highest order.
CIA Agent Skye Gold races through the throngs of Caribbean Carnival pursued by a mystery avenger, in a heart-pumping action thriller.
Loosely based on the short story by Edgar Allan Poe, a witch is sent to death, only to try & return from the grave, seventeen years later, to possess her daughter's adult body.
A mother regrets having forced her son to marry the woman she chose because of the bride's sour dispostion. She encourages her son to meet his former girlfriend and cheat on his wife
Tora receives a letter from Lily, telling him that she is terminally ill. He flies to see her in a Okinawa hospital, and the two get a chance to rekindle their old fling.
An American Vietnam soldier on his way home is left for dead and is saved by a pair of Japanese stragglers from WWII, who train him in the way of the samurai.
Marc moved Los Angeles to pursue an acting career. But like many others, he finds himself having to supplement his income with a day job he hates, but his luck is about to change.
A world's #1 assassin trying to disappear from his past is involuntarily entered into a contest where the best killers in the world are pitted against each other with the last one alive the winner.
Fearless seal Quinn assembles a squad of misfit recruits to stand up to ruthless sharks with razor-sharp teeth and reclaim the open sea.
While dating a woman (Shirly Brener) with anger-management issues, a hitman (Joey Lawrence) finds her journal and uses it as a guide to prove how much he loves her.

movie_name: The Song of the Scarlet Flower
description: About Olavi, a farmer's son who leaves his home after a dispute with his father and leads a life of a womanizing logger.
When a lorry driver realises that he is helping an escaped convict, he threatens to hand him over to the police. The convict begins to narrate the circumstances that landed him in jail.
The son of Italian immigrants to Canada struggles to find the best way to reveal to his parents that he's gay.
Prompted by the death of his father and the grief of his mother, a man recalls the story of how they met in flashback.

movie_name: Martian Successor Nadesico - The Motion Picture: Prince of Darkness
description: In this follow-up to the Martian Successor Nadesico anime series, a 14-year-old, genetically-engineered genius captain of the new Battleship Nadesico must fight an organized Martian Successor attack.
An identical twin seeks his brother, who is terrorized by visions of the devil and is detained in a secretive psychiatric institution.
Exchange of love-letters brings two souls fall in love with each other however business rivalry between their parents makes them go through a series of difficulties in love.
A lady fan and a young television journalist madly in love with a bachelor politician of Delhi and both wish to see him succeed. The love triangle is a revelation for everyone.

movie_name: The Lycan Chronicles: Wolf Creek Murders
description: The Lycan Chronicles~ A small, secluded town in Southern Indiana holds many dark and sinister secrets. Formed and financed by the ruling class of Vampires wishing to expand their covenant ...                See full synopsis »

Giorgi, a man of character, emigrates from Georgia, U.S.S.R. to the U.S. He and other Georgian immigrants there support one another while struggling to find work and become U.S. citizens. Giorgi falls for a cute reporter interested in his case.
An aspiring young Middle-Eastern poet moves to Montreal for medical school and is forever changed by the city and the young women who reveal him to his destiny.

movie_name: Umezu Kazuo: Kyôfu gekijô - Mushi-tachi no ie
description: A husband and wife each believe that the other is cheating on them. The upstairs room in their house becomes a point of bizarre physical transformations.

Farman's wife gives birth to a son and Haidar's wife gives birth to a daughter. Farman names his son Fereydoun. Years later, Fereydoun, who is a talented singer, tries to get married by the suggestion of his mother, Aqdas.
After her marriage comes undone, Soof must re-invent herself and get her tumultuous life back on track.
Upon his return to his ancestral homeland, an American man is bitten and subsequently cursed by a werewolf.

movie_name: Revelation Road 2: The Sea of Glass and Fire
description: With the Rapture now history, traveling salesman Josh becomes a warrior on the road in his plan to return home, but God guides others to help make Josh part of His plan.
A young superhero finds a new, unlikely confidant in a villain through an accidental phone number exchange.
A troubled woman meets her father for the first time and their encounter goes from awkward to alarming when they witness a man swallow a little girl whole.
The death of Padaiyappa's father destroys his family. But his luck changes, and he is able to lead a prosperous life, until his nemesis plots to ruin his happiness once more.

movie_name: Kvinden der drømte om en mand
description: What happens when a sexual connection overwhelms all your senses? A woman puts everything on the line in pursuit of a passionate affair with a man she hardly knows.
Murdock inherits an estate in Africa, on which "Satan's Harvest" (heroin and marijuana) is grown. The thugs growing the drugs want him out of the way, so things get messy.

movie_name: Getting Go, the Go Doc Project
description: A shy but smitten college boy pursues a NY go-go boy through the pretext of making a documentary film about him, with the guys knowing each other only as "Doc" and "Go."
In order to raise money, a young woman resorts to driving a taxi and picks up a passenger that turns out to be a blessing in disguise.

This story is pushing questions as if we can choose the way of our life and if we are capable to follow our dreams. It show us that the happiness is always in our hands and everyone choose his own way for happiness.
Ayush and Pari are about to confess their love for each other but a twist of fate keeps them away. When Ayush reunites with Pari years later, Ayush must learn to love Pari who's not herself anymore.
The film is based on one of Japan's most popular urban legends "Mary's Telephone" and 4 stories more.

A guy looking for an haircut finds himself trapped inside a strange barber shop. Waiting for its turn, he reads a comic book. The four stories he reads, will lead him inside a world of fear, sex and horror.

Top star Lilico undergoes multiple cosmetic surgeries to her entire body. As her surgeries show side effect, Lilico makes the lives of those around her miserable as she tries to deal with her career and her personal problems.
Jochen Falk and two further former Stasi agents embark on a dangerous mission to rescue the kidnapped president of Katschekistan. But soon it becomes clear that Falk pursues his own objectives.

After spending 76 days cooped up at home due to a mental health crisis, Klara does nothing but listen to her favorite radio show. She wonders if it's possible to fall in love with someone she heard on the radio but never met.

When the murdered body of a high school girl is found naked with a strange mark on her forehead, which is to prevent the vengeance of her spirit, Detective Khan from DSI is assigned to investigate the case.

"DASEIN" is a Non Linear, Post Modern, Meta-narrative film. In this film, the filmmaker tries to reinvestigate the core values of Existentialism and Nihilism. This film explores the roots of eternal human Desire and Despair.
A stubborn young woman hires a struggling singer to play her obnoxious suitor in a scheme to overturn her father's objections to the man she really wants to marry.

2034. Japan is divided into north and south parts. York, a nurse in northern Japan goes to South to learn her dead daughter still lives as the data,'information life' and she meets the hackers who fight against the government.
Raj and Kajal lives are shattered when a man with supernatural ability predicts that Kajal will die.
In the aftermath of a botched heist, it's down to the surviving members to finish the job and survive each other.

Hot-blooded district attorney Jin-woo and undisciplined cop Do-young want the same thing; justice. Their methods are completely different but they team up to catch and prosecute a powerful mafia boss and politician YOO.
While helping a wounded agent of the Iga, Shintaro is attacked by Koga agents who think he received an item that they had already killed in an effort to obtain.
Bolo Dugga Maiki is an entertaining movie about Samya who always lead his life as a liar. However when he meets a girl in a train, Uma, his life changes in the blessings of Maa Durga.
A New York City police officer tries to save his estranged wife and several others taken hostage by terrorists during a Christmas party at the Nakatomi Plaza in Los Angeles.
A 7-months pregnant mother and a six year old daughter move into a bigger home where they start to experience unusual paranormal events.
A run-away gangster, a sheltered-life student and a member of a broken family try to define the true meaning of relationship and family.
Roberto, a young slacker from Buenos Aires, begins a relationship with Raúl, an older man. Things take a turn for the worse as Raúl becomes increasingly abusive.

Vanya loses everything in his life and attempts suicide, but when a homeless dog saves him, all of the doors of success begin to open. He must fight against drug dealers, crooked cops, and a corrupt system that wants to see him fail.
The President of an African country decrees that the Arms budget will be diverted in to the "Water For All", project. The journalist, Michael Power, discovers a Coup set by the arms dealers.

movie_name: I Married a Monster from Outer Space
description: Aliens arrive on Earth to possess the bodies of humans. One of their first victims is a young man, whose new wife soon realizes something is wrong with him.
A highway patrolman goes after a ring of hit-and-run drivers known as "Banzai runners," who have fast, expensive cars and stage illegal, dangerous high-speed races on the freeways at night.
Spy chase after the secret formula for uranium, U92, employing various sci-fi gadgetry, and physical violence.
A small group of student filmmakers and a shy young girl with strict parents are simultaneously manipulated, seduced and abused by an older man. They follow his bidding, even when murder is involved.

Before the New Year, everyone wants a little love. Successful businessman Igor is looking for thrills, and his girlfriend is a stunning top model who wants their relationship to finally reach a new level.
A pinup artist (Ronald Reagan) in search of the perfect woman poses as a Czech immigrant to win over a shapely schoolteacher (Virginia Mayo) who’s more into facts than figures.

In the wild, snow covered gold fields of Alaska, two brothers embark on a journey to collect a bounty in a desperate attempt to save their home: but what they find along the way is more than they bargained for.
After the death of her parents, Mary finds the love and compassion she's been missing through three odd stowaways hidden in her basement.
Young Florentines take refuge from the black plague and engage in bawdy adventures and lusty exchanges.
A three-part look at the ironies of love, with stories that involve a young boy, a hostage situation, and a divorced elderly couple caught in a love triangle.
A Young boy takes after his father as a drug lord and rises to power ultimately resulting in a tragic feud between the two.
Agent OSS 117 is dispatched to Rio de Janeiro to investigate an organization developing a mysterious drug which is capable of completely controlling anyone injected with it.
A 16-year-old girl visits her gay half-brother and ends up seducing his boyfriend, thus wreaking havoc on all of their lives.

Gabriel's ex Luiza is now married to Alex, and Gabriel dates Jaqueline, an energetic younger woman. Gabriel and Luiza are apparently happy in their relationships, but an unexpected encounter revives their interest in each other.
It is a story about three modern-day women who make different decisions, how it affects them in the workplace, changes their friendship, and how they find love.
Two misfits form an unlikely relationship after a woman breaks into a man's house only to discover him in the midst of a suicide attempt.
Julia becomes an orphan and is taken in by Laura and Daniel, one of her father's childhood friends. The child makes Daniel remember the horrifying past he had chosen to bury.
No longer able to make a living as a fisherman, Gibraltan Carmelo goes to London to seek his fortune.

movie_name: Over the Rainbow, Under the Skirt
description: A man recalls his youthful dreams and past loves, especially a woman he adored in the summer of 1985.
Reuniting on a remote island from their childhood, two women find themselves haunted by the ghost of a dead girl from their past, but things are not what they seem.
The heroic warrior He-Man battles against the evil lord Skeletor and his armies of darkness for control of Castle Grayskull.
While trying to remain a good husband and father, Superbat and the Avengers of Justice come out of retirement to stop Dark Jokester and Lisp Luthor from freezing the planet.
A tortured Kidnap and Ransom specialist travels to India and hunts down those responsible for abducting the daughter of the Democratic front runner.

A cowardly, weak-eyed man loses his glasses in the street and suddenly a lion appears in front of him and is believed to be a sheep. He decides to imprison it in a butcher shop to discover that he is imprisoned a lion.
While filming a documentary about an agoraphobic woman, a celebrity psychologist is drawn into supernatural events.

Two couples go in search of a long lost Edgar Allan Poe manuscript at the behest of a Ouija board "I will not rest until it's found". Supernatural/horror story about strained relationships, paranormal activity and how life can imitate art.
A terrifying coven of tales designed to take viewers into the nether reaches of insanity, shock and horror.

A notorious doctor (Count Drake) has eyes for a beautiful young lady (Natasha) and holds her prisoner. To free her from the selfish vampire, Brandon becomes a powerful warlock. Yet, this creates problems as he and Natasha fall in love.
After accidentally crash-landing in 2022, time-traveling fighter pilot Adam Reed teams up with his 12-year-old self for a mission to save the future.

Four brothers committing crimes with a promise among them to stop someday. When a deal goes south, the older brother says it's enough, but the other three disagree and recklessly do business with a wanted crime lord.
English language reboot of José Mojica Marins' boogeyman, Coffin Joe, a sly and cunning undertaker who revels in the macabre.
A discovery made by a kung fu obsessed American teen sends him on an adventure to China, where he joins up with a band of martial arts warriors in order to free the imprisoned Monkey King.
A cop goes up against his lifelong friend, who has become one of the city's biggest drug traffickers.
When a government official is killed, an American operative with experience in the Yakuza culture is brought in to investigate.

movie_name: Christmas at the Grey Horse Inn
description: Writer Charlotte Quinn has lost her publisher, boyfriend and Christmas spirit. She flees ATL for NC to settle her aunt's estate and inherits an Inn and a pair of horses that will have to be sold to pay the taxes. How will she save the day?
A man and woman who just met are fugitives after her boyfriend is accidentally killed. They must evade arrest and rival gangs while searching for the money her boyfriend stole.
A woman meets a handsome football player while online dating, only to learn things might not be as they appear.
A young girl's love for her lover prevents her from revealing to him that her life is in danger because of a deadly disease.
This is it. a clean wholesome entertainment for the young and the young at heart. a perfect summer treat of rollicking comedy and vibrant romance.
World renowned journalist Sara Ogden is traversing the world in pursuit of carriers of a fatally dangerous "Stamp of Cain" in order to prevent seemingly unrelated events such as mass ...
On their way to a party on new years eve, a couple of strangers get stuck in an elevator - and has to get to know to each other.

Asif comes to City in search of Captain Khan, who, he learns, paid a price for choosing to be a gangster. Unperturbed, he continues in his search. Does he find Captain Khan and what's the mystery behind his disappearance?

The story of three young men who were taken away by the Japanese invaders for forced labor, and after their release they returned to their native fishing village and enthusiastically set about restoring the economy.
The newest and bloodiest compilation in short horror, Fun Size Horror: Volume Two continues the spine-tingling delivery of an unexpected variety of frightful stories all told in bite size pieces.
A small town youth finds fulfillment and romance in a big city's creative writing course, but feels obliged to sacrifice them when his sister's home life deteriorates in his absence.

After killing a man in self defense, Ryuji goes searching for peace. But when he finds that his elderly mother, Kiyo, is being harassed by a rival family, Ryuji has no choice but to choose the fate of the sword.
A trio of girls set out to change the male-dominated environment of the Seven Oaks college campus, and to rescue their fellow students from depression, grunge and low standards of every kind.
Desperate to leave her parents' house and start a new life with her boyfriend Kabir, Sonia agrees to deliver a mysterious package for her friend. Will her decision help her fulfill her desires.
Alyssa, a girl from town, is invited to the birthday celebration of her best friend in her parents' mansion. During the party Alyssa will propose a disturbing game to the family.
Paranoia spreads like a virus when a crew of land surveyors encounter psychotic campers possibly infected with an unknown sickness.
Jeeva, the son of a don, falls in love with Swarna, daughter of a famous Carnatic singer. However, he chooses to hide the truth about his family background to win her love.

movie_name: Star Wars: The Insurrection of the Empire
description: Some of the Imperial Knights have been seduced by the dark side of the force, but how many and who? Has the dark side infected too many of them? Is there redemption for the knighthood?
A wonderfully eccentric woman who stays around after her death and meddles in her niece's love life in a hilarious and often touching duel of wills.
Master Wu Wen-Yuan's (Chen Kuan Tai) gang of misfits become unlikely heroes when they work to get a Patriotic General to a British Consulate before his enemies and the Japanese can eliminate him.
A photo journalist travels to China on his first assignment after losing his wife and child in a car accident.

Contract killer SET makes a mistake during an operation and her employer doesn't tolerate mistakes. She gets a head start before other killers are sent her way. A young man sees her split lip and treats her like a hurt puppy or kitten.
During the winter season, a family camping in the woods, and a group of camp counselors training in the same forest both find themselves being killed one by one by an unhinged psycho.
The moving relationship of a man in crisis who would like to be a father, and a fatherless, mentally orphaned young rebel.
When you think marrying your best friend means a 'happily ever-after', but it turns out to be just the reverse.
A pair of Twitch podcasters report on the events of an indie horror film after its famous director is murdered, followed by members of the cast.
Like many other men, Ray Dawkins has no intention of getting married. Unfortunately for Ray, he meets the beautiful Barbie Crawford, and falls in love with her.
When an op goes wrong and FBI agent Zack's partner dies, his search for the one responsible takes him to a yakuza in Japan. A mob boss wants revenge for his son's death and Zack's his target.
Byzantine Prince kidnaps a governor and plans to marry Serbian Princess to create a rift within Ottoman Empire. Malkocoglu is sent to save the governor and prevent the marriage.

Recovering from the trauma of being kidnapped last Halloween by the Blue Skeleton, five friends head back out to visit more haunted house attractions. But when signs of the Blue Skeleton start appearing again a new terror begins.
Claire has everything - money, a loving husband and a desired child. But suddenly her life changes. Doubts and lies bring her to the edge of insanity.

A young pathologist seeks answers to the mysterious death of a friend and soon comes into contact with the same cursed videotape that caused the death of the friend's wife and son, which is haunted by the curse of Sadako, a relentless spirit.
Reporter Michael Gordon uncovers intrigue in Damascus, where the Allies and Nazis struggle for control of Arab sympathies.
A young Parisian woman - Evie, who absconds to England to make a fresh start. Evie takes a job as an agency carer and is quickly placed with a tetraplegic patient John.
A special agent's plans to reconcile with his ex-fiancé are ruined when she boards a private jet that is targeted by hijackers working for the same crime lord that he is chasing.
An undercover cop works to take down the Triads in Hong Kong. The movie is based on a popular video game Sleeping Dogs (2012).

The story of the assassination classroom and their teacher target continues with the students' own conflicts, Korosensei's identity, and the fate of the world as the deadline for assassination approaches.
Conner is a hit man. A mob boss gets wrack ed His son, hires Conner to find out who did it. If he refuses or takes longer he's dead.
A well-off bachelor finds himself at a loss for what to do when a married woman comes on to him while he's thoroughly involved with someone else's wife.

Kyeong-ah has no idea where her husband has gone and is confused about why she and her young children are being harrassed by gangsters. She finds a protector in 'Lefty' and the two begin to fall in love

The shocking secret of the lost China Diaries changes the lives of an American pilot and a Japanese businessman when they must finally confront the truth about what their parents really did before WW II began.
After her father's sudden death, Mahalakshmi is left to clear his debts and face the harsh villagers. A taxi driver helps her cremate her father and pledges his taxi to earn her a temporary reprieve.
Carl Malm is a goodhearted man who runs a railway station. He lives together with his maid and her seven kids.
A young girl planning to escape her small, pious town must first overcome herself- then her past- before she can leave.

"Swallow" depicts the story of Cha Eun-sook, who published a book titled "Jebi," which tells a story of the past during the military regime of Chun Doo-hwan in 1983, and her son, Lee Ho-yeon, who finds himself hidden in the book.

Pennsylvania, 1859. Railroad tycoon Brennan (Alan Hale) is muscling in on oil-drilling farmers, led by Peter Cortland (Randolph Scott). Cortland must try to save their oil business, while also saving his marriage to Sally (Irene Dunne).

A kingpin smuggler kills a police officer and succeeds in separating his teen-aged sons. The elder son who had vowed to take revenge, accidentally meets his younger brother. The two join forces to bust the smugglers gang.
A group of strangers must survive an onslaught from the undead that lasts through the night, all while trying to get along, as they wait for help to arrive.

movie_name: Scenes from Life of People on Leave
description: Two reserved people, almost resigned to their loneliness, found each other at the Soviet-era sea resort on the late autumn. Long dinners with senceless conversations transform into a love story

Hanan is a young woman who has moved from her hometown of Buffalo to San Francisco for the love of her beau, Mr. Baby. Watch the trials of tribulation of dealing with homesickness, an annoying job, and the big bad city.
A greedy businessman wants a promotion so bad he arranges for a work rival and his entire family to be murdered. The wife / mother then returns as a vengeful ghost armed with a steel-clawed gloved.
An exalted but short-fused surgeon plunges into a spiral of drugs, alcohol and rage after his intense relationship with his girlfriend turbulently ends.
Leo is a small time crook on the road to redemption. The age old story of a broken man trying to change himself. Escape to Passion is a sleazy action-packed classic.
The Dark Knight of Gotham City begins his war on crime with his first major enemy being Jack Napier, a criminal who becomes the clownishly homicidal Joker.
A blind master swordsman attempts to lead a quiet life with his wife but he is provoked back into battle.
4 years is about Gayathri and Vishal, their college sunrises, canteen sunsets and hostel mid nights.

Rebellious Weiyang(Elaine Zhong) and idealist 'princess' Xiao Qiao(Tan Song Yun) are best friends. Their world becomes complicated when Qiao's fiancee Chao Yan(Luo Jin) falls in love with Weiyang. Then Weiyang makes a surprising decision.

Mass deportations to Siberia of the 1940s as seen through eyes of a young boy called Staszek Dolina. His family members are among the 2 million Polish citizens, who are sent to the cruel Siberian work camps.
The son of a landowner becomes a tutor to a wealthy man's daughter whose widowed sister starts loving him.
A gang manages to steal the Blue Queen, one of the most precious gems in the world. But each member has his own plan for the future.
The Devil is released directing the intelligence community to kill cultural and political leaders throughout time.

movie_name: Gurren Lagann the Movie: Childhood's End
description: Simon and Kamina, brothers in arms, take upon themselves to venture beyond the borders of their world, reality and imagination. Venturing further and further into a hidden truth that has kept humanity prisoners for millennia.
A priest and two Vatican exorcists must do battle with an ancient satanic force to save the soul of a young woman.
Rafal's wife and two children get killed on the road by a drunk truck driver. When police can't find the killer, Rafal starts to work on his own to punish the perpetrator.
Seeking to understand his power to move around in his own timeline, David must eventually confront the disassembled chronology of his own life.
Two women, once a lesbian couple and now just friends, leave for a seminar together. Their current girlfriends, left to their own devices, fall for each other and begin a desperate steamy affair.
A beautiful seductress waits for lost souls on a barren island. It may be too late before anyone finds out if she is evil or not.

An estranged family take a trip to the desert in their used RV but become stranded and isolated in the scorching terrain. They soon learn their RV holds terrible, haunting secrets, and it starts killing them off one by one.
An inexperienced yet naturally gifted ice skater makes a spectacular debut in the skating world before encountering an event that could possibly derail her hopes and dreams.
Sinbad and the vizier of Marabia, followed by evil magician Koura, seek the three golden tablets that can gain them access to the ancient temple of the Oracle of All Knowledge.
The story revolves around a group of teenage boys. When one of them suddenly gets a chance to make a pact with the devil things shift quickly in their lives.

A nasty comedian's assistant has allergy induced sneezes, giving problems at work, et cetera. He accepts weekly injections after seeing the cute nurse. After a dozen injections, he finally asks her out.

Alvaro is an annoying boy who became the Student Council President, while Anggia was his deputy. They never get along in meetings. When she didn't agree to hold a Prom, he mocks that she was afraid because she would not get a partner.

A love story that starts at the immature age of 19 and continues till 27 years, how Arjun and Keerthi dealt with their emotions at each stage of life and how they take forward steps in their career is the main plot
Angga, a student who rarely prays on time, falls in love with the intelligent and religious Ratih. Angga's uniqueness, sincerity, cheerfulness, and demeanor made Ratih want to open her heart.

After the murder of their parents,Nick and Steve Wellington are left to share their Inheritance. However, when the masked Figure shows back up to finish what was started, everyone will learn the hard way that blood runs thicker than water.
Archaeology students uncover a prehistoric manster... part man, part monster, and all bad attitude with a cheap costume.
Zombies have overrun the earth, and young Scott's the last to learn about it - so he can't be too picky when it comes to choosing his safe haven.
In front of their little boy, Camille and Georges dance to their favorite song "Mr Bojangles". With them, there is only place for fun and fantasy.
6-year-old and 10-year-old brothers decide to explore a dead serial killer's former homestead causing strange things to start happening over the next few days.
Patrick Connor's life is quickly turned upside down after taking a job at an abandoned probationary camp for boys.
A wretched piece about a promiscuous woman, who has affairs with every man she meets, including her daughter's boy friend.
A post-apocalyptic thriller about a heartbroken man and his new friends who must together battle marauders in order to survive in a new lawless world.
A love story between a poor fellow and a daughter of respected workshop owner set in an Italian post-war village.

Dustin and Gary are forced to navigate their way through a modern myth when Dustin is bitten by a radioactive chihuahua. Once a curse takes hold of Dustin, he and Gary are forced to run for their lives from the monster slayer, Van Helsing.
This is a story about Vampires and the struggle for rulership amongst the elders and elites. Humanity is at stake and if the wrong House is nominated for rulership it could be doom for the living.
An army major is transferred to a training camp after being blamed by the police for doing their job. However, when the law and order worsens, the police ask him to take over the nation's security.
A politician (a brilliant and well-liked mayor from his fellow citizens, candidate for the Chamber) clashes with a graduate, disappointed and against the current dancer.
Bryan Clark is a researcher looking into the truth of Allegan, Michigan's local Melonhead legend. Pairing up with a local man, Joe Dobbs, the two attempt to track down the monster.
Plagued by endless visions and nightmares, Jenny Adams suspects that, as a child, she was responsible for the brutal murder of her own mother.

Shy Henry is overjoyed to fall into an unexpected romance with gorgeous and popular Samantha the summer after high school graduation. When Henry's love spirals into twisted obsession, Samantha pulls back.
A married woman hits a pedestrian with her car who requests that she must perform a particular punishment as a penance.

When a group of troubled inner city teens are court ordered to participate in an outdoor youth backpacking program as a form of rehabilitation, they run into a psychopath who is hell bent on hunting them down.

A group of American kids in search of a hidden surfing paradise in Mexico get into trouble with some less than welcoming locals. But the real danger comes from someone else: The wave-shredding...UNDEAD!
A murderous drug dealer breaks his partner out of police custody. An undercover cop is assigned to track down the two killers and bring them in.
Whispers of the past and present come together in the darkness of the theater in this Emmy-nominated dance film performed by Ballet Austin and filmed on-site at the haunted Scottish Rite Theater.
Unable to find the happiness he seeks in marriage, the holding boss Erol begins to be with Suzan, whom he met in a pavilion. However, Susan suddenly disappears after a while.
After traumatic childhood experiences, Piotrek can't find his purpose in life. He decides to get into illegal fights and unexpectedly receives an offer that can change the whole of his life.

A young woman tries to find her origins after having been abandoned as an infant at a cemetery wrapped in a cloth with satanic symbols, but as she gets closer to answers a malevolent spirit is telling her to leave.
A clueless, flamboyant college kid discovers that the soul of a great vampire king resides within him. Now he must choose between his friends and his destiny.
A celebrated cop attempts to hunt down a serial killer who has specifically challenged him to put an end to the killing spree.
An anthropologist and his students attempt to track down a Bigfoot responsible for a rash of violent murders, only to uncover something even more sinister.
"Jack Hunter's Paranoia Tapes" is the longest running found footage franchise in history. Now, find find all of the best shorts from every installment of the award winning series in one place.

Gabra is silent about a girl named Ghazal who lives abroad and comes to one of the cities of Iran to sell her grandfather's inheritance; When he enters the city, he encounters unexpected events; until . . .

A film crew shooting their first documentary are tasked with recreating last years Halloween massacre by a psycho dressed as a clown. Little do they know, this production is about to run into their own horrifying fate.
An evil spirit leaves the body of his human host, a criminal on death-row, and sneaks into the body of his next human host, a French magistrate.

Full-throttle splatter-ific Japanese cyberpunk science fiction/horror at its most aggressive, this mind-blower about alien parasites that turn their human hosts into slave "Necroborgs" will leave you dizzy and drained - in a good way.

movie_name: Attila and the Great Blue Bean
description: In a medieval fantasy world, boar warrior Attila the Ham teams up with a tough human princess to find the legendary Great Blue Bean, a source of tremendous power.
"Tarek " young and romantic works in one of the mobile operators, by chance enters on an adventure to save his love of unreal danger.
Soon after Thom starts operating as an illegal taxi driver in New York City, Claire hires him to drive her to California after her estranged father suffers a heart attack.

Tiger, a thief, wants to retire after losing his partner in crime. He plans to pull-off one last heist of $ 7 Billions and recruits Rocky, who is relatively new in the game. Meanwhile Bangkok Police and Mafia Lord, Ringo is after them.
A man arrives in Chennai with a simple wish of buying gold bangles for his mother. However, an event changes his life completely and he becomes famous as the most dreaded criminal in the city.
Freud's essay on anxiety, guilt, and shame, perfectly fits on this middle class Indian housewife, who's guilt when turns into shame, creates a monster which is uncontrollable .
Two friendly thugs take a job of a robbery and the murder of a girl and they find themselves in love with the girl and face many obstacles to keep their promise.

Two US soldiers desert from the Vietnam war and go their separate ways. Both of them reach Europe and become involved in the criminal underworld, and eventually reunite in Rome with plans to escape to Canada.

After Jack's father passes away, he rethinks his life and decides to come clean with his best friend Fred, his ex-girlfriend Debbie and with himself. But in the process he causes everybody more trouble that he can manage.

Bhargava, an efficient, yet jobless young man gets an opportunity to work as an Assistant Engineer with the government because of his good deeds. After being pressurized for signing on illegal files, Bhargava wages a war on injustice but is framed by a criminal minded Minister for corruption and is imprisoned. How Bhargava proves his innocence and takes his revenge makes the rest of the film.
Milan is a boy who lives in a village and has certainly not had an easy life. His grandma is a witch, his father is a drunk and his mother is dead.

A cop killed by his own partner joins RIPD, an afterlife law enforcement department working to apprehend various monsters disguised as humans living on earth, and gets paired up with a smart-mouthed veteran.
In an alternate universe where the wild west never ceased, a lone traveler happens upon a town facing the brunt of lawless creeds and political chaos.
A 26-year old widow is cared for by her younger brother-in-law. He, however, falls in love with her. She opts to run away from her in-laws' house rather than face the situation
The people of a rural Midwestern town go about their daily lives unaware something savage is among them, causing death...and the dead to walk.
Photographer Robert Kincaid wanders into the life of housewife Francesca Johnson for four days in the 1960s.

movie_name: Baba Yaga: Terror of the Dark Forest
description: When Egor's mom dies, he gets a stepmom and then a baby half sister. Things get seriously twisted when his dad gets a hot nanny, who's the witch, Baba Yaga.
On a road trip to Reno for a bachelor party, 4 friends stop at a remote lake cabin where four mysterious crates are delivered.

movie_name: My Inner Demon: A Geraldson Tale
description: While making a series of found footage videos, a pair of filmmakers accidentally summon an evil entity that becomes hellbent on destroying them.
DCP Rudra faces a bunch of challenges after he locks horns with a notorious criminal Nagori Subramanium.
A psychologist with a special needs son boards a transatlantic flight containing a demonically possessed passenger.
An organized gang specializing in high ranking military assassinations bewilders the police. However, their headquarters are located and a special agent is sent to terminate all members of the gang.

A teacher falls in love with a young British woman who works as an English teacher at the same school. He tries to woo her, leads conflicts that come crashing on them as they face the biggest battle of their lives - to get married.

movie_name: How Long Will I Love U
description: A woman from 2018 and a man from 1999 wake up in the same bed. They discover they can time travel using the bedroom door, and make changes to their eras, but that their destinies may not be in their own hands.
Three sisters on the run with a suitcase full of stolen heroin hide out in their childhood home, which is haunted by the ghosts of their parents.
Picking up from the shocking ending of "SoulHood Prime: Luke and Lee", the team must come together at all cost to stop the upcoming dangerous threat.
Deep inside a lush forest you'll find Szepasszony. She's a beautiful young girl with a deep demonic secret. Enter this forest at your own risk.
Three guys who need ghost number, one of them must marry the lovely ghost in order to fulfill the ritual.
After a family tragedy, a racist prison guard re-examines his attitudes while falling in love with the African-American wife of the last prisoner he executed.
Unlucky in love, strangled at work, and tormented at home, Joel Slater is desperately searching for a way to juggle his life. But sometimes, the secret to happiness begins with letting go.
A variety of broad-painted and unlikely characters are trapped in an underground café when a Mississippi River levee breaks and causes flood havoc above and below.

A story of a middle class guy, passionate about becoming an actor and prove his worthiness to his family. Ditching a job interview as a favor from a father to his son, the story leads to new endeavors.
An alien orphan is sent from her abducted planet to Earth, where she grows up to become her adoptive home's first and greatest super-hero.
After witnessing the murder of his father, Little Mute trains in Shaolin Temple for revenge and is taught by various teachers, one of which is clandestine.
A small-town country homebody goes to New York to find her missing fiancé and gets romantically involved with two sophisticated men.
Vampire death dealer Selene (Kate Beckinsale) fights to end the eternal war between the Lycan clan and the Vampire faction that betrayed her.
Han-kyung comes to town to live with her mom. Attracted to her pure charm, the most popular guys Hae-won and Tae-sung fight each other for her.
In the context of China's urbanization, a young man faces existential difficulties and decides to rewrite his life.
Several months after the U.S. entry into World War II, an inexperienced U.S. Navy commander must lead an Allied convoy being stalked by a German submarine wolf pack.

Two romantic burnouts meet at a wedding and almost hook up in the coatroom before putting the brakes on. They agree to exchange candid confessions about their pasts on the off chance that this might be the real thing.
Thomas Baldwin, a veteran of the war in Afghanistan suffering from PTSD, embarks on a journey of unspeakable horror after becoming infatuated with a creature growing out of his bathtub drain.
The Kingdom Of Shadows is a mystical cinematic experience which stirs from the darkness the spirits of our ancestors and reawakens the horror of unresolved crimes and denied desires.
A masked serial killer turns a horror-themed amusement park into his own personal playground, terrorizing a group of friends while the rest of the patrons believe that it is all part of the show.
Trained by a top assassination teams, a young assassin receives his first mission and finds himself tangled in a political intrigue planned for years.
A truck driver falls in love with, and is rejected by, a white-collar career woman. Competition arrives from a dashing male colleague.
A group of young friends are hunted by the gatekeeper of Hell (Gurdian) when they accidentally unlock the portal to the Underworld.
The screening of a 70's so-bad-it's good cult classic takes a dark turn as the ghost story on the screen comes to life.
Seven days afters he was sold out by his boss and murdred by the crime syndicate he was pursuing, policeman Shun possesses his yoinger sister body to exact vengeance on those who killed him.

A womanizing artist finds love that changes his life, only to risk it all In a fight for freedom against religious terrorism and political tyranny that alters the fate of nations. Based on a provocative true story.
It tells the story of a generation of master Huang Feihong's calm and sagacious characteristics, and in the double worries of the provocation of Beiquan and the invasion of foreigners.

movie_name: Molli and Max in the Future
description: A sci-fi romantic comedy about a man and woman whose orbits repeatedly collide over the course of 12 years, 4 planets, 3 dimensions, and one space-cult.
Stright after her marriage Hong Kong officer Mina Kao faces dangerous case of vietnamese criminal refugees.
The story concerns the efforts of seven master swordsman who join together to protect the new inexperienced Shogun Tokugawa Yoshimune from the evil plans of the Owari Clan's corrupt Lord.

Turkish and Neo Nazi gangs battle over territory and drug trafficking in Berlin, while a serial killer is on the loose. This action thriller brings several cultures together wanting to dispose of evil and stop the violence.
Blacklits is female driven futuristic edgy thriller, set a hundred and fifty years into the future that has no current day technology, it's a world that is unthinkable but yet realistic.
In a rural village, a boy named Zoroku suddenly becomes infected with an unknown disease that causes him to rot away slowly.
THE FILM VINDICATES GOVERNMENT EFFORTS TO SOLVE THE PROBLEMS IN MINDANAO, ESPECIALLY THOSE THAT RELATE TO SECESSIONIST MOVEMENTS.
A surreal science fiction noir involving a man trapped in a future where seemingly everyone is a government spy and all-night noodle stands are outlawed.

A young couple from UK Peter and Linda, decide to come to Poland and visit Peter's brother Karol, who they haven't met before. The best time of their lives does not last long. Does the legend of ghastly Galinda really exist?

movie_name: Bala... Dapat Kay Cris Cuenca, Public Enemy No. 1
description: Cris (Ramon Revilla Sr.) tries to avoid trouble to support his family but due to an incident, he becomes a completely notorious criminal.
A young girl goes to Africa to find her lost brother living among sordid people but finds true love with a disqualified pilot.
In a world where luck can be taken from a lucky person by a luckier person's touch, a small group of lucky people compete to be the luckiest and for the other contestants' luck.
Compassionate look at the troubles of two young newlyweds, whose marriage has yet to be consummated.

A PTSD marine goes to extreme measures to rescue his 8 year old brother from a science research facility, where he is being experimented on for his special ability to tap into multi-dimensions across space and time.

A group of filmmakers investigate the legend of America's first serial killer, Jeremiah Godslight. However, they get more than they bargained for and soon learn that by unraveling the secrets of the past, unspeakable evil is unleashed.
When her gangster brother is kidnapped, an upstanding but reclusive teacher must risk everything by plunging into the criminal world to save him.

When a mysterious super soldier hunts down a fellow trooper, leaving a bloody trail of victims through a small Texas town, the soon to be retired Sheriff discovers these men might be the link to his missing-in-action son.

Congressional aide Erica forgoes family Christmas to travel at her boss's behest. At a beach side Air Force base, she clashes with Capt. Andrew Jantz, who knows her assignment is finding reasons to defund the facility.
A young woman uses a magic potion that causes her handsome crush to see her as more attractive than she actually is.
Mark's single engine airplane crashes deep in the forest. An old hiker, Oscar, makes it his quest to help Mark hike out. Along the way, Mark discovers things about himself that have been long hidden.
A young woman discovers she may have psychokinetic powers. A remake of the 2017 Norwegian film 'Thelma'.
An investigative journalist is arrested for cheating banks with fake certificates. He discovers a crime syndicate behind the scam and decides to investigate it himself.
A terrorist couple is pitted against each other when the female counterpart is captured by C.I.A. agents. They convince her to help them bring down the dangerous group in this violent actioner.
When Oliver reluctantly decides to attend a murder mystery party on the anniversary of a town serial killer, he and the guests are swept into a night of terror when it seems the killer has returned.
Tells a very real story of the pressures of relationships and working lives and how they intertwine together.
Two young students, a man and a woman, rent the same appartment without knowing it. They have to arrange with their upcoming feelings, strange neighbours and poverty.
María, a nurse and the only daughter of a smuggler, falls in love with the journalist who investigates her father's tricks.
A young man visiting and helping his uncle in New York City finds himself forced to fight a street gang and the mob with his martial art skills.
Wah and Kinki both working at a computer company. Both of them are not getting on very well initially, but friendship develops into romance when they get to know each other after a while.

It follows Amy Wisez, who is still traumatized after having witnessed her wealthy parents horrific murder suicide. She spends a weekend away with her unfaithful boyfriend and realizes she shouldn't have stopped taking her medication.
Four best friends embark on a luxurious wine tasting and soon find themselves fighting for their lives.
Hidden with a mysterious agenda, a sniper holds a businessman hostage in a closed phone booth, where he is ordered to obey the sniper or he will be killed.

When Peru's Biggest Action Film Star and Jordan's newest rising talent find themselves pursued by a notorious Bookie, a couple of private investigators are forced to choose between their job and their conscience.
The Bellows family causes comic confusion on an ocean liner, with time out for radio-style musical acts.
Over the summer of 1965, two teenage boys fall in love against the backdrop of a beachside town that holds many secrets.
One his wedding day, a young man gets cold feet, and both encouraging and discouraging advice from his four best friends who are various stages in their own relationships.

Follows compulsive gambler Sergio who after receiving a tip-off returns to the betting house trying to recover all the money he has lost , but another gambler bursts into the place with a gun and a gunshot will change his life forever.
Four friends decide to sneak into their high school late at night for fun, but the horrors they soon discover lead to grisly consequences and the uncovering of a morbid district-wide conspiracy.
When a small town teacher mistakes the hit-man hired to kill her for her long lost brother, a tangled web of family secrets, deadly deception and forbidden love is spun that could destroy them all.
A blind girl gets a cornea transplant so that she will be able to see again. She gets more than she bargained for upon realizing she can also see ghosts.
It's love at first sight when a rebellious playboy falls in love with a girl. He now has to go to great lengths to win her heart.
Bumbling simpleton Yeong-koo is back, this time must deal with the chaos created by a fox spirit and a raccoon spirit.
A disgraced, condemned mech-pilot war hero, trapped in an electromagnetic superstorm, is pursued by a mysterious and relentless enemy.

An investigative thriller with elements of romance, the film narrates the story of two couples: a Kochi-based scrap artist named Luca and his girlfriend Niharika; and a police officer named Akbar and his wife Fathima.

As a spate of leopard attacks causes panic, a sceptical Tarzan joins a hunting expedition, only to face a pagan cult of Leopard-God worshippers and their fiendish High-Priestess. Can he escape the sharp claws of the savage Leopard Woman?

The true story of Lord Francis Hope, who inherits the Hope Diamond and marries showgirl May Yohe'. Lord Francis Hope gambles away the family fortune and May Yohe' leaves him--another suspected curse of owning the Hope Diamond.
A man with no name is sent to the Zombie infested and quarantined Hong Kong island to find one survivor who could hold the cure for all mankind.
Three people are transported into a parallel reality, where they find they must use modern technology, but medieval weapons, in order to save the citizenry from a murderous warlord.
Two rival soldiers who were killed in Vietnam are brought back to life in a top secret military experiment that creates superhuman warriors.
Mickey, an NBA referee, meets Ellen, an American airline official, in Paris. It develops into a relationship of ups and downs.

In San Francisco's Chinatown, a Chinese-speaking Caucasian criminal robs an antiquities shop and murders the owners, leaving the police with one clue, the killer's voice heard on the phone by a switchboard-operator.
The daughter of a reclusive couple in the St. Moritz mountains tends to her brother, disabled from the Great War, though a handsome young architect who has just arrived waits for her attentions.
A blind man who is cheated by the girl he loves finds himself trapped in a murder case. While searching the real culprit, he comes across with many thrilling situations.
Tough cop Durai Singam performs an undercover operation and identifies some nefarious activities in the seas around the coastal town.

A successful female editor whose biological clock is ticking and and a struggling writer make a deal to realize her dreams of motherhood and his dreams of literary stardom. But once they get everything they want, are they really happy?
After being hypnotized by his sister-in-law, a man begins seeing haunting visions of a girl's ghost and a mystery begins to unfold around him.

Detective Elizabeth Levin investigates a series of gruesome murders of decapitation and religious sacrifice. She discovers a religious order that started at the beginning of the world to hunt down and kill these blood-thirsty creatures.
A priest, a nun and a showman sneaks into the morgue and sees a dancing vampire and catches it. It all lead to an assault and abduction of Tien Tien.
The family loses the father. The mother finds herself responsible for five sons and daughter to each their own lives, so will she be able to control all of this?

In the year 1206 Norway is raged by civil war. The King's illegitimate infant son, Håkon Håkonsson, which half the kingdom wants killed off, is guarded in secrecy by two men. A story which changed the course of the country's history.

After another failed film, young director Gus Campbell receives one last chance to make his dream project thanks to a mysterious investor. But, when his crew begins to disappear, Gus finds himself in the plot of a real horror movie.
A godless man is recruited by a secret organization who works to combat demonic possessions in order to prepare a new generation in the battle against evil forces.

Religious school principal tries to help a student escape her abusive father in hopes of finding her estranged mother. Dark Daddy, a vicious demon alternate version of her father, who the principal knew from their teens, stands in the way.
Secret agent Dok Su-jeon is sent to Hong Kong to thwart a North Korean plot meant to disrupt the talks between South Korea and Japan.
Billy and Sarah, two delinquent teenage lovers from the suburbs of Los Angeles, travel to a small southern town to falsely claim a dead friend's inheritance.
A gay transfer student pledges to a predominantly straight fraternity where his "straight-with-issues" big brother has a steady girlfriend but privately relishes man-to-man sex.
A wrongly convicted martial artist seeks revenge for the murder of his brother's family by a gang looking for the money he was convicted of stealing.

movie_name: Careers: A Martial Arts Love Story
description: The careers of a struggling kung fu school master and a successful actress interfere with their romance.
Sachio was camping with his fiancée, Yoshiko, in the deep green mountains. They enjoy a daytime affair, suddenly a nearly naked Tetsuji runs into them.
An ex-stock car champion gets out of jail to learn that his son, a controversial up and coming racer himself, is living his life as dangerously off the track as he is on it.
Fearless racer Michel Vaillant attempts to win "24 Hours of Le Mans", the famous highly challenging and prestigious annual endurance race that lasts one whole day.
Two down on their luck men tries to kidnap a wealthy businesswoman's dog to demand a hefty ransom from her. Things goes haywire when the dog goes missing.
After failing to keep his wife's dying wish, a series of tragic events leads Henry to believe she's returned to get revenge.
In 1995, a group of kids who share a passion for movies decide to venture out into the forest to create a horror film, but in the depths of the woods, there is a existent creature who poses a threat.

After finding he is spied on by a secret organization, a screenwriter tries to discover who is stalking him. With the help of an old friend of his, he falls into a maze of problems, and his only way out is by throwing a few punches.
Students investigate a haunted house plagued by spirits who've fallen victim to a deadly drinking game. Naturally the only road to truth is play the game yourself.
This film belongs to a psychological-horror genre. It revolves around a young researcher and take the audience through his mental and physical journeys.

Nearby two village heads son & daughter falls in love despite the rivalry between them. Story revolves around one person who keeps on adding misunderstandings between two families which leads to trouble for the couple on getting married.
Learning of a fortune in gold being secretly shipped to Romania, master thieves Charlie and Riya assemble a crack team to steal it.

Two uneasy friends, a police officer and a TV talk show host, each pursue the mysterious "handcuff killer" with the aid of an artist who sees - and draws - the killer's crimes before they're committed.
Following a mysterious car accident in the desert, Dafne suffers from post-traumatic amnesia. Jake, the first person she sees when she regains consciousness, tells her he's her husband.
The Earth is invaded by stingray-shaped alien "slugs" that ride on people's backs and control their minds.

Duel Vision is a psychological martial arts drama about Jack and Molly. With corrupted memories of Molly vexing Jack, the real Molly must defeat the broken recollections so that Jack can move beyond the past.

A serial killer that was never punished as a child for killing animals, escalates into stalking women and then sadistically killing them. The authorities must catch him before The Association takes matters into their own hands.
Death is inevitable and no one ever knows how or when it will happen. Here are four people who are caught up in fate and are looking for. Will they cheat death?
