Unable to cope with his wife's death, J.M. flees to his sister's desolate farm where he was married one year ago. There, he finds himself haunted by memories and visions of his dead wife, Andrea.

Another Europe, 1991. When Poland is invaded by an unknown enemy from the East, NATO decides to send in recon squads of undesirable soldiers. This is the story of one such squad, and the village they find amidst ruin and horror.
"Using a phone that can make calls through time, she must save the world from a nuclear apocalypse that happened 20 years ago"
He fought valiantly in battle, but he had to fight the world to keep the LOVE of his Korean war bride.

Things look up for an aspiring actor when he trades in the big-city life for a small-town existence. Without so many other actors and bachelors to compete with, Gino finds himself doing well with both employers and women.
Two hitmen and a getaway driver find themselves in the middle of a confrontation between a drug lord, an arms dealer and a con man, all surrounding the mysterious contents of a messenger bag.
When their adoptive mother is gunned down in a store robbery, four brothers decide to investigate the murder and find the killers themselves, but not all is what it seems.
Stripper Blaze Starr, playing herself, drives her agent--who is also her fiancé--to distraction by ignoring scheduled "press functions" and spending her weekends at a nudist camp.
In a dystopian future where illegal pharmaceuticals are the new currency, twelve defectors from North County have three days to rescue their children from the same prison camp they used to be in.
Roving clans of shape-shifting human/hyena creatures prowl and hunt for human prey. They are hunted by one man seeking revenge for the death of his loved ones.
An American teacher falls for a Greek musical prodigy while exploring one of the oldest and most mysterious regions of Greece, the Mani.

France, a reporter working from an international news agency, manages to be paid to visit all of Munich's massage parlors. He wants to find the whereabouts of Sonia, a personal masseuse with whom he experienced perfect bliss.
Seventy-year-old teenagers running away from home. They are not running away from their parents, they are running away from the inevitable.
A romantic comedy, set on Cape Cod in 1905, about three 70-year-old retired sea captains who try to lure an attractive middle-aged woman into marriage.
Good Vampires battle Zombie Vampires while trying to hide their own identity and prevent the infection from spreading.
See EDDIE FERNANDEZ as the millionaire playboy who gets involved in mystery cases, FULL OF EXCITEMENT ACTION - SUSPENSE.
A detective and a psychic investigate a series of murders at a trailer park, and suspect that some of the residents are doing the killings--and they are vampires.

Twist of fate brought Abir back to Hridoypur. There, he is determined to get his childhood revenge, but finds his childhood love Nila instead. Which will ultimately get priority in Abir's mind? Revenge or Love?
A modern-day deputy tracks an abducted girl to a ghost town, and the spirits of the past who took her.

movie_name: Spacehunter: Adventures in the Forbidden Zone
description: On a distant planet inhabited by mutants, two bounty-hunters race to rescue three Earth female captives from the clutches of an evil mutant warlord.
When a young woman with dreams of fame rents a billboard to advertise herself, her life changes overnight.
A poor southern family must deal with a wily stripper and a psychopath attempting to manifest the Antichrist into their bathroom.
A series of kidnappings in a small Texas border town lead a US Marshal to Mexico, where she discovers an extremist cult with grandiose plans.

Three snobbish high school girls prematurely age brought on from a curse, a drug (or something) after the arrival of new transfer student whom they believe is connected to a murder they committed a year earlier. A fate worse than death.

Forbidden love if the theme of "Aliping Maharlika". Amir and Dayang are two people in love. But one is a slave and the other a princess. Native laws of pre-Constitution days forbids such romantic combination. But always, love wins.

Daughter of Ottoman Pasha, Mujgan falls in love with firefighter Murat. Yalaza Nuri is informed about this love. Now, Murat is at a loose end because he promises to Pasha for preserving his honor but Yalaza Nuri is the danger for Mujgan.

A domineering mother sets out to break up the romance and possible marriage of her daughter, Cecily Stoughton, with Ted Pyncheon by several contrived devices and bringing in other candidates more to her liking.

Single mother Anesu's life is turned upside down when her son enters her into a reality TV competition. A refreshing view of contemporary life in Harare, Zimbabwe, told through the lens of a classic romantic comedy.

movie_name: Jimmy and Gret Don't Do Sex
description: An unconventional love story about the relationship between Gret, a forty-five-year-old uptight do-gooder, and Jimmy, an aging recovering alcoholic.
Ilyas Bazna works as a butler in the British Embassy in Turkey during WW2. After Bazna starts to work as a German spy he is going to experience a series of unexpected events.

Urban legend has it,if one is walking alone at night and heard someone calling out his or her name from behind, one has to answer after the third call. Otherwise the person would be trapped in same place and could never find his way back.
An insomniac writer's sleep-deprived hallucinations distort reality as paranoia drives him to extreme violence.
As a struggling actress prepares for the lead role in a horror film, she dives deeper into her traumatic memories and unearths terrifying truths about her family's dark past.

A man and a woman, both in strained marriages, become acquainted during their visits to the Marriage Counselor. The man employs the woman later, and they both become emotionally involved. The story is about how they break from their past.
A French woman mourning over the death of her husband three years prior is courted by a Swedish co-worker.
A string of seemingly unrelated murders reveals a plot to detonate a nuclear device on American Soil.
A psychiatrist and a reporter travel to a small Spanish village in an attempt to determine the cause of a mutual friend's mysterious illness.

Second theatrical spin-off from the popular 1970's police series. Regan and Carter head a Flying Squad investigation into a series of bank raids by a team of well-armed villains who are flying in from the continent.
A woman's past comes back to haunt her when a supernatural stalker seeks revenge in the aftermath of a daring art robbery
Willi receives a wrong call asking to pick up a package. Convinced by his friend José Manuel to change their life of poverty, they decide to go for it.

Zed anticipates an athletic scholarship while Addison is gearing up for Seabrook's international cheer-off competition. Then suddenly, extraterrestrial beings appear around Seabrook, causing more than friendly competition.

movie_name: John Bauer and the Mountain King
description: Two Swedish artists from the 19th century meet at Academy of Fine Arts in Stockholm and falls hopelessly in love and although he becomes world famous they find it hard to live together since he wants the forest and she the city.
An American spinster's dream of romance finally becomes a bittersweet reality when she meets a handsome--but married--Italian man while vacationing in Venice.
A series of events change the orphaned Pip's life forever as he eagerly abandons his humble origins to begin a new life as a gentleman.
A septuagenarian couple are attracted to each other in a retirement home but find the institution and their fellow patients frown on their relationship.
After ripping the door off of an SUV, by hand, a young man comes to recognize the source of his extraordinary strength.
A Parisian sewer worker longs for a rise in status and a beautiful wife. He rescues a girl from the police, lives with her in a barren flat on the seventh floor, then marches away to war.
A chilling recollection of the mysterious disappearance and subsequent death of a young student in a large nature reserve.

Madhiyazhagan Mooriyar and his brother is in love with girls who are sisters and also belongs to antagonist family. This story is all about how Madhiyazhagan Mooriyar is succeeding against all the odds.
A young woman in search of love through a dating app is torn between her best friend and the man of her dreams. Will she trust in the app or follow her heart?
President Isimo wants to get rid of all the ugly children. Paul is one of these children, but he manages to escape and start a movement in an attempt to overthrow President Isimo.
An ambitious and driven, but loveless, young executive falls in love with a seemingly hopeless prostitute.

Master and sisters of Hong's circus come to Kaifeng and arrange their show. They are bullied by local tyrant Hou family and master Hong dies. Hong sisters go to the Shaolin Temple and ask help to take revenge for their father's death.
C-Moe is Dallas's biggest drug dealer who is on top of the world. A tragic accident happens and he has no choice but to learn how to live with the help of a home town nurse.

Eight unsuspecting high school seniors at a posh boarding school, who delight themselves on playing games of lies, come face-to-face with terror and learn that nobody believes a liar - even when they're telling the truth.
A secret agent gets killed by an international criminal gang when he gathers photographic evidence against them, so Gopi (Agent 116) now investigates this case to get the criminal gang arrested.

A collage of human fates, where all shown characters are suffering from panic attacks. Stories like a policeman who is willing to come out or a young business woman who achieved her life goals too early.
Three friends decide to work in watermelon selling, but the head of the vegetables and fruits doesn't like that, so they go on a fight with him.
New York hairdresser Izzy seizes the chance to work at the wedding of a charming prince, but when sparks between them fly, will love or duty prevail?
A journalist desperately tries to find his missing fiancee and finally uncover the truth behind a sinister folklore, leading him down a dangerous road of discovery.
A Russian ex-Spetsnaz working as a mechanic in LA accepts a job freeing a kidnapped woman in Saint Petersburg, as the mob boss also killed his wife and son 7 years ago. The body count begins.
Liz just wants to host the perfect dinner party but an unexpected guest sends the evening into chaos, with potentially apocalyptic consequences.

A hapless producer gets a lucky break with a film in Mexico. Things take an unexpected turn when he finds himself having to spend the $1-Mil budget in cash, drawing unwanted attention and sucking him into a life of danger and mystery.
Güven, who has just been released from prison, commits a robbery in a jewelry store. Escaping from the cops, Güven randomly enters the house of a newly divorced couple and the comedy begins.
A family leaves L.A. for a camping trip - just before a nuclear bomb destroys the city. As the city descends into chaos, the father must fight to keep his family alive.
When a haunted 90's video game resurfaces in the present, Scott and his friends must figure out how to stop the game from a vicious real life killing spree without they themselves facing Game Over .
A Japanese girl studies abroad at a theatre school in Paris, where she gains new values and energy for her future through meeting people from different backgrounds.

Every village, every person, has a secret...none more so than the inhabitants of this isolated, murky village whose fate relies on the luring of two unsuspecting pawns to satisfy their appetite and determine their being.
Dobermann is the world's most ruthless bank robber and with his gang rob bank after bank, now in Paris. What can the police do but to let the mad, morally bankrupt police commissioner loose on him?

Galwakdi is a Punjabi Movie that is full of Comedy and Romance with Drama and Emotionalness in time of a new start of The New Year Weekend for 2022, Starring: Wamiqa Gabbi, Tarsem Jassar, and B.N. Sharma.
Story of a Tibetan refugee youth in India who is a die hard fan of the Hollywood actor Richard Gere.
A crime fighter known as The Spider battles a villain called The Octopus, who is out to sabotage America and install his own government.

Chanti, a soldier, decides to take care of his blind sister and the family property after his father's death. However, he soon comes into conflict with a corrupt MLA who wants to buy his land on where he built his father's memorial.
In a sunken castle underneath the earth, five strangers wake. They have no food. No memory. No water. And no way out. They must organize and band together for the sinister adventure that awaits.
A grieving couple move to a remote Irish village in the wake of their baby daughter's death. They soon take in an orphaned autistic girl, only to become involved in a series of strange occurrences.
Plot details are being kept under wraps. The film is considered to center on a dark 'Justice League' team that consists of John Constantine, Swamp Thing, Deadman, Zatanna and Etrigan the Demon.
A young man finds himself attracted to a cold and unfeeling waitress who may ultimately destroy them both.

An ordinary factory worker buys a camera on the occasion of the birth of his child. The authorities order him to make documentaries about the factory's success. But his endeavor to be truthful leads him to opposition against censorship.
The story of a Jewish espionage network which assisted the United Kingdom in its fight against the Ottoman Empire in Palestine.
Bitten by a rabid bat, a late-night radio host terrorizes her co-workers as she slowly transforms into a vampire.
A musician finds himself on the run from a group of thugs with his friend and his estranged parents.
After reconnecting with his unstable high-school ex, a failed comedian becomes complicit in an absurd revenge crusade that puts him in the crosshairs of a rural cult.

The pressures of fame have superstar singer Noni on the edge, until she meets Kaz, a young cop who works to help her find the courage to develop her own voice and break free to become the artist she was meant to be.
A young Mexican student arrives in Los Angeles with aspirations of success. His travels takes him to East LA. With one brilliant idea he changes the fate of everyone around him.
Preetham, a chef and a compulsive liar goes on a secretive, fun trip to Goa after getting engaged to his rich employer's only daughter.
A woman first insults a blind singer, then gets him cured, falls in love with him but ends up rejecting him.

Just weeks after the end of the coronavirus shutdown, mutated sea lions try to take back the earth. Initially dismissed as rogue mountain lion attacks by authorities, it's up to a rag tag team of locals to stop them.

A painter struggling for inspiration finds an unexpected muse after he accepts a teaching position in a small town and becomes the caregiver to Eddie, a seemingly docile art student with a rare sleepwalking condition.
Apollo Thorne, a supernatural vampire slayer, ends retirement to save his eighteen year old daughter and a small Iowan town from an army of ravenous vampires bent on world destruction.
The story of a guesthouse and it's four inhabitants that explores their lives past and present and beautiful Jeju Island.
A man's kidnapped paramedic Nick's wife, forcing him on phone to play a "game of death" with 12 rounds, directing Nick to different locations.

A second peak of the virus has occurred. Expect the virus hasn't just returned it has mutated into COVID-20. Transforming Those infected into violent rage fuelled monsters known as Cronos, that continue to mutate.

A group of college students ride share to a music festival and have a campfire story competition on the way. As the stories progress, the tensions rise as they realize they are in a story of their own.
Based on the quantum physics theory of light bending space & time, Bend is an epic adventure set in the present day about the retraction of the universe and the race to save humanity.

Lured by Sandra's distressed 911 calls, Special Agent Connor investigates her house. As he seeks to find Sandra, Connor discovers the home has been turned into a facility in which human atrocities are conducted in the name of research.
The good people of a small community in the countryside near Copenhagen enjoy life and find their way to love.
Stuntman Bhaskar, a stuntman, is smitten with Cynthia, a college student. However, his heart is broken when he learns that she doesn't love him back and he tries persuading her.

Nermin is a factory owner's daughter whose car broke and Orhan, a poor factory worker who also writes music, fixed it.They fall in love with each other but her family does not allow this relationship.
Two dog lovers meet at a singles bar, recognizing each other from the dog park. Andy and Lorna are recent singles after their exes met.
A group of friends break into an abandoned factory in order to throw a impromptu party; unaware that it is not as empty as they originally believed.

The son of a rich lady loves to race cars. When he is blinded in an accident, he does not handle it well. He refuses to leave his room and throws temper tantrums. In addition, his beautiful but spoiled girlfriend breaks up with him.

A man saves a woman from the deadly threat of a runaway kokorec cart and then realizes she lost her memory. He lets her stay at his house and hires her at his restaurant, only to find out that she still remembers how to cook food.
A heartbroken bridesmaid gets a second chance at love as she organizes her friend's wedding. Unless his cruel ex-fiancée messes things up.

An Orphan with no desire in life rises against abuse and oppression, his life takes a new path to underworld. When internal conspiracy and notorious mafia becomes threat to his life he must face them to overcome all the consequences.
Updated version of "Tin Pan Alley" concerns two songwriters and their romantic entanglements with the pretty pair of sisters helping them plug their songs.
A young married couple reeling from an abrupt loss must fight for their survival and connection to each other in a post-apocalyptic ravaged city.
An ordinary office worker, Hiroyuki Sano, suddenly begins to exhibit extraordinary powers. Then a man who claims to have same powers as him appears before him...
A traveling mariachi is mistaken for a murderous criminal and must hide from a gang bent on killing him.
A ragtag spaceship crew sent on a rescue mission encounter a formidable enemy, their worst fears projected by their own imaginations.
When Fung's cop boyfriend Tats (Wilson Lam) puts her supposedly reformed triad father (Foo Wang-tat) behind bars, her daughter Fung (Joey Wong) aims to rid the organization of it's dirty ties,

A controversial true crime writer finds a box of super 8 home movies in his new home, revealing that the murder case he is currently researching could be the work of an unknown serial killer whose legacy dates back to the 1960s.
A documentary about the often funny, sometimes sad, but always outrageous lives of the residents of a southern trailer park.

The young policeman Karl-Heinz Krause works undercover to insinuate himself into a group of Autobahn racers. While he gets to like the illegal races, besides he has to chase some people dealing stolen cars.
The renowned gunslinger fends off racism in 1914 America. He's up in years but still as deadly as ever.

Unstable thirty-something introvert, who works as a photographer's assistant, becomes obsessed with his underage female neighbor, who, to his horror, reciprocates his feelings due to possible Electra complex.
A young couple in love want to get married but their plans are thwarted by the revelation that the young man's businessman father had framed the young woman's father for a crime he did not commit.
A tomboy and college jock have been best buds since daycare. Their friendship gets tested with a series of events and proves that even the strongest relationships break.
A sacrifice is about to take place when Nahara appears out of nowhere. She replaces the ordained victim. A stake is plunged into her chest but she doesn't die.
A recent college graduate and her estranged high school friends return to Lantern's Lane, the location of an evil urban legend and must fight to survive the night.

Kindergarten teacher accidentally kills mean parents; cop investigates and falls for the teacher. This film speaks on behalf of battered children like nothing has ever before: Child abuse in all forms is unacceptable.

The Through Another's Series is a Collection of thrilling stories that expand the 7 deadly Sins of the flesh. Each features a complex psychological element to get people to think about the consequences of their actions or lack thereof.

The landlord of a boarding house in 1923 Tokyo, is keen on spying on the bizarre close encounters taking place beneath his roof. One day he sees a prostitute killing a customer, and decides he's found his soulmate.
A widowed matriarch reminisces about her family fortunes, including her romance with a financier/mine owner.
This is a follow-up to the comedy Beetlejuice (1988), about a ghost who's recruited to help haunt a house.

movie_name: The Adventures of the Adventures 2: Denver Rocks
description: The Adventure Family finds themselves on a quest for lost documents that takes them to the city of Denver. But they quickly find themselves on a perilous new treasure hunt in the mountains of Colorado, from which they may never return.

After being cursed into the Labyrinth with the Demigod Minotaur, Ariad sets out to remove the curse and claim title to the throne of Knossis, but finds her younger sister Raven and her mother, Queen Pasiphae, battling for the same throne.
A female radio announcer gets terrorized by a caller named The Hungry Wolf, who claims him self as putting bombs in several locations. And the bombs really do explode.
Follow the story of a young man coming back to Silent Hill, where he has known a great love. Inspired by the second game of the classic survival/horror franchise of Konami.
In the late 1960s there were no CCTV or crime scene DNA testing, but disposing of a dead body was still bloody murder.
A debt-ridden night club owner has to take on Italian and Asian mobsters, corrupt police, and an angry pimp that he threw out of the club to try to keep his club in business.
AN ALTER BOY BECOMES AN OVERNIGHT HERO AFTER HE OVERWHELMS A GANG OF BANDITS WITH THE HELP OF AN AMULET THAT HIS LATE FATHER, A BANDIT HIMSELF, GAVE HIM.
Ashley Feener has the chance to start over when he enters Witness Security Program - but his past won't let go so easily.
CLOVER-LEAF LOVE CHAIN INVOLVES TWO ANTAGONISTIC SISTERS, THE MAN WHO LOVES ONE AND IGNORES THE IGNORES THE OTHER, AND A SECOND MAN WHO LOVES THE IGNORED BUT IS LOVED BY THE OTHER SISTER.

A loan recovery agent assists a young woman run away from home, without realizing that she is the sister of a police commissioner, who thinks that they are eloping together. What will the future hold in store for them?
An FBI agent trying to escort a criminal suspect is ambushed and the pair are forced to go on the run together.

Sarah is a young woman whose life is in a bit of a mess. The last thing she needs is someone else to look after. Yet, like it or not, her Grandmother has bequeathed her a very spoiled pug - Patrick. Surely she must have had her reasons?.
A young black lesbian filmmaker probes into the life of The Watermelon Woman, a 1930s black actress who played 'mammy' archetypes.
When an expired Flu shot turns the High School Faculty into Zombies, the Students must come together to make through the day.
A heartwarming family film about an engaged couple that adopts two puppies. When the couple splits up, the puppies hatch a plan to bring the two back together.
A group of friends whose parents are international diplomats find themselves in over their heads when their reckless behavior pushes their diplomatic immunity to the limit.

Lana's daughter Emma returns from London and announces that she's getting married next month. Things become more complicated when Lana learns that the man who stole Emma's heart is the son of the man who broke hers years ago.
Set in a doomed city cut off from the outside world we follow 3 groups of survivors inside the zombie infested city.

Gonzo journalist Jack gets involved with a new gang. Kat, his new female partner who is a fan of raw violence, gets dangerously close to Jack and he has to make a decision that might change his life for ever.

movie_name: Shen long xiao hu chuang jiang hu
description: A young Chinese man is walking along a deserted stretch of road when suddenly three hoodlums appear and tell him it is the day of his death.
A car salesman decides to escape from his mundane life so he steals a convertible from his boss and sets off on the highways of Korea in search of adventure.

The Rescue is the amazing true story of the young Filipino Scout Ranger's rescue of American missionary Gracia Burnham from the hands of the global terrorist organization Abu Sayyaf Group linked with Osama Bin Ladin.
Contemporary Los Angeles. Two jaded and unromantic Russian-Americans - an unlikely match - find love together in the City of Angels.
A young man and his traveling buddy embark on a global journey onboard their ship, only to be shipwrecked on a desolate island teeming with prehistoric creatures and gold-hunting bandits.
College student Sonja summons the demonic sorcerer Var after viewing a 500-year-old film containing his spirit.
George Lam is a famous conductor, Maggie Cheung an auto-mechanic; he rides a portable bicycle, she a motorcycle.

Aimlessly cruising through his first post-Stanford University summer, 22 year old David Braddock finds himself in China where he meets Mei, an ambitious young girl who urges him to find his life's direction.

Veera, a male chauvinist, is seeking a bride with his own preconceived set of conditions. However, he unexpectedly ends up marrying Keerthi who is the polar opposite to his expectations. What will happen when the truth is revealed?
Plot unknown. A feature film adaptation of the board game where monsters battle against other monsters.

Matt with friends is throwing a party when a Witch takes his sister. With the help of his friends, his brother and a stranger. Matt abandons the party to rescue his sister from the Witch. Will his feeble attempt succeed or fail?
A burgomeister and family man is haunted by a crime he committed 15 years before: robbing a wealthy Jewish Polish seed merchant to pay off his mortgage debt.
A young boy and a group of misfit friends embark on a quest to find a dark magic item of ultimate power before a diabolical tyrant can.

Adrian McCoy - a washed up TV Investigator, decides to retire after one last job. He takes a three man crew, a camera and a script. Once they arrive at the location they find far more than what they initially bargained for.
A story of the betrayal in one generation affecting the lives of the next, peppered with romance, music and the most beautiful scenery the big screen has to offer. A must see - subtitled too.
A low-rent bounty hunter named Rod Rosse, The One Man Posse, gets entangled in a web of danger when he takes on a job from an ex-biker/ex-wrestler turned U.S. senator named "Deathface."
Gerardo was never detached from his mother. So when he presented his first girlfriend, the gorgeous model Ana Verónica, the mother will do everything possible to get rid of her.
Angel is released from prison and is reunited with his friend Rich who helps him smuggle weapons in a gun-running ring. But Detroit police and the FBI have declared war on arms smuggling.

Creatures, who claim to be from another planet, interact with world leaders. But their plot is exposed and their true nature is revealed by a nine-year-old girl. Now they seek to endanger her and all those around her.
Running away from the troubled atmosphere of their respective homes, Daisy and Adam stumble upon each other, but it's not love at first sight.
The plot concerns a passenger train which is stalled when a typhoon wrecks the tracks. The commuters are offloaded onto a shuttle bus, which is then taken over by a pair of sadistic gangsters.
Karthik is a photographer by profession together with his another two friends Arun and Viki. One fine day, he came across Oviya who is after her break-up. Karthik falling in love with her.
A hilarious action adventure about an unstoppable trio of undercover cops known as the "Cypress Tigers".
A young woman revisits her childhood home, a place with a long history of violent and unnatural deaths.

In a desperate attempt to rekindle their marriage, Abby and Sam escape to a quaint bed and breakfast in the middle of nowhere - only to find their marriage isn't the only thing they will be fighting to keep alive.
The zombie ghost of a sunken excursion boat captain haunts an Austrian lake in search of vengeance against those who caused the accident.

Ostracized at a snooty private school because of her rural, poor background, a scholarship student is tormented to the point where her only remaining recourse is revenge, using the only method she knows: her psychic control over snakes!

In a summer in Shonan village, Sumiko is the daughter of an important upper-class Shikishima family, she loves to paint pictures, is going through a cooling-off of an arranged marriage that did not work out.
Following a tragic car accident in Greece, an American tourist finds himself at the center of a dangerous political conspiracy and on the run for his life.

movie_name: Goliath at the Conquest of Damascus
description: The legendary strong man, Goliath, goes through a series of harrowing adventures as he helps an exiled king regain his throne.
Kitaro, a ghost, spends his afterlife helping humans in need of his skills. He thwarts the plans of evil spirits who live to torment humanity.
Because of prison overcrowding, 12 inmates were sent to an island where they must fight and survive for freedom.
Professor Niels Klitgaard lecture in anatomy at the University. With external influences, the heart can beat the so-called Heart Bank faster, proclaiming the Professor.
An Orphaned Child with a price on her head seeks refuge in a Chapel run by a beautiful Nun, but all is not what it seems. High Octane action as they flee the clutches of a Rogue CIA Agent.

A young man, living with his big brothers money who is very rich, tries to deceive him about having a fiancé. For this, he deals with a poor girl with a poor family. But his brother will want to see even the wedding.

A nightclub dancer is given a dangerous assignment by her dying brother during the Sino-Japanese War. This mission forces her to set out from the safety of her home and cross the continent on her own.
A couple and their daughter move to Colombia to take over a family manufacturing plant, only to realize their new home is haunted.
A squad of soldiers on a tour of duty in Mexico search for a fabled city of gold that's protected by an alien race.

movie_name: Space Zombies: 13 Months of Brain-Spinning Mayhem!
description: Dr. Vic McNaughton is pushed to the brink of insanity by the warped misdeeds of feline-loving Space Zombies. Shot on digital video, this film pays homage to B-Movies of the 50s, 60s and 70s - in particular the films of Edward D. Wood Jr.
In 1876 Philadelphia, two sisters vie for the affections of a Frenchman who's come to town to prepare the French pavilion for the Centennial exposition.

On the day of his scheduled execution, a convicted serial killer gets a psychiatric evaluation during which he claims he is a demon, and further claims that before their time is over, the psychiatrist will commit three murders of his own.
Set in a parallel universe, Comet bounces back and forth over the course of an unlikely but perfectly paired couple's six-year relationship.
Liberation Earth is an 90 minute Sci-Fi action comedy in which our group of heroes, Led by an other worldly female must save a young boy genius with autism before rogue factions take over our planet.
Intrepid reporter Tintin and Captain Haddock set off on a treasure hunt for a sunken ship commanded by Haddock's ancestor.

movie_name: Sleepy Eyes of Death: In the Spider's Lair
description: Our anti-hero discovers locals who are oppressed, held captive against their will. For the swordsman to succeed, he first must wade through traps and assassins, and a few seductive maidens.

A poor farmer's daughter dreams of going to college to become a doctor. To make this possible, her father mortgages his farm to a rich landowner. She finishes college, becomes a doctor, and takes back her father's land.
A happy young couple are on their way home from a camping trip, when they run into a terrifying surprise.
A young man grapples with his mother over her engagement to an aging drunken misogynist while falling for his future step sister.
One of only two survivors from a Martian expedition is so traumatized she doesn't remember the circumstances of the trip.
Hopeless American expatriates inhabit a small Spanish village where residents are mysteriously dying after the arrival of a religious cult.
A mainland Chinese girl is, with her husband, a wanted criminal and they have to get to Hong Kong in order to stay alive and be free.

A famed tenor from the US, relaxing on a farm near Naples and singing in the fields, is mistaken by a lady journalist for an unknown talent she has discovered. He plays along and even falls in love with her.
In a distant time and place, power is decided by a cruel game in which two teams of gladiators fight in a vast arena.
Top model Farah Diba is shocked and depressed when her long-standing fiance is seduced by a jealous rival.

Julie is put under pressure by her boss when his paper loses in circulation to a rival. Given the responsibility of devising a series of 'scoops' to regain the paper's popularity, she invites her two friends Barbara and Carol to Hong Kong.
A group of teenagers suffer a terrible accident during a joy ride and get trapped at the bottom of a ravine.

movie_name: M I R R O R
description: A hit man is hired to take out a man who kidnapped his wife who is trapped inside our second dimension..the MIRROR Dimension.
Millions are murdered when a government project proves that their reincarnations are of more use the future world of science, technology, and peace than their present lives are.
When a law student accidentally kills the son of a mob boss in a fight, he finds himself relentlessly pursued by the mob and the police.

Imam (Adipati Dolken) met with Chen Jia Li (Eriska Rein), a Muslim woman from China and he fell in love with her. Imam wanted to express his love for Chen Jia Li, but she had already returned to China to get engaged.
A series of seemingly unconnected events across the world leads to Agent Vinod undertaking a globe-trotting mission to discover why his colleague was murdered.
Shang Li is suspected of murder, so he runs away. While the hunters search for him, they have plenty of time to think of the murder suspect and suspect its someone other than Shang Li

After losing his job Abin along with his wife Priya, who has suffered a miscarriage, decide to shift from Dubai to Priya's family estate in Kerala. However, peace eludes the couple as they run into a set of new troubles.

Irreversible Choices is a harrowing film that deals with a number of existential themes, including notions of home, family upheaval and personal destruction.Dante Kathlego (John K-ay) is ...                See full synopsis »
Anurag wonders about his first love Tanvi, whom he hasn't seen in years. Will their love be rekindled when they reconnect after a long time apart?
Bachelor takes a trip to the Cayman Islands and falls in love with an island girl, but has to choose whether her wants true love or his family business.

The French dispatch a professional assasin to kill one of the richest businessman in Poland who cheated them in business dealings. State apparatus is illegally used by the corrupt businessmen to defend himself.
Anna, a hard charging Indian-Australian businesswoman who has endured one too many humiliating heartbreaks, returns to her small surf town to ask for an arranged marriage.
Two couples are stranded on an abandoned road during a winter storm. A psychotic killer toys with them inside and outside the car.
Six former college friends, with two new friends, gather for a New Year's Eve weekend reunion at a large English countryside manor after ten years to reminisce about the good times now long gone.
The investigation of the robbery in the house of a young girl leads to many revelations about her personal life.
A photographer feels his commitment to his girlfriend beginning to fade when he becomes obsessed with an enigmatic client.
Vijay helps the poor and robs the rich, while Ajay is assigned the job to bring Vijay to justice. Thirsty for each other's blood, both men are unaware that they are brothers separated at a young age.
A trio of vacationing American students cross the border from Finland to the USSR during the Cold War and are soon imprisoned after a skirmish with Soviet soldiers.
Its Ranviir's journey to the discovery of his true calling and destiny which has been a secret till date.
A squad of six vigilante crime fighters must battle sadistic mobsters and an army of crooked cops to maintain control of the city they've fought for years to win.
A man is coerced by his uncle to get married and assigns this task to his secretary. However the man falls for the secretary herself, who has a dark past.

Joel Shore is made captain of the whaling schooner formerly headed by his courageous and admired brother, Mark, who was lost at sea. Accompanied by his bride, who suspects Joel to have a cowardly heart, they set sail for a whale hunt.
The monstrous offspring of a violent crime grows up in seclusion on a remote island, where a boat-full of hapless teens have shipwrecked, unaware of what's lurking in the woods.

Diddi Werner is an orphan and has been raised by her aunts Lotten and Amalia. Amalia wants her to study further after graduation while Lotten wants her to get married. Lotten predicts her future and see a dark, older man in the cards.
A young man, born of a rape committed by a legendary vampire against a living woman, vows to locate and vanquish his undead father.
A writer for a magazine tries to get the attention of a boy by altering the publication's astrological forecasts.

Mike is a young man who is a budding street racer, and owner of a Ford Falcon GT-HO Phase III. His best mate and mechanic, Tony, are both steel workers by day, but when they aren't working, they are racing.

A young man is found wandering around the woods outside a town, naked and covered in blood. He turns out to be the local marshal's brother. A series of unexpected events start to happen that that'll shock the whole place.

movie_name: 30 Nights of Paranormal Activity with the Devil Inside the Girl with the Dragon Tattoo
description: After a stint in a psychiatric hospital, a young woman returns to the house where her father killed the entire cast of The Artist during his exorcism.
The manager of Kay Kyser's band books them for a birthday party bash for an heiress at a spooky mansion, where sinister forces try to kill her.
The spirit of a recently deceased man hunts down nine people who attended his wake in the Philippines, but ignored some important superstitions.
Monsieur Cinema, a hundred years old, lives alone in a large villa. His memories fade away, so he engages a young woman to tell him stories about all the movies ever made.

Jin-hyeok opens a cake shop in an old antique shop, hiring Seon-woo, Korea's best pastry chef, who fell in love with him in high school. Also there, are Su-young, crushing on Seon-woo, ex-boxer Ki-beom, and Seon-woo's French ex-boyfriend.
A teenager discovers that the newcomer in his neighborhood is a vampire, so he turns to an actor in a television horror show for help dealing with the undead.

A rich man's son gets lost at a very young age. His father searches for him in vain and dies after few years. Years later, three men come to the palace, each claiming to be the lost son. Which--if any of the three--is the real lost son?
The girl and boy who have grown up together realise very late that their relationship is that of love. By the time they realise it, they are about to go separate ways.
An middle-aged office worker encounters aliens and is gifted with alien technology and limitless powers.

movie_name: The Dark Knight: Knightfall - Part Three
description: Crimson's grip tightens as his plans come to life, and the only ones who can stop him are Reclaimer and the Defenders.
In this slasher movie parody, students vacationing at a summer house are targeted by a mystery killer.
A introverted old man fulfills his lifelong quest to find the perfect wife, as determined by the shape of her toes.
When rebellious high school student Johnny Grissom is murdered, he returns from the grave as a revenge crazed supernatural creature.
An English nurse and an American soldier on the Italian front during World War I fall in love, but the horrors surrounding them test their romance to the limit.
Aliens attack in order to prevent a scientist from completing his work on the Thunder Dragon. Earth is defended by Princess Alang and the aliens of Castle Elma
An ex-policeman/school janitor (Billy Blanks) shows a new student (Kenn Scott) how to defend himself from a martial-arts bully.
Fearing for the safety of their children, two parents embark on a dangerous mission against the council of Ashton Falls.
When a team of volleyball players get lost in the woods, they encounter a killer clown and his psychotic exhibitionist mother. Will he kill them all or will they find a way to defeat him?
A recently paroled convict becomes the only person who can stop a psychopathic serial killer - who happens to be The Invisible Man.

The first ever warp speed space expedition ends abruptly as an unforeseen meteor shower damages the ship. The crew returns to a future earth collapsed into a dark age. The people of earth believe a crew member is the return of Christ.
Middle age woman gets her deaf handy man to tinker with a young women's car in an attempt to make her death appear an accident.
Albert Samson, a successful architect, and Alice are leading an unhappy married life because of Samson's ambitious and egoistic nature. Hilda Varghese enters Samson's life and changes it completely.
Three street toughs are hired to take down a Tokyo drug dealer in this hard-hitting Toei karate action film.
It's 1906. Under the dark sky of an Apocalypse, a young couple's nightly rituals are disrupted by a mysterious woman burying her husband by the stream.

Hans Wild Duck Gens, an old school industrial spy becomes suicidally jealous when the firm brings in a German performance artist who becomes not only the top agent, but also replaces him in his girlfriend Monika's affections.
Set against the backdrops of Madurai city,the story revolves around a girl ,who pursues a graduation course at a private college,where she undergoes sexual harassment.

A man hires a P.I. to find a hot woman he fell in love with. The woman lives with her underage teen sister who dreams about having sex for the first time, but wants a real man. That's when the P.I. shows up and stirs up the household.
A saga of women warriors each with a score to settle - nothing can appease them but the enemy's blood.

When a psychiatrist falls in love with a beautiful-yet-tragic patient that lives in a fantasy world to escape her trauma, he starts seeing the same visions as her, and begins to question her diagnosis - and his sanity.
A recounting of the story of infamous British-born terrorist Ahmed Omar Saeed Sheikh, who kidnapped and murdered Wall Street Journal reporter Daniel Pearl in 2002.
An American salvage crew discover a mysterious sunken U-boat off the coast of Germany, and the Seaport of Cuxhaven begins to experience horrific haunting.
When an Ivy League-educated C.I.A. Agent is killed during an operation, the secret agency recruits his twin brother (Chris Rock).

A freedom fighter, whose secret organization was brutally dismantled years ago, comes out of self-exile only to become entangled in an international frame-up involving the mafia and the political future of Greece.

On the day of his girlfriend's marriage, Gautam gets kidnapped by an unknown criminal. Bored on the way to the kidnapper's den, Gautam is forced to narrate his cute love story which is filled with loads of twists and turns.
A kidnapping gone wrong leads to mounting tension between Prabha, the kidnapper, and Kathir, the policeman assigned to the case.
A stirring tale of a plotter's efforts to force cattle ranchers to sell their holdings cheap, while keeping them ignorant of the fact that the land contains great oil wealth.
The shadow of war follows a troubled Iraq War vet as he is forced to pursue one of his own into the Pacific Northwest wilderness to finally confront a war crime that has haunted them both.
A young man's life is thrown into a loop when he is asked to be a pallbearer for the funeral of a classmate he doesn't remember, and his old high school crush temporarily returns to town.
Seven years after the slaughter of a group of misfits, the sole surviving killer teen finds her own life, and those of her family, now in peril.
A small group of teenagers are trapped in a deserted movie theater and stalked by a crazed B-movie actress out to kill for the demise of her career.
An insurance investigator examining several recent cases of suicide discovers a demon influencing the deaths, but only he can see it.
After a former special forces agent's son is kidnapped, he must wipe out three dangerous crime syndicates, if he wants to see his son alive again.
A writer who has to achieve success becomes suspicious of his beautiful young wife. He dreams about a bizarre musician and a suspect serial killer who's stalking women in the city.

Spoiled Yuen Si Si, the daughter of an affluent merchant, lives her life dreaming of meeting her idol, the heroic Qin Ge. When her father decides to marry her off, she runs away in search of Qin Ge, with her fiancee in pursuit.
Eva thinks her cousin Georgia's views on motherhood are regressive. Georgia thinks Eva's feminism is playing with fire. As they struggle to reconcile, an ancient Zagori specter stalks them.

A young American tourist and his fiancee spend the Easter holidays in a foreign ski resort and fall into the hands of fanatical, deranged villagers who have very special ideas about "celebrating" Good Friday.

A Japanese restaurant cook/owner dies after answering his daughter's cellphone. Other people are getting strange, same ringtone calls as well and dying painfully. It happened in Taiwan as well. Can the police stop it if it's a ghost?
The story of a young Marine, fresh from Camp Pendleton, who is forced to confront the complexities of adulthood and a volatile home life during a four-day Thanksgiving leave.
Kannan, a teenager, falls in love with his uncle's daughter, Radhika, but things turn upside down when her grandmother disapproves of their relationship.
A "found footage" film about five contestants plus film crew who enter an abandoned mental hospital for the night. German with English subtitles.

A pink-haired perverse girl-next-door named Penny falls in love with her stalker, a disturbed genius named Mira. Caught up in a devastating love affair and a world of drugs, their dreams and realties begin to blur.
When Gina's tampering with dark magic releases something evil, Father Donnely must re-examine his faith to determine if he has what it takes to Vanquish the dark entity once and for all.
A former war commander vows vengeance on the kingdom he once served when the nefarious prince begins trafficking children from his hometown fishing village.
Two killers turn the tables on a trio of robbers when they find themselves in a hostage situation. Surrounded by the police, the robbers must become the heroes before the killers execute everyone.

Ole's neighbor is dying while his gold-digging second wife has ruined him, leaving his daughter with nothing. Ole agrees to help save the farm but the wife's also taken the life-insurance so the horse-race must be won to save the farm.

A laid-back American truck driver in south Australia starts to suspect a man driving a green van of killing young women along his route, and proceeds to play a cat-and-mouse game in order to catch him red-handed.
Dianne a young woman who develops an obsession with magic spells with hopes of conquering love. All seems well, till one day it all goes wrong.

A young Japanese ballet dancer comes to Moscow to study at the Bolshoy Theater, works hard, gets a titular role in Gisele and falls in love with the local sculptor. Then she gets a news that will change evrything...
A man living in a futuristic sterile colony begins to question his circumscribed existence when his friend is chosen to go to the Island, the last uncontaminated place on earth.

Joel Armstrong is a successful celebrity pastor. One day he happens upon Ben, an estranged childhood friend, who has met with hard times. This encounter ignites a series of events that slowly unravel everything Joel holds dear.

A London Times reporter and his inseparable photographer and friend are investigating a number of mysterious cases only to find themselves involved in a bloody mission full of mysteries, plots, and paranormal phenomena.
Suspense, intrigue, hate, fear, and love who among these six people is the deadly gift love from Japan.
Ryoji, a wanderer, arrives in a remote mountain town, carrying a shotgun and claiming to be a hunter. He quickly becomes embroiled in a web of trouble surrounding the town's mill.
A CBI officer goes in search of a ruthless serial killer. Things get worse when the murderer targets the former and her family.
A police inspector (Amit Pachori) investigates murders in an old mansion which are the result of a monster (Randhir Singh) created by black magic.

movie_name: Eye of the Eagle 2: Inside the Enemy
description: When soldier Anthony Glenn discovers that Mai is missing, he sets out to rescue her from the corrupt Major Sorenson pitting soldier against soldier in a bloody game of honor.
Joshua must protect his twin-sister, Emma, who possesses supernatural abilities and keep her safe from an unstoppable secret agent hunting them for an experiment in a classified government program.
When a woman is killed by corrupt cops, she is reincarnated as an assassin charged with destroying those who killed her and her friends.
A story to tug at your heart strings--of young love, its pitfalls, and its final triumph. Lita's acting is a a revelation.
When a group of hard-working guys find out they've fallen victim to their wealthy employer's Ponzi scheme, they conspire to rob his high-rise residence.

In Brazil, Dr. Ann Philips tries to inoculate the superstitious natives against an epidemic. The murderous Jaguar Men oppose the intrusion. The natives take heart when the riverboat captain's helper Pepe volunteers for the first shot.
Balachandran follows in his father's footsteps and becomes a politician to help people. But when he is framed for a crime and sent to jail by some corrupt politicians, he decides to take revenge.
Arrogant teenagers, a party, and a Revenge driven janitor all come together for a night full of bloody carnage. The epic fail is ready for Redemption.
A young girl, who lives in a poor neighborhood with her little brother, falls in love with a rich young man.
A local legend turns into a horrifying reality for a group of young grad students seeking to debunk a Wisconsin haunted house.
After she learns that she's been entrusted to take care of her deceased cousin's children, an architect is torn between focusing on her career and honoring her cousin's wish.

When the fun of double dating begins to grow old, Richard and Bettina share a dirty little secret with their friends Diego and Emilia: They live a double life as swingers, and would love to share this practice with them.
Kievan Rus, late 10th century. After the death of his father, the young Viking prince Vladimir of Novgorod is forced into exile across the frozen sea.
Strangers on a bus find themselves fighting for their lives when one of them reads from a Gothic book and brings to life six dead serial killers who proceed to hunt them down one by one.
A job monger, Shiva ends up as a taxiwala only to realise that his ride is a beyond what anyone could have expected.

Ziba is getting ready for her daughter's wedding when she happens to be captured by a dreaded gang. She tries to break free from this bondage but she does not have much time, because her daughter is also going there unaware of everything.
Amar's family is destroyed at gunpoint by a gangster. Years later, Amar joins the police force with the sole intention of avenging the death of his family.

When his older boyfriend loses interest in him, a filmmaker relocates to Chicago and uses dating apps to cast new lovers in an amorphous project about romantic attraction, compatibility, and attachment that his mother hates.

movie_name: My Heart Dies with You: Hearts Through the Fire
description: In the 4th episode of the My Heart Dies With You saga, the newly knitted family returns home after barely surviving a freak hurricane. In the following days of rebuilding, the family is put through the fire which tests their will, their love, and their faith.

A special forces soldier who has given up country, religion, and even hope, must return to the field of battle to track down a reporter he left behind in the middle of an illegal private contracting operation that went dead wrong.

movie_name: The Secret of the Incas' Empire
description: Hidden somewhere deep inside a volcano in the mysterious South American mountains lies the legendary lost kingdom of the Incas. And buried in this kingdom is a fabulous treasure of inestimable value....
Charlie Gordon and Layla Simpson are American kids who were destined to be together. Their love for music brought them together and will keep them together - forever.

A young deceitful Chinese student is forced to bond with an elderly warm-hearted Australian retired boxing champion, who helps him become an honest man, thus wins the girl of his dream after defeating a local conman.
Emily has mysteriously returned home to her mother and stepfather, after being missing for over a year - and something came with her.
A group of professionals are lured into completing a complex, high tech escape room challenge. What starts as fun, quickly turns violent as they realize this is no game.
Flora, a hitchhiking librarian, creates plenty of chaos for Tim, a simple plumber, and his cow Hannah when he picks her up on his cross-country drive to his wedding.
A man's heavy drinking drives away his family and threatens to destroy his relationship with his little daughter.
On a fog swept chilly hill station, a terminally ill young man (Prakash) meets a boisterous girl (gitanjali). Love blossoms, but there's a shadow behind the light she radiates.

An unlucky inventor's attempt to demonstrate his break-proof glass at a convention goes humiliatingly wrong, but his luck may be about to change when he runs into pretty young woman on the train ride home.
Three flight attendants combine their work crossing the Atlantic with searching for rich, handsome men to marry.
In post World War ii, Max Fletcher's Superman in live action going up against Adolf Hitler and the Super-Race.

Dr. Rossiter, a plastic surgeon wanted by the police, flees to France and under an assumed name acquires, by murder, a run-down circus. His first recruit is a woman criminal. He transforms her face by surgery and trains her.

Trapped in a forgotten amusement park, a young woman (Kristy) finds herself terrorized by the living memories of the park. She must break free from the park's grasp before she becomes its next victim.

movie_name: War of Eden: Volume III - The Garden
description: The daughter of the creator of the new world must flee her city-nation illegally to survive, and discover the truth about the outside world and who is the real threat.
A group of impoverished girls compete for a chance to live amongst the wealthy, where a rebellion is brewing.
THIS SUSPENSE-THRILLER MOVE IS ABOUT A MAN WHO BECOMES PSYCHOLOGICALLY WARPED AFTER HE IS ABUSED AND BRUTALIZED,
An outwardly normal teenage girl faces overwhelming body transformations that put the very nature of her existence into question.
A group of people suffering from mental retardation, blindness and physical malformations work in a traveling circus.

movie_name: The Sun, the Moon, & the Hurricane
description: A story about Rain, a man in his thirties, in quest of happiness, love and the purpose of his life and all incident that occurred. About the people he met and places he went to that shaped his destiny.

More gore, nudity, carnage and mayhem than in any other trailer compilation ever made. The King of Shlock, Tony Newton, opens up his rusty film canisters to bring you an onslaught of the most shocking trailers from around the globe.
A fighter with a heart of gold finds himself drawn into an Internet-streaming underground martial arts tournament.

Two couples, a small crew sail the Caribbean. On a remote island, they are hit by a gang who take the boat to bring drugs to U.S. The daughter of the owner of the yacht must reject her privileged life and do what's necessary to survive.
Showdown in Arizona between the Bonnell brothers, U.S.Marshals, and Jessica Drummond, the iron-fist rancher who controls the territory.
A man fantasizes about his best friend's new girlfriend. He is willing to throw caution to the wind to fulfill his wildest dreams.

In search of a perfect soul mate, Renee Robinson clicks on an app and instead ends up time-traveling to 1966 London, where she finds that the perfectly-manicured life and partner she envisioned may not be what she needs after all.
A coming-of-age story of a teenage girl from a liberal upbringing who moves to a conservative baptist community in rural 1950s America.
In this tale of friendship, there is happiness, fun, pain and so many other things in equal proportion. It focuses on the importance of relationships and how people perceive it nowadays.

A lonely hotel by a lonely road. Sarah is lost, looking for somewhere to sleep. She's come to the wrong place. A lonely hotel by a lonely road. Sarah is lost, Jenny is looking for her. She's come to the right place. The Bridgeburn Hotel.
Wrongfully accused of a bank robbery, a writer seeks the help of his ex-wife, who is now married to the soon-to-be Attorney General of California.

Cam, a hearing impaired person moves to a new city to forget a rough past with a person who could hear and talk. On the first day to work Cam meets Bella at a tram station. Would the two get along given they both know AUSLAN sign language?

A Vietnam veteran with a psychic connection to sharks discovers their exploitation by the local aquarium and begins an underwater reign of terror to avenge them. The movie action scenes were shot using real sharks.
A tribute to the Serie B, in which there will be a killer on the loose, terrorizing the unwary (of any age).
"2 FRIENDS" movie is purely based on friendship. It's a story of sacrifice between two friends, with unexpected twists and unpredictable climax.
The wild adventure of notorious 16th-century pirate John Ward (based on the book Barbary Pirate by Greg Bak).
A recovering drug addict and former CIA agent reunites with an old flame to help save his brother from the criminal underground in Manila. Starring Larry Wilcox, Robin Eisenman and Sam Hennings.
The dead returned to life but the world didn't fall apart, it went back to normal...somewhat. It's one man's job to catch the undead and protect the living.
Honest cop Rudi is a new member of a police unit commanded by his brother-in-law Otto which deals with foreigners. Rudi falls in love with Alena, a young Czech living illegally in Austria.
Irène is a beautiful girl working in Paris, she soon meets a manager and hopes a love story with him. But he tells a lie, so she falls in love with a house painter.
Three rowdy young women shall marry by a certain date, or else they will not receive the wealth their late father left them in testament.

An American college student in 1930s Africa searches for a lost diamond mine near Mt. Kilimanjaro. He must battle Nazis who are using the mine to finance their war plans, Chinese gangsters and murderous local tribesmen.
A woman is raped in her apartment. José a neighboring journalist and his friend Sancho will try to help her by seeing that the police do not come to their aid and the authorities do not do their job.
A woman and her boyfriend struggle to maintain their relationship, and when a reindeer threatens the annual Christmas play, the couple must work together to save Christmas for the town.

movie_name: Mister Seeker: The Midnight Dawn Hotel
description: With one click on a virus encrypted message, a young man is fused in and unable to exit his VR game, plunged into a deadly match of Hide and Seek against a demonic virtual boogeyman. One Round, one life, no second chances.
Wei Sheng's gang are out for old Ho and his small band of swordsmen to gain control of the local salt mine.

A group of students descend into the undergrounds of St. Petersburg to find the legendary Atakan, the cursed stone. Exploring the dark corridors, they realize with horror that aren't alone in this place.

During his summer vacation in Mytilene, a young and lonely small-time clerk, Kostas, becomes bewitched by a femme fatale, Anna Parisi, a thirty-five-year-old German woman married to a wealthy local businessman.
A woman afflicted with paralysis all her life gains the use of her limbs little-by-little as a result of romance.

movie_name: One of Our Aircraft Is Missing
description: During a raid on Germany a British bomber crew is forced to bail out after their plane is damaged. They land in Holland and are aided by Dutch civilians.
A traveling art saleswoman tries to shake off a flaky motel manager who falls for her and won't leave her alone.
Ghost of a man's first love comes back to finish her unfinished business. That is to lose her virginity.

Two cops are fired after being setup by their corrupt boss, who gets appointed as judge, but secretly heads a satanic cult. After his wife is killed by the cult, one of the cops is determined to bring the cult down.
An orphan makes sacrifices for the family who took him in but subsequently faces humiliation and homelessness.

When a newly married woman accompanies her husband to Africa on a business trip, he is kidnapped. There is only one catch - the woman is a police officer who will stop at nothing to track down her husband and bring him back alive.
The lead singer in a school band decided to turn his team into a group of ballet dancers in honor of their fellow classmates who passed away in a tragic accident.

The son of a wealthy and powerful sultan is carrying on an affair with the wife of an infamous criminal. The father determines to end the affair, erase the shame of his son and bring the criminal to justice.

After his cousin is killed in cold blood, Thomas Porter is out for revenge. His desire for vengeance leads him on a quest to find the person responsible and bring him to justice, whatever the cost. As he embarks on his 'quest', he begins to delve deep into a world full of conspiracies, betrayal and deep mistrust.
Rexxx, Hollywood's top canine star, gets lost and is adopted into a shabby firehouse. He teams up with a young kid to get the station back on its feet.
An actor and a chef fathom a plot to fix a horse race and attempt at capitalizing it, while striving to tackle two of the hitmen responsible for the scheme.

On their anniversary, she wants romance, he wants weed. Set in Jamaica, they take a trip full of stalker skinny-cats, nip slips, trips, falls, bearded fireworms, boogers, poop, tinkle accidents and weed. Comedic hilarity ensues.
A screwball comedy about wedding preparations, set in a mountain hotel, told successively from the point of view of three different characters.
An American showgirl becomes entangled in political intrigue when the Prince Regent of a foreign country attempts to seduce her.
A scientist afflicted with the incurable illness epilepsy, meets a beautiful woman haunted by the voice of her dead husband.
A hired assassin targeting a powerful corporate executive runs up against an FBI agent after the same guy.

A young science whiz decides to mete out punishment to those that have wronged him. Can his loving but unstable grandma and a kind ice cream man stop his bloody experiments, or are the town's dark forces too much to overcome?

In an underground prison an inmate escapes during a riot. One year later, a group of friends set out to locate an old hermit shack. Their worst nightmares are revealed when they spawn an evil darkness within the escaped prisoner.
Ben is a young editor for a famous german music magazine in the mid 1990s. His life is falling apart after his girlfriend breaks up with him. From now on he decides to go solo...

movie_name: Kebe Tame Naha Kebe Mu Nahi
description: The good looking singer comes in the way of fiancée of a businessman. A story depicting love vs want.
A young mechanic falls in love with a rich girl. But their lives get shattered after a series of unexpected events. Whether they return back to their normal life ?
After getting fired from his job, fireworks expert, Terrance Nathan Thatcher returns to his childhood home. When people and memories from his past re-emerge, Terrance becomes dangerous and vengeful.
A Soldier returns home in search of peace only to enter a new war against a ruthless Crime Syndicate threatening his best friend.

After a run-in with the law, an angry maladjusted young man starts calling himself "Hate". One night he saves a girl from a lusty Assistant District Attorney. He falsely accuses them of robbery, so they go on the run and make things worse.
Abner is trapped in the rough life of Mexico City. His escape? Boxing. Dr. Frank Irwin and his son Jimmy, a pro boxer, come together to teach Abner that the heart fuels the punches we throw in life.
Snake-Crane Secret is a tale of deceit, lying and mistrust. A family tries to uphold their honor, while keeping their Sacred Kung-Fu book from getting into the wrong hands.
Jerry Cotton is the best agent of the FBI and suspected of murder. So he has to find the real killers of gangster boss Serrano.
When a Scottish servant girl falls in love with her master, it not only turns her world upside down, but potentially all of Stratton Castle.
Three young women are bound by fate and the split parts of an entity that lives within them, fighting to break out.

In order to prove himself to his girlfriend's father, a young man takes up boxing professionally. The father becomes his trainer and a sleazy promoter gets interested in him, but the road to the title won't be easy.
A chilling supernatural thriller about the nomadic spirit of a semi-conscious child -- the only one who can identify a brutal killer.

movie_name: The Huntress: Rune of the Dead
description: Two daughters miss their dad. He hasn't returned from a Viking raid 2 years ago. The older sister Runa does her dad's chores such as bow hunting. She's having bad dreams/visions. Are they omens?
In 2000, a small town hosts The British Hairdressing Championship, where a former 2-time winner, his son, his run-away wife and his runaway wife's lady lover reside (not all on speaking terms).
Tine wants to find her dream boyfriend, but can't find him that easily. Her male best friend enjoys his single life, until they feel attracted to each other.
Soldiers, chambermaids, poets, prostitutes, aristocrats-all are on equal footing in this multi-character merry-go-round of love and infidelity.

Investigating off the Mediterranean, the ultra-deep drilling vessel Yavuz discovers an unknown object 9 kilometers deep in the sea. As the research deepens, the crew will soon have to make radical decisions in the game of survival.
While the young couple dreams of marriage, their families oppose them to be together. Determined to marry the girl he loves no matter what, Erol plans to overcome the obstacles he encounters.
A deserted drifter settles down on the realization of his platonic calf love for a washed up singer.

A stage actress - who is hiding a deep trauma over the car accident that killed her mother - finds herself living a new nightmare when her fellow cast members are butchered by a glass-wielding killer.

When Royal Air Force pilot Lt. Kate Sinclair is shot down over Afghanistan, she finds refuge in an abandoned underground bunker where deadly man-made biological weapons - half human, half alien - are awakened.
The Infidelz MC's former President, Patch Kinkade, is dragged back into his prior life when the peace accord between the clubs is broken.
Julian travels doing auto-stop completely alone. On his way he meets a girl with a somewhat aggressive personality.

A samurai rescues a mischievous tanuki from hunters and sets it free. When the samurai's wastrel son hatches a plot to kill his father for his fortune, the magical tanuki is determined to protect its rescuer.
A mad scientist seeks to mingle human blood with that of an ape, and resorts to kidnapping women for his experiments.

This movie is both one of the best-loved action comedies ever, and Alexander Fu Sheng's comeback film after breaking both his legs. It left no doubt that he was truly back in action, taking on cops, monks, and bad guys galore!
The life of Kübra and Ahmet, who love each other and have a happy marriage, turn into a nightmare because of the events they cannot understand.
A teacher and student reunite after moving on from their respective school years, and start a relationship.

A troubled war vet comes home to Santa Barbara only to find a family and community who seem to shun him from reintegration. With few options, he finds he excels in his new life as a an upscale Beach Cougar Gigolo.
A humble cabinetmaker steals from the rich to give the poor in revenge for ruining their love with a rich young woman.

Twelve-year-old orphan Peter is spirited away to the magical world of Neverland, where he finds both fun and danger, and ultimately discovers his destiny: to become the hero who will be forever known as Peter Pan.

The film revolves around a central character, and explores the nuances of a first kiss and the conflicts in a marital relationship. These factors become the front runner with a comical chaos in the backdrop.

Five years after an unexplained malfunction causes the death of 15 tour-goers and staff on the opening night of a Halloween haunted house tour, a documentary crew travels back to the scene of the tragedy to find out what really happened.
Lorenza, an ambitious woman in her 30s, is successful in everything but love. Therefore she has the idea of renting herself a lover.
A hacker discovers a super-tech cover-up buried in an assassin's brain. Hunted, she threatens to destroy the world to save it. (Inspired by true events.)

Whilst searching for their missing king (Shiro), Kuro and Neko discover Red Clan member Anna Kushina and Shiro are being tracked by the mysterious Green Clan. The Silver and Red Clans team up to protect Shiro and Anna from this new threat.
Charles, a student, is looking for an old mistress of his father. His investigation leads him to discover a cabaret in Pigalle where Clementine lives, a teenager, singularly protected.
A mercernary sets out to assist a tribal chieftain to defeat the chieftain's brother who is now an opponent and an enemy.

When Samir discovered that his daughter, Sandra 6, is one of the three most wanted extraordinary children to be put to death by creatures from the fourteenth planet who want to destroy the planet earth by the 2015.
A self-made businessman rekindles a romance with a former flame while their two teenage children begin a romance of their own with drastic consequences for both couples.

Ralf has sound recording studio deep in countryside. He is working on his dream project to record Muse. He is living there with wife and daughter and gets involved with young musician. Classic love triangle gets destructive.
It is an action movie (lead actor: Wesley Candotti) that tells a story of the world during the apocalyptic process.
Chandu, a gangster, comes to the rescue of Puja, a distressed girl, and they eventually fall in love. However, things take an unexpected turn when Chandu's past comes back to haunt him.

A new super-agent of the renowned Acuario security agency is in charge of an operation to prevent theft. On that mission, full of action and danger, he meets two inexperienced characters who will be his future colleagues.
The horrors and truths of Death Valley are exposed through the diary of a young woman to tell us her secrets as well as the secrets of the desert.

A lonely princess and a poor cobbler fall in love while trying to retrieve three magical orbs that were stolen by a bumbling thief, all while outwitting a powerful sorcerer as adventure and comedic pop culture references abound.

movie_name: Korona Rossiyskoy Imperii, ili Snova Neulovimye
description: The last part of the trilogy, consists of two series. The civil war is over, but not all enemies have been defeated yet. Grown up and matured guys are fighting bandits of all stripes, bringing the bright future of socialism closer.

movie_name: Angelito San Miguel at Ang Mga Batang City Jail
description: Angelito leads a group of young ex-convicts who will risk going back to prison in order to fight a notorious syndicate.

movie_name: Ishq Junoon: The Heat Is On
description: Ishq Junoon is a 2016 Indian Hindi-language film written and directed by Sanjay Sharma and produced by Anuj Sharma and Vinay Gupta under their banners Shantketan Entertainments and Vinr Films respectively.

Rhoda Penmark seems like your average, sweet eight-year-old girl. When her rival at school dies in mysterious circumstances at the school picnic her mother starts to suspect that Rhoda was responsible.
A bright but socially awkward exchange student takes her craving for popularity to horrifying heights.
At a quarantined university, a disparate group of students must band together if they are going to survive during a deadly viral infection outbreak.
Six newly-married, diverse, honeymooning couples face marital bliss and discord, finding out more about themselves, their significant others and life in this happy-go-lucky, quirky drama.
Christine Levitt goes to extreme lengths to become famous, to the dismay of her friend...Billie Cooper.

Liang Danni is a rising star and is unexpectedly photoed with Li Feifan by a puppy. Liang has a relationship with a divorced rich real estate merchant Shi. Shi pays Li a lot to make him promise to act as Liang's boyfriend.

movie_name: No dejaré que no me quieras
description: Two men, each with serious problems with their partners, agree on a plan: one to avenge his lover and the other to retrieve some diamonds. However, the result is not as expected and many complications arise.
Max Walker, an officer for a security agency that regulates time travel, must fend for his life against a shady politician who's intent on changing the past to control the future.

When the girl bully at his new middle school makes him feel like an alien, 11-year-old Jake Galloway is forced to get a grip on the superpowers budding within him in time to stop her from taking over the world.
When 6 strangers are left in the woods to fend for their lives, there's one enemy they weren't expecting.
A private detective specializing in missing children is charged with the task of finding a special child whom dark forces want to eliminate.
During the Indo-Pakistani War of 1971, the Bhuj airbase is attacked and a race against time begins to rebuild the damaged airstrip.

Derek Russell has it all, including his perfect match, the charming and fun loving Toni Culmer. Their love is tested, when he is accused by his brother of shooting, and critically injuring her father.
An older generation of Germans ridicules the suggestions of a forward looking young lieutenant in 1909 that the country needs to build new and more efficient aircraft for eventual military use.
A young woman from a small Midwest town unleashes a relentless, unseen entity when she experiments with drugs.
As a gang of youths terrorizes a city, the weary chief of police finds himself caught between the citizens who cry for blood and a catholic priest who believes the boys will respond to kindness.

movie_name: Guns, Hookers & a Pound of Coke
description: When Steve & Johnny get a deal from "The Chinese" they can't refuse, hitting their payday takes more than just street smarts 'cause their boss Eric Roberts sends them to Hong Kong with Guns, Hookers & a Pound of Coke.

What began as a friendship turns into a fierce romance in this heart-wrenching drama. LUZ is a story of survival, not only for the lives of both men, but for their relationship as it transitions to the world outside their cell.
A homeless amnesiac strives to unlock the secret to his best friends murder but at the cost of unlocking his own checkered past.
Pappu, a teenager, is awaiting his Pre-Degree results to join an Engineering course. He gets attracted to his neighbor Rathi, who is a middle-aged woman, and falls hopelessly in love.
A pilot enters an aviation race in order to win enough money to pay for her brother's medical treatment, and encounters difficulty with a rival pilot.
A private investigator must seek the truth behind a missing girl and the link to an old "Jack in the Box" that might contain an evil that took the girl and now is out.
A MILITARY MAN, TEMPORARILY DISCHARGED FROM SERVICE, RETURNS IO HIS HOMETOWN AND INCURS THE IRE OF A RUTHLESS LANDOWNER WHO ORDERS HIS UNCLE AND BROTHERS KILLED.
An unearthly fog rolls into a small coastal town exactly 100 years after a ship mysteriously sank in its waters.
A serial killer finds an angelic escape from madness in the distorted love of an exotic dancer. Her only demand? Exterminate her brutal companion.

A man is continuously vilified by the other members of the small community in which he lives. One day he meets a strange "doctor" who offers him a great ability with the gun through mysterious magical arts.
As an investigation into a bazaar series of old murders ensues, the murders start happening again. The local legend is that a circus freak is responsible, but no one knows for certain.
Three friends take a road trip to the Mojave desert where their complicated relationships are pushed to their breaking point as the group encounters a reclusive, murderous cult.
A military sergeant from an elite paranormal unit of the US Government and his men must fight for the survival of mankind against an ambushing force of zombies, vampires, and supernatural creatures.
