A man believes he can travel to an alternate reality under the influence of alcohol, to see the love of his life, who was murdered in his reality two years before.
A lawyer has a wife and a mistress. He loves them both equally high and together, they're the perfect wife.
Mathilda follows in her surrogate father's footsteps and becomes an assassin for a major New York crime family.
HARASSED BY HIRED GOONS OF AMERICAN ENGINEERS LUMAWEN 'BONTOC' IS NOT EASILY COWED BUT PUTS UP A COURAGEOUS FRONT.
A couple is terrorized in their new house haunted by the vengeful ghost of the woman's former husband, who possesses their young son.
The universe is thrown into dimensional chaos as the dead come back to life. Now Goku and Vegeta must track down the cause of this uproar.
A disillusioned detective struggles to uncover the sinister secret behind a mysterious cult and embarks on a journey of apocalyptic revelation and personal salvation.
Satan enlists the help of a suicide victim in Hell to lure unsuspecting earthly victims to their eternal doom. Contains three somewhat unrelated Twilight Zone-esque stories.
An adaptation of Jon Hartmere, Jr. and Damon Intrabartolo's musical about the struggles of two gay high school students at a Catholic boarding school.

movie_name: Batman: The Long Halloween, Part Two
description: The killer known as Holiday continues to stalk the Falcone crime family while a new class of costumed criminal rises in Gotham City. Batman suspects that a former ally might be the serial killer.
A late-night radio talk show host decides he is tired of telling stories and interviewing people. He opens the phone lines up and hears the stories straight from the residents of Marshalltown.
Ryan makes a documentary on his friend, Brett, and his first time camping, until a mysterious figure in the woods starts hunting them.
Where a people's honor is at stake, there are no cowards, only heroes. Theirs is not to win or lose, theirs is freedom at any cost.
Dr. Orlof, a former prison doctor, abducts beautiful women from nightclubs and tries to use their skin to repair his daughter's fire-scarred face.
When Hana, a professional gamer who suffers from acute agoraphobia, receives new equipment that enhances her game, she begins to wonder if it is reading her mind - or controlling it.
A coven of witches captures a young man traveling through the woods. He gets involved in a power struggle between a beautiful witch and the evil queen who heads the coven.
With no law within 200 miles horse rancher Jeremy Rodak runs his spread with an iron hand and deals with rustlers even more ruthlessly.
A nun and a priest descend into hell. The nun carries a virus that threatens the white race. She and the priest must escape the dead clowns walking biker's club.

Chloe fakes her own death to steal evidence from a morgue. The Coroner uses the morgue as a front for a sick and twisted business. A scary game of cat and mouse ensues as Chloe learns more about the dead than she bargains for.
After a woman survives a bizarre attack at an abandoned well, her mental state deteriorates as she tries to prove to others what really happened.

At a Hong Kong shopping center, Buck Yuen's (Jackie Chan's) intuition warns him. He saves a robbery's loot and gets on television, ends up in Istanbul via South Korea, and accidentally becomes a spy. Fortunately, he knows Kung Fu.
A novelist and his sexy lover plot to kill the novelist's wife so he can inherit her fortune including her house that happens to be haunted.

A middle-aged rape victim is exacting revenge on her aggressors in a small town outside San Francisco. "Dirty" Harry Callahan, on suspension for angering his superiors (again), is assigned to the case.

Three friends return from abroad and every one of them comes upon at something from his past. Finally they go to their hometown to save the house of one of their childhood friends from being demolished.
A boy in a situation requiring a choice between equally undesirable alternatives sees an opportunity in a lonesome drifter who runs out of gas in his small town.

When Sarpatta Parambarai is challenged to a do-or-die match, will Kabilan, a young labourer, put on the gloves himself and lead his clan to victory, or be dissuaded by his disapproving mother and dangerous politics?

An idealistic jurist realizes, after his family is murdered in a massacre, that everything he used to stand for no longer means anything. As the only survivor, he decides to take justice into his own hands.
A love story of a Moslem freelance journalist and a Catholic college girl, in resistance by their different cultures and religion.

movie_name: S for Sex, S for Secrets
description: Hung and Bobo struggle with their sex life and things get complicated when a mysterious girl steps into their lives.
Three people attempt to stop a gigantic crocodile, who is terrorizing residents in Black Lake, Maine.
Five college students try to go camping at RokSaw trails as a last memory before they go their separate ways in life, but a cult group known as "The Lamb" shows up, and starts slaughtering everyone.

The movie is based on the subject of woman empowerment, it's based on real incidents about how girls get caught by cheaters, blackmailed and used, the movies shows how girls should handle such situation and protect themselves.

Ipang (Vino G. Bastian) and Nugi (Herjunot Ali) are two friends who don't like school. They love to play music and have a dream of becoming rock'n roll musicians. They often skip school to have fun in Sandra's store (Nadine Chandrawinata).
A Special Protection Group officer has to identify the threat to the prime minister, who he is protecting, and also the nation.
In this critically acclaimed comedy, an emotionally stunted New Yorker's miserable love life turns around when he meets a deadbeat vampire and becomes a blood-sucker himself.
Ricardo leads a monotonous relationship with Valentina. When he decides to cheat on her for the first time, troubles will rise.
Set in the Parisian publishing world, an editor and an author find themselves in over their heads, as they cope with a middle-age crisis, the changing industry and their wives.

Best friends Marie and Alexia decide to spend a quiet weekend at Alexia's parents' secluded farmhouse. But on the night of their arrival, the girls' idyllic getaway turns into an endless night of horror.

Director Hirohisa Sasaki is back with an offshoot of his series, teaming up with beloved actress Hasumi for another hit. Her erotic expression combined with her out-of-this-world body will make you lose your breath and go mad.
An undercover cop tries to foil the plans of an unrepentant criminal, who tries to supply an extremely dangerous chemical to terrorists for money.
A psychiatrist plots to murder his wife, but with a new twist: he will brainwash a patient he is treating into committing the crime.
A young Japanese woman who holds the key to stopping the evil spirit of Kayako, travels to the haunted Chicago apartment from the sequel, to stop the curse of Kayako once and for all.
In a war torn post-apocalyptic future, Karl the Butcher faces off against a new ultra-violent serial killer, dubbed Axe.
Three honest accountants steal 10 million during a bank audit. Realizing that honor among thieves is just a guideline, uncovering who wants them dead may not be enough to survive each other.
An old man gives shelter to a couple running away from the girl's father who is out for blood. However, the old man does not know that the girl is his sworn enemy's daughter.
A group of international college grads working in Mexico City find themselves in danger when they test the limits of their diplomatic immunity.

movie_name: A People's History of the Vampire Uprising
description: Vampires, who call themselves "The Gloaming," prepare for a massive uprising to take over the human race.

Local Kung Fu 2 is an action adaptation of William Shakespeare's Comedy of Errors with a twist One pair of twins - the pair who grew up in Guwahati - knows fighting, whereas the other pair - from Tezpur - don't.

To rid the range of a gang of outlaws that are rustling cattle and robbing the banks and stagecoaches, cowhand Bob Calem, working on the gang-leader's superstitions, dons a skeleton-costume to strike fear into the gang.

movie_name: Detective Bureau 2-3: Go to Hell Bastards!
description: Police detective Tajima, tasked with tracking down stolen firearms, turns an underworld grudge into a blood-bath. Suzuki transforms a colorful pot-boiler into an on-target send-up of cultural colonialism and post-war greed.
Jefri's wife, Dilaila, goes missing on their vacation and when she is found, he discovers the woman is not her even though she insists that she is.
Bunta Sugawara and his gangster mom robs a bagful of mafia money. They get in trouble when the mafia sends their finest hit men after them.
Four prisoners find an ancient diary in the wall of their cell which might be the key to getting out.
Story of disparate group of people from across the globe who must climb the iconic Chungking Mansions building amidst a zombie outbreak in Hong Kong.
Selma is a member of a thieving gang. The gang, who wants to rob the house of Orhan Inan, a wealthy businessman, prepares a plan for it. But Selma suffers from memory loss.
Telling the mission of five brothers trying to take revenge for the death of their father but faced with various obstacles that eventually unravel the mystery that exists in their own family.
A former gunslinger is forced to take up arms again when he and his cattle crew are threatened by a corrupt lawman.
Fitter Pet'ka has fallen in love with Lyudmilochka - daughter of booth's owner in fun fair. He does his best to compete with more "suitable match" - photographer.
A deadly outbreak turns the world's population into zombies. A group of strangers try to survive and figure out the cause of the outbreak.
Although married Chinese farmers Wang and O-Lan initially experience success, their lives are complicated by declining fortunes and lean times, as well as the arrival of the beautiful young Lotus.

It's a story about the person "Jeelu". In every re-birth, he is being killed by his enemy in his childhood. Let's see this time if Jeelu will survive and take revenge, for what, he is taking so many re-births.
Chicago homicide detectives Prudhome and Hollingsworth are assigned to investigate a murder. Both become entangled in the plot of a serial killer whose goal is to recreate the body of Christ.

Murali Krishnudu is a 1988 Indian Telugu film, Directed by Kodi Ramakrishna and Produced by S Gopal Reddy. The film Stars Nagarjuna, Rajani and G.Maruthi Rao in lead roles. The music of the film was composed by K V Mahadevan.
A yuppie couple lost in a thick, brush-filled marsh seek refuge at an isolated farmhouse only to discover they've jumped out of the frying pan into the fire.
A young woman in an abusive relationship finds her life change for the better when she tags along on her musician neighbor's tour of the northeast.
The death of a loved one leads a young woman on a quest for a deeper understanding of the supernatural.
An American veteran from the war in Afghanistan finds work as an ice road trucker and gets caught up in a diamond mine robbery.
Conceited actor Emery Slade, on a mission to recruit a Broadway star for Fox, picks unknown Julie Clarke instead.

When a local cop and an overzealous social-worker follow clues on missing persons cases around town, stomach-turning discoveries are unearthed on a pig farm, where the town butcher has been slaughtering more than livestock.

A woman named Keiko Ishida (Pamela Bowie), the librarian, who lives in a small apartment on the outskirts of Tokyo, gets a new neighbor, Kazuto Nishimura (Dion Wiyoko) who returns to Tokyo after 10 years living in America.

Leland is suicidal, so he hires a hitman called Avocado to kill him. Code word for the hit will be "tulips". However, that's when Leland meets his suicidal soulmate Rutanya and changes his mind. Now they must try to stop Avocado.

Ömer's father is an actor in Yesilçam. Ömer, on the other hand, draws attention because he resembles his father very much. One day, Ömer meets a little girl named Asu. Asu likens him to Captain Feza, a Yesilçam space hero.
It is the dawn of World War III. In the west mountains of America, a group of teenagers band together to defend their town, and their country, from invading Soviet forces.
A researcher investigating a notorious serial killer who was hanged 20 years earlier seemingly becomes possessed by the long dead strangler.

A broke woman is hired as a house-sitter for a mansion in the middle of huge gardens. This assignment looks like a dream job until mercenaries try to break in to get a mysterious object in the house, that turns out to be a real fortress.

A reclusive loner, Gwen has an obsession with stalking and studying strangers, always at a distance. When one of her subjects enters her life in an unexpected way it may change her life in ways she could never antipicpate.
An unemployed documentary filmmaker's behavior becomes increasingly erratic in the months after his wife becomes pregnant.
A white youth who is raised in the jungle by the animals is captured by a safari and brought back to civilization as an attraction in a circus.
Follows a high school teacher and his wife as the discovery of a Ouija board and a personal tragedy throw their lives into turmoil.
An upset musician comes to an unidentified place for isolation but his life changes as he meets a girl with extremely spontaneous yet thoughtful nature.

Nala Damayanthi is a 1957 Indian Telugu film, directed by Kemparaj and produced by Kemparaj. The film stars Taraka Rama Rao Nandamuri and Bhanumathi Ramakrishna in lead roles. The film has musical score by B. Gopalam.

movie_name: Ilsa, Harem Keeper of the Oil Sheiks
description: In the vast deserts of the Middle East, lascivious harem keeper Ilsa joins the sex-trafficking ring of a maniacal sheikh who imports helpless female slaves for his perverse amusement.
Hari "Shaam" and Raji "Sneha" are cousins. Hari gets a job in Chennai. He then comes to Chennai and instead of staying at Raji's house he rents an apartment with his colleague Vivek.
Chiranjeevi comes into the outer world leaving his kingdom to find a suitable bride and ends up becoming her bodyguard.

Two backstabbing deserters steal a Gatling Gun from their cavalry unit to attack an Apache tribe and steal their gold. They get help from a naive pacifist pastor. Meanwhile, both the cavalry and the Apache go after them - and the Gun.
Jason Mackenzie, a lightning powered vigilante, is called into action when an ancient Scottish creature, The Caillech, returns to our world and plans to destroy it in three days.

Six students are invited to play a game at night in a school. They have to perform tasks in order to receive cheats for their Final exam. The tasks are easy, but soon the stakes rise, the danger escalates and the game turns deadly.
Based on the 1980s TV action/drama, this update focuses on vice detectives Crockett and Tubbs as their respective personal and professional lives become dangerously intertwined.
Unable to sleep, a man, "Drake Sutter" wanders the filthy city streets all night into the depths of chaos.

It is always been said that "Addiction to Life is more stronger than an Addiction to Drugs". Zindagi Zindabaad takes us to the deep insights of five individual lives who are chained into ...                See full synopsis »
The story of Spanish fighter pilot Jose Bravo Fernandez, who left Spain after victory of Franco and participated in WW2 on the side of the USSR.

After a meteor shower strikes Los Angeles, toxic smoke is released across the city causing people to physically change and become violent. A small group of survivors plans to vacate the city by heading to the coast.

movie_name: I Don't Dream in Spanish Anymore
description: Strange visions send a mother-to-be on a mission to undo the curse that has plagued her family for generations.
A young woman with a miserable life receives a magical book that gives her the power to make every man she encounters fall for her.

A young American [Billy Banner] arrives at Valdonia to collect a debt which the kingdom owes his millionaire father. He impersonates a Valdonian prince for a day, and wins the love of Princess Iris, the queen of the kingdom.
There is always a lesson to be learned, but when a serial killer is involved, that lesson is only taught once.
Things take a dark turn as Mali plots to murder his girlfriend who breaks his heart with the help Aravind.
Modern-day Ifugaos live in Manila's slum area and get mistreated. One of them misrepresents the cultural community by engages in head-taking.
A mysterious driver in a muscle car with a demonic hood ornament hunts down a gang that has taken over a small town.
A group of teens face an ancient enemy of the past when they wake a powerful Mummy from its tomb in an attempt to steal his cursed amulet.

The movie stars Fattah Amin as Ariel, who is investigating the mystery behind a deserted theme park in Malaysia called Mimaland. The theme park operated from 1971 up to 1994, when it was left abandoned following a landslide.

While on a forest hiking trip, a widowed father and his two teenage children are stalked by a mysterious monster, trapping them up high on a small hunter's perch, and pushing them in a fight for survival and their broken family.
A Nordic revolutionary's plans to murder the president go awry when he falls in love with the man's daughter.
Peter's long lost love at the University turns out to be the native priestess who would save his life by the seventh hour.

A once-powerful yakuza clan disbands as a result of a police crackdown but one small group refuses to bow to police pressure, and launches a campaign to take over Tokyo's drug, prostitution, and gambling rackets.

A young couple moves into their dream house, which quickly becomes a living nightmare upon discovering a demonic secret awaiting them perennially in the cellar - with unholy pleasures, fear feasting and a brute for all who cross its' path.
Ravindranath Tagore, a physics professor, forms the ACF [Anti Corruption Force] along with his former students to take on corruption in society.
Action adventure in which the formula for a cancer-curing medicine is stolen, and a kung-fu fighting team must overcome rivals and doublecrosses in order to get it back
The film features the true-life story of the nemesis of another Tondo police character, Asiong Salonga.
Julie, a girl from the valley, meets Randy, a punk from the city. They are from different worlds and find love. Somehow they need to stay together in spite of her trendy, shallow friends.

movie_name: From Zero to I Love You
description: A gay man, whose fear of intimacy leads him to continually fall for married guys, and a closeted married man meet, forcing both men to confront what they really want in their romantic lives.
A historic Hollywood hotel houses a supernatural evil. It's been subdued for decades, but when renovations start, a series of murders take place.

A novelist succumbs to writer's block and decides to live life through the lens of her protagonist. While in character she meets Mr. Right and her writing begins to flow again as she's conflicted and consumed with guilt over her deceit.

In the wake of two back-to-back mass murders on Chico's frat row, loner Brent Chirino must infiltrate the ranks of a popular fraternity to investigate his twin brother's murder at the hands of the serial killer known as "Motherface."

College sweethearts Brad and Ashley venture into the heartland of Germany. Their romantic holiday takes a sinister turn when encountering a German SS Officer, thrusting them into a psychological vortex.
Solomon must overcome Elementals, Djinns, Sukkubuses, giant Worms, and his own ego to fulfill his new role as King and build Jerusalem's first Temple.
Four friends conspire to turn the tables on their women when they discover the ladies have been using Steve Harvey's relationship advice against them.
In the winding EME road of Quezon Province, three groups of strangers find themselves endlessly driving around in circles and soon realize that stranger forces are at work.

A young boy grows increasingly upset when he learns that he must care for his aging neighbor. In order to pass the time, this not-so-innocent senior citizen reads to him from the "Book Of The Damned."
A nightclub performer hires a naive chorus girl to become his new dance partner to make his former partner jealous and to prove he can make any partner a star.

Hendrix and Hawk, the two greatest bounty hunters in the world, must join forces to track down a federal witness. They must complete this task to save their families from a deadly criminal known as The Psycho and his legion of mercenaries.

When her colleague is accidentally shot into the year 8888 and sent to a prison on the Moon, scientist Chloe Trustcott must travel to the future and get arrested herself to plan a prison-break in order to save her.

movie_name: Jack & Jill: The Hills of Hell
description: After searching for her missing daughter, a lady and her search party discover the legend behind the murderous pair of Jack and Jill.
Five Kung-Fu masters who each possess the 5 elements of martial arts, must protect themselves from Khroki who has set out to conquer their gifts.
A reformed kingpin tries to prevent his estranged son from going down the same wrong path that he did.
During an international rally two contestants find a hidden painting in the door of their car. In order to not get removed from the track riders do not report to their team management.
Luke must Battle An Army of super soldiers Created by a Ruthless organization Who's bent on taking over Harlem

movie_name: The House Is Not For Sale
description: With one last chance at a promotion, a down-on-her-luck real estate agent returns to her rural hometown to sell the impossible - a haunted house where countless couples have been murdered.
A timeless teenage romance chronicling an impossible relationship that fights against the advance of a terminal disease.
In 1985, a group of dysfunctional kids face off with one of the most horrific monsters ever known to haunt the locals of a small town in Western Pennsylvania.
CASE 30 tells the story of a murder case which has been assigned to Crime Branch Officer Arjun bharadwaj. How Arjun investigates and unthreads the case is the rest of the story.
When John Connor, leader of the human resistance, sends Sgt. Kyle Reese back to 1984 to protect Sarah Connor and safeguard the future, an unexpected turn of events creates a fractured timeline.
Tired of being taken for granted by his wife and 3 daughters, Rodolfo Guerra wakes up one morning and decides not to go to work. Then the craziness begins.

movie_name: The Lost Diary of Don Juan
description: An alternate look at the life of Juan Tenorio, from his early days as an orphan in a nunnery, to his becoming storied lover Don Juan.
Chop-suey, a kitchen assistant who is a fan of Bruce Lee, finds himself embroiled in a battle against an extortion gang when his aunt is unable to pay the protection fees in time.

Astero, the beautiful step-daughter of a wealthy herder, falls in love with his handsome son, Thimios, whom his father wants to marry off to an affluent shepherdess. Now, she's on the brink of insanity. Can true love set her free?
A brother and sister are shipwrecked on a deserted island only to find that it's not as deserted as they thought.
Twin brothers running a haunted house and an aspiring actress are all affected by the disappearance of a young girl.
"Spring into Harvest Hills" is the second TV special produced for the Enchantimals cartoon series. The TV special ties into the Harvest Hills line.
A congressional candidate questions his sanity after seeing the love of his life, presumed dead, suddenly emerge.
A temperamental figure skater and an arrogant former hockey player attempt to win the Olympic Gold Medal as a figure skating pairs team.
The brainless teenagers form Brain Drain are back and this time they will be going to the Veterinary Faculty at Harvard University.
When an experiment for a new miracle drug goes terribly wrong, the scientists responsible must race to prevent an apocalyptic event from occurring.

A man awakens with fatal injuries and the total loss of his memory. Yet somehow, he begins to heal stronger than before. He must choose to use his new powers as either the man he was destined to be or the hero he can now become.
A narcissistic serial killer blogger must get rid of a stalker who terrorizes her before he gets her first. All of that while doing her main job of slaughtering people at summer camp.
When three stand-up comedians hit the road for a simple weekend showcase, their plans become derailed by a crooked club owner and her homicidal bouncer.

In the snow as bells toll, a hooded figure makes its way through the streets to a church.It is a small child ,and a woman opening up her window across onto the scene comes out to help and ...                See full synopsis »

Gangaram (I.S. Johar) lives in a small village in Punjab. The only quality he possesses is a good singing voice. He is in love with Jamuna and the whole village knows about their affair. ...                See full synopsis »
The festival of Dahi Handi isn't just about fun and games; its political complexity is explored in this movie.
Molly is struggling with being a new mom, but after meeting Beth, things temporarily improve only to turn as Beth's dark intentions are brought to light.
An American family is lured by their inheritance to an estate in Ireland that has been haunted by a Banshee spirit for centuries.

A group of international criminals lead by Dr. Igor steal a large emerald from a Colombian mine and plan to sell it on the black market. Santo works with the Colombian authorities in an attempt to recover the emerald and to stop Dr. Igor.

Fáni, aged 30 had gave up on falling in love long ago because of her troubled past. But one day, a black cat starts courting her, she falls under the spell of this macho cat and loses almost everything that was important to her.

Jamie Stratton's quirky new wife infiltrates MKU to plant Jamie, his twin brother and herself into the MKU assassin data base to take back her beloved oceans and the U.S. gold reserves from wanna be sea lords.
A young policewoman went undercover to get a gangster's son to plant a microphone at a table where the gangsters make their deals. Complications arise when she finds herself falling for him.

Swimming team coach Xiao Wen and her family were living a carefree life, until one of her swimmers commits suicide. Now with secrets coming to light, and her autistic daughter playing with an invisible boy, her life takes a dark turn.
Workers employed at a French vineyard quietly follow old pagan rituals that call for the life of the marquis owner to save his crops during dry seasons.
Four college kids on a spring break road trip are forced by bad weather to spend the night in a small town inn but, what they don't know is, they will pay to stay in flesh!

Mark Sullivan travels the backroads of rural Texas in search of the dog he just purchased. When the breeders seem to raise more questions than answers, he must not only escape their farm with his dog...but his life.
Bruno Santini passionate ideals of Justice and Equality are put to test when he faces the tasks of adulthood, such as getting a job at an industry in Florence and facing working conditions.
After unwittingly selling a life insurance policy to a gangster who receives death threats, a naïve insurance salesman must keep him alive to avoid paying-up the benefits.
A retired hitman agrees to take care of a teen aged girl, but when she becomes involved with unsavory people, he has to rescue her.
A tricky woman criminal, in league with an international crook, falls in love with the honest detective tracking them.
Takakura is a young gang boss tricked by the villainous Toru Abe. His underlings, lead by Chiezo Kataoka, start planning for revenge after Takakura dies in jail.
The lives of four people unexpectedly change, forcing them to confront the new reality and struggle to find happiness.
A guy whose life is in turmoil falls for an attractive real estate broker who moves into the condo next door, but doesn't realize that she expects him to move out for her planned renovation.
A small rural town is shocked when a local Anabaptist preacher claiming to have exorcised demons from a young child becomes possessed himself.
A young man becomes plagued by demonic visions and voices. Is he loosing his mind or desperately trying to hide from the deadly game of life and death he is playing.
In a world where zombies outnumber humans 10,000 to one, it is impossible to tell the difference between men and the monsters.
General Ion Mihai Pacepa, the highest ranking Soviet-Bloc defector of all time, defects to the U.S., bringing with him secrets that will expose the dark science of Disinformation.
A stirring and heroic action adventure of Chi You, once the ancestor of all Chinese, who must fight betrayal and for his love to survive.

A young officer, Ivan Demarin, is sent to the depths of Siberia. Here Ivan meets his first love and, together with his regiment, finds himself drawn into a conspiracy by local princes, who are hunting for Yarkand's gold.
After she loses her mobile phone, a lawyer receives a call from the person who found it. They talk and hit it off very quickly. But she's in shock when she sees that he's very short.

movie_name: Kawan Aku Mati dalam Rumah Sewa
description: One of their friends accidentally died in their house by mistake. What are they gonna do with their friend's corpse?
Maternal instincts mix with paranoia, when a pregnant woman returns to the isolated island of her birth, uncovering dark secrets that threaten her baby.
A chance meeting between two guys develops into a relationship, which the viewer gets to see from beginning to (maybe) end-via a series of fragmented scenes.
It follows Nora, a British journalist who is hired to write a piece for a Hollywood playboy attempting to reinvent his image.
About Reza who is not happy with his nagging wife, Bella. Asks his best friend, Adi to seduce her to make she leave him peacefully.
Inspired by the relationship between Stanly Ho and his fourth wife, Angela, it's a romantic comedy about a billonaire who falls in love with a feisty casino dealer. Rated PG
The film tells the story of Gaffar and his family, who discovered that the village they went to with his family was under the influence of demons.
A surreal comedy set in NYC. Michael has just moved to the city and has to traverse the world of love and work while juggling all the surreal encounters he makes along the way.
Five tales full of horror, comedy and most importantly, Creeping Death. You better pray for your soul.
A group of teenagers at a party find themselves being stalked by a maniacal killer in a Santa Claus costume.

Gothic lesbians prowl the corridors of a miserable little castle in Italy and fall prey to a deranged count with resplendent canine gnashers, a ghostly white complexion and the personality of Atilla the Hun.
Los Angeles is under attack by monsters. The mechs attempting to fight them off are better armed than their precursors, but so are the creatures.

movie_name: Alpha and Omega 4: The Legend of the Saw Toothed Cave
description: After exploring the haunted Saw Tooth Cave and finding a wolf who has been driven away from her pack, Runt musters all of courage to help her.
Multiple life stories of some people who do not know each other who meet on a local bus going from Almansurah to Cairo. All those stories are about love.
Daniel y Alejandra están cerca de sus cuarenta y ahora se embarcan en una aventura: probar suerte en el campo. Pero Alejandra sufre de una seria enfermedad que pondrá a prueba de fuego muchas cosas.
On an isolated island, a small group of people are terrorized by giant voracious shrews in the midst of a hurricane.

A young governess is hired to look after an orphaned girl, but the return of the girl's problematic brother uncovers secrets from their past. A modern take on Henry James' novella "The Turn of the Screw."

A small town in America is suddenly inflicted by a wave of irrational violence. Both scientists and local law enforcement try to determine the cause of the madness. It's the food that is driving everyone crazy.
In a post apocalyptic world, two survivors make an epic journey where staying alive is only the beginning.
The global intensive battle story about the Coronoavirus army against fragmented human beings on the earth in 2020 for revenge of 2003 defeat..
Submarine officers Dorgan and Mason battle on land for the affections of dance-hall girl Carmen. She marries Dorgan but makes a play for Mason when her husband is on duty.
Three young martial artists travel to the big city to retrieve a sacred statue that was stolen by gangsters.
Two vigilantes are hired by their quirky boss to take down a large underground sex trafficking ring.
True story of an attractive Sicilian mob-wife who participates in her husband's drug-dealing business and falls for her husband's lackey.
Set on the last day of camp, in the hot summer of 1981, a group of counselors try to complete their unfinished business before the day ends.

Solar debris crashes down to Earth, causing widespread destruction and unleashing solar radiation around the world. As genetic mutations rapidly spread, a group of friends must fight to stay alive and escape the chaos.

movie_name: O Thanasis, i Ioulietta kai ta loukanika
description: Mad in love with a kind woman, a tireless locksmith has to deal with her rough three brothers and her butcher father, who want to marry her off to a sausage retailer. Will he summon up the courage to save his charming damsel in distress?

A young college student is house sitting for her boss. Little does she know a serial killer has also taken up residence. One by one people disappear into the shadows as her father and boyfriend try to figure out what is going on.

Story centers on an everyday guy with the rarest of blood types who is suddenly and unexpectedly forced to deliver his very own, freshly stolen kidney to an infamous criminal whose life depends on it.
A man becomes a cop in order to take down the police superintendent who may have killed his father, and that of a vengeful Triad boss.

Completely innocent man, Michael Jordon, is drawn into a web of government secrets when a girl carrying a mysterious package gets into a taxi with him. When she's later murdered, Michael becomes the chief suspect and goes on the run.
A jealous mother kills her daughter-in-law with the maid's help. But the murdered woman's spirit takes the form of a cat to seek revenge.
It's the first night of their first tour for all female NYC punk band, The Nemesisters, and it might just be their last night on Earth.
Paul Hameister, an amateur mountain climber made a promise to his daughter that he would return. Step by step this is one man's journey to the summit of Everest. Can he keep his promise?
A scheming couple plot to conceal a hidden cache of stolen money from its rightful owner. The only problem is that the house in which they plan to hide it is haunted.
When a pair of gentrifying hipsters move their artisanal deli into West Philly, Kenni is the only local that suspects they're cannibalizing more than the culture.

Mr Toomey obsessively tears paper to control his childhood monsters, but when he wakes mid-flight to Boston to find most of the other passengers disappeared, he must confront the paper nightmare which threaten to rip everything apart.
An American general with highly confidential defence information has been kidnapped by terrorists and is being held in a cliff-top fortress in the Mediterranean.
When a group of former summer camp friends reunite in a rental cottage in upstate New York, the spirit of youth returns and love is in the air.
After the sudden death of her estranged brother, Lucia accidentally meets his fiancée and falls in love with her.
In the town of Split in the 1930s during Italian occupation, a boy torn between kids' games and sexual awakening finds more about the latter at the nearby whorehouse.
Determined to reform upon leaving prison, a former prostitute falls in love with a cotton-barge owner and must choose between him and her banker lover.
Detective Simmers is on the hunt for a monster stalking Golden Gate Park in San Francisco and calls upon for help from an old friend who gives him the number to Mr. B monster hunter.
When a missing person with a dark past accidentally kills an intruder, he learns to access brutal adrenaline instincts. But exploring this new skill makes him a target for an obsessed detective.
Chuck Scott gets a job as chauffeur to tough guy Eddie Roman; but Chuck's involvement with Eddie's fearful wife becomes a nightmare.

Rose Hindmarsh finds herself at the centre of a controversy when she meets author Sarah Maloney as she investigates the life of Mary Swann, an obscure poet who was brutally murdered in a small town in rural Ontario.
A Heartbroken Youngster believes Foreigners are casual about sex and decides to lose his Virginity to a French Girl settled in Pondicherry.
Holly and her son Aden try to escape hit men sent from the catholic church to kill the Anti Christ, in a action packed journey down the infamous Route 666.
A one-take feature film from the perspective of a blood thirsty creature who stalks a group of campers.
A man has had a werewolf curse cast upon him. If he doesn't get rid of it, he turns into a killer werewolf when the moon is full.

When mysterious teen Decebal strikes up a friendship with elderly, hospital caretaker Milos, it soon becomes apparent he is no ordinary young man and that they share a deadly secret connecting them to a string of local bloody murders.

A lonely husband whose wife has been away hires a lookalike impersonator to fill his place and fool his mother-in-law while he plays around with a pretty coquette. Confusion prevails when his wife returns that evening.
A young Frenchman arrives in Northern California looking to forget a lost love and ends up encountering various forms of feminine power.

A neurotic newlywed bride, Barbara, finds her husband in bed with his old flame. Barbara doesn't get mad, she gets even. Using funds supplied by her wealthy father, the scorned bride turns her husband's love nest into a dungeon of horror.
When a meek father takes drastic measures to provide for his family, he is accidentally transformed into a hideous mutant.
The evil Mr. Chu's control of a village is challenged by a Korean wanderer named Eagle and the three Kung Fu Kids.

In the aftermath of a colossal war, the Geo-political foundations of the world are crumbling. Tel Aviv is huge, bleak, crowded, over-industrialized, and foreboding. Ruins lie jumbled ...                See full synopsis »
Volcanic activity frees giant scorpions from the earth who wreak havoc in the rural countryside and eventually threaten Mexico City.
Swashbuckler about the adventures of pirate Jean Lafitte after he helped save New Orleans from a British invasion during the War of 1812.

The daughter of a businesswoman is kidnapped, but things take a dark turn. A couple's relationship on the rocks because of the woman's erratic behaviour. Two parallel stories that converge in the most unexpected way.
In this French espionage thriller, Eddie again plays the role that made him a star, Lemmy Caution. Lots of two fisted action. From 16mm.

movie_name: Ennodu Para I Love You Ennu
description: Chandu, Azaad and Sanoop are friends at school and are trying hard to get girlfriends. At one point, one of their pursuits turn a lot more than a 'quest for girlfriend.'
A story describing Turkish narcotic police team named "Pars" who are trailing the traffic through Afghanistan, Turkey, Europe and USA.
An anthology homage to 80s shot on VHS films, with stories about a killer wheelchair, murderous squirrels, and a high strung movie director.
An army lieutenant accused of robbery pursues the real thief on a frantic chase through Mexico aided by the thief's fiancee.
A nurse and her elementary school teacher husband go to a good hotel to spend their fifth anniversary but they suffer comic and serious interruptions to their plans.

A mistake of nature, his species was wiped out on earth. As the only survivor, he smuggles himself onto a colonial ship. The emergency program is launched. The last vampire's struggle for survival across the galaxy.
A reporter becomes involved in an investigation to expose a husband/wife team of international smugglers
Mount Vesuvius erupts when a family visits Pompeii. The daughter uses her skill and her father his ability, in order to escape the disaster.
A group of student activists travels to the Amazon to save the rain forest and soon discover that they are not alone, and that no good deed goes unpunished.
Follows a paramedic that is so burnt-out by the job that he is forcing himself to resign, however, he first must embark on one last 24-hour shift to train his replacement.
A teenage boy named Justin gets involved with a Baltimore Police Department sting operation on two of the most violent gangs in the city. Placing himself in the line of fire.
One dramatic evening mixes the fates of three young women who live in the same apartment building in a big city.

Two young couples are on holiday, supposedly safe in the confines of their top-spec 4x4. Targeted and pursued through the wilderness, there is no negotiation with their attackers. The message is clear: don't get out the car.

movie_name: Bee Bop highschool: Koko yotaro kyoso-kyoku
description: College student Mayumi takes a mutual interest in Hiroshi, but their happiness is cut short when two thugs expelled from school eye the new couple.

movie_name: Sonny Boy, Public Enemy Number 1 of Cebu City
description: Sonny Boy's (Romnick Sarmenta) life begins to be in shambles when his parents separate. Can he be put back on the right path in life?
When an alien war comes to earth in search of a lost key to peace, the lives of two young lovers are turned upside down by the Military in a hunt to get to it first.
John McClane and a Harlem store owner are targeted by German terrorist Simon in New York City, where he plans to rob the Federal Reserve Building.

Poul Borg neglects his young, beautiful wife Marianne. He even forget their wedding day, in favor of a new fast sports car, a beautiful silver-gray Jaguar. During his drive, he runs out of gas. A young lady Laura Lublinski helps him.
It centers on a group of female soldiers who disguise themselves as medics to rescue a group of teenagers caught between ISIS and the forces of the Taliban.
A white midwestern girl moves to Chicago, where her new boyfriend is a black teen from the South Side with a rough, semi-criminal past.
After receiving bad news, Marta decides to willingly lock herself down at home. This confinement will not be easy to deal with though, considering that strange things start happening.
A horror novelist plagued by memory loss returns to his childhood home only to discover that the scary stories he creates...are not stories after all.
When a 9-year-old girl is abducted in broad daylight, her family struggles to survive the aftermath.
Vancouver -one of the most ethnically diverse cities of the world witness a Cork and edgy romantic comedy when one character invades the love story of modern day Romeo-Juliet.
Adapted from the best-selling novel. Navy Captain Peter Mackenzie is sent on his toughest assignment when the Soviet nuclear submarine Kirov is stolen and the weapons are aimed at the United States.
When David drops out of medical school, he finds out what life isn't really like. He meets beautiful women, holds a box, helps make a movie, and takes care of 21 cows.
A brash but brilliant Indian intelligence agent leads a covert operation to nab the mastermind behind a series of attacks threatening national security.

At the turn of the century, Earth's monsters have been safely rounded up and studied on Monsterland. Chaos erupts when a race of she-aliens known as the Kilaaks unleashes the monsters across the world.

A £25,000 reward offered by a local newspaper brings documentary makers Matt and his girlfriend Georgia to the remote North Devon moor in a bid to capture the fabled Beast purported to be a wild cat, like a panther or a puma on film.
An home invasion robbery of a 6th generation descendant of a voodoo priest goes awry. The two thieves are then tagged with an unworldly curse that they must expel.
Produced for Fuji TV in 2000, the film reinterprets the story of a special samurai force - the Shinsengumi - at the end of the Edo period.
Different tribes across the country, gather to witness the wedding of Two lovers from different worlds, as both families oppose, tossing their children into uncertainty.

In 1880s Seattle, a toxic gas has turned many of its remaining residents into "Rotters," more commonly known as zombies and a young widow hunts for her teen son amongst airship pirates, a criminal overlord and heavily armed refugees.

A giant egg is unearthed at a construction site and soon opened, releasing the terrible Ivan Ooze, who wreaks vengeance on Zordon for imprisoning him millennia ago. With Zordon dying and their powers lost, the Rangers head to a distant planet to find the mystic warrior Dulcea.

After a terrible plane crash, a group of survivors led by the president's son must find a way to survive the horrific blizzard and an Alien species known as the predator who is stalking and hunting them down one by one.
12 Chefs using their different levels of culinary prowess compete against each other in cooking challenges for the heart of a woman.

The story of a Hollywood star who, tired of his lifestyle, one night encounters his doppelganger leading to a role switch so the star can slip away for some alone time leaving the double to indulge in his fantasies.
In 1970s Los Angeles, a mismatched pair of private eyes investigate a missing girl and the mysterious death of a porn star.
An orphan girl accused of theft is helped by the spirits of her deceased parents and a death shroud ghost.
Lucinda and Daniel start a slow romance just as the worst meteor showers in history rain down on Earth.
Two lovers, having been denied true love 300 years ago, are reincarnated in order to correct that wrong.
An aging hitman for the Italian mob harboring a life threatening secret, reluctantly opens himself up to love, and the consequences that follow.
A weekend of camping in the mountains becomes an excursion into hell for a young couple, who become pawns in a grotesque plot hatched by deranged locals.

Heiner and Florian have been friends for years, despite they couldn't be more different. In matters of love Heiner is a loyal husband; while Florian goes through women in large numbers. A boat trip on Mosel confuses them both.
A mute woman finds herself at the center of a series of murders in the mountains of Spain, which police suspect are being committed by a drug-addled Satanist.
This unique, daring, and strikingly original psychological thriller is a new vision akin to films such as A CLOCKWORK ORANGE and CLERKS.
In 1855, a daimyo sends his men on a grueling marathon to discover if they're tough enough to face the newly arrived Americans. Misunderstanding his intent, the Shogun dispatches assassins.

Graffiti artist Tren and his girlfriend Drama are a young couple who spend their lives in a nightclub where they dance-fight with other crews. The world around them is full of drugs and violence. What does destiny hold for them?

movie_name: In the Eye of the Beholder
description: A starving painter makes a deal with an angel to become the worlds greatest painter but he will come to regret that decision.
A troubled woman on the edge of divorce returns home to her younger sister after years apart. But when her sister and brother-in-law betray her trust, she embarks on a vicious crusade of revenge.
When Sean, an ex-convict is possessed by a Demonic entity, he embarks on a killing spree with a gas-mask and an ax for protection.
To better connect with other people, and her own emotions,an HR manager seeks the mentorship of a coveted escort, who soon opens her heart.

Ancient Pure Blood has some what of a twist behind this story line...It is about an ancient world of vampires where the world finds a change and a shift of non human entities and the human race must struggle to survive.
A rogue government operative reluctantly takes in young girl after her family is murdered and protects her against the very people that created him.
When four couples travel to a remote island for a swingers weekend Lucy's biggest fear was that it would ruin her marriage, she didn't realize that it could cost her her life too.
Tony is really handsome, but he smells. A scientist gives him a potion that should get rid of his fishy smell. Unfortunately, there are some serious side effects.

A young woman Leah (Bridie Latona) is rescued from the train tracks by a young man Sam (Luke Koster) who is dying of a brain tumor. Together they embark on an adventure ticking off his last wishes from his bucket list.
Scotland Yard investigates a series of murders where the victims have died by snake venom poisoning.
A young man falls for the commissioner's sister, Anjali, who betrays him. After finishing his time behind bars, he sets on a mission to save another girl named Anjali who is chased by a gangster.

A photojournalist traveling through the Pyrenees on assignment with a beautiful writer stays overnight at an ancient Spanish castle and hears that the adjoining mountain is occupied by a coven of witches.
Bernadette and Serge decide against all odds to organize their wedding reception while Belgium is in the midst of a zombie apocalypse.
An evil, sadistic count lives in a waterfront castle with his insane family members. One day the survivor of a shipwreck washes ashore near the castle and finds himself a captive there.

In order to resist temptation, Mariana and her girlfriends try their best to control everything and everyone around them. However, the day will come when the urge to scream will be stronger than it ever has been.
A rich Chinatown merchant is murdered by a street gang. The merchant's son and assistant bring him back to life as a vampire, and he and other vampires fight the street gang.
Anthony Alonzo is an idealistic army captain who believes in the government's reform programs for the people of Mindanao.
Beom-wi, a first-rate student of swordsmanship, realizes that he will never be the favored pupil of Master Tae-san until he removes or discredits fellow student Seo-ok.
Sakkarai, a mentally challenged orphan, works for the village chief Thevar. He falls in love with his master's daughter Thamarai. Will Thevar accept their relationship?
In a neon-lit city, a melancholic poet falls in love with a mystifying young woman one evening whilst wandering in search for inspiration.
Invited by a desperate woman the psychiatrist and ex military Nik Jason tries to help her demonic possessed sister and gets into a deadly hell trip of a parallel world.
Autobiographical comedy about a recovering sex addict, about his obsession with prostitutes, and how that affected his relationships and his life altogether.
This movie describes the violent break-up of former Yugoslavia from the Serbian point of view, using the story of ethnicly mixed couple in war-torn city of Vukovar as metaphore.
Three friends stumble upon the horrific origins of a mysterious figure they discover is the root cause of the evil behind unspeakable acts.
A Young man kidnaps a girl for the revenge of the murder of his sister but later falls in live with her. The father of that girl then hires three men to recover her.
Sheriff Dan Tashtego and a team of creeper hunters enlist the help of officer Davis Tubbs to help stop the monster's eating spree.
Inspired by the true events of Colombia's most prolific drug sniffing dog, Sombra, who had a hit put out on her for bringing down hundreds of drug smugglers.
In a world of gambling and syndicates, two people meet and fall in love. Together, they will bet everything they have and try to outsmart a group of people they consider as their worst nightmare.
Ashok is the guy people turn to for love advice. He helps Raja succeed in wooing the girl he loves, only to realise later that the she is none other than Uma, the girl he himself is in love with.
A couple travel to a remote cabin in Montana where an encounter with an overbearing neighbor leads to a terrifying ordeal.

After a four-week partner swap, two couples meet again in a remote beach house and discover that everything has changed. Suddenly, their feelings are put to the test and they start reevaluating their life choices and expectations.

While travelling on their first American tour, Ms. 45, an all-girl punk band, is drugged and kidnapped. They awaken to find their limbs removed and replaced with crude weaponry, and are forced to fight as Gladiators for a sadistic town.

In 1968 the world was shaken by an outbreak known today as the "Night of the Living Dead". On the anniversary of the event...a group of podcasters soon learn that children shouldn't play with dead things.
The drama of a young woman - the victim of high-society gossip. The plot is borrowed from the novel by Sergei Fonvizin 'Gossip'.
While experiencing financial difficulties two private investigators accept a surveillance job that leads to a heist and ring of murders.

January 1945, Lt Catchpole is about to be force marched cross Europe's landscape with thousands of P.O.Ws. To survive, he must battle starvation and his own conscience, promising his families friend parents to return their son home safe.

Since the age of 15, Tony, also known as Squeeze, has known nothing but a criminal life. With the body counts piling up around him, a thriving underground fight club, and the police on his tail, he now needs an exit plan.

A husband and wife, whose marriage is built on shifting sand, find themselves imprisoned by a sadistic killer - forced to make choices that will ultimately determine their family's survival or demise.

In a small southern swamp town, a local girl is found murdered. A young California man passing through town is blamed, and in fleeing the local lynch mob he escapes into the Okeefeenokee Swamp, where he runs into even more dangers.
An actress develops a deadly obsession with internet fame after her manager drops her for not having enough of a social media presence.
The newest romantic team with a veteran character actress in a picture that's packing plenty of excitement, suspense, romance, and thrills.
Han Kuo Tsai, who wants to learn Martial Arts to settle old scores, finds himself entangled with loan sharks and a master who is far more than he appears.

When a ronin requesting seppuku at a feudal lord's palace is told of the brutal suicide of another ronin who previously visited, he reveals how their pasts are intertwined - and in doing so challenges the clan's integrity.
Two special agents come to a contryside town, to investigate the mysterious deaths of several people.
After being violently separated from the woman he loves, a young man must disguise himself in order to keep meeting her.
In a New York public school district torn apart by racial divides, corrupt politicians, and escalating violence, a young Hasidic man falls in love with a Hispanic woman. Inspired by true events.
Stuck in a traffic jam after a one night stand a guy and girl recount the night before through flashbacks.

Students on summer break are exposed to a deadly virus that is spread rapidly through direct human contact. One by one, more and more fall victim to the plague triggering an epidemic that spawns a horde of ravenous zombies.
Sarah lives inside a multidimensional love, torn between a past fantasy and a present too much real.
Coming-of-age story about a suave 15-year-old prep school student who falls in love with his stepmother. When her best friend responds to his advances, he suddenly finds himself in way over his head.

movie_name: The Good the Bad the Weird
description: The story of two outlaws and a bounty hunter in 1940s Manchuria and their rivalry to possess a treasure map while being pursued by the Japanese army and Chinese bandits.

A young writer traumatized by the death of his wife and kid, describes his disturbing experiences to a psychiatrist. A mysterious man, hidden under an umbrella, forces him to finish his book regardless the cost of its consequences.

movie_name: Demonic Toys: Jack in the Box
description: A young orphaned girl without the ability of speech finds that she has been gifted with the notorious Jack in the Box from the Demonic Toys.
After being released from prison for a crime he didn't commit, an ex-soldier attempts to get back his stolen cryptocurrency - worth millions of dollars - and find the people that set him up.

A conscientious scientist develops the "deadliest explosive the world has ever known" but soon it falls into the hands of an evil criminal, Bruto. The five angels band together to stop Bruto's reign of terror.
Gangster story revolving around a boxing match and gambling debts, featuring a heist, pimped cars and scantily-clad women. A local production entirely in the dialect of the city of Trier.
Roja, a part-time singer, works at a finance company where her colleague, Murali, is madly in love with her. However, Roja rejects his proposal as she is the sole breadwinner of her large family.
Saving Kara from a brutal gang rape may have been the biggest mistake Ranger Hilts ever made when they find themselves on the run together in post apocalyptic world.
3 couples are off to a Who Done it Murder Mystery feast, did they get the wrongs directions or were they set up to be captured and prepped to become the freshest of ingredients?
Three friends join their musical talent to escape the harsh reality of their neighborhood. But their lack of money for recordings will force them to involve in shady business.
4 Stories, 4 Directors. 4 Great moving human drama of the Police Force's Achievement and almost incredible Heroism.
When Franny and her family move to a rural town, she starts a romantic relationship with a girl, but her new found freedom threatens to expose her family's dark secret.
An ancient Mayan blessing goes wrong and now Cozumel island in Mexico is under a curse and all the normally docile wildlife attacks its human inhabitants.

When a revenge stricken man dies, the only thing that'll give him peace is killing the women who wronged him when they find themselves alone, outside, in their underwear. Before he does that, he has to get training from the Devil himself.
Two young girls from Corfu, go to Athens to live with their rich uncle. He turns them into real city girls, in order to get them married.

A man beholden to an ancient vampire struggles with qualms of conscience and lack of free will as a dogged NYC Detective working the case in London closes in on what may be more than she bargained for.

Santiago lives in the present. Florencia only thinks about the future. They have been together for a while and their relationship is going through a great moment. But one Sunday morning, a disagreement occurs: present against future.
A triangle set in Morocco involving a nouveau riche businessman, his wife and her former lover.Meanwhile a French officer in Morocco accomplishes much for his country.
Heroic and love story of Mongolian warrior Gada who won the title of "Meilin" for his bravery and loyalty.
Peter and Margaret Eastwood believe they've purchased their dream home to start their lives together but this house seems to be hiding something dark and terrifying in every corner.
The story of actor Peter H. Kent, writer, producer, thrill seeker, longtime stunt and body double to Arnold Schwarzenegger, acting coach to youth and stunt instructor.
The film 'We decide what is real' Friends, associates and just close-minded people whom we have never seen, but correspond every day. Sometimes the best part of our life. Are they not real?

A female, Chinese biker enters an underground race on the streets of Macau to save her younger sister, joining forces with an ex-pat American and using six ancient secrets to defeat their mutual adversary.
When Annabel wakes up in a remote house, she notices that slowly reality starts to fall apart, uncovering a horrific murder.
A film version of the ballet Giselle. Filmed in a studio, using innovative editing and cinematography to go along with the choreography, this film stands out from filmed stage-performances.

After the Gonagala massacre by the LTTE, the villagers are about to flee their village. The village monk persuades them to stay, with the support of a schoolteacher, who later manages to get the village guards trained by the military.
Based on Aimee Stuart's play. Little Scots girl decides to use her inheritance for a "grand tour" of the Continent.

Nancy, a teenage girl, runs away from home. Hitchhiking to Virginia to stay with a friend, she is picked up by a couple on a camping trip. The trip turns deadly when the campers are attacked by a group of crazed Satanists.
Second and final part of epic tale about a legendary battle that changed the course of China history.

It has been almost 2 years since the small town of Santa Carla had suffered in the hands of the raging maniac, Cameron Crowe. Legend around town had it as that he may have been burnt in a fire he started.
Detective Danny Fisher discovers his girlfriend has been kidnapped by an ex-con tied to Fisher's past, and he'll have to successfully complete 12 challenges in order to secure her safe release.
An undercover ATF agent risks his life to destroy a murder-for-hire gang that is run from within a prison by an untouchable criminal mastermind.

Zihni becomes permanently disabled because of car accident. Zihni's brother and sister chase to Zihni's wealth. In such a case Cahide is at loose end. She loves Dr. Kadri but she can't leave from her husband.
A group of college researchers go camping deep into the Florida Everglades .While entering forbidden Native American territory against being advised not to, the group encounters the Swamp Ape.
In the war-torn Europe of 1944, a woman sees her life fall to pieces as she is forced to choose between her treacherous husband and an enemy officer.
Two friends get a bag from their boss to deliever it to another man. But they get curios about the bag and open it to look what's inside.
In 1700s New York, a Boston artist working in the remote Fort Alden is torn between his love for 2 women and thrown into the middle of a Mohawk-Iroquois-American war.
The love story of Lin Qi Zheng (Song Seung-Heon), who is from a rich family, and Zhou Yu (Yifei Liu) who is a smart and beautiful lawyer.

The 80's are almost at an end. Spaniard and Finn re-emerge from London's bleak underbelly of petty crime and drugs, to undertake a deal that catapults them across Europe to the hedonistic nightclubs in Ibiza.
A film about an incident in the last war when a gypsy girl sacrifices herself for her lover, a partisan who has deserted.
Shambu, a famous sculptor, lives with the memories of his late wife, Uma. His life takes a turn after meeting Durga, who falls in love with him.
A Lower East Side bartender becomes entangled in a murder mystery involving a desperate woman, a missing drug dealer and the scion of a powerful investment firm.

Two women chase money that they found and hid in a concert tour bus (Indigo Girls). They travel all over the country, mostly on American Indian reservations, until they find the money and discover themselves...
The troubled daughter of a famous TV chef arrives at her new university and attempts to start a new life. However, she soon discovers it is impossible to escape her brutal mother's shadow.
A rich young man hires his classmate to pretend to be his girlfriend to appease his father. Though it is meant to be purely a business arrangement, real sparks fly as they spend time together.

With his glory days long gone, an overweight former football player will make a bet with his close friends and visit the nearest gym for the ultimate makeover, only to discover the girl of his dreams and his true soulmate.

A new city with gangs to terrorists across Roblox City, two best friends reunite and fought their way through incoming enemies. With JT gone the two fight after him to still complete the last mistery in roblox city.

An unmitigated and sexy conman targets his next mark, the widowed Monique, for his latest swindle. But his routine scam hits a snag when suspicion mounts and his scheme quickly escalate into desperation, betrayal and murder.
Longstanding friendships are severely tested when three buddies who grew up together botch a drug deal and get played.
When his family is killed before his very eyes, Arjun must protect the last thing that connects him to his family.
FBI Agent and a Vatican lawyer decipher a cryptic rhyme to stop a sociopath murdering priests. **Based on the Novel by Nicholas Summers
Neck Of Da Woodz is a graphic wacky comedic horror film, shot in 2 days and totally improvised. It's "necks" versus "bros" when a wrong turn is made...Who will make it out of this neck of da woodz!?

Oichi, the blind bounty hunter, frees a woman from unjust prison and is now hunted by order of the local magistrate. She is concerned with the poor fishermen, who are oppressed and robbed by a gang in collusion with the authorities.

A boy leaves his small country town and heads to the big city to get a job. As soon as he makes it big his sweetheart will join him and marry him. His enthusiasm to get ahead leads to some interesting adventures.
Gabby James must protect the figments of her traumatically fractured mentality, from the one menacing figment that is trying to kill them all.
a heroin-addicted veteran with a tragic past, must stop the forces of evil from using his soul as a tortured pawn in a blasphemous war.

movie_name: Hans Kloss: More Than Death at Stake
description: In 1945, Polish intelligence agent Hans Kloss, codenamed J-23, goes to Konigsberg to search for the treasure stolen by the Nazis. It's there that he meets his old friend and rival, SS Officer Hermann Brunner.
Two teenage siblings endure a terrifying experience while investigating a rural legend near their family's vacation home.

There used to be an Aghori in a village 500 years ago, who had mastered black magic, he used to perform his art by going to different states of the country, he had such a knowledge, with which he could take the form of anyone.

The simple lives of Neelam, a single mother, and Nazia, her daughter, take a horrific turn when an evil force enters into their lives. The story revolves around how Gopi, their helpful neighbor, and Neelam face the odds and save Nazia.

Jonna, successful ad executive with husband Niklas and two small children, leads a double life. She is constantly on the lookout for quick casual sex. When she meets Aleksi, things start going awry in her personal and professional life.

A stillborn baby girl is abducted by a morgue attendant and brought back to life by electrokinetic power. On her 16th birthday, she escapes captivity and sets out to find her birth mother, leaving a trail of destruction behind her.

movie_name: The Extraordinary Adventures of Mr. West in the Land of the Bolsheviks
description: Experience the chronicle adventures of Mr. West and his faithful bodyguard and servant Jeddie, as they visit the land of the horrible and evil Bolsheviks.
An action-packed thriller starring Charles Bronson as Jack Murphy, a cop who is running to stay alive long enough to even the score with his wife's killer.

White Creek is a place from another universe. A place where feudalism remains intact and people struggle to break free from debt. One family must escape the dangers of this decaying society, as the power in their valley changes hands. In the end they are left to decide how to move forward in this universe and the next.

A Los Angeles crew mastered the art of robbery targeting small casinos in Las Vegas. Disbanded and still living off that money, the crew reunites to save one of the crew's girlfriend's sister from the hands of the Coyotes.

A blind masseur sleeps with the wife of a samurai, who catches them in the act and kills them. The murdered couple return as vengeful ghosts. This film is a remake of a 1957 film. It was the final picture made by Daiei Studios.
Never before has science-fiction struck the local screen with such hair-raising thrill and excitement and yet it has action, comedy, suspense, love and romance.
Ex-cop Marie wants to live the quiet life, until her husband is murdered. Now she's taking the law into her own hands in one-woman bloodbath against the mob.
Shaitan Khopdi is an Indian horror film directed by C. Vasna. The film stars Devraj, Vinita and K. Kumar in the lead roles. Watch the full movie Shaitan Khopdi online, only on Eros Now.
A mobster discovers he has the power to summon dark, evil spirits. Based on a series of graphic novels.
A woman must discover the dark secret that is hidden in the building to which she moved, in order to free herself from the supernatural presence that she suspects is harassing her.
A rescue crew investigates a spaceship that disappeared into a black hole and has now returned...with someone or something new on-board.
Angel is the biker who joins a commune of hippies near a small town. When the town rednecks attack them, Angel calls up some of his bad biker buddies to exact revenge.
A comedy that follows nine very different couples on the night they conceive, showing that sex can sometimes be more neurotic than erotic.
When a gang war threatens to spill into her county, a Texas Sheriff uses unconventional methods to protect it.
Detectives investigate a series of unexplained horrific murders, with only one thing in common...an I Ching symbol carved into their foreheads.
Movie made in 35mm about a police that is investigating the murder of a girl who was raped, now nothing can stop him, shows the danger in the big city.
A young girl is seduced into the realm of witchcraft by her treacherous wet nurse and eventually realizes that there is something more deadly hidden in the woods behind her house.

When an Allied prisoner of war ship transporting a cargo of German prisoners is torpedoed by a German submarine in the North Atlantic, three survivors cling for their lives to a raft. The ...                See full synopsis »
Happy Cricket and his cute, adorable friends will have to defeat the evil Wartlord and rescue Linda, the Night Star. This film celebrates the values of friendship, freedom and the defense of nature.
The adventures of Kishore, a "James Bond 777" CBI agent, as he and heroine Sopa battle criminal mastermind "Boss" and his gang which includes whip-cracking Jamilla and a trio of highly trained dogs.
When her home is invaded by a group of people who demand the key to her safe deposit box, a woman with dementia cannot tell between who is her family and who are the criminals.
The outbreak of the First World War. A small town in the borderlands. Its inhabitants hide from a requisition a bell, called "Florian".
An oil-field worker from Texas journeys to Australia to look for his missing sister, and his search winds up getting him involved with a violent drug-smuggling gang.

Chester Zerum is just an average guy living an average life, until he finds himself the victim of a monstrous entity known as Barbatachthian. What can one man do against an ancient being of immeasurable power?
A top secret project between the Trugollian Empire and the US military causes unforeseen complications in the lives of the participants.

After a fun trip to Tijuana Mexico over the weekend, Dave an American college student wakes up in jail, but this is no ordinary jail, unexplainably the inmates start killing each, and Dave must escape in order stay alive.
In Johannesburg, an American parole breaker unknowingly picks up a rental car that will tie him to a web of corrupt local police.
In a mountainous village, in hatred and revenge, unexpectedly a lively story of love blossoms between a rich arch-father and a poor shepherd.

movie_name: Persona 3 the Movie: #4 Winter of Rebirth
description: The season changes to winter. Makoto makes a decision in order to greet the spring that is waiting beyond.

Shady traffic takes place behind the door of a cabaret. The gang leader is Asian Wang spied on by Commissioner Thomas. While Richard leads a double game and, out of love for the landlady, ends up shooting Wang.
A bachelorette party turns deadly when a chemical reaction overtakes a valley, but being indoors could be just as deadly as being outside.
A writer begins to encounter a series of unexplainable events when he's forced to lift the lid on the Pandora's Box holding the demons of his past.

A small town will have visitors from another world. The sheriff will have to solve the mystery of why many people are going missing. Will he protect the town, and his daughter from the visitors who are whispering in the darkness?
A corporate risk-management consultant must decide whether or not to terminate an artificially created humanoid being.
An ambitious Lebanese-American youth is forced to take over his family's gas station after his father's death.
Chase Hudson was the perfect patsy, until he hoodwinks the hit-men, runs to the swamp and devises a plan to turn the tables on the conspirators.
A wisecracking New York reporter intrudes on a research scientist's quest to unmask The Moon Killer.
This beautiful love story that starts in Israel and goes through all scenes of India, its cultural, beauty and religions traditions, brings us to the question: "What is this love?"

Romeo Montague is the alias of (the re-animated) Patient Zero, a skilled, mutated android hit-man/pimp/ancient relics collector, that lives in Verona City, N.Y.; a dystopic metropolis filled with extreme horror and sexual deviancy.

A romantically inexperienced career focused young woman is forced into accosting her handsome neighbour with the cunning plot to act the part of her boyfriend when her parents come to town, with unexpected consequences.
FBI Agent Mark Brock becomes entangled in the very same criminal underworld he is investigating. When he is murdered, it puts those closest to him in danger.

Heikki tries to overcome his financial difficulties by marrying his son Juhani and the only daughter of Nuottaniemi, Hanna. She is in love with the honest Antti and is threatened by the fiery and dangerous Juhani.
In this raucous horror-comedy, a landlord must fight an army of undead ninjas after one of his tenants discovers an ancient sword of necromancy.
A man takes another man's girl as a hostage and goes to a deserted house outside of Tehran. But there another destiny is waiting him.
When a couple discovers that something unusual is visiting their garden at night they attempt to capture it on video
A young boxer gets caught between a no-good father and a crime boss when he starts dating the boss's daughter, although she doesn't know what daddy does for a living.
A foreign agent, Sami Ameni, wants to find another agent, with whom he has collaborated during WWII, in order to blow up a factory.
A story of a man who has nine lives and a girl who falls in love with him. Is he a demon or an angel?
A sage travels to the past and collects a set of legendary swords, which he brings to life as a gang of talented but dysfunctional young men, to fight a battle against evil.
Four families in LA of different ethnicity (Latino, Asian/Vietnamese, African and Jewish) gather together for Thanksgiving dinner.
A struggling social media influencer discovers the house he shares is haunted. The ghost brings him and his friends fame and fortune, but with deadly consequences.
In the small town of Red Rock, a devil-worshipping cult, in league with the local sheriff, kidnaps victims for sacrifice.
It follows a college student as she boards a party train for Halloween, and ends up fighting for her life when a mysterious assailant begins killing the people one-by-one.
A reclusive librarian's life turns upside down when she discovers the high-spirited younger sister she never knew existed.
Bijli's life crashes when her lover Raju dies tragically in an accident. She is in for a bigger shock when she meets Vicky.
A historical, action-infused epic of Emperor Jahangir and Queen Nur Jahan, whose love changed the face of the Mughal Empire in seventeenth century India.
An overweight teen is bullied by a clique of cool girls poolside while holidaying in her village. The long walk home will change the rest of her life.
Two rival sports equipment companies and their heirs, Jadzia and Jan, whose meeting will become a source of funny misunderstandings.
In Wales, a gypsy queen changes her sister's dead baby for one by the same father. The child grows up to marry her daughter.
Two Punjab Police officers head to Canada to solve on a mission. When they get to Canada, their mission isn't as simple as what they first thought.

Set in a gritty, real life New York City, alcoholic Sam meets up with a modern day succubus who marks him and controls his will. As his world unravels he slowly figures out what is happening and has to figure out what to do.
In 1967, a chemical plant near a discreet roadside restroom causes an outbreak of gay zombies. At a near by beach cottage a group of best friends must fight off the undead.
In the 17th century a heroine is aided by villagers in bringing a man to pay for wronging her brother and the villagers.
When a shut-in dies alone and returns as a housebound ghost, he finds himself at the mercy of a world that didn't even notice he was gone.
Liza slowly replaces Melampo, Giorgio's dog. While she accepts it, Giorgio forces her to wear collars and leashes.
Alien brain parasites, entering humans through the mouth, turn their host into a killing zombie. Some teenagers start to fight against them.
Italian western set in the southern Italy before the unity. Antonio Franco's sister is been murdered by a gang of bandits. He swear vengeance and manage to infiltrate the gang to find the murders.
When her mother makes a shocking request, sheltered Ava struggles with reality, escaping into a dream world where she summons up old friends and long forgotten desires.
A film about how Stalin attempted to erase the existence of those who were removed from their positions and lost their lives.
A young couple move in together to their first unit. What they don't realise is that the unit they've rented already has residents. But once they move in, it's hard to move out.
Espe, a teen streamer who dreams of having thousands of followers, accepts a viral challenge in which she has to disappear for 48 hours. But what starts as a game, becomes something dangerous.
Mike begins working at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza. While spending his first night on the job, he realizes every night the animatronics hunt him in the roblox restertuant.

Terrorists takes a nuclear facility hostage, to set off a meltdown the size of Chernobyl - throughout Southern California. Only one man, security agent Mike Jeffers, has what it takes to thwart the operation and divert the deadly attack.
