Fear is the most dangerous disease. When her father is framed for a biological terror attack on Sydney, suspended Federal cop Leyla Nassar is set on a mission to clear her father's name and uncover the truth behind the attack.

Shaken by the recent, unexpected death of her twin sister, Jennifer travels to Buenos Aires to execute the will and claim her inheritance. There, she encounters her remarkably well-preserved grandmother, who might be hiding something.
The film narrates the story of a young man whose imagination compensates for the impoverishment that is dealt out to him in reality.
A team of explorers stumble upon an undiscovered island only to find out its inhabitants have found the Fountain of Youth.
This martial arts/sci-fi film has plenty of action, intrigue and suspense. The story revolves around opposing forces in the world of military espionage.

movie_name: Me he de comer esa tuna
description: In rural Mexico, a young man competes with his best school friend for the love of a girl whose marriage has been arranged by her parents.

movie_name: Mimì Bluette... fiore del mio giardino
description: Mimi Bluette, daughter of a prostitute, lives in Paris where she is idolized by men of all kinds and classes. She is about to settle on a rich man when she meets a stranger in a bar.
The U.S. President, low in the opinion polls, gets talked into raising his popularity by trying to start a cold war against Canada.

Returning to the medical school where they were test subjects decades ago, a pair of outrageously twisted serial killers use shockingly brutal sex acts to start killing off a group of drugged-out med students.
A young, depressed man is trying to move on with his life after his girlfriend's bizarre death. One day, a mysterious woman notices him at work and convinces his coworkers to introduce him to her.

movie_name: Johan Falk: GSI - Gruppen för särskilda insatser
description: Policeman Johan Falk returns to Gothenburg and starts service at the successful special service GSI, but the relation between the unit and the criminals introduces him to a world he never thought existed.
A blind Vietnam vet, trained as a swordfighter, comes to America and helps to rescue the son of a fellow soldier.
A captured Soviet pilot faithful to his childhood friends leads an escape from a German concentration camp and then suffers from communist crimes.
Sundar plays the character of 'Gate Selvam', a man who decides to quit the mafia and lead a peaceful life. The story is all about the circumstances that arise because of this decision.

Without knowing each other, Vila and Rao keep appearing in each other's dreams. Obsessed with finding each other Vila travels to China were after a series of events Destiny finally crosses their paths.
Following an act of bullying, witty high school senior Javier develops psychic abilities which he must use to stop a mysterious serial killer targeting his classmates.
The rays of the moon bring a coven of female zombies back to life. A special police squad is assigned to stop them.
An aspiring filmmaker goes through the ups and downs of romance when he falls for a Christian woman who says she only wants to be friends.

Robbie Mallorca and Anna Alvarado are teachers from an exclusive school headed by the ever-conventional non-conformist principal. The admins of the school greatly disapprove of the students' wish to build a dance group for self-expression.
An auctioneer's daughter and a rich buyer's emissary fall for each other while trying to keep a rare wine out of the hands of evil doers.
Two strangers share a sweepstakes ticket and then embark on an "imaginary" honeymoon with their "winnings".

Sam and Jenny ventured into the woods of their childhood to say goodbye to their dead father. Little did they know that when they set out, they would be caught in the middle of a galactic conflict that would decide the fate of humanity.

A love triangle occurs. Francis and Mary are best friends, but when the beautiful Nick moves into their area, the balance and friendship is disturbed. What's Nick after? They both fall in love, and jealousy knocks on the door.
A young filmmaker documents his ghost-hunting, reality show friends as their routine investigation of an abandoned orphanage turns into a nightmare from which they can't escape.
A Japanese investigator (Morita) and a Detroit cop (Leno) team up to track down a stolen prototype turbocharger.
Freckles (Johnny Downs) comes home from college...and the sheriff accuses him of murder, gangsters put him on the spot, and his girl friend, Jane (Gale Storm), falls in love with a confidence man.
Flash Gordon, Dale Arden and Dr. Alexis Zarkov visit the planet Mongo to thwart the evil schemes of Emperor Ming the Merciless, who has set his planet on a collision course with Earth.
A military vet returns home, becomes a police officer and investigates a supernatural case involving an urban legend.
A female ex-cop uncovers a drug ring led by a bounty hunter with a popular TV show. When corrupt local police get involved, all hell breaks loose.
Delight Scottsdale is a young, curvy woman who lost her mom during her birth and goes through the trenches from foster homes and trying to find her way out in a cruel world.
A young Chicago advertising executive believes a woman he sees in a café is his long-lost love. His belief leads to obsession, as he puts his life on hold in order to trail her.
A young man put in a moral dilemma is forced to choose between saving his dying pregnant wife or going against his beliefs.

A young man who is trying to fight corruption in his company but he ends up being terminated for this; to impress a girl, he comes up with a lie of him being a rich business man. The lie gets bigger and he becomes famous.

When Captain Kyle Fierson's unit is ambushed during a raid to rescue a deadly nuclear device, he must run for his life - not only to track down the missing time bomb, but also to clear his name when he is accused of aiding the terrorists.
A young Italian-American tomboy, Gianna, spent her whole life being told how to live, but after a few terrible blind dates, a young man steps in out of fate and shows her how to be her best self.
A former Ninja must outplay his former Mastress and an evil lord to free his family from certain death.

movie_name: Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer
description: The Fantastic Four learn that they aren't the only super-powered beings in the universe when they square off against the powerful Silver Surfer and the planet-eating Galactus.

movie_name: Shen tan Power: Wen mi zhui xiong
description: A cop turns fugitive when he is framed for the murder of a key witness in a weapons smuggling investigation. On the run the cop befriends a psychic who helps him to capture the real killer.
After accessing a pornographic website, two men wake up to find themselves trapped in a dungeon with a supernatural entity.
Two college students on a survival weekend in the wilderness cross paths with three desperate killers in what turns into a fight for life.

An intelligent graduate and working-class army veteran has an affair and clashes with a 'nouveau riche' young woman, who does not care about birth control or the use of any other precautions to avoid pregnancy.
The young Fred turns out to be a hindrance to Bill Warner and, as he did with his father, Bill will try to get rid of him to take over his ranch.
Soap-opera about a social-climbing Jewish man and his old-world parents who are heartbroken by his rejection of them.
In a post-apocalyptic wasteland in 1997, a comic book fan adopts the persona of his favourite hero to save his enthusiastic friend and fight a tyrannical overlord.
A teen martial arts expert and his martial arts class take on a bunch of thugs headed by a devious real estate developer who is forcing a community to sell out their property so he can build a mall.
Ekaterina Voronina firmly showed her will, did not tolerate concessions both in her work and in her personal life. Her harsh adherence to principles did not allow her to believe even her beloved man.
In 1952, during the Korean War, two American pilots become bitter enemies over the same woman but must shelf their personal feud when confronted by deadly Chinese MIG fighter jets in battle.

The brothers Zef and Roni are very different. In Paris, Zef's wife is buried about the same time as Roni's daughter is getting married. Zef's daughter unknowingly falls in love with Roni's daughter's fiance. Problems arise.
The friendship between two life-long girlfriends is put to the test when one starts a family and the other falls ill.
Vittorio, a goldsmith looking for his perception of beauty, meets Sonia and manages to convince her to lose weight to an unhealthy degree.
A sincere police officer tries to stop an organ trafficking racket. But he is unaware that the man performing the illegal trade is the same person who killed his beloved.
A group of youths find themselves stranded on a bus in the middle of the Brecon Beacons. Night time approaches and unexplained events start to occur.
After a mysterious, lost night on their honeymoon, a newlywed couple finds themselves dealing with an earlier-than-planned pregnancy.

movie_name: Eddie and the Cruisers II: Eddie Lives!
description: A Montreal construction worker joins a band and turns out to be a long-lost rock star from 1960s New Jersey - none other than Eddie Wilson, who mysteriously disappeared after a road accident.
A teenage boy awakens a ghost from an antique pot. To be reincarnated the ghost must help his present day counterpart by helping him find romance.
A woman, lonely and looking for love, arranges a date through a personals ad. What follows is a nightmare of torture and terror.
Ryutaro is a spy employed by the shogun Tokugawa Iemitsu, who is the target of assassination attempts that aim to hand power over to his younger brother Tadanaga.

Áurea is a sentimental older woman, who befriends teenager Áureo. They like each other, so she talks to him about herself, her spirituality, mysticism and existence itself. They become inseparable, so his jealous mother confronts her.
Several women enter a science fiction author's life over the course of a few years, after the author has lost the woman he considers his one true love.
Rising from her coffin, an inter-dimensional female vampire prowls a run down carnival hunting for human blood.
A new twist on a "crazy family" story, the murderous Cultry family faces a challenge when they discover that one of their intended victims might have what it takes to become one of their own.
An ex-GI gathers together some of his army buddies to travel to a Central American dictatorship to free some American POWs being held there.
The story of two best friends who have an affair one night, resulting in the woman becoming pregnant.

When Lily, a love-cursed psychic who dispenses love advice to clients but is despairing at the failure of her own umpteenth romance, finally surrenders to the magic of the Kit, she learns what forgiveness is, and what true love requires.
After his family is kidnapped during their sailing trip in Spain, a young Wall Street trader is confronted by the people responsible: intelligence agents looking to recover a mysterious briefcase.
Max must carry out a series of 3 risky missions in charge of De La Sol, if he fails, the life of Max and his family is in danger. A traditional Sin City-style animation.
A historian from the future arrives in present-day India to recover an object stolen from his world before it falls into the wrong hands and causes a catastrophic change in human history.
Kalyan misinterprets Meghamala's concern for love and tells her that he loves her. But, she refuses his marriage proposal. It remains to be seen why Meghamala refuses the proposal.

When a trio of ambitious media students embark on a film-making assignment into an ancient forest, they not only invoke the wrath of a reticent security guard but also the malevolent 'Spirit of the Wood'.
Alcatraz prison closed in 1963. Twenty two years later the violence and sheer terror return. Conrad and his friends live there. They want Gloria Ramsey to join them - One man stands in the way.

Runaway girl is captured by hospital where she falls in love with patient, Thumper, who can manufacture hallucinations for other people. Love triangle with Head Nurse results in Thumper being experimentally medicated.

A space thief on the space most-wanted list attempts to evade a space bounty hunter at an enormous space warp-gate. Unfortunately, a space robot assassin and more than a few space vikings are going to get in the way.
A Parisian descendant of Don Juan vows to stop philandering in order to win the hand of a virtous young lady with a disapproving father.
Unsatisfied with her life in England, young mother Julia relocates to Morocco with her small daughters, Lucy and Bea. Although the family enjoys various adventures, they struggle to make ends meet.

Elmo is an ex-convict who loves his family. He is wrongly accused of killing Arthur after he caught him abusing his wife Cathy. Elmo is pursued, tried and, brought to court by Arthur's brother, the Mayor.
A senator's daughter (who can't help singing) follows her boyfriend West in the days of the California gold rush.

When Ichigo's sister Yuzu is kidnapped by sinners & he is asked to do something for them in order to get his sister released. Ichigo must find a way to take his sister back from hell with the help of Rukia, Renji & Uryu.
In a future where people are paid to store data in their DNA, a young woman falls in love with a mysterious stranger.
A lonely college freshman forges a strong connection with his resident assistant during a fraternity party.
When student journalism major Carmilla meets a gang of role-playing kids, they introduce her to a vampire game called Eternal Blood. But is it just a game?

During the reign of the Vikings, Kainan, a man from a far-off world, crash lands on Earth, bringing with him an alien predator known as the Moorwen. Though both man and monster are seeking revenge for violence committed against them, Kainan leads the alliance to kill the Moorwen by fusing his advanced technology with the Viking's Iron Age weaponry.
Pledges at a sorority house are plagued by a former sister who happens to be a vampire. Luckily, each of the new pledges is skilled at kickboxing so they are able to defend themselves.
A troubled young filmmaker battles a dark voice inside his head; can a mysterious muse illuminate his way out of it?
A sensitive woman who fell down on account of convencionalism. Her dull life will convey her to a tragic fate.
The Medusa Box tells the story of 2 mismatched hobbyists on a quest across Dartmoor to uncover the secret of 'The Elusive Medusa'.

For several years sisters Amina and Nadja have been on the run from Smirnov who was promised Amina by her parents. They seek shelter in Stockholm but it seems Smirnov and his vampire clan has found them.
The film is an edgy black comedy set in swinging London in the late 60s. The All Saints girls play three street wise sisters who head 'up West' to rob and generally cause trouble.
As a man suffers with post-traumatic stress after the death of his wife at the hands of the living dead, he and his family must compete for access to a safe haven by joining a zombie killing game.

Maggie (Serinda Swan) is a tough and ruthless member of the all-female Dark Moon biker gang led by the merciless Trigga (Pollyanna McIntosh). After Maggie's cousin (Vanessa Dubasso) is drugged at a party, the gang rides out for revenge.

When an American billionaire dies, his poor Italian nephew inherits everything, provided he can arrive in the USA to claim his inheritance before the deadline but the corporate lawyer-executor tries to steal the inheritance.

Hitch, the most popular Rideshare app, has created safe rides for millions. At least, that's what they want you to think. It was only a matter of time before the story went public. The story of that one night. That one, horrific night.

The film is about a group of youngsters aiming to make a fake horror video for someone. But unknown to them, a real ghost begins to create havoc in a frightful atmosphere and puts their lives in danger.
THIS IS Nth VERSIONOF THE TYPICAL ACTION-MOVIE FORMULA: HERO'S PARENTS ARE MURDERED, SISTER IS RAPED, HERO TAKES THE LAW INTO HIS HANDS AND RELENTLESSLY PURSUES THE CRIMINALS.
A family caught in the middle of a jewelry store robbery is chased all over Saigon. They bond and become closer through their hilarious caper.
A reforming ex-gangster tries to reconcile with his estranged policeman brother, but the ties to his former gang are difficult to break.
As three generations of a family in a small Texas town gather for a funeral, we learn the hilarious, sad, trashy truth of their "Sordid Lives."
Investigator Amaira D'Costa rescue a girl from an abandoned mansion and things starts messing up with her.

Eva and Lola are close friends. While Eva tries to cope with her past creating a fantasy life, Lola does not want to handle with the truth of her real identity. Two friends with different views of the same story.
Living under constant fear, a blind teenager realizes that he cannot be bullied any longer thanks to his acting coach.

An industrial tow truck driver suffering from insomnia returns to his childhood home after the untimely death of his father, to discover that a paranormal presence has been living in the house and haunting the sacred land it was built on.
A nameless psychopath who videotapes the horrific murders of beautiful, young women discovers that he may actually be a character in someone else's snuff film.
A lost 1926 American silent-comedy film starring Bebe Daniels and directed by Arthur Rosson. The film was produced by Famous Players-Lasky and distributed by Paramount Pictures.
Follows Marjorie Finnegan, a thief who likes to steal every shiny-gleamy-pretty-sparkly thing she can lay her hands on, as she loots her way through history.
Four college students stumble across an occult website and accidentally release a demon that is imprisoned there. Hilarity ensues.
Sadism and sleaze dominate this fast-paced film about the getaway aftermath of a heist-gone-wrong-turned-kidnapping.

A lonely wife of a workaholic husband on the magical Isle of Capri meets a charming and attractive young man. An exciting affair must end when word gets back to the husband and he becomes ill. Then the daughter enters the scene.
Four disparate assassins are given ten hours to hunt and kill a mob boss before he turns State's evidence against his own organized crime family.

When serial killer Havoc escapes from his prison, there is no holding back. He descends upon unsuspecting lovers in their cabin get away. The world's most brutal killer is loose and his thirst for blood cannot be stopped.
Spring 1944 and the Allies stand ready to return to France. The men of the 13th Parachute Battalion will be at the spearhead of that return. This is their story.

The Epix go on their final adventure, fighting alongside their previous foe, Grand Admiral Thrawn, to defeat their cruelest threat ever, Darth Progenius. A fearsome foe with an evil apprentice, Bully Maguire.

A former L.A. drug dealer has moved to Houston to make a new life for himself as a married architect. Everything falls apart when he is suddenly visited by one of his former cohorts who comes carrying heroin.
Too old grandpa is being celebity by news maker who came from centre. But then he recollected something weird things about his missus .
Ramiro faces a hard struggle: his love for Antonieta - his father's former mistress and the fresh tender feelings towards young Celia.
The dressmaker Annemarie and the upcoming businessman Victor falls in love. But Annmaries simple background is not good enough according to Victors family.
A pair of professional con-men who swore never to meet again, get together again to pull off one more swindle.
In a tragic twist of fate, two star-crossed lovers kill themselves in a monumental misunderstanding.

A scientist recovers a powerful weapon created by inventor Nicola Tesla in the early twentieth century. Now, the plane carrying the device and a disparate group of passengers crashes in the Canadian mountains. The battle to survive begins.
An ex-marine returns to Vietnam when he learns his former mercenary partner whom he thought was killed is being held by a sadistic general.
An undercover Nazi in Libya aims to steal fuel and deliver it to a specific location in the desert where an Italian bomber would refuel on its way to Allied target.
A man's life is in trouble when he gets infected with rabies. However, a ray of hope strikes through the gloom when a girl enters his life.
Faced with real-world opportunities and challenges, a couple endures the highs and lows of trying to make a long-distance relationship survive.
A group of gangsters plan to rob a post office, while two friends who have no plans for life, meet a mysterious girl named Gloria. Their storylines cross after the heist.
After being forced to take a room in a boardinghouse, an immigrant in search of the American Dream finds herself in a nightmare she can't escape.

When Sam moves into her ex-mentor's house, she unwittingly unleashes an ancient, vengeful evil. When the demon possesses her girlfriend, Sam must choose who to trust, and unravel a web of secrets and lies in a vicious fight for survival.
Beethoven, the St. Bernard dog, becomes a father, but his girlfriend Missy is dognapped, and his puppies are in danger of the same fate.
A group of Russian teenagers spend their summer at a summer camp. Mitia falls in love and gets so occupied with his own problems that he forgets the others.
A man goes to Hong Kong to locate his long lost elder brother. There he meets a mysterious woman and falls into a romance that seems doomed from the start
Best friends make a pact to be together in a decade if neither finds love. With two months left until their deadline, they both scramble to find someone to avoid being each other's last resort.
Against a luxurious Venice background, a daredevil German secret service captain pits his wits against an older man,a sinister antiquities dealer who is stealing drawings of weapons.

An aging porn star agrees to participate in an "art film" in order to make a clean break from the business, only to discover that he has been drafted into making a pedophilia and necrophilia themed snuff film.
A couple head to a remote cottage, where the wife falls under the spell of a mysterious vampire, who starts a painful and horrifying transformation in her.
Political thriller involving the players related to the assassination of presidential candidate Coloso.
A former mafia footsoldier tries for a quiet life working in a used book store but his life is up-ended by the arrival of his hot-headed nephew who is instantly drawn into the gangster lifestyle.
Andy is all set to graduate from high school when he flunks his English exam--despite the fact that the Judge went through the trouble of getting him his very own private secretary.

A married couple on the brink of separation find themselves stranded in the desert with two strangers and only one bottle of water. Will their struggle for survival bring them closer together or tear them further apart?

Strange forces keeps a vacationing couple trapped on a secluded island; the spirt of a murderer set it's sight on siblings in a apartment building, and two rich bickering siblings are kidnapped and taken to the lair of a hungry Impakto.
Life takes a turn for Jackie, a happy-go-lucky chap who has to go in search of a girl for whose disappearance he has taken the blame.

With her father presumed dead during the German occupation in Athens and with an ailing mother, a poor secretary faces incarceration after a treasonous theft at the office. Only a kind friend can help her; however, is she truly guilty?

A goat farmer discovers a newborn baby among the bodies of a cult's mass suicide. In nurturing the baby, the farmer's cancer-ridden wife starts getting better. But there's something dark about the child's power.
Four friends spend a final summer together tangled in a web of sexual obsession, alienation and magic.
A police officer is in a frantic search for a compatible bone-marrow donor for his gravely-ill son. The only match is a convicted vicious killer who is now on the run. All he has to do is catch him.

Fed up with constantly getting fired, an adorable young woman sets her mind on keeping her new job as a columnist; however, a blunder threatens to send her back to square one. Can her love-smitten colleague save this delightful cutie-pie?

Welcome to Southtown, a city built by hustlers and fueled by their money. Everyone in this town is a hustler, or thinks they are. Three classes of individuals in the town must find a way to survive the concrete jungle.
Kate and Lee, two twenty-somethings burned out on relationships, meet and agree to become a couple for exactly one year.
A hunchbacked gangster is betrayed by his gang during a robbery, and plots his revenge with the help of his no-good brother.
A popular high school football player becomes a werewolf after a trip to Romania, and struggles to come to terms with his new reality.
Arthur and Roberta are facing the end of life's journey but unexpectedly find each other, and a chance for love and a glorious new beginning.

Every monster has their own beginning. For a troubled young woman named Carrie Ann, her nightmarish life is about to take an even more terrifying turn for the worse when she wanders into the wrong neck of the woods.
A photographer is forced into witness protection after witnessing a man being thrown from a window by a man on the FBI's Top 10 Most Wanted List.
In the 22nd century, a scientist attempts to right the wrong his ancestor created: the puzzle box that opens the gates of Hell and unleashes Pinhead and his Cenobite legions.
Arkisha is the woman who will do everything just to make her ex-boyfriend, Adam Jacob, stay in her life. But after that breakup, there's something they can't get enough of - benefits.

movie_name: Forbidden Martial Arts: The Nine Mysterious Candle Dragons
description: Telling the story of the ancient Candle Dragon who has been asleep for 27 years and is about to wake up. In order to avoid catastrophe, Xu Mo, Mu Yuhan and other knights embarked on a thrilling road to suppress the dragon.
A group of High School girls with guns go on a killing spree. They are intent on ridding the world of scummy men.

The Spirit Stalkers reality show, once a big hit, faces cancellation without a ratings boost, which leads the investigative team to Gloria Talman, whose house is rampant with unexplained ghostly activity.
An inventor uses his time machine to defeat a rival inventor who has been stealing his ideas while his neglected girlfriend uses it to warn her younger self not to date him in the first place.
A man goes on the run after being accused of stealing diamonds from the future in-laws of his sister.
A computer scientist and drone pilot is put on a hit list due to his religious beliefs. He and his sister are pursued by super soldiers, called Erasers, to capture them dead or alive.

Upon returning to Korea after completing his music studies abroad, a man finds that his ex-lover's husband has been kidnapped by North Korean soldiers. Rather than dwell on the issue, the two rekindle their passion for each other.
A mentally unstable elderly woman, recently released from a mental asylum, proceeds to slaughter all the guests staying at her motel.
Brokers , Freddy and Nicholas, try various ways to make money to repossess their boat from a businessman. However, they get into trouble when they resort to illegal ways to earn money.
The convoluted continuation of the adventures of the time-traveling, now-human Monkey King, who attempts to fulfill his divine destiny.

A struggling novelist moves his wife and young son to an old country home, but when a presence begins to communicate with his son, the family must escape an evil that threatens to doom them to the house for eternity.
Mathias and Antoine become a modern-day odd couple when they move in together in London. But while establishing house rules is easy, handling relationships with the opposite sex is another matter!

After visiting the morgue for some routine photos, a rookie photojournalist starts experiencing strange visions. She soon believes that after being "touched" by a corpse at the morgue that she has been infected with death.
A love story set in 1930s England that follows 17-year-old Cassandra Mortmain, and the fortunes of her eccentric family, struggling to survive in a decaying English castle.
A swashbuckling adventure which takes place in the mid-1800's on the South Pacific islands where bloody raids and battles were once the rule of the day.

Set in the 1920s, an American doctor and his wealthy patient travel to the French Riviera where they surround themselves with their circle of friends and become entwined in a complicated love triangle.
358 days ago, Mark Barton's wife and baby daughter were killed in a tragic accident. But Mark believes that they are still with him. And now, he can finally prove it.

Lui, along with his partner Keung, are among the best cops in Hong Kong. But their high success rate comes at a high level of violence, and after Keung goes too far with a suspect, he is thrown off the force.
Present day. Events unfold that hint at the famous Irish myth of the Banshee. Is she real or just superstition?
Stranded together on an industrial rooftop in the midst of a global pandemic, strangers Cillian and Ellen battle starvation, dehydration, and each other.
In war-ravaged Afghanistan, love blooms slowly between an Afghan man (Qaisy) and a Malaysian aid worker (Laila) who is trying to escape her own personal demons at home.
The film revolves around two families hailing from the South Indian state of Kerala who have spent some important years of their lives in the Middle East.

Aathi and Meera fall in love after the usual playful tiffs. On a visit to a friend's village for his marriage, the two of them help the friend marry his sweetheart instead of the bride. After many conflicts, Aathi and Meera are together.

Xavier and Mico join a writing camp, where they get to know each other more. But with their friends and other people around them twist and turn them in different directions, will they be strangers no more or strangers again?
An angry and embittered army veteran returns from Vietnam to his village, high in the Savoy mountains of France, where he attempts to brutalize those around him.
After nine years in Egypt, Azzam (Kholidi Asadil Alam) finally finishes his study and return to Indonesia. But good luck is not on his side yet, he still struggle to find job and love.
A carnival huckster and his 17-year-old foster daughter try to be accepted by the townspeople when she and a handsome lad fall in love.
A high school guy finds a mask in the lost and found at school, but him and his friends realize the mistake of taking the mask, when the original owner comes back looking for it.
A woman raises her son with his uncle, when she is forced to leave her home after her mother-in-law's death.
Bisexual travel writer Nathan examines his increasingly complex feelings for Maggie as they travel through California's wine country on assignment.
Esteban is on the run. The FBI wants him back as star/only witness against a drug lord, who wants him dead and sends killers on his trail. It comes to a showdown in a small southern town.
China White lived a life of privilege until a handsome young suitor exposes her to a dark side of the city that leaves her in danger of losing her soul, her mind, and her body.
Emotions are ignited amongst the complacent townsfolk when a handsome drifter arrives in a small Kansas community on the morning of the Labour Day picnic.
At a remote lake where several people mysteriously has vanished, a video crew records a reality show called "Mini-skirt Adventures".
A priest's son becomes the first host for a government-created artificial super intelligence, and his father must race to stop him before he brings devastation to millions of humans.

In a utopian society created at the end of the third world war, a female warrior who has been plucked from the badlands begins to see cracks in this new facade. And what does this community have planned for the rest of humankind?

Esteemed writer Mahmoud suffers from writers block. While trying to work at the family estate, concerns about an unproductive pear tree trigger in him memories of his childhood love for beautiful tomboy "M".
The lives of several couples and singles in New York City intertwine over the course of New Year's Eve.
A Gang tries to rescue their leader from the prison, where others stuck at a problem, the jailer of the prison shows off to stop them all.
A mentally-disturbed teenager kidnaps and brainwashes children into cannibalistic psychopaths - but not when the adults intervene.
Goose herder Chin Pao, has an unorthodox master who trains him in Goose Boxing. Chin Pao hones his techniques to do battle against Ghost Hand Chui Lan, who is terrorizing the province.
The movie is actually based upon Roman Polanski's Rosemary's Baby (1968)even though it is not credited.
The girlfriend of a young gypsy tries to guide her life in a proper way but does not achieve it. When she gets difficulties because of a fight everything changes.
When Hoppy's falsely accused young friend is killed while supposedly trying to escape from jail, an embittered Hoppy is blamed and drummed out of the Texas Rangers.

movie_name: Buscando el camino de tu amor
description: Francisco, the protagonist of the film, tries to find true love, so he passes from one lover to another driven by an exacerbated passion. He ends up being the victim of a plot to end his life.
A young boy decides to taken on alien invasion and rescue the world. Then he becomes a superhero to protect the world.

When Anna Wyncomb is introduced to an underground, all-female fight club in order to turn the mess of her life around, she discovers she is much more personally connected to the history of the club than she could ever imagine.

Logline: A group of friends on their way to a martial arts tournament decide to take a detour to save time. The friends stumble across a group of satanic bikers performing a human sacrifice and find themselves fighting for their lives.

Archaeologist Kirsten Scott travels to Slovakia to view a priest's diary, from the 1700s. It holds clues to a burial site, deep in the mountains. The thrill of discovery turns to horror, as the tomb contains something not quite dead.
A group of friends who were World War I flyers ride their motorcycles across America in search of what they believe their generation lost during the war.

When a disastrous earthquake hits the town of Ravenshaw, the Rose family loses sight of their little girl within the town's zoo. The Rose family must fight to survive whilst rescuing their daughter, but family bonds cannot be broken.
After a top secret mission unveils a new threat, Special Forces Commander, Maxx Yeager is recruited to lead a new Black Ops team to stop it.

The realities of the daily life of a young couple and a mother-in-law with their qualities and their faults, facing the difficulties of life, human relations and who are desperately looking for happiness and freedom.

In London, Alex leads a solitary life marked by Tourette's syndrome, which he suppresses through music. His routine is turned upside down by meeting an aspiring singer. A romance about reconciling artistic expression with daily survival.
Jeon Woo-chi, an undisciplined womanizing Taoist from the Joseon era, ends up in present-day Korea causing mayhem with his knack for magic.
Kochu Kurup and Aniyankutty fall in love with the same girl. When Aniyankutty comes to know that she loves his friend, he plans to sabotage their relationship, resulting in hilarious events.

'Hitoe', a woman who spent a long time aimlessly drinking and drinking every day. It doesn't cut down on the actual 'Masaru' or gives it satisfaction. Then one day, 'Masaru' disappears in front of her.
Triangles are always messy and the one between the disciplined Sania, the gentle Armaan and the maverick Samir was more than she bargained for.

Small time Hungarian matchmakers get the job to make a Hollywood star fall in love with a Russian 'businessman's spoiled brat sister. They get one million dollars if they succeed, but if they fail, they will have to pay with their lives.
A bank manager is unjustly framed for robbery by his colleagues and imprisoned. After his release, he assumes another identity to exact vengeance.

"El Rata" is released from prison after having served a sentence for "political" crimes during Franco's dictatorship. Now, on the street and with very few opportunities to work, he decides to commit a crime again.
Ike and Naya have been friends since university, but in their search for love, have they overlooked the fact that they could be perfect for each other?
1986 - A weird disease is changing office employees into mindless aggressive Zombies but everything Karl cares about is that he may lose his beloved office desk job.
The village of Three Mile Bend in north China undergoes transition from mutual assistance groups to communization. Part of this is allowing young people to marry as they wish.
The electronic blueprints for human modification have come up missing and now two competing villains are on the hunt to retrieve it.
Two sisters turn their family mansion in Louisiana into a guest house. One of their guests is an aide to a congressman, and turns their lives inside out.
A father invents a lurid past for his awkward young nephew to present him as an exciting suitor for his daughter.
A group of thieves break into the house hoping to walk away with a massive fortune but they ended up themselves entangled in a mystery involving the house's dark past.

A young woman's journey to reconnect with her high school sweetheart leads her to confront more of her exes and come to terms with the unresolved feelings from their past relationships and the uncertain future that lies ahead.
An Indie film that follows the friends of Daisy Reed retracing the steps of what happened the night she disappeared.
A young woman looks to escape her abusive life by moving to a friend's farm near Atlanta. Unfortunately, she learns her place of supposed comfort offers more terrifying forms of abuse.
In this modern setting for the Shakespeare classic, two small-town boys head to the big city looking for adventure and romance. But when they both fall for the same girl, friends become rivals.

Ganesh is obsessively in love with Sandhya, but she is not interested in him. His relentless pursuit leads to a lot of problems. However, everything changes the day he loses his father in an accident.

This is the first bloodless movie in the world of bulls, where there is no blood or animal abuse. A film written and directed by a former bullfighter so that it can be seen in all countries...                See full synopsis »
David has just started working for a large pharmaceutical company and falls madly in love with a young and very beautiful colleague, Angelica.
The first civil guardsman rises to the task of apprehending a dangerous serial killer before his city descends into chaos. Set ten years before the events of 'The Siege'.
Follows wealthy publisher Britt Reid, who goes under cover at night to fight crime alongside his friend Kato.
Bride to be June's bachelorette getaway turns deadly when her blood thirsty fiance and his friends show up to crash the party.
A Korean company analyst rear-ends an American man's car then discovers he's her new boss. Unlucky at love, she begins to take romance lessons from him in order to seduce him.

Two U.S. Marine investigators looking into a series of grisly murders in Manila discover that the crimes are tied to an amulet with a 400-year-old curse on it that has unleashed supernatural forces which can possess people.

"If load falls or shifts, it can kill or crush. Do not stand or walk under load" is the warning sticker on bulldozer 13. But on the night of the meteor from beyond, this piece of machinery becomes alive with a thirst for mankind's blood.
A CIA officer finds himself the target of a rendition operation after being scapegoated for the death of an interrogation subject.
A boy who is visited by a light powerful force which reveals to the boy his destiny of how he will save the world from a chaos that will wipe out the whole of humanity.
Nejat looks for his sister he lost 17 years ago. When he find his sister, she is shooted by her troubled lovers. Since then Nejat chases the revenge.
An alien invasion threatens the future of humanity. The catastrophic nightmare is depicted through the eyes of one American family fighting for survival.
This is a lovely love story because when love leaves its color then life becomes even more colorful.
In the 1930s in Konya, Turkey, the famous belly dancer Cemile dreams of going to the big city. Murat falls in love with her.

movie_name: A God Among Sheep -- The RIse of Maria Salvatore
description: They said she was a woman, only good for sex and making babies, she would never be a Boss. She vowed to show them a different truth, a hard truth, a woman can be whatever they chose to be.
Life for the young and beautiful Kim becomes unbearable. Her boss, Marshall, helped to find her apartment - where the previous tenant was killed. Kim begins to suspect Marshall may be the murderer.
After the death of her mother, an estranged daughter struggles to save her brother, and those around her from a malevolent faceless spirit.

Alex despises Modern Art but when he falls in love with an adorable French artist, he understands that the only way to conquer her heart is to pretend he is an artist. He now must win a Modern Art contest in order to win her heart.
Desperate men perform a bank heist and get more than they bargained for when they break into the vault.
A girl genius born with a bilateral cleft lip and pallet has to navigate high school to figure out who's with her and who's against her.

Two Americans on a hunting trip in Scotland become lost. They encounter a small village, not on the map, called Brigadoon, in which people harbor a mysterious secret, and behave as if they were still living two hundred years in the past.
Pigs squeal. Blood flows. Seven best friends driving to a ski resort meet an alien force that traps them on a hog farm where mutations abound and the kids fight to survive.

After a generation of peace, the Earth Federation's new space colonies becomes a battlefield. To save his friends and family, the reluctant warrior Seabook Arno becomes the pilot of a new Gundam which bears the code name F91.
A teenager involved in illegal car races runs a pedestrian over in a hit-and-run case where the victim turns out to be his mother.
A bowling night will turn into a bloody death match for a team of teenagers, as a deranged serial killer is taking them down one by one.
When a man with a dark secret sees his daughter threatened with eternal damnation, he seeks help from an unpopular Native American seer.

Christopher Skase. He ruled Australia and stole a fortune, fleeing to the coast of Spain. No one could touch him. No one could stop him. Until Peter Dellasandro and a small force of men swore they'd bring him down.
This "feminist" reworking of Fritz Lang's classic M focuses on the mothers of children stalked by a deranged pedophile.
Brisbane history and art collides in a romantic comedy of two strangers in pursuit of a lost artefact in the city.

Female police psychologist is targeted by a supernatural devil-worshiping serial killer who wants to prove to her that she's the Antichrist. A tough cop, his inept womanizing comic relief partner and a reverend try to stop him.

movie_name: The Twelve Stories of Glen Anggara
description: Inspired to become a better person, a young man attempts to fulfill 12 unrealized life wishes of a woman he knows.
Modernization of Charles Dickens' classic story finds the hapless Finn as a painter in New York City pursuing his unrequited and haughty childhood love.
In the small Australian town of Coober Ridge, a chain of unexpected events set several interwoven stories crashing into each other like dominos.

A down-on-his-luck rodeo rider meets a rich preppie-type girl. In the midst of a wild and turbulent journey through the southwest's rodeo circuit they fall in love. Will they stay together, or will their past lives tear them apart?
An ex-mercenary turned bodyguard struggles with an offer to make a fortune by assassinating her celebrity client.
A retired detective journeys to a haunted Colorado mining town to investigate the only case he failed to solve.
A young man's fiancé dies after contracting a terminal illness, and in his efforts to contact her he gets involved with a group of spiritualists.
Unscrupulous cocaine dealers, violent assassins, Irish and African gangsters and a mute are all on the hunt to track down the whereabouts of Sean Parish along The West Coast of Ireland.
Two garbage men uncover a conspiracy involving illegal toxic waste dumping and decide to bring the whole operation down.
During the Vietnam war, an army sergeant rebels against his tyrant commanding officer, whilst they are cut off by the enemy in the jungle. Things get worse for all of them after that.
Across a post-apocalyptic landscape haunted by spirits, a guilt-stricken woman must choose to abandon her husband or die with him.

Deadly Affair is the story of a married man who commits a deadly mistake of cheating on his wife and the repercussions are disastrous. His lover is sexy, smart, dangerous and she stops at nothing to get what she wants.
A teenager copes with his sexuality on the last day of school in 1984. It shows him coping with being gay and being with friends.
While a couple edits a Charles Manson movie in an Airbnb, the film's dark events begin to come true in the mysterious plot of a hidden leader.
Following the lives of five teenagers as they try to go through life while trying to avoid their own family backgrounds.
A pro-Japanese propaganda film directed by Japanese director Shimada under the Korean pseudonym Jeon-jang Do. The film is about sending guards to the border.
An innocent female clown must summon the courage to conquer hell in order to save herself and her beloved man.
A groovy, spooky and totally dysfunctional ghost story about lost souls smoking cursed PCP obtained from a witchdoctor.
Four burglars end up stealing a vehicle from robbers as well as unknowingly breaking in the house of a notorious gangster.

A widow bullied by traders in the fish market from further commercial aims after the death of her husband,a worker stand by her side and help then married her,but does the money and power change him ?
A private vacation turns deadly when an unexpected visit from old friends forces a young couple to unravel the mystery behind a supernatural horror.
A unique retelling of one of the most female-focused events in American history - the Salem witch trials.
The lives of some visitors and residents of Rome and the romances, adventures and predicaments they get into.
Science activism for health in sports, medicine, and tiger team research and development from Canada and International open collaboration to help anti-radiation material Borax to Japan.
Like a bag of Halloween candy after a night of trick or treating, Fun Size Horror: Volume One delivers an unexpected variety of frightful flavors all told in bite size pieces.
A mixed martial arts champion is forced out of retirement for one last fight in order to unravel a major conspiracy.
In this society drama set in contemporary England, a noblewoman pretends to be an adulteress in order to protect her sister-in-law, who actually is.
This movie chronicles the life of a South Indian ruler of the Satavahana Empire in South India in the 2nd century CE.
Often, we fail to see the other side. But, it's never too late. There is always an unexplored other side.
An American couple in England stumble upon a rambling mansion where a number of powerful individuals have been summoned by its patriarch regarding the home's legacy.
When a ruthless group of human traffickers invade a nearby town and kidnap a teenage girl, a former military mother must find her before she disappears for good.
A small-town librarian is gifted the lost diary of a dead teenager, exposing long-buried secrets as a murderous scarecrow stalks the streets.
The Egos discover an unaired Halloween Special and try to play it but the DVD player inside the PS4 isn't working properly. A comedic horror anthology is unleashed instead.
Zaiton seduces a drifter named Amran into murdering her elderly husband, Ibrahim, to get his money and land.
Four hikers go missing in a small town. The town is reminded of murders from ten years ago. The town sheriff must confront his past.

You have forty eight hours and then you are dead. A countdown from the moment you take possession of the chain. But if you unlock the secret of the chain you might be able to break the curse and then maybe you might get to stay alive.

movie_name: Sono toki wa kare ni yoroshiku
description: A romantic love story of Satoshi, Karin and Yuji - who were friends in their childhood and suddenly bump back into each others' life after 13 years of parted away. Gentle, moving and meaningful, that what love is in "Say hello for me".
After being lured to a mysterious and isolated party, a young introvert begins to lose his grasp on reality as he is thrust into an intensifying push-pull between his morals and his sanity.

Two hit men who don't know each other end up trapped in a car for 24 hours parked in a Los Angeles street awaiting orders to kill a target. Both men will undergo a conscience check as well as human existence conflicts.

movie_name: Luna de miel en Puerto Rico
description: Manuel, the manager of the Hotel Condado Beach in San Juan, and his assistant Paquito decide to promote their establishment by offering free honeymoons in Puerto Rico to newlywed couples.

The world's best fighters are invited to DOA, an invitational martial arts contest. There, four female rival fighters will have to work together to uncover the secret that the organizer of the tournament is trying to hide.

A group of college students decide to shoot a documentary on the psychological causes that lead to a form of demonic possession. However, the boys will remain trapped in their game of suggestion with tragically unexpected effects.
Father Colm Mcdwink must battle mysterious demons that endanger as young woman and the world when they take over the bodies of some innocent looking puppets.

Adam and Eden fell in love as teens despite the fact that they live on twinned worlds with gravities that pull in opposite directions. Ten years after a forced separation, Adam sets out on a dangerous quest to reconnect with his love.
Feature version of the award winning short about a young couple kidnapped, forced to procreate with their babies being sold on the black market.
A publicity stunt staged on a train known as the Broadway Limited creates problems because of an unknown baby that was part of the stunt.

Berna, who lost her parents in a traffic accident on a stormy night, is traumatized. Doctors tell Berna, who is struggling to cope with the pain of losing her family, that a change of air will be good.
An elite group of soldiers investigates the mysterious happenings on a remote island, only to discover vicious creatures who appear to be eerily too human.

When a Japanese pilot crash-lands on the tiny remote Hawaiian island of Ni'ihau, he is met with courtesy and traditional Hawaiian hospitality from the locals - until they discover he was part of the recent attack on Pearl Harbor.

A story of hope and despair as a group of immigrants are unknowingly recorded by one of the members within the group. Witness their journey with its twists and turns as they make their way North in pursuit of a better life.
Meandering drama of Brothers Burke and Sacks, who rob a bank, kill a cop and kidnap Thornton, a witness to their crime.

As told through the eyes of the new Attorney General for the Government, DR. Alfred Carroll, tells of a twisted tale of marijuana drug dealers leading innocent college students to insanity, destruction, torment and even death.
In researching her family tree Amy finds that an ancestor was cursed at the burning of a witch and now has to fight to save her daughter.
An idealistic director hired to make a demonic possession film pushes the lead actress too hard for realism.
Four horror stories focusing on a group of neglected children and their unfortunate guardians come to life in this terrifying anthology from Wild Dogs Productions.

A group of scientists and immune soldiers must take an unknown Commission from one city to another in a Post-apocalyptic world but on the way they must take care of beings that mutated due to contagion

Berk leaves Diony and their baby to hunt down his mother's murderer and is believed to be dead. Evan provides for them & marries Diony. Berk returns and challenges Evan to a fight but Diony will not be fought over "as if I'm not human".
Hope, a researcher who studies infectious diseases, the struggle for survival in a world where a deadly virus but decimated the population .
Nearly dying in an accident, a husband and father is resuscitated after being dead for minutes - only to discover that he's now being haunted by his own ghost which now threatens his families' lives.
When Norman's nightmares become reality, he must overcome his fears and confront the demonic forces that have possessed Hugo, his prize Doll.
In 1743, outlaw Leon Alastray is hunted by the Spanish army but is given sanctuary by a priest in a village terrorized by marauding Yaqui Indians.

A woman named Yeon-hee (Ha Ji-won) lives in Busan with her boyfriend Man-sik (Sol Kyung-gu) near Haeundae Beach. But, when they find out a tsunami will hit the city, They realize they only have 10 minutes to escape!

movie_name: RISE OF THE SUPER SOLDIER: THE NEW BLOOD
description: Adam Welch carries the Super Soldier third strand of DNA "The Triple Helix". As a plan to reverse engineer his DNA the Russians stage an ambush. Adam will have to thrusts forward knowing the uncertain awaits him at every corner.
When Ramu becomes a cop and is posted in an area ruled by a gangster, he has to undergo nightmarish trials and tribulations in order to serve justice.

While an Egyptologist searches for the secrets of a long-buried prophecy, he unleashes an ancient evil and must battle demonic spirits, a dark cult, and the gods themselves to save the world and the woman he loves.

A woman wins an all-expenses-paid trip to a company's gorgeous "institute" outside of Florence, and also the chance to meet the restaurant chain's wealthy and charismatic owner. She finds a different adventure than the one she imagined.
Super-thief The Owl kidnaps the Emperor's 36th wife, and three hapless heroes get tasked with ensuring her return.

Inspector Shiv resigns from police force when a bullet gets stuck in his head removing which could lead to his death but manages to teach the culprits a lesson by fighting from the other side of the law.
After outlandish encounter with an eerie figure, young woman sees her whole world shattered. She becomes desperate to find a reason for her misery.
A story told through the eyes of U.S. Marines, an evil warlord and the innocent girl who is unfortunately trapped in the middle.
A tough Russian policeman is forced to partner up with a cocky Chicago police detective when he is sent to Chicago to apprehend a Georgian drug lord who killed his partner and fled the country.
After years spent in war-torn Syria, He decides to return to Italy, to finally put behind his terrible experiences, and regain his life. But in order to do so, he will have to pay a very high price.
A beautiful hæmophage infected with a virus that gives her superhuman powers has to protect a boy in a futuristic world, who is thought to be carrying antigens that would destroy all hæmophages.
Maggie's life is in shambles; but upon hitting rock bottom, a manipulative and cunning former lover re-enters her life with the promise of salvation.
Confusion ensues when a man wins the lottery with a ticket he hadn't realized was stolen at the time he bought it.
A down-and-out man finds a new job in Tokyo's red-light district as a scout who recruits women to work in the adult-entertainment business.

When his aging mob boss is whacked, Charlie Swift, a loyal friend and hired gun, will stop at nothing to bring down the new crew coming up that took him out. Based on the Edgar Award nominated crime novel, GUN MONKEYS.

movie_name: The Despicable Fantasies of Quentin Sergenov
description: After being outed and blacklisted from the industry, a gay pro-wrestler is transformed into a dinosaur by a group of mad scientists and attempts to reintegrate into society with disastrous results.

movie_name: Love Freely But Pay for Sex
description: 89% of people in England have adopted a pay for sex lifestyle exchanging money for sex and the British Government now want a piece of the action.
London 1895: Cabinet minister, Sir Chiltern, and bachelor, Lord Goring, are victims of scheming women.

Ak Poshla Bristi Director- Jafor Al Mamun, Production- Shapla Media, Music- Ayush, Belal khan, Lyrics- SK Dip, Titon, Singer- Ashok sing, Rajosree, Belal khan, Kheya, Coriographer- Jakir Hossen, Fight Director- Cunnu

movie_name: Detective K: Secret of Virtuous Widow
description: Detective genius Detective K is enlisted by the king to investigate a string of murders that may be linked to a government conspiracy. But when K becomes a suspect himself, he'll have to catch the killers to prove his own innocence.
While navigating their careers in Los Angeles a writer and a chef fall in love only to feel they aren't enough for each other.
After ten years, Hella Mayer and her boyhood friend Andreas meet again in Berlin on the street. Both know each other from common dance lessons times.
Zora and Izzy move into an old home that is within their budget. Strange things quickly begin to happen soon-after.
After an experimental drug trial goes horribly wrong, the surviving test subjects must fight off sleep, and each other, to stay alive.
A young woman realizes her friends are being murdered by their own doubles. She and her boyfriend work to solve the mystery before becoming victims themselves.
In the story of a mildly schizophrenic man whose brother is kidnapped and returns 19 days later with supposedly no memory of what happened to him.

To get the money hidden by Gray before he was caught, the Rangers send Perkins to prison to become his friend. When the two get out, Perkins is unaware that Gray has printed the map to the loot on the bottom of his foot.

A man hires an actor to help him with an oral presentation. The two work on the delivery of dialogue , scene setting, and prop usage in an old theatre. As the night goes on, the actor is haunted by a sinister ghost.

A rebel without a cause at an elite uptight High School discovers some of his classmates have formed an even more elite clique hell-bent on ridding the school of what they deem to be its undesirables because of ethnicity, politics, etc.
A princess from a Nordic European country(Snellenburgh) is obligated to marry the boy her family chose. She escapes and discovers love in the arms of a beautiful swimming teacher(Bova).

When three young martial artists embark on a relentless treasure hunt in order to free their friend from the grasp of a ruthless gangster, they get entangled in a complex conspiracy staged to dethrone Berlin's underworld kingpin.

Marcos Vargas returns home to Ciudad Bolívar after finishing his studies in Caracas. There he decides to start a business transporting merchandise to the interior of the jungle. A local chieftain will not make things easy for him.

Three second-rate delinquints - a retired, crippled pickpocket, a man born and raised in a prision who's never seen a day of freedom, and a young loser - escape from the police van that is ...                See full synopsis »

When a whistle-blower has been found murdered, a state police detective named Karen investigates a suburban water supply pollution scandal that a chemical company is trying to cover up in New York state.
An adopted woman returns to her home country and the family home that she never knew and must face the mystery that lies there.
An American detective travels to Ukraine to investigate the disappearance of his former mentor, and with the help of his mentor's daughter, the pair uncover a sinister plot involving an ancient cult.
A young American composer separates from his wife, and moves to Rome. Soon, he falls for Mirella, a beautiful girl in that country. As his work and relationship progress, the dangers of war arise.

When a virus threatens to turn the now earth-dwelling friendly alien hybrids against humans, Captain Rose Corley must lead a team of elite mercenaries on a mission to the alien world in order to save what's left of humanity.
Three friends break into their neighbors' house to investigate their suspicious behavior. They unknowingly unleash a horror upon their town that none of them could have ever imagined or prepared for.
A drug peddling assignment causes havoc in the lives of three friends, and the people involved in it.
A series of unsolved crimes from the past prove to be the common thread in three stories that intertwine to reveal big problems in a small town.
Philadelphia Police Task Force members Andrew McJones and Jon Byers investigate the disappearance of one of their own, which may be linked to a mysterious artifact.
A young brother and sister must work together to outwit a barrage of peculiar zombies, rescue their mom and save the town.
A locomotive driver falls in love with a beautiful woman without knowing that she is the wife of an older railroad worker.

5 HK cops (4 horny males) on vacation in Pattaya, Thailand, are told to contact an informant there but he gets murdered. They return to Hong Kong to contact his girlfriend and protect her. 3 other colleagues are busy fighting criminals.
Despite his manly appearance and reputation, Yukimura Sanada is a coward. A bunch of ninja decide to help him to be a real hero.
A group of college kids discovers the remains of an evil warlord from an old cave and brings it to their dormitory, which ultimately awakens the warlord's ghost.
Trainees in the FBI's psychological profiling program must put their training into practice when they discover a killer in their midst.
Following a horrifying experience with the occult in Africa, a schoolteacher moves to a small English village, only to discover that black magic resides there as well.
On the most glamorous night in the adult entertainment industry, an unknown killer stalks young porn stars at a live party event.

Adult campground sounds like heaven But when one of the camp counselors mysteriously doesn't show up to pick up the previous kids and teenagers they are told to stay inside as adult night continues and also as the night gets worst .
The Countess Clara is in love with Andrea Valverde but agrees to marry the Count Guido when he learns that Andrew is his brother from his mother's side.

Two struggling pals dress as police officers for a costume party and become neighborhood sensations. But when these newly-minted "heroes" get tangled in a real life web of mobsters and dirty detectives, they must put their fake badges on the line.

A Girl is abandoned by her parents because they blame her for her brothers death, so her uncles take her in and teach her how to be an assassin. Fast forward thirteen years and she's a deadly assassin devoid of emotions.

Touching story about love of a young romantic man (Zhenia), who is a soldier of Guard Mortar Division (Division of "Katusha" Reactive Mortars) and a girl-telegraphist (Little Zhenia) at the last months of WW II.
Set in the chaotic years. A writer and a doctor fall in love. The writer is going to be arrested because of honesty and faith in truth.

When a headstrong teen and his ghost hunting friends investigate a condemned high school to find the truth about the massacre that closed the school, they find themselves in the fight of their lives against a supernatural evil.

University students, Ray, Anna, Tyler, Halle, and Eisuke are enjoying student life while chasing their dreams. However, they have a secret mission, to fight against invading Reptilians from outer space.

The line between good and evil becomes blurred as a death row inmate fights to maintain his sanity and escape the clutches of a deranged Warden and his sadistic guards. Based on the comic book mini-series from Alterna Comics.

movie_name: Cho Em Gan Anh Them Chut Nua
description: As a grieving medical student copes with reality, an energetic photographer tries to open his heart to love while keeping her own truth under wraps.
In the near future, special forces are fighting a virus unknown to science. Dark action based on the story of Ivan Okhlobystin

Every twenty years, The Witch returns to terrorize on the family responsible for the Salem witch trials. With only two family members left, a brother and sister reunite to stop the forces against their bloodline.
An elderly couple are forced to live hundreds of miles apart when they lose their house and none of their five children will take both parents in.
Genteel aristocrats and the terrible impasse erect in front of them their debts, forbidden loves and marriages interests, passions and conflicts.
A platonic love story between a young woman with a phobia about being touched, and the therapist who helps her to overcome her fears.
Jake has to go to brother's wedding in Hawaii. He hires a bride to pretend he's engaged as his brother is marrying his ex. Anna the rental bride falls for Jake.
The wild and sexy story of two passionate young people who take to the road for the incredible adventure of their lives.
Eva is a 2020 Malayalam-language thriller. A few problems a girl can have in a canteen overnight.An officer comes to investigate the problems that may arise later thus the case is being sought.

Assigned the easy task of assassinating a couple in a hotel room, instead, a hardened contract killer finds himself fighting for his life in a maze-like place crammed with demonic henchmen. Can he escape from the nightmarish Hotel Inferno?
A young undercover cop fights to control a constantly changing reality while trying to maintain her own grip on sanity when she joins the hunt for a brutal serial killer.
Framed by their ruthless arch-nemesis, a mismatched LAPD crime-fighting duo has to put its differences aside to even the score with the evil kingpin who put them behind bars once and for all.
A mythological story about a goddess who created the entire universe. The plot revolves around the consequences when humans build a temple for her first-born.

Paralyzed from the waist down after an accident, Cássio's relationship with Julia goes through difficulties. Feeling rejected, she starts a new romance. Based on the novel "Lady Chatterley's Lover" by D. H. Lawrence.

A former mobster finds himself on a violent mission, searching for his supposedly dead daughter and wife. His chase to find his loved ones leads him through a hellish underworld, caught in a state of dream to nightmare feverishness.
The lives of Calcutta's most powerful Gunday, Bikram and Bala, changes when Nandita enters it. Then a counter-force takes charge and a thriller unfolds.
A Japanese martial artist Tomioka sends out the challenge letter to the world class martial artists all over the world to challenge them to become the strongest martial artist in the world.
A boy and a girl, who have run away from their respective homes for different reasons, meet and eventually fall in love. On their way, they commit a number of crimes.
Sheriff Roy Rogers fights chemical induced frogs turning his townspeople into zombies down on the Louisiana bayou.
A beautiful young girl takes shelter in the house of a poor painter. She wants to get away from her past and the ghosts haunting her. She becomes the artist's model and lover.

A young man, a womanizer and gambler, undertakes the murder of a woman in order to pay his debts. She lives in the castle of Monemvasia and when they get to know each other, their life will change because they fall in love.
A deranged, wealthy woman offers $100,000 to three men if they can stay alive for 24 hours in Manhattan, and then hunts them down.
An orphaned young woman struggles to prevent her younger brother from unleashing an ancient evil after accidentally killing the only man who can stop it.

An attempt to summon a demon using the sacrifice of a prostitute misfires - the evil entity instead possesses the body of the intended victim! With the ability to leap between hosts, how can it be stopped before it tracks down its target?

Tom Brandon, a young doctor who, working with and for the police department, takes a job as the doctor for a gang of criminals. His fiancée, Mary Davis, who he can't tell the real reason for his actions, breaks their engagement.
A young couple living in a barren, post-apocalyptic Budapest in the year 2121, struggle for food and life.
A look at the top-secret, high-tech espionage war going on between cats and dogs, of which their human owners are blissfully unaware.
Using the stolen research of a rabbinical scholar, a heartbroken young bride resurrects her murdered fiancé - and discovers the perils of love beyond the grave.
The story of surgeon Cristóbal Payano, who tried to rob a bank office in Santo Domingo in March 1993, in a 12-hour hostage situation that ended in tragedy.
A 43-year-old woman living in a small town discovers that she is actually a man. Will she change her sex and suffer the reaction of a narrow-minded society?

In this hilarious romantic comedy, non-working actor Cam is claimed as a "dependent" by his breadwinning girlfriend Alice. As he stumbles from one humiliating job to the next, he tries to keep his dream alive as well as his relationship.
Revanth Deshpande is a rich kid but doesn't depend on his father's money. He is a rockstar who goes by the name Raymo. Soon, he meets Mohana and they fall in love. Will their love be successful?
When a teenage girl is possessed by a mysterious entity, her mother seeks the help of two priests to save her daughter.
Two neighboring Indian kingdoms are ruled by cousins - King Ranjit and King Sohat. Unbeknownst to Ranjit, Sohat is plotting to seize control of his kingdom.
Titanic forces, criminal and government, clash in an epic take-all battle for control of illicit trade in 1982 New York City.

movie_name: Nicolas Feliciano ... ang huk-figther ng tarlac
description: A TRUE STORY ON THE LIFE - AND TIME - OF TARLAC VICE GOVERNOR NICOLAS Y. FELICIANO WHO WAS ASSASINATED ON JULY 10. 1968. THIS FILM IS SO DEDICATED THAT HIS DEATH WOULD NOT HAVE BEEN IN VAIN.
Raul, a Puerto Rican born in New York, meets Maria, a young Puerto Rican woman visiting NY, one night. Struck by love at first sight, he travels to Puerto Rico in search of this beautiful girl.
Hana spends twenty years suppressing a maleficent curse that was placed upon her bloodline, only to have a family member knowingly release it forcing her to kill or to be killed.
A facially-deformed and mentally-unhinged man wreaks his revenge, with a series of brutal murders, on those who deformed him.

Rafael is 30 years old, divorced and father of three children. His life is even more complicated when his ex-wife announces that he will travel out of the country for 6 months and that he will have to take care of his 3 little kids.
Beautiful girls are dying at the hands of a deranged masked killer. Every kill is more brutal than the last. Worst of all, it's happening live on camera.
An idealistic, modern-day cowboy struggles to keep his Wild West show afloat in the face of hard luck and waning interest.
A recently widowed city-slicker must travel to the Amazon and face a terrifying legend in order to save his daughter's life.
A French sailor, returning to Hamburg where he had been imprisoned during WWII, looks for a German woman he had loved in those days, and finds her in a night club.
Ezgi, who constantly wakes up with nightmares and tries to illuminate her father's death, tells about the events that developed after being haunted by demons

Emanuelle is trapped in the middle of a brutal war, as both sides set out to claim her. Unfortunately for them, Emanuelle is not only beautiful but quite intelligent and uses her charms to seduce the soldiers to gain an advantage.
Two Art Teachers are obsessed with eternal youth. Somehow they manage to get Elizabeth Bathory's diary. Soon, they start to practice bloody rituals that end up unleashing hell on earth.
The love of a young couple finds resistance in the girl's father, who, betrayed by his wife, tries to protect his daughter from a possible erotic disappointment.
Susan Roces and Sharon Cuneta play sisters who sell fish at a public market and play instruments in their town's brass band that has been consigned to playing funeral music.
A wrestler and a detective team up to stop a mad scientist who is kidnapping athletes and replacing their brains with those of animals to make them stronger and live longer.

movie_name: The Documents of Dr. Kasper Kross
description: A professor and his bodyguard travel to a secluded mountain village, searching for a missing man linked to a bizarre medical experiment.

A stern old woman, who owns the largest factory in a small town and has ruled both the factory and the town with an iron hand, finds herself battling with the wife of her nephew, the man she has picked to succeed her.
Japanese horror starring Stephen Fung as a man who dies in a skiing accident, only for his best friend to marry his wife and inherit his fortune. Supernatural hijinks ensue.

A college student, Ajay Sahane, is passionate about boxing and wants to make a career out of it. Facing one too many hurdles, Ajay goes against all odds to make his dream his reality but will he succeed?

The Civil War, as Sherman's Army burns its way across Georgia, a village of women, left alone after the war has taken their sons and husbands, forms a militia with pitchforks and rusty flintlocks to defend their town.
A mother from a small village searches for her son in Hyderabad; unaware that he has changed his name and is now both a target and a threat for all the gangsters of the city.
A naive police officer gets caught in the middle of a dangerous international drug operation in the Costa del Sol.
Surrender's mother tells him that she has found him a bride. Before the couple can meet, his mother dies in an accident. He sets out to find the woman his mother wanted him to marry.

Husband and wife share the spotlight as two of Mexico's most famous ranchera singers, but when they decide to pursue solo careers, a Spanish theatrical empresario and an Italian female chocolatier will threaten their marriage.
A troubled lawyer takes on a high profile murder case that forces him to come to terms with his own past.
A solar storm hits the Earth sending a city into chaos and three of its inhabitants on a journey of discovery, pursuit and death.
YAARO is an edge of the seat Horror Psycho Thriller that will have a pattern set against the backdrops of a murder mystery.

Monster Killers packs the goods...and the gore. This monster-themed anthology features some of the best up-and-coming short horror filmmakers from around the world. When monsters rise, it's nighty-night for the rest of us.

movie_name: Captain Underpants: The First Epic Movie
description: Two overly imaginative pranksters named George and Harold hypnotize their principal into thinking he's a ridiculously enthusiastic, incredibly dimwitted superhero named Captain Underpants.
An old-fashioned romantic tells his personal love story to a modern man who has just broken up with his girlfriend. Has love really ever changed?

movie_name: The House That Never Dies II
description: A hundred years after a mutiny by warlords in Beijing, a building restorer encounters supernatural phenomena in a mansion on 81 Chaoyangmennei Street.

movie_name: Berserk: The Golden Age Arc II - The Battle for Doldrey
description: For three years, Guts believed his mission was to pursue Griffith's dream together with him. But in order to become Griffith's equal and truly be called his friend, Guts realizes he will have to leave the Band of the Hawk.
Three college friends decide to make the film on the remote village only to hunt them by the spirit.
A jobless boy Bakhtu (Momar Rana) moves to village to live away from tangled life of the city. Their he finds peace of life and love of life in very absorbing situation.

Lancelot is sent through time by Merlin to protect young Arthur before he becomes King of Camelot, but by accident, they both end up in present day world along with the villains. Only technology can help them now.

movie_name: Taco Belly and the Attack of the Mockbusters
description: After accidentally unleashing the ungodly awfulness that is mockbuster movies onto the world, Taco Belly and Burrito Head must save the day before this movie gets any worse.

Feature length adaptation of the cult British zom-com web series following the adventures of three inept survivors of a zombie apocalypse through a video blog they maintain to ease the boredom of day to day survival.
A fraternity president becomes obsessed with a young coed but his hopeful courtship decays into sinister pursuit as unnatural secrets surface about his brotherhood.

movie_name: Just Another Girl on the I.R.T.
description: With hopes of becoming a doctor and not a product of her environment, a Brooklyn teenager is faced with numerous challenges that threaten her dreams.

Bangladesh's first wildlife action thriller film based on RAB's adventures in the Sundarbans. Starring Siam, Riaz, Nusraat Faria, Shatabdi Wadud, Roshan, Taskeen, Rawnok Hasan, Manoj Paramanik, Directed by Dipankar Dipon.
Mary Donnell, a young legal secretary with a past, elopes with a client's son, but his father has the marriage annulled without knowing she's pregnant.
Four high school girls in Echo Park deal with everyday adolescent issues: life, family, school, love, and felony crimes.
A greedy businessman-turned-renegade foments an Indian uprising against the coming telegraph to perpetuate his economic stranglehold on the territory.
An attempt to steal Uranium from a university's research reactor is thwarted by a group of students.

A group of hard-up bounty hunters must survive the night in a desert motel against a horde of savage cartel killers as they realize their fugitive, a mysterious Chinese woman, is much more than she lets on.
This film portrays the story of two college friends - Mungerilal and Pintu. Their college life throws various challenges and problems at them forcing them to walk on a very risky journey.

movie_name: A Nightmare on My Street Part II: Still Dreamin'
description: Worlds collide as Jack's surviving victims must band together to try and stop his many faces that have run wild between both the real world and the dream realm.
